Settled in midfield, soon came to challenge after straightening, ran on well to take charge over 100 M out, won going away.

Began moderately, ridden along in midfield far side before improving to 1L 3rd coming out of back straight when 3-wide without cover, similar turning for home, no answer to winner's late burst of speed inside final 200 M, plugged on.
Broke well from a low draw, held slender advantage until headed by eventual winner over 100 M out when found no extra.
Never far off settling in 4th to straight, could only produce moderate headway without quickening.
Towards rear, picked up nicely under pressure inside final 200 M, did best work late.
Close up on rails early, shuffled back to forward of midfield around the bend, saved ground turning in, kept on well to the line.
Began moderately, remained in last few to straight, fought on under pressure down centre of track to be nearest at finish.
Raced wide without cover in forward of midfield, remained similar turning in, unable to sustain effort inside 250 M.
Mainly in rear of midfield before home turn, baulked behind runners early in straight, kept on same pace to finish.
Never far off and mainly in 5th up to straight, baulked after straightening, faded under pressure inside 200 M.
Sluggish at start travelling in last few, given reminders approaching home turn, made no impression in straight.
Soon dropped to last few, never a danger.
Disputed lead outside leader before stopping abruptly about 300 M out. (Bled.)
Travelled at the back, never seen with a chance.
Settled behind midfield, 3 wide without cover on the circle. Commenced to improve after the 500m and lengthened nicely to land an easy win.
Raced midfield the fence. weaved a run in the final stretch, shifting out about 4 horses, finished off well.
Dictated the pace on the fence with steady sections. Kept on gamely to finish in the frame.
Settled midfield the fence, peeled out early in the home straight into clear running and closed off soundly.
Raced 1 out 1 back. Straightened up with every chance and maintained an even gallop to the finishing post.
Raced handy early before proving difficult to settle when awkwardly placed near the 900m, settling close to midfield, 1 off with cover. Finished off satisfactorily.
Slow to begin then settled with the backmakers, 3 wide with cover. Failed to mount any serious threat in the straight, weakening in the run to the line.
Worked forward to cross and travel outside the leader. Was challenged after the 400m and struggled thereafter.
Settled in last position 2-3 wide with cover. Came at least 5 deep rounding the home turn, however did not show any turn of foot.
Enjoyed the run of the race behind the leader along the paint. Had every chance, fading noticeably over the final 200 M.
Raced 3 back 1 off with cover. Paddled over the final stages.
Began well then was taken back to a position with cover, behind midfield 4 deep. Had cover on the circle but only plodded to the finish.
Settled with the rear of the field along the rails. Failed to close off.
Slow to begin then used plenty of petrol to circle the field coursing at least 4 wide without cover behind the speed. Running on empty over the latter stages. (See Racing Incidents.)
Soon rolled into a prominent spot and held the same position into final stretch. Rallied along the fence and hit front 150M. Took charge closing stages.
Good jump. Disputed lead on fence passing 1400M. Clear by 1L home turn. Headed 150M but hung on gamely to figure in quinella.
Travelled nicely ahead of midfield on fence through to the home turn. Left the rail to make his run on straightening. Finished off well but the front pair had enough to hold on.
Pressed early but could only stay 3-wide towards rear. Came widest and was 6Ls down making home turn. Covered good ground thereafter.

Began nicely but trapped wide at midfield. Eased to rear in a 3-wide position passing 1300M. Swung wide and was 7Ls off turning in. Found traffic in the straight and had to go through gaps 200M out. Found the line well once into clear.
Broke well from high draw. Elected to sit 3-wide behind midfield passing 1400M. 5Ls behind the speed turning into home. Closed off fairly well but no threat to the principals.
Sat within 5Ls of the pace on fence through to the home straight. Barely saw daylight until 100M and ran on steadily thereafter.
Soon found the fence towards rear from outside barrier. 5Ls off into home straight. Held ground on rail.
Away in line but soon dropped towards rear in a 3-wide position. Shifted 2-wide passing 1200M and was 6Ls away at bend. Held up most of the home straight and was not fully tested.
Pressed early. Travelled wide and without cover ahead of midfield until weakened 350M.
Disputed lead early. Sat 2-wide behind the leader rounding the turn. Failed to turn up a notch passing 400M. Faded final 100 M.
2-wide better than midfield until home turn. Attacked the lead leaving the bend. Every chance but failed to sustain final 250 M.
3-wide at midfield through to the home straight. Plugged on until 200M from home.
Hard ridden early but failed to muster. Raced 2-wide at midfield from 1400M. Not much to offer in the home straight.
Broke only fairly, driven to get across just behind the leader, travelled nicely in middle stages, clicked into gear and hit the lead at the top of home straight, kept on strongly to win.
Jumped fastest, found the fence then sat handily, travelled keenly when restrained in middle stages, responded well under pressure final 250 M, finished off soundly for 2nd.

Out in line, settled within striking distance from the leader, caught 3-wide with no cover however, patiently ridden at the top of home straight, placed under pressure final 300 M, ran on steadily and just did enough for 3rd.
Held up in a midfield position, caught 4-wide with no cover, travelled keenly in early and middle stages, responded well when asked for efforts final 350 M, ran on steadily, just late for a place.

Broke well, prominently placed in a one-off position just off the pace, showed good turn of foot when asked for efforts passing 400 M, looked at least a place but could not find extra to challenge the principal final 150 M.

Lacked early speed despite being niggled along, ended up in a 2-wide position two from the rear, placed under pressure 400 M out, did make up some ground in the straight but never threatened the principals.
Jumped fairly, pressed on to lead and found the fence passing 1000 M pole, 1L clear turning for home, overhauled by the winner near 300 M, kept on until got tired last 100 M.
Slow to begin, niggled along to catch up 5Ls behind the speed, caught 4-wide with cover, travelled keenly midway, gave very limited response when asked for efforts final 300 M.
Lacked early speed and travelled 7Ls off the pace at the rear, placed under pressure at the top of home straight, only managed to pass the tired rivals.
Out in line, settled 2-wide in midfield, travelled well throughout, lacked a kick when asked at the top of straight, dropped out passing 300 M.
Urged along to hold a fence position in midfield, failed to quicken final 350 M, soon dropped out.
Taken to rear from the wide alley, only passed the tired runners in home straight, made no impression.
Out in line, settled one-off in midfield, travelled keenly in early stage and checked near 900 M, failed to make up any ground in home straight.
Always rearward, urged along early to hold the position, weakened near 300 M, never competitive.
Jumped fastest, prominently placed on/close to the rails 2Ls behind the pace, shifted wider for home, clicked into gear passing 400 M , hit the lead 250 M out, kept on well to score.

Taken back in search of cover, ended up sitting 2-wide just behind midfield, travelled nicely throughout, launched a challenge down centre of home straight when clear 250 M, finished off soundly for 2nd.
Lacked early speed, settled two from the rear 6Ls behind the leader, responded well when asked for efforts final 350 M, ran on strongly, narrowly beaten by the top two.

Broke well from the widest alley, niggled along to track leader in a 3-wide position with no cover, fought bravely in home straight, held the 2nd position until headed in final 50 M, just lost a place.
Drawn wide, urged along to get across, ended up in the box-seat just behind the leader, had his chance in home straight, made up ground gradually final 350 M but failed to threaten the principals.
Broke well from gate 13, driven to take the one out one back spot, lacked turn of foot under pressure at the top of straight, overhauled by the winner 250 M, remained one-paced to the line.
Broke well from the wide stall, held up to get across and soon found a 2-wide spot in the mid-division, carried wider rounding bend, gave limited response when asked for efforts final 450 M.
Out in line, restrained to a 3-wide position in midfield, overraced in the middle stages, made up little ground down centre of home straight under pressure final 300 M without offering threat.

Bit slow to begin, pressed on to catch up 4Ls off pace in midfield, travelled with no problem on the rails, struggled rounding the bend, placed under maximum pressure in home straight, made no impression.
Out in line, lacked early speed and drifted back to rear, covered little ground in the home straight before the run ended 150 M out.
Broke well, niggled along to lead 1L on the rails, travelled until got tired 300 M, gave ground quickly.
No early speed despite being ridden hard along, sat three from the rear on rails at the first turn, failed to make up any ground in the homes straight.
Very slow away, always at the rear, proven beaten at the top of home straight.
Eased to sit in midfield, 2.5Ls off the leader, trapped 3 wide throughout, demonstrated strong finishing efforts 300M and scored.
Eased to sit behind midfield, 4.5Ls off the leader 2 wide, not suited by the slow pace, moved forward 600M along the fence, dashed well 400M and finsihed 2nd.
Eased back, 6Ls off the leader 2 wide, dashed strongly 300M desipte harmed by the slow pace and ran a remarkable 3rd.
Eased to sit in midfield along the fence, 2.5Ls off the leader, not suited by the slow pace, held up 400M, dashed strongly when clear.
Eased to sit in midfield early, trapped 3-4 wide, then allowed to stride forward 1400M and sat outside the leader, suited by the slow tempo, held ground in straight.
Settled in box seat, lacked room 400M, no turn of foot when clear.
Eased to sit in midfield early, raced keenly, moved forward 1200M and sat 1.5Ls off the slow pace 2-3 wide, ran on until 200M flattened.
Eased to rear, 9Ls off the leader 2-4 wide, dashed well final 250 M despite not suited by the slow pace.
Very slow away, at rear, 8Ls off the leader, trapped 3 wide and lost ground, harmed by the slow pace, dashed fairly.
At back, 7Ls off the leader 2 wide, not suited by the slow tempo, lacked room 400M, no dash when clear.
Pushed forward to cross in front, sat 1.5Ls off the slow pace 2 wide, bumped 400M, weakened afterwards.
Eased back, harmed by the slow pace, trapped 3-4 wide throughout and lost too much ground, never better than midfield.
Hard ridden to take the rail and led by 0.5L at slow sectionals, soon dropped off 400M.
Pushed to sit in front of midfield, 3Ls off the slow pace 2 wide, faded quickly 500M.
Out in line, sat handily right behind the leader, kicked impressively under pressure final 400 M, drew clear easily.
Broke well from the far side, niggled along to lead 1L and found the stand rails at 600 M, responded well when asked for efforts passing 450 M, headed in 150 M out but still kept on.
Jumped fast, prominently placed within striking distance from the leader, lost cover near 600 M, responded fairly well when asked 400 M out, no extra final 150 M.
Awkwardly started, urged along to catch up 2-3Ls off the speed, could not match the strides of the top three final 350 M, kept on for 4th.
Broke well, soon found the stand rails and travelled 1L off the pace, bit outpaced when tempo quickened at 450 M, never threatened the principals.
Lacked early speed, always struggled at the rear, made some late progress under maximum pressure final 200 M.
Drawn on the far side, settled in midfield without cover, gave very limited response when asked for efforts final 450 M, proven beaten inside 200 M.
Slow to begin, never better than midfield, failed to make up any ground in concluding stages.
Awkwardly started, sat 2Ls off the lead on the stand rails, outpaced when tempo quickened at 450 M, soon dropped out.
Settled well behind midfield and came with a well-timed challenge inside 400M, kept on resolutely after hitting the front 200M out and fended off challenges on the outside in late stages.

Towards the rear and was way off the pace in early stages, moved closer on final turn, held up briefly early in straight but picked up strongly when clear and made significant headway inside 150m. Just held.

Dropped to last and trailed over 10Ls from leader in middle stages, taken out to challenge 500M, took time to muster in straight but ran on strongly final 200M to get within half length of the winner.
Along the fence in midfield, 4Ls down coming off the bend, picked up really well once switched and ran a respectable race against higher rated opponents under equal weight.
Travelled 2-wide in mid-division, way off the pace in early stages but moved closer on the turn, produced with every chance final 400M, stayed on well enough for a close 5th.
Tracked leaders in 3rd and well positioned to strike coming off the bend, came with a promising looking run inside 350M, briefly led near 200M but was swamped close home.
Fractious in stalls and began awkwardly, held inside running behind midfield, made a mild bid after turning in, stayed on but not reached leaders.
Began awkwardly and couldn't cross to the lead until passing 850M, not able to shake off his pursuers turning into straight, headed near 200M and weakened gradually towards the line.
Quickly crossed to the rail from draw 11, cut out the early running to 800M then sat behind leader, briefly threatened early in straight but run ended passing 200M.

Towards the rear, patiently ridden and over 10Ls off the pace in middle stages, switched out to make his challenge but found disappointingly little in the drive home, eased final 150M. (Unacceptable performance.)
Settled in 4th 4Ls behind leader but failed to pick up under pressure in straight and was readily left behind entering 200 M.
Restrained to a 2-wide position in midfield, driven but no progress inside 400M, weakened over final 200M.
Broke well, held up 3Ls off the pace, 3-wide with no cover, travelled keenly in early and middle stages, dashed well when asked for efforts final 350 M, hit the lead 150 M out, kept on to score.

Out in line, taken to midfield and travelled 5Ls behind the leader, 3-deep with cover, travelled comfortably throughout, ran on strongly when placed under pressure final 350 M, finished off soundly for 2nd.
Given a waiting ride as usual and travelled 5-6Ls off the pace just behind the mid-division, held up for room early in straight, dashed well when clear final 250 M, took 3rd in the final stride.
Taken rearward from the wide alley, travelled keenly when restrained in early stages, blocked early in straight, kicked strongly when clear final 300 M, just missed out a place.

Jumped only fairly, niggled along to sit prominently just behind the pace, travelled well throughout and had every chance in home straight, lacked a decisive kick in concluding stages, just missed out a place.
Shared the lead on rails easily, 1L clear passing 400 M pole, kept on well under pressure until overhauled by the winner at 150 M, soon flattened.
Travelled cosily 3-4Ls off the pace, held up for room early in straight, only one-paced when asked for efforts final 250 M.
Bit slow to begin, settled on rails 6Ls off the speed, made up little ground along the inner final 300 M, but never really threatened the principals.
Slow to begin, urged to catch up 6Ls off the pace, travelled keenly when restrained in middle stages, only passed the tired rivals in the home straight.
Fair jump, niggled along to sit 2Ls off the pace on rails, gave very limited when asked in home straight, outpaced 2.
Taken to the rear from gate 14, made up little ground along the inner early in straight, blocked at 100 M, not fully tested.
Lacked early speed, sat rearward 8Ls off the pace, made no impression in home straight.
Out in line, travelled comfortably on rails in the mid-division, only held ground early in straight, got tired passing 250 M.
Sat 2Ls off the pace early, allowed to run up to share the lead when tempo slackened near 1200 M, weakened sharply near the 400 M pole, gave ground and finished tailed out.
Bounced to lead, set a decent tempo with attention from outside horses throughout, still shaded to turn, gained advantage straightening and held off rivals to score.
Away well enough, held a prominent spot on leaders back throughout, improved to challenge on turning in, kept to task well in straight running leader to 1/2L.
Restrained from a wide gate, next to last in running line best part of 10Ls down, still well back turning, came to outside and made remarkable ground to take 3rd.
Even getaway, settled 3 wide in midfield 3 to 4Ls back had a good trail to turn, clear from 300 M and closed nicely just losing 3rd place late.
Slow into stride, positioned behind midfield 6Ls back in 2 wide line, fair trip to bend, suited by speed on, closed soundly down middle to be nearest on line.
No speed and soon near rear, 7 to 8Ls or so back in running line, aided by strong tempo, improved gradually turning, covered good ground final 300 M to be closest at finish.
Began with them, ended up stranded 4 wide without cover in midfield, did it tough with pace on, 3Ls down turning, stuck on OK in straight given hard run.
Showed usual pace to duel for front, 3 wide without cover challenging throughout, used too much to bend, run ended inside 300 M.
Fair break, midfield 5Ls or so away on rails, had an easy time on bend, couldn't lift a notch in straight and battled final 200 M.
Angled into 1 out 1 back spot on back of speed, used a little with solid pace on 2Ls down on turning, lacked a pick up in straight and just battled to line.
Didn't muster usual speed 5Ls away in running line in middle stages, in traffic turning, didn't let down when clear.
Fast away, challenged for front early, sat outside leader and worked throughout shading inside horse to bend, soon struggling turning and folded after a hard run.
Even break, pressed on and raced 3 wide 2Ls behind speed with cover, did work to turn, dropped out at 300 M.
Tardy and lost considerable ground at start, settled near last 10Ls back, always a long way back, no impression in straight.

Began fairly, soon ridden to join speed, hit front at the Rock holding 1L advantage into straight, hung on well to win unchallenged.
Settled in prominent 3rd, 1L back on rails turning in, failed to quicken to threaten.
Broke well from the widest draw, raced wide just better than midfield down far side, similar turning in, kept on steadily without quickening.
Began with others, gradually settled in midfield, hampered and lost position around home bend, made up some late ground closing stages.
Settled in forward of midfield, saved ground turning in, kept on well in the run home.
Quickly driven forward to lead, headed at the Rock dropping to 3rd into straight, faded gradually.
Broke well from a poor draw, gradually settled in 4th about 3Ls off the speed, similar turning in, faded steadily.
Always struggling in last few, made no impression in the run home. (Distressed.)
Towards rear to straight and made no show.
Slowly away and very sluggish at start, trailed the field into straight, only ran past well-beaten runners.
Raced wide in rear of midfield, raced awkwardly and lost position at Rock, dropped further out tamely in straight.
Raced wide behind midfield, hampered and lost a few lengths at Rock, never recovered.
Sent forward to cross and lead early. Travelled comfortably along the rail, got a breather after the 1000 M then quickened passing the 600 M to create an unassailable lead. Won in good style.
Settled behind midfield 1 off with cover. Inched forward mid race and swung into the home turn full of running and finished off nicely under hard riding.
Raced in 3rd position 1 off. Enjoyed a good run in the race and battled on gamely over the latter stages.
Taken back from an outside gate to settle with the backmakers on the fence. Peeled out early in the straight and closed off soundly.
From a wide alley was taken across behind runners to settle towards the rear along the fence. Finished off strongly.
Parked behind the front runners along the paint. Made fair ground in the straight.
Travelled slightly worse than midfield, 1 off with cover. Whacked away at the same pace in the run home.
Settled around midfield on the rails. Kept to the inside in the final stretch but stayed on at the same speed.
Settled in second position along the fence. Didn't quicken when the tempo increased after the 600 M and struggled over the concluding stages.
After being caught wide in the early stages was eased back to the rear of the field. Failed to lengthen in the home straight.
Caught 3-wide early without cover then managed to get a trail after the 1000 M. Weakened noticeably in the run to the line finishing well back. (To trial.)
Settled 1 off with cover behind the speed, then after the 1000 M, raced 3-wide without cover. Tailed out in the straight. (To trial.)

Settled 2-wide towards rear through to the home turn. 5Ls down leaving the bend. Made his run through runners early in the straight. Got clear run passing 200 M and kept on strongly to cut down rivals close home.
Pressed early from high draw. Slotted into one-out-one-back passing 900 M and was urged along to hold the position to home turn. Fought on in the straight. Just denied by the winner closing stages.
Soon rolled to the prominent spot. Took a split between runners top of home straight. Every chance final furlong. Caught by the front pair few strides before the line.
2-wide at midfield early and middle stages. Peeled out and was 3Ls away on straightening. Battled with the front trio but couldn't charge them down.
Always on fence at midfield. Plugged on in the straight but no real threat to the placegetters.
2-wide behind midfield through to the home turn. 4Ls off turning in. Made up some ground without troubling the principals.
Raced within 6Ls of the pace before the bend. Took inside run and was 4Ls off turning into home. Picked up moderately before steadied 200 M. Ran on steadily once resumed.
Slow to begin and was hard ridden early to catch up. Travelled wide and without cover at midfield thereafter. Couldn't sustain in the straight.
Eased to rear on fence from wide barrier. Moved away from the rail on straightening and made up minor ground thereafter.
Sat outside the leader until early home straight. Weakened 200 M.
3-wide towards rear throughout. No impression.
Led on fence until peaked 300 M.
Out in line, urged to find a one-off position 3Ls behind the leader, travelled nicely throughout, niggled along rounding bend, kicked impressively final 300 M, drew clear easily 100 M.
Held up in a fence position 5-6Ls off the pace, patiently ridden until the home straight, responded well when asked for efforts final 250 M, ran on soundly for 2nd.
Travelled keenly in early stages when restrained 2Ls off the speed, allowed to stride forward passing 1000 M, tracked leader until headed in by the winner 100 M, fought hard for 3rd.
Broke fairly, pushed forward to lead 1L on rails, joined from 400 M, kept on well under pressure in home straight, overhauled by winner 100 M out, unlucky to lose a place in the final stride.
Slow to begin, restrained 4Ls off the pace on rails, checked 1100 M and 700 M, made ground steadily under pressure final 250 M without offering threat to the principals.
Jumped fast, ideally placed in the box-seat just behind the leader, niggled along rounding final bend, only one-paced when asked in home straight, outpaced final 200 M.
Jumped fast, urged along to occupy a 2-wide position just behind the mid-division, improved little along 3-deep at the final turn, gave very limited response when asked final 300 M.
Lacked early speed, always rearward, swung widest for home, only passed a few beaten runners.
Broke well from gate 1, sat prominently within striking distance from the leader, struggled rounding bend, could not find extra final 200 M, soon dropped out.
Jumped awkwardly from the widest, failed to muster, caught wide with no cover in early stages, crept closer in middle stages and travelled 2Ls off the speed, hung in and weakened 250 M out.
Taken to rear from gate 11, travelled 8Ls away on the rails, failed to make up any ground in home straight.
Held up in a rearward position 3-wide with cover, made no progress in home straight.
Jumped fast, pushed hard to take the lead and find the rails passing 900 M, suited by the soft tempo, responded strongly when asked for efforts in home straight, never threatened.
Pushed hard to hold a fence position in midfield, urged along turning for home, ran on strongly under pressure final 250 M but found it too late to challenge the winner.
Broke well from gate 1, niggled along to take the box-seat just behind the leader, crowded for room early in straight, fought hard for 3rd under maximum pressure.
Driven to sit cozily in the one out one back spot, had his chance in home straight, hung in and bumped near 200 M, just lost a place in last few strides.
Jumped well, prominently sat 2-3Ls off the speed, travelled well throughout, had every chance in home straight, only one-paced when asked for efforts final 250 M.
Awkwardly start, sat comfortably in the mid-division, 2-wide with cover, shifted wider for home, responded only fairly when asked, made some late progress final 150 M.
Given a waiting ride as usual and travelled 6Ls behind the pace, crept closer along 3-wide from 600 M, made little ground in home straight but never really troubled the principals.
Lacked early speed, travelled 6Ls behind the leader, struggled rounding bend, made no impression in home straight.
Started very awkwardly, ended up in fence spot 5L off the pace, checked at 700 M, made no progress in home straight.
Broke only fairly from the outside barrier, settled last on the rails, saved some ground rounding bend, lacked a kick in home straight.
Out in line, sat 3-wide with no cover in midfield, gave no response when asked inside 300 M, well beaten.
Slow to begin, caught wide and struggled at the rear throughout, never competitive.
Settled nicely in box seat, took all advantages of the situation including the soft sectionals, closed the race off strongly 300 M to win by a nose.
Eased at start to cross behind the field, 6Ls off the leaders 2-wide, not suited by the slow tempo, dashed strongly 300 M, just beaten by a nose in 2nd.
Eased back, 5-1/2Ls off the leaders, harmed by the slow pace, trapped 3 to 4-wide throughout and lost ground, dashed strongly 200 M to grab 3rd.
Eased to sit midfield, 5Ls off the leaders 2-wide, harmed by the slow pace, held up 500 M and was carried out to 3-wide at home bend, dashed well 250 M despite all negative racing situations.

Eased to near last for cover, raced keenly and detached in early middle stages, 9-1/2Ls off the leaders 2-wide, demonstrated remarkable finishing efforts 200 M despite harmed by the slow pace, promising.
Pushed to hold the rail in midfield, 4Ls off the leaders, not suited by the slow sectionals, lacked turn of foot and just held ground in straight.
Slow away, pushed to sit in front of midfield, 3Ls off the leaders 2 to 3-wide, not suited by the slow tempo, under pressure 600 M, ran on fairly in final stages.
Hard ridden to take the rail and led by 1/2L at advantageous slow sectionals, hung on until 150 M overhauled and flattened.
Jumped well but immediately taken back to rear, 7-1/2Ls off the leaders 2-wide, harmed by the slow pace, no dash.
Bumped start, at rear, 7-1/2Ls off the leaders on the fence, harmed by the slow pace, no turn of foot in straight.
Hard ridden to take the rail in front and then sat just off the leader, enjoyed the slow early sectionals, soon weakened 250 M.
Hard ridden forward, 1-1/2Ls off the leaders 2-wide, benefited by the slow tempo, but soon weakened 300 M.
Broke well, bit keen in early stages when restrained just behind the leader, kicked strongly when clear 300 M out, kept on well under pressure, just did enough to hold off challengers.
Taken back from the widest alley, travelled 8Ls off the pace at the rear, swung widest for home, launched a strong challenge down centre of home straight final 300 M, just late.
Jumped well, soon found a one-off position behind mid-division, niggled along rounding bend, finished off soundly under pressure final 250 M, narrowly beaten by the top two.
Broke well from the wide gate, eased rearward to save ground, 7Ls off pace 2-wide with cover, held up early in straight, ran on strongly when clear final 150 M, just missed out a place.
Broke well, urged to hold a fence position 3Ls off the speed, blocked early in home straight, finished off well when clear 200 M but insufficient to get place.
Out in line, settled 2-wide in midfield, niggled along rounding bend, responded well when asked for efforts in straight, looked possible for a place but lacked a decisive kick in concluding stages.

Lacked early speed, ended up in a rearward position 6-7Ls behind the leader, patiently ridden until home straight, made up some ground under pressure final 250 M, but offered only very little threat to the principals.
Out in line, settled 5Ls behind the pace on rails, badly held up early in home straight, made some late progress final 150 M, not fully tested.
Pressed on to track leader in the one in one out spot, tried to contest the lead early in straight but failed to keep on final 200 M, soon weakened.
Driven to lead 1L on rails, quickened when challenged near 700 M, held ground until overhauled near 250 M, soon faded.
Mustered bit slowly under hard riding in early stages, ended up sitting 2-wide 2Ls off the pace, had every chance in home straight but failed to keep up final 150 M, soon dropped out.
Awkwardly started, urged to hold a midfield position, strode forward along 3-deep from 1000 M out, tracked leader until the end of home turn, weakened sharply final 250 M, finished tailed out.

Soon moved across from draw 12 and settled towards the rear 7Ls back, taken out to make his move passing 400 M, responded positively and hit the front 150 M out, cleared away and won with plenty in hand.

Settled 4 to 5Ls back in mid-division and saved ground on the inside, picked up well on straightening and burst through a gap to challenge, couldn't threaten the winner but continued on well to go 2nd close home.

Restrained to a 2-wide spot behind midfield, taken wide to make his move passing 500 M, came with a promising looking run inside 250 M, kept on well to the line but had no answer to the winner's turn of foot.
Slotted into a 2-wide position and settled 6th in midfield, ran on in straight but lacked pace to seriously challenge.
With leaders early then settled in 4th in chasing group just off the pace, briefly threatened inside 250 M but couldn't sustain his run in late stages.
Switched off after the start and raced in last over 9Ls behind leader, had plenty to do final 350 M, stayed on but was never seriously involved.

Dropped back after the start, raced in 2nd last over 8Ls from the lead and not used till 300 M, ran on from off the pace but not reached leaders. (Jockey reminded to avail himself of advantageous positions wherever possible.)
Cut out the early running till 1000 M then sat in 3rd tracking leaders, had his chance but could only keep on at the same pace.
Pushed along after the start, took over passing 1000 M and went a slow gallop in middle stages, couldn't shrug off his pursuers turning into straight, headed 200 M and weakened.
Obtained a rail spot behind midfield after an awkward start, 5Ls down inside 400 M but lacked a response when asked. Never any impression.
Broke well form draw 1 and tracked leaders along the fence, keen in middle stages and couldn't pick up turning into straight. Never threatened.
Went forward and raced outside the lead, under serious pressure over the home turn and weakened noticeably final 250 M.

Gradually settled in forward of midfield, closer up onto course proper, hit front over 200 M out, won easily.
Never far off on rails, fought on steadily to reach 2nd late.
Shared the pace most of way, unable to sustain effort inside final 200 M. (Mucus.)
Amongst leaders, failed to respond to winner's late burst of speed inside final 200 M, kept on same pace but lost 2nd late.
Not far off, gradually shifted across near grandstand side of the track, faded under pressure inside final 200 M.
Badly bumped and unbalanced jumping out, remained behind midfield most of way, kept on at the same pace without quickening.
Showed early speed, soon ceded lead approaching course proper, dropped out tamely.
Not far off early stages, gradually shuffled back to midfield approaching course proper, found nothing under pressure.
Began with others, soon dropped behind midfield racing down the centre of the course, no further impression after coming onto course proper.
Settled within 3Ls of speed early stages, gradually faded after coming onto course proper.
Badly jostled jumping out, remained well behind throughout, found nothing under pressure.
Soon dropped behind midfield racing down the centre of the course, no further impression.
Always struggling.
Ducked sharply out at start bumping others, soon dropped to tail-end, never a factor.
Settled towards the rear of the field, 2 wide with cover. Came wide in the home straight and worked home well to snare victory in the shadows of the post.
Rated behind midfield, 1 off with cover. Was briefly held up near the 350m but found the line strongly after spearing through runners.
Tracked the leader along the paint. Left a little flatfooted after the 500m and was placed under pressure soon after. Hit the front after the 100m, but was nabbed close to the post.
Travelled in the lead 1 off. Kicked early in the straight and was in the clear near the 200m but gave ground over the final bounds.
Stalked the leaders, racing about 1 with off with cover. Maintained a constant gallop right to the wire.
Raced 1 off in a midfield position. Kept on at the same pace over the final stages.
Camped midfield the fence. Battled to the line fairly.
Settled in last position. Swung wide on the home turn and rattled home nicely.
Raced inside the leader along the fence in 2nd spot. Faded in the run to the line.
Positioned midfield 3 deep with cover. Made a forward move after the 600m, shifting into a 4 wide line but failed to sustain its run.
Traveled slightly ahead of midfield 3 deep with cover. Carried out to race 4 wide after the 600m, was a beaten horse early in the straight.
Slow to begin settling towards the rear 4-5 wide no cover. Struggled in the home straight. (Found to be lame the following day.)
Travelled behind midfield, 3 wide with cover. Made no impression in the run home.
Began awkwardly losing ground then was allowed to settle near the rear of the field. Failed to show any dash in the straight.
Urged early and sat 4Ls behind the leader passing 800M. Pressed from midpoint and progressed steadily. Still a length off final furlong but then kicked impressively to draw clear closing stages.
Showed superior early speed to lead on stands' rail despite the low draw 700M out. Disputed lead 400M and was ahead by a length 200M. Unable to hold off winner final 100M.
Raced within 2Ls of the lead thereafter. Kept on when asked from 400M but failed to match on terms with the front pair. Prevailed in a battle for 3rd near the line.
Soon on leader's back near the stands' rail. Challenged the lead passing 400M but was put aside near 300M. Plugged on and missed out on place close to home.
Always ahead of midfield on stands' rail but never posed any threat to the principals.
2Ls behind the speed early. Levelled up passing 600M. Responded only fairly when the race got serious 300M out.
Never better than midfield on stands' rail. Just held ground to the line.
Always behind midfield. No real progress from there.
Moved gradually towards the centre of the track from far side after start and sat towards rear passing 700M. Made very limited headway 300M from home.
Raced at midfield early. No response when asked from midpoint.
At midfield near the centre of the track through to midpoint. Beaten passing 400M.
At rear throughout. Never a factor.
Trailed field always. No impression.
Pressed early and stayed behind midfield passing 600M. Couldn't keep up from 400M. Struggled final furlong.

Driven to occupy a fence position 2Ls behind the leader, travelled cosily throughout, niggled along rounding bend, responded well when asked for effort final 250 M, hit the lead a few strides before the line.
Pushed hard forward to lead on rails, joined turning for home, kept on strongly under pressure final 350 M, just headed in by the winner final 30 M.
Taken back from the widest alley and travelled two from the rear 6Ls off the speed, shifted wider for home, finished off well under pressure final 250 M, fought hard for the 3rd.

Broke well, sat handily just behind the leader, joined the lead at the final turn, had every chance in the home straight, could match the strides of leader passing 200 M, soon flattened and lost a place eventually.
Bit slow to begin, soon caught up 3Ls off the pace 3-wide with cover, improved along 4-deep at final turn, hung in near 250 M, kept battling on but lacked extra pace to mount a serious challenge.
Out in line, checked before the first turn, ended up in a one-off position 2Ls off the pace, tightened near 200 M, remained one-paced under maximum pressure in concluding stages.
Jumped only fairly, taken rearward 6Ls off the pace, improved along 3-deep from 600 M, could not find extra in the home straight.
Slow to begin, sat in a fence position in the mid-division, travelled comfortably throughout, failed to make up any ground in the home straight.
Broke only fairly and mustered slowly as usual, 8Ls off the speed at rear, niggled along throughout the entire trip, made very little progress in the home straight.
Out in line, urged along to hold a 2-deep position in the mid-division, struggled from 800 M, weakened at the top of home straight, soon faded.
Jumped fast, pressed on to track leader in the one out one back spot, placed under maximum pressure from 700 M, failed to keep up at the top of home straight, yielded ground quickly.
Out in line, caught wide at the first turn and then eased back in search of cover, ended up traveling 5-6Ls off the pace 4-wide, outpaced rounding bend, soon dropped out.
Broke fairly, pushed hard forward to sit 2Ls off the pace, caught 4-wide with no cover, struggled from 800 M, soon got tired, finished tailed out.
Broke well, soon occupy a fence position in midfield, comfortably throughout, dashed well when clear 350 M out, hit the lead near 150 M, kept on to score.
Out in line, driven to sit prominently 2-3Ls behind the pace, responded well when asked for efforts final 400 M and briefly led near 200 M, soon caught by the winner, did enough for the 2nd.
Jumped fast, held up to a one-off position just in front of the mid-division, improved along 3-deep rounding bend, contested lead but could not find extra passing 150M, just kept a place.

Restrained in mid-division 3-wide with no cover, strode forward 600 M while caught very wide, ran on soundly and briefly led near 250 M, lacked a decisive kick and soon turned one-paced, just lost a place.
Taken to the rear and travelled 9Ls behind the speed, crept closer rounding bend, made up some ground down centre of the home straight but lacked extra pace to challenge the principals final 100 M.
Niggled along to sit prominently 4Ls off the pace, travelled nicely throughout, had every chance in home straight, only one-paced when asked for efforts.
Lacked early speed and travelled 10Ls off the pace, swung widest for home, held up early in straight when hanging in, finished off soundly final 200 M but never really troubled the principals.
Sat rearward 8-9Ls behind the leader, patiently ridden until the home turn, did make up some ground early in straight, but was not properly clear final 150 M, remained one-paced.
Broke well, taken rearward 9Ls off the speed, travelled bit keenly in early stages when restrained, made up little ground along the inner from 300 M.
Awkward start losing ground, pushed forward to catch up in the mid-division, gave very limited response when clear 400 M out, flattened passing 200 M.
Given a waiting ride as usual and travelled 7-8Ls off the pace on rails, held up for clear early in straight, failed to make up any ground under pressure final 200 M.
Lacked early speed, travelled at rear over 10Ls off the pace despite being niggled along, made no impression in the home straight.
Mustered fast to track leader, kept on until flattened 300 M out, soon got tired and yielded ground.
Strode forward to set the early pace, led until overhauled passing 350 M, weakened sharply and finished tailed out.
Hard ridden forward, 1.5Ls off the fast pace 2-3 wide, closed the race off strongly to hold its unbeaten record on the surface.
Hard ridden forward, settled in box seat, not suited by the fast sectionals, led 400m, hung on strongly until 100M overhauled, ran on for 2nd without any other threat.
Pushed to keep up with the leaders along the fence, 3Ls off the fast pace, ran on well to the line for 3rd without threatening winner.
Slow away, pushed to keep up 6Ls behind the leader, suited by the fast tempo but trapped 3 wide, progressed steadily in straight, bumped 300M.
Eased to sit in front of midfield, 3Ls off the fast pace 2-3 wide, just held ground in straight.
Eased to sit in midfield, 4.5Ls off the leader 2 wide, never progressed.
Bumped start, took rail at rear, 7.5Ls off the leader, favoured by the fast pace, ran on fairly.
Hard ridden to keep up with the field, 7.5Ls off the leader 2 wide, benefited by the fast pace, no dash.
Midfield, 4.5Ls off the leader along the fence, suited by the fast tempo, flattened 250M.
Bumped start, at rear, 8.5Ls off the leader, helped by the fast pace but trapped 3 wide, no progress.
Bumped start, pushed to sit in midfield, 4.5Ls off the leader 3 wide, suited by the fast tempo, but weakened 300M.
Pushed to take the lead in 2 wide by 1.5Ls at fast sectionals, dropped off quickly 400M. (Substantial mucopus.)
Broke fairly but mustered fast to lead 1L on rails, kept on strongly when asked for efforts final 350 M, drew clear with some in tank.
Out in line, settled 5Ls off the pace just behind the mid-division, dashed well when clear passing 400 M pole, and nicked the 2nd in the final stride.
Given a waiting ride as usual and travelled 6-7Ls behind the leader, took long to obtain clear run in home straight, showed strong turn of foot final 150 M, just bit too late for the 2nd.
Tracked leader in the one out one back spot, kept on well in home straight under pressure, flattened final 100 M and lost a place in the final stride.
Slow to begin, urged along to hold a fence position 3Ls behind the pace, made some ground under pressure final 300 M but only offered little threat to the principals.
Prominently placed just behind the leader, travelled well throughout, responded only fairly under pressure final 400 M, held ground until flattened 150 M out.
Jumped well, chased leader in a 3-wide position with no cover, gave very limited response when asked at the top of home straight, outpaced 200 M, soon faded.
Out in line, sat one-off 5Ls behind the pace, shifted widest for home, failed to make up any ground in the straight.
Jumped fastest from the wide draw, taken rearward and travelled 7Ls off the speed, swung widest for home, made no impression in the straight.
Broke well, prominently sat within striking distance from the leader, outpaced at the top of home straight, weakened sharply passing 200 M.
Jumped only fairly, niggled along to hold a 2-wide position in the mid-division, struggled rounding bend, got tried and dropped out passing 200 M.
Very slow to begin, rearward throughout, never competitive.

In midfield along the fence and close enough turning in, quickly swept to the front 400M out, held off a serious challenge from the eventual 3rd before prevailing in a close finish against the fast finishing 2nd down the far outside.

Settled 2-wide in midfield and travelled strongly to the straight, ran on well from 400M but shifted towards the stand's side under maximum pressure in late stages and was just edged out in a photo finish.
Held up towards the rear and saved ground on the inside, responded well and challenged strongly up the fence, battled on well but was always held by the winner.
Well covered in a 2-wide position towards the rear, made steady progress from the back of the field under top weight but offered little threat to the first three.
Settled 3-wide in mid-division, switched wide with his challenge and stayed on without threatening the principals.
Close enough to the leader and raced handily, briefly threatened early in straight but turned one-paced over the final 200M.
Blundered at the start, settled 8Ls back in last place and remained there until the straight, switched widest for a clear run but responded only fairly.
2-wide in chasing group behind the pace, used little to top of the straight, briefly held up near 400M but couldn't find a turn of foot when clear. Never threatened.
Switched off after the start and raced in the rear group 8Ls off leader, had plenty to do turning in, made some progress on this yielding ground but not reached leaders.
More prominent than usual and settled in 3rd along the fence, first to make his move, kept on till finding no extra inside 200M.
Settled 3-wide ahead of mid-division but without cover throughout the trip, driven but no progress inside 400M, weakened and eased final 100M.
Travelled 3-wide behind midfield, checked near 1100M and was difficult to settle after that, kept on at the same pace final 400M and never got into it.
Had a clear lead to 450M then weakened rapidly on straightening, eased.
Jumped fairly, urged to catch up a fence position in midfield, niggled along from 700 M, dashed impressively final 300 M and took the lead passing 100 M.

Jumped fast, sat cosily within striking distance from the leader, responded well when asked for efforts final 300 M, fought hard to contest the lead, overhauled by the winner near 100 M. (Lost left front plate.)
Bit slow to begin, urged to hold a 2-wide position in the mid-division, made ground steadily down centre of home straight final 350 M, got a solid 3rd without offering threat to the first two.
Lacked early speed, niggled along throughout to remain in touch, did cover some ground in the home straight but never really troubled the placegetters.

Broke fairly, tracked leader early, took the lead when pace slackened in the middle stages, created a 4Ls gap turning for home, kept on until flattened passing 200 M pole, soon weakened and lost a place.
Given a waiting ride as usual and travelled 10Ls off the pace, had much to do turning for home, made up substantial ground in the straight but still far too late for a place.

Broke well, taken to rear over 10Ls off the pace, travelled bit keenly in middle stages when restrained, shifted to the inner at the top of home straight, ran on strongly but too late to threaten the principals.
Sat patiently in a rearward position, made gradual progress final 350 M under pressure, but never really troubled the principals.
Slow to begin, urged along to catch up a 2-wide position just behind midfield, bit outpaced rounding bend, only passed the exhausted rivals in the home straight.
Driven to take the lead early then eased to 2nd passing 1200 M, niggled along from middle stages to hold the position, had no more in tank turning for home, gave ground rapidly.
Niggled along to keep the on-pace position, caught 3-wide with no cover, outpaced rounding bend and proven beaten passing 400 M. (Cut in left hind leg.)
Out in line, held up within striking distance from the leader, travelled well throughout but gave no response when asked 400 M out, yielded ground quickly in the straight.
Never better than midfield, travelled bit keenly in early stages, outpaced rounding bend, weakened and proven beaten at the top of home straight.

Drawn widest and mustered bit slowly in early stages, caught very wide at the first turn, struggled in midfield throughout, weakened sharply turning for home, finished tailed out. (Heart irregularity.)
Amongst first few to jump, pressed on to race first without cover, had a fair run to bend, set out after leader straightening, hit front inside 200 M and fought strongly to defy rival late.
No early toe, slotted in on rails 3 to 4Ls back, enjoyed an easy trip in mid-section, saved ground on turning, chased hard in straight and narrowly failed to run down principal.
Bounced with them, faded back into midfield, raced 4 to 5Ls down in running line, responded under riding final 400 M to eventually work into 3rd well clear of top pair.
Nice getaway, ideally positioned on leaders back, had no excuses 1 to 2Ls down to turn, took inside runs and kept on fairly just losing a place late.
Showed usual pace to take up running, ran along freely 1 to 2Ls clear in front, still in command until 200M when run ended. Tired last bit.
Drifted back to race near to last almost 8Ls off speed, set plenty to do and came wider turning in, closed off well making best progress final furlong.
Fair to begin, settled behind midfield on rails, 6Ls from leaders but consumed energy in mid-section, improved rounding bend, made some minor ground without looking likely.
Prominent from outset, ended up in 1 out 1 back spot, had all favours 3 to 4Ls down to bend, angled into clear on turning, peaked at 300 M and was disappointing thereafter.
Drifted back soon after start, raced well back to bend 3 wide 6 to 7Ls off speed, still plenty to do on turning, passed a few runners late but never threatened.
Slowly out losing 3 to 4Ls, then failed to muster, raced 8Ls or so back on rails, last turning, just passed tired runners late.
Began nicely, forced to restrain seeking a trail, ended up 3 wide just off pace with cover, 4Ls back on turning, gradually faded when condition gave out.
Tardy to begin, settled much further back than usual 7Ls or so away in running line, well back to bend, poor response in straight.
Moderate jump, raced 3 wide behind midfield 6Ls off pace, had a trail however did work to bend, not sighted in straight.
Out in line, pressed on but posted 3 wide without cover, worked hard on circle, 2 to 3Ls back rounding bend, folded after a hard run.

Quickly ridden from the widest barrier to one-out-one-back position, held similar spot into straight, hit front under pressure 100 M out, held on well to finish.
Settled one back in 3rd on rails within 2Ls of speed, same turning in and briefly baulked 200 M out, fought on under pressure to reach 2nd final strides.
Settled in 4th within 3Ls of speed, soon came under pressure after straightening, made steady headway under pressure without threatening.
Soon took up running, led the field until headed by winner 100 M out, died on its run close to home.
Raced 3-wide with cover in forward of midfield, slightly closer up turning in, fought on steadily under pressure without threatening.
Towards rear, made moderate headway down straight to be nearest at finish.
Raced wide just worse than midfield most of way to straight, produced good late impression.
Settled in midfield, saved ground turning in, kept on steadily without quickening under pressure.
Settled well behind, closer up turning for home, kept on same pace without quickening under pressure.
Slightly slow out, niggling at towards rear when hampered and lost about 2Ls at about 1000 M, remained in last few thereafter but produced some late impression nearing finish.
Always struggling.
Settled in midfield on rails, commenced to give ground rounding home bend, soon struggled.
Showed enough gate speed to be in front early then camped on the back of the leader along the rails. Gained the ascendancy near the furlong and proved to strong in the run to the finish.
Travelled behind midfield 2 deep with cover. Swung wide in the straight and worked to the wire in good style.
Got a clean start then was checked when crowded for room near the 1100 M, settling 1 out 1 back. Ran on well in the straight.
Stoked up early and crossed to lead on the fence after the 900 M. Set decent fractions only tiring inside the 100 M.
Settled at the tail of the field, 2 to 3-wide with cover. Closed off soundly.
Settled midfield 1 off with cover. Was inclined to half cart along the back straight whilst maintaining a trail. Never really quickened when asked for an effort turning for home.
Coursed very wide early before being able to shift in to race outside the leader near the 700 M. Faded inside the furlong.
Began well and was with the front division before copping a check near the 1100 M and settling 3 back the paint. Kept on at the same pace over the latter stages.
Jumped on terms however was checked near the 1100 M and settled 4 back the fence. Failed to make any appreciable ground in the final stretch.
No Comments on Running information for this horse.
Settled with the backmakers along the fence. Had to be checked off heels near the 700 M, but despite this was well beaten in the run to the line.
Raced towards the rear, 3 deep with cover. Struggled in the run home.
Soon led by 1L on fence. Same margin clear through to last turn. Never seriously challenged and won with some comfort.
Quickly into stride but was caught 3-wide. Parked one-out- one-back from 900 M. Dashed strongly in the straight but the winner had enough to hold on.
Dropped back from high draw. Stayed 3-wide towards rear middle stages. Swung widest and was 6Ls down on straightening. Made substantial headway and was nearest at finish.
Hard ridden after start. Settled 3-wide behind midfield from 800 M. Forced wider and was 4Ls away turning in. Covered good ground to make frame.
Raced within 3Ls of the pace on fence through to the home straight. Ideal spot to attack but kept one-paced.
Away in line from high draw. Taken to race 4-wide at rear first turn. Found the fence approaching the Rock. Took inside run and was 6Ls off into final stretch. Progressed moderately.
Began awkwardly. Driven to take prominent spot before first turn. Well positioned to strike in the home straight but couldn't turn up a notch.
Slow to begin. Pressured along the fence and took a spot behind midfield from 900 M. 4Ls adrift rounding the turn but never improved from there. (Lame right fore.)
Moderate jump and was caught wide. Shaken up and slotted into a 2-wide position at midfield passing 900 M. 3Ls behind the leader leaving the bend. Found little when asked.
2-wide on leader's back through to home turn. Urged from 450 M but got no extra.
3-wide ahead of midfield early and was gradually eased to 2-wide behind midfield. Failed to make any impact thereafter.
Well enough away but was caught wide. Taken towards rear from 1000 M. Never recovered.
Out in line, driven to hold a one-off position 3L off the pace, clicked into gear passing 200 M pole, finished off soundly to score.
Restrained in the one out one back spot, suited by the soft tempo, niggled along rounding bend, briefly led 200 M out, soon headed in by the winner, still kept on well.
Sat 5Ls behind the pace, 2-wide with cover, urged along turning for home, made late progress final 200 M, nicked 3rd in the final stride.
Took the box-seat just behind the leader, travelled nicely throughout, had every chance in home straight, did kept on but bit too one-paced, just lost a place in the final stride.
Sat one from the rear 6Ls behind the speed, improved along 3-wide 500 M out, made up gradual ground down centre of home straight final 300 M, just too late for a place.
Slow to begin, sat two from the rear, 5Ls off the pace on rails, drifted back to last turning for home, took time to obtain clear run early in straight, finished off well final 200 M.
Jumped fast, sat 2Ls off pace early when caught 4-wide with no cover, strode forward to lead passing 1100 M, kept on only fairly early in home straight, overhauled near 200 M, soon flattened.
Taken back from gate 12, travelled 8Ls off the pace at the rear, urged along throughout the trip, swung widest for home, only passed the tired rivals in home straight.
Broke well, held up in a fence position in midfield, only one-paced in home straight, held up near 200 M, failed to recover.
Sat 4Ls off the pace, 3-wide with no cover, travelled keenly in middle stages, struggled rounding bend, got tired at the top of the home straight, raced ungenerously near 100 M.

Placing: UR
Comment: Lost rider, took no part.

Pushed forward to occupy a one-off position 4Ls off pace, travelled nicely under the strong tempo, niggled along rounding bend, dashed well final 250 M, fought hard and took the lead just before the line.
Jumped well and mustered fast to lead 2Ls, quickened 400 M out, kept on well under maximum pressure in the home straight, headed in by the winner in the last few strides.
Sat cozily in a fence position in the midfield, suited by the strong tempo, made up ground steadily down centre of home straight, just did enough to take a dead-heat 3rd.
Lacked early speed as usual and travelled over 10Ls off the speed, crept closer rounding bend, swung widest for home, fought hard in the straight for a dead-heat 3rd. (Lost right front plate.)
Jumped fast, sat prominently in a fence position 4 to 5Ls off pace, obtained clear run soon after entering the home straight, kept on fairly, never likely for a place.
Broke well, easily ran up to get across in the front and sat just behind the leader, struggled rounding bend, kept fighting in home straight but could not find extra to challenge the principals.
Jumped fairly from gate 12, niggled along to sit in the one out one back spot, hung out throughout the trip, struggled turning for home, only one-paced in straight.
Slow to begin, urged along to catch up 8Ls off the pace on rails, made up some ground along the inner early in straight, not properly clear in concluding stages, not fully tested.
Started awkwardly, ended up in a 2-wide position 8 to 9Ls off the speed, shifted wide for home, gave very limited response when asked for efforts in the straight.
Broke well from the wide draw, urged along and soon found the fence just off the pace, held ground until got tired near 150 M.
Crowded start, driven to hold a 2-wide position 5 to 6Ls off the pace, struggled rounding bend, failed to make up any ground in home straight.
Always rearward, never competitive.
Settled in midfield along the fence, 4-1/2Ls off the good pace, progressed steadily 200 M to score.
Pushed to take the rail and led by 1L at good pace, hung on until 50 M when overhauled, ran on for 2nd.
Pushed early to sit in front of midfield, 3Ls off the good pace 2-wide, made steady ground 250 M and grabbed 3rd.
Pushed along to occupy the box seat, just held ground in straight.
Eased back as usual, 6-1/2Ls off the good pace on the rails, progressed steadily in straight, blocked and checked 150 M.
Eased back, 5-1/2Ls behind the good pace 2 to 3-wide, made minor ground in straight.
In front of midfield, 3Ls off the good pace along the fence, no turn of foot in straight.
Eased at start, 6-1/2Ls off the good pace, trapped 3 to 4-wide and lost too much ground, ran on ok in last quarter.
Pushed along to keep up with the field at rear, 7-1/2Ls off the good pace 2 to 3-wide, held up 4-2, made ground when clear.
Pushed early to obtain a prominent spot, trapped 3-wide at stable bend, sat 1L off the good pace outside the lead prior to home bend, weakened 200 M.
Hard ridden early, took cover in midfield, 4-1/2Ls behind the good pace 2-wide, no progress in final stages, checked 150 M.
Hard ridden forward to cross, 2Ls off the good pace 2-wide, emptied 300 M.
Standard jump, urged to sit 2 to 3Ls off the pace, 2-deep with cover, swung wide for home, dashed well but hung in badly final 300 M, bumped heavily with rival at 150 M, kept on strongly to score.
Taken back from the widest alley and travelled 5Ls behind the leader, swung wide for home, kicked strongly down centre of the straight, line came too soon.
Jumped well, sat 3 to 4Ls off the pace, lost cover and caught 3-wide from 800 M, asked for efforts from 400 M, dashed well final 300 M to contest the lead, lacked a decisive kick final 50 M.
Jumped fairly and lacked early speed, travelled 7Ls away at the rear, swung widest for home, finished off strongly final 300 M, just late for a place.
Out in line, held up in a fence position just behind the mid-division, bumped for a few occasions early in straight, made up some ground along in the inner but never really troubled the principals.
Broke fairly and caught wide early, allowed to stride forward to share lead from 800 M, kept on well until heavily bumped by anther horse at 150 M, soon overhauled and flattened.
Jumped fast, held up just off the pace in a 2-wide position, carried inward early in straight, kept on until flattened passing 150 M.
Broke well, travelled cozily in a fence position just off the pace, bumped for a few occasions from 200 M to 100 M, only one-paced under pressure. (Roar.)
Driven to hold a one-off position in midfield, travelled well early in straight but was badly held up for room final 200 M, not fully tested.
Lacked early speed, travelled 5 to 6Ls off the pace at a rearward position, failed to make up any ground in the home straight.
Driven to share the lead on rails, overhauled and weakened sharply at the top of straight, yielded ground quickly.
Started very awkwardly, took no part.

Showed good speed to lead and went a strong gallop through the early and middle stages, was taken on making the turn but quickened well 350 M out to extend her lead, kept on determinedly to the line and won in track record time.
Close enough in 5th, made good headway over final 250 M to go 2nd in late stages but offered no threat to the runaway winner.
Broke well, went forward before the turn to take on the leader, all out in straight but was gradually outpaced by the impressive winner, turned flat and lost 2nd close home.
Crossed to the fence passing 800 M then held up just behind the pace, kept on well enough but never looked like getting near to the leaders.
Held up in last about 6Ls behind the lead, had plenty to make up off the bend, ran on well final 200 M and did best work late.
Taken back to a midfield position with cover but was a shade keen in middle stages, edged out into clear 300 M, stayed on but not reaching leaders.
Caught 3-wide with no cover behind leading pair, remained at the same pace in straight and never looked dangerous to the leaders.
Lacked pace and had to be driven along in early stages, towards the rear throughout and didn't find much when put under pressure. Never threatened.
Positioned on the fence just ahead of mid-division, lacked any acceleration when asked and had no extra left final 100 M.
Began awkwardly and ended up behind midfield about 4Ls off the pace, couldn't lengthen his stride when needed. Never any impression.
Dropped back after the start and was difficult to settle in early stages, swung 3-wide into straight and could only make limited progress inside final 200 M.
Restrained to a 3-wide position in midfield on jumping from draw 12, didn't pick up at all when asked inside 350 M and ran well below par.
