Began from a wide draw, settled wide behind midfield, commenced move rounding home bend, ran on steadily from midfield into straight to just get up on line.
Soon improved to a prominent spot, travelled 1-out-1-back around the bend, hit front upon straightening gaining a 1L break under pressure over 200 M out, pipped at post.
Settled in midfield, baulked for a run until 300 M, ran on resolutely to be nearest at finish.
Settled just better than midfield in 6th, became 7th around the around, worked home fairly to miss out on 3rd final strides.
Settled in last few after beginning from a wide draw, came under pressure to challenge after straightening, ran home well to be nearest at finish.
Travelled in last few to straight, ran home steadily to be nearest at finish.
Soon in rear, finished off race well down centre of straight.
Broke well from wide draw, gradually crossed to rails before making home bend, led until approaching home straight, soon faded out of contention.
Settled just better than midfield, made some late impression past beaten horses.
Not far off in 5th or 4th within 3Ls of speed, slightly closer up turning in, ran home one-paced.
Broke well from a high draw, settled in prominently 3rd within 2Ls of speed, in one-out-one-back spot turning in, weakened under pressure. (Mucus.)
Began awkwardly losing ground, always struggling at the back.
Travelled on rails in midfield, similar turning in, found nothing under pressure in straight.
Broke well, gradually settled just better than in midfield in 5th, dropped out tamely in straight.
Crossed over from the outside alley to travel behind midfield 2-3 wide with cover. Rolled out to race 4 deep on the home turn and under spirited riding lengthened enough to grab victory late.
Settled about 3 back, 2 deep with cover. Peeled out near the 400m and looked the likely winner before being nabbed in the shadows of the post.
Stalked the leading division along the rail. Experienced some traffic problems early in the straight, recovered well to finish off nicely.
Enjoyed the run of the race on the back of the leaders, 1 off with cover. Came 3 wide rounding the home turn and swept to the front at the 200m. Was collard inside the last 50m.
Travelled with the backmakers 2-3 wide with cover. Angled out after the furlong and ran on solidly.
Always travelled 1 off back in the field with cover. Commenced to work out into the clear after the 500m, closed off soundly.
Camped midfield the paint. Maintained a solid gallop right to the wire.
Settled midfield, 2 deep with cover. Worked home steadily.
Caught on a limb, 3-4 wide with out cover for most of the trip, midfield. Weakened over the last 100m.
Travelled back in the field, 2-3 wide with cover. Came wide in the straight and plugged to the line.

Settled in last position 2 wide, finding the fence on the circle. Was steadied near the 700m, and when travelling inside another runner thereafter commenced to race more tractable and in the straight got home well.
Speared across from a wide gate to make the running after the 800m, travelling 1 off. Hung in for most of the trip and faded over the concluding stages.
Led early in the event before being taken on after the 800m, travelling 3/4 of a length back to the inside in 2nd position. Folded quickly after the last furlong.
Travelled behind midfield the fence. Struggled in the final stretch.
Settled within 7Ls of the pace near the fence early. Took closer order making the home turn. Swung out and was 5Ls down on straightening. Kept making up ground and ran down rivals close to home.
Handy position, one-off the fence behind leaders until home straight. Shifted to the rail for clear run and hit front 200M. Caught by the winner last stride.
Caught 3-wide behind leaders through to home turn. Ran on fairly well in the straight but couldn't quite beat the front pair. Just held 3rd.
Sat within 3Ls of the speed in a 2 to 3-wide position before leaving the bend. Kept giving and nearly snatched 3rd.
Soon in the leading section on fence. Headed 200M but hung on. Not beaten far.
Sat outside the leader until home straight. One-paced to conclude.
Raced within 4Ls of leaders in a 3-wide position early. Moved closer to the rail and was 3Ls off at bend. Made run towards inside and finished off fairly well.
Towards rear on fence early and middle stages. 7Ls back out wide swinging for home. Improved substantially thereafter.
Sat 7Ls behind leaders in a 3-wide position through to home turn. Taken very wide on straightening and covered decent ground.
Towards rear early. Came widest into final stretch. Made some headway.
Trapped 3-wide without cover in the front rank until faded 300M. (Substantial amount of blood in horse's trachea).
Ahead of midfield along the rail early. Moved up to prominent spot passing 1200M. Urged to maintain position rounding the turn. No more to offer in the straight.
Never better than midfield. Beaten passing 300M.
Always at rear. No impression.
Broke well from gate 14, mustered fast to lead and found the fence passing 1000 M pole, dashed impressively under pressure final 350 M, drew clear easily to score.
Jumped fast, sat prominently within striking distance from leader, raced keenly when restrained in middle stages, ran on well final 400 M for 2nd but failed to threat the winner.
Jumped fast, restrained in a 2-wide spot 1L behind the leader, had every chance in home straight, could not match the strides of winner at 300 M but did keep on soundly for a place.
Out in line, cosily placed in the box-seat just behind the leader, travelled nicely throughout, only one-paced in home straight, lost a place final 100 M.
Broke well from the wide draw, held up in a 3-wide position with cover 2Ls off the speed, had his chance in home straight, kept on fairly but never threatened the placegetters.
Jumped only fairly, sat three from the rear on rails, hampered turning for home, made up little ground along the inner in the straight, only beat the tired runners.
Lacked early speed, placed rearward 5Ls off the pace, swung widest for home, ran on steadily when clear late at 250 M but never troubled the principals.
Out in line, settled 3-4Ls off pace on rails, only gave limited response when asked for efforts final 350 M.
Broke only fairly, held up in a 3-wide position in midfield, overraced when pace slackened rounding bend, lacked a kick when placed under pressure in home straight.
Lacked early speed as usual and travelled 6-7Ls off the pace at rear, swung widest for home, made little progress down centre of the straight final 250 M.
Awkwardly drawn, caught very wide with no cover when held up in midfield, strode forward from 900 M to track leader, outpaced passing 400 M pole, soon got tired.
Taken to a 4-wide position just behind the mid-division, could not find extra in the home straight, weakened final 150 M.
Out in line, niggled along to hold a one-off position in midfield, bumped near 900 M, struggled from 600 M, weakened and dropped out early in straight.
Slow to begin, urged to catch up 6Ls away at the rear, failed to make up any ground in home straight.
Bumped start but soon took the box-seat just behind the leader, responded well when asked for efforts final 400 M, hung in but kept fighting hard in the straight, hit the lead just before the line.
Jumped fastest and led, found the fence passing 1200 M pole, kept on strongly in home straight, headed in by the winner in the last stride.
Out in line, prominently placed 2-3Ls off the pace, obtained clear run at the top of straight, kept on fairly well for 3rd.
Broke well, sat cosily in midfield on rails, was blocked at 400 M, kept fighting in straight and looked possible for a place, just missed out.
Bumped start, held up in midfield, caught 3-wide with no cover, crept closer rounding bend, tried hard to contest for a place in the home straight, flattened final 100 M and missed out.
Taken rearward from the wide draw and travelled 5Ls behind the pace, checked near 800 M, only gave limited response when asked final 400 M, made up little ground without offering any threats.
Taken back to the rear and travelled 7Ls off the pace, swung wide for home, made some late progress down centre of the straight final 250 M.
Held up in a one-off position in midfield, travelled keenly in middle stages when restrained, drifted back gradually at home turn, made up little ground final 250M.
Jumped well from gate 11, caught 4-wide when being eased, ended up travelling 6Ls off the pace, struggled rounding bend, no extra in home straight.
Broke fairly from the widest, soon took the one out one back spot and travelled satisfactorily, failed to quickened when placed under pressure final 350 M, soon weakened and dropped out.
Jumped fairly, settled in the mid-division, 2-wide with cover, only gave very limited response when asked for efforts early in straight, proven beaten at 200 M.
Lacked early speed, travelled three from the rear 6-7Ls off the speed, swung widest form home, made no impression in straight.
Bit slow to begin, niggled along to catch up the mid-division, no response when placed under pressure at the top of straight, soon proven beaten.
Slow away, driven to catch up 7Ls behind the leader, struggled throughout, eased out at 250 M.
Took rail easily and led by 1.5Ls at fast early sectionals, made all to score and clocked remarkable finishing time.
Settled in front of midfield, 4Ls off the fast pace, progressed steadily 300M to finish a strong 2nd, drifted away from rest of the field.
Hard ridden to take a prominent spot, 2Ls off the leader 2 wide, not suited by the fast tempo, hung on strongly for well beaten 3rd.
Settled in midfield, 5.5Ls off the leader 2 wide, benefited by the fast pace, ran on well to the line.
At back, 7.5Ls off the leader 3 wide, favoured by the fast tempo, made ground in straight.
Eased back, 7.5Ls off the leader along the fence, benefited by the fast pace, made some ground 250M.
Hard ridden to occupy the box seat, not suited by the fast tempo, out of fuel 300M.
Pushed to keep up in midfield, 7Ls off the leader 2 wide, favoured by the fast pace, no turn of foot in final stages.
Eased to rear and took rail, 10Ls off the leader, suited by the fast sectionals, ran on fairly in straight.
Eased to rear, 9Ls off the leader 2 wide, helped by the fast tempo, never progressed.
Behind midfield, 7Ls off the leader, benefited by the fast pace but trapped 4-5 wide, no progress.
Midfield, 5.5Ls off the leader, favoured by the fast tempo, however trapped 4 throughout and lost ground, soon weakened 600M.
Very slow away, hard ridden to obtain a midfield spot along the fence, 5Ls behind the fast pace, dropped off 400M.
Eased to rear, suited by the fast pace, but never competitive.
Broke well and soon occupied a one-off position just behind the leader, quickened well at the top of home straight and hit the lead near 250 M, kept on strongly, scored with some in tank.
Sat in a 2-wide position in midfield, bit overraced when restrained in middle stages, held up for room early in home straight, clear 200 M out and finished off soundly for 2nd.
Started bit awkwardly but soon ran up to track leader in a 2-wide position, briefly led at the top of home straight, reeled in by the winner near 250 M, kept on well for a place.

Jumped fastest, niggled along hold a midfield position 3-4Ls behind the speed, caught 3-wide with no cover, moved closer rounding bend, remained one-paced under maximum pressure in home straight, never really troubled the principals.
Jumped fast, taken to the rear and travelled 9Ls behind the speed, swung widest for home, did make up some ground down centre of the straight but failed to offer any threats to the placegetters.
Sat cosily in a fence position 3-4Ls off the pace, had every chance in home straight, only one-paced under maximum pressure.
Taken rearward from the widest alley, patiently ridden until the home turn, held up for rooms at the top of straight, made little late progress final 250 M.
Broke well and soon took the box-seat just behind the leader, held ground until outpaced near 200 M, soon got tired and dropped out.
Given a waiting ride as usual and travelled 6Ls behind the speed, obtained clear run and placed under pressure at the top of home straight, gave very limited response and proven beaten final 150 M.
Missed the gate, ended up in fence position about 5Ls off the pace, lacked a kick when asked for efforts 400 M out, flattened and dropped out passing 200 M pole.
Driven to lead and found the fence passing 1400 M, overhauled passing 400 M pole, soon weakened sharply, finished tailed out.

Quietly ridden in early stages and held up in midfield 3-4Ls off the lead, had to wait momentarily in early straight but quickened impressively once clear 250M, made significant headway and got up a few strides from the line.
Restrained to the rear 4-5Ls back, came with a well timed challenge final 400M, picked up strongly down the outside, just held.
Settled 2-wide in midfield, close enough turning in, ran on well down the inside final 300M but was overhauled by the first two in late stages.
Tracked leader one out one back, came with a promising looking run to hit the front 200M out, kept on but couldn't repel the first three final 50M.
Pushed to the lead after a slightly sluggish start, set steady tempo upfront and led till 200M, battled on but gradually weakened over final stages.
Quickly into stride but was unable to cross, caught wide without cover throughout, soon outpaced coming off the bend. (Jockey advised not to cover unnecessary ground.)
Caught wide in midfield throughout, stayed on but never reached leaders, faded in late stages.
On the rails towards the rear, not picked up when asked inside 400M, no impression.
Dropped back to last 5Ls off the pace, stayed on same pace towards the finish and never threatened.
Never far off the pace but had to be nudged along approaching the home straight, soon weakened.
Travelled rearward 7Ls off the pace, shifted ground in search of clear run at the top of home straight, dashed impressively between horses final 300 M, battled bravely and hit the lead near 50 M.
Taken rearward from the wide gate, swung wide for home, launched a strong challenge down centre of the home straight, fought hard to contest the lead final 200 M, narrowly beaten by the winner.
Sat in a 3-wide position just off the pace, no cover in the early stages, ran on to lead 300 M out, fought hard but failed to hold off the challenge from the top two final 100 M.
Broke fairly, settled in a one-off spot just behind the mid-division, held up for room until 250 M, finished off soundly for 4th but only offered little threat to the principals.
Out in line, prominently placed 1-2Ls off the speed on rails, blocked early in home straight, finished off satisfactorily final 250 M but lacked a decisive kick to challenge the principals.
Took the box-seat in early stages but had to shift out when pace slackened near 1000 M, ran on to lead at home turn, overhauled at 250 M, kept on until flattened passing 150 M.
Bit slow to begin, soon ran up to hold a fence position in midfield, tried to improve along the inner early in home straight, could not find extra passing 200 M, soon got tired.
Jumped fast, taken to a 3-wide position in the mid-division, made up little ground down centre of home straight from 400 M, crowded near 200 M, only one-paced after the interference.
Slow to begin, urged along to catch up 7L off the pace in a rearward position, finished off fairly final 400 M and passed some tired rivals.
Got across behind the bunch of horses and ended up settling about 4Ls behind the leader, gave very limited response when placed under pressure final 400 M, never a factor.
Jumped only fairly from gate 14, niggled along to lead and found the fence near 1000 M, overhauled at 500 M and got tired soon after entering the home straight.
Driven to sit 3-4Ls off the pace, one-off with cover, outpaced passing 300 M, soon dropped out.
Caught 3-wide with no cover in the mid-division, weakened sharply early in home straight, finished tailed out.
Drifted back to race 3 wide behind midfield, had trail 5Ls or so away to turn, kept responding under hard riding in straight to overhaul leaders in shadows of post.
Showed good early speed, took a sit 1 out 1 back behind pace, travelled well to bend, cut inside and engaged in lead battle from 300 M, just missed out late.
Began well enough, had a nice sit in midfield 4Ls away, in traffic to bend, worked into clear from 250 M and did best work late missing out in 3 way go.
Plenty of pace at start, worked forward to a clear lead 1L in front, didn't cross to rails, applied pressure to inside horse throughout, in mix until 100 M when run ended.
Moderate beginning, nice trail 3Ls back on fence, saved ground on bend, kept to task in straight and just missed frame.
Taken in behind soon after start, ended up 4 to 5Ls away on fence, saved ground on bend, same margin back to bend, worked to line soundly.
Restrained from awkward gate, best part of 8Ls down, moved 3 wide on circle, produced a good finish widest in straight to be nearest on line.
Out with rest, angled into running line 5Ls from lead, shifted back approaching bend, in traffic turning, made some progress before awkwardly placed late, doubtful to have threatened.
Taken back from a wide alley, 6 to 7Ls away near to last, pace suited but set a lot to do turning, worked home OK without threatening.
No early speed, settled in rear division on rails, 7Ls or so back in mid-section, lacked clear running at 300 M and held up at 200 M. Pay to forgive.
Fast away, held inside running and kept speed on at top end, shaded throughout, worked back turning, couldn't lift final 200 M.
Went forward but unable to get in, raced 3 wide without cover close to speed, did work to turn, faded final 300 M while hard run took toll.
Pressed on from outside alley, posted 4 wide without cover 2 to 3Ls off speed, worked to hard throughout and dropped out in straight.
Awkwardly away, unable to be as prominent as usual, raced 3 wide in middle stages, had cover to bend, soon weakened out.
Settled on rails in rear of midfield, not much room in straight until the 250 M, fought on stoutly to just get up.
Never far off in 5th just over 2Ls off the speed, ran on steadily to hit front inside 200 M, but only to be pipped at post.
Settled just better than midfield, ran on steadily to hold every chance in straight until the final 50 M.
Well there, 2L 4th on rails around the bend, briefly baulked early in straight, fought on under pressure until finding no extra over 50 M out.
Began moderately, settled in rear of midfield, in similar position turning in, met minor interference 300 M out, fought on steadily to narrowly miss the place-getters.
Soon crossed to rails in rear of field, remained behind while saving ground turning in, finished off race well with the fastest sectional.
Ridden along up with the pace out wide after beginning from a poor draw, still 3-wide in close-up position turning for home, faded out gradually after straightening.
Began fairly, gradually taken backward to settle 3-wide just worse than midfield, produced an even finish.
With leaders early, gradually drifted back to midfield far side, wider turning in, found nothing under pressure.
Soon taken back to travel well back, wide turning in, kept on steadily without quickening down centre of straight.
In similar position throughout, made no impression in straight.
Never a danger. (Jockey warned re his riding in the straight.)
Gradually took up running after the start, held narrow advantage until joined early in straight, dropped away quickly inside final 200 M.
Handy to straight, dropped out noticeably.

Keen and inclined to hang out during the run, responded well to urge and led 200M out, soon clear.
Close enough 1L off the pace, kept on final 400M for 2nd but offered little threat to the winner.
Soon crossed to the stand's rail and settled one back from the leader, driven passing halfway but took a while to pick up, stayed on final 150M to take 3rd.
In touch but couldn't find much when placed under pressure, no extra final 100M.
Slow to begin then rushed to the front and led till 200M, gradually weakened towards the line.
Trailed at the back of the field after a slow start, driven 350M out but no progress.
Settled at the rear of the field 2 deep with cover. Swept to lead the near the 100m posting a sound win.
Hampered at the start settling midfield the fence. Ran home solidly after obtaining clear running near the 200m.
Parked behind midfield, 1 off with cover. Took runs through runners in the straight, working home soundly.
Camped midfield, 3 wide with cover. Hit the front by the 200m but failed to sustain its effort.
Raced slightly worse than midfield, 3 deep with cover. Came 5 wide after the 500m, covered further ground on the home turn, battled gamely to the post over the concluding stages.
Stalked the leaders along the fence. Loomed up as a chance of finishing in the frame before peaking on its run after the 150m.
Settled in last position. Worked to the line soundly.
Raced behind midfield 2 wide with cover. Came wide in the straight and commenced to work home well before tiring near the 100 M.
Tracked the leaders 1 off with cover. Had every chance.
Travelled in 2nd position, 1 off. Was overhauled near the 200m and gave in quickly soon after.
Travelled behind the speed, but was caught 3 wide without cover. Never likely.
Raced with the backmakers along the fence. Failed to close off in the straight.
Made the running along the fence in good fractions. Faded sharply inside the final furlong.
Settled midfield 1 off with cover. Struggled in the home straight.

Soon led one off the fence. Elected to sit ahead of midfield approaching home turn and was 4Ls down on straightening. Rallied on to challenge the lead and put rivals aside final 100M. Won with comfort.
Trailed 2-wide 8Ls away until home straight. Shifted widest to make his run passing 350M. Covered substantial ground to nick 2nd without troubling the winner.

Away in line from high draw and was eased towards rear near 1000M. Improved wide from 650M and was 7Ls adrift turning in. Ran on strongly and looked dangerous near 200M but failed to sustain its run. Lost 2nd near finish.
Well enough away but insufficient speed to lead. Caught 3-wide without cover ahead of midfield home turn. 4Ls away swinging for home. Kept giving in a battle for 2nd and settled for 4th at the post.

Ridden along after start contending for lead. Settled behind the leader on fence passing 650M. Strode forward with the principals in the straight but couldn't match their finishing touch close stages.
Sat 2-wide behind midfield early, ended up towards rear at bend. 8Ls behind the leader turning into home. Made run towards inside and improved continuously.
Pushed early and burst to lead on fence near 900M. Restrained to sit behind pace rounding the turn and was 3Ls off leaving the bend. One-paced to conclude.
Wide at rear before home straight due to high draw. Made up good ground down the centre of the straight before finishing its run final 100M.
Jumped nicely, on leaders' back along the fence early. Dropped to midfield home turn and was 4Ls down into final stretch. Failed to turn up a notch.

Began well from high draw. Gradually taken to sit 3-wide behind midfield approaching home turn. Bumped and became unbalanced near 850M. Resumed to race wide at midfield approaching home straight. Emptied 300M.
Soon in the front rank but was trapped 5-wide. Driven to cross the field from 900M. Eventually led on fence at 600M and opened up a 2Ls gap at 400M. Caught near 250M and weakened thereafter.
Fair start. Pushed to race 2-wide ahead of midfield passing 1000M. Checked to midfield at 850M. Given reminder from 750M to maintain position but no response. No show in the straight.
2-wide behind midfield early. Checked towards rear at 850M. Ran on fairly in the home straight.
Hard ridden along the fence after start but could only stay behind midfield. Beaten before home straight.
Bumped start, easily ran up to lead 1L, travelled nicely on rails throughout, quickened well when placed under pressure at 300 M, kept on but could not find extra final 100 M, still won.
Niggled along to catch up 4-5Ls off the pace, made ground down centre of home straight final 350 M, finished off soundly for 2nd.
Taken back from gate 11 and travelled 6-7Ls away at the rear, improved gradually between horses from 500 M, properly clear 200 M out, kicked strongly for 3rd.
Driven to hold a fence position in midfield, made up ground gradually under maximum pressure in home straight, looked at least a place final 200 M, just missed out.
Broke fairly, pressed on to take the box-seat just behind the leader, gave limited response when asked for efforts final 300 M, rather one-paced and lost a place near 50 M.

Widely drawn, held up 3-wide with no cover behind the mid-division, checked at 700 M and drifted further back, niggled along round bend, made some late progress final 200 M down the centre of home straight.
Lacked early speed, pushed hard along to catch up 4-5Ls off the pace, travelled well rounding bend, finished off soundly under pressure in home straight, blocked final 150 M, not fully tested.
Broke well, pressed on to track leader but caught 3-wide with no cover, gave very limited when asked for efforts in home straight, outpaced near passing 200 M pole, soon dropped out.
Jumped fast, pushed forward to sit one-off just behind the pace, niggled along at final turn, could not find extra final 250 M, soon got tired.
Lacked early speed, travelled rearward despite being urged along, lost touch at home turn, never competitive.
Awkward start, sat 3-wide just off the pace, started struggling rounding the bend, kept yielding ground under hard riding, lost touch at the top of straight. (Lame in right front leg.)

Bumped start losing ground, niggled along to catch up 3Ls off the pace, travelled satisfactorily until weakened sharply at the top of straight, gave ground and finished tailed out. (Bled and lost left front plate.)

Jumped fast and soon occupied a one-off position 2Ls off the speed, travelled keenly in middle stages, crept closer at home turn, ran on to contest lead at the top of straight, fought hard to win by a nose.
Jumped well from gate 14, driven to lead and found the fence near 900 M, uncontested until the straight, overhauled at 200 M, kept battling on under pressure, almost fought back, lost by a whisker.
Out in line, held up in a 3-wide position just behind the mid-division, made up ground steadily under pressure in home straight, could not find extra to challenge the top two final 100 M.
Broke fairly, sat 4Ls behind the speed, held up for room early in straight, ran on steadily when clear final 200 M, just lost a place.
Slow to begin, sat one from the rear and travelled 6Ls off the pace, made up gradual ground down centre of the home straight but never really troubled the principals.
Prominently placed just behind the leaders, proven very difficult to settle when restrained in early and middle stages, kept on fairly under pressure until turned one-paced final 150 M.
Lacked early speed, sat 5Ls off the pace and caught 4-wide with no cover, crept closer rounding bend, took bit long to quicken early in home straight, made some late progress final 200 M.
Sat in the mid-division, caught 3-wide with no cover, ran on to join the lead at home turn, held ground until flattened passing 200 M pole, checked near 80 M.
Out in line, easily ran up to take the box-seat just behind the leader, only held ground at the top of home straight, outpaced passing 200 M pole, hung out at 50 M.
Given a waiting ride as usual and travelled 5-6Ls behind the speed, gave very limited response when asked for efforts in the home straight, made no impression.
Slow to begin, sat 7Ls off the pace at the rear, placed under pressure at the top of home straight, only made little ground and passed the tired runners, checked at 50 M.
Jumped fast but lacked early, sat in a 3-wide rearward position 6Ls behind the speed, shifted widest for home, failed to make up any ground in the home straight.
Bit slow to begin, placed in a fence position just behind the mid-division, gave no response when asked for efforts at the top of home straight, soon dropped out, checked at 50 M.
Broke only fairly, sat just behind the pace and proved very difficult to settle in early and middle stages, weakened sharply passing 400 M pole, finished tailed out.
Eased to rear for cover, 8Ls off the leaders 3 wide, benefited by the fast pace, progressed steadily 300M to score.
Pushed to take a forward spot as usual, 3.5Ls off the fast pace, trapped 3 wide throughout, moved further forward 800M, led 350M, hung on strongly until 100M overhauled, ran on for 2nd.
Eased at start to cross at rear, 6.5Ls off the leaders 2-3 wide, favoured by the fast tempo, progressed steadily 250M for 3rd.
Pushed along throughout to maintain the box seat, not suited by the fast sectionals, just held ground in straight.
Hard ridden early to take a more prominent spot, 3.5Ls behind the fast pace 2 wide, made good ground 400M.
Eased at start to cross behind the field, 5Ls off the leader 2 wide, benefited by the fast tempo, made ground 250M without much threats.
Eased to rear and took rail, 7Ls off the leaders, helped by the fast pace, made steadily ground in straight, lacked room 200 M.
Slowly away, pushed to obtain a midfield spot, 4Ls off the leader along the fence, suited by the fast tempo, just held ground in straight.
Hard ridden early but failed to muster, settled in midfield, 5Ls off the fast pace 2-3 wide, made early move 800M, however run ended 200M.
Hard ridden to hold the rail and shared the lead at fast sectionals, hung on until 300M weakened.
Hard ridden early but didn't muster, trapped 3-4 wide, never a factor at rear.
Eased back, trapped 4 wide throughout and lost too much ground, never better than midfield.
Awkward away, trapped 4 wide first bend, hard ridden forward to share the lead 2 wide at fast pace, burnt up too much fuel in early stages, faded quickly 400M.
Hard ridden forward, 2Ls off the leaders 2-3 wide, not suited by the fast pace, checked 500M, dropped off afterwards.

Broke well, niggled along hold a one-off position in midfield, checked at 700 M, over 10Ls behind the tearaway leader at home turn, kicked strongly and improved along the inner final 350 M, hit the lead in the final stride.

Held up in midfield on rails, checked at 1500 M, crept closer rounding bend but still had 9Ls to make up at home turn, ran on strongly final 400 M, briefly led final 50 M but headed in by the winner in the last stride.

Driven to lead and found the fence passing 1400 M pole, quickened at 800 M and opened up a 8Ls gap rounding the home turn, kept on well until flattened at 100 M, reeled in by the top two in last few strides.

Urged along to chase the pace group along rails in early and middle stages, placed 3rd but 9Ls away from the leader at home turn, made up ground gradually but lacked a decisive kick final 100 M, just lost a place.
Sat four from the rear over 10Ls off the pace, whipped in middle stages to hold his position, checked at 350 M, made up some ground final 250 M, blocked final 100M, not fully tested.
Travelled 3-wide in the mid-division, lost cover rounding bend, made up gradual progress in the home straight but never really troubled the principals.
Slow to begin but soon ran up to hold a one-off spot just behind the pace group, checked and lost ground near 900 M, placed under pressure at the top of straight, covered some ground final 250 M.

Lacked early speed despite being pushed hard, travelled rearward early, checked and crowded rounding home turn, made up substantial ground down centre of the home straight final 400 M but still far too late.
Given a waiting ride as usual and travelled two from the rear about 10Ls off pace, swung widest for home, only passed the tired runners in the straight.
Driven to sit handy in a one-off position, shaken off by the leader when pace quickened at 900 M, failed to keep up at the top of home straight, soon dropped out.
Taken back from gate 14, always rearward, urged along in middle stages, bumped at home turn, made no progress in home straight, never a factor.
Driven to chase after the speed, shaken off by the tearaway leader from 800 M, struggled rounding home turn, got exhausted final 300 M.
Jumped fastest, niggled along to hold a 3-wide position in the mid-division, struggled at home turn, gave no response when asked for efforts at the top of home straight, soon weakened sharply.
Broke only fairly, urged along to race on-pace, weakened and gave ground from 1000 M out, finished tailed out. (Heart irregularity.)
Placed behind midfield and always going strongly, driven 350M and showed a brilliant turn of foot to find the front in a matter of strides, drew clear and cruised home.
Never far off in 4th, no match with the winner's acceleration inside 300M but did well enough and put up a career best performance to finish 2nd.
2-wide in midfield 4Ls off the steady pace, made steady progress inside 400M but was comprehensively beaten by the winner.
Tracked leader, had every chance going into straight but was outpaced by the first three final 200M.
Towards the rear on the inside, 6Ls down passing 400M, took time to muster in straight and did best work late.
Switched off to the rear and travelled 6Ls off the pace, made some progress inside 350M but never looked likely.
Broke well but was restrained to a position behind midfield, swung 3-wide into home, ran on final 400M but not reached leaders.
Pressed on after an ordinary start, led uncontested to straight, headed inside 200M and found no extra to the line.
Sat in 3rd, always in touch, driven inside 400M but no progress and soon behind nearing 200M.
Prominently placed just off the pace, caught 3-wide with no cover but suited by the soft tempo, contested the lead from 400 M to 200 M, dashed well and drew clear to score final 100 M.
Jumped fast, pressed on to take the lead and found the fence before the first turn, suited by the soft tempo, quickened well at 400 M, kept battling on but headed in by the winner final 100 M.
Held up in a 3-wide rearward position, crept closer when pace slackened rounding the bend, made gradual ground down centre of home straight final 350 M, finished off satisfactorily for 3rd.
Niggled along to hold a fence position 2-3Ls off the pace, overraced when pace slackened midway, checked at 800 M, blocked in early straight, ran on well when clear 200 M out, just lost a place.
Urged along to hold a 3-wide position in midfield, had his chance in the home straight, kept on fairly when placed under pressure at 400 M but lacked a kick to challenge the principals.
Niggled along to reach the one out one back spot, suited by the soft tempo and had every chance in the home straight, gave limited response when asked for efforts final 350 M, only one-paced.
Taken back from the widest alley and travelled rearward on rails, shifted wider for home, finished off fairly well down centre of the straight final 350 M, but only passed the tired runners.

Niggled along to take the box-seat just behind the leader, checked at 800 M, gave very limited response when asked for efforts at the top of the home straight, held ground until outpaced passing 200 M pole.

Jumped fastest, prominently placed within striking distance from the leader, checked at 800 M, lacked a kick when asked for efforts at the top of home straight, outpaced final 250 M, soon dropped out.
Slow to begin, urged along to catch up 5Ls off the speed, blocked and bumped at the top of home straight, failed to make up any ground when clear final 300 M.
Slow to begin, niggled along to hold a fence position in midfield, checked at 800 M, gave no response under pressure in the home straight.
Lacked early speed as usual and travelled 7Ls off the pace, swung widest for home, failed to make any progress.
Broke well, held up in a one-off spot in the mid-division, travelled keenly when restrained in the middle stages, checked at 800 M, made no impression and proven beaten early in home straight.
Held up in the mid-division but caught 4-wide with no cover, crept closer when pace slackened rounding the home turn, failed to keep up and yielded ground final 250 M.
Out in line, ended up in midfield 6Ls or so off pace, suited by tempo in middle stages, improved from 400 M, extended nicely final 200 M to win with some in hand.
Outpaced early stages, raced 3 wide in midfield 6Ls back, had cover to bend, shifted wider turning and closed genuinely down middle, couldn't wear down margin.
No early speed, back behind midfield 7 to 8Ls off top end, tracked eventual winner on bend, in traffic and hampered at 300 M, closed soundly when clear.
Faded back from a wide alley, back 9Ls from top end, aided by strong tempo, took run between horses on turning, worked home nicely from rear.
No early speed, assumed usual role near to rear 8 to 9Ls off leaders, helped with speed on, in traffic turning to 200 M, made some ground when clear.
Drifted back from widest draw, 8Ls off pace 3 wide with cover, suited by circumstances, even wider turning, closed steadily in straight.
Away in line, 3 wide with cover 4 to 5Ls away early, difficult to settle and improved position on bend, kept on to 200 M before run ended.
Crowded at start, soon a clear last, needed urging early stages, best part of 10Ls down on circle, made some minor ground late when race was over.
Average jump, ridden up to hold a spot outside leader, worked with challenge from outside horse, kept going to 250 M, unable to lift when gas ran out.
Bounced to lead, kept a genuine pace on, in 3 way battle on circle, still there to 200 M but stopped soon after due to early work.
Pressed forward, used too much petrol early challenging for front, unable to slot in and posted 3 wide without cover on circle, kept working to turn, hard run took toll final 200 M.
Away reasonably, slotted in 3Ls back on rails, followed a strong speed to bend, urged turning, never really picked up.
Fair beginning, soft trip 6Ls away to turn, saved ground in straight and made some progress to 250 M, weakened out thereafter.
Even getaway, made use of to get a spot on back of speed, did work with decent tempo, under pressure straightening, dropped right out.
Raced fiercely in forward of midfield, slightly closer up around the bend, quickened up well to hit front over 100 M out, won readily.
Raced wide without cover in better than midfield, quickened under pressure after straightening while shifting in away from whip, inconvenienced by winner 100 M out, fought on without threatening.
Raced wide in rear of midfield, ran on nicely to be nearest at finish.
Slowly away, travelled in last few, dropped back to last rounding home bend, no clear passage until 200 M, produced a strong finish.
Soon taken back after beginning from the widest barrier, went wide into straight, produced good late impression down centre of the track.
Quick to take up running, led the field to straight, came under pressure to hold position when about 1L clear 300 M out, gradually overhauled.
Sluggish at start, travelled well behind to straight, making strong progress when badly baulked over 100 M out, never recovered.
Slightly slow out, soon picked up along rails to midfield, took even closer order turning in but failed to quicken to threaten.
Settled toward rear, snuck up on rails down inner of straight to go as close as 2Ls off the lead 200 M out, unable to sustain effort closing stages.
Broke well, travelled in one-out-one-back position around the bend, kept on same pace until crowded and lost ground inside 200 M, never recovered.
Broke well, quickly taken back to last few, trailed the field into straight, went past well-beaten horses.
Began fairly, raced 2-wide in 2L 4th to straight, fighting on doggedly when crowded and lost a lot of ground inside 200 M, never recovered.
Behind midfield when forced to check and lost position about 800 M out, baulked early in straight, kept on same pace without quickening.
Settled one back in 2L 3rd on rails, soon dropped out under pressure after straightening.

Well back early, made swift progress out wide down far side to park in midfield, commenced move and went widest turning for home, fought on determinedly under pressure to just get up on line.
Never far off, lost position when hampered by slackened pace early in back straight, saved ground turning in, hit front under pressure over 200 M out only to be pipped at post.
Began slowly, soon taken across to stalk the field, remained in last few to straight, finished off race strongly to snatch 3rd late. (Tactic questioned.)
Travelled in forward of midfield to straight, kept on well to the line.

Slightly slow out, raced wide in rear of midfield into the stables bend, made rapid progress to take up running 800 M out, went 2Ls clear before coming back to the main field approaching home straight, weakened further in straight.
Quickly driven to take up running, steadied pace turning into back straight, held box seat behind lead from 800 M, amongst leaders turning for home, found nothing under pressure.
Began with others, settled in midfield, shuffled backward around 1000 M bend, saved ground turning for home, kept on steadily without quickening.
Settled towards rear, not much room early in straight, rattled home late.
Never better than midfield, ran home one paced.
Prominent to straight, faded under pressure shortly after straightening.
Slow to jump, soon crossed to rails to race in last few, saved ground turning in, faded inside final 200 M.
Prominent when hampered and lost about 2Ls around 1000 M bend, midfield on rails turning in, weakened under pressure. (Questioned for disappointing performance.)
Tracked the leader along the paint. Railed up in the straight, hit the front after the furlong and went on to score easily.
Bowled along in front on the fence. kept up a sound performance in the run home.
Parked in 2nd position outside the leader. Maintained a solid gallop right to the wire.
Slow to begin settling midfield the fence. Worked home well whilst remaining along the inside.
Camped midfield, 2 wide with cover. Shifted out rounding the home turn but evened out on its run over final 100m.
Settled 1 out 1 back. Weakened over the final stages after having every chance.
Slow to begin then from the outside gate settled at the rear along the rail. Rattled home without threatening.
Raced behind midfield, 3-4 wide, had cover for most of the trip, labored in the final stretch.
Crowded at the start, settling worse than midfield on the fence. Raced greenly for most of the trip and only plodded to the line.
Settled behind midfield, 2 deep with cover. Copped a check near the 600m, failed to close off in the run home.
Was caught out on a limb until slotting in to travel 1 off with cover near the 600m, midfield. Struggled in the straight. (Horse classified as a roarer by vet, post race.)
Began well then was restrained early from a wide gate to settle at the rear of the field, 1 off with cover. Plugged home down the outside. (See incident report.)
Hard ridden early. Settled within 6Ls of the pace on fence from 1400 M. Shaken up and swung out approaching home straight. Dashed well and kept on determinedly final 100 M to repel challengers.

Began awkwardly. Slotted 2-wide towards rear and was 6Ls down 1400 M out. Commenced his run outside field passing 500 M and was 2Ls down turning in. Ran on strongly and battled with the winner final furlong. Just denied.
Slow to begin and stayed towards rear on fence until home turn. Came wide and was 5Ls away on straightening. Rallied on with the front pair but lacked the finishing touch to beat them closing stages.
Raced within 3Ls of the speed in a 2-wide position until home straight. Kept going but failed to match strides with the front trio. Made frame with some comfort.
Prominent spot through to home turn. Contended for lead top of home straight and every chance final 200 M. Unable to sustain its run thereafter.
2-wide behind pace until home turn. Disputed lead leaving the bend. Still in front until overhauled final 150 M.
Slowly away. Raced at rear near the fence. 7Ls adrift turning into home. Covered decent ground thereafter but was of limited significance overall.
Raced within 4Ls of the leader through to home straight. Picked up moderately before steadied at 200 M. Resumed fairly.

Fair start and trapped wide from high draw early. Taken to stay 3-wide towards rear before stable bend. Urged to move closer and was forced to travel wide home turn. Limited progress and past only beaten rivals thereafter.
Travelled 3-wide without cover ahead of midfield until emptied top of home straight.
Never better than midfield. Pressed from 400 M but found nothing.
Ridden vigorously early and took lead on fence eventually from stable bend. Headed shortly after straightening. Faded 150 M.
Out inline, niggled along to lead 1L on rails, joined by another runner from 600 M, quickened well when asked from efforts final 300 M, kept on well to score.
Broke fairly, urged to sit within striking distance from the leader, had every chance in home straight, responded under pressure final 250 M, finished off soundly for 2nd.
Jumped only fairly, caught 4-wide early and strode forward to join the lead midway, raced greenly and hung out at 600 M, kept battling in home straight, just lost the 2nd before the line.
Broke well, easily ran up to track leader in a one-off position, kept on fairly under maximum pressure final 300 M, never threatened the principals.
Taken rearward from his wide gate, 6Ls behind the speed turning for home, made up little ground when placed under pressure final 300 M.
Held up in midfield, improved along 3-deep from 600 M, swung widest for home, only one-paced when asked for efforts.
Jumped fastest, pushed very hard forward to hold a fence position 2 to 3Ls off the pace, hung in at 250 M, could not find extra early in home straight, soon proved beaten.
Sat cosily in midfield on rails, made no impression in home straight.
Slow to begin, sat two from the rear on rails, gave very limited response when asked final 300 M.
Bit slow to begin, sat one-off 4 to 5Ls of the pace, failed to make up any ground in home straight.
Jumped fastest, caught 4-wide with no cover in the mid-division, gave very limited response when asked for efforts in home straight, got tired final 150 M.
Taken back from the widest alley, always at rear, never competitive.
Out in line, held up in a one-off position just behind the mid-division, response well when asked for efforts final 300 M, ran on strongly and hit the lead in the last dew strides.
Widely drawn, easily ran up to sit one out one back, niggled along and quickened well turning for home, kept on well in home straight, no extra final 50 M and headed in just before the line.
Prominently placed just behind the speed, travelled nicely throughout, kept on well in home straight for 3rd, but never troubled the top two.
Taken rearward gate 6 and soon found the fence, patiently ridden until the home turn, finished off fairly well down centre of straight without threatening the principals.
Urged along to hold a one-off position in midfield, swung widest for home, rather one-paced in the straight, no extra final 50 M.
Held up in midfield and travelled nicely on the rails, checked early in straight, finished off only fairly when clear 200 M out.
Taken back from his wide draw and travelled 6Ls off the pace at rear, swung widest for home, only passed the tired runners in the straight.
Widely drawn, niggled along to chase leaders, caught 3-wide with no cover, struggled from the home turn, held ground until flattened final 250 M, soon dropped out.
Eased to a rearward position and travelled 3-wide with cover, finished off only fairly when obtained clear run final 200 M.
Broke only fairly and lacked early speed, urged along to hold a 3-wide position in midfield, no kick early in home straight, soon proved beaten.
Prominently placed 2 to 3Ls off the pace on rails, struggled from 700 M, got tried early in home straight, soon dropped out.
Urged to lead and found the fence at 1400 M, struggled at home turn, soon overhauled and got tired, finished tailed out.
Took rail easily and led by 1L at good pace, never had much challenge.
Pushed to occupy the box seat, ran on well to the line for 2nd without much threats to the winner.
Slow away, at rear, 6.5Ls off the good pace on the rails, made ground steadily 250M and took 3rd.
Eased to sit in front of midfield, 2.5Ls off the good pace, trapped 3 wide throughout, just held ground in final stages.
Bumped start, at back, 4.5Ls off the good pace, trapped 4 wide throughout and lost too much ground, progressed steadily 200M despite all negative situations.
Pushed to obtain prominent spot, 2Ls behind the good pace 2 wide, no turn of foot in straight.
Pushed early to keep up in midfield along the fence, 4Ls off the good pace, lacked turn of foot, just held ground in straight.
Eased back, 5Ls off the good pace, trapped 3 wide throughout and lost ground, raced keenly, blocked 300M, little dash when clear.
Hard ridden forward to sit 1L off the good pace, trapped 3 wide throughout and lost ground, emptied 200M.
Eased to sit in midfield, 4Ls off the good pace 2 wide, held up 4-2, no progress when clear.
Hard ridden forward, trapped 2-3 wide early, parked 1L off the good pace, weakened 200M.
Hard ridden early but failed to muster, never competitive at rear.
Broke well from gate 11 and soon occupied a one-off spot in the mid-division, swung widest for home, launched a strong challenge down centre of the straight, hit the lead at 100 M, kept on to score.
Held up in a 2-wide position just behind midfield, responded well when asked for efforts final 300 M, dashed impressively down centre of home straight, narrowly beaten.
Urged to hold a fence position 2 to 3Ls behind the speed, niggled along rounding bend, finished off soundly final 250 M for 3rd.
Lacked early speed, driven to hold a fence position 6 to 7Ls behind the leader, made gradual progress along the inner final 250 M but never really troubled the placegetters.
Ran up lead 1L and found the fence rounding first bend, kept on fairly well early in home straight but could not find extra final 150 M, remained one-paced under pressure.
Sat cosily in midfield on rails, swung wide for home but got blocked and bumped at 300 M, finished off fairly well when clear late at 150 M.
Widely drawn, held up rearward and travelled 7 to 8Ls off the speed, gave limited response when asked for efforts final 300 M, only passed the beaten rivals final 150 M.
Awkwardly started and travelled one-off close to the rear, made no impression in the home straight.
Taken back from the widest alley and travelled about 10Ls off the pace, made little progress final 250 M but never really a factor.
Prominently placed 2 to 3Ls off the pace, only gave limited response when asked early in straight, flattened final 150 M.
Easily ran up to sit one out one back, kept on early in straight but weakened sharply near 150 M.
Driven to take the box seat just behind the leader, held ground until outpaced final 200 M, soon faded.
Soon crossed to a 2-wide position in midfield after the start, always going well and came with a strong run inside 300 M to strike the front near 50 M. Won with total authority.
Showed good early speed to cross over and took them along unchallenged, drew nicely clear at 200 M, kept on but was unable to repel the impressive winner inside final 50 M.
Jumped well but was restrained to a position behind midfield, used little in running and was a fairway back turning for home, got a run down the outside and stayed on well to go 3rd close home.
Broke well then taken to a midfield spot 5Ls back, battled on in the straight but ran out of it final 100 M and lost 3rd close home.
Soon in last after a sluggish start, along the fence 9 to 10Ls off leader, took time to muster in straight and began to pick up over the final 200 M for some late impression.
Caught wide till 600 M, close enough turning in, had his chance and ran on but couldn't find the extra to seriously challenge.
Taken back from draw 12 and settled in the rear group 10Ls away, had much to do turning in and progressed steadily from the rear inside 300 M without threatening.
Placed ahead of midfield 3 to 4Ls off leader but stayed on only one paced in straight despite being crowded for room near 150 M.
Towards the rear over 8Ls behind, made some progress final 300 M but never threatened.
Jumped ordinary then pushed forward to a one out one back position, couldn't sustain his run in straight and weakened quickly over the final 100 M.
Broke well and tracked leader prominently, under pressure over the home turn and found no extra final 200 M.
Settled behind midfield after an awkward start, looked to be making some progress in early straight but slowed down nearing 200 M, eased. (Jockey said horse appeared to falter in its action.)

Awkward start, close up far side, 2nd outside lead around bend, hit front turning in, won well despite rider dropped rein.
Broke well, settled 2-back in 4th, lost position first turn, fought on but not threatening.
Prominent without cover early, taken back for cover first turn, closer order around bend, failed quicken under pressure.
Well back, shifted wide home turn, finished strongly under pressure.
Well there, 2L 3rd around bend, gradually faded.
Jumped awkward, settled midfield rails, lost position around bend, saved ground home turn, moderate headway under pressure.
Settled midfield, found nothing in straight.
Well back, wide around bend, ran on.
Drawn wide, soon crossed behind, rear of midfield, shifted wide turn, one paced.
Jostled at start, towards rear, blocked in straight till too late.
Jostled at start, took time to find cover behind midfield, progressed wide turn for close-up 5th, no impression in straight.
Restrained to midfield, 3-wide around bend, not far off home turn, faded gradually.
Middle draw, wide with leaders far side, led around bend, dropped out in straight. (Tactic questioned.)
Midfield, dropped out in straight.
Travelled midfield down the outside rail. Battled gamely over the final stages to post a hard fought win.
Was tightened soon after the start, settling close to midfield, 3 off the outside rail. Forged a passage between runners and hit the front near the 100m, was collared close to home.
Recovered after being hampered at the start to settle just behind the speed towards the grandstand side. Maintained a good gallop right to the wire.
Settled with the leading division along the grandstand side. Kept up a sound effort to finish in the frame.
Parked behind midfield towards the centre of the course. Made a grinding effort to finish not far of the placings.
Dictated terms in front at an even tempo towards the outside. Came up short when pressured by other runners over the concluding stages.
Camped midfield close to the outside fence. Worked home steadily despite having to be eased to avoid heels near the 100 M.
Was prominent in the run near the centre of the track. Struck some traffic near the 100m, and was never fully tested thereafter.
Allowed to settle behind the speed, about 4 off the outside fence. failed to quicken at the business end of the race.
Settled towards the rear of the field. Made some steady progress but went to the line one paced.
Settled with the backmakers near the middle of the course. Only plodded to the line.
Travelled worse than midfield about 5 off the grandstand side. Failed to show any dash over the final furlong, and gave ground in the run to the line.
Raced handy to the leaders early, close to the middle of the track, was a spent force by the 200m.
Took up a position towards the rear. Always under pressure and commenced to weaken well before the 300m.

Urged early along the fence to stay in touch towards rear. Moved closer and was 5Ls down rounding the turn. Took inside run and picked up gradually on straightening. Dashed well passing 200M and caught the leader near post.
Disputed lead in a 2-wide position through to home straight. Ran on well and hit front 200M. Looked set for victory until the winner flashed home closing stages.
Ridden along after fair start. Travelled 3-wide behind pace approaching home turn. Kept on in the straight but couldn't reel in the front pair.
Slow to begin. Under pressure early and raced 2-wide behind midfield 800M out. Swung widest and was 5Ls away on straightening. Covered good ground and was nearest at finish.
Away in line. Soon driven to race 2-wide behind leading section. Plugged on in the straight without serious threat to the front trio. (Abnormal breathing noise.)
Shaken up early. Disputed lead on fence from 900M. Hung on until headed 200M. Not beaten far.
Pressed early but could only maintain a spot behind midfield on fence. 3Ls off turning into home. One-paced to conclude.
Jumped well but was trapped 4-wide. Elected to sit 3-wide better than midfield from 900M. Every chance in the straight but couldn't turn up a notch.
Well enough away and took prominent spot 900M out. Ran on in the straight without troubling the principals.
Quickly into stride but was caught wide. Gradually dropped to midfield in a 4-wide position from 1000M. Came wide and was 4Ls down turning in. Finished off fairly.
Began awkwardly and raced at rear on fence until home straight. Passed only beaten rivals thereafter.
Raced 2-wide behind midfield early. Shuffled further back when crowded for room near 850M. Never recovered.
Travelled wide and without cover ahead of midfield until top of home straight. Faded thereafter.
Always at rear. No impression.
Niggled along to occupy the fence position just behind the leader, ran on strongly under hands and heels riding final 350 M, hit the lead at 100 M and scored easily.
Jumped fastest, urged along to lead on rails, opened up a 3Ls gap rounding the home turn, quickened well when asked for efforts final 300 M, reeled in by the winner 100 M out, kept on for 2nd.
Jumped fastest, prominently placed 3Ls off the speed, finished off well under maximum pressure final 350 M, just did enough for a place.
Lacked early speed despite being urged along, ran on strongly down centre of home straight final 350 M, just late for a place.
Held up in the midfield, caught 4-wide and pulled hard in the middle stages, finished off well when asked for efforts final 300 M, but only offered little threat to the placegetters.
Drawn gate 14, caught very wide with no cover in early stages, ended up travelling 3-wide in the mid-division, only one-paced when placed under pressure in home straight.
Occupied a fence position in the mid-division easily, niggled along turning for home, responded only fairly when asked for efforts final 400 M, flattened passing the 200 M pole.
Slow to begin, settled one from the rear about 8Ls off the speed, made some late progress final 250 M but only passed the tired rivals.
Lacked early despite being urged along, travelled 6-7Ls behind the leader, struggled round the bend, failed to make up any ground in the home straight.
Jumped fastest, allowed to drift back in the mid-division, travelled in a one-off spot 4Ls off the speed, gave no response when placed under pressure in the home straight.
Lacked early speed, travelled rearward and caught 3-wide, made no impression in the home straight.
Bumped start, always rearward, made little progress in the home straight, never a factor.
Broke only fairly, raced on-pace but travelled keenly without cover, held ground until got tired 300 M out, yielded ground quickly.
Slow to begin, driven to hold a fence position in midfield, checked at 800 M, struggled turning for home, weakened at the top of straight, finished tailed out.
Easily ran up to lead and found the fence passing 1000 M pole, suited by the soft tempo, left contested until final 200 M, kept on soundly to score.
Out in line, held up in a one-off spot within striking distance from the leader, responded well when asked for efforts final 300 M, finished off strongly but the line came too soon.
Prominently placed 1-2Ls behind the leader, travelled nicely throughout, kept on soundly in home straight for 3rd.
Niggled along to take the box-seat just behind the leader, suited by the soft tempo, kept battling on in home straight, lacked a kick final 100 M and lost a place.
Travelled one-off in the mid-division, obtained clear run early in home straight, but finished off only well enough for a dead-heat 4th. (Mucus.)
Awkwardly start, ended up in a rearward position on rails, held up for room early in home straight, made up gradual ground when clear final 250 M, too late.
Jumped fast and soon settled in midfield on rails, lacked a kick when asked for effort final 400 M, very one-paced.
Broke fastest from gate 11 but soon taken to the rear, made gradual improvement along the inner final 350 M but never really troubled the principals.
Out in line, taken to the division and caught 4-wide with no cover, travelled keenly when restrained in the early and middle stages, only passed the beaten rivals in the home straight.
Widely drawn, taken to the rear and travelled 6Ls off the pace, niggled along turning for home, checked 350 M out, never recovered.
Intended to ease back from the widest alley, found very difficult to settled when caught 5-wide with no cover, strode forward from 1000M out, weakened sharply final 300 M.
Settled 3-deep in the mid-division, swung widest for home, finished off only fairly, failed to make up any ground in the straight.
Awkwardly started, caught wide and found very difficult to settle in the early and middle stages, got tired and lost touch at the top of home straight, finished tailed out.
Eased to rear for cover, 7Ls off the leader 3-4 wide, harmed by the slow pace, made early move 600M, dashed well to the line and scored its first victory.
Behind midfield, 5.5Ls off the leader 2 wide, harmed by the slow tempo, held up 4-2, dashed well when clear and took 2nd.
Eased to rear, 8.5Ls off the leader, trapped 3-4 wide throughout and lost too much ground, dashed strongly 300M despite not suited by the slow pace, just missed 2nd in last few strides.
Midfield, 4Ls off the leader, trapped 3 wide throughout, harmed by the slow pace, little dash in straight.
Eased to sit in midfield, 4Ls off the leader 2 wide, not suited by the slow tempo, lacked turn of foot, ran on OK in final stages.
Eased to rear and took rail, 7Ls off the leader, checked severely 800M, harmed by the slow pace, little dash 200M despite all negative racing situations.
Eased back, 5.5LS off the leader 3 wide, not suited by the slow tempo, just held ground in straight.
Very slow away, behind midfield along the fence, 5.5Ls off the leader, checked badly 800M, harmed by the slow pace, held up most straight, never tested.
Pushed forward, 2.5Ls off the leader, enjoyed the slow sectionals but trapped 3 wide, flattened 300M.
Hard ridden to cross in front, led by 1L at slow sectionals, hung on until 250M overhauled and weakened.
In front of midfield, 2.5Ls off the leader 2 wide, harmed by the slow pace, pushed back 400M, held up until 200M, flattened when clear.
Pushed to sit in front of midfield along the fence, checked badly 800M, not suited by the slow pace, blocked most straight, flattened when clear.
Hard ridden to occupy the box seat, checked 800M, suited by the slow tempo, faded 400M.
Settled just off the leader 2 wide, benefited by the slow pace, however dropped off 300M. (See Racing Incidents.)

Given a waiting ride as usual and travelled 8Ls off the pace just behind mid-division, crept closer rounding bend, dashed impressively down centre of home straight when asked final 350 M, hung in at 200 M, drew clear to score easily.
Driven to hold a one-off position in midfield, responded well when asked for efforts final 300 M, checked at 200 M, soon recovered and ran on soundly for 2nd. (Objection overruled.)
Jumped only fairly, niggled along to hold a one-off position 3-4Ls off the speed, ran on steadily when placed under pressure final 300 M but soon overhauled by the winner, kept on for a place.

Awkwardly started, taken rearward to sit 10Ls behind the leader, travelled nicely on rails, niggled along from 650 M and swung wide for home, made gradual progress down centre of the straight, too late for a place.
Jumped only fairly, sat cosily just behind the pace, quickened to challenge the leader from 600 M, kept on well early in home straight, overhauled at 250 M, remained one-paced.
Broke well, prominently placed about 4Ls behind the speed, never properly clear in home straight, not fully tested.
Easily ran up to lead 1L, left contested until the home turn, kept on until overhauled passing 200 M, soon got tired.
Out in line, given a waiting ride as usual and travelled over 10Ls behind the leader, niggled along rounding bend, made up little ground final 250 M.
Settled 3Ls behind the speed, travelled nicely in early and middle stages, held ground early in home straight but could not find extra to challenge the principals final 150 M.
Out in line, held up in a fence position in midfield, gave very limited response when asked final 400 M, never a factor.
Broke well, taken rearward and travelled about 10Ls off the pace, pulled hard when being restrained in the early stages, made no progress in home straight, never competitive.

In midfield and not hurried in early stages, moved into contention approaching the straight, swept to the lead 250M, kept finding what was required to hold off the persistent runner-up and stretched his unbeaten record to six.

Travelled well a fair way back in 6th, responded well inside 400M and came through inside to challenge, rallied on when the eventual winner ranged alongside, refused to give up and fought all the way to the line.
Positioned in 4th in what was a strongly run race, ideally placed to strike turning in, didn't quite have the pace of the front pair but kept on well enough to hold on for 3rd.
Along the fence in midpack, behind horses turning for home and had to be switched for a run, clear inside 250M but couldn't peg back the first two.
Towards the rear over 10Ls back, waited with till 450M, made steady headway and did best of those to come from off the pace.
Placed 3-wide in mid-division and raced without cover in the first half, stayed on final 400M but could not find another gear when it was needed.
Behind midfield over 10Ls back in middle stages, shakened up passing 600M but responded only fairly, battled on to the line but couldn't find the extra pace to challenge seriously.
In 3rd 6Ls behind the runaway leader, crept closer over the turn but could find only the one pace final 400M and never looked like winning.
Way off the pace in 2nd last, headway from 400M then ran into traffic 250M, ran on again once switched but couldn't reach leaders.
Switched off out the back and trailed over 12Ls in middle stages, kept to inside throughout and could make very limited progress in early straight before fading late on.

Gradually crossed from draw 14, went a strong gallop upfront and kicked 4Ls clear in middle stages, was pegged back over the final turn and had no extra left when headed 350M. (Trainer and Jockey questioned.)
4Ls back chasing leader which went off a strong pace, joined the lead passing 550M but found little when asked in straight, weakened inside 300M.
3-wide behind mid-division and left with no cover from 800M, swung widest into straight, not picked up and was eased over final 150M.
Placed 2-wide behind midfield 10Ls off the strong pace, struggled passing 600M and was beaten a long way.
Broke well and soon found an ideal position about 2Ls behind the leader, responded well when asked for efforts final 300 M, hit the lead 250 M, drew clear to score with some in tank.
Prominently placed in a fence position in midfield, checked at 700 M, held up for room at the top of home straight, ran on soundly final 250 M but never really threatened the winner.

Taken back from gate 14 and travelled about 10Ls behind the speed, shifted widest for home, made ground strongly down centre of straight when asked for efforts final 350 M, nicked the 3rd in the final stride.
Lacked early speed, urged along to catch up 8Ls off the pace, improved along the inner of home straight under pressure, finished off soundly but just missed out a place in the final stride.
Held up in a rearward position and travelled 8Ls off the pace, no cover in early stages, ran on bravely between horses final l350 M, just missed out a place.
Broke well, niggled along to share the lead, 1L clear turning for home, kept on fairly well early in straight, overhauled by the winner at 200 M, could not find extra and lost a place final 50 M.

Jumped only fairly, driven to hold a one-off position 3Ls behind the leader, had every chance in home straight and looked possible for a place final 200 M, but failed to keep up in the last few strides.

Prominently placed in a fence position 3Ls off the speed, niggled along rounding bend, made ground steadily along the inner early in home straight, checked at 200 M, remained one-paced after the interference.
Taken back from gate 12 and travelled about 9Ls off the pace at rear, finished off well under pressure final 300 M but only passed the tired rivals.
Sat one-off in the mid-division, caught 3-wide and lost cover rounding bend at 700 M, gave very limited response when placed under pressure final 350 M, proved beaten passing the 200 M pole.
Bit slow to begin, travelled in a fence position just behind midfield, made no impression in home straight.
Lacked early speed despite being urged along, travelled 3-wide with no cover just behind the mid-division, failed to make up any ground in home straight.
Pressed on to contest the lead in early stages, struggled turning for home, got tired early in straight, yielded ground quickly.
Awkwardly started, sat in a 3-wide position just behind the midfield, broke down near 300 M, eased out.
Out in line, ended up 3 wide in midfield, had a trail 5Ls off leaders in mid-section, improved on turn, stuck to task in straight snatching victory right on wire.
Began with rest, posted 3 wide without cover 3 to 4Ls back, did work in mid-section, improved 4 wide approaching bend, dug in and hit front at 200 M, overhauled late.
Fastest to begin, pressed on to take up running, set even sections in front, kept on bravely in straight losing advantage final 150 M.
No speed and faded back to rear from a wide alley, best part of 7 to 8Ls back at tail, still plenty to do on turning, made remarkable progress in straight to be nearest on line.
Awkwardly away, pressed on to take a prominent spot 1 out 1 back, all favours in run to turn, came 3 wide straightening, place chance to 100 M before run ended.
Only fairly away, urged into a spot behind midfield 5Ls away in running line, reasonable trip to turn, closed off gradually to be nearest on line.
Drifted back from a wide alley, raced 3 wide with a trail 6Ls back to bend, made some even progress in straight to be closest at finish.
Jumped OK, elected for a trail in midfield 4 to 5Ls off lead, travelled kindly throughout, not far away turning, battled away holding ground without threatening.
Reasonable beginning, held spot behind leader, had a decent trip to bend, took inside runs but was one-paced final 200 M.
Out with rest, raced 3Ls away on rails, had an easy time and saved ground on bend, just kept on in behind horses in straight.
No early speed, shared rear on rails, 7 to 8Ls off top end, still well back to turn, passed only tired horses late.
Fair to begin, 5Ls away on rails throughout, saved ground on turn, held up early straight and didn't see much daylight until 100 M when too late.
Began well, too keen early and was closer than expected, still level with leader on bend, struggling soon after turning and faded out.
Slowly away, back with last few 7Ls off speed, no excuses in run, lacked a pick up and never produced a finish. Disappointing.
