Drawn wide, ridden early, crossed to 2L 3rd on rails before bend, shifted out to challenge home bend, hit front 200 M out, scored easily.
Jostled at start losing ground, gradually recovered far side to midfield, sustained steady progress down straight to be nearest at finish.
Made use of good draw to lead, headed 200 M out, weakened.
Soon taken back to race in midfield on rails, took closer order around the bend, close up turning in, failed to quicken to make any impression.
Towards rear, made good progress in straight to do best work late.
Drawn wide, settled wide in midfield, drifted widest turning for home, hung out and a difficult ride in straight.
Squeezed at start, remained towards rear, saved ground turning in, fought on steadily without quickening.
Driven along from a poor draw to be just better than midfield, failed to quicken under pressure in straight.
Slightly slow out, travelled just worse than midfield, ran home one paced.
3-wide in forward of midfield, shifted wide turning in, found nothing under pressure in straight.
Well there outside leader most of way to straight, faded away noticeably.
Never seen with a chance.
Missed the start settling midfield 2 deep with cover. Swung about 4 wide turning for home, steered out into clear running near the 300m and went to the wire full of running to score a strong win.
Settled 3 wide with cover behind the leading quartet. Shot to the lead near the 200m, but was mowed down inside the last 50M.
Rallied early to camp on the back of the leaders along the rail. Fenced up in the straight and kept on soundly after having every chance.
Slow to begin settling behind midfield the fence. Had some difficulty obtaining clear running near the 150m, went to the post one paced thereafter.
Settled with the backmakers, 1 off with cover. Worked to the outside in the straight an got to the line fairly.
Tracked the leading group 1 off with cover on the circle. Failed to make any impression after enjoying a nice run in the race.
Ridden along early to take up a forward position, then was settled to take up a trailing position near the 600m, 4 wide with cover. Weakened in the run to the line.
Pressed forward and assumed the fence after the 500m whilst vying for the lead. Faded over the final 200m.
Burnt plenty of petrol to race with the leaders 2-3 wide, no cover. Struggled over the final furlong after having hit the front early in the final stretch.
Travelled a distinct last 1 off with cover. Failed to close off.
Hard ridden from the outside alley to race prominently but coursed 4-5 wide without cover. Was a spent force after the 400M.

Not the best away but soon gathered momentum to surge forward from a wide gate. Unable to cross and was posted 3-4 wide, no cover in the leading division. Was gassed early in the straight. (Blood in the trachea.)
Soon led on fence. Opened a 2Ls gap turning in. Never seriously challenged.
Crowded after a fair start. Got the fence at midfield passing 1100 M. Urged along 400 M out. Kept making up ground inside to snatch 2nd without troubling the winner.
Broke nicely. Elected to take prominent spot from first turn. Ran on steadily in the straight but couldn't catch the leader. Outrun by the 2nd placegetter final 100 M but hung on for 3rd.
Sat 2-wide behind midfield through to the home turn. 6Ls behind the leader entering final stretch. Made decent headway to make frame but was not threatening to the front trio.
Last out. 4-wide at rear first turn. Found the fence behind midfield from 900 M. 6Ls behind speed on straightening. Picked up steadily before checked 100 M. Resumed fairly well.

Good jump but trapped 5-wide. Slotted in 3-wide ahead of midfield at 900 M. Ridden approaching the Rock and settled 2-wide 2Ls behind leader home turn. Failed to sustain its run home straight. One-paced final stages.
Well enough away but was caught extremely wide. Gradually eased to sit 3-wide towards rear making first turn. Swung widest and was 7Ls off leaving the bend. Covered decent ground thereafter.
Taken to rear from high draw. Stayed on fence and was 7Ls behind the pace turning into home. Progressed moderately until checked at 100 M. Just ran on thereafter.
Travelled 3-wide at midfield through to home turn. No extra in the straight.
Began well but was trapped very wide. Gradually taken to rear in a 2-wide position from 900 M. Past beaten rivals in the straight but no real improvement.
2-wide behind midfield until home turn. Found nothing when asked 400 M out. Beaten soon after straightening.
2-wide behind speed early and middle stages. Pressed on home turn but no response. Overhauled 200 M.
Broke well, led 3-wide at first turn, crossed to rail near 1200 M, dictated the pace, strongly challenged final 200 M, just held on.
Broke well, took position in 3rd on rail behind leader, sustained challenge straight, just failed to get up.
Reined back to second last from wide draw, travelled well, pulled wide to challenge straight, finished strongly, good effort.
Slow away, ridden, but last early, pulled out to challenge in straight, finished well but too much to do.
Took good early position one off rail behind leader, tried to match strides with eventual winner in straight but could not get past, no extra, faded.
Ridden early but not pace to take better than 4th on the outside, 5th in back straight, tried to improve three wide, hard ridden, weakened.
Midfield on rail, niggled approaching straight then hard driven, not enough pace to challenge.
Ridden early, but not enough pace to take advantage of favourable draw, never travelling well, found little in straight.
Slightly slow from gate. Took good position on rail in fourth far side, ridden entering straight, no kick.
Broke well, but 4-wide first turn, pulled briefly early in back straight, ridden wide straight, no response.
No pace early, settled on rail in 3rd last, ridden on rail in straight, found nothing.
Looked for position from outside draw but still well wide first turn, and always wide thereafter., weak move far side, last into straight, weakened.
Driven to lead at fast tempo and found the fence near 1100 M, quickened at 600 M and created a 3Ls gap, kept on well in home straight under maximum pressure, scored without being really threatened.
Pressed on to take the box-seat just behind the leader, 3Ls off the pace turning for home, responded well when asked for efforts final 300 M, kept on soundly for 2nd.
Urged along to take a fence position 2Ls off the speed, placed under pressure rounding the home bend, made ground steadily in the home straight, did enough to keep a place.
Broke well, urged along in the early stages and ended up in the mid-division holding the rails, obtained clear run passing 200 M pole, made ground steadily, just late for a place.

Bit slow away, travelled in a one-off spot 6Ls off the pace, niggled along rounding bend and swung widest for home, covered some ground down centre of home straight, but never really troubled the principals.
Driven early, held up rounding the first bend when caught wide but soon found the fence just behind midfield, made little progress when clear at 200 M.
Given a waiting ride and travelled over 10Ls away at the rear, shifted widest for home, covered some ground down centre of the home straight, but only passed the beaten rivals.
Lacked early speed as usual and travelled 8 to 9Ls off the speed one from the rear, niggled along rounding home turn, only passed the tired runners in home straight, never a factor.
Travelled 2 or 3-wide just off the pace, held ground until outpaced 200 M out.
Lacked early speed despite being pushed hard along, travelled 8Ls off the pace on rails, failed to make up any ground.
Jumped fast from gate 12, caught wide early until allowed to shifted in near 1100 M, travelled 4Ls off the speed in midfield, struggled rounding the bend, proved beaten at the top of home straight.
Driven to find the one out one back spot, outpaced when tempo quickened at home turn, yielded ground from the top of the straight.
Took rail easily and led by 1L at fast early sectionals, strongly benefited by the rail-run, made all.
Pushed to hold the box seat, not suited by the fast tempo but strongly favoured by the rail-run, closed the race off well to the line for 2nd.

Eased back for cover, 4Ls off the leader 2 wide, suited by the fast tempo, made early move 900M around the field in 4 wide, kept launching well to the line despite the amount of energy being used at home bend, solid 3rd.
Settled in front of midfield along the fence, 3Ls off the fast pace, benefited by the rail-run, made steadily ground 300 M.
Eased to rear, 6Ls off the leader 2-3 wide, favoured by the fast tempo, progressed steadily in straight.
Pushed early to obtain a midfield spot, trapped 3 wide throughout and lost too much ground on bends, 3-1/2Ls off the fast pace, held ground in straight despite all negative racing situations.
Eased back, 6-1/2Ls off the leader on the rails, benefited by the fast pace, switched 3 wide to improve round the home bend, made minor ground 200M.

Pushed early but failed to muster and to cross, trapped 3-4 wide throughout without cover and lost significant amount of ground on bends, sat 1-1/2Ls off the leader, harmed by the fast pace, emptied 250M.
Eased to sit in midfield, 4-1/2Ls off the leader 2 wide, helped by the fast pace, however being carried back at prominent stage from 600M and lost ground, ran on ok in straight.
Checked early, eased to sit behind midfield, 6-1/2Ls off the leader along the fence, suited by the fast tempo, no progress at any stages.
Sat just off the leader 2 wide, used up too much fuel during the fast early sectionals, faded 500M.
Pushed to occupy a prominent spot, 2-1/2Ls off the leader 2 wide, not suited by the fast tempo, dropped off rapidly 600 M.
Jumped fastest and driven to lead 1L on rails, kept on strongly in the home straight, drew clear final 150 M, scored very easily.
Pressed on to occupy the box-seat just behind the pacesetter, attempted to fight for lead early in home straight, could not match the strides of the winner final 150 M but did keep on well for 2nd.
Awkward start, held up in a fence position just behind the midfield, responded well when asked for efforts final 300 M finished off soundly for 3rd.
Broke fastest, took time to muster and caught 3-wide early, urged along to chase the leader in middle stages, kept battling on in home straight and looks at least for a place, just missed out.
Out in line, driven to travel one-off 2 to 3Ls off the pace, swung widest for home, only one-paced when asked for efforts final 300 M.
Bit slow to begin, niggled along to catch up to mid-division but caught 3-wide with no cover, finished off fairly well down centre of home straight without offering threats to the principals.
Cozily placed on rails in the mid-division, niggled along rounding the bend, had every chance in home straight but finished off disappointingly, failed to make any progress.
Taken to the rear from gate 12, patiently ridden until the home straight, only made very limited progress along the inner.
Prominently sat 1-2Ls behind the leader, responded only fairly when asked for efforts early in the home straight, could not find extra final 100 M, soon dropped out.
Given a waiting ride as usual and travelled 7 to 8Ls off the pace, swung widest for home, gave no response when asked for efforts final 250 M, never competitive.
Lacked early speed and ended up traveling rearward 6Ls off the pace, outpaced rounding the home turn, proved beaten soon after entering the straight.
Out in line but soon drifted back towards the rear, travelled 3-wide throughout, failed to make up any ground in the home straight.
Given a positive ride and sat handily just off leaders, driven near 400 M and swept to the front 250 M out, battled well when strongly challenged by the runner-up in late stages. Won gutsily.
Badly hampered soon after the jump, raced with last few before going forward passing 600 M, kicked clear along with the winner final 200 M, put in good late work but was always held.

Unable to cross on jumping from draw 10, dropped back to midfield for cover, attempted a narrow run down the inside final 350 M, kept on for a non threatening 3rd. (Jockey questioned re his riding from 300 M to 200 M.)
Behind midfield and not used in early stages, 6Ls down turning in, made some progress final 300 M and just missed out on 3rd.
Slow to begin, ended up in the rear group 6Ls behind leaders, effort inside 500 M, stayed on down the outside but never looked like catching the first two which went well clear.
Emerged to lead from 1100 M and went a sound gallop up front, under pressure nearing 400 M, kept on till 200 M and found no extra in late stages.
Pressed on to obtain a rail position soon after the start, never far off leaders but couldn't find another gear when the race got serious, weakened inside 150 M.
Taken across from a wide barrier, settled in 2nd last 7Ls behind leader, driven 400 M from home but found limited response only, checked near 250 M.
Placed in midfield along the fence, steadied near 250 M but could keep on at the same pace only when clear.
Restrained to a midfield position 5Ls back, checked at 500 M and shuffled further back, found nothing in straight and eased over final 200 M.
Slow to muster, caught wide over the first turn then moved gradually to the front down the back straight, under pressure inside 400 M and dropped rapidly out of the race.
Went forward and pressed the pace in early stages, gave ground from 500 M and dropped to last approaching home straight, heavily eased. (Unacceptable Performance.)

In touch, loomed up outside leader 350M, quickened well and was always in control once going to the front.
Shared lead and kicked well clear inside 300M, couldn't fend off the winner but ran a respectable race in defeat under a 7lb penalty.
Positively ridden to obtain the lead along the stand's rail, lacked a turn of foot to threaten the first two but stayed on best of the rest.
Handily placed just off the pace, kept on but lacked pace to mount a serious challenge final 300M.
In midpack not far off leaders, hard driven from halfway but could remain at the same pace only.
Raced prominently on the outside of field, couldn't quicken under pressure 400M out, gradually weakened.
Towards the rear but found very little when asked inside 400M. No impression.
Behind midfield but never far off the pace, struggled to keep up passing 400M and had no extra left in late stages.
At the rear throughout, under pressure halfway, well beaten.
Strolled to the lead early and made every post a winner, drawing away over the final 200m.
Parked 3 back, 1 off with cover. Peeled out on the home turn and maintained a sound gallop right to the wire.
Raced in second position 1 off, about a length behind the pacesetter. Improved to travel within a length of the leader, but failed to quicken thereafter. Battled on gamely to finish in the frame.
Settled midfield 2-3 wide with cover. Recovered from being hampered near the 600m to make steady ground without threatening in the run home.
Travelled behind midfield 2-3 wide with cover. Angled widest in the straight and worked home one paced.
Settled on the back of the speed but was posted 3 wide without cover on the circle. Only paddled to the finish line.
Slow to begin settling midfield the fence. struggled in the final stretch after blundering badly near the 600m.
Enjoyed the run of the race on the back of the leader along the paint. Had no excuses, weakened appreciably in the last furlong.
Raced 4 deep with cover, slightly worse than midfield. Only plodded home.

Began well, shifted out soon after the start then despite being ridden along didn't muster speed. Was obliged to course wide and without cover, 4 deep for most of the trip close to midfield. Never likely.
Settled towards the rear along the fence. Never fired a shot in the home straight and weakened noticeably in the run to the line.

Placing: UR
Comment: Not the best away, then rider expressed concern regarding his saddle shifting whilst racing in last spot. Rider was dislodged early in the straight.
Raced 2-wide behind midfield early. Improved gradually from 700M and was 3-wide 3Ls down on straightening. Finished off strongly and took control final stages.
Hard ridden to lead on fence before taking seat 2Ls behind the pace making home turn. Battled with the leader in the straight but both were unable to contain the winner closing stages.
2 to 3-wide behind midfield early. Took inside run and was 4Ls away approaching home straight. Closed off satisfactorily to nick 3rd and was nearest at finish.
Urged to go forward from high draw. Led one-off the fence from 800M. Maintained a 1L advantage turning in. Fought on until headed by the front pair 150M.
Raced within 4Ls of the pace in a 2-wide position. Ran on in the straight but was not threatening to the principals.
Never far off the pace but couldn't turn up a notch when the race got serious.
Settled 2-wide towards rear early. 6Ls behind the lead rounding the bend. Just held ground in the straight.
Prominent position through to home straight but couldn't pull out extra thereafter.
Taken to race 2-wide at rear from high draw. Swung wide turning into home but was held up until 250M. Finished off moderately once into clear.
Sat 3-wide behind midfield throughout and never really improved from there.
Pressed early to stay behind midfield on fence but ended up towards rear turning in. Never recovered.
Always at rear. Very limited response when asked in the straight.
Travelled wide and without cover ahead of midfield until no extra on straightening.
3-wide behind midfield early and middle stages. Pressured approaching final stretch but no response. Faded thereafter.
Broke smartly from stall 2 to lead on outside after 200m, crossed to one off near rail after 200m, soon clear, ridden out, unchallenged, eased last 50m.
Tracked across from number 1 draw into midfield, improved between runners, closed well on winner last 100m, but never looked like getting to him.
Broke well, raced one off rail in 5th, scrubbed along from halfway, kept on steadily along rail without threatening winner.
Broke well, among leaders on near side rail until headed after 200m by winner, bustled along and stayed on but never pace to challenge.
Broke smartly, headed early. Kept on in centre of track but never got in a blow at the leader.
Broke awkwardly but took good position on rail in second, hard ridden 200m out but weakened quickly.
Good break, tracked leader, ridden halfway, no response, weakened.
Broke well but unable to maintain good early position, hard ridden, ran on through beaten horses late.
Put head in air shortly after start but quickly recovered, tracked leaders on outside, ridden 200m out, found nothing.
Could never go the early pace, passed beaten stragglers late on.
Lost a length at start, never near front rank, ridden from 400m out but ran out of steam last 100m.
Couldn't go early pace, always under pressure on outside of field, never a factor.
Good break, took position on rail, but bustled along very early, gradually lost ground.
Slow away and two lengths last early, ridden before halfway, passed to then weakened back into last place.
Lost ground start, unhurried down back straight travelling comfortably on rail, challenged on inside to take lead 100m out and gradually pull away.
Fifth on rail early, moved closer entering straight, challenged in centre and ran on well without being able to resist winner's finishing surge.
Broke well, but no early urgency, 6th one off rail far side, urged forward entering straight, pulled wide to challenge, ran on but no match for front two.
Slowly away, ridden, but slipped back to third last far side, back on bit briefly just before entering straight, ran on well but perhaps didn't give full co-operation throughout the race.
Broke well but then gradually slipped back through field although urged to hold position, ridden early in straight, then hard ridden, ran on quite well but lacked punch.
Broke fairly well, urged to keep place midfield one off rail far side, shaken up early in straight, challenged mid track, lacked pace to reach leaders.
Unhurried early, raced 6 from rear down far side, but niggled, made a little ground in straight but could not get to leaders under driving.
Slow into stride although ridden, 3rd last and pushed along far side, closed entering straight, ran on under pressure before weakening final 50m.
Unhurried early and tacked over to rail from wide draw, 4th last one off the rail far side, pulled wide to challenge, drifted to near rail, not quick enough to threaten.
Scrubbed along to get early position in second, 4th on outside back straight, shaken up and driven in straight, hampered by horse going past him 200m out, weakened.
Ridden up from high draw to take 4th on outer far side, moved to within length of leader entering straight, led briefly 300m, then swamped by the pack.
Allowed to find own pace from outside draw, second last far side, last into straight, pulled wide and ran on briefly, weakened.
Ridden early to take forward position on rail, needed mild encouragement far side, pulled out to challenge straight, found nothing.
Broke fast and scrubbed along to lead until pressed entering straight, soon folded, long last.
Pushed to obtain a comparatively more prominent spot, 3Ls off the leader, trapped 3 wide, not suited by the slow pace, closed the race off strongly 300M to score.
Midfield on the rails, 4.5Ls off the leader, harmed by the slow pace, dashed strongly 250M to grab a strong 2nd.
Pushed to take the rail and led by 1L at advantageous slow sectionals, hung on strongly until 100M when overhauled, ran on for 3rd.
Trapped 3 wide throughout in midfield, 4.5Ls off the leader, harmed by the slow pace, dashed well 300M despite all negative racing situations.
Hard ridden to obtain a prominent spot but trapped 3-4 wide throughout, favoured by the slow tempo, flattened 200M.
Hard ridden to occupy the box seat, enjoyed the slow early sectionals, weakened 200M.
Eased to sit in front of midfield, 3Ls off the leader 2-3 wide, not suited by the slow tempo, no progress.
Eased at start to cross at rear for cover, 7.5LS off the leader 2 wide, overraced and harmed by the slow pace, just ran on OK in straight.
Eased back, 6Ls off the leader 2-3 wide, harmed by the slow pace, no dash in straight.
Hard ridden to hold the rail in front of midfield, 3Ls off the leader, not suited by the slow tempo, flattened 300M.
Bumped start, pushed to sit behind midfield, 6Ls off the leader 2 wide, harmed by the slow pace, no turn of foot in final stages.
Hard ridden to sit in midfield 2 wide, not suited by the slow pace, never competitive.
Eased back, not suited by the slow pace, never a factor.
Awkward away, hard ridden forward, trapped 5 wide early, crossed to 2 wide and sat 1L off the slow pace prior to home bend, dropped off 400M.
Out in line, held up one-off in the mid-division, responded well when asked for efforts final 350 M, finished off strongly and hit the lead in the final few strides.
Prominently placed 2Ls off the speed, dashed well to take the lead 250 M out, kept on well but headed in by the winner inside 50M.
Prominently sat 3Ls behind the leader, responded well when placed under pressure final 350 M, finished off soundly for 3rd.

Taken rearward from the wide drawn, travelled keenly when restrained in the early and middle stages, swung widest for home, covered substantial ground down centre of home straight, hung in, just late for a place.
Niggled along to lead and soon found the fence, overhauled near 250 M, kept on fairly under maximum pressure, could not find extra and lost a place inside 50 M.
Very slow to begin and travelled 9Ls behind the pace at the rear, made up gradual ground down centre of home straight final 350 M without really threatening the principals.
Urged along to hold a fence position 2Ls behind the speed, gave limited response when asked for efforts final 400 M, held ground until flattened near 100 M.
Broke only fairly, taken to a 2-wide spot just behind the mid-division, swung widest for home, only one-paced under pressure, passed some beaten rivals in the concluding stages.
Lacked early speed as usual and travelled one from the rear rear 8Ls behind the pace, took time to obtain clear run at the top of home straight, finished only fairly when clear at 200 M.
Urged to hold a fence position 3Ls behind the pace, niggled along rounding bend, on heels at 350 M and 200 M, responded only fairly when asked for efforts, held ground until flattened final 150 M.
Driven to take the one out one back spot, held ground until flattened near 300 M, soon weakened.
Niggled along to sit 2-3 Ls off the pace, caught 3-wide with no cover in the early and middle stages, finished off disappointingly in home straight, outpaced final 250 M, soon dropped out.
Never better than midfield, failed to make any progress in home straight.
Urged along to hold a 3-wide position in midfield, struggled rounding bend, flattened and yielded ground final 350 M, finished tailed out.
Soon driven to the lead and set a decent pace upfront, strongly challenged final 250M and despite being headed, rallied back to regain the lead 100M from home.
Held up in midfield 7Ls back, had to be shifted for a clear run passing 300M, closed off the race well but met interference close home. (Promoted from 3rd.)
Vied for early lead, restrained back to 2nd passing 1000M, responded well under urge and took a slender lead 150M but couldn't sustain his effort and drifted out in late stages.
Placed ahead of midfield and had a smooth run along the fence, stayed on well to the line without ever looking like getting to the leaders.
Taken to 3rd under a positive ride, well placed to strike turning in, had every chance but was unable to make headway on leaders.
From a wide draw crossed to a midfield position 2 off the fence, progressed from 400M and did best work late.
Settled 2-wide behind midfield, held up early in straight but found less than expected when clear passing 300M.
Hard ridden out the gate but lacked early speed, ended up towards the rear over 10Ls back at one stage, responded fairly inside 400M, never threatened.
Placed behind mid-division 3-wide, had plenty to do turning in, made limited progress down the outside, drifted in under pressure final 150M.
Given a waiting ride towards the tail of the field, not used till inside 400M, switched widest to challenge but ran on only fairly.
Switched off to the back and was over 10Ls down in middle stages, not quickened under pressure inside 450M, no impression. (Jockey lost whip 200M.)
From draw 14 gradually crossed to a 2-wide position ahead of midfield, outpaced passing 300M, no extra close home.
In midfield 5Ls back, shifted out 500M to commence his run but found very little in the finish.
Along the fence behind mid-division, moved out to challenge rounding the home turn but could not pick up.
Niggled along to keep in midfield, improved along 3-deep rounding bend, dashed impressively down centre of home straight final 350 M, hit the lead at 150 M, flew home without being challenged.
Niggled along to hold the fence on the inside of the leader, responded well when asked for efforts final 350 M, briefly led near 200 M but soon headed in by the winner, kept on soundly for 2nd.
Prominently placed 1-2Ls off the pace, had every chance at the top of home straight, could not match the strides of the top two final 200 M but kept on well enough for 3rd.
Lacked early speed despite being urged along, ended up travelling rearward 5Ls off the pace, finished off soundly down centre of home straight final 350 M but too late for a place.
Broke well from gate 11, driven to share lead, overhauled at 300 M, only one-paced under maximum pressure.
Chased leaders but caught 4-wide with no cover, gave limited response when asked for efforts final 350 M, outpaced at 200 M.
Driven to sit 3Ls off the pace on rails, niggled along round the home turn, lacked a kick in home straight, outpaced at 250 M.
Crowded start, niggled along to hold a fence position in midfield, crept closer rounding bend, could not find extra to challenge the principals final 200 M, soon faded.
Crowded start, never better than midfield, made no progress in home straight.
Lacked early speed and soon drifted back towards the rear, failed to make up any ground in home straight.
Driven to chase leader but caught 3-wide with cover, failed to keep up final 300 M, weakened sharply and gave ground.
Awkward start, always struggled at the rear, lost touch at the top of home straight.
Began evenly, sat 3 to 4Ls back behind pace on rails, soft run to bend, into clear at 300 M, hit lead inside 150 M and outlasted fast finishing rival.
No pace as usual, back a clear last 10Ls away, began to improve on bend, in traffic turning, weaved between horses, in straight and closed hard for 2nd despite trouble at 100 M.
Out in line, ended up in midfield 4 to 5Ls back, enjoyed a good trip in mid-section, challenged inside 300 M, just couldn't get close last 50 M.
Began with rest, couldn't get closer than 3 wide but had cover, best part of 7Ls or so back to bend, made useful progress in straight to make frame.
Showed early speed, worked across from outside gate to sit outside leader, kept speed even in middle stages, in mix most of straight just gassed final 100 M, restricted room late.
Began with more purpose, slotted into 1 out 1 back spot closer than usual, 2 to 3Ls back rounding bend, battled away at same speed in straight.
Average break, 7 to 8Ls back in rear division on rails, saved ground on bend, worked home soundly along inside despite running out of room at 100 M and not ridden out late.
Tardy jump, improved into midfield but raced 3 wide 4 to 5Ls back, had cover to bend, kept trying but extra ground covered took toll and emptied 300 M.
Showed speed to hold spot on leaders back, sectionals good in mid-section, close enough turning, didn't see out trip final furlong producing a one paced finish.
Little early speed, rear division 7 to 8Ls back, never nearer in mid-section, made only minor ground without threatening.
Standard break, 5Ls back in running line throughout, still behind midfield to bend, didn't improve and struggled in run home.
Away well, went on to lead, set an even tempo in front, was joined leaving turn, gave in inside 250 M and faded out.
Well enough away, pressed on but stuck 3 wide without cover 2Ls back, faced a hard journey to bend, run took toll and dropped right out.
Standard jump, midfield or worse racing on rails, 6Ls back to bend, didn't act on surface and weakened to be beaten a long way.

Began well, taken back to settle in 3rd or 4th on rails about 2Ls off the speed, shaken up to challenge upon straightening, ducked out under pressure at the 200 M, responded well to snatch victory in the shadows of the post.
Broke well, led until joined far side, then taken back to track leader, one-out-one-back turning in, hit front over 150 M out but caught close home.
Settled just worse than midfield racing keenly in slow-paced race, saved ground turning for home, made steady progress under pressure without threatening.
Very sluggish at start despite given reminders, remained well back early stages, commenced move around the bend, finished off race nicely to produce good impression in the run home.
Began awkwardly losing about a length, raced keenly and wide without cover around stables bend before taking up running far side, led until headed when on extra inside 200 M.

Began with others holding narrow advantage early, settled one-out-one-back around stables bend, became 2L 3rd far side, similar position turning in, minor inconvenience 250 M out , kept on well to finish. (Questioned.)
Began awkwardly losing ground, took time to muster pace early, raced wide in rear of midfield around stables bend, towards rear in last few far side, widest runner turning in, never nearer.
Jumped slowly, trailed the field to straight, saved ground turning in, kept on steadily under pressure without quickening.
Jumped slowly, gradually picked up to midfield on rails in the slow-paced race, raced keenly early far side, similar position turning in, made no show in straight.
Began with others, settled in midfield of the slowly-run race, then raced keenly in similar spot far side, failed to quicken under pressure in straight.
Raced wide without cover in midfield to straight, soon weakened under pressure after straightening.
From a wide gate was held deep along the back straight before managing to cross and vie for the lead near the 600 M. Keep finding extra over the concluding stages to record a solid win.
Pushed vigorously to lead early on the rail, was headed at the 600 M, maintained a sound gallop to retain 2nd.
Tracked the principals along the paint. Made steady progress in the run home.
Settled 1 out 1 back by the 600 M. Never went up a gear at the business end.
Raced prominently, 3 deep on the circle, no cover. Same speed to the finish line.
Pressured to maintain a midfield spot along the fence. Didn't really handle the turn at the 500 M, finished off well late.
Raced worse than midfield along the paint worked to the line one paced.
Settled close to midfield 2 to 3-wide with cover. Kept on at the same speed along the inside in the straight.
Began awkwardly lost ground, then was outpaced early becoming somewhat detached from the bulk of the field. Swung wide on the home turn and worked home well.
Crowded for room at the start settling a distant last. Fenced up in the straight but only plugged to the line.
Couldn't match the early speed and drifted back in the race. Made the turn awkwardly at the 500 M and was checked off heels. Never a factor.
Travelled back in the race 3 to 4-wide with some cover on the circle. Struggled in the final straight.

Soon in front rank but was caught wide. Driven to shift in first turn and led on fence passing 900 M. Levelled up turning. Ran on to kick clear final furlong but was seriously threatened near finish. Just lasted.
Raced within 3Ls of the pace in a 2-wide position until home straight. Rallied on and launched a strong challenge closing stages. Denied in a bobbing of heads.
Travelled 3-wide after fair start. Rolled forward and eventually parked outside the leader from 400 M. Hung on in the straight without troubling the front pair.
Raced 3-wide in midfield early and was 4Ls down approaching final stretch. Kept covering ground to make frame at finish.
Stayed towards rear on fence early and was 5Ls away turning in. Took run between runners and finished off fairly well. Just failed to make frame.
Eased to rear near fence from high draw. Remained on fence and was 7Ls off on straightening. Made up good ground thereafter.
Began awkwardly. Ridden along the fence early and raced in midfield. Shifted 2-wide and was 4Ls behind the leader leaving the bend. Made decent headway.
Well enough away. Took seat behind pace first turn but ended up at midfield rounding home turn. Ran on steadily in the straight but was not threatening.
Out nicely. Elected to sit behind leader from 900 M. Failed to turn up a notch in the straight.
Never far off the pace early and middle stages. Just held ground in the straight.
Crowded for room at start. Sat 2-wide towards rear through to home turn. Minor progress in the straight.
Soon dropped to rear and never improved.
Broke well, dropped back to seventh on rail but going very strongly, pulled out, found gap between horses, hit front 200 M out, won with plenty of authority.
Broke well, no pace to go with leaders, dropped back to eighth home turn, improved, then really hit stride 150 M out, finished strongly but no chance with impressive winner.
Broke well, fifth on rail behind bunched leaders, travelling well turning for home, not match finishing pace of first two.
Slowly away, far back and driven, ran on very well in straight.
Broke well, lost out to four others in fight for lead, found gap and tried to run on 300 out, no kick.
Broke well, got up on rail for narrow lead after 400 M, still led into straight, weakened last 200 M.
Missed break, always struggling, made some ground on rail into midfield after halfway, weakened.
Fast away from outside draw, but beaten by three horses in bid for lead, three wide turning for home, challenged in mid-course, never near winner.
Broke well and ridden, not pace to get near lead, hard driven home turn, kept on to pass beaten horses.
Broke well, led briefly, headed after 200 M, just second but driven at top of straight, drifted to centre of course, weakened.
Quick out of gate but no early pace, ridden, but no real progress.
Ridden for brief lead early, third three wide into straight, weakened.
Broke well, settled in sixth one off rail, restrained far side, made ground approaching straight, finished fast down centre of course to collar leader 100 M out and win well.
Broke well, second on outside of leader after 400 M, going strongly, driven to lead 400 M out, stayed on well but just caught by lightly weighted rival.
Ridden early to take position on rail in sixth, restrained in fifth far side, ridden entering straight, tried hard but not quite match first two.
Broke a little awkwardly, but fourth one off rail far side going well, pulled out to centre of course in straight, not quite pace to challenge.
Broke fast and ridden early in attempt to counter outside draw, led after 200 M and steadied although eager, challenged by second early in straight, fought on gamely but gradually weakened.
Not hurried early, settled fourth last, ridden before straight, hard driven in midfield but no real impression.
Broke well, took rail behind leader in third place, still well placed on rail when driven early in straight, no kick.
Held up three from rear, ridden in straight to challenge mid-course, no impression.
Held up in second last, moved a little closer on outer on far side, ridden, no response.
Slow early, in rear, tried to quicken, failed.
Crossed in front easily and settled 1-1/2Ls off the leader 2-wide, benefited by the very slow tempo, closed the race off strongly 300 M to win.
Eased to sit in midfield along the fence, 3-1/2Ls off the leader, harmed by the very slow pace, stormed home strongly 250 M and finished 2nd.
Hard ridden to take the rail and led by 1-1/2Ls at advantageous slow sectionals, hung on until 200 M overhauled, ran on for 3rd.
Eased to sit in front of midfield, 3-1/2Ls off the leader 2-wide, harmed by the very slow tempo, held up 4-2, dashed well when clear.
Midfield, 4-1/2Ls off the leader 2-wide, dashed well 200 M despite not suited by the very slow pace.

Pushed to keep up in midfield, 3-1/2Ls off the leader, harmed by the very slow pace, trapped 3-wide throughout and lost too much ground, little dash in straight despite not suited by all negative racing situations.
Pushed to occupy a more prominent spot along the fence, 2-1/2Ls off the leader, not suited by the very slow sectionals, just held ground in final stages.
Pushed to obtain the box seat, enjoyed the very slow early sectionals, however soon weakened 250 M.
Eased back, 6Ls off the leader 2 to 3-wide, not suited by the very slow pace, little dash 200 M.
Bumped start, 5-1/2Ls off the leader, trapped 3-wide throughout and lost too much ground, harmed by the very slow tempo, just held ground in straight.
Very slow away, raced keenly and checked off heels early, 6-1/2Ls off the leader 2-wide, harmed by the very slow pace, held up 4-2, just ran on when clear.
Eased back, 5Ls off the leader along the fence, harmed by the very slow pace, no progress.
Out in line, driven to share the lead early when caught 3-wide, found the fence passing 600 M, quickened well when asked for efforts final 250 M, kept on strongly to win without being challenged.
Urged to sit 2 to 3Ls off the pace, checked at 1000 M, responded well when asked final 250 M, finished off soundly for 2nd.
Broke well, held up to a 3-wide spot in midfield, crept closer at home turn, kept battling on in home straight, just lost the 2nd.
Jumped fastest, sat one-off in the mid-division, took time to obtain clear run early in the home straight, finished off well when clear at 200 M.
Prominently placed just off the pace, niggled along rounding home turn, kept on, could not find extra final 150 M.
Broke well, cozily sat just behind the leader, struggled rounding the home turn, gave limited response when asked in home straight, one-paced.
Taken back from the wide alley, ended up traveling 4Ls off the pace on rails, made up little ground early in the straight, no extra final 150 M.
Lacked early pace as usual, travelled 5 to 6Ls off the pace at the rear, made gradual progress along the inner in home straight, but never really troubled the principals.
Given a waiting ride as usual, travelled rearward 5Ls off the speed, made some late progress final 200 M but only passed the tired rivals.
Driven hard to hold a fence position in midfield, niggled along at home turn, held ground until flattened near 200 M, soon dropped out.
Taken back from the widest alley and travelled 3-wide close to the rear, failed to make up any ground.
Driven early to track leader but caught 3-wide, struggled at home turn, weakened at the top of home straight, soon dropped out.
Taken across after the start and travelled strongly behind midfield, found plenty in the straight to reel in the runner up inside 100 M and scored with something in hand.
Handily placed in 3rd, urged along passing 500 M to keep up with leader, briefly looked the winner 250 M out with a promising run but couldn't match strides with the winner inside final 100 M.
Placed 2-wide in mid-division, gradually responded to pressure inside 350 M, stayed on well to go 3rd inside 50 M.
Given a patient ride in the rear, saved ground along the inside but had to switch out for a clear run near 250 M, stayed on well without threatening the winner.
Pressed the pace in early stages, took over passing 700 M and built up a 2Ls advantage turning in, kept on till finding no extra 150 M from home.
Soon crossed to the inside and held a midfield position 4Ls off the lead, quickly moved to a handy position 350 M, had his chance but lacked pace to challenge seriously.
Broke well but was gradually taken back to the rear, 8Ls down turning for home but didn't have the clearest of runs in early straight, ran on when clear but never looked like getting there.
Positioned behind midfield 6Ls off leader, shifted to outside of field passing 500 M but found disappointingly little in the finish.
Never far off in 4th, nudged along approaching 400 M but no progress, weakened over final 100 M.
Placed in midfield and was 3-wide without cover throughout, found little when asked and weakened rapidly in final stages. (Lame next day.)
Took up the early running and set a decent pace at the front end, was taken on passing halfway, gradually outpaced inside 400 M and weakened tamely in late stages.
Couldn't slot in from a wide draw and raced without cover in the first half, dropped to last making the turn and swung widest for home, soon lost touch, heavily eased. (Unacceptable Performance.)

Began with others, settled in last few and waited with, came to challenge 300 M out, responded well to take command closing stages.
Settled just worse than midfield, inconvenienced 400 M out, ran on steadily under pressure to be nearest at finish.
Disputed lead, taken back to stalk leader around the bend, came to challenge upon straightening, hit front inside 300 M drawing 2Ls clear, flattered and overhauled final strides.
Began fairly, ridden along from a wide barrier to settle in 3L 4th around the bend, similar position turning in, ran home one-paced.
Made running to 300 M, faded under pressure.
Slightly slow into stride, settled in midfield, made a nice impression in the run home.
Settled in midfield, ran home steadily at the one pace.
Began with others, travelled in midfield, closer up turning in, ran home evenly for a nice debut.
Began slowly, gradually picked up to rear of midfield, went wide around the bend and into straight, made no impression.
Broke with others, settled in forward of midfield on rails, saved ground turning in, weakened under pressure from 2L 3rd over 300 M out.
Began awkwardly, settled one from last to straight, made no progress.
Began awkwardly, soon taken back to last on rails from the widest barrier, trailed the field to straight, made no progress.
Broke well from a wide draw, settled in 3L 3rd, closer up turning in, dropped out tamely.
Travelled in midfield, weakened out of contention from approaching home turn.
Settled 1 out 1 back. Kicked clear at the 200m and scored a solid victory.
Enjoyed a nice run on the back of the leaders along the rail. Finished off well after having difficulty obtaining clear running until the furlong.
Got its head up on a number of occasions when being restrained early, back top a position behind midfield, 2 deep with cover. Came wide on the home turn, ran on nicely.

Pushed along from barrier rise to go forward and take up the lead. Was pressured soon after the 900m by another runner, settling in 2nd position along the paint. Kept whacking away right to the finish.
Camped midfield the fence. travelled on the bridle and improved midrace, worked to the post satisfactorily.
Went forward to race as the leader, 1 off and to the outside of another runner. Faded over the concluding stages.
Bumped at the start then ridden along early to settle 3 back, 1 off with cover. Shifted out to travel 3 wide without cover after the 700m when overracing. Kept on one paced in the run to the line.
Began awkwardly then was steadied soon after the start traveling back in the field along the rail. Closed off fairly.
Was steadied soon after the start, settling with the backmakers, 2-3 wide, didn't have cover for the entire part of the circle. Worked home only fairly.
Parked 3 back the rail. Peeled out to improve and travel 1 off near the 700m. Stayed on at the same pace in the straight.
Travelled with the tailenders along the fence with cover. Railed up in the home straight but only plugged to the line.
Raced at the rear, 2-3 wide with cover. Gave no response when asked for an effort in the final stretch.
Slow to begin settling back in the field 1 off with cover. Failed to close off.
Settled slightly ahead of midfield, 2 deep with cover. Struggled in the straight.
Quickly into stride. Urged early to hold lead on fence. Eased gradually to take box-seat making home turn. Picked up well in the straight and hit front final furlong. Drew clear to score easily.
Began well but trapped wide. Travelled 3-wide in the leading section rounding the turn. Ridden passing 300M when challenged by the winner but was soon knocked out. Barely hung on for 2nd.
Handy position, one-off on the fence behind leading section through to home straight. Finished off well and nearly snatched 2nd.
Driven to maintain midfield spot on fence early. Same position turning for home. Covered ground steadily in the straight. Made frame near the line without troubling the front trio.
Prominent spot through to the home straight but was one-paced to conclude.
Detached early despite rider's effort. Reached the back of the field passing 700M. 8Ls down on straightening. Made up decent ground late.
Niggled early and tucked in behind midfield on fence approaching home turn. Soon under pressure after straightening. Ran on steadily but was not threatening.
Elected to stay towards rear in a 2 to 3-wide position through to the home straight. Vigorously ridden thereafter to make some headway.
Caught wide in the front rank after start. Gradually taken to sit 3-wide behind midfield from 1000M. Last few entering the final stretch wide. Minor progress thereafter.
Trapped 3-wide ahead of midfield through to the home straight after a nice start. Failed to turn up a notch when asked.
Never better than midfield. Found nothing when the race got serious.
2-wide towards rear throughout. Never improved from there.
3-wide behind midfield through to the home turn. Pressed along approaching the home straight but no progress. Beaten long way before the post.
Shaken up early to go forward from high draw. Disputed lead making home turn. Soon weakened passing 400M.
Fast break, travelled comfortably in lead, kicked clear 400m out, never in danger.
Untidy start, one from rear early, good progress between horses straight, finished strongly.
Ridden to take early position in fourth, made ground three wide home turn, stayed on steadily.
Just enough early speed to take fifth on the rail, made ground on inside in straight, flattened out.
Second early outside comfortable leader, tried to attack at 400m, left behind when winner quickened.
Eased back from wide draw, ridden for finishing pace down outside, found some, but not enough.
Short of early pace, then pulled slightly when driven up, settled in midfield, challenged mid-track straight, no kick.
Ridden early to take third place on rail, every chance straight, no finish.
Missed break, two lengths last early, ridden up on rail almost into midfield, asked to quicken straight, found little.
Declined to join battle for lead, fourth last far side, challenged three wide, met interference early in straight, kept on but no chance thereafter.
Dropped back last from wide draw, driven early in straight, limited response.
No pace early, then took some setting far side, pulled out to challenge straight, found nothing.
Ridden up three wide into midfield from wide draw, five wide turn, no progress straight.
Made some ground into midfield from ordinary break, five wide and treading water home turn, weakened.
Bounced out fast from stall 9, led narrowly 400m, length up into straight, kicked clear, challenged strongly last 100m, fought back gamely to win.

Lost half length start, but good position going well on rail in fifth far side, improved between horses straight to perhaps take fractional lead 50m from line, just worried out of it by as run came to an end.
Ridden early from wide draw, dropped back to midfield, niggled briefly far side, then back on bridle, hard ridden straight, ran on well without quite getting to front two.
Sluggish start, held up, improved between horses straight, finished quite well.
Broke fast, second on outside after 400m, tried to challenge leader straight but easily beaten off, weakened.
Slowly away, held up towards rear on rail, ridden approaching straight and all the way to the line, but only moderate progress.
Broke well, fourth one off rail early, held position until straight, then challenged three wide but no kick.
Only moderate start, towards rear, tried to improve wide, but no real impression.
Unhurried start, toward rear, made wide move approaching straight, ridden, no impression.
Restless in gate but broke quite well, sixth down far side, tried to improve on outside, but no extra.
Broke well, up on rail to follow leader in third place, ridden on inside in straight, empty tank.
Slowish start, toward rear early, made some ground approaching straight, ridden, no progress.
Not too sharp start, midfield far side, up on rail into fifth at home turn, ridden, weakened.
Caught wide early, held up towards the rear, niggled along rounding bend, failed to make up any progress in home straight.
Midfield, 5Ls off the leader along the fence, favoured by the fast pace and the rail trip, progressed steadily 300M to win.
Pushed early to take a rail spot in front of midfield, 3.5Ls off the leader, helped by the fast tempo, lack room 400M, made ground steadily when clear, just beaten by a narrow margin in 2nd.
Eased back, 6.5LS off the leader on the fence, benefited by the fast pace, held up 4-2, progressed steadily when clear and grabbed 3rd.
Pushed to obtain a prominent spot, 2Ls off the leader 2 wide, not suited by the fast early sectionals, led 300M, hung on well until 100M overhauled, just missed 3rd.
Midfield, 5Ls off the leader, trapped 3 wide, helped by the fast pace, made ground 400M, flat 100M.
Eased back, 9LS off the leader 2-3 wide, favoured by the fast tempo, progressed steadily 300M.
Eased back, 7Ls off the leaders along the fence, benefited by the fast pace, made ground 250M without much threats.
Settled in box seat, not suited by the fast tempo, ran on well until 200M flattened.
Pushed to sit in front of midfield, 3.5Ls off the leader 2 wide, suited by the fast tempo, ran on fairly in final stages.
At rear, more than 10Ls off the leader, hard ridden from 1300M and throughout, raced 3-5 wide, made ground 800M, flat 100M.
Very slow away, at back, 6.5Ls off the leader 3-4 wide, suited by the fast pace, no turn of foot in straight.
Hard ridden to sit outside the lead, used up too much fuel during the fast early sectionals, weakened 300M.
Urged along early and travelled 3-4Ls off the pace, caught 3-wide with no cover, no response when asked for efforts final 450 M, soon weakened sharply.
Pushed to take the rail and led by 0.5L at fast pace, dropped off quickly 300M.
Broke well from 7, travelled well in fifth, got first run on Fellowship as both quickened brilliantly, held on very gamely, great ride.

Broke well from outside draw but didn't try to mix it early and 2Ls last, closed up back straight, last turning winner, found seam in straight, and charged, almost joining eventual winner on line, excellent effort.
Broke in line, close up on rail behind leaders, got split and went after front runner halfway up straight, completely outpaced by front two.
Claimed lead after 300m, two lengths clear setting decent but not outrageous pace, quickened clear early in straight, finishers much too strong.
Unsurprisingly short of early pace, ran on quite well into fifth in straight, very respectable comeback run.
Broke well, dropped back to fourth, tried to make ground straight, not pace of main contenders.
Three from rear early, challenged three wide home turn, no progress.
Ridden up along rail to share lead, headed and raced in second until straight, kept on but rest of field too good.
Placed in midfield 2-wide, shifted out to improve round the outside of field passing 700M, had an uninterrupted run from 400M and made steady headway to just get up on the line.
Never far off in 5th and was ideally positioned to strike turning in, quickened to lead 250M, stuck to his task well but was just caught on the line.
Along the inside in mid-division but not helped by the slow pace in middle stages, progressed steadily in straight, had every chance but was out-sprinted by the first two inside 250 M.
Always close up behind leaders, switched out from fence passing 600M to improve, kept on well but turned one paced final 100 M.
Bagged a rail position in midfield, saved ground on the inside but was being held up when the pace quickened over the final turn, stayed on without reaching the principals.
Taken back from draw 14, settled in last and over 10Ls behind in early stages, made his move round the outside of field passing halfway, battled on but was gradually outpaced inside 300 M.
Given a patient ride behind midfield, swung 3-wide for home, made some headway down the outside but never looked like getting there.
Positioned 2-wide in midfield, 4Ls off the pace inside 400M, kept on without making ground on the leaders.
Dropped back towards the rear and waited with till 350M, stayed on but lacked the extra pace to get seriously involved.
Obtained a spot just in behind leaders, proved difficult to settle down the back straight, moved to a striking position passing 600M, had every chance but stamina ran out over final 200 M.
Ordinary jump but gradually moved forward to track leader, was disappointingly one-paced when put under pressure and failed to get involved.
Took them along uncontested and set slow sectionals, headed 300M and dropped rapidly out of contention.
Towards the tail of the field over 10Ls back, given a waiting ride but couldnt quicken with the rest inside 400 M. Never a factor.
At rear over 10Ls behind leader in a slowly run race, didn't find anything in straight and was eased 200M out.
Sent straight into lead from gate, headed after 300m and dropped back to third travelling well, pulled out and ridden to lead straight, drive, but always in charge.
Tightened a little at start, but nothing serious, followed leaders in fifth down far side, slightly short of room mid-straight, but got out and ran on well, not peg back winner.
Broke well, but not hurried early, raced fourth just outside eventual winner, tried to quicken with first two but not quite enough pace.
Squeezed back start, raced midfield, still going quite well entering straight, ran on without being able to challenge.
Broke very awkwardly, always up against it thereafter and racing three or four wide, far back into straight, but ran on very well, good effort.
Broke smartly, steadied on rail back to second last, then ridden briefly, comfortable in back straight and close enough if good enough at home turn, ridden, inadequate finish.
Lost about a length at start, but sixth and looking comfortable back straight, every chance but found little, weakened finish.
Lost ground after moderate start, still rear entering straight, ridden and made some ground, never a threat.
Second last early and urged to take place on rail, travelling reasonably well at home turn, driven, but lacked required pace.
Ridden early to head off leaders, led going quite well entering straight, headed, folded quickly.
Broke well, eager in midfield, settled on outside, challenged down centre, found nothing, weakened.
Held up near rear, tightened briefly back straight, ridden in rear entering straight, driven, little progress.
Broke in line, moved up wide into second place, still second into straight, ridden, weakened quickly.
Ordinary jump, positioned 8Ls back in running line, helped by solid tempo, plenty to achieve on bend, motored down middle picking up rivals in final 150 M to score a solid win.
Reasonable break, angled into midfield 5Ls off solid tempo, had easy time to home bend, produced a strong close to push winner right to wire.
Out in line, camped behind pace group, enjoyed a good trail 3 to 4Ls back, loomed full of running on turning, couldn't fight back inside 200 M but kept on well for a clear 3rd.
Bounced well, ended up in ideal spot 1 out 1 back, did some work close to decent speed, challenged turning in, battled away evenly to make frame once headed inside 250 M.
Restrained from a wide gate, soon at rear 12Ls off pace, well back to bend, made many lengths in straight and continued to close despite being steadied at 150 M.
Faded back soon after break, raced behind midfield 6 to 7Ls off speed, helped by tempo, well back turning, made some late ground to be nearest on line.
Slow to begin, in rear division, 9 to 10Ls from leaders, saved ground on circle, made some minor headway without threatening.
Began with rest, sat in midfield 6Ls back on rails, aided by tempo and saved ground on circle, shifted out to offer something but came up with little and just battled late.
Well enough to break slotted in behind leader, did a bit of work on strong speed, 1L down turning, gradually weakened from 300 M.
No early speed, urged along to hold spot, raced 9 to 10Ls back in running line, niggled on bend, failed to offer much in straight.
Showed good speed, took front but did share of work with pressure from outside horses headed soon after turning in, weakened out badly.
Didn't muster early and failed back to share rear, got further behind despite urging, pushed up on bend, made some late ground from impossible spot in straight. (See Racing Incidents.)
Pressed on from an awkward draw, posted 3 wide without cover in 3 way speed battle, struggling turning in, folded tamely.
Good speed, prominent despite a wide alley, worked in 3 way challenge outside leader, still there but under pressure turning, dropped out.

Began moderately, soon picked up to midfield to settle, similar turning into home straight, finished off race strongly down centre of track to take command close to home.
Settled in midfield or better on rails, came to challenge under pressure upon straightening, ran on under pressure only to find winner too good.
Slow out, settled well behind, saved ground turning in, produced good effort down inner of straight to be nearest at finish.
Began fairly, moved up gradually to take lead turning into back straight, made running home straight when joined while plugging on, overhauled final 50 M.
Settled on rails around midfield, made nice impression in straight without posing any serious threat to the place-getters.
Led early, headed into back straight, tracked leader, re-gained lead momentarily 200 M out, soon tired badly.
Broke well, soon held back to race in one-out-one-back position in 4th or later 3rd, outside leader turning in, faded steadily under pressure in straight.
Behind midfield, wide into straight, kept on same pace.

Began with others, settled on heels of leader on rails, travelled just 2Ls off the speed far side, shuffled further back around the bend but saved ground on inside turning in, faded gradually under pressure in the run home.
Towards rear, found nil in straight. (Tactic questioned.)
Travelled better than midfield within 3Ls of speed, 4 wide turning into straight, dropped out.
Raced wide without cover in midfield or just worse, dropped to last turning for home, no further impression. (Tactic questioned.)

Enjoyed a nice run in the race parked behind the leader along the paint. Swung off the rail rounding the home turn, worked to the lead at the 100 M and fought of challenger to record a well fought win.
Camped on the rail, behind midfield. Fenced up early in the home straight and after switching out near the furlong, went to the post soundly.
Began awkwardly settling at the rear 1 off with cover. Circled the field after the 1000 M and joined the leaders near the 600 M. Made a concerted effort right to the wire.
Ridden along from a wide gate to slot in and settle worse than midfield 2 deep with cover. Closed off nicely.
Enjoyed an uncontested lead setting slow sectionals. Had every chance, weakening in the run to the line.
Jumped full of running to settle 1 out 1 back. Couldn't capitalize, going to the line 1 paced.
Settled with the backmarkers, 2 to 3-wide with cover for the major part of the race. Plodded home fairly.
Travelled at the tail of the field. Made reasonable ground in the final stretch.
Settled 3 back on the fence. Had no excuses.
After being caught wide early, pressed on leaving the straight on the first occasion to settle outside the leader. Struggled in the run home.
Slow to begin but was then caught midfield 3-wide and without cover for the majority of the race. Never likely.

Fair start. Soon settled towards rear on fence through to home turn. Swung wide and was 6Ls down on straightening. Got clear run near 200 M and showed impressive turn of foot to sweep away rivals at post.

Soon taken to race 2-wide towards rear. Driven outside field to get closer from 500 M and was 5Ls away into final stretch. Launched a sustained challenge to cut down rivals before caught by the winner final strides.

Broke well and occupied a handy position ahead of midfield early. One-out-one-back middle stages. Well positioned to strike turning in. Battled determinedly but lacked the finishing touch to charge down the front pair.

Away in line from high draw and slotted into a 2-wide spot towards rear making first turn. Commenced his run 3-wide approaching the rock and was 2Ls off turning into home. Kept giving but failed to contain the front trio near finish

Shaken up to race forward from high draw but was caught 4-wide near 1400 M. Tracked leader 2-wide 1100 M out. Disputed lead top of home straight and hit front 200 M. Unable to fend off the principals closing stages.
Jumped fairly. Settled 2-wide behind midfield through to home turn. 3Ls behind the pace leaving the bend. Ran on with the principals before disappointed for running passing 200 M. Not fully tested.
Out nicely and took fence at midfield. Trapped towards rear when other runners improved rounding the home turn. Made up ground inside home straight but was not threatening.
Urged wide from outside barrier. Eventually took lead on fence from 1100 M. Held a 1L advantage back straight. Levelled turning in but fought on until swamped 150 M.
2-wide at midfield through to the home straight and was one-paced to conclude.
Rolled forward 3-wide first turn. Led on fence near 1300 M. Eased to sit behind speed 1200 M out. Never really saw daylight in the straight.
Raced keenly within 3Ls of the leader through to the home straight. Held ground before no extra final 100 M.
Slow to begin. Backmarker always. Made up minor ground late.
Broke alertly, enough speed to take ideal spot on rail in fourth, wound up in straight, split front two to take lead 200 M out ran on well.
Lost a length at start, but still sixth on rail after 300 M going well, challenged at same time as winner but one horse wider, not quite enough.
Slow away, last early, ridden and improved but still eight lengths to find halfway up straight, finished strongly.
Broke well, but got on heels after 200 M and lost a length, urged before straight, challenged wide, ran on quite well.
Slow out of gate, second last after 200 M but restrained, just last entering turn, finished well down outside.
Broke fast, led on outside early, second outside leader after 400 M, led entering straight, weakened.
Sharp start, fourth after 300 M, challenged two wide entering straight, driven but not as much pace as closers.
Broke well, but could not go pace of leaders, dropped to fifth last, challenged wide in straight and slightly hampered.
Broke fast but headed on both sides after 200 M, dropped to fifth, ridden straight, found little.
Moderate start, restrained early, ridden straight to challenge on inside, found little.
Broke well, led on rail early, length clear far side, ridden before home turn, no resistance to challengers in straight.
Broke well, ridden early, but outpaced, midfield, back to last on outside entering straight, left far behind.
Broke well, took unhurried second behind clear leader, driven into lead mid-straight, held on well.
Fair break, held up near rear, improved approaching straight, challenged along inside rail, finished strongly.
Jumped smartly, took third on rail, pulled out to challenge early in straight, kept on but no real burst of speed.
Unhurried start, held up in second last one wide, improved approaching home turn, ran on strongly but never able to challenge.
Slight stumble just after start, travelled in fifth on rail, improved to challenging position straight, no extra last 100 M.
Good break, slightly checked when trying to take position after 200 M, raced in sixth twelve lengths behind clear leader, closed on outside in straight, but not quite quick enough to get involved.
Decent break but dropped back last, not hurried, improved approaching home turn, path blocked and lost some momentum early in straight, ran on well.
Broke quite well but little early pace, midfield on rail seeming to race in snatches, close enough if good enough early in straight, found very little.
Reasonable start, urged far side, wide and driven into straight, fair finish but never near enough to challenge.
Blasted out from wide draw, ridden for lead, four lengths clear down far side, still two clear early in straight, folded.
Moderate break, raced in fourth one wide, back to fifth early in straight, lost ground all the way to the line.
Broke quite well but four wide into first turn, never got near rail, tried to improve far side but still wide, ridden, dropped away.
Eased back, 5-1/2Ls off the leader 2 to 3-wide, harmed by the slow pace, dashed strongly 300 M to win by a narrow margin.
Took rail easily and led by 1/2L at advantageous slow sectionals, hung on strongly until final stride, just missed.
Pushed forward, 2Ls behind the slow pace 2-wide, raced keenly, closed the race off strongly 200 M for 3rd.
Settled in box seat, favoured by the slow tempo, just held ground in last quarter.
Eased at start to cross behind the pace group, 2-1/2Ls off the leader on the fence, not suited by the slow pace, little dash 200 M.
Pushed to sit outside the lead, benefited by the slow early sectionals, ran on until 200 M flattened.
Pushed forward but failed to cross, 1-1/2Ls off the slow pace, trapped 3-wide throughout and lost too much ground, flattened 250 M.
Eased to sit in midfield, 3-1/2Ls off the leader 2-wide, not suited by the slow tempo, just held ground in straight.
Hard ridden to take a midfield spot, 3-1/2Ls off the leader, not suited by the slow pace, trapped 3-wide throughout and lost too much ground, held ground in straight.
Eased to sit behind midfield along the fence, 4-1/2Ls off the leader, harmed by the slow tempo, raced flat until 100 M showed little dash.
Eased back, 8Ls off the leader 2-wide, not suited by the slow pace, no progress.
Very slow away, at rear, harmed by the slow pace, never competitive.
Slight bump just after start, but took up good position in fourth on rail, not hurried, still lobbing in fifth approaching straight, pulled out to challenge and take lead, ran on well.
Ridden early, seventh one off rail far side, challenged on outside at same time as winner, not quite enough pace.
Restrained in second last one off rail, improved early in straight, then really took hold under driving, finished best of all.
Broke well, ridden to get near lead, taken wide by slight bump first turn, took third on rail behind leaders, comfortable as pace slowed, challenged rail, ran on but not enough pace.
Fair break, midfield and not much room first turn, towards rear and going well far side although still not much room, pulled out to challenge in straight but others finished more strongly.
Fair break, ridden early for position on rail in midfield, challenged one off rail in straight, momentarily checked, ran on.
Dwelt start and lost a length, restrained in third last on rail, challenged on inside straight, ran on fairly well.
Broke well, not rushed, but no route to rail, three wide most of race, pulled wide and stayed on quite respectably.
Broke well, led on rail, joined and headed first turn, brief lead straight, swamped.
Quick break, joined lead first turn, two lengths clear far side, soon collared in straight, weakened.
Hard driven in bid for lead on outside, fifth down far side, tried to improve but found nothing in straight.
Reined back to rail from wide draw, last early, driven straight and ran on reasonably well to finish on heels of bunched field, but never pace to get involved.
Positively ridden on jumping from a wide barrier, always in touch, produced a good turn of speed to hit the front 60 M out and maintained his momentum to fend off late challenges on the outside.
Towards the rear 8Ls off the pace, commenced his run on the outside passing 400 M, came with a sweeping run final 200 M to beat everything bar the winner.
Placed 2-wide in midfield and stayed on strongly final 300 M. Sound effort.
Held up behind midfield, picked up well inside 300 M, steadied near 150 M then ran on strongly again to finish a close 4th only half length behind winner.
Set steady tempo in front and responded well under pressure in straight, led till final 60 M and was swamped close home.
Checked shortly after the start, settled in 9th 6-7Ls off the pace, had plenty to do turning in but made some encouraging late headway to get within 1L of the winner.
In chasing group 2Ls off leaders, briefly threatened in early straight, kept on well and only lost a place a few strides before the line.
Hard driven out the gate to press the lead, had his chance but was done with before final 200 M.
Taken back from draw 12 and raced as the back marker 9Ls off the pace, took time to pick up and made some minor headway late on.
In midfield along the inside but found very little when placed under pressure over the final 300 M. No impression.
Began awkwardly, placed in mid-division 4Ls behind the lead, failed to quicken up final 300 M and weakened towards the line. (Mucus.)
Restrained back to midfield after a good start, driven 400 M out but no progress, gradually weakened.
