Broke well from the highest draw, settled one back on stands rails within 2Ls of speed, commenced run over 200 M out, responded well to soon take charge, easily.
Never far off racing down the centre of the track, failed to quicken under pressure to threaten throughout final 300 M.
Began from the lowest draw, quickly into stride to cross to stands side, disputed lead until late.
One of the best jumping out, soon taken back to settle one back with cover, commenced move inside 400 M holding good chance, missed a placing by the narrowest of margins.
Tightened at start, soon picked up to forward of midfield, finished off race nicely down centre of track.
Began awkwardly, settled just worse than midfield, didn't have the clearest of runs in the early part of the race, fought on under pressure to close off with a nice impression.
Broke well to lead, soon crossed to stands side, weakened out of it over 100 M out.
Settled in a close up spot, soon came under pressure to challenge coming onto course proper, failed to respond.
Slightly slow out, settled in last few, made no impression thereafter.
Began with others, settled in rear of midfield about 3Ls back, found nil under pressure.
Settled in midfield down centre of the track, faded out of it from halfway out.
Began with others, soon dropped to last few, never a factor.
Slightly slow out of a low draw, settled at the back, made no show.
Soon dropped well behind, never a danger.
From the outside alley was allowed to settle in a rearward position, 1 off with cover. Angled wide rounding the home turn and closed off strongly to finish over the top of the principals.
Parked 3 back 1 off no cover. Rolled out to race on the back of the leaders from the about the 600m. Got a trail into the home turn, swept to the front at the furlong but was nailed 50m out.
Raced midfiled 2 wide with cover. Rallied 4 deep on the home turn and maintained a solid gallop right to the wire.
Raced just behind midfield the fence. shifted out to race in the 1 off line from about the 800m. ranged up and looked likely near the 200m, but peaked 100m from the wire.
Positioned worse than midfield along the paint. Tracked up nicely turning for home and worked home soundly.
Travelled behind midfield 1 off with cover. Rolled out to race 3 deep after the 600m, was one paced in the run home.
Slow to begin settling with cover at the rear along the fence. Only plodded to the post.
Stalked the leader on the rails. Peeled out approaching the home turn and commenced to mount a challenge, but was overhauled near the furlong and tired quickly soon after.
Began well then from a wide gate settled in the last 2, 1 off with cover. Came wide in the straight but failed to close off.
Raced with cover 3 back the paint. Stayed to the inside in the straight but failed to respond to riding and gave ground in the run to the finishing line.
Slowly away settling with the rear division along the fence. Commenced to make steady ground in the home straight until the 100m, but weakened from that point on. (OVE prior to starting again.)
Settled in a midfield position. Was left racing without cover 3 deep from the 800m, never likely thereafter.
Began awkwardly traveling 4 back the fence with cover. Struggled in the final stretch.
Worked forward to lead along the fence. Faded after the 300 M.
Shaken up to go forward from high draw. Raced 3-wide behind leading section before tracking leader one-off the fence 700M out. Did enough to repel the runner up closing stages.
3-wide behind midfield through to the home straight. Launched attack from 300M but found the winner too strong closing stages. Cleared the rest by a comfortable margin.
Soon in leading section. Led solo on fence passing 800M and held a 1L advantage turning in. Outrun by the front pair final furlong but hung on for 3rd.
4-wide at midfield before slotting 2-wide making home turn. Forced to go wider entering the final stretch. Kept on fairly well but was one-paced.
Broke well on fence. Elected to take box-seat passing 800M. Made the turn at 650M awkwardly. Held ground in the straight.
Raced 5-wide behind midfield before home turn. Urged 3-wide from 700M and was 5Ls down turning into home. Ran on steadily but was not threatening.
Sat near rear on fence through to the home straight. Switched to the centre of the track for clear run and improved moderately.
Out nicely. Elected to take a 3-wide spot towards rear approaching home turn. Almost 10Ls behind the speed leaving the bend. Covered decent ground thereafter.
Travelled wide and without cover towards rear. Made fair progress in the home straight.
Last out. Driven to make up lost ground and sat at midfield on fence 1000M out. Ran on to beat tired runners in the straight.
Elected to sit at rear from wide barrier. 10Ls adrift rounding the bend. Made up minor ground late.
Never far off the pace but found nothing when asked 300M from home.
Raced within 3Ls of the leader on fence through to the home straight. Failed to quicken when the race got serious inside 300 M.
Back with last few throughout. Never in contention.
Cozily sat just behind the leader, checked at 1000 M, niggled along turning for home, kept battling on in home straight, won by a whisker.
Jumped fastest, took the one out one back spot easily, responded well when asked final 400 M, fought hard to contest the lead in home straight, just caught on line.

Took time to muster speed, ended up travelling 2Ls off the pace, 3-wide with no cover, responded well when placed under pressure in home straight, made up gradual ground final 300 M, finished off soundly for 3rd.
Driven to lead and found the fence passing 1000 M, left contested until the home turn, overhauled at 300 M but still kept on, lost a place final 50 M.
Broke well, prominently placed within striking distance from the leader, travelled one-off with cover, remained one-paced when placed under pressure final 400 M, never really troubled the principals.
Awkward start, urged along to sit one from the rear 8Ls off the speed, shifted wide for home, kicked well when clear 350 M out, made up substantial ground down centre of home straight.
Taken rearward from gate 12, 3-wide with no cover, strode forward rounding bend, kept on early in straight, could not find extra final 200 M, remained one-paced.
Out in line and settled in midfield early, badly checked at 1000 M and drifted towards the rear, made up ground steadily final 400 M, no extra final 150 M.
Broke well, niggled along to hold a fence position just behind the pace group, struggled at home turn, gave very limited response when asked for efforts in home straight.
Out in line, travelled well in the mid-division and found the fence near 800 M, niggled along at home turn, only one-paced when placed under pressure in home straight.
Awkward start, driven to catch up 6Ls behind the speed, niggled along rounding bend, gave limited response when asked for efforts in straight, failed to make up any ground.
Lacked early speed, urged along to sit 7-8Ls behind the speed, made no progress in home straight, never a factor.
Slow away, no early speed despite being niggled along, always rearward, made no impression.
Sat in midfield on rails, unbalanced rounding bend at 700 M, outpaced at the top of home straight, soon faded.

Broke well, prominently sat one off just behind the leader, ran on to contest the lead at the top of home straight, hung out, hit the front passing 200 M, finished off soundly, did enough to hold off the challenger.
Lacked early speed as usual, ended up travelling 5-6Ls on rails, held up for room early in home straight, dashed well when clear at 200 M, line came too soon.
Driven to take the one out one back spot, joined the lead turning for home, responded well under maximum pressure final 350 M, could not match the strides of winner at 150 M, kept on for 3rd.
Prominently placed 2Ls off the speed, travelled nicely on rails throughout, had every chance in home straight, kept battling on, just lost a place.

Held the fence and settled in the mid-division, shifted wider for clear run at the top of home straight, looked possible a place, hung out, finished off satisfactorily but could not find extra final 150 M.
Taken back from gate 12, patiently ridden until the home straight, only gave limited response when asked for efforts final 350 M, rather one-paced.
Slow away, travelled 5-6Ls behind the speed, made up gradual ground in the home straight without threatening the principals, checked at 200 M, no extra.

Broke well from the widest alley, driven hard to get across in front and obtained cover near 800 M, ran on to contest the lead at the top of home straight but proved too one-paced final 200 M, soon flattened.
Travelled 5-6Ls off the pace and caught wide throughout, made up little ground in home straight, checked 200 M, no extra.
Slow away, lacked early speed and travelled close to the rear, responded only fairly under maximum pressure in home straight, made no impression.
Niggled along to hold a one-off position in the mid-division, struggled turning for home, held ground until got tired passing the 200 M pole.
Urged along to take a 3-wide spot in midfield, outpaced rounding bend, weakened and dropped out at the top of home straight.
No early speed despite being pushed along, always rearward, never a factor.
Driven hard to lead and found the fence at 800 M, weakened sharply at the top of home straight, tailed out. (Heart irregularity.)
Eased back, 6Ls off the leader 3 wide, harmed by the slow pace, dashed strongly 300M to score its first goal without being fully tested.
Settled in front of midfield, 3.5Ls off the leader 3 wide, not suited by the slow tempo, dashed well 200M and took 2nd.
Hard ridden to occupy a prominent spot, 2Ls off the leader, benefited by the slow pace, ran on well to the line for 3rd.
Pushed to hold the box seat, enjoyed the slow early sectionals, just held ground in straight.
In front of midfield along the fence, 3Ls off the leader, not suited by the slow sectionals, little dash 200M.
Eased back, 6.5Ls off the leader 2 wide, dashed strongly 200M despite not suited by the slow tempo.
Slow away, hard ridden to obtain a midfield spot, 5Ls off the leader 2 wide, harmed by the slow pace, held up 4-2, dashed strongly when clear.
Eased to rear, 7.5Ls off the leader along the fence, demonstrated very strong finishing efforts in straight despite harmed by the slow pace, on heels 100M.
In front of midfield, 3.5Ls off the leader 2 wide, not suited by the slow tempo, held up most straight, just ran on.
Hard ridden to take the rail and led by 1.5Ls at slow sectionals, hung on strongly until 100M when overhauled and emptied.
Eased to sit in midfield along the rails, 4.5Ls off the leader, not suited by the slow pace, blocked whole straight, never tested.
Eased at start to cross at rear, 6Ls off the leader on the fence, harmed by the slow tempo, blocked whole straight, little dash without fully tested.
Eased to sit in midfield, 5Ls off the leader 3 wide, harmed by the slow pace, no progress.
Very slow away, at rear, not suited by the slow pace, never competitive.
Jumped well, third on outside early, urged along to keep place and improve to second far side, challenged entering straight, led 300m out, fought on very gamely under top weight.
Tacked over from wide gate, last early, two lengths last far side but not hurried, three wide approaching home turn, challenged widest of all, finished strongly, only winner too tough.
Broke well, but eased back to second last early, moved up one off rail, challenged between horses straight, checked momentarily 400m, finished well.
Broke quickly, led on rail early, headed far side but unhurried, found gap and challenged two wide straight, no finishing kick.
Ridden up outside leader early, took lead after 300m, two lengths clear far side, half length lead into straight, lost brief battle with winner, wakened late.
Eased back from outside draw, second last early, one off rail travelling between horses, moved into fourth in straight, ridden and ran on but not pace to challenge.
Fourth on rail far side, gradually dropped back to last in bunched field, ridden early in straight, plugged on but no impact.
Missed break by a length, three wide far side and throughout thereafter, ridden straight, found nothing.
Patiently ridden in early stages, 6Ls back in 11th turning for home, switched out 400M and quickened well to seal the race 50M from the line.
Settled midfield and swung 3-wide for home, picked up well inside 300M but just found one too good.
Driven to the lead and went a decent gallop, was strongly challenged passing 400M but refused to give in and kept battling away under pressure, headed inside 100M but managed to hold on for 3rd.
Always prominent, alongside leader approaching the top of the straight, all out inside 300M and fought on well to the line.
Broke well from the inside barrier, tracked leaders and used little to straight, produced with every chance final 300M, kept on but lacked extra pace to challenge seriously.
Not hurried after a slow start, settled 2nd last 7Ls behind leaders, responded to a point but turned one-paced in closing stages. (Jockey dropped whip 200M.)
Up with the early pace but dropped back midfield, angled out passing 500M and progressed steadily, momentarily crowded for room near 100M then ran on again in late stages.
Soon bagged a rail position and settled 4Ls off the pace in midfield, pushed along 500M out, made steady progress down the inside but ran into traffic 50M from home.
Away in line, settled in midfield but never far off leaders, driven inside 450M but ran on only one-paced, weakened final 100 M.
Dropped back towards the rear but was kept wide throughout, switched widest in straight but could make minor headway only.
Positioned 2-wide in midfield, held up to 350M but ran on only fairly when clear.
First attempt over 1200M. Taken back to last about 8Ls behind leaders, gave limited response 400M out, never factored.
Tracked leaders one back, 3-wide over the turn and gradually outpaced approaching 600M, soon behind and was done with before 200 M.
Unable to cross from draw 10 and caught wide without cover throughout, run ended inside 400M and gave ground rapidly, eased.

Broke fast, ridden to lead from wide draw, two lengths clear after 300m, then relaxed, accelerated out of back straight, clear again entering straight, four clear at 200m, hard driven and just held on.
Broke well, fourth one off rail after 300m, third straight and driven in pursuit of clear leader, closed fast, just failed.

Jumped fairly well but then eased back to fourth last, still in group fifteen to twenty lengths behind leader turning out of back straight, began to improve well at 400m, finished fast, not quite fast enough.
Mid pack, but not chasing leaders early, near head of rear group of nine out of back straight, made good ground in straight but not quite get there.
Broke well, allowed to drift back on rail to midfield far side, improved entering straight, challenged one off rail and driven, not reach leader.
Bobbled slightly start, last after 300m, some improvement on outside after entering straight, ran on well down outside but never got in a blow.
Broke reasonably well but held up towards rear, made some ground out of back straight, not much room for a few strides, got out then finished well, but never near enough to challenge.
Wide early and dropped back to rear trio, ridden to keep place, improved a little out of back straight, hard ridden 400m out, gained some ground but never near winner, weakened last 50M.
Not rushed when leaders got away, fourth last in detached group far side, rear on rail as leaders turned into straight, made some ground between horses but never a factor.
Slowly into stride, dropped to rear, bustled but not much progress, on heels briefly far side, settled in rear as leaders got away, driven and some slight improvement but never near leader.
Relaxed early on outside looking for rail, rear group far side one off rail, tried to quicken in straight but no acceleration.

Broke well and ridden up towards lead on inside, second on rail after 300m, tried to go with leader and four lengths in front of third entering straight, beaten off and ran out of steam completely last 200m.
Fair break, tried to get lead early but left three wide in fourth entering straight with long gap to fourth, weakened quickly.
Ridden up early into distant fifth but could not go the pace of the leaders, weakened very quickly.
Angled back to race just behind midfield 5 to 6Ls off top end, had a reasonable trip to mid-section, checked at 400 M, didn't see daylight until 150 M, flew late to get up.
Out with rest, unable to slot in and raced 3 wide with cover in midfield, 5Ls or so back in circle, gradually worked into race from 300 M and looked winner before caught on line.
Drifted back soon after start, best part of 8 to 9Ls away at rear, tracked wide turning, made remarkable progress from well back in straight to snatch 3rd.
Taken down to rails soon after start, had soft run on fence 5Ls back to bend, held up badly at 300 M, clear final furlong and closed off soundly, unlucky.
Began well, in an ideal spot 1 out 1 back, travelled well to bend, loomed strongly and led inside 300 M, couldn't lift final 100 M.
Out in line, positioned behind speed 3 to 4Ls back in running line, close enough turning for home, worked to line evenly at same speed.
Reasonable break, easy time travelling behind speed 3Ls or so away on rails, spent nothing 400 M, just kept on behind them in straight.
Slow into stride, ended up 6 to 7Ls away on rails, aided by speed on at top end, didn't make an impression and just held ground in straight.
Away well, posted 3 wide outside horses without cover, did work 2 to 3Ls back in mid-section, niggled turning, didn't close off after early work.
Tardy into stride, raced behind midfield 6 to 7Ls back, still had job to do turning, made some progress to 200 M but was one paced thereafter.
jumped nicely, pushed up on leaders back, did some work with OK speed on, close enough turning, no response in straight.
Taken back after start, niggled along when a clear last more than 10Ls back, improved slightly to turn, just passed tired runners late.
Pushed on to race outside leader, contributed to decent tempo in mid-section, found little at 400 M and soon faded out.
Showed speed, lead at a decent tempo with pressure from outside horse, narrow advantage turning, gave in cheaply soon after and dropped out.

Settled in midfield or just worse, switched wide for a run turning in, quickened well to take charge close to home, readily.
Gradually improved to be within 2Ls of speed on rails, fought on steadily at the one pace without threatening in straight, jockey reported saddle shifted mid-race.
Broke well with a few others, gradually crossed from the wide gate to lead approaching home bend, held over 1L break early in straight, swamped close to home.
Struggled to keep up early, eventually picked up to midfield along rails, saved ground turning in, fought on steadily inside final 200 M without threatening.
Settled well behind after beginning from a wide draw, trailed the field to straight, widest turning in, finished off race well to do best work late.
Settled in last few, saved ground turning in, went steadily past well beaten horses.
Began moderately, gradually picked up to forward of midfield, 3L 5th turning in, found nil under pressure in straight.
Began fairly, gradually settled in last few, saved ground on rails turning in, kept on steadily at the one pace under pressure.
Began with others from the widest draw, ridden along to go the early speed, settled for one-out-one-back spot rounding home bend, tired noticeably upon straightening.
Niggled at to keep prominent position, gradually shuffled back to a wide midfield spot before home bend, made no impression thereafter.
Began moderately, soon picked up to midfield spot when least 3-wide, weakened in straight. (Questioned for disappointing performance.) (Lame next day.)

Placing: TNP
Comment: Missed the start badly, reluctant to race and took no part.
Camped on the back of the speed and from the circle raced 3-wide without cover. Rallied strongly over the final stages to snare victory.
Worked to the lead and crossed to the fence near the 700 M. set at even tempo, was collared late.
Settled slightly worse than midfield, 1 off with cover. Came wide from about the 500m, made some ground late.
Was prominently ridden but always raced 4 wide in the run, no cover. Maintained a sound gallop to the wire.
Parked 3-back the fence. peeled out after the 500 M, but was one paced in the final stretch.
Sent forward from a wide gate to cross and travel outside the leader. Was a spent force by the final furlong.
Raced 4-deep with cover behind midfield. Lost cover on the circle and was never likely from then on.
Tracked the leader along the rails. Was a beaten horse turning for home, no excuses.
Settled 1-out-1-back. Had every chance but came up well short at the business end.
Raced in last position along the paint. Made steady ground along the inside on tiring runners.
Travelled wide for most of the trip with cover at the tail of the field. Made no impression in the home straight.
Began awkwardly settling behind midfield 3-deep with cover. Raced tight between runners for some distance after the 900 M. Struggled in the straight. (To trial prior to racing again).
Rolled forward after start and took prominent spot from stable bend. Attacked the lead into final stretch and hit front 200 M. Ran away to score easily.

Well enough away but was caught 4-wide. Slotted 2-wide behind midfield stable bend. Moved closer gradually from 700 M and was 4Ls down turning in. Dashed well to snatch 2nd near the post but was beaten far by the winner.
Hard ridden early to take lead on fence from stable bend. Held a 1L advantage into home straight. Caught by the winner at 200 M. Hung on for 2nd until close home.
Ahead of midfield on fence through to the home straight. Every chance but was one-paced to conclude.
Settled on fence as backmarker. Moved out for clear run and was 8Ls down passing 400 M. Covered good ground thereafter without troubling the principals.
Caught 3 to 4-wide ahead of midfield through to the home straight. Out of petrol thereafter.
Began fairly. Ridden for a better position but was forced to go 3-wide in midfield stable bend. Given reminder halfway but failed to progress. Ran on through tired runners late.
3-wide towards rear early and middle stages. Some progress along the fence behind midfield from 700 M. No extra final 200 M.
Niggled early to occupy a 2-wide spot at midfield. Never improved from there.
Taken to sit 2-wide towards rear. No progress at any stages
Never far off the speed until outpaced after straightening.
Tracked outside leader before swamped 300 M from home.
Back with last few always. No impression.
Broke well, then eased back to third last one off rail, improved slightly entering straight, pulled wide, finished fast, getting up close home.
Unhurried early, eased back to fifth last going well, pulled out to challenge in straight, finished well to lead 50 M out winner just too strong.
Not rushed early, took good position in third behind leader far side, second entering straight, ridden to lead at 200 M, fought on but unable to hold off first two.
Taken to rail, midfield early, improved into fourth entering back straight, challenged 400 M, hit front momentarily 100 M, weakened last 50 M.
Sent inside to rail in rear after start, went for run on rail in straight, gaps came at right time, but no real acceleration.
Broke well, led on rail after first turn, two lengths clear far side setting good pace, tried to clear away early in straight, but unable to accelerate, weakened last 100 M.
Six wide first turn, still wide and dropped to rear far side improved between horses early straight but his path blocked, pulled out and ran on quite well.
Ridden for an early position but beaten for speed to first turn, dropped out on far side, improved between horses but couldn't get a run and checked twice in mid straight, ran on.
Ridden for early position but three off rail and wheeling wide first turn, settled, tried to challenge wide in straight, others found more pace.
Broke well, vied for lead out wide, second one off rail far side, ridden approaching straight, gradually weakened.
Moderate start, midfield on outside early, refused to settle far side, tried to improve entering straight, found nothing.
Missed break, eased over to rail, pulling early, two length last after 300 M ridden and tried to improve on inside approaching straight, found nothing.
Broke well, determined attempt at lead but didn't make it, raced in fourth until approaching straight, driven, weakened quickly.
Bumped repeatedly on both sides wide first bend while seeking a position, dropped back, ridden approaching straight, not bullied when cause hopeless.
Broke fast but back to second last on rail after 300 M, made ground approaching home turn, fierce finish on rail to lead 100 M out and win going away.
Broke well, three wide at first turn, reined back to third, pulled out straight, led 150 M out, until winner swept past.
Broke well, fourth on rail after 200 M, slight interference back straight, pulled out in straight and finished well, but no chance with winner.
Ridden for early position on outside of leader, involved in battle for the lead, led entering straight still one off rail, kept on but no extra pace.
Joined early battle for lead, then raced in fourth in back straight, pulled out in straight then challenged on outside, ran on quite well.
Not get near lead or rail from wide draw, ridden straight and ran on past beaten horses.
Ridden hard for early lead on rail, harried and headed leaving back straight, tried to fight back straight, weakened late.
Fair break, raced wide in sixth early, then up to fourth one off rail, ridden early in straight, weakened.
Fair break, eased back, but still three off rail, made ground wide entering straight, ran on but no impression.
Slowly away, last on rail early, made ground on inside, then checked by horse dropping back early in straight, ran on reasonably well but never near leaders.
Slightly awkward break, and no early pace, dropped back to long last, ran past only one beaten horse in straight.
Broke well, ridden into fourth on rail after 300 M, dropped back sharply entering straight as though something wrong, allowed to come home in his own time.
Settled just behind the leaders 2-wide, favoured by the slow pace, demonstrated strong finishing efforts 300 M to win by a neck.
Pushed to sit outside the lead, benefited by the slow early tempo, closed the race off strongly 300 M, just beaten by a neck in 2nd.
Pushed to take the rail and led by 1/2L at advantageous slow sectionals, soon under pressure and overhauled 300 M, ran on for 3rd.
Settled in box seat, enjoyed the slow early sectionals, just held ground in straight.
Eased back, 6Ls off the leaders, trapped 3 to 4-wide and lost ground, dashed well 250 M despite harmed by the slow pace.
At rear, pushed along to keep up with the field, 7Ls off the leaders on the fence, not suited by the slow pace, little dash 200 M.
Very slow away, behind midfield, 4-1/2Ls off the leaders 3-wide, harmed by the slow pace, no turn of foot in final quarter.
At rear, 7-1/2Ls off the leaders 3 to 4-wide, harmed by the slow pace, no progress in final stages.
Eased to sit 4Ls off the leaders along the rails, not suited by the slow tempo, never better than midfield.
Pushed early but failed to muster, not suited by the slow pace at rear, never a factor.
Midfield, 4Ls off the leaders 2-wide, not suited by the slow tempo, dropped off quickly 600 M.
Very awkward away, behind midfield along the fence, faded 400 M. (Bled 2nd time.)
Fair break but no route to rail, wide throughout early part of race, improved three wide home turn to lead 300 M out, ran on very well.
Broke well, ridden up to take good sit following leader on rail holding place comfortably, pulled out to challenge mid-straight, winner too good.
Broke slowly, held up towards rear, forward move on outside entering straight, ran on well.
Broke well but unhurried, took up midfield position on rail, made ground approaching straight, challenged between horses but denied clear run, finished well.
Not hurried early, held rail position in midfield in midfield, fifth down back straight, challenged on inside with no serious traffic problems, just not quick enough.
Broke quite slowly, near rear and outside back straight, moved up on outer approaching home turn, driven but never quite able to challenge, weakened last 50 M.
Good break, up to share lead on outside, then dropped back to second, led early in straight until 300 M, weakened.
Quick break, fourth one off rail far side, close up fifth and chance mid-straight, not quicken.
Fair break, sixth one off rail far side, lost pitch entering straight, ran on quite well to finish just behind leading group.
Slow into stride, held up rear, improved wide entering straight, kept on but no real progress.
Ridden early, good speed to lead on rail, settled in front far side, narrow lead into straight, ridden, weakened.
Broke fairly well but not go early pace, back to midfield one off rail, ridden early straight, no kick.
Moderate start, crossed to rail in third last, struggled to keep place, dropped to last entering straight although ridden, no improvement.
Moderate start, midfield on outside early, refused to settle far side, tried to improve entering straight, found nothing.
Taken across from a wide draw and raced as the back marker 8Ls behind leaders, waited with till 350 M then came strongly from near last to take the race close home.

Made some use early to maintain a position midfield, quietly moved to a striking position approaching the top of the straight, quickened well to lead 200 M out but was caught by the fast finishing winner in dying strides.
With leaders early, dropped back to chasing group on entering the back straight, stuck to inside throughout, picked up well final 300 M but was comfortably held at the line.
Not hurried in early stages, settled 2nd last 7Ls off the modest pace, taken outside to make his run, ran on well from the back of the field and narrowly missed out on 3rd.
Never far off in 5th, came through to challenge after straightening but lacked the extra pace over final 200 M.
Taken back early, 3-wide turning for home, had every chance inside 400 M and plugged on for a never dangerous 6th.
Close to the pace all the way, briefly took over early straight, had every chance but could not find extra when challengers loomed up on both sides nearing 200 M.
Held up on the inside 5Ls back in mid-division, didn't have the clearest of runs in straight and had to be angled out for room near 200 M, made modest late gains when clear.
Travelled 2-wide in midfield and well covered, ran on fairly to 200 M but found no extra late on.
Obtained a rail spot in mid-division, 4Ls behind passing 400 M but held up by beaten runner in mid-stretch, made minor headway once switched back to the rail.
Placed handily behind leader after cutting out the early running, found disappointingly little when the race got serious, eased 100 M out.
Placed 3-wide in midfield in early stages, moved to outside of leaders nearing 400 M but gave very limited response once under pressure, weakened badly close home.
Caught wide on the 1st turn until reaching the lead 1200 M, was collared approaching home straight and ran out of it passing 250 M, weakened rapidly.
Towards the rear 6Ls back and never travelled at any stage, soon left behind turning in, eased. (Unacceptable performance.)

Began fairly, settled on rails in rear of midfield, baulked early in straight, quickened inside 250 M to gain upper hand final strides.
Midfield on rails, saved ground turning in, baulked early in straight, ran on steadily down inner for every chance throughout final stages.
Began fairly from a wide draw, soon came across to settle 2-wide in 4th about 2Ls off the speed, hit front momentarily over 200 M out, only to be denied in the closing stages by a small margin.
Began awkwardly, midfield before taking closer order around the bend, quickened to hold some chance early in straight, unable to sustain effort close to home.
Settled in midfield, fought on dourly under pressure early in straight, but unable to sustain progress nearing home.
Began very awkwardly losing ground, remained towards the rear, shifted wide turning for home, produced moderate late impression.
Began well, among leaders early settling outside the lead in 2nd spot, hit the front briefly on straightening, soon weakened out of it under pressure.
Forward of midfield on rails within 3Ls of speed, tight run early in straight and checked passing 200 M, not recover.
Began moderately, soon settled one back in 3rd on rails, faded gradually in the run home.
Began from the widest barrier, travelled wide in forward of midfield without any cover to straight, made no impression under pressure.
Always well behind and never seen with a chance. (Questioned for disappointing performance.)
Checked at start, always struggling. (Questioned for disappointing performance.)
Broke well to soon lead on rails, held half a length advantage until headed into straight, weakened under pressure.
Jostled at start, always well behind, no response under pressure around the bend.
Enjoyed a nice run in the race, midfield the fence. Angled out into clear running soon after turning for home, and let down nicely to register a solid win.
Had a dream run behind the leader along the paint. Peeled out early in the straight and worked home soundly.
Wasn't given a lot of peace in the lead along the fence, faded in the final stretch.
Settled 3 back and 3 deep with cover. Kept on at the same speed in the run to the finishing post.
Taken back from a wide gate to race at the rear of the field with cover. Shifted out further rounding the home turn and in the straight made sound ground.
Overraced for the better part of the trip 2-3 wide with cover, close to midfield. Kept on one paced.
Raced behind midfield, 1 off with cover. Became one paced over the final stages.
Camped midfield 1 off with cover. Kept grinding to the line but not in a position to finish in the frame.
Slow to begin settling with the rear division, 1 off with cover. Worked home steadily without threatening.
Taken back at the start to settle at the rear. 2 to 3-wide with cover. Had to be checked near the 600, came up somewhat one paced in the run home.
Settled early 1 out 1 back. Hung on the circle and was not likely hereafter.
Travelled worse that midfield the fence, 3-wide with cover. Failed to close off.
Ridden with plenty of enthusiasm to improve and eventually crossed to sit outside the leader near the 900m. Was gassed early in the straight.
Travelled behind midfield, rolled to the fence after the 900 copped a check soon after but was never a factor.
Pressed early. Got the fence and led home turn. Challenged throughout the straight but hung on well for victory.

Hard ridden early from high draw. Sat one-off the fence behind leader home turn. Battled gamely with the winner until fended off closing stages. Barely hung on to deny the strong finishing 3rd placegetter at the post.
Eased to rear from high draw. 8Ls away rounding the turn. Switched widest for clear run passing 400M. Dashed home impressively to nearly snatch 2nd.

Urged along the fence to sit midfield. Moved closer to race 2-wide behind leading section turning into home. Launched attack passing 300M. Matched strides with the front pair but couldn't catch them. Lost 3rd close home.
Dropped 3-wide towards rear from wide barrier. Similar position near the fence and was 7Ls down leaving the bend. Shifted out for clear run passing 400M. Ran on well to cover good ground.
Raced 2-wide behind midfield early. Hampered and was taken 4-wide near 700M. One-paced to conclude.
Niggled early but could only stay towards rear on fence through to home straight. Kept on to make up some late ground.
Jumped well but insufficient speed to lead. Urged along to stay 3-wide behind midfield passing 1100M. Improved wide and without cover from 700M. Failed to sustain its run home straight.
Shaken up early to maintain 2-wide near the pace. Driven to race with leaders turning in. Looked dangerous top of home straight but peaked final furlong.
Travelled wide behind midfield throughout. Finished off fairly.
Raced 2-wide towards rear through to home turn. Came close to heels and was steadied near home straight. Past beaten rivals thereafter.
Prominent spot through to home straight. Found nothing when asked and was swamped inside 400M.
Out nicely but couldn't work across. Elected to stay 3-wide ahead of midfield until dropped out after straightening.
Raced 2-wide behind midfield early. Shuffled to midfield at bend. Plodded on home.
Broke well, but taken back, fourth last back straight, made ground four wide entering straight, finished strongly to lead on the line.
Broke well, up to third on outside 400m, second into straight, won extended battle with longtime leader, headed on the line.
Broke fast, led wide early, led by two lengths into straight, fought on very well but collared 150m out.
Slow jump, dropped to rear, unhurried early, improved on outside entering straight, ran on strongly down outside, but flattened last 50m.
No rush early, back to last after 400m, two lengths last entering straight, pulled wide, ran on quite well, but never really threatened.
Fair break, raced midfield, one off rail, trapped behind horses in straight, going very well, got out too late, then ran on well.
Fair break but back towards mid/rear on rail far side, challenged between horses in straight, but not quite quick enough to take a gap, slightly checked, then ran on.
Jumped well but headed off for lead by runners from outside, raced fourth on rail, tried to challenge between runners straight, ran on but never dangerous.
Broke well, taken back to midfield, improved three wide approaching straight, ridden, no acceleration.
Fair break but no early speed, settled on rail in third last far side, slight check leaving back straight, went for rail run but no gaps available, pulled out and ran on well when in the clear.
Broke slowly, made ground to lead briefly early, then back to third on rail, ridden early in straight, no improvement, weakened.
Broke well, but not much early pace, fifth, one off rail far side, ridden home turn attempting challenge between horses, enough room, but no progress.
Wide back straight, forced three wide, third approaching straight, ridden, weakened, lost two places last 25m.
Awkward start, ridden up on rail into midfield, tried to challenge on rail, ridden, no response.
No rush early, held up third last, improved on turn and launched down outside, finished fast, comfortably.
Broke well, midfield rail position, slight check far side, improved between horses entering straight, challenged towards inside, unable to match winner's finish.
Fair break, ridden to lead early, length clear into straight, two lengths clear 250m to go, cut down by first two.
Ridden up three wide for share of lead, crossed to rail and tracked leader in third place, tried to challenge mid-straight, weakened.
Only midfield after 200m, ridden up into fifth, challenged four wide in straight, never dangerous.
Wide early, reached fifth place one off rail entering straight, challenged in mid-track, no real impression.
Very awkward start, losing several lengths, last by four lengths after 300m, closed up approaching straight, pulled wide and finished well under urging.
Mediocre break, mid to rear one off rail far side, ridden entering straight, checked mid straight, ran on after.
Slight bobble at start, ridden up to fourth three wide, taken back to rail, pulled out entering straight to challenge mid-track, no response.
Lost length at start, second last early, bustled entering straight, ridden and slight check 200m out, ran on but never a danger.
Missed a beat at start, checked far side, four wide, improved wide into home turn, stayed on fairly well.
Ridden for lead on rail, headed and reined back to sixth, no progress in straight, vets report lost front plate - and coughed next day.
Broke well, ridden for lead but caught three wide, second one off rail into straight, ridden but checked quite badly 300m out, found nothing thereafter.
Good break, vied for early lead then reined back to midfield, dropped to rear entering straight, no progress.
Pushed to share the lead at good pace 2 wide, ran on well to the line and just scored consecutive goal by a nose.
Pushed to take the rail and led at good pace, pressured throughout, hung on strongly, just beaten on the line.
Eased to sit in midfield, 2.5Ls off the good pace 2 wide, progressed steadily 300M to grab 3rd.
Pushed to keep up just behind midfield, 4.5Ls off the good pace, trapped 3-4 wide, progressed steadily 400M, run ended 100M.
Eased back, 7.5Ls off the good pace 2 wide, made steady ground 250M.
Eased back, 6Ls off the good pace 2-3 wide, progressed steadily 300M whilst hanging in.
Maintained the box seat throughout, pace good, no turn of foot and just held ground in straight.
Eased to rear, 9Ls off the leaders 2-3 wide, pace good, dashed well 250M.
Obtained a more prominent spot just behind the lead 2 wide, raced keenly as the pace slackened 1000M, ran on until 200M flattened.
Pushed early but failed to muster, held the rails in midfield, 3Ls off the leaders, pace good, no turn of foot in straight.
Pressed forward early, soon eased to sit in midfield, shifted to 3 wide as the pace slackened 1000M, raced keenly 2Ls off the leaders, weakened 250M.
Settled in midfield on the rails early, shifted to 3 wide 1200M, forced to race 4 wide and went forward 1.5Ls off the leaders as the pace slackened 1000M, emptied 400M. (Rider questioned.)
Eased to sit behind midfield along the fence, never a factor.
Settled behind the leaders early, trapped 3 wide without cover, went forward and sat outside the leaders when the pace slackened 1000M, soon dropped off 500M.
Broke fast wide out, settled in second one off rail, led early in straight, went two lengths clear, held on well.
Fair break, midfield, improved to sixth entering straight, challenged down middle of course, ran on well.
Fair beak, reined back and held up third last, improved on outside entering straight, challenged wide and ran on, weakened slightly last 50m.
Broke well but taken back and held up rear of midfield, slight check when trying to improve at home turn, pulled out wide in straight and ran on quite well, never nearer.
Fair break, wide just behind leaders early, fourth one off rail into straight, but never able to threaten.
Fast away, back to fourth on rail, driven between horses in straight, not enough pace to threaten.
Smart enough break but no interest in early battle for lead, held up, eighth into straight, tried to challenge middle to inside, stayed on one pace.
Missed beat at break, not hurried in fourth last early, third last into straight, driven on inside, made some ground but no real impression.
Fast away, led on rail, headed and rated in second, pulled out to challenge in straight, found nothing.
Unhurried start, tracked over from wide berth, shared last place until pulled out and tried to improve entering straight, passed beaten horses late.
Slow break, last and pulling slightly early on, still last into straight, tried to improve but no impression.
Away well on wide outside, used up plenty to take lead and cross to rail, led into straight, headed 400m out, weakened.
Quick break, eased back to midfield on rail, improved towards straight, tried to quicken between runners, no pace to challenge.
Led from 1400 M and dictated the pace from thereon, went a decent gallop and kicked almost 2Ls clear inside 300 M, kept on well enough in late stages to hold his pursuers at bay.

Placed behind midfield along the fence and travelled strongly 4 to 5Ls off the pace, had no clear run in early straight before a gap appeared nearing 200 M, finished best of all and came within half length of the winner.
Positioned 3-wide in midfield, switched out 450 M to challenge, gradually responded and went 3rd close home.
Moved forward to race at the shoulder of the leader, held every chance, lacked extra pace to challenge seriously but kept on well for 4th.
Switched off to rear 7Ls off the pace, held up 300 M then made late headway to finish 5th never nearer. (Jockey reminded to make every endeavour to avail himself of clear running.)
Soon taken across from draw 14, keen at the back in early stages, switched widest approaching home straight, ran on fairly without ever looking likely to take a hand in the finish.

Began well then dropped back to a position behind midfield, well covered throughout but got into difficulties when trying to squeeze between horses 200 M out, ran on late without reaching the leaders.
Soon crossed to the fence and obtained a prominent position just behind leaders, kept on one-paced under pressure. (Jockey obliged to stop riding over final 50 M.)
Placed in 6th 3Ls off the pace and had a smooth run along the rail, briefly threatened near 300 M but couldn't sustain his effort, gradually weakened.
Given a patient ride in the rear, shifted away from fence passing 500 M but was held up until passing 200 M, made late gains when clear.
Close enough in the first half, came under pressure rounding the home turn and outpaced gradually inside 400 M.
Ordinary jump, moved forward to a 3-wide position in chasing group just off the pace, driven 400 M but found no response and was done with inside 200 M.
Settled 2-wide in midfield, well placed to challenge turning in but failed to pick up, steadied near 100 M then eased.
Began very awkwardly, refused to race and consequently became detached from the field, never in contention.
Broke sharply, followed leaders on outside as field tracked over to near rail, out to challenge and soon led 200m out, ran on very well.
Missed break, rear on far side after 200m, improved under pressure far side, ran on strongly without getting blow at winner.
Fast away, crossed to rail and led, still narrow leader 200m out, ridden, unable to resist first two.
Slightly awkward start, towards rear after 200m, ran on in middle of course, passed by second late.
Fidgety in the stalls but broke well on outside, widest of four leaders mid point of race, winner swept past, followed by others.
Broke well, rated behind near side leaders, no immediate gap when required, but ran on quite well when one appeared.
Broke quite well on what became wide outside, ridden halfway, no progress, weakened.
Reared slightly when gate opened but soon made up ground, rail position behind leaders, plenty of room but not quicken, weakened slightly late.
Fair break, settled in behind leading group going well, no gaps appeared for him to drive into or would probably have finished closer.
Fair start, led in centre, then three off rail as field crossed to near side, just the leader 250m out until mobbed by finishers and weakened.
Fair break, not much room early, midfield behind leaders, ridden 400m out, found little.
Jumped well, led early, one of four leaders halfway, ridden, weakened.
Good break, settled behind leaders near side, ridden, failed to quicken.
Squeezed at start and fell back last on rail, tried to quicken halfway, found nothing.
Pressed on to slot in 3Ls off pace in 2 wide line, came 3 wide on circle, into mix from 300 M, asserted authority thereafter and ran out convincing winner.
Box seated in 1 out 1 back slot tracking decent speed, improved on turn and loomed as a serious threat, no match for winner final 250 M.
Taken back from a wide gate, settled last 8Ls off top end, pace suited, came to middle in straight and worked home soundly for 3rd from impossible spot.
Behind midfield from an awkward alley, best part of 7Ls back, shifted back on circle, had a bit to do straightening but finished off OK to make frame.
Pushed forward from widest alley, used to lead and not given peace in front, headed turning and fought to 250 M but couldn't find extra thereafter.
Trapped wide from an awkward alley, 3-4 wide 6Ls or so back, had cover on circle, kept on reasonably in circumstances.
Positive early, raced on speed first behind leader, had reasonable run to turn, didn't improve when run presented and struggled last 200 M.
No speed early, settled 5Ls back on rails, used little in run, took inside runs on turning in, made some ground to 200 M before emptied.
Lacked pace as usual, ended up 3 wide 5-6Ls back, lost spot on circle, back in pack near last turning, made some minor progress. (See Racing Incidents.)
Showed usual speed but unable to slot in, posted 3 wide without cover outside leaders, worked too hard to bend, levelled up turning but soon under pressure and faded out.
Reasonable break, raced 3Ls back on rails, had a quiet time in mid-section, struggling to pick up turning, condition gave out in straight.
Missed kick, rushed forward but planted 3 wide, pushed 4 wide without cover on circle, worked too hard in run, gave in turning and was beaten a long way.
Standard jump, 5Ls or so away in running line, raced ungenerously on bend, weakened out of it cheaply.
Even break, went forward to challenge for front, applied pressure to 400 M, not much there and folded tamely.

Settled in midfield on rails, commenced run 3-wide around the bend, sustained effort to gain upper hand shortly after straightening, fought on dourly.
Soon restrained to race in 5th just better than midfield, circled the field swiftly around the bend, fought on gamely in straight but never able to draw level.

Slowly away, soon improved to forward position, raced wide around stables bend to take lead turning into back straight, ceded advantage going up Rock to trail leader into straight, every chance early on but unable to sustain run at the 50 M.

Tightened at start dropping to last few, made swift progress far side to lead from the Rock, held advantage into straight but gradually worn down under pressure, swamped for a placing inside final 50 M.

Benefitted from the one draw to lead early, soon conceded lead rounding stables bend to settle just off the speed on rails throughout far side, fought on under pressure without quickening in the run home.
Minor interference at start, travelled in well back position to straight, saved ground turning in, kept on steadily past well beaten horses, did best work late.
Soon restrained to race in last few, saved ground turning in, made some late impression final stages.
Jumped awkwardly, settled on rails in midfield, shifted wide for a run turning for home, made no headway.
Settled in rear of midfield or just worse, went wide into straight, made no impression.
Quickly into stride to cross for rails run and settle in 4th within 3Ls of speed, gradually shuffled backward after the Rock, saved ground turning for home, found nothing under pressure in straight.
Taken across the rear of field after beginning from the widest barrier, remained well behind throughout.
Soon driven from a high draw for a prominent spot, settled in 3rd or 4th about 2Ls off the speed, remained similar turning in and gradually faded out of it after straightening. (Lame.)
Enjoyed all the favours tracking the leader on the fence, maintained the inside running in the home straight and never looked in doubt.
Travelled worse than midfield, 2 deep with cover. Was stoked up after the 500m, and rounding the home turn came widest. Closed off soundly.
Parked about 3 back along the paint. Shifted out near the 300m, and ran an honest race to the wire.
Rolled forward to lead along the rails. Maintained a fair gallop to the finish.
Camped 3 back 1 off with cover. Peeled out rounding the home turn but didn't show any turn of foot.
Settled midfield 1 off with cover. Kept on one paced in the run to the line.
Travelled on the fence towards the rear of the field. Kept to the inside in the straight but never ran on.
Settled behind midfield,1 off with cover. Failed to quicken in the home straight.
Slow to begin settling with the backmakers, 1 off with cover. Made no impression in the home straight.
Used plenty of gas after being caught wide early to go forward and take up equal leading duties mid race, tired from bend.
Had to do some early work to cross and race settle outside the leader near the 1200m. Took up a trailing position 1 off midrace, was checked near the furlong and faded soon after.
Blew the start and after trailing the field was never a factor.
Away in line. Found the fence behind midfield first turn. Picked up gradually down the Rock and was 5Ls away on straightening. Responded well under hands and heels. Took charge close to home.

Standard jump. Slotted at midfield on fence first turn. Urged along from the Rock and was 4Ls down turning in. Every chance but failed to fend off the winner closing stages. Hung on for 2nd by narrow margin.
Prominent spot through to home straight. Caught the leader passing 200 M but couldn't contain the front pair final stages. All out to hold 3rd.
Quickly into stride but was trapped 3-wide. Elected to sit one-out-one-back from first turn. Looked threatening passing 200 M but unable to sustain its effort critical stages.
At rear through to home straight. Covered some late ground down the centre of the track but was beaten fair way by the principals.
Soon led on fence. Attempted to run away passing 600 M and opened a 2Ls gap leaving the bend. Hung on until weakened passing 200 M.
2-wide towards rear early and middle stages. Hard ridden and was 8Ls adrift passing 450 M. Made some headway but was of limited significance overall.
Never better than midfield. No response when asked from 500 M.
2-wide at midfield from first turn. Couldn't follow when the race got serious passing 450 M.
Always at rear on fence. Beat tired runners home.
Moderate start and was taken to sit towards rear on fence. Never improved from there.
Raced 2-wide behind the pace until faded passing 500 M. Finished tailed out.
Good break but no great early speed, settled fifth on rail, pulled out entering straight, path blocked momentarily, challenged four wide, ran on, just got up.
Quick break on rail to share lead, then back to third on rail, ridden leaving back straight, found split on rail, squeezed through to lead, just nailed last few strides.
Not the fastest away, but plenty of speed to lead by over a length after 400 M, led into straight until second got through on his inside, fought on well but no extra.
Fastest away but headed after 200 M, raced second one off rail, challenged straight and ran on quite well, but could not get past.
Fair break, midfield one off rail back straight, challenged five wide entering straight, slightly short of room 300 M out, finished quite well.
Reined back from wide draw and held up last, ridden leaving back straight, made some ground between horses straight but never able to challenge.
Fair break but fourth last one off rail after 300 M, improved three wide entering straight, ran on down middle of the course but not enough pace to challenge, weakened last 50 M.
Fair break but not rushed early, midfield back straight and bustled along, sixth on rail into straight, no progress.
Fair break, up three wide into fourth, still wide home turn, gradually lost ground straight.
Reined back from widest draw, second last, three wide all the way, challenged widest of all, no extra.
Good break, bustled out of gate but only sixth one off rail exiting back straight, ridden, could not quicken.
Not enough early pace to take advantage of good draw and decent break, towards rear, ridden on inside, found little.
Fast out on rail, headed and settled in third, going well entering straight but route blocked half way up, pulled out of pocket, finished fast, got up.
Ridden up early to take position outside leader, challenged and lead 300 M out, caught near line.
Not rushed from wide draw, slight check after 200 M, held up last, improved leaving back straight, brought wide, ran on well.
Fast break, led after 150 M, set pace in his own time, tried to kick clear nut headed mid straight, weakened near line.
Always wide from outside draw, up to fourth leaving back straight, ridden entering straight, ran on quite well but not quicken.
Fast break, hard ridden early, then settled fifth, tried to improve leaving back straight, drive, found little.
Well enough away but could never quite get to inside, raced one off rail throughout, tried to challenge three wide into straight, weakened.
Fast break but not involved in battle for lead, rear early, then improved to midfield entering turn, driven in middle of course, little acceleration.
Lost half length at start, held up midfield, modest progress two off rail in straight until path blocked last 150 M.
Fair break but checked after 100 M, third last one off rail exiting back straight, not much room in straight, but no progress anyway.
Lost length at start, ridden up on rail into sixth, niggled back straight, tried to improve on rail, no impression.
Fair break but lost ground abruptly almost immediately afterwards, raced in second last, last into straight, found nothing.
Pushed to take the rail and shared the lead at good pace, just hung on well enough to win by a short head.
Pushed to occupy a more prominent spot in front of midfield, 3Ls off the good pace 2 wide, progressed steadily 250M, just beaten by a narrow margin in 2nd.
Hard ridden to cross and shared the lead 2 wide at good pace, closed the race off strongly to take 3rd.
Fair break, up to third one off rail far side, three wide home turn, challenged down middle of course, no extra close to home.
Eased to sit in midfield, 5Ls off the good pace 2 wide, made ground steadily 200M.

Slow away, hard ridden to gain a forward spot at good pace, however trapped 4 wide throughout without cover and lost too much ground on bend, held ground in straight despite all negative racing situations.
Eased back, 6Ls off the good pace, raced 3 wide throughout, made steady ground in last quarter.
Pushed to obtain the box seat, ran on ok behind the good pace, checked 400M, flattened in straight.
Pushed to hold a rail spot behind midfield, 6Ls off the good pace, ran on fairly in final stages.
Very slow away, pushed early to keep up with the field at tail, 9Ls off the good pace along the fence, made some ground in straight.
Very slow away, at rear, 7.5Ls behind the good pace 2 wide, made minor ground 200M.
Eased back, hung out badly and raced 4 wide throughout, never competitive.
Fair break, up to third one off rail exiting straight, back to fifth far side, challenged between horses straight, hit front 200 M out, held on.
Broke well but reined back to rail from outside draw, improved three wide and between horses approaching straight, ran on strongly, just failed.
Jumped well from inside stall, made running, joined approaching straight, ran on gamely, winner too strong.
Taken back after start to fourth last one off rail, waited with, tracking eventual runner-up, finished well but not enough.
Broke well, fourth on rail almost entire trip until pulled out mid-straight, ran on well but not able to challenge.
Not rushed early, last passing post first time, moved up wide back straight, challenged three wide approaching home turn, stayed on one pace.
Not quick enough from gate to get good early position, eased back to near rear to take rail, pulled out to challenge early in straight, never nearer.
Taken back to rail near rear, last far side, ridden approaching straight, driven and improved between horses, never able to threaten leaders.
Ridden up on outside to share lead one off rail, then travelled in second, middle of three-way battle for lead entering straight, driven, weakened.
Broke well, restrained in fifth one off rail far side, ridden and improved approaching straight, weakened.
Lost length at start, rail position midfield, ridden straight, found nothing.
Ridden early looking for a position but caught three wide, ridden far side but dropped back last anyway, weakened, tailed off.
Raced keenly behind leaders, quickly moved to the lead 250 M, pressed strongly by the runner-up over final 200 M but found enough to hold on.
Unable to cross and was forced wide in early stages, held up towards the rear and made his move approaching 400 M, quickened well and pushed the winner all the way to the line.
Led as expected but was taken on for the lead approaching back straight, headed 250 M but battled on well and held on for 3rd.
Settled in a 2-wide position 5Ls off the pace, crept closer rounding the home bend, quickened to go 4th near 200 M, kept on to line but was never getting to the first two.
Dropped back to a position behind midfield, switched away from fence halfway round the home turn, into clear 300 M and made steady progress from off the pace.
Well placed tracking the leaders but could keep on same paced from 300 M out.
Switched off the back on jumping from a wide barrier, waited with till 500 M then driven along to improve round the outside of field, ran on final 300 M without threats.
Positioned midfield along the inside but never posed much of a threat after being pushed along passing 400 M, eased final 150 M.
Taken across behind runners and travelled in the rear group 8Ls off the lead, became detached making the home turn and not quickened under pressure.
From an outside draw was gradually brought across to press the pace, under pressure 450 M and soon beaten, eased 200 M.
Checked after the start, strode forward making the 1st turn and reached the lead near 1000 M, 3-wide no cover to straight and faded away inside 400 M, eased.

Began from a low draw, never far off down centre of the track, commenced move inside final 200 M to take charge over 100 M out, won readily.
Settled in forward of midfield within 3Ls of speed, finished off race well inside final 400 M to do best work late.
Always there and thereabouts, failed to quicken to respond to first two's late surge of speed.
Never far off, came under pressure inside final 250 M but failed to quicken to threaten. (Blood in trachea.)
Prominently placed 1L behind the leader, travelled well until badly checked at 400 M, only one-paced when asked.
Led or disputed lead to 400 M, weakened noticeably under pressure.
Quickly into stride, travelled with leaders to 400 M, weakened out of it under pressure.
Ridden along to keep up early but soon dropped well behind.
Slow away, travelled well back and never seen with a chance.
With leaders to half-way, gradually weakened out of it after coming onto course proper.
Close up briefly, soon taken backward to race behind pace, found nothing under pressure after coming onto course proper.
Close up early, dropped out under pressure approaching course proper.
Very sluggish at start, never on terms.
Slow away, urged along throughout and travelled 5-6Ls behind the pace, gave no response when asked for efforts final 400 M, finished tailed out.
Sent forward to travel as the leading duo along the paint. Kicked clear near the 300m to land a solid win.
Missed the start settling with the backmakers 2 deep with cover. Peeled out early in the straight and despite racing greenly made nice late ground.
Raced towards the rear of the field along the rail. Closed off soundly.
Rated 3 back, 1 off with cover. Rolled out rounding the home turn, maintained a steady gallop to the wire.
Had every chance after stalking the leading pair along the rail, weakened over the final stages.
Worked forward to race as leader for the better part of the trip, 1 off. Faded inside the furlong.
Camped midfield the fence. Was disappointed for running near the furlong and went to the line fairly.
Travelled about midfield, 2-3 wide with cover. Kept on one paced in the final stretch.
Settled behind midfield, 1 off with cover. Wacked away at the same speed in the run to the line.
Travelled at the tail of the field along the rail. Fenced up in the straight but failed to close off.
Raced worse than midfield, 3 deep with cover. Struggled in the run home.
Ridden along early then overraced when travelling 1 out 1 back. Continued to pull hard and was shifted out near the 800 M to race 3 wide without cover thereafter. Not likely.
Showed good early speed as usual. Led all the way. Never challenged.
Raced within 2Ls of the winner but could never get closer. Held 2nd with comfort.
Slow to begin. Covered lost ground gradually and was 2 to 3Ls behind the leader midpoint. Ran on for 3rd but was far beaten by the front pair.
Away in line and sat towards rear near the stands' side early. Urged from 700M and got clear run at midfield 400M out. Just plugged on for a non-threatening 4th.
On leader's back along stands' rail but couldn't accelerate with the pace which quickened passing 400M.
Soon detached. Responded well when asked near 400M and covered substantial ground late.
Towards rear near the centre of the track early. Improved to midfield midpoint. No further headway from there.
Broke well, settled 3Ls off the speed, outpaced midway, gave very limited response under pressure final 400 M, soon faded.
Behind midfield always. Never any real progress.
Raced within 3Ls of the pace until no extra passing 400M.
Drawn low, took up running on the far side towards rear early. Improved to midfield at 600M but failed to make up further ground. Weakened final 150M.
Back with last few always. Never a factor.
Towards rear near the far side early. Found nothing when asked passing midpoint. Plodded on home.
Sat midfield early. Struggled from midpoint. No impression.
Good break wide out, midfield three wide after 400m, challenged three wide in straight, hit front 300m out, ran on well.
Back through field from wide draw, bustled early, second last on rail back straight, short of room early in straight, ran on very strongly on inside rail.
Fair break, up to fourth one off rail far side, third into home turn, ridden to almost join winner 300m out, could not get past.
Slow break, towards rear on rail early, not much room on inside in straight, pulled out and stayed on steadily.
No early rush, three wide back straight in midfield, pulled out for a run in straight, reached third place then weakened slightly.
Broke well, held up mid to rear on rail, challenged on inside, weakened last 50m.
Sluggish start, back to rear, some improvement wide on home turn, ran on wide.
Good break, ridden early to get near lead, settled midfield when failed to do so, niggled back straight and lost ground, no run early in straight, ran on quite well when gap appeared.
Quickly away but headed off, took rail position on inside midfield, bustled leaving back straight, ridden straight, found little.
Driven from outside stall to lead by three lengths after 450m, still good lead leaving back straight, two lengths clear half way up straight, headed, weakened.
Sluggish start, ridden early, third last far side, tried to improve leaving back straight, ridden on outside, found little.
Fair break but not rushed from outside draw, three wide in fifth last far side, ridden in straight, no progress.
Broke well, up with lead, then fourth on rail, ridden leaving back straight, weakened.
Fair break, ridden early, clear second far side, ridden straight, no response.
Not rushed after decent break, fifth one off rail out of back straight, spun wider home turn, challenged down middle of course, hit front 100m out, held on well.
Fair break, disputed lead, back to third, three wide home turn, ran on to lead mid-straight, just run out of it.
Not fastest away, midfield three wide, ridden and lost a little ground back straight, ran on well for vigorous hands and heels riding in straight.
Good break, wide early, reined back towards rear, ridden approaching straight, ran on gamely.
Not much speed out of gate, settled second last on rail, made ground approaching home turn, ran on well in straight.
Fast break, took position one off rail in fourth, improved on inside in straight, not pace to challenge.
Slowish break, caught wide, taken back, but still three or four wide entering straight, ran on well.
Steadied after start, three wide back straight, four wide into straight, ran on but never able to challenge.
Broke well, disputed early lead on wide outside, led after 400m, crossed to rail, ridden and headed mid-straight, weakened.
All went well early as broke fast and took up rail position inside leader, held that place until challenged one off rail straight, then ridden, weakened.
Fair start, reined back to take rail in rear six, checked far side and dropped back last, ran on in straight but never able to challenge.
Fast break on wide outside, but drifted back to share of last as bend unwound, widest into straight, never on terms.
Missed break, ridden up on rail to join leading group, midfield turning out of back straight, weakened.
Fair break, hard ridden to take lead on rail, headed after 250m, gradually lost ground thereafter.
Eased back, 5Ls off the leaders 3-4 wide, harmed by the slow pace, dashed strongly 300M to win.
Pushed to obtain a midfield spot, 3Ls off the leaders 3-4 wide, raced very keenly, moved up 600M and took advantages of the slow sectionals, led 400M, hung on until 150M overhauled, ran on for 2nd.
Eased back, 4.5Ls off the leaders 2-3 wide, dashed well 200M to grab 3rd despite not suited by the slow pace.
Eased at start, 6.5Ls off the leaders, harmed by the slow pace, raced 3-5 wide and lost too much ground, dashed well 400M, run ended 100M. (Lame morning after.)

Pushed to obtain a midfield spot, 3.5Ls off the leaders, harmed by the slow pace, trapped 4-5 wide without cover throughout and lost significant amount of ground, ran on well to the line despite all negative racing situations.
Hard ridden forward, 1.5Ls off the leaders 3 wide, benefited by the slow tempo, ran on until 200M emptied.
Settled in box seat, enjoyed the slow tempo, momentarily held up 400M, flattened 200M.
Bumped start, pushed to keep up with the field at rear, 6.5Ls off the leaders 2 wide, harmed by the slow tempo, little dash 200M.
Very slow away, at rear as usual, 6.5Ls off the leaders along the fence, harmed by the slow pace, blocked 4-2, ran on ok when clear.
Hard ridden to share the lead at slow sectionals 2 wide, soon weakened 400M.
Slow away, pushed to hold the rails behind midfield, 5Ls off the leaders, not suited by the slow pace, no turn of foot in straight.
Hard ridden to occupy a midfield spot on the rails, 3Ls off the leaders, not suited by the slow tempo, held up 4-2, flattened when clear.
Hard ridden to take the rail and shared the lead at slow sectionals, soon weakened 400M.
Pushed to obtain a prominent spot, 1.5Ls behind the slow pace 2 wide, held up 400M, dropped off 300M.
Quick break, but unhurried, eased back into fourth last one off rail, travelling comfortably, ridden at home turn, quickened well down outside, ran on strongly.
Broke well, led on rail, then eased back to third, made challenge in straight two off rail, ran on strongly, just outgunned.
Good break, three wide early then settled second one off rail, challenged and led 250m out until 50m from line.
Broke well, led after 300m, dictating pace, tried to kick clear entering straight, could not fend off first three.
Fair start, raced fourth one off rail after taking while to settle, ridden home turn, only laboured improvement.
Slowish break, back to second last on rail, last and ridden leaving back straight, made ground under driving in straight without ever threatening.
Moderate break, eager early, fifth on rail, urged far side, ridden entering straight, kept on but no real acceleration.
Fair break but no great early speed, third last on rail on settling, ridden entering straight, found little.
Slow start, shared last early, ridden leaving back straight, three wide into straight, no progress, eased late, tailed off.
Travelled well in 3rd, produced with a strong run to take it up passing 300M and maintained his effort to just last home.
Never far off in 4th, pressed forward passing 600M, lacked the winner's acceleration in early stretch but stayed on well final 200M and was closing all the way to the line.
Restrained to a rearward position 9Ls off the pace, produced a good late run inside 200M to go 3rd a few strides before the line.
Raced keenly behind midfield, taken widest to challenge, ran on without looking likely, drifted out under maximum pressure final 200 M.
Led uncontested at a steady pace, headed 300M, battled on, weakened in late stages and lost 3rd in dying strides. Good effort nevertheless considering his 5lb penalty.
Sat one out one back, produced with every chance but couldn't find another gear when the race got serious inside 450 M.
Placed in 5th 6Ls behind the lead in first half, crept closer approaching home straight, kept on but couldn't find extra pace to challenge seriously.
Settled midfield 6-7Ls back, switched out for a clear passage turning in, ran on without threat.
Towards the rear and not hurried, 6Ls down turning in, slowly picked up but was checked near 100M. Not going to win but would be closer.
Placed in midfield 2-wide, nudged along 600M out but gave very limited response, left behind passing 200M.
Always at the back, driven passing 500M but no progress.
Held up behind leaders in fifth place, improved to second entering straight, chased clear leader on inside, got up near line under strong driving.
Broke well from out wide, led after 300m soon clear, shaken up in straight and ran on very gamely, just caught.
Fair start but taken back to near rear, not hurried far side, threaded a way through horses in straight, ran on well.
Taken back to rear from fair break, improved slightly back straight, launched on wide outside in straight, ran on well.
Broke well in centre, reined back to midfield on rail, tried to improve approaching straight, ran on.
Reined back from wide draw, fourth last early on outside, improved on home turn, taken wide and ran on but never threatened.
Decent break, up to second on inside of clear leader after 400m, still second on rail into straight, weakened.
Sluggish start, three wide towards rear, challenged between horses in straight, slightly interfered with approaching line as overtaken on both sides.
Fair start, midfield one off rail after 400m, short of room when looking for outside run in straight, finished on heels of outside bunch.
Missed break and lost a length or two, second last on rail, ridden inside in straight, stayed on but never near leader.
Good break, led early until headed by eventual runner-up, fourth on rail into straight and ridden, no progress.
Jumped well enough but stuck out wide in midfield from high draw, tried to improve wide in straight, no kick.
Even break, rail midfield but refused to settle briefly, ridden inside in straight, no acceleration.
Fair break, fourth on outside early, three wide leaving back straight, ridden, weakened.
Usual speed, pressed forward but took a trail on speed pair, relaxed on strong pace, came off heels turning, ran away final 300 M to score well.
Drifted back, best part of 8Ls from leaders in running line, helped by strong tempo, held up early in straight, closed nicely final 200 M to run in a nice 2nd.
Pressed on to angle into a role in front of midfield, 3Ls off decent speed throughout, made a run on turning, battled strongly last 200 M to snare 3rd.
Showed speed, engaged in speed battle with leader, used up racing outside pace, came back to inside turning in, closed respectably given workload.
Drifted out of it early from a wide alley, 8Ls away 3 wide with cover, suited by strong speed on, still well back turning, made gradual progress to be nearest.
Taken back from a wide alley, at rear nearly 10Ls from top end, aided by solid tempo, last turning, worked home nicely through the pack.
Standard break, soon midfield 6Ls back on rails, soft run in mid-section, saved ground turning, made minor headway without threatening.
Nice break, raced 4Ls or so away behind solid speed, kept to rails to bend, steadied 300 M but lacked usual kick when in clear, disappointing finish. (Jockey reported "flat".)
Usual speed to lead, kept working with pressure from outside horses, narrowly in front turning, soon faded after early work.
Out in line, settled behind midfield 6Ls or so back, OK run to turn, lacked a finish and just battled in straight.
Rearward as usual, 9 to 10Ls away on rails, aided by strong tempo, improved turning but didn't let down as usual, shortened stride at 200 M and blundered when eased down.
Fairly away, parked wide without cover in midfield, 5Ls back to turn, struggled in straight after a hard run.
Average break, raced 3 wide behind midfield 7Ls or so back, had cover to bend, didn't let down in straight.
Took a midfield role soon after start, 5Ls back and didn't use much mid-section, faded out cheaply in straight. (Blood in trachea.)
