Raced wide in rear early stages, moved forward to take up running passing winning post the first time but soon headed at Stables Bend, tracked leaders until switched out for a run into straight, hit front at the 100 M to score readily.

Suffered from slackening pace turning into straight the first time, soon recovered to race 3-wide in midfield, slightly closer up down far side but still racing wide, finished off race well without threatening the winner.
Broke well from the one draw, chased leader early stages before shuffling backward to midfield far side, ran home nicely to be nearest at finish. (Jockey warned re his riding over 600 M out.)
Began awkwardly, settled in last few racing keenly in the muddling pace at times in early stages, switched out to take closer order going up Rock, closed off well in straight to be nearest at finish.
Sluggish at start, raced keenly behind mid-division in slow-paced field, switched out Stables Bend to go forward for lead, made running until narrowly headed into straight, no extra close to home.
Never better than midfield, produced steady headway down straight without threatening.
Travelled on rails in midfield, shuffled backward towards rear of field down far side, maintained steady headway in the run home.

Made early running before handed up lead passing winning post the first time, travelled within striking distance down far side, renewed effort around the bend to hit front into straight, swamped final 100 M.

Raced keenly in a prominent spot, settled one-out-one-back going down back straight the second time, dropped to 3L 4th when pace quickened around the bend, kept on same speed until finding no extra inside final 150 M.

Began with others, soon crossed for prominent one-out-one- back spot, gradually shuffled backward to midfield far side, made short-lived effort to be close up early in final straight, dropped out tamely passing the 100 M mark.
Always struggling at the back.
Soon taken back to race in rear, met interferences 1700 M out, remained in last few thereafter.
Speared forward from a wide barrier to park 3/4 of a length back and to the outside of the leader. Hit the front by the 200 M and drew away to win convincingly.
Camped slightly in advance of midfield 1 off the fence. Closed off strongly despite ducking out near the 150 M.
Raced in 3rd position, 1 out 1 back. Peeled out after the 200 M to continue into clear running and kept on soundly over the final stages.
Showed superior gate speed from a wide alley to cross and lead on the fence by about the 800 M. Was overhauled by the furlong and faded thereafter.
No Comments on Running information for this horse.

Enjoyed a nice run early on the back of the speed along the fence. Received interference near the 500 M and after cornering about 4-wide failed to respond to riding and weakened noticeably near the 100 M.
Crowded at the start, copped a check near the 800 M, saddle broke at about the 600 M, eventually settling behind midfield along the paint. Maintained a steady gallop in the straight.
Slow to begin settling at the tail of the field 2 deep with cover. Whacked away at the same speed over the final 300 M.
Travelled with the backmakers, 1 off with cover. Only plodded to the line.
After being checked near the 800 M, settled along the fence near the tail of the field. Failed to make any appreciable ground in the home straight.
Caught deep early and drifted back to travel at the rear of the field, 2 to 3-wide with cover. Struggled in the final stretch.
Quickly into stride. Elected to sit on fence behind leading section from the Rock. Angled out and was 3Ls down on straightening. Ran on well and dominated closing stages.
Jumped fairly at midfield on fence. Gradually dropped towards rear despite the effort of rider back straight. Swung wide and was 7Ls adrift turning in. Closed off strongly and was nearest at finish.
Bumped at start and became unbalanced. Resumed to race 2-wide at midfield first turn. Moved closer at the Rock and was 3Ls back rounding the turn. Battled for place and just clung on for 3rd.
Checked at start and was last on fence from first turn. Shifted out abruptly when steadied near 500 M. 9Ls away turning into home. Covered substantial ground thereafter to nearly get 3rd.
Travelled 3-wide behind midfield through to home turn and was 4Ls behind the leader into final stretch. Remained in a battle for place until no extra gear closing stages.

Soon in front rank but was trapped 4-wide first turn. Sat 2-wide 2Ls behind leading section 900 M out. Kept pressing the leader early home straight but couldn't resist the finishing effort of the principals close home.

Checked at start, then was bumped and became unbalanced. Ridden to race at midfield on fence first turn. Struck heels and blundered passing 700 M. 5Ls off home turn. Took inside run thereafter and made some headway.
Driven forward from high draw but was caught 5-wide first turn. Eventually led on fence at the Rock. Held a 1L advantage leaving the bend. Hung on until 200 M.
Close to pace in a 2-wide position early. Took a spot ahead of midfield on fence from 900 M. Plugged on home straight but was not threatening.
Taken to rear after start. 2-wide behind midfield back straight. Given reminder from 400 M but could only make up minor ground.
2-wide with leaders early. Sat behind the pace on fence from 800 M. Ideal spot to strike in the straight but couldn't quicken. Weakened final stages.
Well enough away but was trapped wide. Gradually taken to rear in a 2-wide spot passing 1000 M. Never improved from there.
Slow start, third last one off rail first turn, improved on rail final turn, finished very fast on rail, won drawing away.
Broke fast from wide, headed off field to lead at post first time, dictated pace, two lengths clear back straight, tried to kick clear entering straight, fought on but no answer to winner.
Fair start, second on rail leaving straight, third on rail far side, second into straight, ran on and momentarily headed second, weakened last 50m.
Slow break, second last on rail early, improved far side and entering straight, ran on four off rail, finished well.
Missed a beat at start, three wide near rear first turn, made ground wide in back straight, challenged three off rail in straight, ran on until weakened last 75m.
Fair break but headed early, unhurried on rail in fifth, took a pull entering far turn, tried to challenge between horses straight, no kick.
Fair break but no early speed, last out of straight first time, still last entering straight, made run up inside rail but tightened up, finished well.
Fair break but steadied back to fourth last on rail, up to midfield far side, awkward round turn and hung slightly right in straight, ran on without threatening.
Fast break but soon outpaced and back to midfield one off rail, snatched up far side, improved wide into straight, but no real impression.
Quick break but soon headed from outside, fourth one off rail far side, ridden between horses straight, no extra.
Fair break but soon squeezed back by faster rivals, last far side, tried to improve wide in straight, no extra last 150m.
Fair start but caught wide first turn, raced up far side to sit outside leader, began to weaken leaving back straight, dropped back, tailed off.
Good break, ridden up three wide into second place, half length outside leader, driven straight, ran on gamely to lead near line.
Fair break, ridden up to take rail just behind leader, challenged on inside in straight, led narrowly 100m out, just weakened near line.
Good break, reined back from out draw to third last on rail, made run up the rail in straight, finished well.
Ridden early after decent break but not speed to get near lead, midfield and bustled back straight, challenged between horses straight, snatched up when path blocked 200m out, may have been unlucky.
Fair break but not enough early pace to hold position, reined back to midfield on rail, slightly checked turn, then tightened up in straight, ran on quite well until no extra last 50m.
Slow break out wide, last down far side, made bid on inside, closed quite well but never a threat.
Fair break, sixth one off rail on settling down, challenged on outside in straight, weakened last 75m.
Quick break, led early, still in front until weakened 200m out.
Good break, fourth one off rail far side, ridden in middle of course straight, weakened.
Driven up on outside from wide gate, not pace to get to lead and caught wide, wide into straight, stayed on until last 200m, never a danger.
Fair break, not much early speed and caught out wide, back to second last, wide into straight, found nothing.
Eased to rear, 7-1/2Ls off the leader 3-wide, favoured by the fast pace, progressed steadily 200 M to win.
Pushed to hold the rail 1/2Ls off the leader, not suited by the fast sectionals, hung on strongly until 50 M overhauled, ran on for 2nd.
Pushed to obtain a forward spot, 2-1/2Ls off the fast pace 2 to 3-wide, ran on well to the line for 3rd.
Eased back, 6Ls off the leader, trapped 3-wide throughout, suited by the fast pace but lost too much ground at bends, progressed steadily 200 M.
Eased to sit midfield, 4-1/2Ls off the leader 2-wide, helped by the fast tempo, checked 400 M, made ground 200 M, lacked room 100 M.
Hard ridden to take the rails in midfield, 3-1/2Ls off the leader, benefited by the fast pace, checked severely 400 M, just held ground in straight.
Hard ridden to lead by 1/2L at fast pace 2-wide, soon weakened 300 M.
Pushed early, behind midfield, 5-1/2Ls off the leader, checked badly 400 M, benefited by the fast pace, just held ground in straight.
Eased back, 6Ls off the leader 2-wide, checked early and again 400 M, suited by the fast pace, but ran on fairly.
1L off the leader 2-wide, not suited by the fast pace, weakened 400 M.
Pushed early, trapped 4-wide without cover throughout in midfield, 5Ls off the fast pace, ran on ok in final stages despite the ground lost at bends.
7-1/2Ls off the leader along the fence, favoured by fast pace, checked 400 M, no progress.
Quick break, up to second one off rail entering straight, led 200m out, held on well.
Broke well, reined back to midfield one off rail, challenged out wide in straight, ran on well, run just flattened last 50m.
Good break from wide, reined back to last on rail, improved approaching straight, brought wide, ran on strongly.
Bounced out of inside gate but back to midfield on rail, challenged on inside in straight, kept on to line.
Fast away, third on rail exiting back straight, aimed for gap on rail, not quite quick enough to take it.
Missed break slightly, held up on rail in rear group, ridden leaving back straight, ran on in centre of course, finished quite well.
Charged out of gate 9, led after 200m, settled in front, led into straight, ridden, weakened last 200m.
Ridden up on outside start, fourth three wide far side, ridden entering straight, kept on quite well until weakened late.
Fair break but not go early pace, last one off rail far side, swung wide into straight, ran on quite well.
Broke well, settled midfield, ridden exiting back straight, driven, no extra.
Not much early speed but moved up three wide in back straight, ridden straight, found nothing.
Joined charge for early lead but quickly drifted back, third last far side three wide, shaken up, no response.
Always within striking distance behind leader, went through a narrow gap to take the lead in mid-stretch then repelled a strong challenge from the 2nd over final 100 M.
Midfield and had a smooth run along the inside, quickened well when asked 350 M, kept on although always being held towards the finish.
Led uncontested at a steady tempo, all out inside 300 M, not pace of first two but managed to repel several late challenges for a 3rd.
In midfield early stages, taken to outside and strode forward from 900 M, produced with every chance in straight, outpaced by the first two final 150 M but kept on well for a 4th.
In touch, driven 350 M but had no clear run early in straight, ran on when clear passing 200 M.
Placed behind midfield 4-5Ls back, made a mild bid turning in but not reached leaders despite having had to shift ground near 250 M.
Switched off out the back and not hurried, kept to inside throughout but gave limited response under pressure 300 M.
Travelled 3-wide throughout and never better than midfield, stayed on same pace in the finish.
Towards the tail of the field 7Ls behind, crept closer passing 600 M then swung 3-wide into straight, plugged on at one pace only final 300 M. Never a threat.
Taken across behind runners, given a waiting ride towards the rear 6Ls back, steadied near 300 M, switched out for a clear run and ran past beaten runners over final 200 M.
Positioned one out one back, came under pressure approaching 400 M, soon beaten turning in.
Placed 2-wide in mid-division, attempted a narrow run 350 M out but was checked when the gap closed, never recovered.

Broke well, never far off, cantered to lead shortly after coming onto course proper, won convincingly.
Broke well, soon crossed to race on stands side racing amongst leaders, failed to match pace with winner in the closing stages but hung on well for clear 2nd.
Raced in last few along stands rails, shaken up inside final 300 M, produced good late impression to be nearest at finish. (Questioned.)
Settled mostly 3Ls off the speed in 5th, kept on same pace under pressure without quickening closing stages.
Not far off in 4th, failed to quicken when asked inside 250 M.
Held narrow advantage to 400 M, gradually weakened.
Always well behind, never seen with a chance.
Reared and lost ground at start, remained in last few, tailed off from halfway.
Travelled outside the leader, a length back. Hit the front at the furlong and drew a margin in the run to the wire.
Stalked the leader along the rail. Had every chance, maintained a sound gallop to the post.
Settled behind midfield 3 deep with cover. Peeled out rounding the home turn, battled away gamely.
Worked forward to race prominently 3 wide without cover. Kept on at the same speed in the final stretch.
Parked 3 back, 1 off with cover. Went to the line one paced.
Jumped well then was allowed to settle midfield along the fence. Made steady ground in the straight without threatening.
Sent forward from the outside gate to lead along the paint. Faded over the final 100m.
Camped midfield, 1 off with cover. Only plodded to the line.
Travelled close to midfield, but coursed 4 deep no cover. Never likely.
Raced with the backmakers, 1 off with cover. Never closed off.
Travelled in 2nd last position near the fence with cover. Struggled in the straight.
Last on settling traveling 2-3 wide with cover. Failed to pass another runner. (To trial.)
Slow to begin but soon resumed to sit behind pace on fence. Had a duel with the leader on straightening and put the rest of the field far behind. Prevailed 100M and ran away.
Led on fence until challenged by the eventual winner rounding home turn. Battled determinedly until knocked out 100M. Held 2nd by a comfortable margin.

Soon dropped to rear from high draw. Somewhat detached early despite the effort of rider. Reached the back of the field at 600M and was 6Ls down turning in. Landed on 3rd closing stages but was beaten far.
Well enough away but failed to work across. Restrained to race at midfield on fence from 1000M. Improved to prominent spot home turn. Hung on for a non-threatening 3rd until 100 M.
Way back early notwithstanding the effort of rider. Got to the back of main bunch and was 6Ls down from 500M. Made up some ground along the rail but was of limited significance overall.
Niggled along but could only stay towards rear back straight. 4Ls behind the leader turning into home. Ran on without troubling the main contenders.
Urged to sit within 2Ls of the pace in a 2-wide spot early. Checked to midfield 700M. Shuffled further back leaving the bend. Past beaten rivals home.
3-wide in front rank through to home straight. Plugged on before weakened 200M.
Hard ridden early in a forward position but insufficient speed to lead. Ended up 3-wide at midfield passing 1000M. No real progress from there.
Travelled 5-wide without cover ahead of midfield until faded early home straight.
Away in line but was caught widest. Taken to race 2-wide behind midfield at 1000M. Rolled to midfield before checked towards rear 600M. Never resumed.
Behind the speed until struggled soon after straightening. (Blood in trachea).
Sharp break, got across to second on rail far side, challenged straight, led 200m out, driven, held on well.
Fair break, raced midfield, improved on rail in straight, finished well, just failed.
Fair break, ridden to lead, led into straight, fought on well.
Fast away, led, then back to third far side, pulled out to challenge straight, not quite enough pace.
Not rushed early, held up, made ground along rail and good progress, path blocked late, and no further progress.
Fast break, but back towards rear, two off rail far side, brought down centre of course, finished quite well.
Good break and up to fifth on rail far side, pulled out and ran on, but not quicken.
Level break but reined back from out wide, rear group, improved approaching straight, ran on wide.
Fair break, no early speed, rear group, kept on but never a threat.
Taken back after fair start, one off rail midfield, blocked in straight, then again slightly by faster finisher, kept on.
Jumped well, steadied to fourth, one off rail, ridden straight, no kick.
Fair break but then squeezed and snatched up, fifth last into straight, ridden, found little.
Decent break, held rail in midfield, slight check far side, gradually lost place, brought down midfield, found little.
Quite well away, moved up three wide to midfield, wide into straight, ridden, folded.
Broke fast, led after 400m, two lengths clear, led into straight, driven clear, stayed on well.
Fair break, not hurried, midfield one off rail, on outside into straight, kept on well, not get to winner.
Good break, taken back to third far side, second into straight, ridden, not quicken.
Fair break, not rushed, near rear going well, outside straight, stayed on without being able to quicken.
Fair break, squeezed back, towards rear on rail, angled out straight ran on well.
Fair break, reined back from wide draw, second last far side, last early in straight, ran on well in centre.
Good break, fourth on rail far side, pocketed briefly early straight, but no major response when extracted.
Decent break, taken back from wide, third last two off rail, improved wide entering straight, ran on until weakened last 50 M.
Broke well but not much early pace, sixth one off rail far side, ridden straight, found little.
Fly jumped leaving stalls and lost two lengths, on rail into midfield, ridden straight, found little.
Good break on rail, shared early lead, then tracked leader, third on rail in straight, ridden, found nothing.
Decent break on rail not pace to go with leaders, mid to rear far side, no progress.
Fair break, wide, always three wide, ridden, weakened.
Blew start badly, last far side, ridden before straight, no response.
Pushed to take a prominent spot, 2.5Ls behind the fast pace 2-3 wide, led 400M hung on strongly to score.
Settled in front of midfield, 4.5Ls off the leaders on the rails, made ground steadily 300M to finish a close 2nd.
At rear, 8.5Ls off the leaders, trapped 3-4 wide, progressed steadily 400M to grab 3rd.
Pushed to occupy the box seat, not suited by the fast sectionals, momentarily held up 400M, just held ground when clear.
At rear, 9.5Ls off the leaders 3-4 wide, favoured by the fast pace, raced flat unitl 200M to make steady groud.
Eased to sit in midfield, 4.5Ls off the leader 2-3 wide, sutied by the fast tempo, however no progress in straight.
Midfield, 6Ls off the leaders 2-3 wide, helped by the fast pace, but no progress in final stages.
Hard ridden to hold the rail and shared the lead at fast sectionals, dropped off 400M.
Eased at start to take rails behind the field, 7.5Ls off the leaders, benefited by the fast pace, lack room 4-2, no turn of foot when clear.
Pushed early but failed to muster, 4.5Ls off the fast pace, trapped 3-4 wide, emptied 400M.
Pushed early to sit in midfield, trapped 3-4 wide, then eased back, favoured by the fast pace, however never a factor.
Eased back, suited by the fast pace, never competitive.
Awkward away, eased back, 6Ls off the leaders along the fence, suited by the fast tempo, checked 350M then weakened.
Pushed to share the lead 2 wide at fast sectionals, faded quickly in straight.
Skipped out of gate, slight bump early, led easily crossing to rail, had them all off bridle after 500m, drew away.
Broke well, tried to match strides with winner, outpaced but ran on gamely.
Slight bump from winner on leaving stalls, travelled well behind leader then outpaced, weakened slightly last 50m.
Broke well, just short of pace halfway, ridden, ran on.
Broke well, travelled well behind leader to halfway, outpaced.
Good break on rail, looking for room halfway, ran on when clear but no chance with winner.
Broke well, not pace to go with leaders, travelled on outside, ridden midfield, stayed on.
Slightly awkward start but lost little, shared lead on outside to halfway, outpaced.
Blew start losing two lengths, wide outside near lead to halfway, ridden, left behind.
Fair break, midfield, ridden to challenge in centre, outpaced.
Fair break but no early speed, well behind last at halfway, ran on late.
Sluggish start, rear early, ridden halfway, no kick.
Fair break but soon rear group, ridden, not quicken.
Decent break, ridden early, settled on rail, bustled bustled following eventual winner, completely outpaced.
Went forward as expected but was taken on for the lead throughout, kicked 1.5Ls clear near 350M, kept on well in late stages to hold off the fast finishing runner-up.
Held up in midfield and taken to a 3-wide position rounding the home bend, made steady progress final 300M and only just failed.

Vied for early lead then taken back to obtain cover passing 800M, ran on in straight but never looked like getting to the winner, lost 2nd close home. (Jockey reported the horse did not appreciate the track conditions.)
Vied for lead 2-wide, kept on till 200M then gradually weakened.
Behind midfield 5Ls off the pace, made some progress inside 400M but not reached leaders.
In midfield along the fence, driven passing 500M, shifted out abruptly under whip near 200M, stayed on same pace in late stages under hands and heels riding.
Shaken up early to obtain a position ahead of midfield, ran on one paced in straight.
Dropped back to last trailing 8Ls to leaders, switched out passing 500M, made minor headway only.
Drawn 12 and was kept wide throughout behind mid-division, had to be pushed along nearing 500M, never threatened, eased 150 M.
With leaders early, outpaced passing 600M and soon behind turning home. (Mucus)
Pressed the pace on the outside, 4-wide swinging for home and had no extra inside 300M, eased.
Towards the rear always, no progress under pressure 400M.
Fast break wide out, second leaving back straight, out to challenge early straight, ran on to lead 100m out, kept on well.
Good break, led early until halfway up straight, not resist winner.
Fair break, taken back to sixth, pulled out to challenge, not get to first two.
Missed break, back on rail far side, blocked momentarily straight, got out and finished fast.
Good break, headed, held rail in fourth far side, third into straight, no further progress.
Even break but not much early speed, back to midfield on rail, pulled out and ran on steadily.
Fair break, but drifted back to third last, ridden exiting back straight, pulled wide and ran on but could not get to leaders.
Slow into stride, last early, ridden into straight, made some ground on rail, but never threat.
Good enough break but caught three wide in battle for lead, eased back to midfield, ridden midfield, not much impact.
Fair break but soon left behind on wide outside, back to second last, urged back straight, came wide, finished quite well.
Fast away, disputed lead on outside, back to sixth still wide, tried to challenge, no improvement.
Fair break, ridden early, up to second after 300m, bustled exiting back straight, ridden, weakened.
Slowish start, midfield three wide, tried to improve entering straight, no extra.
Moderate break, ridden up wide to reach fourth, out of back straight, ridden, weakened quickly.
Travelled well 3-wide in better than midfield in 5th, hit front over 200 M out, won confidently.
Settled in midfield, fought on steadily under pressure without threatening.
Broke well from a wide barrier, soon crossed for lead, made running to about 200 M, accepted defeat after passed by runner-up 50 M out.
Began fairly, settled in midfield, saved ground turning in, kept on steadily at the same pace without quickening.
Began from the widest barrier, disputed lead before settling outside leader, pegged back leader on straightening, hampered and weakened 300 M out.
Settled towards rear, saved ground on rails turning in, ran home one paced.
Raced wide in rear of midfield, switched out for a run after straightening, made modest headway without quickening.
Not far off and mostly in 3rd on rails, faded under pressure in straight.
Well behind, briefly baulked early in straight, ran past well beaten horses closing stages, jockey said horse not stretched out.
Slightly slow out and raced tight between runners in early stages, travelled just worse than midfield, steadied 150 M out, not recovered.
Raced in midfield after beginning from a wide barrier, one of the widest runners turning for home, never recovered.
Raced wide in 3rd last, swung widest turning for home, never recovered.
Travelled in forward of midfield, wide turning in, dropped out tamely.
Raced wide without cover in prominent position, faded out of it from rounding home bend.

Never far off, in 3rd within striking distance rounding home bend, responded well to hit front inside 100 M, won well.
Began well, gradually drifted backward to settle in midfield, fought on under pressure in straight to reach 2nd late.
Began slowly, travelled in rear of field to straight, fought on steadily under pressure to be nearest at finish.
Began from the widest barrier, remained wide in a prominent spot, improved to race outside leader around home bend, faded under pressure inside final 100 M.
Broke well from the one draw, chased along behind leader to 600 M, ran home one-paced.
Driven along from a wide barrier to take up running, maintained narrow advantage to 100 M, overhauled under pressure.
Began awkwardly losing ground, soon recovered to forward of midfield, lost position around home bend, ran home one-paced. (Bled.)
Began moderately, niggled along when forced to steady and lose position approaching Rock, remained in second last turning in, went past well-beaten runners late.
Soon taken back to race in rear and then tailed-off, produced late effort past well beaten runners in straight.
Began with others but soon outpaced racing wide behind midfield, found nothing under pressure in straight.
Prominent early, forced to steady and lose position approaching Rock, raced wide without cover in midfield to straight, dropped out tamely.
Began quickly, not far off when steadied approaching home bend, gradually dropped out of contention after straightening.
Held the fence and travelled in 2nd position. Drew clear after the 400m and repelled a late challenge.
Stalked the leader along the fence. Was reluctant to hold its position after the 400m however closed off well after peeling out prior to the home turn.
Was in the leading trio early, 3 deep, before managing to slot in and park on the back of the leaders, 1 off with cover after the 800m. Kept up a sound effort over the concluding stages.
Worked forward to take up leading duties whilst traveling 1 off. Hung out for most of the trip, maintained a fair gallop to the post. (To trial.)
Positioned behind midfield, 2 wide with cover. Rounded the home bend about 5 deep and made nice ground in the straight.
Taken back from a wide gate to travel back in the field, 1 off with cover. Straightened about 4 deep and made good ground in the run to the wire.
Camped midfield, 2 deep with cover. Kept on one paced in the run to the line.
Proved a handful early whilst overracing taking up a position at the tail of the field. Battled away down the outside in the final stretch.
Began awkwardly, lost ground settling at the rear, 3 wide without cover. Never likely.
Began on terms then drifted back to travel with the backmakers along the paint. Failed to close off.
Travelled 3 back along the paint. Fenced up in the home straight but only plodded to the line.
Travelled 2-wide ahead of midfield from first turn. Reached the leading section into final stretch. Hit front near 200M and ran on to score an easy victory.
Raced within 3Ls of the pace near the fence through to home turn. On the back of leading section turning in. Kept giving but no match with the winner's turn of foot. Hung on for 2nd.

Taken 3-wide at rear from high draw after start. Made run outside field passing 500M and was 3Ls behind the leading section on straightening. Responded fairly well under pressure to snatch 3rd near the line.

Away in line but was then steadied when crowded for room. Sent to race 2-wide towards rear first turn. Improved wide to leading section rounding home turn. Stayed in battle for place until closing stages.
Bumped at start and was ridden to race 2-wide in the front rank first turn. Took lead on fence from 1100M. Leveled turning into home. No extra gear to trouble the principals passing 200M.
Sat towards rear on fence after start. Commenced his run outside passing 450M and was 6Ls down leaving the bend. One-paced to conclude.

Raced on fence behind midfield first turn. Dropped to last when other runners improved passing 500M. Took inside run thereafter and made some headway until final 100M when disappointed for running. Not fully tested.
Quickly into stride. Eased to sit at midfield on fence from first turn. Shifted out for clear run top of home straight but responded only fairly.
Urged to go forward from high draw but was trapped 4-wide approaching first turn. Slotted 2-wide behind leader from 1200M. Challenged for lead early home straight but peaked final furlong.
Pressed after start but failed to muster. Took a 2-wide spot behind midfield from 1400M. No real progress thereafter.
Hard ridden early and led on fence before first turn. Took seat behind leader from 1200M. Found nothing when asked home straight.
3-wide near midfield through to home turn. No show in the home straight.
Fair break, ridden to take third one off rail, travelled well but back to fifth exiting back, driven between horses, led 300m out, ran on well.
Settled fifth one off rail, back to midfield, then improved leaving back, challenged between runners straight, ran on.
Taken back to rail from break, second last early, slightly checked back straight, ran on wide in straight, finished well.
Quick break, led early, headed off, sixth on rail after settling, ridden straight, finished quite well.
Good break, ridden into fourth on rail, improved entering straight, found gap but not quicken.
Fair break, but no early pace, settled rear division, ridden and made ground straight without ever looking dangerous.
Frisky in gate, not great start, ridden for midfield position, wide early straight, ridden, no extra.
Quick break, led after 200m, headed and settled second, ridden early straight, gradually weakened.
Sluggish start, midfield on rail, back to fourth last, kept on one pace straight.
Hopped leaving gate, second last early, improved outside to challenge entering straight, weakened.
Sluggish early, last after 200m, tried to improve far side, driven, found little.
Fair break but three wide first turn, ridden to improve, clear lead leaving back straight, weakened quickly.
Moderate break, ridden early, sixth one off rail, moved up wide leaving back straight, hard ridden straight, ran on very gamely.
Fair break but wide first turn. Second one off rail into back straight, led, fought on very well, winner just too strong.
Fast break, reined back, settled midfield, improved as pace slowed, challenged wide in straight, ran on well.
Good position on rail early, travelled well, trailed leader into straight, pulled out to challenge, never quite on terms.
Held up second last, nearly caught on heels as pace slowed far side, improved on rail, ran on well.
Taken back from wide draw, held up last, no way through as tried to quicken on home turn, tightened up straight, good finish but run petered out very late.
Not rushed early, then moved to midfield on rail, going well far side, tried to quicken straight, no real kick.
Lacked pace to get near railnear rear far side, ridden, ran on but never a threat.
Quick break, ridden three wide early, fourth back straight, challenged far turn, weakened straight.
Fast out and ridden for ealy lead, reined back to third on rail, tried to challenge exiting back straight, gradually weakened.
Vigorously ridden early but never near lead, effort on inside home turn, no response.
Ridden early but dropped back third last, ridden far side, no response, tailed off.
Pushed to take the rail and led by 1L at advantageous slow sectionals, no major challenges until 50M, just good enough to hold the win.
At back, 5.5Ls off the leader 2-3 wide, harmed by the slow tempo, held up 400M, stormed home with strong finishing efforts and took 2nd.
Midfield, 3.5Ls off the slow pace, trapped 3 wide throughout and lost ground, made early move 600M, closed the race off strongly to the line for 3rd.
Eased back, 6.5Ls off the leader, harmed by the slow tempo, trapped 3-4 wide and lost ground, made early move 600M, dashed strongly 300M, just missed place.
Pushed to obtain a midfield spot, 4Ls off the leader 2-3 wide, dashed strongly 300M despite not suited by the slow pace, just missed place.
Pushed to sit outside the lead, benefited by the slow sectionals, flattened 200M.
Very awkward away, took rail at rear, 6.5Ls off the leader, harmed by the slow pace, held up 4-2, dashed well when clear.
Settled in prominent spot, 2.5Ls behind the slow pace 2 wide, just held ground in straight.
Eased to sit in midfield along the fence, 3.5Ls off the leader, harmed by the slow pace, blocked most straight, just ran on, not tested.
Hard ridden early to occupy a midfield spot on the rails, 5.5Ls off the leader, not suited by the slow tempo, little dash 100M.
Settled in box seat, enjoyed the slow pace, flattened 200M.
Eased at start to take cover at rear, 8Ls off the leader, raced 4 wide and lost ground, harmed by the slow pace, ran on ok in final stages.
Fair break, held up on rail near rear, improved approaching straight, burst through three wide, won going away.
Led, fought on gamely straight, no match for winner.
Quick break, on leader's shoulder far side, just lost hard battle with runner-up.
Led early, headed off, settled third on rail, ridden straight, ran on.
Slow start, taken back to rail in last place, squeezed through on rail early straight, ran on.
Quick break, taken back to fourth one off rail, effort straight, ran on one pace.
Wide early, held up near rear three off rail, wide into straight, ran on quite well.
Fifth on rail early, ridden entering straight, weakened.
Slow away, midfield between horses, slightly short of room straight, no response to pressure.
Fair break, midfield but three wide, effort leaving back straight, ridden, no improvement.
Fair break, settled near rear, effort entering straight, found little.
Allowed an easy lead early but was taken on passing 800M, responded well under hands and heels riding in straight and always found enough to hold off the persistent runner-up.
Had to overcome a wide barrier, vied for lead 2-wide, kept on well inside 300M but was always held by the winner.

Taken across behind runners after the start but proved difficult to settle in early stages, raced in last 5-6Ls off the steady pace, switched to clear 300M, made good progress from the rear and was nearest on the line.
Slowly away and held up towards the rear, driven 400M and made steady progress in straight for a non-threatening 4th.
Broke well then dropped in behind midfield, challenged wide into straight, ran on well final 200M for some late impression.
Slowly away, towards the rear early but crept closer to a midfield position in middle stages, kept to inside throughout, ran on one paced inside 300M.

Obtained a handy position behind leaders after a slightly slow start, switched away from the fence approaching 400M, had every chance turning in but couldn't produce a change of pace to challenge seriously.
Given a waiting ride, placed towards the rear 6Ls off leaders, last turning in but ran on well when asked, late headway inside 200M. (Jockey and Trainer questioned re riding position.)
With early leaders to 1000M then taken back to midfield 3-wde, had an uninterrupted run in straight, kept on till finding no extra final 100M.
Close enough in midpack, well covered but found no extra pace when pressed inside 300M.
With leaders early but dropped back to midfield, unable to tuck in and was wide throughout, driven 350M but no progress. (Jockey was told his riding lacked necessary judgement and initiative.)
Pushed along early, tracked leaders but struggled to keep up passing 400M, weakened rapidly 200M. (Bled 2nd time. Retired after racing.)
Broke well, up to fourth one off rail after 400m, challenged three wide, led 300m out strongly pressed, back in charge well before line.
Fair break, found spot one off rail, just forward of midfield, improved early straight, out to challenge 300m out, joined leader, beaten off.
Eased back from wide draw, second last on settling, good straight run between horses to close on leaders.
Fair break, settled midfield two off rail, challenged three wide entering straight, ran on.
Fair break, ridden up to fifth on rail, ridden before straight, drive, never really threatened.
Fair break but short of early pace and soon back to fourth last, ridden entering straight, ran on between horses.
Fast away, driven to lead, joined and ridden early straight, weakened.
Sluggish start, ridden to hold third last position, tried to improve wide into straight, ran on.
Fluffed start, last early, third last into straight, ran on down outside.
Quite fast away but trapped wide, ridden straight, not much to offer.
Ridden up to second, raced on leader's shoulder, then challenged exiting back straight, ridden, weakened.
Broke well, got involved in early battle for lead, then back to third, ridden early in straight, weakened.
Travelled well along the inside in mid-division, switched to 2-wide 700M, soon into clear on straightening, picked up strongly to strike the front 50M from home. Won decisively.
Settled in 3rd and within striking distance of the leader always, quickened well despite hanging in to briefly lead 100M but couldnt match pace with the winner in closing stages.
Driven to the frony and led uncontested throughout, kicked 2Ls clear turning home, continued on well and was only headed inside 100M.
Along the rails in a position behind midfield, switched to 2-wide making the home turn, came with a promising looking run on straightening, finished strongly and just missed out on 3rd by a whisker.
In midfield early but got shuffled back to the rear approaching back straight, made good progress turning in but didn't have the clearest of runs, was steadied 200M then raced tight close home.
Soon crossed to bag the inside rail, patiently ridden in last over 7Ls behind, headway 400M out and stayed on well to the line.
Ordinary jump, crept forward to track leader prominently, briefly threatened in mid stretch but turned one-pace inside 100M, steadied close home.
Behind midfield 6Ls back, had to be rushed along making the home turn, ran on fairly final 300M without threat.
Taken across behind runners and raced towards the rear 6-7Ls off the pace, proved difficult to settle in 1st half, swung widest for home and never able to quicken.
Stepped up to a mile first time. With leaders early, dropped back to 4th entering the back straight, driven 350M but no progress, dropped off rapidly final 200M.
Assumed running in midfield 2 off the fence, outpaced nearing 400M, soon left behind.
Slowly away, strode forward to midfield when caught wide without cover making the 1st turn, no progress inside 350M, soon beaten.

Driven along to lead from the widest barrier, gradually came across to eventually reach the rails before home bend, kicked 3Ls clear turning in, won unchallenged.
Began with others, settled in midfield, obtained a clear passage 300 M out, ran on steadily without threatening.
Broke well, settled in rear of midfield, shifted out for a run turning in, fought on steadily under pressure to be nearest at finish.
Sluggish at start, trailed the field to home bend, did not find much room in straight until over 100 M out when too late, produced a respectable run all things considered.
Never far off in prominent spot in 3rd, kept on under pressure early in straight before yielding ground inside final 200 M.
Ridden for early pace, settled in 4th about 2Ls off the speed, in similar position turning in, gradually faded.
Niggling along in last few when forced to steady on rails coming out of back straight, remained well behind turning for home saving ground on rails, found nothing under pressure.
Began moderately, travelled towards rear, shifted out the widest for a run turning in, failed to quicken to make any impression. (Tactic questioned.)
From an unfavourable draw, soon drifted back to last few, remained well behind and never on terms.

Niggled along from a wide gate, remained wide throughout, close up early before dropping back to midfield approaching home bend, weakened further in straight. (Questioned for disappointing performance.)
Niggled at for early speed settling for 2nd before home bend, held position under pressure early in straight, but dropped out tamely inside final 200 M.
Camped midfield along the rail. Shifted off to race 2-wide near the 800 M, rallied 4 to 5-wide on the home turn then threaded a course between runners to snare the prize in the shadows of the post.

Ridden along early from the outside gate but after being prominent and caught wide early was steadied to race 3 deep with cover midfield. Was carted 4-wide no cover after the 700 M, hit the lead at the 100 M, but was mowed down.
Settled back from a wide alley to race with the backmakers, 2 deep with cover. Commenced to improve near the 600 M, cornered wide, and closed off nicely.
Tracked the leader early along the paint then raced 3 back after the 800 M. Made good steady ground along the inside in the home straight.
Led along the rails before handing up near the 800 M. Was shuffled back slightly when the pace quickened passing the 700 M. Kept on one paced when in clear running after the 300 M.
Raced 1 off early worse than midfield. Shifted out to improve between runners, 3-wide with cover after the 700 M. Made steady ground in the final stretch.
Worked to the lead eventually finding the fence near the 1100 M. Faded easily near the 150 M, after dictating terms in front.
Settled at the rear along the rail. Fenced up in the straight and whacked away over the final stages.
Settled behind midfield the fence. Peeled off to race 2-wide after the 700 M. Maintained a fair gallop to the wire.
Travelled at the tail of the field, commenced to shift out and attempt to improve 3 deep with cover after the 700 M. Struggled in the straight when produced down the outside.
Raced prominently however was cast 3-wide without cover for most of the trip. Never likely.
Tracked the speed 1 off in a trailing position. Lost cover near the rear the 800 M, but still had every chance, finishing well back.

Jumped fairly well but was eased to sit 2-wide towards rear from 1600 M. Took inside run rounding home turn and was 6Ls down into final stretch. Got traffic until 100 M. Dashed well between runners to snatch victory final strides.

Sat towards rear on fence after start. Made run along rail passing 600 M and was 5Ls off turning into home. Peeled out to challenge but was held up until passing 250 M. Ran on well to beat all but the winner near the post.

Away in line and was driven forward after start. Taken to rail ahead of midfield from 1500 M. Urged from 650 M and was on leader's back turning in. Fought on but couldn't contain the finishing effort of the front pair close home.
Travelled on fence in midfield after start. Improved gradually and was 2Ls behind leader approaching home straight. Every chance final 150 M but failed to sustain its effort final stages.

In search of cover from high draw. Landed a 2-wide spot in midfield from 1500 M. Shaken up outside field and was 6Ls back at bend. Made up good ground thereafter without seriously troubling the principals.
Pressed early to go forward but was caught 3-wide ahead of midfield. Similar spot back straight. One-paced to conclude.
8 to 9Ls behind the leader before swinging out to make up minor ground home.
Asked to maintain in the leading section one-off the fence through to home straight. Hit front at 250 M but was overhauled 150 M.
Somewhat detached at rear on fence for the major part of the race despite the effort of rider. Beat tired runners home.
Handy position until no extra gear top of home straight. Faded final 100 M.
2-wide at midfield early and middle stages. Couldn't follow from 500 M. Out of contention before home straight.
Led on fence until swamped 250 M. Struggled home.
Fast out, led one off rail far side, kicked on at turn, ran on strongly.
Fair break but bustled to hold sixth place on rail, slightly short of room when pulled out to challenge, ran on well.
Good break but unable to lead, third one off rail, challenged on turn, ran on, not peg back winner.
Decent break, fourth on rail, kept on one pace.
Fair break, rear division one off rail, asked to improve at turn, ran on one pace.
Steadied after fair start, third last far side, ridden turn, driven straight, ran on late.
Fair break, midfield, tried to improve wide, no kick.
Good break but caught wide, fifth into straight, driven, weakened.
Good break but caught wide, back to fifth last, improved on outer, ridden, weakened.
Quickly away, second on rail until leaving back straight, weakened.
Fair break, ridden but lacked early speed, back to rear division on rail, some response in straight until baulked late.
Moderate start, rear and ridden, stumbled far side, last into straight, found nothing.
Fast away, second on rail with good lead on third, led early in straight, ran on strongly.
Good break but lacked early pace, fourth on rail six lengths behind leader, challenged on inside, ran on but not trouble winner.
Good break, third one off rail, ridden turn, ran on, not quicken.
Fair break, fifth on outer, lost ground approaching turn, driven, ran on well.
Not fast away, back to second last, brought wide straight, ran on well.
Fast away, two lengths clear halfway, ridden, weakened.
Fair break, no early speed, three wide back straight, improved wide, weakened.
Slow away from wide draw, kept on along rail, but never a danger.
Good break but not go pace, midfield rail, ridden turn, kept on but no kick.
Fair break but outpaced early, not settle far side, kept on.
Slow away, driven fourth last, ridden straight, lost action abruptly late.
Broke well, lacked early pace, wide, dropped back gradually, ridden, weakened.
Eased to sit in midfield, 3Ls off the leader 2 to 3-wide, benefited by the fast pace, made early move 800 M, led 300 M, hung on strongly to win.
Eased to rear for cover, more than 6Ls off the leader 2 to 3-wide, suited by the fast tempo, moved forward 800 M and settled just behind the leaders, ran on well to the line for 2nd.
Eased to rear for cover, 7-1/2Ls off the leader 2-wide, favoured by the fast pace, progressed steadily 300 M for 3rd.
Settled in midfield, 4-1/2Ls off the leader 3-wide, helped by the fast tempo, made ground 600 M, flat 100 M.
Pushed to obtain the box seat, not suited by the fast pace, just held ground in straight.
Eased back, 6Ls off the leader 2-wide, benefited by the fast pace, made steady ground in straight without real threats.
Pushed forward, 3Ls off the leader 2-wide, suited by the fast tempo, however soon flattened 400 M.
Behind midfield, 5Ls off the leader, favoured by the fast pace but trapped 3-wide, never a factor.
Pushed to take rail and led by 2Ls at fast sectionals, weakened 250 M.
Hard ridden to occupy a midfield spot on the fence, pushed back badly 500 M, never progressed.
Pushed to cross towards the rail in front of midfield, not suited by the fast tempo, soon dropped off 500 M.
Fair break, fifth on rail early, split horses in straight, finished powerfully.
Fast break, into battle for lead, second straight, no match for winner.
Fast break but eased back to fourth one off rail, challenged on outside in straight, ran on well.
Quickly away, led on inside, two lengths clear mid straight, headed, weakened
Good break, got into four way battle for lead, third into straight, brushed by winner on his way through, kept on.
Broke well, eased over from wide draw, sixth into straight ran on one pace.
Not fast away, fourth last early, ridden to improve before turn, ran on, never nearer.
Early speed but soon overtaken on inside, ridden from halfway, kept on.
Slowish start, ridden early, ran on along rail, never nearer.
Slow away, some progress turn, outside run, flattened out.
Missed break, always out paced but kept on.
Broke well but not pace to go with leaders, gradually slipped back, ridden, weakened.
In chasing group just off the pace and travelled strongly into contention, picked up well inside 300 M to edge out rival close home.
Tracked leader prominently and had a smooth inside run, quickened to strike the front 150 M, kept on well but was just denied close home.
Soon taken to the front, disputed early lead then sat one out one back to straight, briefly threatened from 250 M to 150 M but couldn't sustain effort in late stages.
Assumed running in midfield 5Ls off the steady pace, had an uninterrupted run inside 300 M, stayed on for a non- threatening 4th.
Never far off in 5th, had his chance but ran on one-paced only.
Held up towards the rear, 7Ls down turning in, made minor headway in late stages.
Attempted to lead but showed insufficient early speed, positioned 2-wide in mid-division, ran on fairly final 300 M.
Emerged as the leader passing 1100 M, led steadily to 250 M, no extra late on.
Hard driven early after a slow start, placed towards the rear 7Ls back, lacked a finish final 300 M.
Taken back and crossed to the fence, in 2nd last throughout, made very limited progress on straightening.
Crossed to the fence and raced 6Ls back in midfield, under pressure approaching 400 M, weakened 200 M.
Always at the rear, never a factor.

Settled wide in forward of midfield, closer up around the bend, quickened up under pressure to gain upper hand close home.

Gradually crossed from the wide draw to settle outside the leader before home bend, disputed lead around the bend and into straight, held slender advantage throughout closing stages until pipped at post.
Moderate start, gradually recovered to midfield before home bend, saved ground turning in, fought on steadily under pressure to miss narrowly.

Slightly slow out from a wide draw, soon prominent ploughing his lone furrow early, moved in to join the field in one-out-one-back spot coming onto course proper, had every chance throughout straight.
Midfield on inside early, gradually shifted out approaching home bend when without cover, fought on nicely in straight to be nearest at finish.
From the widest barrier, settled in last few, finished off race well inside final 200 M.
Began with others settling in midfield or just worse, similar position turning in, kept on same pace, never nearer.
Broke well, settled in 4th on rails within 2Ls of pace, slightly closer up in 3rd rounding home bend, gradually faded under pressure in straight.

Given reminders early, gradually settled for 5th about 3Ls off the speed, shuffled further backward slightly around the bend, hampered and lost position upon straightening, made no further impression.
Slow out, travelled well behind most of way, saved ground turning in, failed to quicken under pressure.
Slightly slow out, trailed the field to straight, widest runner turning for home, hung in a difficult ride and failed to improve in straight.
Began from a wide draw, settled 3 wide in rear of midfield, similar turning for home, made no serious impression.
Made running far side, joined after the bend, dropped out tamely under pressure after straightening.
On rail in midfield, took slightly closer order around the bend, soon found nothing after straightening.
Settled well back, 3 deep with cover. Rallied about 8 wide on straightening. Let down smartly to snatch victory over the concluding stages.
Rated 3 back the fence. hit the lead approaching the 200m, but was overhauled late to nabbed close to home.
Blew the start, settling in last position. Gained a split between runners after running into some traffic near the 300m, got to the line strongly. (See incident report.)
Didn't enjoy the best of runs copping some interference midrace whilst in a midfield position 1 off with cover. Cornered about 5 deep and ran home nicely.
Raced towards the rear of the field along the fence. Closed off soundly between runners.
Enjoyed the run of the race stalking the leader along the rail. No excuses.
Positioned with the backmakers, 2 deep with cover. Worked home well down the outside.
Settled worse than midfield along the paint. Closed off fairly along the inside in the final straight.
Settled midfield the fence. Maintained its position despite striking some interference near the 650 & home turn. Kept on one paced in the run home.
Settled behind midfield 1 off with cover. Only plodded to the line.
Camped 1 out 1 back. Had every chance.
Worked forward to cross and race to the outside of the leader by the 800m. faded over the final furlong.
Rated 3 back, 1 0ff with cover. Struggled in the final stretch.
Lead along the fence. Gave ground quickly in the straight, collapsed shortly after the post.
Away in line. Elected to sit behind midfield on fence. Peeled out and was 6Ls down on straightening. Balanced up and made strong run from 300M. Challenged 150M but easily held off rivals.
Quickly into stride. Taken to sit 2-wide behind the pace group. Got clear run from 300M. Gave some pressure to the winner passing 200M but was soon knocked out. Beat the rest by some margin.
Ridden along after start but was trapped 4-wide behind midfield. Swung wide and was 7Ls adrift turning in. Kept making up ground to snatch 3rd at finish. Did the best work late.
Jumped fairly and tucked 3-wide behind midfield from high draw 1000M out. 6Ls behind the speed turning into home. Finished off fairly well to make frame at line.
Out in line. Raced within 4Ls of the pace near the fence through to home straight. Not entirely clear on fence until 250M. Ran on without troubling the front pair. Lost in a 3-way finish for 3rd.
2-wide, never far off the pace through to home straight. Hit front briefly approaching 200M but couldn't sustain the finishing effort of the principals final stages.
Dwelt at start and lost a considerable amount of ground. On the back of the field home turn. Came widest and was 8Ls off into final stretch. Made up some ground thereafter.
No Comments on Running information for this horse.
Took a 3-wide spot towards rear after start. Hampered and was 7Ls back rounding home turn. Closed off fairly well until held up final 150M.
2-wide at midfield through to home turn. 4Ls behind the leader home straight. Failed to turn up a notch thereafter.
Urged along the fence to maintain prominent spot through to home straight. No response when asked final 350M.
Rolled forward after start and took lead on fence at 900M. Disputed lead at bend but opened up a 1L gap entering home straight. Hung on until 250M.
Hard ridden early but was trapped 3-wide of midfield through to home straight. No extra gear final 300M.
Travelled wide and without cover in the front rank until dropped out 350M.
Fast jump, up on rail to third, second into straight, led, headed, fought back to lead on line.
Broke well wide out, fourth one off rail, challenged three wide in straight, neck up approaching post, headed on line.
Slow start, third last one off rail, moved up gradually three wide, pulled wide for challenge, ran on well.
Fast break from outside, led, two lengths clear leaving back, headed mid-straight, weakened slightly.
Fast break, midfield on outer, improved three wide far side, wide straight, not quicken.
Fair break, held up rear division, improved entering straight, slightly short of room, ran on.
Eased back to rail from wide draw, held up second last, ridden straight, stayed on quite well.
Good break, second early one off rail, three wide entering straight, ridden, not quicken.
Fair break, midfield pulling a little far side, settled in sixth, up to third entering straight, ridden, weakened.
Lost length start, back to rear, ridden, last into straight, some progress but never near leaders.
Fair start, ridden to get midfield position, short of room far side as overgalloped, short of room early straight, no kick.
Fair break, fifth one off rail, progress in middle of pack straight, weakened late.
Lost two lengths start, ridden up on rail to midfield, sixth into straight, ridden, weakened.
Fair break wide, taken back but still three wide, second last out of back straight, ridden, found nothing.
Ridden from wide gate to sixth, three wide, bustled home turn, seventh and hard ridden early straight, picked up and mowed them down.
Good break, fourth on rail early, led by a length mid straight, no answer to winner.
Good break, but three wide in third out of back straight, wide in straight, ran on well, winner too strong.
Not much early speed, back to fourth last, ridden, wove through in straight, finished strongly.
Lost length at break, ridden, up to midfield fifth in straight, kept on one pace.
Sluggish start, ridden to keep midfield rail, kept on, but no kick.
Quick break, up to second on leader's shoulder, challenged straight, no extra.
Fair break, one wide midfield, ridden into straight, kept on but no impact.
Slow break from wide, back to last on rail, improved far side, brought wide, ran on but no real impression.
Fair break, fifth one off, looking for room straight, found it, but no kick.
Fair break, four wide briefly back straight, wide bid straight, no improvement.
Fast way, led, headed mid-straight, weakened.
Fair break, but back to rear, last one off into straight, ridden, found little.
Fair break, over-raced briefly far side when held up last, ridden, weakened.
Pushed to take rail and shared the lead at very slow early sectionals, kicked well 400M and won without having much threats.
Settled in a prominent spot, 1.5Ls off the slow pace 2 wide, held up 500M as the field commencing to sprint, closed the race off very strongly 400M to run 2nd.
Shared the lead 2 wide at advantageous slow sectionals, ran on well to the line for 3rd without threatening the winner.
At back but comparatively more prominent than usual, 5Ls off the leaders along the fence, dashed strongly 250M despite not suited by the slow pace.
Settled in box seat, enjoyed the slow tempo, however soon flattened 300M.
Eased to sit in midfield, 3Ls off the leaders 3 wide, harmed by the slow sectionals, just held ground in straight.
Settled in front of midfield, 2Ls behind the slow tempo 3 wide, made early move 700M, however soon emptied 300M.
Travelled well along the fence in midfield, 3.5Ls off the leaders, not suited by the slow tempo, just held ground in straight.
Hard ridden early to keep up in about midfield, 4.5Ls off the leaders 3-4 wide, harmed by the slow pace, lacked turn of foot in straight, momentarily held up 250M.
At back, 6Ls off the leaders 2 wide, harmed by the slow pace, dashed well 200M.
Pushed to sit in front of midfield, 2.5Ls off the leaders 2 wide, not suited by the slow pace, flattened in straight.
Trapped 4-5 wide in midfield and lost too much ground, 3Ls off the leaders, not suited by the slow tempo, no turn off foot.
Eased back, 4Ls off the leaders 2-3 wide, not suited by the slow pace, never a factor.
Eased to rear, 7Ls off the leaders along the fence, harmed by the slow pace, no progress.
Raced in fourth one off rail, travelling comfortably, kicked on early in straight, always holding opposition.
Fair break, settled sixth one off, travelling well, improved to challenge, run flattened last 50m.
Broke well, midfield on rail, kept in pocket early straight, extracted and finished well.
Quick break, third on rail, pulled out to challenge early straight, kept on.
Squeezed start and lost length, fourth last on rail, improved on inside in straight, ran on well.
Away well from wide, led after 200m until passed by winner early straight, kept on one pace.
Sluggish break, fifth from rear one off rail, bustled before straight, driven, no kick.
Unhurried start, settled third last, tried to improve wide entering straight, driven, no kick.
Sluggish start, back to second last, last into straight, wide run, moderate progress.
Broke well, settled fifth on rail, pocketed, then checked straight, never threatened.
Not rushed from wide draw, last early, got no run in straight, but never dangerous.
Ridden up to join leaders from wide gate, travelled second one off, ridden early straight, weakened.
Travelled nicely in behind the steady pace, picked up strongly and got up 150M, continued on willingly to fend off late challenges on both sides.
In 5th position along the inside, pressed along passing 500M, quickened up well to challenge seriously in mid-stretch but was always held by the winner.
Had a smooth run in mid-division, waited with till 400M, picked up gradually, strong rally in late stages to get within a neck of the winner.
Niggled along early to find the lead, enjoyed an uncontested lead at slow tempo, kept on well till headed near 150M, weakened close home but held on for 4th.
Switched off the back 7Ls off the pace, driven 350M and took time to gather, did best work passing 200M before running into traffic close home.

Towards the rear and not hurried in early stages, difficult to settle near 1600M due to slackening tempo, shifted out for a clear run leaving the home bend, ran on well final 200M. (Jockey questioned re his riding.)
Placed one out one back, had every chance inside 400M if good enough but was outsprinted in late stages.
Tracked leader along the fence but couldn't accelerate when the race got serious inside 450M, kept on one paced.
Placed towards the rear 6Ls off the pace, kept on till finding no extra 150M.
Sharply out, ridden for position in fourth, pulled slightly, up to third home turn, pulled out, ran on gamely.
Good break, taken back to midfield one off, finished strongly, just failed.
Broke well, settled sixth on rail, slight interference far side, pulled out, ran on.
Good break, third on inside driven in straight, pocketed briefly, joined lead on inside when extracted, no extra near line.
Good break, back to midfield three wide, ran on well on outside without threatening.
Sluggish start, back to rear, driven straight, ran on quite well.
Good break, second one off rail, led in straight until weakened quickly late.
Not rushed early, fourth last far side, improved on rail straight, weakened.
Slow away, last early, wide straight, some late progress.
Fair break, ridden up on outside into fifth, ridden straight, weakened.
Fair break, but back to rear, fourth last into straight, driven, found little.
Only moderate start, back on rail to midfield, ridden, no kick.
Hard ridden from wide to lead early, headed early straight, weakened.
Away well, sat close to speed first without cover, did some work with reasonable sections, challenged turning and took over inside 250 M, kept on too well late.
Out in line, slotted into midfield, had good run 6Ls off top end, still had job to do when steadied on turn, closed hard late but couldn't wear down margin final 50 M.
First to hit ground, angled back to be 3Ls away 3 wide with cover, did a bit in mid-section, improved on turn, peaked inside 200 M.
No early dash and positioned at rear 8 to 9Ls from top end, aided by good tempo, tracked through well on turning, made a solid effort last 200 M to make frame.
Handy from outset, enjoyed a good run on leaders back, right there turning, into clear from 300 M, didn't find extra and just held ground late.
Even break, sat behind speed 3 to 4Ls away in running line, had decent run to bend, in traffic at 300 M and steadied at 200 M, out when race was over.
Taken down to rails soon after start, raced 5Ls back in midfield, had a quiet run to turn, made steady progress but couldn't go up a notch, tightened late.
Displayed usual speed to roll on and lead, set genuine sections in front, 1L advantage turning in, collared at 250 M and didn't find as expected. Below standard effort.
Average jump, ended up 3 wide behind midfield 6Ls off lead, awkwardly placed on circle, into clear at 400 M, lacked usual finish and just battled. (Lame next day.)
Faded back from a wide gate, raced 8Ls or so back 3 wide with cover at rear, checked at 850 M, still well back at 400 M, no real impression.
Crowded early, regathered to press on, raced 3 wide without cover 2Ls off pace, worked hard to bend, gradually dropped out after a tough run.
No early dash, planted 4 wide without cover for duration, set too much to do, weakened out in straight.
Away nicely, lobbed ideal spot 1 out 1 back on speed, did a bit with decent speed on, niggled on turning and folded cheaply.
No speed and drifted back from a wide alley, 8Ls back on rails, never likely.

Began with others, settled just better than midfield, commenced move around the bend, quickened well to take charge over 100 M out, soon drew clear.
Broke well, settled within 3Ls of speed in 4th or 5th on rails, improved to joint 3rd into straight, held some chance early on but winner too strong.
Began moderately, soon crossed for inside run behind midfield, remained similar to straight, saved ground turning in, fought on under pressure to be nearest at finish.

Began from the widest barrier, driven to take up running before stables bend, ceded advantage turning into back straight, settled inside leader to straight, renewed chance briefly upon straightening but soon folded up under pressure
Broke well, settled in midfield, remained similar to straight, met interference 200 M out, sustained progress to the line.
Began moderately, soon picked up to a prominent spot eventually taking over turning into back straight, held slender lead 2-wide until home turn, gradually weakened under pressure.
Began fairly, trapped wide before taken back to rear of field for inside run, shifted wide into straight, made up some late ground down outside to be nearest at finish.
Began with others, niggled along in midfield, went wide around stables bend, made steady progress when still wide down far side, carried widest and lost position turning in, never recovered.
Slow out, settled at the back, trailed field most of way, only went past backmarkers in the run home.
Broke well, settled outside leader early stages, became 2L 3rd far side, dropped out tamely shortly after Straightening.
Settled on rails in rear of midfield, saved ground turning in, faded under pressure in straight.
Began with others, soon settled towards rear, never a factor.
Parked 3 back the fence. Ran to the lead 100 M out and although inclined to shift out in the run to the line managed to hold on to victory.
Camped towards the tail of the field 3 deep with cover. Cornered wide and came with a strong burst down the outside to finish in a head bobber, despite shifting in over the latter stages.
Tracked the leader on the fence. Hit the front after the 200 M but was mowed down over the final stages and near the winning post struck solid interference.
Slow to begin settling behind midfield along the rail. Inclined to overrace early and was then held up until the 200 M, ran on steadily.
Camped midfield, 1 off with cover. Was in the firing line at the furlong and commenced to close off however struck interference over the final 100 M, and failed to finish in the frame.
Settled with the backmakers along the paint. Closed off well although was hampered close to the line.
Slowly away travelling worse than midfield, 1 off with cover. Maintained an even gallop right to the wire.
Throughout the race travelled 3-wide without cover in a midfield position. Never likely.
Ridden along early before being restrained and taking up a prominent trailing position, 2 deep with cover. Was steadied close to the line but was well beaten prior.
Settled at the rear, 1 off with cover. Struggled in the run home.
Worked hard to race in 2nd position, 1 off no cover. Faded over the concluding stages.
Led along the fence. Overhauled near the furlong and gave ground quickly soon after.
First to hit ground. Eased to prominent spot from 1000 M. Found run on fence at 300 M. Fought on all the way to the line. Just lasted.
Away in line. 2 to 3-wide, no worse than midfield through to home straight. Kept making up ground and was just denied.
Hard ridden early along the fence. Took lead 1000 M out. 1L clear turning in. Ran on well but kept hanging out. Settled for 3rd by a narrow margin.
Slow to begin and was then sent to rail at rear. Improved to race behind midfield from 1000 M. 4Ls down into final stretch. Finished off well once into clear at 250 M. Nearest at post.
Well enough away. Eased to sit at midfield on fence 1100 M out. Kept giving in the straight and was awkwardly placed from 150 M. Lost 4th near the line.
Shaken up after start but was trapped 5-wide in the front rank first turn. Shifted 2-wide behind leader 900 M out. Kept on but was one-paced in the straight. Checked near 50 M.
Out in line and raced 3-wide at midfield early. Shifted 4-wide and without cover ahead of midfield 700 M out. Found the line fairly well down the centre of the track.
Began awkwardly. Ridden along but was caught 4-wide first turn. Shifted to the fence at rear from 900 M. 5Ls away on straightening. Made up some ground thereafter.
Travelled wide and without cover ahead of midfield until home straight. Couldn't turn up a notch passing 300 M.
Caught wide and without cover behind midfield until shifting 3-wide from 700 M. No show in the straight.
Never better than midfield and barely got cover through to home straight. No response when asked.
Away with them. Crowded for room 1000 M and dropped to rear. Never recovered.
Good break, up on outside to lead after 400 M, steadied pace, kicked on straight, stayed on well.
Good break, fourth one off, ran on well to take second late.
Fair start but not go early pace, last early, improved leaving back, wide run, finished well.
Smack leaving stalls to put mind on job, midfield one off, driven straight, stayed on steadily.
Sluggish start, circled field to race second leaving far side, ran on in straight, but not trouble winner.
Fast break, settled in third, fell back on rail to midfield, ridden, slightly checked mid-straight, stayed on.
Slow away losing two lengths, raced fifth last taking time to settle, went for rail run straight, ran on well.
Sluggish start, second last on settling, slight check far side, last into straight, modest progress rail.
Taken back from wide draw, fourth last three wide, improved entering straight, slight check straight, no further progress.
Fair break but no early pace, midfield one wide, improved exiting back, ridden, weakened.
Fair break, then sluggish, third last one off, ridden straight, no progress.
Fair break, ridden for early lead, headed, third into straight, gradually weakened.
Quickly away, took relaxed position in fifth one off rail, challenged on outside straight, ran on strongly.
Quick break, third one off leaving back, ran on well in straight.
Fast away, led rail, ran well straight, collared 100 M out.
Lost length start, midfield one wide, improved leaving back, wide, ran on well.
Fair break, held up fourth last one off rail, improved entering straight, ran on steadily.
Fair break, back to fourth, took time to settle, baulked for inside run in straight, no further progress.
Not rushed early, midfield on rail, ridden, kept on one pace straight.
Fair break, then no pace, back to rear, second last and driven entering straight, ran on but never dangerous.
Well enough away, but no early speed, third last and bustled, stayed on straight but never near to challenge.
Broke well, ridden up on outside to share lead, neck lead far side, ridden straight, flattened out.
Slow break, last, driven straight, no real progress.
Fair break, ridden up to join leaders, gradually lost ground.
Pushed to occupy the box seat, enjoyed the slow early sectionals, drifted away 200 M to win easily.
Checked early, traveled well along the fence in midfield, 5Ls off the leader, dashed well 200 M despite not suited by the slow pace and secured 2nd.
Midfield, 4-1/2Ls off the leader 2 to 3-wide, harmed by the slow pace, held up 300 M, dashed well when clear and took 3rd.
Pushed to take rail and led by 1L at slow sectionals, hung on until 200 M flattened.
Hard ridden to obtain a midfield spot, 3-1/2Ls off the leader 2-wide, not suited by the slow tempo, just held ground in straight.
Eased back, 5Ls off the leader, harmed by the slow pace, trapped 3 to 4-wide throughout and lost too much ground, ran on ok in final stages despite all negative racing situations.
Eased to sit in midfield early but trapped 4-wide, then allowed to stride forward and sit outside the leader, benefited by the slow sectionals, weakened 250 M.
Eased back, 6Ls off the leader 2-wide, not suited by the slow pace, jumped shadow 800 M and lost ground, no progress.
Pushed forward, settled just off the leader to enjoy the slow tempo, however trapped 3-wide throughout and lost too much ground, faded 300 M.
Never a factor at rear, checked badly 800 M.
Never competitive at rear.
Pushed to sit in front of midfield, 2-1/2Ls off the leader, not suited by the slow tempo, trapped 3-wide throughout and lost too much ground, dropped off 400 M.
Not fast away, ridden, but back on rail to midfield. Took off like Arazi far side, led into turn, kicked clear, held on well.
Fair break, raced behind the leaders in sixth, one off, blocked briefly in straight, finished strongly.
Moderate start, taken back to last, improved leaving back, weaved through horses, finished fast.
Relaxed start, fourth one off, pulled wide straight, finished strongly.
Quick break but not hurried for lead, still one of five leaders into first turn, settled fourth one off, brought wide, ran on.
Quick break, took good spot on rail behind leaders, midfield far side, ran on straight, no impression.
Fair break, not hurried, held up second last, stayed on quite well along rail, not enough pace to challenge.
Good break, took spot on rail behind leaders, out to challenge straight, faded last 200 M.
Broke well, led early, joined, headed, ridden home turn, no progress, weakened.
Fast away, joined battle for lead, led into back straight, headed by winner, ridden, weakened.
Quickly away, joined battle for lead wide out, ridden when winner swept past, no more to give.
Taken back to rail from start, bustled to keep place, stride shortened quickly leaving back straight, found nothing.
Placed 2-wide in midfield, shaken up near 400 M and made rapid headway on straightening, hit the front 100 M out and finished well on top.
In 2nd last and not hurried in early stages, launched an outside move from 500 M and finished off the race willingly.
Held up behind midfield, pressed forward from 500 M and looped 3-wide over the final turn, led near 200 M, continued gamely and just failed to last late on.
Pressed the pace from outside, kept on same pace final 300 M and not a threat to the top three.
Slow to begin, shaken up early to obtain an inside position in midfield, shifted out 2-wide making the home turn but went back to inside to get clear in straight, ran on fairly final 200 M.

Positioned in 5th never far off the pace, held up briefly early straight, came through a narrow gap and made some late progress. (Jockey fined $20,000 for failing to ride his horse out to the end of the race.)
Unable to slot in and raced 3-wide without cover throughout, moved closer to pace passing 1200 M, couldn't pick up when needed and came up empty in late stages.
Quickly into stride and stalked leader to straight, badly held up from 300 M to 100 M and not able to have a clear crack.
Towards the rear throughout, had plenty to do turning in but not able to quicken.
Quickly into the lead from an outside barrier, led steadily to straight, found little when asked then eased passing 150 M.
Held a rail position in midfield, outpaced passing 300 M, never a factor.
Switched off the back 9Ls behind leader but was under urge halfway to maintain position, soon left behind in straight. (Unacceptable performance / Mucus.)
