Began fairly, niggled along to settle in 2nd inside leader, switched 2-wide around the bend when HINYUEN PALADIN crossed to rails, disputed lead turning in, gained upper hand over 100 M out.
Broke well from the widest barrier of 7, soon crossed over to lead, held narrow advantage until headed over 100 M out.

Slightly slow out, settled in mid-division of small field within 2Ls of speed, baulked behind heels of leaders on straightening, failed to quicken to threaten early in straight, kept on steadily to finish.
Began with others but soon detached from main field, picked up to join rear of field before home bend, fought on steadily under pressure.
In last few of small field far side, took closer order around the bend, improved to one-out-one-back position in 4th into straight, weakened tamely inside final 200 M.
Settled in last few of small field, slightly further behind turning in, made no impression in straight.
Travelled wide without cover in prominent positions to straight, folded up quickly inside final 300 M.
Settled early 3 back the fence. worked off the rail near the 400m, held off late challenge to claim the prize.
Camped behind midfield, 2 deep with cover. Came to the outside on straightening, ran on strongly.
Settled worse than midfield, 2-3 wide with cover. Peeled out turning for home and closed off soundly.
Raced ahead of midfield, 2 deep with cover. Cornered 4 wide battled away over the final stages to finish in the frame.
Settled in front of midfield coursing wide & without cover. Kept on one paced in the home straight.
Travelled with the backmakers, 1 off with cover. Dour in the final stretch.
Raced behind the speed 1 off with cover. Shifted out to pass a tiring runner near the 900m, settling 2 deep without cover. Assumed the lead near the 300m but ended its run passing the 100m.
Settled at the tail of the field 2 deep with cover. Commenced to run on early in the straight but peaked before the 100 M.

In the early and middle stages travelled wide and without cover and after the 1200 Metres was ridden forward to obtain a position closer to the rail on the back of the leader. Struggled in the run home.
Travelled 4 back the fence. struck trouble near the 900m and was again steadied near the 650m. failed to chase despite riders efforts after the 500m. was well beaten in the run to the line.
Settled with the backmakers on the paint. Copped some interference near the 900m failed to close off.
Took up leading duties along the rail. Pinched a break after the 900m, but faded soon into the straight.
Tracked the leader along the paint. kept to the inside in the straight, but weakened noticeably after the final furlong.
Travelled prominently before compounding badly near the 900m, finishing tailed out. To trial. (See incident report.)
Quickly into strides. Eased to sit 3-wide behind midfield from 1400M. Swung widest and was 8Ls down turning into home. Made up ground steadily and ran down rivals closing stages.
Jumped fairly but soon raced in front rank. Settled one-out-one-back 1300M out. Gave plenty in the straight but lacked the finishing touch to fend off the late effort of the winner.
Pressed early and occupied prominent spot from 1300M. Kept finding the line well with the front pair in the straight but couldn't quite beat them.
Urged along from high draw after nice start. Eventually sat one-off behind the pace from 1200M. Hung on and went home close with the front trio but was one-paced.
Rolled forward after start and took lead on fence 1200M out. Headed final 50M. Not beaten far.
2-wide at midfield through to home turn. Peeled out and was 4Ls off on straightening. Progressed gradually under pressure without seriously troubling the principals.
Gradually taken back from high draw. Sat towards rear on fence 1300M out. Under pressure and angled out rounding home turn. 7Ls back top of home straight. Made up good ground thereafter.
Failed to muster early despite effort of rider. Raced as backmarker through to home straight. 8-9Ls behind the speed passing 400M. Ran on fairly well to cover decent ground.
Always at midfield on fence through to home straight. Well positioned to strike but couldn't turn up a notch.
Given reminder early to stay behind midfield on fence. Similar position turning in. Ran on but not threatening.
Some 9-10Ls behind the leader through to final stretch. Made up minor ground to beat tired runners home.
Travelled 3-wide without cover ahead of midfield until no extra passing 200M.
Never better than midfield early and middle stages. No impression in the straight.
Parked 3-wide at midfield before dropped out passing 400M.
Good break, on rail in sixth, out to challenge on outside, ran on strongly.
Slow away, held up third last, tried to improve entering straight but little progress, took hold late and ran on strongly.
Good break, fifth on rail, pulled out to challenge but no real kick.
Quickly away out wide. Fourth one off on settling, out to challenge, ran on, then outpaced.
Fast out, back to midfield one off, ran on quite well between horses.
Fair start, three wide early, challenged for lead leaving back straight, led briefly, weakened.
Ridden early, but back to last from wide draw,, driven, some progress straight.
Lost length start, fifth last on rail, ridden, modest progress.
Fair break, ridden early to lead, joined leaving back straight, ridden, weakened.
Fast away but little early speed, up on inside to midfield, ridden straight, one pace.
Slow start, last early, modest progress along rail.
Good break, taken back from outside draw, rear division one off rail, came wide straight, no progress.
Sluggish start, rear div one off, time to settle, brought wide, found nothing.
Fluffed start slightly, ridden up to share lead, headed, ridden from turn, found nothing.
Fair break, ridden up to fifth two wide, led 500m out, kept on gamely.
Fair break, seeking cover early, fourth last, driven straight, finished fast.
Good break, not rushed, third on rail, looking for room constantly in straight, ran on well when escaped pocket, unlucky.
Good break, up on outside to lead, crossed to rail, ridden early straight, kept on.
Sluggish start, up on rail to midfield,, bid between horses, not quite get to grips with leaders.
Ridden early to take position on leader's shoulder, led 500m out, weakened late.
Lost length start, up to seventh one off, ran on well straight until weakened slightly last 50m.
Fair break, fifth last on rail, kept on, slight check late, but never threatened.
Good break, third one off, ridden straight, kept on one pace.
Fast ot, but no route to rail, back to midfield three wide, wide in straight, kept on.
Not rushed, taken back to last on rail overracing, tried to make ground on rail, little progress.
Early speed out wide, then back to third last, not settling, kept on but never threatened.
Good break, but not involved in battle for lead, back to last, kept on until eased late when all chance gone.
Fair break, midfield, wide into straight, weakened.
Jumped very well, eased to take the box seat, 2Ls behind the fast pace, lacked room 400M, closed the race off strongly to score nicely.
Pushed to take the rail and led by 1L at fast sectionals, hung on strongly until 50M, ran on to hold 2nd.
Prominent, 1L off the leader 2 wide, used up too much fuel to keep up with the fast sectionals, still ran on well to the line and took 3rd.
Awkwardly away, hard ridden early but failed to muster, ended up in midfield, 4.5Ls off the leader 3 wide, suited by the fast tempo, made ground steadily 250M.
Eased back, 6.5Ls off the leader 2 wide, helped by the fast pace, progressed steadily 300M.
Hard ridden forward, 2.5Ls off the fast pace 2 wide, just held ground in straight.
Pushed to obtain a prominent spot, 2Ls off the fast sectionals 3 wide, just held ground in straight.
At back, 6.5Ls off the leader along the fence, favoured by the fast tempo, just ran on ok in last quarter.
Eased to sit in midfield, 3.5Ls off the leader 2 wide, benefited by the fast pace, no turn of foot in final stages.
Hard ridden forward, 1L off the leader 2 wide, not suited by the fast pace, out of fuel 250M.
Eased to sit in midfield, 3.5Ls off the leader along the fence, favoured by the fast pace, soon weakened 300M.
Eased at start to take rail at rear, 9Ls off the leader, suited by the fast tempo, however no progress.
Eased at start, helped by the fast pace, but never competitive.
Fair break taken back to midfield rail, nice run through entering straight, pulled out, ran on strongly.
No rush early, eased back to rear, pulled wide straight, ran on very strongly.
Fair break, midfield one off, going well in straight when momentarily short of room, ran on.
Fast out, shared lead then back to fourth one off, out to challenge, led briefly, no extra.
Good break, not driven early, slipped back to fifth last on rail, ran on well between horses.
Broke well, back to seventh three wide to avoid lead battle, ran on well until weakened late.
Good break, reined back to sixth , checked far side, challenged mid-track, no extra last 200m.
Moderate break, fourth last early, unhurried, brought wide straight, ran on, but no real impact.
Air break, ridden up behind leaders, found slot on rail in fifth, tried to squeeze though on rail, no gap, no danger thereafter.
Smart break, but not quite get to lead, travelled second, ridden straight, weakened.
Slow away, second last, tried to improve entering straight, no progress.
Fair break, ridden early for third spot on rail, drive early straight, faded.
Fair break, but no early speed, third last, tried to make ground on rail, found nothing.
Fast out, led to 500m from home, weakened quickly, eased.
Allowed an easy lead and set a slow tempo at the front end, quickened up well and kicked 2Ls clear in mid-stretch, kept on in late stages and just lasted home.
Blundered at the start, towards the rear early but moved a shade closer approaching home bend, ran on strongly inside 300M to finish closest at the line.
Slow to begin, placed 2-wide 3-4Ls off the slow pace, ran on well inside 350M under a 5lb penalty.
Dropped to rear about 5Ls behind leader, angled out approaching home straight and made promising headway down the outside.

Forwardly placed behind leaders, not suited by the slow tempo and became unsettled approaching the Home Turn, kept on without quickening and was outpaced by the fast finishers inside 100M. (Jockey questioned.)
Raced at the hindquarters of the leader, kept on in straight but couldn't find extra pace when the race got serious.
Taken back to last, took time to muster in straight and never looked like reaching leaders. Minor headway inside 200 M.
Broke fastest but was reserved off the leaders, kept on one paced until weakening inside 150M.
Fair break, midfield one off, pulled out, finished very fast.
Good break, fifth on rail, easily gobbled up leaders 400m out, ran on, nailed on line.
Well away, up for third three wide, challenged alongside runner up, no extra.
Fast break, led on rail, joined after 400m, ridden, led again, no more to give late on.
Slow after gate, settled back fourth last, ridden straight, responded very well, checked last 50m.
Fair break, but no great early pace, third last, urged in straight, running on very well until checked 125m out.
Broke well, fourth one off rail, ridden straight, found little.
Good break, but could not go with leaders, reined back to sixth, ridden early straight, some progress until wakened late.
Good break, reined back, second last overracing slightly, ridden, some progress until checked late.
Fair break, held up behind leaders, progress on rail, flattened out.
Broke well, up on outside of leader, led into straight, weakened.
Fair break, no rush early, last far side, ridden straight, found nothing.
Fair break, slight check far side, fifth last entering turn, tried to improve, failed.
Fair break, tried to go with early pace, seventh and wide into turn, weakened quickly.
Dropped into nice spot 5Ls back in midfield with speed on, tracked well to turn, kept chasing final 300 M and eventually wore down winner in final strides.
Began nicely, took a trail on pace pair, held ground in first 400 M despite bumping, 2Ls back to bend, cruised to front and in command most of straight, run down late.
Got well back from a wide alley, best part of 10Ls off lead, aided by strong tempo, came to middle and made many lengths for 3rd.
Began with more purpose, ended up 4Ls back in 5th, easy time on rails to bend, kept on respectably in straight to make frame.
Slow into stride, ended up 8Ls down on rails, hot tempo in front suited, saved ground on bend, worked home soundly to be nearest on line.
Faded back from outside draw, shared rear 12Ls off speed, aided by tempo, produced a decent finish before racing in restricted room near 200 M, just held ground thereafter.
Restrained to tail from wide alley, 11Ls or so from fast pace, saved ground on rails on bend, made decent progress along inside in straight.
Broke nicely, 3 wide early before being forced to tuck in behind speed, bit keen 3 to 4Ls back to bend, loomed but didn't go on final 300 M, disappointing.
Average break, ended up 5 to 6Ls away on rails, used little in run, just held ground in straight.
No early pace, settled close to rear 9Ls off top end, aided by tempo, plenty to do turning, made some minor progress without looking likely.
Average beginning, positioned 7Ls of solid speed, even run to bend, didn't let down as usual and just plodded away in straight.
Broke well, pressed on to race outside leader, helped create a solid tempo in pace battle early, still challenging rounding bend.
Trapped 3 wide behind midfield 8Ls or so from lead, had no cover in mid-section, struggled turning and dropped out after hard trip.
Showed plenty of ready pace, set a solid tempo when challenged, drew 3Ls clear in pace battle on circle, niggled on turning, dropped out when hard run took toll.
Held up in midfield in early stages, fought on steadily in straight to just get up on line. (Questioned for improved performance.)
Began from a wide draw, gradually taken across to travel in a prominent spot, worked home well to miss by a narrow margin.
Always handy, disputed lead into straight, fought on well and only to be denied by a narrow margin.
Settled just better than midfield in 5th, in similar position turning in, baulked for a run 200 M out, finished off race strongly late.
Raced in last few, closed off race strongly to be nearest at finish.
Travelled wide in rear of midfield without cover, equally wide turning in, fought on steadily to be nearest at finish.
Soon took up running after beginning from the middle draw, held slender lead until joined early in straight, fought on dourly only to be overhauled close to home.
Settled towards rear, shaken up to challenge after straightening, made good progress between runners until running out of room late.
Raced wide in rear of field to straight, never nearer.
Soon taken back to race in rear, made no impression in the run. (Tactic questioned.)
Settled in rear of midfield, jostled between runners after straightening, soon dropped out under pressure.
Settled in midfield, saved ground turning in, kept on before fading over 200 M out.
Always struggling at the back.
Began moderately, soon picked up along rails to trail the leader, dropped out sharply after straightening.

Began from a wide gate, settled in a prominent position just off the rails, soon came to challenge upon straightening, took charge under pressure over 200 M out, won readily.
Began with others, niggled at early but gradually settled for forward of midfield spot, fought on dourly under pressure to grab 2nd close to home, winner too good.
Began well, led early, became 2nd around the bend, still up there turning in, faded under pressure over 200 M out.
Soon dropped to rear, remained in last few before taking closer order when wide around the bend, sustained progress in straight to be nearest at finish.
Broke well, always prominent, ran home one-paced without quickening.
Broke well, disputed lead early, gained one length advantage around the bend, joined early in straight, folded up quickly over 200 M out.
Began fairly, travelled in forward of midfield on rails, saved ground turning in, soon weakened under pressure.
Began slowly, soon picked up to travel just worse than midfield, ran home one paced.
Failed to muster speed early, soon dropped back to tail-end, saved ground turning for home, made no progress in straight.
Began moderately, gradually shuffled back to last few, made no impression in straight.
Settled just worse than midfield, wide around home bend when given reminders, made no impression in the run home. (Lame.) (Questioned for disappointing performance.)
Soon taken back from the widest gate to the rear, tailed-off into straight, made no impression. (Tactic questioned.)
Parked midfield the fence. Cornered four deep and finished off gamely to repel late challenge.
Settled towards the rear along the rail. Worked into the clear after the furlong and chased strongly to come up marginally short.
Stayed within a length of the leader to its outside. Hit the front near the 400 M, maintained a good gallop right to the wire.
Camped behind midfield the fence. Peeled out early in the straight and ran on well.
Travelled worse than midfield, 2-wide with cover. Closed off soundly.
Settled with the backmakers on the rail. Fenced up in the home straight and ran on nicely.
Enjoyed a nice run on the back of the speed after shifting out to travel 1 off with cover near the 900 M. Had every hope.
Raced towards the rear with cover. Passed tiring horse in the home straight.
Settled in near last position 1 of with cover. Came wide in the straight, whacked away at the same pace over the final stages.
Had every chance after shifting in near the 900 M and tracking the leader along the fence. No excuses.
Got back in the field from a wide gate, settling 2-wide with cover. Copped a check near 200 M, not likely thereafter.
Coursed wide early before slotting in to race 1 off with cover near the 900 M. Failed to run on.
Settled behind midfield, 1 off with cover. Failed to close off and was disappointing.
Led along the fence for most of the trip. Was a beaten horse turning for home, finishing well back. To trial. (See Racing Incidents.)
Soon led on fence. Accelerated passing 350 M and ran away. Won convincingly.
One-off the fence behind leader until home straight. Never able to challenge the runaway leader. All out to hold 2nd.
Away in line and raced 2-wide towards rear. Took inside run home turn. Peeled out and was 9Ls down on straightening. Made up good ground to snatch 3rd but was beaten far by the winner.
Well enough away. Elected to sit 3-wide ahead of midfield early. Shifted 2-wide and was 3Ls away rounding home turn. Kept giving in the straight with a good place chance. Just lost 3rd on line.
Quickly into stride but insufficient speed to lead. Raced 2-wide in midfield and was 5Ls off through to home straight. Ran on fairly well.
Ridden early along the fence to occupy prominent spot until home straight. Couldn't turn up a notch thereafter.
Jumped well. Raced within 3Ls of the pace in a 2-wide spot until home straight. Well positioned to strike but not much response when asked. (Roarer.)

Lifted its front feet off the ground at start and was slow to begin. Stayed behind midfield on fence through to home turn. Shifted 3-wide and was 8Ls adrift entering home straight. No pick up thereafter.
3-wide behind midfield early and gradually dropped towards rear turning for home. Passed beaten runners home.
Trapped widest and without cover behind midfield early and middle stages. Failed to quicken in the straight.
Began well and was taken to a spot behind midfield but was caught wide and without cover. Hung out on bend. No show in the straight.
Always at rear. No impression.
Good break, speed to take position on rail behind leaders, going well, split came early in straight, ridden to lead, comfortably.
Ridden from gate to take fifth on rail, slight check leaving far side, challenged down centre, not pace of winner.
Not rushed from outside gate, last early, improved leaving far side, midfield on rail into straight, ran on strongly on inside.
Good break, but not much early pace, midfield on rail, slightly short of room far side, ran on well.
No rush early, second last on rail, improved on inside leaving back, no immediate gap, pulled out and ran on.
Fair start, up on outside to grab lead on rail, joined, led into straight, headed, weakened.
Good break, back to midfield one off, lost places after slight check, pulled wide, ran on one pace.
Slightly fluffed start, but soon up to sixth one off, improved on outside entering straight, ridden, no extra.
Fair break, ridden up on outside to share lead, second exiting back, tried to challenge, weakened.
Good break, but short of early speed, mid to rear, some late progress.
Fair break, but slow into stride, drifted back through field, no real progress straight.
Fair break, but squeezed back early, one off rail near rear, tried to improve exiting back, no progress.
Fast out wide, taken inside when failed to lead, fourth exiting back, weakened.
Not much gate speed and reminders early, three wide, ridden, weakened.
Fair break, able to take ideal spot on rail, behind leader, had to wait for gap in straight, second got first run on him, got up near line.
Good break, followed leaders in fourth, one off rail, three wide turn for clear run, led 200 M out until near line.
Fair break, fifth on rail on settling, followed second through, ran on well.
Fast away, soon two lengths clear, led until challenged and passed mid-straight, weakened late.
Quick away, but not rushed, found spot on rail near rear, wide straight, ran on well.
Fair break, midfield one off, taken back off heels far side, clear run straight but could never get to grips.
Good break, not enough speed to lead and caught wide, up to second one off, ridden, weakened.
Fair break, one off in sixth, ridden turn, found little.
Taken back from wide draw, third last far side, tried rail run, no acceleration.
Taken back from wide draw, fifth last entering straight, ridden, not improve.
Dwelt and left five lengths, last, improved turn, tried to run on wide, never in the hunt.
Moderate start, back to rail near rear, ridden entering straight, found nothing.
Taken to rail from wide draw, rear, ridden, found nothing.
Pushed to secure a prominent spot, 1-1/2Ls off the fast pace 2-wide, closed the race off strongly 250 M to score.
Settled in midfield, 3Ls off the leader along the rails, benefited by the fast pace, held up 4-2. Made steadily ground when clear and took 2nd.
Pushed to take the rail and led by 1/2L at fast sectionals, hung on strongly until 100 M overhauled, ran on for 3rd.
Bumped start, hard ridden to keep up with the field at rear, 5-1/2Ls off the leader 2 to 3-wide, checked 600 M, favoured by the fast pace, progressed steadily 300 M.
Eased early but trapped very wide, then allowed to stride forward to sit outside the lead, not suited by the fast tempo, flattened 200 M.
Slow away, 3-1/2Ls off the leader along the fence, favoured by the fast pace, checked 600 M, just held ground in straight.
Hard ridden to occupy the box seat, not suited by the fast sectionals, out of fuel 250 M.
At back as usual, 5-1/2Ls off the leader 2 to 3-wide, helped by the fast tempo, just ran on fairly in final stages.
Eased to sit behind the leaders, 1-1/2Ls off the fast pace, trapped 3-wide, emptied 300 M.
Midfield, 3Ls off the leader 2-wide, benefited by the fast pace, no dash, flattened 250 M.
Eased at start to cross behind the field, 4Ls off the leader 3 to 4-wide, suited by the fast tempo, no progress.
Hard ridden early but failed to cross in front, trapped 4 to 5-wide and significant amount of ground, eased to sit behind midfield, never better.
Fast out, led, headed after 500 M, settled third, challenged mid straight, led and ran on strongly.
Good break but beaten for early speed, sixth on rail, squeezed through gap on rail, ran on, but winner long gone.
Out well, followed winner in fourth, ridden straight, ran on well.
Not rushed early, fourth last on rail, ran on in straight, finished well.
Fair break, midfield, shaken up entering turn, ran on quite well.
Fast out but five wide, taken back, ran on well.
Fair break, midfield, but three wide,, bustling but slipping back, ridden on outside, some progress, never dangerous.
Fast away from wide gate, shared lead three wide, back to second, soon ridden, weakened.
Missed break, then up fast to lead, two lengths clear into straight, caught 150 M out, swamped.
Fair break, not go early pace, last and bustled, stayed on in modest fashion.
Good break, in second wave of three early, tried to make ground on outside in straight, weakened.
Fair break, but no early pace, checked far side, ridden straight, found nothing.

In midfield along the fence, 5Ls off the fast pace in middle stages, shifted out for clear run 300M and soon found his stride once straightened up, ran on well to edge out the runner-up in late stages.
Had a smooth run behind the pace, knuckled down well to reach the front near 50M but was caught by winner late on.
In last pair over 12Ls off the pace, improved from 700M and ran on strongly in the home straight for some late impression.
Positioned behind midfield, driven passing 500M, finished well from off the pace without troubling the top 2.
Soon led but was taken on in middle stages and set a fast tempo down the back straight, had a commanding lead on straightening but effort flattened out inside 100M and was swamped in late stages.
Never far off but was kept 3-wide without cover to final turn, stayed on but found no extra pace to challenge.
Given a patient ride in the rear and was over 13Ls behind pacesetter in early and middle stages, still had plenty to do on straightening, ran on strongly over final 300M.
Pressed the early pace, taken back in chasing group down the back straight, kept on one-paced till finding no extra inside 200M.
Towards the rear over 10Ls back, driven inside 400M and progressed steadily but never looked threatening from off the pace.
Dropped back towards the rear over 10Ls off the pace, made steady progress on straightening but never looked like getting to the principals.
Held a 2-wide position ahead of midfield, hard driven halfway round the home turn and remained at the same pace to the finish.

Couldnt muster early, raced 4-wide round the first turn then strode forward from 1200M to chase the pace, under pressure and outpaced from over 500m out. (Jockey said his mount didn't appear comfortable on surface.)
Settled behind midfield 9-10Ls off the pace, had to be nudged along making the final turn, soon beaten.
Never better than midfield, shifted to 3-wide making the final turn, under pressure near 500M, made no progress and dropped off rapidly passing 200M. (Unacceptable performance.)

Began well from the one draw, held rails run in prominent position early, shifted out to be 2-wide in joint 4th rounding the bend, went wider turning in, responded well to assert authority inside final 300 M.
Moderate start, soon ridden to forward of midfield along the rails, fought on steadily in straight without threatening winner.
Settled wide towards the rear, ran on well down centre of straight to be nearest at finish. (Heat stress.)
Soon dropped to the rear, shaken up shortly after straightening, finished off race well inside final 200 M despite shifting ground.
Just behind midfield, switched out to challenge upon straightening, fought on steadily to be nearest at finish.
Raced wide in midfield far side, remained similar and without cover around the bend, ran home one-paced under pressure.
Contested early lead after beginning from the widest barrier, hit front briefly approaching home bend but handed up lead for the bend, trailed front runner into straight, soon found no extra.
Driven along to contest lead throughout early stages, crossed to the front around the bend, weakened noticeably inside final 200 M.
Began with others, remained in prominent position to straight, kept on before dropping out tamely inside final 200 M.
Slow out, soon dropped to the rear, picked up to one or two from last around the bend, went past well beaten horses in straight. (Questioned for disappointing performance.)
Niggled at throughout early stages, settled in rear of midfield around the bend, saved ground turning in, found nothing under pressure.
Broke well, gradually taken back to be just better than midfield but continued to race keenly, faded under pressure in straight.
Sluggish start, soon found himself in last few, never sighted thereafter.
Raced wide in forward position disputing second around the bend, soon compounded in straight.
Settled towards the rear 1 off with cover. Came widest in the home straight and closed off strongly.
Parked midfield the fence. commenced to work off the rail passing the 500m, rounding the home turn about 5 deep. Raced to a narrow lead 50m out but was nailed near the winning post.
Tracked the leader along the rail. Shifted out and gained a clear passage near the 300m, struck the lead near the 100M but was mowed down close to home.
Sent forward from the outside alley to race outside the leader. Hit the front near the 300m, but commenced to tire over the latter stages.
Settled midfield 2 deep with cover. Was carried out to race 3-4 wide without cover after the 500m. Cornered wide and worked home steadily before ending its run short of the line.
Camped 1 out 1 back. Carried out turning for home but only plodded to the finish.
Travelled 3 back along the rail. Shifted off the fence near the 500m to improve, but peaked on its run 100m out.
Settled worse than midfield the fence. railed up in the final stretch but went to the post one paced.
Led along the fence. was headed after the 400m, faded in the run to the line.
Travelled behind midfield, 2 wide with cover. Never really quickened and loboured over the final stages. (Vet reported mucopus.)
Raced in last position 1 off with cover. Failed to close off finishing well back.
Began awkwardly settling towards the rear along the paint. Struggled in the run home.
Raced within 2Ls of the pace early. Commenced his run from 500M and reached the leading section at 300M. Had a duel with the runner-up final 100M and prevailed closing stages. (Distressed.)
Sat behind the speed near the stands' rail. Hard ridden from 400M and responded well. Fought determinedly with the winner final 100M. Beaten narrowly at the line and left the rest of the field far.
Quickly into stride. Shared lead on stands' rail until headed 300M. Barely hung on for a non-threatening 3rd.
Closed to the pace near the far side early. Lacked the turn of foot to sprint with the front pair passing 300M. One-paced to conclude.
Showed good early speed and led until overhauled by the front trio final furlong. Lost 4th at post.
Back with last few early. Urged from 500M. Picked up fairly well passing 300M and was nearest at finish.
Always at midfield. Never nearer.
Failed to muster early despite the effort of rider. Improved from rear 300M out. Past beaten runners home.
Travelled behind the pace group early and middle stages. No response when asked inside 400M.
Towards rear always. Never really progressed.
In front rank until faded final 400M.
Near the pace early. Struggled from midpoint.
At midfield before dropping out midpoint. Never in contention.
Settled 2-3Ls behind the leader, one-off with cover, quickened well when asked at he top of straight, kept battling on, did well enough to withhold the challenger. (Lost left front plate.)
Broke well, urged to hold the fence in the mid-division, finished off well under pressure final 300 M, just late.
Broke well from gate 9 and soon obtained cover in the mid-division, dashed well when asked at the top of the home straight and looked possible to win, laid in, narrowly beaten.
Awkward start, soon caught up 5-6Ls off the pace on rails, checked at 1000 M, finished off satisfactorily final 350 M but never really troubled the top three.
Pushed to lead 1L, hung in early, left uncontested until the home turn, headed in by the winner at 300 M, kept on fairly under pressure.
Urged to hold a fence position in midfield, not properly clear until final 150 M, dashed well but really too late.
Easily ran up to take the box-seat just behind the leader, niggled along at the home turn, only one-paced when asked in the straight.
Jumped fast and soon occupied the one out one back spot, travelled nicely, kept on until couldn't find extra passing the 200 M pole. (Mucus and inflamed epiglottis.)
Lacked early speed and travelled 5-6Ls off the pace 3-wide with cover, finished off fairly well down centre of the home straight but failed to threaten the principals.
Lacked early speed despite being urged along, about 7Ls off the pace turning for home, made very limited progress under pressure final 250 M.
Taken to the rear from gate 12, raced fiercely and checked when pace slackened at 1000 M, laid in in straight, finished off only fairly.
Broke well from gate 13 but soon eased to the mid-division, caught 4-wide without cover early, finished off only fairly when clear at 400 M, never a factor.
Out in line, raced fiercely in the early stages when being restrained to the mid-division, checked at 1000 M, failed to make up any ground in the home straight.
Urged to take a one-off position just behind the pacesetters, ran on to take the lead 400 M out, kept on strongly and soon drew clear, impressive.
Lacked early speed despite being niggled along, ended up settling 6Ls off the pace 3-wide with cover, dashed well down centre of home straight final 400 M, finished off soundly for 2nd.
Easily ran up to take the one out one back spot, travelled nicely throughout, headed in by the winner passing the 400 M pole, kept on well enough for a place.
Urged along to hold a fence position in midfield, swung wide for home, made up ground quickly at the top of straight and looked possible for 2nd, failed to keep on final 100 M and lost a place.
Slow away, sat 5-6Ls off the speed on rails, crowded at 800 M, took time to obtain clear run in home straight, made up gradual ground final 250 M but never likely for a place.
Broke well, restrained 3Ls off the pace, 3-wide without cover, bit outpaced at the top of home straight, picked up late near 200 M, made ground steadily.
Settled cozily in a fence position in midfield, saved some ground rounding the bend, only one-paced when asked for efforts final 350 M.
Slow away, settled 3-4Ls behind the leader, checked at 800 M and 600 M, on heels at 100 M, gave limited response when asked in home straight, flattened passing 200 M.

Jumped fast but soon taken to the mid-division, travelled keenly when caught 4-wide without cover in the early stages, responded only fairly under pressure in home straight, crowded at 200 M, remained one-paced.
Niggled along to take the box-seat just behind the leader, struggled at the top of home straight, flattened passing 300 M, soon dropped out.
Jumped well from gate 14 but soon taken to the rear, travelled 7-8Ls behind the speed, on heels at 400 M and 250 M, failed to make up any ground after the interference.
Eased back from gate 11 and travelled about 6Ls off the pace, moved bit closer rounding bend, was blocked in the home straight, never tested.
Slow away, lacked early speed as usual and travelled 7Ls off the pace, niggled along rounding bend, failed to obtain clear run in the home straight, never tested.
Out in line, pulled his way up to lead 1L on the rails, travelled satisfactorily until headed at the top of home straight, soon weakened sharply, finished tailed out.
Pushed to take the rail and led by 1.5Ls at good pace, just good enough to make all.
Pushed forward as usual, settled just behind the leader with good pace, closed the race off strongly, just beaten by a nose in 2nd.
Eased to sit in front of midfield, 3.5Ls off the good pace along the fence, made steady ground 300M and grabbed 3rd.
Midfield, 4LS off the good pace, trapped 3 wide throughout, progressed steadily 300M.
In front of midfield, 3Ls off the good pace 2 wide, raced keenly, lacked room 400M, just held ground when clear.
Eased to sit in midfield, 4.5Ls off the good pace 2 wide, made minor ground in last quarter.
Hard ridden to occupy the box seat, bumped 400M, checked 250M, flattened onwards.
At rear, 7.5Ls off the good pace, trapped 3-4 wide and lost ground, ran on ok in final stages.
Prominent but trapped 3 wide without cover, 2.5Ls off the good pace, ran on until 200M flattened.
Slow away, pushed to hold a rail spot in midfield, 5.5Ls off the good pace, no dash in final stages.
Eased back, 7.5Ls behind the good pace 2-3 wide, ran on fairly in last quarter.
Very slow away, at rear, 7Ls off the good pace on the rails, no turn of foot in straight.
Eased back, 6Ls off the good pace 2 wide, no progress.
Eased back, trapped 3 wide, never better than midfield.
Awkward start, soon ran up to share the lead on the stand rails, kept on strongly under hands and heels riding, never really troubled by the only challenger.
Bumped start, soon ran up to track the leader, launched a furious challenge final 450 M, performed really well but still insufficient to threaten the winner.
Broke fast from gate 1, showed good early speed as usual and soon got across towards the stand side, failed to match the top two near 400 M but did keep on well enough for 3rd.
Out in line, settled 2-3Ls off the pace, took time to pick up when clear at 400 M, finished off soundly final 250 M, just late for a place, pleasing debut.
Started awkwardly but soon caught up 2Ls behind the leader, travelled fiercely when restrained early, looked possible for a place passing the 200 M pole, failed to keep on final 50M, however.
Jumped fastest, crossed towards the stand side and travelled just behind the leader, struggled when pace quickened halfway, picked up late at 200 M, made gradual ground down centre of the track.
Broke well, travelled about 2Ls off the speed on the stand rails, outpaced near 500 M, rather one-paced in the concluding stages.
Settled 3-4Ls behind the speed, checked at 400 M, only gave limited response when asked for efforts after the interference.
Lacked early speed as usual and travelled 3-4Ls off the pace, kept on fairly well when not properly clear from 500 M to 300 M, failed to offer extra in the concluding stages.
Pushed forward to catch up 2-3Ls behind the leader, struggled when pace quickened at 500 M, yield ground and soon dropped out.
Out in line, settled 2-3Ls off the speed on the stand rails, failed to quicken when asked for efforts final 400 M, soon faded.
Out in line, settled 3Ls off the speed, couldn't find extra when pace quickened at 500 M, soon outpaced, finished tailed out.
Given a patient ride towards the rear and was miles off the pace in middle stages, waited with till 450M, stayed on strongly inside 250M and got up in closing strides.

Towards the rear about 10Ls back in first half, shifted out 550M to improve but was forced very wide nearing the entrance of straight, quickened well down the outside, led inside 200M but couldn't fend off the winner in late stages.
Behind mid-division early, strode forward from 1400M to race just off leader, ran well despite being 19 lb out of handicap and rallied on to claim 3rd in closing stages.
Positioned 2-wide in chasing group, shifted out to challenge passing 500M, took over from 350M-200M but couldn't sustain effort in late stages.
Held up towards the rear, way off the pace in first half but crept closer making the home turn, responded well in early straight but turned flat passing 150M.
Not helped by the slow sectionals and raced keenly behind mid-division, shifted out to improve 600M, briefly looked a chance in early straight but run ended passing 200M.
Along the fence in midfield before switching 2-wide entering the back straight, pushed wider over the home turn, stayed on same pace final 400M and was never likely.
Taken forward to sit in group chasing the pace, shuffled back to midfield after halfway, not quickened on straightening and could keep on one paced only.
Placed 2-wide in 6th, not suited by the slow tempo and raced keenly at times, shifted out 600M to improve 4-wide, had no excuses in straight but found less than expected, outpaced 250M then eased.
Tracked leader and saved ground on the inside throughout, held up by a beaten runner early straight but didn't find much when clear.
Set slow tempo early, went quicker down the back straight and opened up a 5Ls lead at halfway, restrained near home turn, headed inside 400M and found nothing left in reserves, eased.
Cozily sat just behind the leader, suited by the soft tempo, kept on well in the home straight and caught the exhausted leader final 50 M.
Easily ran up to lead 2Ls, left contested, quickened well when asked at the top of home straight, flattening final 100 M and soon headed by the winner.
Given a waiting ride and travelled 7Ls away near the rear, responded well when asked for efforts final 350 M, finished off soundly for 3rd.
Broke well but soon restrained towards the mid-division, one-off with cover, made up ground steadily final 350 M, just late for a place.
Restrained early and travelled 3-wide with cover in the mid-division, shifted widest for home, finished off fairly well down the centre of the straight, but insufficient for a place.
Out in line, prominently placed within striking distance from the leader, had every chance in the home straight, only one-paced under pressure, couldn't find extra final 100 M.
Taken to the rear from gate 12, held up for clear run early in straight, dashed well when asked for efforts final 300 M, blocked again 100 M out, not fully tested.
Lacked early speed, travelled 6Ls away just behind the mid-division, bumped at 350 M, finished off only fairly under pressure.
Urged along to hold a fence position 3-4Ls off the speed, travelled satisfactorily, gave very limited response when asked for efforts final 350 M, outpaced 250 M out.
Taken back from the widest alley, caught 4-wide with no cover, crept closer rounding the home turn, failed to quicken when asked for efforts at the top of home straight, never in contention.
Settled 6Ls off the pace on the fence, checked at 500 M, placed under pressure final 350 M, failed to make up any ground.
Jumped well, prominently placed about 2Ls behind the leader, held ground until flattened at 250 M, soon dropped out.
Broke well from gate 10, given a waiting ride as usual and travelled 7Ls behind the speed, failed to obtain clear run in home straight, not fully tested.
Widely drawn, urged to take a 3-wide position 4Ls off the pace, failed to hold its position passing 400 M pole, soon weakened and finished last.
Began with more purpose, pressed on to lead, joined by outside horse on circle, found good kick on turning and dashed clear final 300 M to go to win easily.
Out better than usual. Positioned prominently 2 to 3Ls back on rails, tracked well to bend, couldn't match dash of winner but stuck on well in straight.
Away with rest, settled in midfield on rails 5 to 6Ls back, had an easy time to turn, took inside runs and worked home before steadied at 200 M, came again late despite being difficult to ride.
Even break, ended up just in front of midfield, 5Ls from top end, reasonable run in mid-section, kept on at same pace in straight.
Settled behind midfield in running line, 8Ls from leaders in middle stages, came wide on turning, closed off nicely from well back.
Faded back to settle next to last, 10Ls or so from top end, well back and took inside runs, in traffic and held up final 200 M, not properly tested.
No early pace, dropped to rear 12Ls or more from lead, still last in impossible spot turning, worked home well down outside to be nearest on line. (Ride questioned.)
Began well, pushed on to race outside leader, gradually worked level rounding bend, lacked extra gear and dropped off from 200 M.
Lost some ground at jump, behind midfield 9Ls back to turn, came wide but set too much to do, made gradual progress without threatening.
Out with rest, posted 3 wide 5Ls back in midfield, further back than expected but had cover throughout, crept closer on bend, didn't find and faded 300 M.
Well enough away, pressed on to be just behind pace 3 wide facing breeze, challenged turning, hard run took toll and faded out final 250 M.
Standard break, best part of 9Ls back on rails, even trip through mid-section, didn't respond in run home.
Urged to take a prominent spot, sat behind leader on even speed, niggled turning, gradually faded in straight.
Only fair to begin, 6 to 7Ls back behind midfield on rails, soft run throughout, no response in straight, ordinary effort.

Settled just off the speed on rails in 3rd, similar turning in, fought on dourly to snatch victory final strides.
Attempted to make all, kicked 2Ls clear under pressure early in straight, unable to sustain effort, overhauled inside final 50 M.
Soon taken across for rails run around midfield, saved ground to come closer turning in, did not find much room throughout straight but still nearest at finish.
Sluggish at start, trailed the field and tailing off early, saved ground turning in, held up to 250 M in straight, finished off race well closing stages.
Began with others, soon improved to one-back-one-back spot, slightly further back turning for home, ran home one-paced. (Lame.)
Soon taken back to last few from a wide gate, finished off race nicely despite hanging in and a difficult ride in straight. (Tactic questioned.)
Raced wide in midfield, ran home one-paced.
Raced keenly just better than midfield, tight between runners after straightening, ran home one-paced.
Soon taken back from the widest draw, remained well behind in last few, saved ground turning in, made some impression down inside early in straight.
Settled just worse than midfield, did not find much room throughout straight, not properly tested.
Began fairly, soon improved to a prominent spot, mainly 2 back 3 wide down far side, similar turning in but folded up quickly.
Began from a wide draw, remained 4 wide in midfield without cover down far side, widest runner turning in, no further impression.
Sent forward to lead on the rails, setting a good clip. Pinched a break after the 500 M, and was able to maintain its advantage all the way down the running.
Enjoyed the run of the race, tracking the leader along the paint. Switched out to challenge after the 300 M, ranged up and looked the likely winner but was unable to claw back the margin.
Parked 3 back the fence. Pushed along after the 500 M to improve, stayed on soundly.
Camped 1 off close to midfield with cover. Cornered 3-wide, and after being steadied early in the home straight, maintained an even gallop to finish in the frame.
Ridden along early to travel slightly ahead of midfield, 3-wide no cover. Kept on one paced over the concluding stages.
Settled behind midfield, 3 deep with cover. Angled out into clear running near the 300 M, closed off fairly.
Lacked early speed as usual and settled 7 to 8Ls off the speed on rails, swung widest for home, made little ground when asked for effort final 300 M.
Slow to begin, settling at the rear of the field, 1 off with cover. Switched to the inside early in the run home and worked to the post fairly.
Urged along to hold a one-off spot about 3Ls behind the leader, held ground until outpaced passing 200 M, soon faded.
From the outside barrier was taken back to a position at the tail of the field, along the rail. Failed to run on in the final stretch. (See Racing Incidents.)
Urged along early but failed to muster speed, ended up travelling 9Ls off the pace, struggled throughout the trip, failed to make up any ground in the home straight.
Settled midfield the fence. Gave ground quickly in the home straight. Post race vet report, heart irregularity.
Jumped well. Elected to sit 2-wide behind midfield from first turn. Swung 5-wide and was 3Ls down turning into home. Rallied on and dominated final 100 M.
Crowded for room at start. Taken to rear on fence from first turn. Took some time to shift out for clear run top of home straight. Did the best work inside final 250 M to snatch 2nd at post.

Well enough away and held the fence making first turn. Elected to sit prominently from approaching the Rock. Every chance in the straight but found the winner too strong final 150 M. Hung on for 2nd until last stride.
Worked early in leading section but couldn't cross. Ended up 3-wide in midfield passing 1000 M. Forced to go widest and was 3 to 4Ls away rounding home turn. Kept on fairly well.

Quickly into stride but was trapped 3-wide making first turn. Shifted 2-wide behind the pace group from 800 M. Well positioned to strike in the straight but lacked the finishing touch of the principals.
Slow to begin but was soon driven to race 2-wide ahead of midfield. Took inside run leaving the bend but found traffic until 200 M. One-paced to conclude when clear.
Shaken up after start but didn't quite muster. Rolled to a 2-wide spot towards rear from first turn. Some improvement passing 450 M but was held up top of home straight. Just ran on thereafter.
Hard ridden early from high draw but was caught wide. Under pressure until leading one-off the fence approaching home turn. Still in front early home straight. Headed final furlong.
Pressed early but was trapped 4-wide. Urged along and eventually settled on fence behind pace 600 M out. No extra final 200 M.
Always behind midfield. Never nearer.
Towards rear always. Never in the hunt.
Travelled wide and without cover with leaders before dropped out 300 M from home.
Sat 3Ls off the pace, caught 3-wide without cover early, strode forward at 800 M and hit the front at 600 M, dashed impressively when asked at the top of home straight, drew clear easily.
Prominently placed 2Ls behind the speed, ran up rapidly when pace quickened at 600 M, could not match the strides of the outstanding winner in home straight but did well enough for 2nd.
Widely drawn, driven to race one-off just behind the mid-division, bit outpaced when tempo quickened near 600 M, finished off well under maximum pressure final 250 M, ran on for soundly for 3rd.
Cozily sat 4Ls off the speed, ran up steadily under pressure when pace quickened at 600 M, only one-paced when asked for efforts in the home straight and lost a place inside 100 M.
Lacked early despite being pushed hard early, ended up travelling 4 to 5Ls behind the leader, niggled along rounding home turn, made up gradual ground under maximum pressure final 300 M.
Widely drawn, urged to try to get across in front and ended up travelling one out one back, pushed hard when pace quickened at 600 M, could not find extra final 250 M.
Slow away, taken across behind runners and travelled 5 to 6Ls off the speed, rather one-paced when asked for efforts in the home straight.
Urged along to occupy a fence position 3Ls off the pace, carried backward by a tired runner from 400 M, made up late progress when clear final 200 M.
Taken to the rear from gate 12 and travelled about 7Ls behind the leader, made very limited progress in the home straight.
Prominently sit 1L off the speed on rails, bit outpaced rounding the home turn, held ground until flattened at 200 M.
Urged along to travel 6Ls off the pace, struggled rounding the home bend, swung widest for home, failed to make up any ground.
Easily ran up to lead 1L, passed at 600 M, held ground until flattened at 200 M, soon faded.
Broke only fairly, soon driven to catch up 2Ls off the pace, travelled one-off with cover, ran on to contest the lead at the top of home straight, fought hard to withhold the challenger.
Niggled along to share the lead, hung out badly at 550 M, hung in but kept battling on in the home straight, narrowly beaten by the winner.
Jumped fairly, settled just behind the pace on 3-deep, badly checked and carried very wide at 550 M, recovered soon after entering the home straight, finished off soundly final 200 M for 3rd.
Pushed hard forward to hold a fence position 3Ls off the speed, raced in restricted room final 200 M, finished off satisfactorily, just missed a place.
Urged along to share the lead on rails, headed by the winner at 200 M, kept on fairly well under pressure, laid in the concluding stages.
Lacked early speed and travelled 5Ls off the pace, finished off well and made up gradual ground final 200 M under pressure.
Jumped fastest, urged along to share the lead on 3-deep, carried very wide by anther runner at 500 M, kept on fairly in the home straight, could not find extra final 150 M.
Slow to begin, urged along to catch up 5Ls off the pace, failed to make up any ground in the home straight.
Lacked early speed and ended up travelling 7Ls off the speed, no response when asked at the top of home straight, never in contention.
Jumped well from gate 12, pushed hard forward to share the lead on 4-deep, carried very wide at 550 M, got tired passing 300 M, gave ground quickly.
Slow away, always rearward, struggled halfway, lost touch at home turn, finished tailed out.
Hard ridden to sit outside the lead, not suited by the fast early sectionals, closed the race off strongly and won by narrow margin.
Eased at start to cross at rear for cover, 7-1/2Ls off the leader 2-wide, favoured by the fast pace, lacked room 300 M, progressed steadily when clear and ran 2nd, just beaten by a neck.
Eased to sit just behind the leading group, 2-1/2Ls off the fast pace 2-wide, ran on well to the line for a close 3rd.
Hard ridden to take the rail and led by 1/2L at fast early sectionals, hung on strongly until 100 M overhauled and flattened.
Midfield, 4-1/2Ls off the leader 2-wide, benefited by the fast pace, made steady ground 200 M.
Midfield, raced very keenly, 3Ls off the leader 2-wide, suited by the fast tempo, made minor ground 200 M.
Checked badly first bend, at back, 5-1/2Ls off the leader along the fence, benefited by the fast pace, held up 4-2, progressed steadily when clear.
Pushed to occupy the box seat, not suited by the fast tempo, blocked whole straight, never tested.
Midfield along the fence, checked early, 4-1/2Ls off the leader, helped by the fast pace, however lacked room most straight, not really tested.
At back, 5-1/2Ls off the leader 2-wide, favoured by the fast tempo, made some ground 200 M.
Hard ridden early but failed to take lead, 3Ls off the fast pace along the fence, just held ground in straight.
Bumped start, never traveled well at rear, 8-1/2Ls off the leader on the rails, suited by the fast pace, but ran on only fairly.
Out in line, soon ran up to share the lead on rails, quickened well when asked for efforts at the top of home straight, did well enough to withhold the challenger.
Settled 2Ls behind the pace, caught 3-wide until found the fence at home turn, improved along the inner in the home straight, finished off well final 200 M for 2nd.
Pushed hard forward and sat 2Ls off the pace on rails, kept battling on in the home straight under maximum pressure, got a place in the final stride.
Niggled along to track the leaders on 3-deep, kept on well in the home straight, bit one-paced final 50 M, just lost a place.
Jumped fast, prominently placed one-off just behind the pace, not properly clear early in the home straight, finished off satisfactorily final 150 M but too late for a place.

Checked after start, travelled at the rear despite being urged along early, 4Ls behind the leader turning for home, blocked early straight and checked at 200 M, finished off soundly final 150 M, but really too late.

Jumped well, lacked early speed despite being urged along early and drifted back toward the rear, shifted wide for home, made gradual ground down centre of the straight, but never really troubled the principals.
Broke well from gate 12, travelled within 2Ls off the pace but caught very wide throughout the trip, held ground until got tired 100 M out.
Out in line but soon taken to the rear, travelled 4 to 5Ls off the speed on 3-deep, swung widest for home, only made limited progress in the straight.
Driven hard to share the lead, struggled turning for home, failed to keep on passing the 200 M pole, gave ground quickly.
Broke only fairly, soon ran up to the front but caught very wide with no cover, outpaced at the top of home straight, soon faded.
Placed 2-wide in mid-division, got a shade keen over the first turn, switched wide 400 M to deliver his challenge, put in a sustained effort and got up in late stages.
Moved forward to race one out one back after a slow start, responded well to pressure and led mid straight, galloped on but was eventually run down in late stages.
Stalked leader off the rail and travelled strongly to straight, box seated and held up near 200 M, altered course and made up ground late despite a narrow passage.
Never far off the steady pace, ran on well final 300 M and posted a solid effort in defeat.
Broke well, led steadily to 200 M, got tired and dropped out of contention.

Held up behind mid-division, well covered but proved difficult to settle at times, ran on fairly in straight and never looked like reaching leaders. (Jockey reminded to ride out his horse to the end.)
Towards the rear on the inside, 6 to 7Ls behind leader making the final turn, took time to muster on straightening and made some minor headway late on.
Broke well from gate 1 and had a smooth run off the rail throughout, 4Ls down turning in but couldn't find the necessary response when the race got serious.
In mid-division but was left 3-wide without cover entering back straight, pressed along 400 M but not quickened, kept on same pace to the line.
Off the rail behind mid-division, stayed on same pace to the line. Never a factor.
Taken across behind runners, settled in last 8Ls off leader, no impression on straightening.
Slow to begin, positioned 3-wide towards the rear, driven 350 M but no progress, weakened 100 M out. (Mucus.)

Began with others, soon held back to stalk leaders, showed a great turn of foot inside final 200 M to win impressively.
Fast to begin, settled just off the speed but without cover, came to challenge inside final 300 M, responded well to outsprint the rest of the field except to find the winner too good.
Began moderately, settled about 3Ls off the speed along stands' rails, obtained clear passage inside final 300 M, kept on steadily at the one pace without quickening.
Showed good early speed despite stumbled jumping out, held lead or disputed lead until overhauled under pressure inside final 200 M.
Began awkwardly, settled about 3Ls off the speed, failed to quicken under pressure inside final 200 M, plodded on.
Showed early speed to soon get across from the one draw to dispute lead, folded up quickly inside final 250 M.
Began with others, settled about 3Ls off the speed near the centre of the track looking for cover halfway out, ran home one-paced under pressure.
Met minor interference at start, soon dropped towards rear, raced greenly under pressure throughout, produced some late impression.
Slightly slow to begin, settled about 3Ls off the speed down centre of the track, gave ground gradually under pressure inside final 400 M.
Very slowly away, detached until running past well beaten horses inside final 350 M.
Ridden to muster pace early, gradually weakened under pressure from towards the rear after coming onto course proper.
Began moderately, soon picked up to a prominent position, led or disputed lead from 600 M to 300 M, dropped out tamely.
Stumbled at start and lost ground, soon recovered to travel within 3Ls of speed down centre of the track, yielded ground gradually after coming onto course proper.
Began slowly, remained in rear throughout.
Hard ridden to maintain its position behind midfield along the rail. Got runs through the field in the final stretch to claim victory well before the winning post.
Ridden along to keep a midfield position, the fence. Kept to the inside in the straight and once properly in the clear near the 200m, fought strongly to the line.
Camped worse than midfield, 1 off with cover. Was shunted wide after the 600m and lost ground. Regained momentum soon after and closed off well.
Parked 3 back, 2 wide with cover. Eased out early in the straight and maintained a good gallop to the wire.

Handed up front running duties near the 900m & stalked the leader thereafter along the fence. peeled out early down the running and hit the front at the furlong but was overhauled to finish out of the frame.
Settled 2 wide, midfield with cover. Whacked away at the same speed in the run to the line.
Travelled midfield, 3 wide without cover. Struggled in the home straight.
Settled in second last position, 1 off with cover. Coursed wide from about the 600m, passed tiring horses in the straight.
Ridden forward from the outside alley to make all along the fence approaching the first turn. Faded after the furlong.
Worked forward to settle in 2nd position, 1 off. Was disappointing in its failure to finish the race off and was well beaten.
As the start was effected reared, hit its head on the overhead bar and consequently lost a considerable amount of ground, settling a long last. Never recovered. (To trial.)
Settled towards the rear along the fence. Proved a handful, making the first turn awkwardly and shifting out abruptly. Never a factor. (To trial.)

Urged along the fence to maintain behind midfield after start. Surrounded by runners top of home straight. Still 2Ls to make up when clear at 200M but kept chasing the leader gamely to score victory near the line.
2-wide at midfield through to home turn and was 3Ls down on straightening. Kept finding the line well under pressure but shifted out from 100M which nearly cost its 2nd.
Took a seat at midfield on fence after start. Shifted 3-wide and was 2Ls away turning into home. Ran on to build a clear advantage passing 200M. Caught by the winner final 50M and lost 2nd at post.
Jumped well but was eased to rear from 1400M. Gradually shifted to the stands' rail and was 6Ls off after 400M. Made headway under pressure to narrowly miss a placing.

Standard jump. Gradually eased towards rear in a 2-wide spot from 1300M. Swung wide and was 5Ls adrift leaving the bend. Kept making up ground and a good place chance inside 100M. Just failed to sustain its effort close home.

Under some pressure early to race forward. Handed up the lead passing 1400M. Dropped back a bit when other runners improved at 1100M. Hard ridden approaching 600M but couldn't go with the principals final 300M.
In search of cover from widest gate after start. Raced within 3Ls of the pace in a 2-wide position from 1200M. Reached the back of pace group into final stretch. Couldn't turn up a notch thereafter.
Slowly away and raced towards rear from 1300M. Hung in and was awkwardly placed at 600M whilst progressing. Steadied at 400M and was checked at 200M. Ran on to beat tired runners home.
At rear on fence through to home turn. Improved in the straight before checked and held up for running final 300M. Resumed passing 100M and ran on.
Pressed to go forward after a fair start. 2-wide handy from 1400M. Hit front briefly at 450M and was headed 300M. Weakened passing 200M.
Failed to muster despite being ridden along early. Stayed 2-wide behind midfield 1400M out. Never improved from there.
Rolled forward from high draw. Eventually led on fence at 800M. Levelled turning in and found no extra to fight thereafter. Faded final 100M.
Worked across to lead on fence at 1200M. Took seat behind pace at 1000M. Shifted out to challenge the lead entering home straight but soon dropped out of contention.
Travelled wide and without cover near the pace until weakened leaving the bend. (Substantial blood in trachea.)
Out fast, settled second one off rail, challenged two wide, wore down leader, held on.
Broke well out wide, fifth one off exiting back, six lengths to find halfway up straight, ran on strongly, just failed.
Fast away, led on rail, challenged by two horses early straight, beat one off, could not hold the other or the runner up.
Away well wide, settled fourth one off, ridden early straight, ran on one pace.
Fair break, third on rail, challenged early straight, briefly drew level, weakened late.
Sluggish start drifted back to second last, ridden before straight, stayed on well wide out last 150m.
Fair break but not much early pace, midfield and ridden, ran in snatches, got the idea late, ran on.
Fair break, midfield, bustled, only moderate progress.
Fair break but not go early pace, urged along on rail but only modest progress.
Fair break but no early pace, back to last one off, came wide, ridden, found little.
Slow away, held up second last, ridden before straight, no headway.
Fair break, fourth last one off, wide turn, ridden, found nothing.
Ridden early to take fourth on rail, travelled well, gap came, finished strongly, comfortably.
Fair break, ridden up to share lead, fourth leaving back, ridden early straight, ran on, not reach winner.
Good break, led rail, joined and passed, third into straight, led briefly, no extra.
Fair break, up to fifth unhurried, took while to settle and back to midfield, pulled out, ran on.
Away on terms but not rushed, fourth last one off, made ground between horses straight, ran on without being able to challenge.
Fair break, midfield on rail, bid inside straight, ran on but no danger.
Steadied after fair start, midfield one off, improved wide turn, ridden, no real progress.
Slow start, ridden, followed winner on rail, driven, one pace.
Moderate start, scrubbed along early, settled midfield, improved leaving back, ridden, found little.
Taken back from wide draw, second last, improved three wide, ridden straight, no further progress.
Taken back from wide draw, ridden leaving back, tried to run on wide, no progress.
No rush early, back to last, tried to improve on rail straight, never a threat.
Not fast away, settled near rear, ridden wide and slight bump, found nothing.
Out well, ridden from wide draw, up to second, bustled to keep pitch, ridden, weakened.
Pushed to obtain the box seat, not suited by the fast early tempo, closed the race off strongly and won by a narrow margin with the help of a 10-pounds claimer.
Eased to sit in midfield, 5.5Ls off the leader 2 wide, benefited by the fast tempo, lacked room 4-2, progressed steadily when clear, just beaten by a short head in 2nd.
Settled in front of midfield, 3Ls off the fast pace 2 wide, failed to keep up with leaders 600M, made some late ground 200M and took 3rd.
Eased to sit in midfield along the fence, 5.5Ls off the leader, favoured by the fast pace, held up 4-2, made steady ground when clear but never threatening the winner.
Pushed to take the rail and led by 1.5Ls at fast sectionals, hung on strongly until 100M overhauled, just missed a place.
Eased at start, 8Ls off the leader 2 wide, benefited by the fast pace, made good ground in straight, lacked room 200 M.
Eased to sit in midfield, 4.5Ls off the leader 3 wide, suited by the fast tempo, however just ran on ok in final stages.
Eased back, 7Ls off the leader 3 wide, benefited by the fast tempo, progressed steadily 300M.
Eased at start, 9Ls off the leader 3-4 wide, favoured by the fast pace, made steady ground 300M, run ended 100M.
Prominent, 1.5Ls off the leader 2 wide, not suited by the fast sectionals, weakened 200M.
Very slow away, pushed to sit 5.5Ls off the fast tempo, trapped 4 wide throughout, moved forward 800M, soon exhausted 400M.
Never competitive at rear and tailed out.
Eased to sit in front of midfield, 3.5Ls off the fast pace on the rails, dropped off rapidly 400M.
Behind midfield on the fence, never a chance, checked 800M and tailed out.
Fair break, steadied midfield one off, challenged wide, ran on strongly.
Fair break, third last leaving back, slightly checked straight, found room and ran on very well, unlucky.
Not rushed from wide draw, midfield into straight, found room and ran on, not pace of first two.
Fast away, led rail but headed on outside, ran on early straight, led to 150m out no extra.
Ridden early, third and bustled, settled fourth, challenged two off, ran on, no kick.
Fair break, fourth one off, had to wait for gap in straight, ran on when clear but never dangerous.
Ridden out wide but could not reach lead, settled midfield three off, wide, no progress.
Never go pace from moderate start, improved wide, stayed on one pace.
Good break wide but massed ranks inside him, back to last and ridden, last leaving back, kept on past beaten horses.
Fair break wide but back to second last, tried to improve wide, no great impact.
Taken back from wide draw, found rail spot midfield, ridden before straight, kept on without threatening.
Good break, up with leaders but four wide, still wide into straight, ridden, weakened.
Ridden from gate to share lead one off rail, ridden early straight, weakened.
Missed break, losing two lengths, hard ridden to take midfield position rail, ridden, weakened quickly.
Given a waiting ride and placed towards the tail of the field, swung 3-wide for home, quickened up impressively down the outside and was well on top inside 100M.
Towards the rear on the inside, shaken up 500M, closed off the race willingly but just found one too good.
Disputed lead one off the fence, had every chance turning in but outpaced by the first two inside 100M.
In midfield 4Ls back, had to be nudged along rounding the home turn, ran on well to go 4th in late stages.
Positively ridden, vied for lead on the inside, kept on till weakening in late stages.
Stood flat-footed at the start and gave others a big start, rushed along to make up lost ground, 6Ls back in last approaching 400M, finished the race reasonably well considering the early hard run.

Made some use early to hold a position along the fence just behind leaders, not quickened when asked and kept on same pace to the line. (Jockey reported his saddle shifted at the entrance to the straight.)
Ridden vigorously to the front from a wide barrier, 4-wide on the turn, remained same pace till weakening 200M.

Not far off in early stages but under serious pressure to hold his position passing 700M, eased off by jockey entering the home straight, ridden again 200M and made minor late headway. (Unacceptable Performance / Jockey questioned.)
Positioned 3-wide in chasing group, crowded for room approaching 300M, no progress when clear.
Chased the pace early, checked 1000M and shuffled back, drive inside 400M but found disappointingly little in the finish, eased in closing stages when beaten.
Not mustered, dropped in behind midfield, outpaced making the home turn and faltered soon on straightening.
Broke awkwardly but lost no ground, joined leaders wide out, led after 400m, dictated pace, always in charge.
Taken back from wide draw, second last early, pulled out for run, finished fast on wide outside.
Held up near rear from wide draw, ran on through horses straight, finished well.
Good break, led two off early, then back to second, challenged straight but easily turned back by winner.
Fourth last early and urged along, ran on well straight in spite of traffic problems.
Slow away, up on rail to sit behind leaders, tried to challenge along rail, stayed on without threatening.
Good break, midfield one off, ridden early straight, ran on quite well.
Fair break, midfield one off, launched wide straight, some progress but never dangerous.
Away well, took good position in fourth on rail, slight check far side, ridden, found little.
Quickly away then back to sixth, ridden, stayed on one pace.
Air break, midfield one off far side, ridden early straight, no progress.
Well away but kept out wide by other runners, three wide home turn, ridden, weakened.
Lost half length start, ridden up to lead on rail, over galloping far side, ridden straight, weakened.
Fair break but lacked early pace, back to third last, ridden before home turn, found nothing.
Even getaway, positioned 3 wide in midfield with cover, never too far away in a compact field, 2Ls back turning, let down nicely from 300 M holding rivals well over the concluding stages.
Lobbed box seat 1 out 1 back behind speed, ready to strike on bend, angled out at 350 M and made a strong bid but found winner had more dash final furlong.
Lacked early speed as usual, pushed hard to catch up 4-5Ls off the pace, crept closer rounding bend and swung widest for home, ran on down centre of the straight, finished off soundly for 3rd.
Out in line, pressed on but unable to slot in, caught 4 wide without cover 2Ls off speed, worked into it turning and took over at 300 M, lost place last 50 M.
No early speed, ended up in rear division, only 3 to 4Ls back in compact field, had most of the field to beat turning and held up at 300 M, came through well when clear.
Bounced out to hold spot on leaders back, had run of race throughout, inside runs opened at 400 M and held up to 300 M, but lacked a turn of foot and just held ground final furlong.
Tardy into stride, ridden along for first part to tack onto field 4 to 5Ls down on circle, came wide and made some late progress without threatening.

Lost considerable ground at start, 5Ls off 2nd last horse early, did work but pace slackened mid-section so eventually tacked on, in traffic in straight and finished OK in circumstances. (See Racing Incidents.)
Away only fairly, raced 3Ls away on rails behind the bulk of the field, had something to offer but again never got a clear run in straight and was not fully tested.
Out with there, drove through to lead, set terms to suit, stacked field up to 900 M, folded cheaply under pressure final 300 M.
Fair to begin, unable to get nearer than 4 wide, did have cover 2 to 3Ls back, got closer under riding turning, weakened out final 300 M.
Showed some speed, couldn't cross and caught 5 wide without cover, did too much despite steady tempo, faded out late.
Urged along to share the lead 3-deep without cover, did work and got tired passing 300 M, soon dropped out.
Well enough away, went on to sit outside leader, had some attention from outside horses but pace to suit, niggled turning and gave on cheaply.
Soon crossed to the fence and raced keenly behind leaders, held up to 350M then picked up strongly up the inside rail to forge to the front in the final stride. Promising debut.
Raced at the hindquarters of leader, travelled strongly to straight, soon took over and shook clear passing 300M, galloped on well but was just caught in the final stride.
Held up along the fence in midfield, rallied well to go 3rd 200M from home.
Always within striking distance, pressed 450M from home, kept on well to the line but found no extra pace to challenge top two seriously.
Raced 3-wide and never far from the lead, ranged up to lodge a brief bid, battled on till weakening inside 150M.
Restrained to a rail position behind midfield, shifted out to challenge passing 500M but lacked a finishing kick.
Placed 2-wide towards the rear, stayed on final 300M but not getting to the leaders.
Awkwardly away, ended up in last about 8Ls off the pace, ran on fairly over final 400M but never got close enough to land a blow.
Dropped back to a rearward position, angled out from fence 450M for a clear passage, made very limited progress down the outside and was never any real threat.
Crossed to the lead from draw 12, set steady tempo to straight but found no extra when pressed on passing 350M, weakened.
Seasonal debut. Positioned behind midfield 6Ls back, driven 400M but made no progress.
With leaders early, dropped back to midfield approaching home turn, shifted out to improve nearing 500M but found very little in reserves, ran on empty final 150M.
Settled in midfield but was pushed widest making the home turn, not able to quicken and soon behind.
Never far off but was caught 3-wide throughout, found nothing when asked inside 400M, eased.
