Began only fairly, soon picked up coveted one-back spot on rails always within striking distance, came to challenge upon straightening, hit front easily passing 200 M, drew clear for a comfortable victory.
Amongst leaders, raced wide disputing 2nd most of way, remained same turning for home, failed to quicken to threaten winner throughout straight, hung on well to finish.
Made good use of low draw to soon take up running, held 1L advantage around the bend and into the straight, failed to answer winner's turn of foot inside final 200 M, pipped for 2nd at post.
No Comments on Running information for this horse.
Began with others, prominent early, shuffled back to worse than midfield around the Rock, renewed effort after straightening, fought on steadily without threatening.
Slightly slow out, travelled mainly in forward of midfield far side, similar turning for home, kept trying under pressure without quickening in straight.
Began well from the middle draw, close up and wide early stages, gradually drifted backward to midfield approaching home bend, similar turning in, ran home one-paced.
Slowly away, soon settled well behind, took closer order along rails around the bend, gained further ground turning in, briefly tightened over 200 M out, no further impression.
Chased leader amongst seconds into straight, folded up badly.

Showed good speed from the widest barrier, raced wide without cover with leaders early stages, gradually drifted backward to be 3Ls off the speed around the bend, wide into straight, no further impression afterwards.
Niggled along when in prominent position early briefly, soon dropped towards rear of field, one from last turning in, no further impression.
Began moderately from a wide gate, gradually settled in rear dropping to last approaching home bend, weakened further after straightening.
Was 3-wide early without cover before taking up 2nd position outside the leader approaching the 1200 M. Hit the lead approaching the furlong and was never headed to score a resounding win.
Managed to settle 1 out 1 back near the 1000 M. Closed off soundly.
Parked behind the leader on the rails. Had no excuses, battling away one paced over the latter stages.
Sent forward to lead along the rail. Kept on at the same pace for the majority of the home straight.
Rated behind midfield, 1 off with cover. Shifted wider on the home turn and made good late headway.
Began awkwardly settling midfield, 1 off with cover. Straightened up about 4 deep but was only one paced in the run to the line.
Parked 3 back on the fence. had every chance turning for home but failed to make any impression.
Settled at the rear of the field, 2-wide with cover. Came wide in the final stretch but found little over the concluding stages.
Traveled worse than midfield the fence. Railed up in the straight but only plugged to the line.
Was posted 3-wide without cover, midfield for the duration of the trip. Never likely.
From the outside barrier was taken back to a position at tail of the field. Struggled in the run home.
Settled with the backmakers, along the rail. Failed to close off and was disappointing.
Travelled 3-wide in leading section first turn. Cut to the fence and led from the Rock. Held a 1L advantage turning in. Always had enough to fend off rivals.
Soon led on fence. Took seat behind pace from the rock. Chased strongly in the straight but lacked the kick to reel in the leader. All out to resist the strong finishing 3rd at post.
2-wide at midfield before swinging out to challenge on straightening. 3Ls down at 300 M and responded well under pressure. Just missed 2nd by a narrow margin.

Well enough away but was caught wide. Gradually taken to race 2-wide towards rear first turn. Slotted 2-wide behind midfield from the Rock. Made some headway in the straight to make frame but not threatening.

Out nicely and sat 2-wide ahead of midfield. Forced to go 3-wide and without cover from 800 M. Went on to challenge the lead home turn. Couldn't sustain its effort 300 M out. Held ground closing stages.
Showed good early speed and raced 2-wide behind pace group from first turn. Every chance in the straight but just ran on steadily.
Quickly into stride on fence. Elected to race ahead of midfield first turn. Driven up to track the pace home turn. Failed to turn up a notch thereafter.
2-wide towards rear before making up some ground in the straight. Fair run.
Hard ridden early but was trapped wide and without cover in midfield. No progress in the straight.
Slow to begin. Shaken up to recover but was checked towards rear approaching 1000 M. Improved to midfield home turn. No extra gear in the straight.
Jumped well and opted to sit midfield but was checked towards rear approaching 1000 M. Never recovered.
Always at rear. No response despite the effort of rider home turn. Beaten before home straight.
Fair break but no early pace, ridden hard to reach second last place, made ground leaving back, driven straight, picked up and flew to win going away.
Broke well, tracked leader on rail in third, led 400 M out until winner swept past.
Well away but taken back to third last one off, ridden early straight, pulled out and ran on well out wide.
Taken back from outside draw, last early, kept on well between horses.
Fast out, led rail, kicked clear straight, no extra last 300 M.
Well away but caught wide first turn, back to fourth last, brought down centre of track, ridden, no real progress.
Fair break, midfield rail, ridden into straight, kept on along rail but no danger.
Fair break, tracked leaders one off in sixth, ridden exiting back, some progress, weakened.
Ridden from wide gate to take second entering back, tried to challenge home turn, weakened.
Fair break, ridden early, third three off first turn, sixth exiting back, nothing to give.
Lost half length at start, up to third one off, raced fourth far side, ridden, no progress, eased.
Fair break, not pace to challenge for lead, midfield far side, weakened straight, eased.
Fair start, back to third last, waited with, improved leaving back, challenged wide, finished fast, easily.
Hard ridden from wide out, but never reached rail and bustled the whole way, still stayed in well in mid-track, very good effort.
Quickly away, third on rail, then back to midfield, challenged on inside straight, ran on but no chance with winner.
Broke well, up on outside to fifth two off, kept on in middle of track, but never a danger.
Fair break, ridden early, midfield one off, fifth into straight, never able to challenge.
Fast away, led until 300 M out, headed, weakened.
Fair break, midfield one off, came wide, kept on but no kick.
Sluggish start, no early speed, second last far side, ridden between horses, no real improvement.
Fair break, some early pace, ridden straight, weakened.
Fair break but completely outpaced early, hard ridden and four lengths last after 400 M, some progress late but never near leaders.
Fast away, led early, headed, raced fourth on rail, ridden leaving back, weakened.
Moderate start, checked after 200 M, ridden, brought wide, no progress.

Eased at start to cross at rear, 8-1/2Ls off the leader, benefited by the fast pace, held up 300 M, closed the race off strongly when clear, hampered 50 M, finished short-head 2nd but was promoted to 1st.
Obtained the box seat, not suited by the fast pace, closed the race off strongly 300 M, hampered 50 M, finished close 3rd but was promoted to 2nd.

Behind midfield, 5-1/2Ls off the leader 2-wide, favoured by the fast tempo, switched 4-wide and improved at 500 M, kept hanging in 300 M, hampered other runners 50 M, first to cross the line but was demoted to 3rd.
Eased to sit in midfield, 4-1/2Ls off the leader along the fence, benefited by the fast pace, made good ground in straight along the slower part of the track.
Took rail in midfield, 4Ls off the leader 2-wide, helped by the fast pace, pushed back 400 M, lacked room 300 M, made minor ground in final stages.
Pushed early, 6-1/2Ls off the leader on the rails, favoured by the fast tempo, however held up whole straight, never really tested.
Eased to rear, 7-1/2Ls off the leader 3 to 4-wide, benefited by the fast pace, made steady ground 250 M.
Hard ridden to cross towards rail in front, 2-1/2Ls off the fast pace, flattened 200 M.
Settled in a more prominent spot, 2-1/2Ls off the fast pace 2-wide, flattened in straight.
Pushed to take the rail and led by 1L at fast early sectionals, hung on until 250 M out of fuel.
Eased back early, trapped 3-wide and no cover, then allowed to stride forward 1100 M, sat 2Ls off the leader, still wide and no cover, harmed by the fast pace, emptied 400 M.
Pushed to take a midfield spot, 4Ls off the leader 2 to 3-wide, suited by the fast pace, soon weakened 400 M.
Lost half length start, recovered to race fifth one off, brought wide to challenge straight, ran on strongly, just got up.
Broke well, took second just outside leader, challenged straight, ran on well, just caught.
Not rushed early, held up second last, improved on inside leaving back, ran on well.
Good break but no early speed, settled midfield on rail, made ground along rail into fourth home turn, challenged on inside, ran on until no extra last 50 M.
Fast away, led rail, swung wide entering straight, ran on but outpaced close home.
Lost length start, settled fifth last one off, ridden entering turn, progress but never threatened.
Steadied start and taken to rail fourth last one off, kept wide back straight, tried to circle field but no impression.
Broke well, joined leaders out wide, fourth two off first turn, raced wide back straight, ridden wide straight, no impression.
Good break, third on rail on settling, ridden early back straight, no progress.
Taken back to rail from start, last early, tried to make ground on inside straight, found little.
Moderate start, ridden up to midfield one off, drifted back through field exiting back, ridden, no response.
Moderate start but sixth on rail passing post first time, ridden before straight, weakened.
Settled last in the first half, made a bold 4-wide move approaching the home turn, put in a sustained effort to get up inside 100 M, cruised home.
Vied for lead in early and middle stages, took over and built up a 2Ls lead passing 600 M, galloped on soundly but was outpaced by the winner inside 100 M.
Settled 2-wide in mid-division, moved closer rounding the home turn, stuck on well down the inside.
Towards the rear in early stages, improved 3-wide from 700 M, kept on till weakening in closing stages.
Settled behind midfield 6Ls off the pace, checked near 400 M then taken to outside for a clear run, ran on well from off the pace.
Driven to a handy position just behind leading pair, pressed on approaching 400 M, kept on till finding no extra in late stages.
Towards the rear 8Ls back, patiently ridden, shifted out from fence 400 M out to commence his run, stayed on but never got close to the leaders.
Raced 3-wide throughout and never better than midfield, ran on one-paced turning in. Never a factor.
Settled in midfield along the fence, inconvenienced by beaten runner over the home turn and got shuffled back, made limited progress in straight.
Knuckled over at the start but soon recovered to race one back from leader, struggled to keep up rounding the home turn, soon beaten. (Jockey reported that his horse failed to run out the distance.)
Raced 3-wide without cover in the group chasing the pace, found nothing inside 350 M, eased 200 M when beaten.
Made use early to go forward, dueled for lead off the fence, outpaced from 600 M and dropped away tamely.

Gradually improved from the lowest draw to settle in a prominent spot mainly in 3rd, commenced move inside 300 M, asserted authority 100 M out, won convincingly.
Soon took up running, attempted to make all only to find winner too strong, outsprinted inside final 100 M.
Never far off, 3L 5th halfway out, kept on past fading front-runners.
Broke well, settled on stands rails about 3Ls off the speed in 4th, failed to quicken under pressure inside final 300 M.
Rear early, took closer order approaching course proper, fought on under pressure to the line.
Began with others, soon dropped to midfield, failed to quicken under pressure.
Settled just worse than midfield, plodded on.
Always well behind, kept on past well-beaten horses.
Gradually dropped to last few, made no impression throughout.
Began awkwardly losing ground, well behind before making short-lived effort approaching course proper, reverted to type as a back-marker over 300 M out.
Broke with others, soon dropped to the rear, trailed the field onto course proper, found nothing under pressure.
Travelled just off the lead to halfway, dropped out badly.
Never better than midfield, dropped away quickly inside final 300 M.
Hampered at start, race in last few down centre of the track, soon weakened under pressure passing 400 M mark.
Slowly away but speared forward from the widest alley to park outside the leader. Cruised to the front early in the straight and went to the line strongly without undue pressure, scoring an easy win.
Camped 3 back close to the rails. Eased out early in the home straight and finished off soundly to record an honest effort.
Had every chance after settling 1 out 1 back. Maintained an even gallop down the running.
Slow to begin travelling worse than midfield, 1 off with cover. Straightened up 5 wide and made late headway to finish in the frame.
Settled midfield, about 3 wide without cover. Maintained a satisfactory gallop right to the wire. (See incident report.)
Recovered after beginning awkwardly to box seat. Was inclined to show some inexperience at times and failed to show any dash at the business end of the race.
Fair Break, short of early pace, midfield one off, ridden early straight, kept on one pace.
Drifted back in the early stages to settle back in the field along the fence. worked home adequately in the final stretch.
Positioned towards the tail of the field 3 wide with cover. Came wide in the straight, plugged away over the final stages.
Settled in last position 2-3 wide with cover. Worked to the post fairly.
Sent forward to lead along the fence. Commenced to tire early in the straight. A veterinary inspection showed a substantial amount of blood in the horse's trachea.
Settled midfield, 3 wide with cover. Only plodded to the line. Vet reported that the horse had bled.
From a wide gate, was allowed to settle with the backmakers, 3 wide with cover. Failed to close off. (See incident report.)
Travelled midfield the fence. struggled in the home straight weakening noticeably.
Hard ridden early along the fence to occupy the prominent spot 1200M out. Ran on steadily top of home straight and came with a strong challenge passing 200M. Asserted authority final 50M.
Quickly into stride and rolled to sit one-off the fence behind the leader from 1200M. Chased strongly and looked possible to score final 150M until the winner made a sweeping run final stages.
Shaken up after start to lead on fence from 1300M. Held a 1L advantage turning in. Outrun by the front pair final 100M.
Raced within 2Ls of the pace in a 2-wide position through to home straight. Match strides with the front trio but lacked the kick to beat them.
Away in line. Eased to sit 2-wide behind midfield passing 1200M. Gradually moved to 5-wide and was 4Ls down rounding home turn. Made some headway without threatening the principals.
Began awkwardly. Driven to race 3-wide at midfield 1200M out. Commenced run and was 3Ls off approaching home straight. Looked dangerous at 300M but couldn't sustain effort final 150M.
2-wide towards rear despite the early effort. Swung widest and was 6Ls away on straightening. Covered minor ground thereafter.
3-wide without cover ahead of midfield until no extra final 300 M.
Slow to begin. Given reminder to chase the field along the fence and raced behind midfield from 1200M. Failed to quicken in the straight.
Fair break, midfield one off, mid track challenge, reached third place 200m out, no extra.
Jumped fairly and was gradually eased to rear on fence 1100M out. Same position into final stretch. Past beaten rivals home.
Travelled wide and without cover behind midfield before dropping out top of home straight.
Always at rear. Never in contention.
Taken back from wide draw, fourth last two off, driven in mid-track straight, got up last stride.
Broke well, led after 250m dictating pace, kicked straight and still two lengths clear 300m out, caught on the line.
Fast away, led narrowly 200m, back to third on rail, challenged between horses, just outpaced.
Lost half length start, lacked early pace, third last on rail, pulled wide for bid, ran on well.
Good break, ridden up on outside into second, driven straight, weakened late.
Quickly away, joined battle for lead, then back to fourth one off, hard ridden straight, weakened.
Fair break, midfield two off, urged far side and again early straight, kept on one pace.
Fair break but no early speed, back to last on rail, ridden for inside bid straight, stayed on without threatening.
Fair break, ridden hard early but not reach lead, three wide turn and straight, no progress.
Quickly away, led, headed and back to fifth, ridden along rail straight, no kick.
Moderate break, up to sixth one off, over-racing far side, ridden straight, weakened, slight interference 150m out when already beaten.
Taken back from wide draw, rear but still wide and no cover, over-raced, ridden straight, kept on but no real progress.
Moderate start, no early speed, back to second last one off, wide into straight, found little when asked.
Driven early but not go pace, midfield on rail, ridden, weakened steadily.
Fast away from out wide, ridden to take third one off, allowed front two to stretch clear, closed early straight, headed by third 200m out, fought back to win.
Fair break, ridden to take fifth one off, slight traffic problems, pulled out to challenge, led 100m out, winner fought back.
Well away but not hurried early, midfield two off going well, four wide into straight, led 150m out, weakened late.
Fair break, midfield one off, ridden home turn, stayed on well.
Stumbled just after start and jockey nearly dislodged, last early given time to recover, wide straight and ran on very well, unlucky.
Good break out wide, but taken back to second last one off, improved three wide turn, ran on quite well without threatening.
Fast away, up to second on rail, then settled fifth, hard ridden straight, no further progress.
Sluggish start, interference far side, back to rear group, improved turn, no run early straight, ridden, ran on quite well.
Missed break, third last early, took check exiting back, no run early straight, kept on well on rail.
Good start, led after 200m, soon headed on outside, raced second four lengths in front of third, led early straight, swamped, weakened.
Fair break but not pace to lead, settled rail midfield, ridden straight, found little.
Fair break, hard ridden from wide gate to lead by three lengths after 400m, led to straight, headed, weakened.
Lost half length start, back to midfield four wide, ridden before straight, weakened.
Moderate break, midfield three wide, met interference twice far side, wide into straight, weakened, tailed off.
Pushed forward and settled just behind the leaders 3 wide, benefited by the slow tempo, led 300M and dominated onwards.
Eased to sit in midfield, 2.5Ls off the leader 3 wide, checked 800M, not suited by the slow tempo, dashed well 300M and grabbed 2nd.
Eased back, 4Ls off the leader, trapped 4 wide, harmed by the slow tempo, dashed strongly 300M, run ended 100M and held 3rd.
Eased to rear, 5Ls off the leader, trapped 4 wide throughout, dashed strongly 200M despite not suited by the slow pace.
Pushed early to keep up in midfield, 4Ls off the leader 2 wide, harmed by the slow pace, blocked 4-2, dashed strongly when clear.
Eased to rear, 5Ls off the leader 3 wide, harmed by the slow pace, held up 400M, dashed well when clear.
Pushed forward and sat outside the lead, enjoyed the slow sectionals, ran on until 200M flattened.
Hard ridden to take the rail and led by 0.5L at fairly slow sectionals, weakened quickly 400M.
Hard ridden early, 2.5Ls off the leader 2 wide, not suited by the slow tempo, no dash, flattened 200M.
Hard ridden to gain the box seat, out of fuel 300M.
In front of midfield, 2.5Ls off the leader along the fence, not suited by the slow pace, weakened 300M.
Trapped 4 wide without cover throughout in front, not suited by the slow tempo, faded quickly in straight.
Settled in front 3 wide, suited by the slow tempo, soon dropped off 300M.
Eased back, never competitive and tailed out.
Very fast away, ridden to lead after 150m, headed and tucked in behind leader, pulled out to challenge mid-straight, led 50m out.
Fast away, led after 200m, kicked clear early straight, looked winner until fading last 100m.
Not rushed early from wide gate, fourth last entering turn, brought wide straight, finished well but not reach front pair.
Good break, sixth one off, ran on but never pace to challenge.
Fair break, settled midfield two off, brought wide and outpaced mid straight, ran on late.
Fair break, ridden early, up to third one off back straight, second into straight, ridden, weakened.
Moderate start, mid to rear far side, ridden and ran on between horses straight, never pace to trouble leaders.
Taken back from wide draw, third last one off, ran on quite well past beaten horses.
Fair break but not involved in lead battle, tried to run on wide, closed slightly without threatening.
Well away but short of early pace, midfield rail, made some ground along rail straight until run flattened out last 250m.
Fair break but not go early pace, rear division on rail, no run available briefly straight, gap came, stayed on one pace.
Fair break, midfield wide, up to fourth on outside at home turn, ridden, weakened.
Fair break but short of early pace, last early, shaken up entering straight, no progress.
Missed a beat at start, third on rail, ridden, weakened.
Settled off the rail in midfield, briefly held up in early straight but came through a gap to hit the lead near 100M, found enough to hold on in late stages without being asked for a maximum effort.
Switched off to rear, 7Ls down making the final turn, switched wide approaching the top of the straight, finished off the race strongly and was closing on the winner with every stride.
Travelled 3-wide in mid-division, responded well despite being keenly throughout, briefly led inside 150M, fought on but turned flat in late stages.
Never far off in 4th, picked up gradually passing 400M and battled well to the line.
Set even pace at the front end, kept on well in early straight, headed nearing 150M and found no extra.
Dropped back after the start and raced 5Ls behind the pace, ran on from off the pace but couldnt get close to the leaders.
Restrained in midfield under a strong hold, held up till 200M, made minor headway when clear.
Raced one out one back from leader but lacked the necessary response when the race got serious, gradually weakened half way up the straight.
Proved difficult to settle, positioned ahead of midfield but was kept wide without cover throughout, not quickened when urged 400M and finished off the race at the same pace.
Close up stalking the pace on the inside, kept on same pace till weakening inside 200M.
In last pair about 6Ls off the pace, swung 3-wide for home, found very little when pressed and dropped out tamely in closing stages.
Towards the rear, made no progress on straightening and was well behind inside 200M. (Bled.)
Broke well, up to fourth one wide, strong run to lead 150m out, kept on well.
Fast away, two lengths clear after 200m, led until challenged by winner 250m out, fought well but just outpaced.
Taken back from wide draw, third last two wide, ran on well out wide but never got in blow at first two.
Well away but not fast into stride, loped along fourth last early, shaken up straight, picked up and finished very well.
Slow away, second last on rail, brought wide, finished fast.
Good break but not pace to lead, up to second, challenged turn but not get past leader, weakened late.
Out well, but back to midfield three wide, ridden, kept on one pace.
Well away, fourth on rail after 400m, sixth into straight, ridden, no real progress.
Fair break, midfield one off after 300m, sixth into straight, ridden, no progress.
Slow away, back to last from wide draw, last into straight, ran on past beaten horses.
Midfield, ridden straight, no extra and eased last 100m.
Broke well, third on rail exiting back, ridden early straight.
Ridden from gate to hold rail position but not pace to do so, back to third last on rail, driven but continued to lose ground, tailed off, eased.
Began well, had ideal trail behind pace 2Ls or so away on rails, spent nothing in run, took gap passing 200 M, accelerated strongly under hands and heels to socre.
Out in line, unable to slot in, posted 4 to 5 wide outside speed, did plenty of work in mid-section, joined in at 250 M, still in front until inside 100 M. Solid run.
Showed good speed, up challenging on pace but 3 wide without cover, joined leader turning and took front at 250 M, run ended inside 150 M, battled bravely.
Standard jump, raced behind midfield 5 to 6Ls back, saved ground on bend, improved turning but in traffic at 250 M, clear 200 M and did best work late to make frame. (See Racing Incidents.)
Taken back from a wide alley, raced just off midfield 5Ls back to bend, improved turning, made a little late progress but no real threat.
Began in line, took a sit just behind decent speed, 1 to 2Ls back to bend, run appeared at 350 M but didn't quicken and just held ground in straight.
Well enough away, ended up in midfield 3 wide with cover, even trip but tightened at 600 M, just ran on steadily in straight.
No early pace, drifted back to rear 6 to 7Ls back, pace suited, plenty to do on turning, worked home soundly through pack to be closest on line.
Broke nicely, up challenging for front, caught in speed battle racing outside leader, took over turning and lead to 250 M, folded after a hard run.
Poor getaway, mustered into a midfield position 4Ls off pace, had chance with decent pace on, loomed at 350 M but unable to go on with it final 200 M. (Blood in trachea.)
Out in line, posted 3 and 4 wide behind midfield with cover, 5Ls down on bend, came widest and closed to 200 M before run ended.
Faded back to rear from widest gate, 2Ls down off strong tempo, never really travelling over shorter journey, didn't find much.
Began OK, 4 wide with cover in mid-division, 3 to 4Ls down to bend, didn't respond on straightening and condition gave out late.
Bounced out, led easily, challenged for front by wall of horses, worked hard to bend, niggled turning and faded right out.

Gradually crossed from a wide gate to settle in midfield, saved good ground on rails turning in, briefly baulked about 250 M out, quickened to hit front over 100 M out.
Began awkwardly, settled in last few, went widest turning in, finished off race strongly down centre of track.
Settled in forward of midfield, improved to hold every chance early in straight but unable to sustain effort inside final 100 M.
Jostled at the start, settled well behind, saved ground turning in, baulked early on before obtaining a clear run passing 200 M, produced some late impression.
Settled just worse than midfield, went widest into straight, ran on steadily to be nearest at finish.
Niggled along before settling wide without cover in a prominent spot, travelled a 2L 4th far side, similar turning in, ran home one paced.
Settled in rear of midfield, came under pressure around the bend, failed to quicken under pressure.
Soon dropped to the rear, trailed the others most of way, ran past well beaten horses close to home.
Showed early speed, gradually taken back to trail leader within 2Ls of pace, similar turning for home, folded up quickly from over 200 M out. (Questioned for disappointing performance.)
Settled in midfield, found nothing under pressure in the run home.
Showed early speed from the widest barrier to cross to front, held narrow lead to 200 M, dropped away quickly under pressure.
Travelled outside leader to straight, weakened noticeably from over 200 M out.
Enjoyed the box seat position. Railed up turning for home and was never headed after hitting the lead approaching the furlong.
Wasn't the best to begin but showed good speed to park midfield, 2 deep with cover. Travelled nicely in the run and in the straight closed off strongly.
Shared front running duties along the fence. Pinched a break entering the final bend, but was collared over the concluding stages.
Always niggled throughout the mid section to maintain a midfield spot along the rail. Didn't show much dash after the 400 M, but commenced to work home well once properly balanced in the straight.
Was taken across behind runners from the outside gate to travel behind midfield, 1 off with cover. Made steady ground down the running.
Taken back from a wide alley and settled with the backmakers, 2-wide with cover. Closed off soundly.
Was part of the front running duo, 1 off. Lead by a narrow margin at times, maintained a fair gallop in the home straight.
Travelled at the rear of the field, 3-wide with cover. Came wide in the straight but only plugged to the line.
Worked forward to race prominently, but was posted 3-wide without cover. Drifted back on the final circle, never likely.
Began poorly, settling with the rear division along the fence. Failed to find any extra in the run home.
Began awkwardly settling midfield, 3-wide with cover. Made no impression in the final stretch.
Settled 1 out 1 back. Kept to the inside in the home straight but only struggled.
Soon in front rank. Settled 2-wide ahead of midfield approaching wining post first time. Worked to chase the runaway leader down the Rock. Hit front 250 M. Kept on to score with some comfort.
2-wide behind midfield before commencing run down the Rock. Hard ridden and was 4Ls down passing 400 M. Finished off soundly but couldn't catch the winner.

Ahead of midfield on fence through to back straight second time. Under pressure to track the eventual winner down the Rock and was 3L off turning into home. Every chance in the straight but only ran on steadily.

Began fairly. Caught wide first turn before sitting outside the pace. Took fence behind the runaway leader stable bend. Moved closer passing 500 M and reached the back of the speed turning in. One-paced to conclude.
2-wide at rear until making run outside home turn. Swung widest and was 7Ls adrift on straightening. Made up decent late ground.
Began slowly and was then driven to race behind midfield on fence from high draw. Trapped in the same position when other runners quickened rounding home turn. Closed off fairly.
Slow to begin and stayed towards rear on fence. Made run 2-wide passing 500 M and was 5Ls back entering home straight. Couldn't turn up a notch thereafter.
3-wide ahead of midfield early. Raced keenly and switched out to go forward approaching winning post first time. Opened up a 7Ls gap back straight. Caught 250 M and weakened final 100 M.
Travelled 3-wide behind midfield. Checked at 400 M and steadied at 100 M but never looked dangerous.
Urged forward outside the field first turn and led on fence before staying ahead of midfield passing winning post first time. Failed to quicken when the race got serious passing 500 M.
Travelled wide and without cover at midfield throughout. Beaten before home straight.
Well enough away and gradually eased to sit 2-wide towards rear. Never recovered and finished tailed out.
Fast away, led after 150 M, two lengths clear exiting back, kicked clear early straight, ran on well.
Broke well settled third on rail, tried to challenge straight, not quite reach leader.
Fair break, unhurried early, back to third last, ridden and ran on very well between horses straight.
Ridden along from wide gate, up to fourth exiting back, hard ridden straight, not pace to reach leaders.
Fair break, ridden up wide to second one off, kept on in straight until weakening late.
Sluggish start, bustled up to midfield on rail, not settling immediately, pumped along in straight, ran on quite well.
Lost ground at start, two lengths last early, improved on outside exiting back ran on wide, finished quite well.
Hard ridden from gate but not reach lead, settled fifth on rail, over galloping briefly, driven straight, no progress.
Moderate break, then stumbled after 50 M, back to second last, shaken up in straight, made late ground inside.
Fair break, not great early pace, took two checks far side, may have got on heels, kept on one pace straight.
Good break but lacked early pace, back to midfield rail, bustled exiting back, no kick straight.
Fair break but reined back sharply soon after start, fourth last one off, found little straight.
Well away from wide gate but three wide first turn, led back straight and went clear by four, breather leaving back, kicked clear early straight, gone beyond recall.
Fast away but not rushed, settled rail midfield, wide to challenge straight, ran on well but winner long gone.
Fair break but lacked early pace, back to last rail, made ground inside turn, not get in blow at winner.
Fair break but lacked early speed, back to fourth last rail, not immediately settling, made good ground inside on turn, hit flat spot, then kept on well.
Good break but not quite hold place among leaders, took bump entering first turn, settled midfield, ridden, no real kick.
Well away, up on outside to fourth one off no cover, wide into straight, kept on but no impact.
Fast out on wide outside, led and crossed entering back straight, back to second and settled, ridden straight but not quicken with winner, weakened.
Fair break, ridden up on rail into fifth, restrained going well, pulled out to challenge straight, found little.
Fair break, not join battle for lead, took slight bump first turn, fourth last, urged leaving back, came wide, driven, little response.
Missed half a beat leaving stalls, never with leaders, settled near rear, ridden before straight, one pace.
Level break but no early speed, restrained, shaken up straight, little response.
Away well, led on rail until headed, settled third one off, ridden, gradually lost ground, tailed off.
Hard ridden forward, sat 1L off the good pace 2-wide, dominated 200 M and stormed home with good time.
Pushed to take the rails and led by 1L at good pace, hung on until 200 M overhauled, ran on strongly for 2nd.
Pushed to keep up with the front runners, 3Ls off the good pace 2-wide, ran on well to the line for 3rd.
Hard ridden to obtain the box seat, just ran on fairly in last quarter.
Eased to sit in midfield, 4-1/2Ls off the good pace 2-wide, just held ground in straight.
Settled in front of midfield, 3Ls off the good pace 2-wide, ran on until 150 M flattened.
Pushed early but failed to take box seat, 3Ls behind the good pace on the rails, weakened 250 M.
Hard ridden early, 5-1/2Ls off the good pace on the rails, no turn of foot over this trip.
Very slow away, behind midfield along the fence, never better than that.
At rear, 6-1/2Ls off the good pace 2-wide, no progress.
Eased to rear, never a factor.
Steadied start and taken back to rear on rail, began to make ground on rail leaving back, gaps opened as field fanned out, finished powerfully.
Moderate start, then ridden up to second fighting for his head, settled third, ridden straight and ran on well without being able to match winner's kick.
Out well, settled sixth on rail over racing slightly, ridden turn, kept on well in straight.
Fair break, taken back to last one off, improved on rail in straight, ran on well.
Fast break, led, tried to steady pace, kicked in straight and clear until weakened 200 M out.
Out fast, fifth but three wide with traffic problems first turn, up to second one off, tried to keep on in mid-track, gradually faded.
No rush early, taken back to third last on rail, fighting for head a little, settled, then made ground inside until one pace mid-track straight.
Moderate start, seventh one off on settling, shaken up straight, found little.
Well away, up to third two off, fourth back straight, driven in mid-track straight, no real progress.
Fair break but back to last one off and restrained, not much impression straight.
Fair break but stuck out wide, still two off far side, ridden wide straight, found nothing.
Fair break, ridden up wide but not make lead, five wide first turn, three wide back straight, found nothing in straight, tailed off.
Reserved off the pace, 3-wide turning for home, quickened well passing 300 M, kept on powerfully to win comfortably.
Chased pace then loomed up alongside leader over the home turn, soon led on straightening, kept on strongly and just found the winner too good.
Settled well in midfield 3-wide, strongly challenged inside 300 M, stuck on well.
Sat one back from leader after leading early on, had every chance turning in, ran on but never looked like getting there.
Broke well then restrained to midfield along the fence, kept to inside on straightening but couldn't find extra pace to challenge.
Not far off but was 3 to 4-wide throughout, ran on one paced final 300 M.
Soon driven to the lead from a wide barrier but not able to cross until the end of back straight, gradually weakened on straightening.
One off the fence in midfield, had to be shaken up approaching 400 M, found little.
Taken back on jumping, with last few 5Ls off the pace, made very limited progress turning in.
Fractious in stalls then awkwardly away, settled towards the rear off the rail, driven 350 M but didn't respond to riding.
Kept very wide early then taken back to the rear, swung 3-wide for home, made no progress on straightening.

Gear: Comments on Running is not available for this race.

Quickly ridden from a wide barrier to cross to lead virtually making all, held on well to finish.
Began well, settled just off the speed and well within striking distance in 4th, took time to gather momentum after straightening, flew home late.

Began with others, niggled along to muster early speed, settled outside leader approaching home bend, came under pressure to challenge over 200 M out holding some chance, unable to sustain effort closing stages.
Failed to muster speed early, raced wide in midfield before taking closer order when without cover around the bend, gained close-up joint 3rd turning in, unable to sustain effort after straightening.
Settled in rear of midfield, ran wide into straight, made minor progress early on, kept on for remote 5th.
Travelled in forward of midfield, came under pressure when in similar position turning for home, found nothing under pressure.
Ridden along from towards rear on rails to reach midfield before home bend, hampered and lost about 1L making the bend, found nothing under pressure in the run home.
Raced wide in rear of midfield, remained wide in similar position throughout, made no impression in straight.
Gradually improved to be 2L 3rd before home bend, in similar position turning in but soon folded up quickly after straightening.
Very sluggish at start, remained well behind to straight, plodded on past well-beaten horses in the run home.
Towards the rear, kept on one pace without quickening in straight.
Began with others, soon dropped to tail-end, made no show thereafter.
Broke well to travel better than midfield, slightly worse turning into home straight, dropped away quickly after straightening.
Began slowly, travelled wide towards the rear, made no impression in the run home.
Shared leading duties, 1 off. Hit the front approaching the final furlong and was never headed.
Travelled handy in the run, 3 wide without cover. Was checked near the near the home turn but recovered and finished off well.
Drifted back early from the outside gate, then made a concerted effort to rally forward to settle about 3 back the fence. peeled out into clear running early in the straight and ran on soundly.
Began very poorly settling at the rear 2-3 wide some distance off the field. Commenced to make ground in the middle stages and worked home nicely through the field.
Settled behind midfield, 3 wide with cover. Made steady ground in the final stretch.
Settled along the rails in the leading pair. Was overhauled near the 200m, gave ground soon after.
Ridden along from barrier rise but failed to muster speed, settling 3 wide no cover, midfield. Closed off fairly.
Camped 1 out 1 back. Had every chance but failed to capitalize, giving ground in the run to the post.
Tracked the leader along the fence. Commenced to fade inside the furlong.
Settled towards the tail of the field, 2-3 wide with cover. Failed to close off.
Travelled 2 deep, midfield with cover. Was never really in contention, finishing well back.
Settled with the backmakers, 1 off with cover. Struggled in the run home.
Travelled wide in front rank before parked outside the leader passing 800M. Fought for lead in the straight and prevailed near the post.
Broke well and strode forward. Took seat behind leaders home turn. Ideal spot to strike entering home straight. Chased hard but was fended off by the winner.
Soon led on fence. Joined by the eventual winner passing 800M. Battled gamely to hold lead in the straight until outsprinted by the front pair closing stages.
3-wide at midfield and shifted 5-wide to challenge on straightening. Ran on steadily for a non-threatening 4th.
Hard ridden early to stay 2-wide behind midfield. Improved to midfield turning in. One-paced to conclude.
Eased to rear from high draw after start. Raced 4-wide with last few from 700M. Covered minor ground in the straight until no extra final 100M.
Caught wide and without cover all along and was never better than midfield.
Niggled to maintain prominent spot through to home straight. Found nothing thereafter.
Slow to begin and was shaken to hold fence at midfield. Dropped towards rear despite effort of rider rounding home turn. Beat tired runners late.
Failed to muster despite early effort and raced towards rear. No real progress in the straight.
Fair start and was taken towards rear. Never likely.
Stumbled at start. Urged to resume but was trapped 4-wide without cover ahead of midfield home turn. Raced wide with leaders turning into home. Dropped out 300M.
Soon in leading section. Dropped towards rear gradually despite effort of rider home turn. Struggled home.
3-wide behind midfield early. Some progress outside approaching home straight before faded 400M.
Fair break, up to third on rail, restrained, pocketed briefly in straight, gap came just in time, finished strongly to lead near line.
Fair break, up to fifth one off, urged just before turn and again early straight, good response and got first run on winner, led 200m out, just caught.
Up to midfield one off, took time to hit stride in straight, then finished very well down middle of track.
Well away, led after 200m and went two lengths clear, steadied in front, led to 200m out, kept on.
Fair break, ridden early, settled midfield, settled midfield on rail, kept on well straight, but not pace to challenge.
Fair break, lacked early pace, back to second last one off, slightly short of room turn, finished well out wide.
Fast break, restrained early, third last one off, blocked for run twice in straight, finished well.
Bustled along from even break but still back to rear three wide, stayed on mid-course in straight but never dangerous.
Fast away, shared lead early, back to second one off, ridden turn, gradually weakened.
Moderate start, not rushed early, near rear, tried to make ground on rail straight, no progress.
Fair break but could never get near rail, three or four wide the whole way, kept on past beaten horses.
Lost length at start, midfield one off, shaken up home turn, no progress.
Taken back from wide gate, last early, ridden early straight, found little.
Fast away, not pace to lead, fourth two off at turn, shaken up, found nothing.
Ridden from outside gate to take forward position rail, steadied midfield, pulled out to challenge mid track, ran on strongly to lead then hold off second.
Unhurried early, found midfield position then improved sharply three wide, ran on very strongly mid-track, just failed.
Out well, led one off then settled third on rail, pumped along and slightly short of room mid-straight, ran on well.
Broke well but caught wide, moved up fast to lead, headed exiting back, fought back to lead but caught and swallowed up late.
Taken back from wide draw to sit second last on rail, began to improve wide home turn, ran on well without being able to trouble leaders.
Fair break, taken back to seek and find rail, began to improve wide home turn, ran on well without being able to trouble leaders.
Fair break, midfield one off, bustled along exiting back, shaken up straight, kept on but never a danger.
Slowly away driven along rail, pulled back off heels 200m, midfield thereafter then lost places far side, launched wide, ran on until flattened out late.
Well away, third one off, fourth exiting back, hard ridden, weakened late.
Out fast, circled field to lead first turn, tried to steady pace but quickly headed, raced second until went on again leaving back, ridden straight, faded.
Fair break, back from wide draw to third last, tried to make ground on rail, already beaten when short of room late.
Taken back to look for position from wide, last early, tried to improve on rail, couple of smacks, found nothing at all, eased.
Settled in midfield, 4Ls off the leaders, enjoyed the rail trip and favoured by the fast pace, progressed steadily 400M to score.
Settled in box seat, not suited by the fast sectionals, closed the race off strongly for 2nd.
Shared the lead along the fence at fast sectionals, hung on strongly until 200M overhauled, ran on for 3rd despite being pressured in early stages.
Very slow away, at back, 6.5Ls off the leaders 2 wide, benefited by the fast pace, progressed steadily in straight without real threats.
Very slow away, at back, 7.5Ls off the leaders 3 wide, helped by the fast tempo, held up 400M, made steady ground when clear.
Midfield on the fence, benefited by the fast pace, switched to 4-5 wide 800M and progressed around the field, just ran on ok in straight.
Hard ridden to obtain a midfield spot, 4Ls behind the fast pace, trapped 3-4 wide throughout, flattened 300M.
Hard ridden early but not muster, 5Ls off the leaders 2 wide, suited by the fast pace, flattened 200M.
Midfield, 5Ls off the leaders 2-3 wide, favoured by the fast tempo, blocked and checked 400M, no progress when clear.
Hard ridden to share the lead 2 wide at fast sectionals, bumped 400M, dropped off afterwards.
Hard ridden forward, 2.5Ls off the leaders 2-3 wide, harmed by the fast pace, faded 400M.
Eased back, never a factor.
Hard ridden to keep up in midfield, dropped off rapidly 400 M.
Never competitive and tailed out.
Out fast on wide outside, led one off, kept on straight, never in danger once third mastered.
No early pace, second last and wide, still wide into straight, looking for better ground, flew down outside late, passing all except winner.
Fair break, up to second on rail, ridden to challenge leader, kept on once headed.
Broke well, then midfield two off, brought wide for better ground, stayed on but never threatened.
Good break, up to fifth on rail one off, hung towards rail straight, kept on but no threat.
Well away, midfield one off and urged, kept on well after escaping from pocket halfway up straight.
Fair break but not go early pace, rear division until improved well on better ground down centre, slight interference mid-straight.
Fair break, held rail in fifth, ridden before straight, gradually weakened.
No rush from wide draw, back to last, kept wide to look for better ground, then moved to rail, tried to improve between horses, kept on.
Ridden to join pace from wide draw, settled third, ridden before straight, weakened.
Fair break, midfield one off, ridden turning in, weakened quickly late.
Hard ridden early in attempt to keep place, ridden again entering straight, no progress, unable to handle wet track.
Fair break, held up four from rear, ridden, no response, eased when became unbalanced on surface.
Tracked leader, acted on this rain soaked track and soon found his stride, in front 150M and kept on gamely.
Led at a reasonable pace given the underfoot conditions, responded well entering into straight and kept grinding away to the line.
Placed midfield, chased the winner for 300M in straight then faded away.
Never far off in 3rd, not quickened inside 400M, kept on same pace to the finish.
Held up in last 6-7Ls off the pace, had big task in hand turning in, ran past a couple beaten runners only and never factored.
5Ls behind leader in 6th, could not pick up on this soft ground, never a factor.
4Ls back in 5th, pushed along inside 500 but made no progress, eased. (Jockey said horse didn't handle the track conditions.)
Out well from wide gate, moved through field comfortably to take position behind leaders, led mid-straight, ran on very well.
Out fast, up to third two off, ran on well straight but winner much too good in prevailing conditions.
Even break, held rail in third or fourth, kept on under pressure straight but never threatened front two.
Not hurried early, took rail in second last, made ground and kept on well on straight in spite of being checked 300m out.
Well away, ridden up to sit on leader's shoulder, led narrowly and briefly entering straight, then swamped.
Out very fast, three clear after 200m, steadied and joined, headed early straight, kept on gamely but no chance with the mid-runners.
Fair break, midfield five wide, deliberately kept to centre on better ground, ran on but never got to leaders.
Good break out wide, mid pack entering straight, boxed on but never got in a blow.
Fair break, midfield one off, tried to quicken turn, no progress.
Well away stayed wide, pumped along entering straight, no progress.
Fair break, seventh three off rail into straight, ridden, weakened.
Ridden to join leaders from fair break, scrubbed along early straight, no response, eased.
Level break, soon dropped back to last although ridden, soon adrift.
Midfield after 400m, slipped back to second last into straight, floundered.

Broke well from the middle draw, soon taken back to stalk leaders throughout far side, came to challenge under pressure upon straightening, snatched victory in the shadows of the post.
Began fairly, well there throughout, hit front under pressure inside 200 M only to be piped at post.
Travelled just worse than midfield on the rails, saved ground turning in, fought on under pressure without threatening.
Attempted to make all from the one draw, unable to sustain effort and headed inside final 200 M.
Soon dropped behind midfield after beginning from a wide draw, commenced move to reach midfield around the bend, sustained progress to the line to be nearest at finish.
Very slowly away, soon picked up to travel one from last down far side and around the bend, saved ground turning in, fought on under pressure without threatening.
Remained wide throughout in midfield far side after beginning from the widest gate, lost position around the bend but picked up some late ground under pressure near finish.
Never far off in better than midfield position, gradually faded under pressure in the run home.
Raced wide without cover in prominent position far side, widest runner turning for home, never recovered.
Soon improved to first few, weakened under pressure in straight.
Lacked pace and failed to muster under pressure at any stage, remained well back throughout.
Began with others, niggled along before badly blundered and lost position approaching home bend, never recovered.
Tracked the leading pair on the paint. Shot to the front 100 M out and won easily.
From an awkward alley went forward and vied for leading duties. Increased its margin on the field to be outright leader along the rail near the 500 M. Stayed on well.
Camped behind the speed 1 off with cover. Peeled five wide on rounding the final bend, maintained a good gallop right to the finish.
Was 3 back the fence by the time the field had reached the 600 M. Inclined to travel on the bridle, kept to the inside in the run to the line, finishing soundly to make the frame.
Raced handy to the leaders but travelled 3-wide without cover for most of the circle. Maintained a fair gallop to the wire.
Settled midfield, 1 off with cover. Failed to make any impression over the latter stages.
Raced behind midfield along the paint. Fenced up in the home straight, was one paced in the straight. (Collapsed after the post.)
Settled towards the tail of the field, 2-wide with cover. Pushed along after the 500 M, kept on evenly in the run to the finish.
Did a bit of work early to race prominently 3-wide no cover. Coursed 2 deep after the 600 M, faded in the run to the post.
Raced with the backmakers, 1 off with cover. Was well beaten in the home straight.
Travelled at the rear of the field on the fence. Struggled in the final stretch.
Slowly away settling in last position along the rail. Failed to pass another runner.

Caught 3-wide without cover before slotting 2-wide ahead of midfield from stable bend. Lacked clear run top of home straight but hit front promptly when a gap opened 100 M. Kept on to repel rivals at finish.
Urged early and stayed on fence at midfield through to home straight. Finished off well inside but couldn't resist the late drive of the winner.

Bumped at start and was shaken up early to race 2-wide at midfield. Moved away from the fence gradually whilst making up ground home straight. Dashed well final 50 M through a tight run to nearly snatch 2nd.

Trapped 4-wide behind midfield before striding forward from 1300 M. Travelled 3-wide without cover with leaders 800 M out. Hard ridden 400 M and stayed in the battle until no extra gear to threaten the front trio closing stages.
Jumped well but not quick enough to lead. Settled box-seat from first turn. Angled out to challenge turning in but was one-paced to conclude.
Soon eased towards rear on fence. 7Ls down on straightening Covered substantial ground thereafter and was nearest at finish.
Raced 2 to 3-wide behind midfield before home straight. 5Ls away at 300 M and picked up well thereafter to make good headway.
2-wide towards rear through to home straight. 6Ls adrift at 300 M. Did the best work late to make considerable progress.
2-wide behind pace before moved up to challenge the lead home turn. Looked threatening passing 200 M but couldn't turn up a notch final stages.
Soon led on fence. Levelled home turn. Hung on until 150 M.
Always at rear. Never a factor.
Niggled along early but failed to muster. Stayed behind midfield before brief improvement down the Rock. No extra home straight and weakened 150 M.
Prominently placed just behind the leader, on heels at 500 M, clicked into gear final 250 M, fought bravely under maximum pressure, hit front in the final stride.
Broke well, soon occupied a fence position 2Ls off the pace, shifted out and joined the leader rounding bend at 600 M, hit front at 250 M, kept on well under maximum pressure, just caught on line.
Knuckled at start, soon ran up to lead and found the fence passing the 600 M pole, headed in near 200 M but did keep on well for a place.
Pushed hard to hold a fence position in the mid-division, took time to pick up early in the home straight, finished off satisfactorily final 200 M, just late for a place.
Crowded start, taken back from gate 9 and travelled 4Ls off the pace on rails, crowded again at 600 M, made gradual ground along the inner final 250 M but never threatened the principals.
Broke well, soon drifted back to the mid-division despite being urged along, finished off fairly well under pressure in the home straight.
Lacked early speed as usual, settled one-off with cover 4Ls off the speed, responded only fairly when asked for efforts final 200 M, rather one-paced.
Crowded at start, lacked early speed and soon settled at the rear, only gave limited response when asked for efforts in the home straight, never troubled the principals.

Bumped at start, caught wide and proved difficult to settle in the early stages, checked at 900 M, drifted back towards the rear rounding the home bend, made up some ground final 200 M. (Mucus, roar.)
Lacked early speed and travelled one from the rear, swung widest for home, failed to make up any ground in the straight.
Bumped at start, sat 2Ls behind the leader, caught 3-wide with no cover, struggled from the home turn, failed to keep up passing the 200 M pole, soon faded.
Travelled 3Ls behind the pace, caught wide throughout the trip, got tired at the top of home straight, finished tailed out.
Raced handily on the rails, travelled nicely throughout, responded well when asked for efforts at the top of home straight, hit front 100 M out, kept on soundly to win.
Awkwardly started and soon settled 5Ls off the pace on rails, crept closer rounding the bend, kicked final 200 M under maximum pressure, ran on soundly for 2nd.
Widely drawn, driven to get across in front and led on the rails, left contested from 700 M, quickened well when asked at 300 M, headed at 100 M, kept on for a place.
Niggled along to hold a fence position in the midfield, responded fairly well when asked for efforts at the top of home straight, bit too one-paced, just missed a place.
Urged along early and soon occupied a one-off spot just behind the speed, swung widest for home, made gradual ground 300 M out, but could not find extra to challenge the principal final 100 M.
Crowded at start and soon settled behind horses, patiently ridden until turning for home, only made limited progress down centre of the straight.
Missed the start and lost substantial ground, gradually caught up 7Ls off the speed, made gradual progress final 250 M without threatening the principals.
Travelled about 3Ls behind the pace, caught 3-wide with no cover, held ground until outpaced passing the 200 M pole, soon faded.
Urged along early to hold a one-off spot just behind the mid-division, on heels at 1400 M, only one-paced in the home straight.
Pushed forward to get across from his widest alley and soon sat 2Ls behind the leader, started struggling rounding the home turn, soon weakened and dropped out.
Raced handy but caught 3-wide early, strode forward at 1200 M, failed to match the strides of leader at home turn, got tired at the top of straight, gave ground.
Taken rearward, proved difficult to settle in the early stages, caught wide and travelled ungenerously throughout, failed to finish off the race.
Eased to take the box seat, enjoyed the rail trip and benefited by the track that strongly favoured front runners, closed the race off well to win by a narrow margin.
Pushed early to gain a midfield rail spot, 4-1/2Ls off the leader, dashed strongly 300 M despite not suited by the track that strongly favoured front runners, just beaten by a head in 2nd.
Pushed to obtain a midfield spot along the fence, 3Ls off the leader, not suited by the track that strongly favoured front runners, dashed well 200 M and grabbed 3rd.
Pushed forward to take rail and led by 1L, benefited by the rail run and the track that strongly favoured front runners, overhauled 200 M, ran on ok.
Eased to rear and took rail, 6-1/2Ls off the leader, dashed strongly 250 M despite not suited by the track that strongly favoured front runners, lacked room 50 M.
Bumped start, settled 1L off the leader 2-wide, benefited by the track that strongly favoured front runners, however flattened 200 M.
Eased back, 5Ls off the leader 2 to 3-wide, not suited by the track that strongly favoured front runners, checked 400 M, no turn of foot.
Eased to rear, 6-1/2Ls off the leader 2 to 3-wide, not suited by the track that strongly favoured front runners, checked 400 M, no progress.
Behind midfield and trapped 3-wide throughout, 4-1/2Ls off the leader, not suited by the track that strongly favoured front runners, emptied 400 M.
Eased to sit 2-1/2Ls off the leader, trapped 3-wide throughout and lost too much ground, weakened 400 M.
Bumped start, 2-1/2Ls off the leader 2-wide, dropped off 500 M. (Bled.)
Hard ridden throughout but failed to keep up with the field, trapped 4-wide at back throughout and lost significant amount of ground at bends, dropped off 400 M.
Awkwardly drawn, given a waiting ride and settled 4 to 5Ls off the pace, swung widest for home, kicked impressively down centre of home straight, hit front 100 M out, drew clear with plenty in tank.
Lacked early speed despite being urged along, ended up travelling one-off in the mid-division, responded well when asked for efforts final 250 M, ran on strongly for 2nd.
Lacked early speed as usual, travelled one from the rear on the rails, dashed well under pressure final 300 M, finished off soundly for 3rd.
Travelled 3-wide in the mid-division, ran on steadily when asked for efforts final 350 M, could not find extra to challenge the principals in the concluding stages.
Urged along to share the lead on 2-deep, kept on fairly well until passed at 150 M, only one-paced under pressure.
Pushed hard forward to share the lead on rails, laid in and caused interference at the top of home straight, headed at 150 M, remained one-paced under maximum pressure.
Prominently placed on rails early but pulled very hard in the middle stages, shifted away from the fence at 900 M and joined the lead on 4-deep with no cover, kept on until flattened at 150 M.
Driven early and ended up travelling 2-wide in the mid-division, niggled along rounding the bend, only one-paced in the straight.
Niggled along to take the fence position just behind the leader, badly checked at the top of home straight, never recovered.
Broke well, prominently placed on rails within striking distance from the leader, badly checked when quickening at the top of home straight, never recovered.
Taken back from the widest alley, failed to make up any ground when urged along at home turn, never a factor. (Heart irregularity.)
Slow away, soon caught up with the pace group but trapped 3-wide with no cover, struggled turning for home, weakened sharply 300 M out, finished tailed out.
Placed 2-wide ahead of midfield, picked up smartly inside 300 M and swooped past the runner-up in closing stages.
Broke smartly and travelled well in the slipstream of pacesetter, got through a narrow gap 250 M, kept on strongly and was just caught close home.
Off the fence and never far off in 5th, attempted an inside run on straightening but the gap closed near 250 M, ran on again in late stages to claim 3rd.
Tracked leaders 2-wide, kept on to the line but lacked extra pace to challenge seriously.
Raced keenly in early stages then tucked in behind midfield 4 to 5Ls off the pace, driven nearing 400 M, ran on.
Positioned 2-wide in mid-division, shaken up passing 400 M, stayed on without threatening.
Raced 3-wide in midfield early, strode to the front entering the back straight, kept on till no extra 150 M.
Went forward but not able to bag the rail until making the home turn, headed inside 250 M, gradually weakened.
Swiftly crossed to a midfield position off the rail from draw 12, ran on one-paced turning in and was crowded for room in late stages.

Slow to begin, ended up towards the rear 6 to 7Ls off leaders, switched to 3-wide making the home turn, driven 350 M but found little. (Jockey reported his saddle shifted during the race placing him at a disadvantage.)
Taken back after the jump, towards the rear 7Ls back, switched to outside on straightening but made no progress.
In last throughout, never in the hunt.
