Began well and soon took up running, held narrow advantage upon straightening, always holding runner-up at bay closing stages.
Soon settled one back in 3rd on rails despite the wide draw, held similar position turning in, fought on under pressure but found winner too good.
Settled about 3Ls off the speed, similar turning for home, fought on well to grab distant 3rd close to home.
Broke well to settle outside leader, remained similar turning for home, gradually faded close to home.
Towards rear, fought on steadily down inner without threatening.
Niggled along 3Ls off the speed, kept on same pace to the line.
No Comments on Running information for this horse.
Settled in midfield, ran home one-paced.
Began with others, gradually drifted back from the widest barrier to travel well back, saved ground around home bend and turning in, kept on steadily at the same pace without threatening.
Behind midfield far side, ran wide into straight, made no further impression.
Soon picked up to midfield, similar turning in, found nothing under pressure.
Midfield far side, yielded ground from home bend, tailed-off halfway out.
Tracked the leading division close to the rail with cover. Peeled out rounding the final bend and fought on strongly to hold the advantage.
Parked behind midfield the fence. kept to the inside in the straight and finished off gamely.
Positioned worse than midfield, 2 wide with cover. Came widest over the final stages and ran on well.
Raced back in the event, 2 wide with cover. Closed off soundly.
Travelled with the backmakers 2 wide with cover. Made good late headway in the final stretch.
Settled at the rear 3-4 wide with cover. Saved ground on the home turn and ran to the line evenly.
Sent forward easily to cross and lead along the paint. Set an even tempo but was collared near the 150m.
Tracked the leader early along the fence before shifting out to travel 1 off after the 800m. Gave ground over the concluding stages.
Travelled in front of midfield, 2-3 wide with cover. Came under pressure near the 700m, failed to respond and was disappointing, finishing well back.
Raced behind the speed 2 wide, was then carted 3 deep without cover after the 800m. Was swamped near the furlong and faded quickly soon after.
Raced midfield the fence. Improved position early in the straight but gave out on its run well before the line.
Raced back in the field, 2 wide with cover. Failed to figure at any stage.
Positioned close to midfield 3 wide with cover. Struggled in the home straight. (To trial.)
Worked had and scouted wide in the early in and middle stages to obtain a forward position but was posted 3 then 4 wide without cover after the 800m. Never likely. (To trial.)
2-wide at rear. Swung widest on straightening and was 3Ls back at 400M. Kept making up ground steadily to catch the leader close home.
Held the rail in leading section throughout. Caught final stages but hung on for 2nd well.

3-wide behind midfield early. Commenced run but was forced wide approaching 600M. 2Ls away at 400M. Rallied on with the winner to chase the leader but no extra to challenge the front pair closing stages.
Midfield on fence early. Moved to prominent spot home turn. Plugged on to make frame without threat to the front trio.
3-wide towards rear before charging to take closer order 600M out. 4-wide 3Ls off rounding home turn. Ran on well and had every chance until peaked final furlong.
Began well but was caught widest. Gradually taken to sit 2 to 3-wide at midfield before home turn. Made up minor ground home.
2-wide behind midfield through to home straight. Got traffic problem thereafter and ran on steadily when clear.
Soon taken to fence at rear after start. Urged along the paint to race midfield approaching home turn. Failed to quicken when asked home straight.
Shaken up early and sat outside the pace through to final stretch. Emptied inside 300M and faded.
2-wide ahead of midfield. Dropped out 300M.
Towards rear early. Given reminder at 600M but no response. Beaten before home straight.
Away in line but was trapped wide. Strode forward and raced in front rank without cover from 1400M. Soon weakened after straightening and finished tailed out.
Taken back from wide draw to fourth last one off, eager entering back straight, improved wide home turn, ran on strongly to lead 100m out.
Taken back from fair break, fifth last on rail, finished well between horses to snatch second late.
Lost a little ground start, taken back, last and three wide far side, improved wide, ran on well late.
Fair break, ridden early to midfield one off, bustled early straight, kept on.
Good break, up to fifth one off, improved three wide into straight, led 400m out, swallowed up.
Fair break, midfield one off, scrubbed along entering straight, kept on wide.
Well away, rail far side, pumped along straight, kept on one pace.
Fair break but taken back, third last on rail, kept on along rail straight, checked late, but never threatened.
Fair start, sought and found the rail midfield, one off exiting back, tried to improve wide, weakened late.
Fair break but no early pace, rear early bustled along, still last halfway up straight until passed beaten horses late.
Good break, up to lead rail, headed back straight, second leaving back, ridden, weakened.
Fast away out wide, led briefly the third one off, urged, third into straight, weakened.
Fair break, not rushed early, midfield one off, ridden, no progress.
Fair break, driven early but not pace to lead until went on far side, two lengths clear exiting back, weakened, eased when beaten.
Moderate break, midfield one off, brought wide straight, ran on strongly to lead 100m out.
Well away, midfield rail, pulled out to find nice gap, led 300m out until caught last 50m.
Well away out wide, taken back to fourth last, reined exiting back, improved turn, ran on strongly late.
Fair break, midfield two off, improved wide, not quite pace to challenge.
Fast away, took second on rail, ridden and every chance early straight, no kick.
Well away, led, then third one off, ridden, no extra.
Not fast away, sixth one off, driven straight, found little.
Fluffed start, last early on rail, improved looking for gaps straight, kept on without ever really threatening.
Lost half length start, mid to rear on rail, shaken up straight and some progress, no real kick.
Poor start, third last one off, improved wide on turn, run flattened straight.
Good break, fifth on rail but not settling immediately, tried to improve rail straight, no acceleration.
Taken back from wide, last and pulling slightly early, tried to challenge wide, no kick.
Good break, up to lead, swamped straight.
Well away, wide fifth early, up to second wide turn, weakened quickly, eased.
Eased back, settled well 7.5Ls off the leader 2 wide, benefited by the fast tempo, progressed steadily 300M, dominated 100M, not fully extended.
Pushed to take the rail and led by 0.5L at fast early sectionals, drifted away rest of the field 400M, hung on strongly until 150M overhauled, ran on for 2nd.
Eased to rear, more than 10Ls off the leader 2-4 wide, favoured by the fast pace, progressed steadily 250M to grab 3rd.
Eased to sit in front of midfield, 4.5Ls off the leader 2 wide, benefited by the fast pace, made ground 300M without threatening.
Eased to sit in midfield on the rails, 5.5Ls off the leader, suited by the fast pace, held up 4-2, made some ground when clear.
Eased to sit in front of midfield, 4.5Ls off the leader along the fence, helped by the fast tempo, just held ground in straight.
Eased to rear, 10Ls off the leader 2 wide, benefited by the fast pace, blocked 4-2, made steady ground when clear.
Eased to sit in midfield, 6Ls off the leader 3-4 wide, favoured by the fast pace, however lacked turn of foot, just held ground in straight.
At back, 8.5Ls off the leader 3-4 wide, suited by the fast tempo, just ran on fairly.
Hard ridden early but failed to muster, 7.5Ls off the leader, trapped 4-5 wide throughout and lost too much ground, no progress in final stages.
Hard ridden to keep up with the front runners, 3Ls off the fast pace 2 wide, held up 400M, checked 250M, no progress.
Hard ridden to occupy the box seat, not suited by the fast pace, emptied 300M.
Pushed forward, 1.5Ls off the leader 2 wide, not suited by the fast tempo, soon weakened 400M.
Hard ridden forward to pressure the leader 2 wide, harmed by the fast pace, faded 400M, checked 250M.

Broke satisfactorily, soon settled in a fence position in midfield, shifted out for clear run at the top of straight, dashed well under maximum pressure final 250 M, hit the front in final few strides.
Settled cosily in a one-off spot in the mid-division, travelled nicely throughout the trip, ran on soundly 350 M out, briefly led passing the 200 M pole, headed by the winner in the last few strides.
Awkwardly drawn, taken back and soon obtained cover just behind the mid-division, swung widest for home, responded when asked for efforts final 400 M, finished off soundly for 3rd.
Easily ran up to get across and settled just behind the pace, bumped at 400 M, ran on well final 350 M and looked possible to win, lacked a decisive kick final 100 M, just missed a place.

Prominently placed just off the speed, proved difficult to settle in the middle stages, held up for clear run early in home straight, crowded at 200 M, finished off satisfactorily final 150 M. (Sustained cut to both hinds.)
Slow to begin, lacked early speed despite being urged along and ended up settling in a rearward position, took time to pick up early in home straight, finished off satisfactorily final 200 M.
Bumped start, taken to a fence position just behind midfield, dipped at 1500 M, crowded at 1300 M, only one-paced when asked for efforts final 350 M.
Bumped start, taken rearward from gate 14, patiently ridden until the home turn, made ground steadily down centre of the straight 300 M, never really troubled the principals.
Broke fast from gate 10 but soon taken to the midfield to obtain cover, lacked a kick when asked for efforts in the home straight, very one-paced. (Lost left front plate.)
Settled in a fence position near the rear, blocked early in home straight, failed to make up any ground when clear final 250 M.
Driven to hold a fence position 4-5Ls behind the speed, not properly clear in home straight, on heels at 150 M, not full tested.
Started awkwardly form gate 12, urged along to lead and found the fence near 1000 M, kept on under pressure until got tired passing the 200 M pole, soon faded.
Jumped well, tracked leader early, kept on until flattened at 250 M, soon weakened sharply.
Lacked early speed despite being urged along, always rearward, never in contention.
Soon in front took them along at a strong pace, shook off rivals to open a clear lead 200M, never challenged and won in class record time.
Broke well and positioned in midfield off the fence, rallied well up the inside to go 2nd 50M from home but could make no impression on the runaway winner.
Pressed leader, had every chance in straight but no match with the winner, kept on to final 100M and tired late.
Settled off leading trio, had a good trail throughout, maintained momentum to final 100M then lacked a further bid.
Hard driven out the gate but was steadied in traffic near 1000M, shuffled back to 9th position, ran on final 300M without threatening.
Slowly away, raced at the tail of the field along the inside, ran on only fairly inside 300M and was not threatening at any stage.
Reserved off the pace, 6Ls down turning in, swung out in straight for a clear path but found disappointingly little in the finish.
Tucked in behind midfield but finished off the race rather one paced. No impression.
Hard ridden early to maintain a 3-wide position ahead of midfield, kept on one paced then faded inside 200M.
Rushed to a 3-wide position at the front, tired and weakened rapidly inside 200M.
In last pair 6Ls off the pace and could make no impression on straightening.
In chasing group 2-wide, driven 350M but no response, dropped out.
Caught 3-wide without cover in midfield early, crept closer rounding the bend, responded when asked for efforts final 350 M, hit the front 100 M out, hung in, just prevailed.

Urged along to occupy a fence position in midfield, travelled nicely throughout, quickened well when asked for efforts final 350 M, on heels at 100 M, kept on strongly, just late. (Objection overruled.)
Driven to hold a one-off spot in midfield, launched a strong challenge down centre of the home straight 300 M out, ran on soundly, lacked a decisive kick to beat the top two final 80 M.
Lacked early speed and travelled 7Ls off the pace on 3-deep, crept closer rounding the bend, made up gradual ground down centre of straight final 350 M, no extra near the line.
Lacked early speed and travelled 8Ls off the speed, took time to obtain clear run at the top of home straight, picked up late at 200 M, finished off soundly under maximum pressure, too late.
Taken rearward from gate 11, swung widest for home, ran on satisfactorily under pressure final 350 M, but never threatened the principals.
Given a waiting ride and settled just behind the mid-division on rails, responded fairly when asked for efforts final 400 M, made up some ground but rather one-paced.
Widely drawn, driven to lead and soon found the fence near 1100 M, left uncontested and looked very promising throughout, kept on only fairly under pressure final 250 M, headed at 100 M, flattened.
Settled 7Ls behind the leader on rails, only made limited progress when placed under pressure final 300 M.
Settled cosily just behind the leader, travelled satisfactorily until weakened at 200 M.
Taken back from gate 12 and travelled 10Ls off the pace, held up for room early in home straight, dashed strongly when clear at 200 M, blocked again at 100 M, not fully tested.
Started awkwardly, settled 7Ls off the pace, never better than midfield, outpaced at 300 M.
Pushed hard forward and soon settled one-off 3Ls behind the pace, failed to hold his position passing the 400 M pole, soon weakened sharply.
Prominently placed 2-3Ls behind the leader on rails, proved difficult to settle in the early stages, checked at 1200 M, gave no response when asked at the top of home straight, soon weakened.
Bounced out, ended up behind leaders 3Ls down on settling, used little in run and travelled strongly to bend, gained a split at 300 M and sprinted quickly, driven away to win easily.
Reasonable jump, positioned behind lead group 4Ls off top end, had an easy time to bend, shifted out passing 300 M, chased gamely but no match for winner.
Away fairly, just behind midfield 5Ls or so, soft run in middle stages, kept to inside and closed gradually for a distant 3rd.
Began well enough, angled across into midfield 4 to 5Ls back in running line, close enough on turning, didn't dash but closed evenly to make frame.
Settled just behind speed 4Ls from lead, enjoyed a cosy trail to bend, improved and loomed briefly at 300 M, didn't see out trip.
No early pace, ended up back with last few, 7 to 8Ls off top end in middle stages, saved ground on circle, closed best of rest and was nearest on line despite traffic at 200 M.
Began OK but did some early work to end up outside leader from outside draw, even trip thereafter, niggled turning, flat final 300 M.
Out in line, assumed a midfield position 6Ls back, fair run to turn, responded fairly to riding but peaked inside 300 M.
Faded back to last 10Ls from lead, on rails throughout with field to beat turning, only managed to pass tired runners in straight.
Lacked pace as usual, shared rear 9 to 10Ls from leaders, plenty to do turning, didn't show usual finish and plugged away in straight.
Ended up in rear division best part of 8Ls off lead, well back to turn, didn't produce a finish and struggled in straight.
Began well, led but eventually let outside horse take over, came 2 wide on circle to sit out leaders girth, not far away turning for home, didn't find much and folded tamely.
Showed speed to eventually work to lead, held a 1/2L advantage thereafter, challenged turning in and quickly gave in, dropped right out.
Allowed to dictate the pace, surged clear passing 400M, collared by the runner up inside 200M but dug in to prevail in game fashion.
Settled off the pace in the 3 path, moved up alongside leader and challenged strongly inside 250M, couldn't quite get past the winner but ran a creditable race in defeat.
Raced in mid-pack along the fence, angled out inside 450M for a clear path, kept on but offered little threat to the first two which drew well clear.
Tucked in behind mid-division, switched 3-wide turning for home, kept on but couldn't get to the leaders.
Behind midfield, not suited by the tempo and proved difficult to settle in middle stages, mild rally final 300M.
Placed 3-wide in midfield, inclined to lay out over the home turn and couldnt step up a gear leaving the bend. One-paced throughout.
Switched off the back and made a 3-wide turn for home, made limited from off the pace and didn't factor.

Raced keenly behind leaders, couldn't pick up on straightening and faded over the concluding stages. (Jockey reported that his horse with blinkers on for the first time would not settle due to the tempo of the race.)
Broke well and raced prominently at the hindquarters of leader, outpaced from 300M and weakened rapidly in late stages.
Well covered in midfield, kept on same paced to line, never threatened.
Fractious in stalls then slowly away, ended up towards the rear 5-6Ls off the pace, switched widest to challenge but made no progress, dropped out.
Reserved off the pace as expected but found disappointingly little in the finish, eased.
Tracked leader, dropped out quickly ion straightening.
Detached in last after a slow start and never in contention.

Began slowly, soon crossed for rails run behind, waited with, ran home strongly to snatch victory in the shadows of the post.
Settled in prominent one-out-one-back spot, held same turning in, hit front over 100 M out only to be piped at post. Jockey said horse resented whip when questioned for his riding out his mount.
Soon taken across from the widest barrier to settle at the back, baulked behind runners after straightening, switched out for a clear run over 200 M out, finished off race well.
Soon took up running after beginning from wide-ish draw attempting to make all, swamped inside final 200 M.
Began from a wide draw, travelled just worse than midfield, fought on steadily to be nearest at finish without threatening.
Soon taken back to race in rear of field, remained same turning in, produced good late impression down centre of straight.
Began moderately, travelled on rails in midfield, saved ground turning in, unable to sustain run after straightening.
Began with others, settled 3-wide just better than midfield in 5th, made short-lived effort when widest around the bend, found nothing from 3Ls 4th into straight.
Settled just worse than midfield, saved ground on rails turning in reaching midfield 200 M out, made no further impression closing stages.
Began with others, settled in midfield, made no impression in straight.
Began well, settled just off the speed on rails, dropped out tamely from 2Ls 3rd entering straight.
Raced 3-wide without cover just off the speed sharing 2nd, yielded from around home bend.

Covered ground midfield then pushed forward to make a line of 3 in the leading division near the 800 M, no cover. Managed to save ground by slotting into the 1 off line after the 600 M. Let down strongly for a convincing win.
Settled 3 back the fence. Peeled out to make its run early in the straight, battled on gamely.
Slow to begin then travelled 3-wide with cover until about the 600 M. Thereafter was carted wider and when under pressure in the straight was inclined to lay in. Worked home soundly.
Stalked the leader along the rail. Had every chance but peaked on its run 100 M out.
Camped behind midfield the fence. Made some late headway over the final stages.
Raced midfield, 1 off with cover. Shifted out and obtained a trail 3 deep on the circle. Maintained a steady gallop to the finish.
Settled at the tail of the field close to the rail. Made fair ground along the inside in the run to the line.
Settled near the backmakers, 1 off with cover. Swung wide on the corner but failed to make any impression.
Raced 1 out 1 back for most of the trip. Peeled out to travel 3-wide without cover from about the 500 M. Never fired in the home straight.
Settled at the rear of the field, never really travelled and failed to be competitive, finishing well back. (See Racing Incidents.)
Began awkwardly then proved difficult to settle in the early stages whilst leading along the fence. Faded quickly in the home stretch.
Travelled outside the leader in 2nd position. Was a beaten horse near the 600 M, tailing out in the straight. (To trial.)
Raced 3Ls behind the pace in a 3-wide position through to home straight. Chased strongly passing 250 M to cut down rivals in final stages.
Jumped smoothly and stayed on fence at midfield first turn. Attempted to shift out for running but was blocked until 200 M. Dashed well once into clear but the winner had enough to hold on at finish.

Away in line and was trapped 4-wide behind the pace group first turn. Rolled forward to eventually sit one-off behind the pace home turn. Fought on well but couldn't resist the finishing effort of the top pair close home.
Taken to race 2-wide towards rear from high draw after start. Swung wide and was 6Ls down on straightening. Covered substantial ground to make frame at finish.
Began well but elected to sit 2-wide behind the pace group until the home straight. Every chance but lacked extra gear to stay in the battle for top three inside 100 M. Lost 4th at finish.

Hard ridden early from wide draw and was trapped 3-wide in the leading section first turn. Urged back straight to lead on fence approaching home turn. Hung on until no extra to fend off the principals final 150 M.
Quickly into stride. Took prominent spot first turn. Ended up midfield on fence home turn when runners improved outside. Under pressure in the straight but remained one-paced.
Always behind midfield. Never nearer.
Pressed early and took lead near the fence first turn. Eased to box-seat near 600 M. Failed to turn up a notch home straight.
Always at rear. No real progress final stretch.
Soon taken to rear from high draw after start. Never recovered.
Raced wide and greenly behind midfield. Never a factor.
Well away, up wide to take fifth one off, made ground three wide home turn, drive, got up close home.
Well away out wide, led and crossed first turn, booted clear early straight, just worn down near finish.
Fair break, slight bump early, third last one off, began to improve turn, stayed on well centre.
Good break but slightly cramped early, settled midfield rail, ran on straight until flattened out late.
Fast away, led until headed on outside, raced second place, chased eventual runner up straight, weakened late.
Bobbled start, taken back to last one off, pulled wide straight, ran on well.
Slightly awkward break, back to rail second last, short of room turn, ran on well between horses.
Fair break, rousted early, raced third one off, asked to quicken straight, no response.
Even break, raced midfield one off, shaken up early straight, rolled, found nothing.
Slow start then squeezed back, tried to improve home turn, no progress.
Fair break, shared early lead rail, headed first turn, fourth on rail, ridden straight, found nothing.
Broke well but no great hurry early, tracked leader box seat, slightly short of room early straight, gap came, ran on powerfully.
Fair break, taken back to last on rail, struck to rail throughout, gaps came, ran on well, winner too strong.
Level break, rail midfield, going well home turn, shaken up then checked, ran on well late.
Sluggish start, back to fourth last one off, short of room far side, ran on well under driving straight.
Fast out, led early then caught three wide, back to fourth one off, urged out of back straight, almost joined leader, weakened late.
Well away, up wide for share of lead but five wide first turn, up to second one off, led early straight, swallowed up.
Sluggish early, reined back sharply after 150 M, held up last, asked to improve wide on turn, stayed on but no impression.
Missed break and lost length, toward rear three wide no cover, ridden wide straight, passed beaten horses.
Fair break, one off behind squabbling leaders, midfield back straight checked and near rear early straight, plodded on.
Fair break, up to join leaders wide, then midfield wide, ridden, weakened.
Broke well, bustled early, led one off, headed, back to midfield, ridden, found little.
Moderate start, ridden early, up to share lead wide, led and tried to settle in front, headed, weakened, eased.
Eased back, 5-1/2Ls off the leader 2-wide, dashed impressively 200 M to win despite not suited by the slow pace.
Pushed to obtain a more prominent spot in front of midfield, 3Ls off the leader 2-wide, not suited by the slow tempo, dashed well 200 M to grab 2nd.
Settled in front, enjoyed the slow early sectionals, ran on well to the line for 3rd.
Eased back, 5-1/2Ls off the leader along the fence, harmed by the slow pace, dashed strongly 250 M.
Pushed early but failed to muster, then eased back to sit 5Ls off the leader, trapped 3-wide throughout, dashed well 300 M despite not suited by the slow pace.
Pushed to take the rail and led by 1-1/2Ls at advantageous slow sectionals, hung on well until 150 M flattened.
Eased to rear, 7Ls off the leader, trapped 3-wide throughout and lost ground, harmed by the slow pace, little dash 300 M.
Settled in box seat, benefited by the slow tempo, weakened 150 M.
Pushed forward, 2Ls off the leader, trapped 3-wide throughout, not suited by the slow pace, ran on until 150 M flattened.
Pushed early, 4-1/2Ls off the leader 2-wide, harmed by the slow tempo, just held ground in straight.
Pushed to obtain a midfield spot on the fence, 3-1/2Ls off the leader, not suited by the slow pace, flattened 200 M.
Midfield, trapped 3-wide, harmed by the slow pace, emptied 300 M.
Sharp break from out wide, good work by jockey to get him into position only three wide at turn, challenged 250 M out, led, ran on strongly.
Well away and up to lead on rail, held narrow lead until went on home turn, ran on well but not cope with winner.
Put head down and lost ground start, last early, made ground on rail exiting back, not much room but good finish between horses to snatch third on line.
Lost length start, bustled up behind leading group, ran on between horses straight without ever quite threatening leaders, caught for third close home.
Well away, settled fourth rail, challenged but not get on terms straight, no extra.
Fair break, back to third last one off, pumped along straight, ran on well.
Fair break, up to share lead two off, horses got up inside, shaken up straight, found little.
Fair break, midfield then back to second last three wide, driven, kept on wide.
Out well, taken back, midfield three wide no cover, ridden wide straight, no progress.
Shaken up after fair start to share early lead three wide, lost ground home turn, ridden, weakened.
Good break but not pace to retain lead, back on rail to midfield, urged, no progress, eased late.
Moderate start, no early pace, three lengths last into straight, ridden but no progress.
Placed towards the rear and confidently ridden, had plenty to do turning in but quickened up well once a gap opened up 200 M, made rapid headway in latter part of straight and got up before the line.
Never far off the pace in 4th, bid 3-wide into home straight, picked up well to hit lead 100 M from the line but had no answer to winner's late surge.
Placed 2-wide in mid-division, driven passing 400 M, finished off the race evenly and briefly looked a winning chance before the winner swept past in last 100 M.
Unhurried in early and middle stages and positioned at the tail, switched to outside midway on the turn, ran on steadily to go 4th close home.
Ahead of midfield early, moved up to track leader 2-wide passing 1100 M, rallied to take over inside 250 M, had every chance but weakened over final 100 M.
Caught wide for 500 M then tucked in behind midfield for cover, angled out into clear 250 M, stayed on without threatening.
Gradually crossed to the lead, collared in early straight then weakened under pressure passing 200 M.
Never better than midfield, travelled 3-wide to home straight and left without cover from 900 M, driven approaching 300 M but lacked a further response.
Positioned in midfield off the inside rail, failed to mount a serious challenge turning in, no extra closing stages.
Driven to the front after the start, sat in handy 3rd entering the back stretch, not picked up in straight and weakened rapidly inside 100 M.
Towards the rear 7Ls off leader, circled 3-wide while launching his bid on the final turn, gave way passing 250 M.

Placing: PU
Comment: Pushed for early lead, blundered near 1300 M, pulled up. (Lame / retired after race.)

Began from a wide barrier, used early to take up running before home bend, held clear advantage turning in, hung on well to win unchallenged. (Questioned for improved performance.)
Settled in 5th just better than midfield, similar turning in, produced a steady late run inside final 200 M to be nearest at finish.
Began moderately, soon ridden for pace, settled just better than midfield, 4th on rails within 3Ls of speed around the bend, kept on same pace under pressure.
Began with others, settled wide in last few, no clear passage until 300 M early in straight, finished off race well.
Began with others, settled just off the speed on rails, pulled to 2-wide 2nd onto home bend, found nothing in the run home.
Began fairly, raced one-out-on-back far side, received a bump coming out and taken slightly wider and back to 2L 3rd rounding home bend, failed to quicken under pressure in the run home.
Settled 3-wide in midfield, kept on same pace under pressure.
Niggled at early to gradually pick up to midfield along rails, remained similar turning in, fought on steadily in straight without threatening.
Soon taken well behind and crossed for rails, improved to rear of midfield before home bend, plugged on under pressure in straight.
Settled in last few, saved a lot of ground turning for home, never nearer.
Settled in midfield, shifted wider into straight, found nil in the run home.
Began slowly, soon picked up to just worse than midfield, went wide home turn, shifted ground under pressure in straight, made no impression.
Settled towards rear and wide, went wider turning for home, found nothing down centre of straight.
Began from the widest barrier, raced wide without cover in midfield down far side, gave ground quickly from around the bend.
Raced close to the lead towards the middle of the course. Hit the front at the furlong and won convincingly.
Made his run from close to midfield. Angled out after the 300m to race closer to the grandstand side, finished off nicely.
Raced handy to the leaders about 3 off the outside rail. Kept on gamely over the concluding stages.
Began awkwardly but recovered to track the leader along the outer rail. Whacked away well to finish in the frame.

Shot forward to lead along the grandstand side. Commenced to hang in early in the race and drifted off the rail in the middle stages. Proved somewhat difficult to ride out and was checked near the post.
Prominently positioned about 5 off the outside rail. Stayed on well.
Slow to begin then ridden along to settle midfield upsides the outer rail. Kept up an even gallop over the latter stages.
Settled towards the middle of the track behind midfield. Maintained its gallop right to the wire.
Travelled towards the centre of the course close to midfield. Kept on at the same speed in the run to the line.
Settled back in the event towards the middle of the field. One paced over the final stages.
Began a little awkwardly settling with the backmakers towards the outside rail. Failed to accelerate at the business end of the race.
Blundered at the start, settling behind midfield along the grandstand side. Never really got into the race.
Hung out whilst racing towards the tail of the field. Only plodded to the line.
Struggled throughout the race to stay in touch with the field, travelling behind midfield. Finished tailed out. (To trial.)
Raced 4-wide at midfield before driven to sit one-off behind the pace home turn. Rallied on to challenge the lead in the straight and dominated final 100M.
Quickly into stride. Elected to sit 2-wide ahead of midfield from 800M. Well positioned to strike in the straight. Closed off well without troubling the winner.
Jumped fairly but soon urged to race at midfield on fence. Swung 3-wide and was 3Ls down into final stretch. Progressed steadily but no real threat to the front pair. Just held 3rd at post.
Caught wide after standard jump. Gradually taken to 4-wide at rear. Took inside run and was 6Ls off leaving the bend. Finished off satisfactorily until bumped 50M.
Began well but was trapped wide. Crossed to fence and led home turn. Headed passing 200M and weakened final stages.
Prominent spot through to home straight. Just held ground thereafter.

Bounded in the air at start and lost ground. Restrained to stay 2-wide toward rear from 1000M. Under pressure passing 500M and made up minor ground before peaked 100M. (Substantial amount of blood in horse's trachea.)
Never better than midfield on fence. No progress home straight.
Travelled wide and without cover at midfield and moved up to race outside the pace group turning in. No extra final furlong.
Trapped wide after moderate start. Gradually dropped to rear but was still wide and without cover. Never likely.
Hard ridden early but didn't muster. Stayed 3-wide towards rear before dropping out top of home straight.
2-wide behind midfield early and middle stages. Found nothing in the straight. (Bled.)
Well away, found rail midfield and clung to it, challenged between horses straight, ran on strongly to lead last 50m.
Broke well, unhurried early, settled midfield one off, fifth last into straight, wide challenge, ran on well, just failed.
Broke well, sat midfield one off, challenged wide, led 400m out until last 100m.
Well away, not much early speed, mid to rear on rail, went for run between horses straight, long wait for gap, then ran on well, unlucky.
Well away, up two wide to take sixth, ridden mid-track straight, not pace to challenge.
Missed break, held up fourth last rail, wide challenge, not pace to trouble leaders.
Poor start, stumbled early, second last far side, improved wide exiting back, kept on under pressure but not reach leaders.
Poor start, back to last held up, widest of all straight, driven, kept on.
Fair break, ridden early, up for third one off, urged leaving back, fourth into straight, weakened late.
Lost half length start, taken back to second last rail, tried to improve between horses, no real impression, impeded late.
Fair break, bustled up early to take rail in fourth, third into straight, almost joined leaders mid-straight, weakened late.
Fast away out wide, ridden to share lead one off, headed, second into straight, ridden, found nil.
Fair break wide, kept four wide early, then fifth one off, ridden before straight, no progress.
Well away, slight stumble, shared lead until went on, folded straight.
Missed break, settled near rear one off, had to wait for gaps, ran on very strongly once they came.
Fast away out wide, led and crossed, headed leaving back, led again 100m out, not resist winner.
Well away wide, circled field to lead leaving back, kept on well straight until headed 100m out.
Fair break out wide, taken back but still wide, ran on well in straight.
Good break, pumped along early to take fourth on rail, driven straight, kept on but no impact.
Fair break, not much early, midfield two off, every chance straight, no extra.
No Comments on Running information for this horse.
Taken back from fair break but could never get near rail, wide throughout and without cover, ridden straight, never a factor.
Broke well, not speed to lead, midfield rail, lacked pace to take gap straight, kept on.
Good break but short of early speed, midfield one off, ridden straight, no kick.
Slow start out wide, last early, checked on turn, found little straight but ran on past beaten horses.
Scrubbed along early after fair break, fourth last one off, shaken up turn, found nil.
Fair break, up out wide to challenge for lead, settled third one off, ridden straight, found nothing, lame next day.
Moderate break, no early pace, rear far side, tried to improve turn, no progress.
Settled in front of midfield, 3Ls off the fast pace along the fence, closed the race off strongly 300M to win without much threats.
At rear as usual, 7.5Ls off the leader 2-3 wide, suited by the fast pace, dashed well 300M to secure 2nd.
Eased back and took rail, 6.5Ls off the leader, benefited by the fast tempo, progressed steadily 400M to grab 3rd.
Midfield along the fence, 4.5Ls off the leader, benefited by the fast pace the rail trip, made steady ground in straight.
Hard ridden to obtain the box seat, harmed by the fast pace, ran on well until 200M flattened.
At back, 6Ls off the leader, trapped 3 wide throughout and lost ground, favoured by the fast tempo, ran on ok in final stages.
Midfield, 4.5Ls off the fast pace, trapped 3 wide throughout, carried back 600M and lost ground, ran on fairly in straight.
Dipped start, never a factor at rear.
Pushed to take the rail and led by 1.5Ls at very fast pace, hung on until 200M emptied.
Pushed early, 6Ls off the leader 2 wide, benefited by the fast pace, ran on ok in straight until 100M run ended and stopped quickly.
Prominent, 3Ls off the leader, trapped 3 wide throughout, not suited by the fast tempo, weakened 400M.
Hard ridden forward but trapped 4 wide first bend, sat 1.5Ls off the leader 2 wide from 800M, harmed by the fast pace, out of fuel 400M.
Hard ridden early, just obtained a midfield spot on the fence, 4.5Ls off the fast pace, faded 400M.
Hard ridden to keep up in midfield, trapped 3 wide throughout, dropped off quickly 600M.
Fair break, slight nudge early, soon moved up easily to join leaders, asked to quicken 250m out, soon outclassed opposition.
Lost length at start, soon in touch mid track, ridden 250m out, no chance with winner.
Moderate start, rear early, bustled along throughout, kept on very well late.
Good break, shared early lead rail, kept on but no chance with winner.
Broke well, pumped along early, shared lead rail, led 200m out, weakened.
Out well, joined leader mid track, ridden 200m out, weakened.
Fair break, lacked early pace, kept on under driving, but never dangerous.
Ridden early to share lead one off rail, driven but gradually lost ground.
Moderate break, couple of slight bumps early, midfield, ridden, never threatened.
Fair break, ridden early but could never get involved.
Awkward start and slight bump early, last on rail after 200m, passed only beaten horses.
Well away, ridden early but not pace to stay with leaders, driven mid track, found little.
Some early speed, joined six way battle for lead, soon beaten off and weakened, eased late.
Broke well then restrained to a position ahead of midfield, showed a smart change of pace on straightening and got past the battling runner-up near 100M. Won in class record time.

Recovered from a sluggish start to be tracking leader along the fence, swiftly moved to the lead 250M, ran on gamely but couldn't fend off the impressive winner. (Jockey reported his saddle shifted during the race.)
Not hurried, placed in midfield and saved ground along the inside, shifted out inside 350M for a clear run, kept on well for 3rd but was soundly beaten by the first 2.
Settled 2-wide behind midfield, driven 400M, ran on and just missed out on 3rd, but no threat to the top 2 which drew well clear.
Settled towards the rear 5-6Ls off the strong pace, progressed steadily from 350M but was never a threat.
Sped to the lead off the rail and set a strong pace throughout, headed 250M and had little left late.
Reserved early and was gradually taken across to the rail, kept to inside on straightening, ran on fairly.
Tracked leader, had every chance but lacked a further response, no extra in late stages.
Chased the pace 4-wide early then turned 3 deep over the home turn, soon weakened on straightening.
Kept 3-wide in midpack and couldn't offer any response on straightening.
Hampered shortly after the start, lacked pace, detached in last throughout and never in contention.
Travelled 3-wide no cover just off the pace, weakened rapidly on straightening, tailed out. (Unacceptable performance.)
Fast out, shared lead wide, crossed to rail, kicked clear straight, fought on well when strongly challenged.
Well away, led rail, then trailed winner, strong challenge straight, just held.
Flew gate, then settled one off in third, hard ridden straight, but could never quite get to first two.
Slow away, lost two lengths, second last early, made ground along rail, ran on well but never got in challenge.
Well away, fourth one off, every chance down mid-track, not pace to challenge.
Ridden early from fair break, sixth one off, every chance, kept on but unable to challenge.
Slow away, last early, still last into straight, ran on wide outside.
Good break, taken back to midfield one off, urged leaving back, not much room early straight, kept on well but never a danger.
Level break, back to midfield rail, pulling, ridden straight and kept on, but no threat.
Sluggish from wide, up to midfield one off, ridden, no kick.
Fair break, sixth one off, slightly hampered far side, ridden straight, no progress.
Fair break, no early pace, third last, made ground wide on turn, no further progress.
Sluggish start, fourth last and overracing, ridden straight, one pace.
Fair break wide, fifth last one off, ridden turn, weakened.
No speed early and faded back to rear, ended up 12Ls from lead, strong pace advantaged, saved ground on bend and weaved a passage clear from 400 M to 200 M, flew late to score.
Even break, behind pace group 5Ls away on rails travelled well on rails throughout, improved on bend, joined in at 300 M and looked set for victory before being caught last 50 M.
Closer than usual in a midfield role, 6Ls or so away in mid-section, made some progress rounding bend and turned in usual honest effort making good ground for place.
Began with first few, trailed early leaders but gradually crept closer on bend, made an early effort at 500 M, challenging 3 wide, peaked inside 200 M but hung on to make frame.
Positioned well trailling speed 6Ls back in 6th, even run in mid-section, same margin down to turn, kept on without threatening.
Lost ground at start, mustered to be behind midfield, nearly 12Ls down in mid-section, aided by tempo, saved ground on rails rounding bend, closed gradually without threatening.
No speed from jump, soon at rear more than 14Ls of fast pace, had plenty to do but improved on circle, impossible spot turning but did work home reasonably in straight.
Broke well and crossed to lead, took a trail but improved to leaders girth on circle, in 3 way battle turning in, there to 200 M before run ended after being used in mid-section.
Faded back from an awkward alley, 12Ls or more from speed, fast pace suited, plenty to do on bend, made some minor ground passing tiring runners.
Rolled forward from widest alley to take over, made use of with good speed on, challenged again from 500 M, struggling by 300 M and folded soon after.
Away only fairly and received a back check and nearly fell, best part of 11Ls off top end in mid-section, appreciated pace on but didn't respond in straight. (Lame after race.)
Reasonable break, settled just off speed 4 to 5Ls away, niggled on bend, faded out in straight.
Drifted back to race in midfield 7 to 8Ls from lead, did work wide without cover with strong speed on, folded after a tough trip.
Settled in midfield on rails. 6 to 7Ls back, not asked in mid-section, struggling on turning and stopped soon after. (Heart irregularity.)

Soon ridden to a prominent spot settling on heels of leader, came to challenge upon straightening taking charge over 200 M out, won easily.
Driven to lead from a wide draw, held under a length's advantage to straight, headed under pressure over 200 M out, just held on for 2nd.
Began fairly, settled in forward of midfield on rails, quickened to challenge upon straightening, ran on under pressure to be nearest at finish.
Began awkwardly from a wide-ish draw but soon ridden to prominent 4th about 2Ls off the speed, remained similar turning in, kept on steadily without quickening.
Towards rear early, gradually picked up to rear of midfield, similar turning in, fought on well to do best work late.
Settled wide without cover in midfield after beginning from a wide barrier, remained similar turning into straight, ran home one-paced.
Began very awkwardly, soon raced in last few, similar turning in, ran home one-paced.
Began with others but quickly dropped well back, remained behind turning in, only ran past well-beaten runners.
Soon taken back from the widest barrier to travel well behind, trailed the field into straight, only went past well-beaten runners.
Raced in forward of midfield, gradually faded under pressure in straight.
Soon ridden to first few, settled in 3rd about 2Ls off the lead, dropped out tamely under pressure after straightening.
Began with others, settled towards rear, amongst last few turning in, made no impression in straight.
Began moderately, settled in rear of midfield along rails, similar turning in, weakened under pressure in straight.
Made his run from midfield, 2 deep with cover. Commenced to peel out after the 700m, cornered about six deep and fought strongly to claim victory, drawing away in the run home.
Parked behind midfield, 1 off with cover. Worked to the finish well.
Settled worse than midfield, along the rail. Angled out into clear running midway down the home stretch, maintained an even gallop right to the wire.
Camped 3 back, 2 wide with cover. Kept on one paced for most of the straight.
Parked in third position 1 off with cover. Only plodded to the line.
Was posted 3 wide without cover after the 1000m not far from the leaders. Never a factor. (Vet reported that the horse pulled up lame & blood in the trachea.)
Positioned at the back of the field towards the rail. Hung in badly in the straight and proved difficult to ride out.
Settled with the backmakers 2-3 wide with cover. Never really ran on.
Travelled at the tail of the field 2-3 wide with cover. Came wide in the home straight but failed to close off.
Took up leading duties along the fence. was joined soon after the 900m, and travelled as the leading duo thereafter. Faded after the 200m.
Travelled midfield on the fence. gave little when under pressure in the final stretch.
Was checked at the start settling towards the rear near the rail with cover. Struggled in the run home.
Gradually worked its way across to race in the lead, 1 off approaching the 900m. Gave in quickly near the final furlong and finished well back. (To trial.)
Tracked the leaders along the paint. Was a beaten horse early in the straight and tailed out. (To trial.)

Began well and sat 2-wide ahead of midfield first turn. Not hurried and dropped to midfield when others improved home turn. Shaken up and was 5Ls off on straightening. Launched a sustained challenge to cut down the leader final stride.

Sat behind pace on fence through to home turn. Urged from 600 M and kept chasing the runaway leader top of home straight. Hit front 150 M and looked likely to score until overhauled in the shadows of the post.

Bumped at start. Raced 3-wide at midfield first turn. Left without cover at 1000 M and improved outside the field passing 800 M. Led by 3Ls at 300 M. Hung on until no extra to fend off the top pair closing stages.
Hampered at start. Caught 4-wide ahead of midfield first turn. Improved to sit one-off behind the pace from 1200 M. Ran on steadily in the straight without troubling the front trio.
Soon taken to race 2-wide at rear. Moved closer 600 M. Swung 5-wide and was 7Ls away rounding home turn. Made up some ground in the straight but not threatening.
Soon eased towards rear on fence. Took closer order approaching 600 M. 6Ls back turning into home. One-paced to conclude.

Began awkwardly. Driven to go forward but was caught wide first turn. Slotted 2-wide ahead of midfield from 1600 M. Niggled to maintain position from 700 M but couldn't turn up a notch. No headway in the straight.
Pressed early and raced behind midfield on fence. Gradually moved away from the fence approaching home turn for running but gave very limited response when asked. Never likely.
2 to 3-wide behind midfield. Came widest at bend. No progress in the straight.
2 to 3-wide towards rear. Under pressure from 700 M but found nothing. Never a factor.
Pressed forward from high draw and led on fence first turn. Headed at 650 M and dropped out gradually in the straight.
Midfield on fence early and middle stages. Beaten top of straight.
Always at rear. No impression.
Broke well, led early then sat one off in third, went on 200 M out for comfortable win.
Fair break but then slow into stride, up to midfield one off, ridden along straight, hit stride very late to snatch second near line.
Broke well, settled fourth on rail, squeezed through gap to challenge 150 M out, just lacked finishing pace.
Well away, up for share of lead four wide, then outright leader until 250 M out, kept on when headed.
Fair break, sixth one off on settling, challenged wide, no extra last 150 M.
Fast out, then slightly outpaced, urged along on rail midfield, kept on but never quite on terms.
Fair break, up to second but three wide at turn, ridden early straight, not go on.
Even break, up fast to lead after 200 M, reined back and headed, raced third on rail, tried to challenge rail, one paced.
Fair break but no early speed, urged along but slipped back to second last rail, improved entering straight, ridden, not go on.
Missed beat at start, urged fourth last rail, out wide for bid, no real progress.
Fair start but caught wide, ridden mid track straight, no real progress.
Fast break but parked six wide and pulling first turn, always at least four wide, ridden but found little.
Issued break, second last one off, ridden before straight, nothing to give.
Missed break and lost two lengths, ridden up on outside to midfield wide, already in trouble before straight, eased when beaten.
Out fast, led and crossed, saw off challengers one by one in straight.
Fair break, fifth one off, pulled out to challenge, ran on well but never quite got to leader.
Fair break but no early speed, urged in second last far side, made steady ground but could never get in a challenge.
Fair break but forced four or five wide with no cover, kept on well down centre in straight.
Quick break, joined leaders four wide, still challenging for lead mid straight, gradually weakened.
Moderate break, ridden up to sit one off one back, led briefly early straight, driven, weakened.
Fair break, midfield rail, tried to challenge on inside but never going pace to reach leader.
Fair break but lacked early pace and midfield one off, slight check far side and back to last, kept on quite well.
Moderate break, rear early, up to fifth last one off, bustled turn, ridden straight but no kick.
Fair break, sixth but three wide, urged early straight, drive, no progress.
Fair break, back to last one off, urged entering turn, no progress.
Missed break, third last two off, pumped along on rail, found little.
Broke well, good position on rail half length behind leader, weakened quickly straight.
Moderate break, no route to rail, tried to improve wide, soon ran out of steam in straight.
Eased to sit in front of midfield, 3.5Ls behind the fast pace along the fence, progressed steadily 400M, dominated 200M.
Eased to sit in midfield, 6Ls off the leaders 2 wide, favoured by the fast pace, progressed steadily 400M to grab 2nd.
Settled in prominent spot 2 wide, faced head wind first half mile, not suited by the fast sectionals, closed the race off strongly for 3rd.
Pushed to share the lead 2 wide at very fast sectionals, faced head wind first half mile, hung on strongly until 250M overhauled, ran on well.
Very slow away, 8Ls off the leaders 3 wide, suited by the fast pace, made minor ground 250M.
Very slow away, hard ridden to take a midfield spot on the fence, 5Ls off the leaders, benefited by the fast tempo, just held ground in straight.
Eased to rear, 9Ls off the leaders 3 wide, favoured by the fast pace, made no ground in straight.
Pushed forward, 2Ls off the leaders 3 wide, faced head wind first half mile, harmed by the fast pace, out of fuel 300M.
Midfield, 4.5Ls off the leaders 2 wide, suited by the fast tempo, emptied 300M.
Eased to sit in midfield, 6.5Ls off the leaders 3-4 wide, benefited by the fast pace, however no progress in straight.
Eased back, took rail, favoured by the fast tempo, never a factor.
Trapped 4-5 wide throughout, faced head wind first half mile, never better than midfield.
Eased back, suited by the fast pace, never competitive.
Pressed forward to hold the rail in the lead, clocked very fast sectionals and faced head wind first half mile, dropped off 400M.
Fast break, led and crossed, settled third on rail, out to challenge straight, led 250 M out, ran on gamely.
Well away, fourth out wide with no route to rail no cover, stayed on well straight, just failed.
Good break, up to share lead three wide, took second place one off, ridden early straight, kept on.
Moderate break out wide, short of early pace, back to last one off, ran on well out wide.
Well away, comfortable in fifth one off, out to challenge, strongly ridden, stayed on one pace.
Well away but lacked early speed, settled midfield rail, tried to challenge straight, no real kick, kept on.
Missed beat start and could not tuck in, four wide without cover, improved wide turn, ridden, kept on quite well.
Away well, eased back to third last two off, very short of room early straight, kept on.
Fair break, one off rail midfield, pulling, one pace.
Fast away, led and crossed, headed 300 M out weakened.
Slightly awkward start, no early speed, second last far side, last into straight, inside bid, no progress.
Fair break, taken back to fifth last rail, pulling, short of room early straight, not run on.
Lost half length start, fourth last one off, eager, ridden straight, no progress.
Fair break, up to fifth two wide pulling hard, never really settled, pumped along straight, nothing in tank, eased.
Travelled handily just off leaders, briefly held up on the inside early straight, took over passing 300 M, ran on strongly and always had enough to hold off the persistent runner-up.
Settled 3-wide in mid-division, moved up swiftly on straightening and pushed the winner all the way to the line.
Tucked in behind midfield about 4-5Ls off the pace, ran on strongly final 200 M to go 3rd just before the line.
Recovered from a slow start and raced in mid-pack along the inside, kept on well to the line and just lost 3rd close home.
Switched off to the rear, had plenty to do passing 400 M, took time to muster but picked up well inside 250 M for some late impression.
Positioned 3-wide ahead of midfield, had his chance but run ended 100 M.
Raced with last few after a slow start, had 6Ls to make up turning in, switched widest and made steady progress towards the line.
Niggled along to maintain a position in midfield, steadied near 700 M, had a troubled passage up the inside but didn't offer much when clear passing 150 M.
Went forward and pressed the early pace, tracked leader one out one back, rallied to 150 M, no extra late.
Kept 4-wide in midfield without cover, couldn't pick up when placed under pressure, faltered final 100 M.
Slowly away, not hurried and raced towards the rear 6Ls back, had no clear path until passing 200 M and made minor headway in late stages.
With leaders for the first 200 M then dropped back to midfield, driven 400 M but lacked a further response, eased over final stages.
Driven along after the start and crossed to the lead nearing 800 M, headed inside 250 M, weakened.
Rushed to the front and chased leader 3-wide, weakened rapidly on straightening, eased inside 200 M.
Jumped well from wide draw, restrained early but still up to fourth one off, powerful run straight, comfortably.
Out fast, led, crossed, two length lead exiting back, kicked early straight, kept on well but could not resist winner.
Slow into stride and outpaced early, second last on settling, still rear 400 M out, surged down the outside to take third late.
Broke well, sixth one off overracing slightly, shaken up entering straight, ran on steadily.
Broke well, midfield three wide, bid down centre, kept on without threatening.
Luffed start, up to midfield one off overracing slightly, ran on well without being able to get in blow at leaders.
Fair break, taken back from wide draw to last one off, pumped along entering straight, kept on wide but no threat.
Fair break, back to fourth last one off, some progress straight but could never threaten.
Fair break, ridden but could not get to lead, settled third, tried to challenge along rail, no real progress.
Broke well, second on rail leaving back, tried to challenge early straight, weakened.
Bobbled start, third last on rail, tried to improve on inside straight, no more to give.
Broke well, ridden up to take fourth on rail, then midfield, driven straight, no response.
Fair break but slow into stride, up on rail to midfield not really settling, ridden along rail straight, no progress.
Away well but caught wide, midfield three off, no progress straight, not persevered with.
Out with rest, ended up posted wide 5Ls or so back, without cover from midpoint, forced to cart field up to runaway leader, stuck to task and took advantage late for a strong win.
Out fairly, posted 4 wide early without cover, pressed on and took up running by top turn, didn't let up and kept rolling on turn, 3Ls clear at 300 M, just tired late. Big run.
Standard jump, ended up in 2nd half of field, 6 to 7Ls back on rails, used little in mid-section, in traffic turning, clear from 250 M and closed off soundly to take a place.
Even break, drove through to take a spot on the back on pace, had a fair run in mid-section, into mix on turn, stayed on soundly without threatening.
Drifted back from a wide alley, 6 to 7Ls away in running line behind midfield, had job to do rounding bend, closed nicely down middle to be not far away at finish.
No early speed, ended up sharing rear 8Ls off top end, 3 wide with cover on bend, same margin down turning, made many lengths in straight to be nearest on line.
Pressed on from an awkward draw to sit first without cover, did a bit of work when new leader emerged and pace increased, niggled turning, faded inside 250 M.
Ordinary jump, soon sharing rear, 8Ls off lead in middle section, set a task when still last turning, steadied at 300 M, made some minor ground late.
Average to begin, regathered to be 5Ls down in middle stages, overraced on circle, came wide turning but didn't finish off as normally would.
Out in line, positioned 3 wide behind midfield 5Ls off speed, had cover in run, same margin down turning, never made impression in straight.
Some early speed, on leaders back early, shifted back by mid-point, took inside runs when 4Ls down turn, ordinary finish in straight.
Lost a few lengths at start, mustered to join rear division, 7 to 8Ls back throughout, saved ground turning but never really made ground. (Jockey reported never comfortable.)
Tardy into stride, drove through to hold position 4 to 5Ls back in midfield, soft run to turn, found little 400 M, weakening out tamely.
Fastest out, pressed on to lead, taken on and headed by midpoint, under pressure turning and dropped right out. (Mucopus.)
Never far off leaders, moved up to challenge inside 400 M, took lead approaching 100 M and held on gamely under strong urging.
Positioned 2-wide in midfield, had to shift out twice for a clear passage in straight, did best work late and was just denied.
Stalked leader off the rail, took over 350 M, fought back when challenged over final 150 M and continued willingly to the line.
Went forward and sat prominently just off the pace, kept on to 100 M, weakened late.
Given a waiting ride near the rear, made promising headway down the inside but was severely checked 50 M form the line. Would have been closer.
Settled nicely in midfield along the inside, kept on to 100 M but lacked extra pace to seriously challenge, turned flat close home.
Reserved off the pace, held up early in straight, ran on final 300 M but not getting to the leaders.
Never far off but kept very wide throughout, not quickened on straightening and hung in badly. (Jockey reported he was unable to test the horse due to its racing manner.)
Driven early to stay in midpack, one-paced going into final 300 M, never threatened.
Taken back to last on jumping, reserved to 400 M, took time to gather and made minor headway final 200 M.
Dropped back and raced near last about 6Ls off the pace, never a factor in the straight and made limited progress only.
Settled off the fence behind midfield, lacked further response on straightening, weakened 150 M.
Sped to the lead but unable to make the cross until 700 M, had little left coming out of the bend, eased.
Obtained a midfield position along the 3 path, gave way 300 M then eased. (Jockey expressed concerns over the horse's action.)

Soon took up running, held slender advantage before kicking 1L clear around the bend, went further away to over 2Ls upon straightening, won readily.
Settled in midfield on rails, saved ground turning in, fought on under pressure for 2nd, flattered by easing winner.
Began moderately, improved steadily along rails early to settle just off the speed, failed to quicken under pressure after straightening, plugged on for 3rd.
Travelled in last few, hampered coming out of back straight, saved ground turning in, made up some ground down inside of straight, never threatening.

Soon taken back for rails run after beginning from a wide barrier, remained in 9th towards rear of field most of way to straight, switched out for a run on straightening, kept on steadily without quickening.
Behind midfield, hampered and lost position coming out of back straight, made some late headway past well-beaten runners in the run home.
Broke well, disputed lead briefly, settled one-out-one-back in 3rd to straight, gradually faded under pressure after straightening.
Began well from middle draw, settled 3-wide in 5th far side, became 4th but not closer up around the bend, gradually faded after straightening.
Began from the widest barrier, soon taken back to settle in rear of field, widest runner around the bend and into straight, made no impression thereafter.
Niggled along in 6th in forward of midfield, cropped a bad bad check rounding the bend, never recovered.
Soon driven from a wide barrier to share second 2-out-one-back, struggling to hold position rounding home bend, soon dropped out after straightening.
Raced in front of midfield one off the fence. Peeled out turning for home and dug deep over the latter stages to score nicely with a well timed effort.
Held the front along the rail early, then was pressured soon after the 600m, dueling for leading duties. Was collard over the final stages despite shifting out abruptly near the post.
Rolled forward from the outside alley to eventually cross and park outside the leader near the 600m. kept on gamely despite the workload and being bumped close to home.
Made his run from near the tail of the field along the fence. Ran on well.
Slow to begin but recovered to stalk the leader along the paint after the 650m. had every chance but whacked away at the same speed over the final stages.
Couldn't go the early speed of the race settling near the rear of the field, 3 wide with cover. Made good ground after straightening up towards the centre of the track.
Settled close to midfield, 1 off with cover. Was steadied near the 600m, worked home fairly.
Copped a steady near the 600 M and lost its position whilst behind the speed, settling worse than midfield. Only plodded to the line, weakening in the final stages.
Camped behind the leaders passing the 600m, but then travelled 3 wide without cover on the turns. Faded inside the furlong.
Not the best away settling towards the tail of the field about 4 wide. Raced wide thereafter failing to make any appreciable ground in the home stretch.
Settled about midfield but coursed wide and without a lot of cover, giving ground on the circle. Struggled in the run home.
Raced prominently but was always posted very wide without cover. Never likely.
Caught 4-wide in the leading section after start. Slotted 2-wide behind the pace from first turn. Made a sweeping run final 300M and dominated inside 100M.
Pressed early to take prominent spot until home straight. Took time to obtain clear passage before chasing strongly final furlong to snatch 2nd.
Sat outside the leader through to home straight. Hung on well but couldn't fend off the finishing effort of the winner passing 200M. Held 2nd until final stride.
Led on fence through to home straight. One-paced to conclude.
Eased towards rear on fence from high draw. Improved gradually home turn and was 5Ls down on straightening. Made up ground steadily and nearly made frame.
Behind midfield on fence before shifting out for clear run home straight. Just held ground thereafter.
Slow to begin and was taken to rear near fence before first turn. Back with last few and was 7Ls off turning in. Made some headway home straight.
2-wide behind midfield early. Dropped towards rear home turn. Switched out gradually and closed off fairly.
Well enough away to race with front runners. Taken to sit 2-wide behind midfield after first turn. Swung wide into final stretch to beat tired runners home.
Travelled wide and without cover in the front rank until weakened passing 250M.
Began well but raced wide. Taken to sit 2-wide towards rear first turn. Never improved from there.
Jumped fairly. Driven outside the field to eventually settle 3-wide ahead of midfield at 850M. Pressured to maintain position home turn but failed to respond. Beaten top of home straight.
Fast out, ridden to lead, dictated pace, kicked clear early straight, never in danger thereafter.
Out well, settled fourth on rail, ridden before straight, stayed on without threatening winner.
Slow start, held up fourth last, improved turn, stayed on well.
Fair break, taken back to last from wide draw, urged far side, still rear entering straight, finished fast.
Broke well, up to third three wide, then second one off, chased winner, weakened late.
Broke well, up to second but overracing, settled in third, ridden turn, kept on without threatening.
Moderate start, urged along fifth last rail, improved on inside turn, kept on but not pace to challenge.
Broke well, settled fifth one off, ridden leaving back, kept on one pace.
Broke well, taken back from wide gate, third last one off, ridden, very little progress.
Fair break, then stumbled shortly after start, midfield one off, wide turn, ridden, no progress.
Moderate start, taken back to second last, urged back straight and again turn, found nothing.
Fair break but caught wide, checked exiting back, back to last, not driven once clearly beaten.
Fair break, ridden early to take fourth one off, took time to settle, challenged down centre of course, led 200m out, ran on strongly.
Broke fast, led and crossed, dictated pace, quickened turn, stayed on but no match for winner.
Fair break, moved to rail and driven to take spot behind leaders, settled fifth, inside run, stayed on well.
Slow start and bumped along early, last on rail, kept on steadily, but no real impression.
Broke well, not rushed early, midfield rail, slightly short of room in straight but did not affect placing.
Broke well, took third on rail, out to challenge early straight, driven, weakened.
Sluggish start, bumped early, three lengths last and ridden, sharp move four wide home turn, kept on well down centre.
Quickly away but no route to rail, caught wide and back to midfield one off, tried to improve down centre, no kick.
Fair break, taken back, looking for rail, launched wide on turn, kept on quite well.
Broke well, then back to fourth last one off, not settling immediately, asked to quicken entering straight, found little.
Fast away, driven to join lead, one off and pulling, settled second, ridden early straight, no extra.
Fair break, settled sixth one off, ridden turn, found nothing, eased late.
Pushed early to keep up in midfield, 5.5Ls off the leader 2-3 wide, suited by the fast pace, made ground steadily 450M around the field, dominated 100M.
Very slow away, at rear, 7.5Ls off the leader 2 wide, favoured by the fast pace, progressed steadily along the fence from 300M and took 2nd.
Hard ridden to cross towards rail in front of midfield, 2Ls off the leader, not suited by the fast pace, ran on well to the line for 3rd.
Hard ridden to occupy the box seat, not suited by the fast early sectionals, led briefly 250M, overhauled 100M and flattened.
Pushed to obtain a forward spot, 2.5Ls behind the fast pace 2-3 wide, ran on until 150 flattened.
Bumped start, hard ridden forward to cross in the lead, clocked very fast sectionals, soon out of fuel 250M.
At back but on the fence, 6Ls off the leader, benefited by the fast pace, however no turn of foot in straight.
Eased to sit in midfield, 4Ls off the leader 2 wide, favoured by the fast tempo, no progress.
Pushed to hold the rail in midfield, 4Ls off the leader, benefited by the fast pace and the rail trip, however flattened 200M.
Bumped start, hard ridden early but failed to cross in front, trapped 2-3 wide, never better than midfield.
Hard ridden early but did not muster, trapped 3-4 wide wide throughout and lost too much ground, suited by the fast tempo but never a factor at back.
Hard ridden forward, 1.5Ls off the leader, trapped 3 wide, harmed by the fast pace, dropped off rapidly 500M.
Fair break, fourth on rail on settling, looked to pull out to challenge turn, path blocked and switched to rail, ran on strongly to lead 50m out.
Fair break, midfield rail, pulled out to challenge outside, led, caught last 50m.
Well away, took second on rail, challenged and led early straight, headed 150m out.
Fair break, midfield one off, urged,, improved wide approaching turn, kept on well, not pace to challenge.
Sluggish start, back to fourth last one off, improved wide exiting back, ridden, kept on well without threatening.
Broke well, up three wide to third, crossed to rail, ridden, not pace to threaten.
Fair break, not hurried from wide draw, back to second last one off, tried to improve wide turn, switched inside, kept on but never a threat.
Even break, not hurried, held up fifth last rail, improved slightly between horses straight, no kick, no impression.
Fair break, ridden early, fifth one off, slight check turn, never dangerous.
Taken back to rear from wide draw, refused to settle early, third last rail, ridden straight, no response.
Taken back to rear and held up, ridden, no impression.
Broke fast, led early, built up six length lead by halfway, ridden exiting back, headed, weakened.
Never far off in the pack chasing the pace, picked up strongly under urging, took the lead 100M from home and ran out a clear cut winner.
Reserved in midfield, shifted out from fence approaching 450M and had an uninterrupted run in straight, kept on and took 2nd right on the line.
Average start only, rushed to the lead but not able to cross, kept on well only to be headed near 100M, tired near the line and lost out in a photo finish for 2nd place.
Kept 3-wde in the first half of the race, gradually crept forward to race in 3rd just off leader, kept on well between horses and just lost 3rd on the line.
Crowded for room after the start and ended up in the rear, made a 4-wide move 550M out, ran on well down the outside and just missed out on 3rd.
Towards the rear 5Ls back, saved ground on the inside, gradually picked up passing 250M, not beaten far.
Broke well, bagged the rail and raced ahead of midfield 3Ls off leader, briefly threatened at the 200M mark but couldn't sustain his run in late stages.
Dropped back to a spot behind midfield, checked 550M and shuffled further back, ran on fairly in straight but couldn't get near to the leaders.
Placed 2-wide in mid-pack early stages, shuffled back to near last approaching home straight, made limited progress final 300M and got past beaten runners only.
Hard driven out the gate and obtained a forward position off the fence, kept on till finding no extra 200M. (Jockey questioned re the positioning of his horse.)
Unable to cross and kept 3-4 wide ahead of mid-division, struggled to keep up halfway round the home turn, soon beaten.
Taken back from draw 12 and swiftly crossed to the rail, raced as the back marker throughout and not picked up on straightening. (Confirmed a roarer in post race exam.)
Fair break, not hurried, fourth last one off, improved between horses turn, challenged mid-track under strong driving, got up 50m out.
Broke well, led rail, uncontested, three lengths clear early straight, caught last 50m.
Fair break, no early rush, back to rear on rail, improved turn, hard ridden between horses, not quite pace to get up.
Fair break, midfield rail, challenged along rail straight, kept on well without being able to challenge.
Relaxed start, held up last one off, ridden turn, ran on wide, flattened out last 50m.
Slightly awkward start, third last rail, tried to challenge along rail but never a factor.
Quick break, ridden early to share lead, settled second one off, slight stumble entering straight, weakened late.
Fair break, fourth on rail, ridden entering straight, gradually weakened.
Fast away, ridden up to share lead, then third one off, had trouble negotiating first turn, fifth two off, driven turn, up to third, weakened.
Sluggish start, fifth last and three wide, ridden turn, passed beaten horses late.
Fair break, sixth and wide first turn, could never get near rail, wide into straight, no extra, eased.
Broke well, lacked early pace, midfield one off, urged exiting back, driven, nothing to give, eased.
Handily placed behind leading pair and well suited by the fast pace, moved to the front 200m out then rallied strongly to fend off the 2nd in late stages.
Within striking distance in 4th, showed good acceleration on straightening and looked the likely winner near 200M, kept on but was outbattled by the winner in closing stages.
Went forward as expected, crossed to lead passing 1100M but was pressed by a runner on the outside and went very fast, headed inside 200M and tired in late stages.
Placed in midfield more forward than usual, stayed on to finish a distant 4th.
Along the fence behind mid-division, kept on same pace and never looked likely.
Tucked in behind midfield 4-5Ls off the pace, niggled along over the home turn but couldn't find extra pace to challenge seriously.
Trapped 3-wide and never better than midfield, ran on one-paced final 300M.
Slow to begin, in last and was severely checked near 1000M, had plenty to do turning in but could make limited progress only.
Always rearward and became unsettled near 1000M, no impression on straightening. (Unacceptable Performance. To barrier trial around a bend.)
Towards the rear section and travelled 3-wide for the majority of the race, lacked further response on straightening, eased inside 100M.
In midfield early then dropped back towards the rear passing 1200M, driven inside 300M but no progress. (Lame.)
Pressed the pace outside leader, weakened approaching home straight, soon behind and finished tailed off. (Unacceptable Performance.)
