Soon took up running, set a leisurely pace early, quickened up pace middle stages, strolled clear after straightening, won unextended.
Raced outside leader, slow to respond after straightening, fought hard to retain 2nd.
Settled one back in 3rd on rails, quickened to look a threat to TAI SING YEHs quinella spot early in straight, unable to sustain effort over 100 m out.
Trailed in 4th and last throughout, unable to keep up in straight, never seen with a chance.

Was crowded soon after the jump settling in advance of midfield along the paint. Peeled out near the final furlong and despite drifting towards the grandstand side over the final stages, won in good fashion.
Was near enough to midfield, 3 deep with cover. Rallied wider on the home turn and finished off gamely.
Was tightened shortly after the start settling behind midfield along the rail. Made good late headway in the final stretch towards the inside.
Ridden aggressively to dictate the running and held a commanding lead by the 400m. was swamped over the final 100m.
Settled handy in the run, 1 off. Made a dash early in the straight but was gassed close to home.
Travelled close to the fence towards the tail of the field. Was steadied early in the straight, worked home farily.
Settled midfield 2 wide with cover. Worked home evenly without making any great impression.
Travelled prominently 3 deep. Failed to quicken when asked for an effort early in the straight and never hit top gear.
Missed the start travelling at the rear of the field. Came wide in the final stretch but was never a factor.
Settled ahead of midfield about 3 deep. Failed to plough through the track conditions.
Travelled worse than midfield 2-3 wide with cover. Only paddled in the run home.
Slow to begin settling with the backmakers 3-4 wide. Struggled in the home straight.
Settled with the rear division 2-3 wide with cover. Only plodded to the line finishing well back.
Enjoyed a nice run in the race in 2nd position along the fence. Was a spent force early in the final straight and weakened noticeably.
Sat behind the pace near the fence before moving up to join lead home turn. Ran away from 350M. Never challenged.
Urged early but caught wide and without cover at midfield. Improved gradually at bend. Did the best of the rest in the straight but was beaten far by the winner.
3-wide behind midfield. 8Ls down on straightening. Finished off well before checked severely at 300M. Kept on steadily thereafter for 3rd.
Travelled wide and without cover towards rear. 8Ls down turning in. Made steady progress despite hanging in in the straight.
Raced within 3Ls of the pace in a 2-wide position before home turn. Under pressure to reach the back of leaders approaching home straight. One-paced to conclude.
Niggled early and raced behind midfield on fence. Asked to maintain position passing 700M. Made up minor ground and beat tired runners home.
Never far off the pace until no extra gear to threaten the principals passing 400M.
Travelled wide behind midfield. Never nearer.
Back with last few through to home straight. Not much to offer when asked.
Soon dropped to rear. No real progress in the straight.
Shaken up early to lead one-off the fence until weakened badly 300M from home.
Always at rear. Checked to avoid fallen rider at 200M. No further impression.
In front rank early. Struggled to stay in touch home turn. Beaten soon after 400M.

Placing: UR
Comment: Pressed early to race at midfield. Limited progress in the straight, clipped heels and dropped rider at 200M.
Fast away to share lead on rail, kicked early straight, never headed thereafter.
Fair break, followed leader in fifth, slight bump first turn, out to challenge straight, ran on well without threatening winner.
Lost length start, back to fourth last exiting back, nowhere to go at turn, found gap on rail and stayed on well.
Missed break and driven early, last then improved between runners to mid/rear, check far side, stayed on well when clear.
Fair break, in second rank of leading pack three wide, wide into straight, driven, kept on.
Fair break, ridden up wide for share of lead but two off, back to third and ridden turn, no further progress.
Fast away, shared lead one off, tried to match winner's kick early straight, gradually weakened.
Fair break, second rank of leading bunch one off, ridden exiting back, kept on but no more headway.
Fair break but slow into stride, ridden but back to last on rail, kept on quite well past beaten horses straight.
Slightly missed break, third last one off, then three off, wide bid, found little
Fast out, ridden to join leaders, not pace to stay with them, back to midfield, ridden, no progress.
Fast away from outside draw but caught very wide, travelled much further than better drawn rivals, found nothing straight.
Broke well, up with leaders but four wide, five wide into straight, ridden but nothing to give, eased late.
Fast break, led and clear first turn, led throughout, unchallenged.
Fair break, found good slot midfield rail, fourth entering turn, ran on well without being able to reach winner.
Moderate break, back to second last one off, improved along rail entering straight, stayed on well.
Missed beat start, midfield two off, ridden turn, kept on steadily but never a threat.
Fast break but caught wide, midfield one off, improved wide early straight, no extra late.
Well away but no route to rail, eased back to fourth last one off, ran on quite well straight but never threatened.
Fair break but no early speed, third last rail, kept on wide but never near leader.
Well away, up to second one off, followed winner until left behind early straight, no extra, weakened.
Good break, joined leaders wide, back to midfield still wide, ridden straight, no more to give.
Fair break, took nice slot behind leader in third, ridden and hung turn, not extra, not very enthusiastic.
Slow into stride, last early, still last at home turn, angled wide, some late progress past beaten horses.
Fair break but lacked early pace, wide near rear, no progress, later found to be lame.
Fair break, short of early pace, one off in fifth, ridden before turn, nothing to give.
Fair start but lacked early pace, mid/rear one off, dropped back to last, no improvement.
Pushed to keep up in midfield, 3.5Ls off the good pace 3 wide, progressed steadily 400M to score without much threats.
At back, 5.5Ls off the good pace 3 wide, made steadily ground 300M to secure 2nd.
Hard ridden early but failed to take lead, 1.5Ls behind the good pace 3 wide, ran on well to the line and took 3rd.
Hard ridden to obtain a midfield spot, 3.5Ls off the good pace 2 wide, made ground 400M.
Took back to rear, 6.5Ls off the good pace 2 wide, progressed steadily 250M.
Hold rail, shared the lead at good pace without making too much use, hung on until 100M flattened.
Very awkward away, behind midfield but on the fence, 5.5Ls off the good pace, made some ground 200M.
Pushed early but failed to muster, 5.5Ls off the good pace 2 wide, just held ground in straight.
Shared the lead 2 wide at good pace, ran on until 200M emptied.
Hard ridden early but not muster, 2Ls off the good pace, trapped 4 wide and lost too much ground, flattened 500M.
Prominent, 1L off the good pace 2 wide, ran on until 250M weakened.
Eased back 2 wide, never a factor.
Prominent early, soon raced awkwardly and lost ground steadily, dropped off 600M.
Fair break, urged up to join leading group but caught wide, six wide into straight, kept on but never dangerous.
Lost ground start, last on rail, improved quickly on rail turning in, led on line.
Well away, up to fifth one off, wide challenge, led 150m out until caught on line.
Fair break, midfield, led 250m out, headed 100m out, kept on.
Fair break, not rushed early, settled midfield one off, bid between runners mid track, not quite quicken.
Fair break, held up third last rail, angled out but no run, cut back in and stayed on well, but never a threat.
Missed break, lost length, up on rail to take fourth rail, up to second 300m out, flattened out.
Broke well, joined leaders rail, led turn until 400m out, weakened late.
Untidy start, ridden early, second last one off, wide challenge, little progress.
Fair break, not much early, fourth last and urged far side, wide run straight, never threat.
Away well, led one off, but not clear to cross, second into straight, ridden, weakened.
Well away from outside, caught four wide, back to fifth one off, driven, no response.
Well away from wide but caught four wide, up to third entering straight, ridden, weakened.
Well away out wide, but unable to cross and kept wide by rivals, no progress straight, weakened.
Led and dictated the pace, moved clear inside 400M, kept on strongly to line and was never seriously challenged.
Tracked leader one out one back, couldn't get near the winner but rallied well inside 200M to hold 2nd.
Dropped back to last of a 6 runners field, commenced his move round the outside passing 550M, briefly went 2nd inside 200M but turned flat in closing stages.
Sat one back on fence, had his chance but couldn't step up a gear when the race got serious.
Towards the rear in a field of 6 runners, outpaced when the tempo increased approaching 400M, ran on final 200M but not reached leaders.
Positioned in 4th 2-3Ls off the steady pace, driven passing 400M but no progress, soon behind.
Fair break, tracked leader rail, had to wait for gap, ran on well when it came, held on.
Fair break, fifth on rail, squeezed through between horses straight, ran on well, just failed.
Fast away, led rail until 150m out, ran on well but outpaced by first two.
Broke well, up to fourth one off, kept on mid track but never pace to challenge.
Bobbled start, back to rear, up on rail to midfield, not quite pace to challenge.
Well away from wide, up to second one off, led narrowly till headed 150m out, weakened late.
Not well away, ridden early, third last rail, improved turn, ran on along rail under driving but never threat.
Sluggish start, last and urged, improved turn, angled out, only modest progress.
Fair break, short of early pace, urged entering turn, no real progress.
Moderate start, midfield and urged, checked and lost places far side, kept on straight but never threat.
Fair break, midfield one off, driven mid-track straight, not pick up.
Sluggish start, fifth last one off, kept on in straight, but no improvement.
Fair break, eased back from wide draw, ridden early straight, no progress.
Fair break wide, but could never get near rail, wide throughout, found nothing straight.
Closer than usual behind midfield on rails, 5 to 6Ls off top end in middle stages, took inside runs turning and didn't round a horse, drove to lead inside 100 M for a deserved win.
Settled in an ideal position 1 out 1 back, 2Ls of speed in middle stages, loomed up at 300 M and lead until inside 100 M when overhauled, hung on for 2nd.
Positive from outset, settled outside leader making light work of outside gate, enjoyed easy pace throughout, took over turning and in mix for most of straight before out lasted late.
Ordinary jump and got back in rear division, raced 3 wide with cover, pace didn't suit and was 6 to 7Ls back to bend, came widest and made plenty of progress late to make frame.
Began well, pressed on to lead, set terms to suit throughout, challenged and headed turning in, kept on strongly but run ended inside 200 M.
No early pace, settled behind midfield 3 wide with cover, 5 to 6Ls back throughout, pace not ideal in mid-section, did best work late closing to be nearest on line.
Standard jump, caught wide but did get in 3 wide with cover before bend, 4 to 5Ls away in midfield throughout, made some brief ground but just held same position final 200 M.
Well enough away, took a spot on the leaders back, enjoyed easy time with steady speed, close enough turning but was very one paced final 300 M.
Out well, went on but couldn't get closer than 3 wide without cover in mid-section, did too much work to bend, faded out when workload took toll.
Faded back from an awkward draw, back with last few 6Ls or so from top end, still well back to bend, made only minor progress passed tiring runners. (Restricted action day after.)
Even break, 3Ls or so from leader in middle of pack, had an easy time throughout, didn't find much and battled away in straight.
Began well, slotted into midfield 4Ls back, bit keen in mid-section, same margin back turning, found little when pressured, dropped out.
Posted very wide from an awkward alley, better than 4 wide without cover, kept working in run, folded from straightening after tough trip.
No speed and soon at rear, 7 to 8Ls away on rails, always well back and struggling, no impression.
Ideally placed on the fence just behind leader, showed a smart chance of pace to surge into the lead inside 400M, kicked well clear and won its debut with total authority.
Restrained in a position behind midfield, fought on well between horses to take 2nd 50M from home but the winner had gone out of reach.
Heavily restrained from the off, raced 6-7Ls off the pace and was the last one turning in, found running room down the inside, ran on well final 200M to go 3rd close home.
Never far off the pace but caught 3-wide for the entire trip, rallied on and looked a place chance near 200M but turned flat in closing stages.
Handily placed in the group chasing the pace, hard driven 400M out and briefly threatened, couldn't sustain effort though and faded inside 150M.
Switched off to the rear and was given a waiting ride, swung wide for home, picked up gradually form off the pace but couldn't get close to the principles.
Well covered in mid-division, 4Ls down going into straight, stayed on fairly before running into a pocket with 80M to go.
Began with them, travelled 2-wide in midfield in a steadily-run race, out into clear 400M, ran on at the same pace and never looked likely.
Vied for the lead on the inside but found disappointingly little when placed under pressure 400M out.
Kept 4-wide in midfield and covered more ground than others, couldnt pick up when asked and finished off the race one-paced.
Dueled for the lead on the outside, outpaced passing 450M and soon dropped out of contention. (Lame right front leg.)
Chased the pace in a 3-wide position, moved to the lead approaching home straight, soon headed inside 400M and weakened tamely.
Rushed to a midfield position off the rail after a slow start, run ended 250M and gave ground rapidly.
Towards the rear, lost action and became badly unbalanced near 800M, never recovered and weakened rapidly on straightening. (To barrier trial around a bend.)

Settled just off the speed well within striking distance, came to challenge over 200 M out, gained upper hand about 100 M out, readily.
Began well, held narrow advantage to 200 M, fought on well until headed late.
Began well, soon settled in rear of midfield about 4Ls off the speed, came under pressure after coming onto course proper, ran on steadily to be nearest at finish.
Began with others, settled in midfield about 3Ls off the pace, quickened under pressure passing 200 M, unable to sustain effort close to home.
Bumped at the start, travelled in midfield down centre of the track, came under pressure passing 400 M but failed to quicken to threaten.
Began with others, held back to race just behind leaders, forced to check 300 M out, finished off nicely without threatening.
With leaders to 300 M, gradually weakened under pressure.
No Comments on Running information for this horse.
Never better than midfield, ran home one-paced under pressure.
Began awkwardly, soon dropped to last few, never a danger.
Prominent briefly, soon dropped back to worse than midfield, made no impression in the run home.
Began with others, with leaders to 350 M, dropped out tamely. (Questioned for disappointing performance.)
Soon outpaced, never in contention.
Began well, amongst leaders to halfway, dropped out under pressure inside final 300 M.
Settled about 3 back along the rails. Peeled out near the 200 M after gaining a split, grabbed victory in the shadows of the post.
Sent to the front along the paint. Fought to the line nicely.
Parked 1 out 1 back. Finished off gamely.
Worked forward to race outside the lead. Held its ground over the final stages.
Clipped heels early, settling 3 wide with cover behind midfield. Cornered wide but rallied to make the frame.
Raced handy to the leaders but was left racing 3 wide without cover on the circle. Stayed on despite covering extra ground.
Settled close to midfield 1 off with cover. Came deep on the home turn, worked home one paced.
Settled at the rear from a wide gate, 2 wide with cover. Ran on well down the outside.
Raced behind midfield, 2 deep with cover. Worked home soundly.
Camped worse than midfield the fence. kept on one paced in the run home.
Settled 3 back, 1 off with cover. Switched to the inside early in the straight but copped a check soon after and failed to recover.
Travelled near the tail of the field, 1 off with cover. Never a factor.
Settled with the backmakers along the fence. Failed to make any impression.
Enjoyed the run of the race in the box seat. Had no excuses weakening quickly after the furlong.
2-wide at midfield to home straight. Rallied on and took charge final 100 M.
Urged early and led on fence from 800 M. Not hurried top of home straight. Ridden out 300 M. Hung on well but failed to repel the winner final 100 M.
Sat behind midfield near the fence. Peeled out and was 4Ls down passing 400 M. Responded fairly well but couldn't quite catch the front pair.
Niggled early. Stayed ahead of midfield on fence before home straight. 3Ls away passing 400 M. Kept on steadily to make frame at line.
Ridden early but trapped wide. Slotted one-out-one-back from 800 M. Held ground in the straight and lost 4th final stride.
Soon taken to race 2-wide at rear from high draw. 8Ls back turning in. Made up good ground thereafter.
Crowded for room at start and raced at rear on fence. 8Ls adrift turning into home. Covered decent ground and steadied closing stages.
Quickly into stride. Took box seat approaching home turn. Well-positioned to strike in the straight but couldn't turn up a notch.
Began awkwardly. Raced towards rear near the fence to home straight. Made up minor ground thereafter.
Driven up early and settled one-off behind the leader passing 800 M. Hard ridden from 400 M but no response. Faded gradually final furlong.
3-wide towards rear. Never progressed.
2 to 3-wide behind midfield early. Wide and without cover from 800 M. Dropped out despite effort of rider 300 M out.
Fair break, midfield one off, back to fourth last entering straight, mid track challenge, got up near line.
Fair break, no rush early, back to fourth last two off, improved wide turn, challenge down centre, led 50 M out, just nailed.
Well away, up on outside to third one off, challenged and led narrowly mid straight, driven, no extra.
Fair break, not rushed, back to third last rail, second last into straight, improved between horses, never quite able to challenge.
Fast away out wide, led and clear after 450 M, steadied in front, kicked early straight, ran out of steam late.
Fair break, no early pace, slight check first turn, improved wide home turn, kept on one pace.
Missed break, lost length, up on rail to midfield, went for rail run, no gap, kept on well late.
Out fast, led, headed, settled fourth on rail, ridden early straight, no extra.
Good break, fifth one off, effort early straight, one pace.
Moderate start out wide, no early pace, last by four lengths far side, closed up turn, some improvement very late.
Level break, up to share lead, then second rail head in air, ridden early straight, no progress.
Well away, up on rail to fourth, lost ground turn, slight check early straight, ridden, found nothing.
Fair break, midfield but three wide, improved turn, third early straight, run petered out.
Fair break, joined battle for lead but then outpaced, ridden entering straight, weakened late.
Back to rear from wide draw, improved steadily round field, ran on strongly to lead 200 M out, finished well.
Jumped well, eased to one off two lengths back, forward move turn, led briefly 200 M out, rallied when joined by winner, no extra last 50 M.
Eased to rear one off, forward move to track winner turn, battled on and still making ground at line but no kick.
Jumped with head in air, unbalanced early, settled last, on heels, very wide turn, ran on steadily mid straight.
Taken back to midfield two off, forward move to tackle winner straight, kept on until run flattened 250 M out.
Jumped well, led one off, headed on inside, went on again turn, led into straight, weakened when headed 300 M out.
Missed break, taken back to fourth last rail, short of room mid straight, kept on once clear.
Well away but wide, could never get nearer rail than three wide, ridden early straight, kept on.
Well away, up to share lead, headed entering turn, ridden, not quicken.
Slow into stride, ridden early, rail midfield, bustled, no progress under pressure.
Fair break, slight bobble early, midfield one off, no progress straight.
Good break, taken back from wide draw but always two or three wide, driven, found little.
Well away, share of early lead out wide, back to fourth, weakened.
Clumsy out of gate, up on rail to third, ridden, found nothing.
In front of midfield, 3-1/2Ls off the leader 2-wide, not suited by the slow pace, dashed strongly 300 M to score.
Settled outside the lead, enjoyed the very slow early tempo, ran on well to the line for 2nd.
Pushed to sit in midfield, 4-1/2Ls off the leader 3-wide, dashed strongly 250 M despite not suited by the very slow pace and grabbed 3rd.
Took rail easily and led by 1L at very slow sectionals, overhauled 300 M, just ran on for 4th.
Prominent, 2Ls off the leader 2-wide, benefited by the very slow pace, however no turn of foot in straight.
Very slow away, behind midfield along the fence, 6-1/2Ls off the leader, not suited by the slow tempo, just held ground in straight.
Hard ridden to keep up in midfield, 4-1/2Ls off the leader on the fence, harmed by the very slow sectionals, no turn of foot in final stages.
Pushed to occupy a midfield spot along the fence, 3Ls off the leader, not suited by the slow pace, flattened 300 M.
Eased to sit in midfield, 5-1/2Ls off the leader 2-wide, not suited by the very slow tempo, no progress.
Eased back, 8Ls off the leader along the fence, harmed by the very slow pace, no progress.
Eased back, trapped 3-wide, harmed by the very slow pace, never competitive.
Eased back, not suited by the very slow pace, never competitive.
Eased to take box seat, raced very keenly, dropped off 400 M.
Eased back, raced 3 to 4-wide, never a factor and tailed out.
Good break, tracked over from low draw, midfield and ridden mid track, responded very gamely to driving, just got up.
Not best away, soon up to second rank, going well, quickened, led, just unable to hold winner.
Out fast, tracked across to rail, led 200 M out, just collared.
Fair break, not rushed early, back to midpack six lengths off lead, ridden, ran on well without threatening.
Fair break, slight nudge early, three lengths off lead mid track, ridden, kept on, not pace to challenge.
Moderate break, soon improved to join leaders rail, ridden midway, outpaced.
Fair break, short of pace, could not improve.
Fair break, early speed out wide, two lengths clear halfway, ridden, weakened.
Fair break, not go early pace, tracked rail leader, ridden and made some ground late.
Fair break, not go early pace, ridden halfway, no progress.
Awkward start lost two lengths, second last tracking midfield bunch, then out to challenge but found nil.
Fair break, ridden early, gradually outpaced.
Broke well, up with front rank, found nothing when asked, eased late.
Reared and lost five lengths start, never a factor thereafter.
Keen in early stages but had a smooth run along the inside once settled, picked up strongly from midfield entering 400 M, came through horses to lead inside 100 M and finished willingly.
Behind midfield and travelled strongly throughout, responded well and came with a sweeping run, briefly led near 100 M but was outrun by the winner in late stages.
Settled along the 2-path in midfield, gradually picked up to go 3rd close home without threatening the top 2 which drew well clear.
Tracked leader in a truly run race, moved to the lead 350 M but hung out under pressure and was headed nearing 100 M.
Never far off the pace but was 3-wide without cover throughout, kept on well enough in straight considering the tough early run.
Handily placed in 4th, loomed up early in straight but couldn't sustain his effort, weakened inside 150 M.
Switched off to last and over 10Ls behind leader in a strung out field, switched wide inside 600 M, had plenty to do off the bend, made some progress final 300 M but offered little threat.
Settled midfield in the 2-path, made a short lived effort in straight and turned flat passing 200 M.
Positioned towards the rear about 10Ls behind leader, kept on same pace inside 400 M and never threatened.
Towards the rear in a strung out field, couldn't step up a gear and never looked like reaching the horses in front.
Over 10Ls off the pace in last pair, taken wide passing 700 M to commence his run but made very limited progress from 400 M, no extra in late stages.
Took them along at a decent pace then gave way rapidly inside 350 M.
Tracked leader prominently after crossing from draw 14, found little under pressure and weakened tamely inside 400 M, tailed off.
Taken to a midfield position off the rail, struggled to keep up inside 500 M, weakened rapidly and finished tailed off.
Fair break, settled fifth on rail, took time to get organized in straight, then surged powerfully to win going away.
Fair break, back to midfield rail, got first run on winner to lead, then unable to resist.
Fair break, midfield two off, followed first two through in straight but unable to make further ground on either.
Fast out, then reined back but still held out three wide, made ground wide in straight, kept on very well.
Fast out, then slightly outpaced and back to midfield one off, kept on mid track in straight but not able to trouble leaders.
Sluggish start, bustled to take rail just back of midfield, kept on well down centre of track.
Well away, up to join leaders three wide, taken back to third one off, challenged mid straight, easily brushed aside.
Taken back from wide gate, second last rail, improved along rail straight, ran on well.
Fair break, up on inside to share lead, led early straight, no extra once headed.
Fair break but lacked early pace, ridden up to fourth on rail, blocked for run mid straight, not find much when clear.
Moderate break, mid to rear two wide, wide into straight, one pace.
Fair break, lacked early pace, rear group one off, ridden, no progress.
Taken back from wide draw, two lengths last leaving back, urged, ridden, no response.
Well away, led one off, unable to cross, began to weaken mid straight, stopped quickly, eased.
Out well, camped on leaders back, had good run to bend, improved from behind horses at 400 M, took over inside 250 M and did well to hold off a strong finish.
Box seated throughout 1 out 1 back, had all favours in run, loomed passed 300 M just off leader, chased hard but couldn't pair back light weighted rival.
Sluggish start, raced at rear, urged entering turn, ran on very well out wide.
No early speed, occupied spot in rear division 8Ls back early, set a job with plenty to do turning, closed soundly making many lengths to turning.
Positioned behind midfield from an awkward alley, 2 wide 6Ls back in mid-section, gradually improved turning, kept on well late to be nearest on line.
Little early speed, back with last few throughout nearly 10Ls from lead, had too much to do turning, kept making ground to be closest at finish.
Began in line, raced midfield on rails 4 to 5Ls away, used little in run and saved ground turning in, kept on OK without seriously threatening.
Missed break, lost length, back to second last one off, last into straight, kept on but never a threat.
Began well enough, pressed on but posted 2 to 3 wide throughout, 1L down when challenging rounding bend, led briefly but had no extra final 250 M, faded.
First into stride, led easily rolled along 2Ls clear on bend, had a 1L advantage rounding bend, couldn't lift when challenged, dropped off.
Positive from outset, sat outside leader and ensured OK tempo early, 1L back turning, folded easily when challenged 250 M, dropped off easily.
Out nicely, trapped wide and forced to go forward, caught 3 wide without cover 3Ls back, improved 4 wide turning, stopped passing 300 M when workload took toll.
Out with rest, raced 3 wide in midfield 5 to 6Ls back, had cover to bend, ordinary close and didn't factor.

Settled one-out-one-back in 3rd, commenced move turning in, soon hit front upon straightening, careered away for an easy victory.
Settled in midfield of a small field within 3Ls of lead, shaken up to challenge upon straightening, ran on steadily without quickening.
Began moderately, travelled in 4th on rails about 2Ls off the speed, in similar one-back position on rails turning for home, failed to quicken to threaten in straight.
Disputed lead on rails far side, moved half a length clear around the bend, headed into straight, found nothing under pressure.
Began moderately, behind midfield most of way, produced some late impression under pressure in straight.
Niggled along at the back, saved ground turning in, kept on past well beaten horses.
Travelled mainly just worse than midfield, in similar position turning in, ran home one-paced.
Always struggling at the back.
A joint leader far side, raced outside lead around the bend, dropped out tamely soon after straightening.
Parked behind midfield towards the centre of the track. Commenced to make good ground near the 200m and grabbed victory close to the line.
Tightened on jumping but soon recovered to track the leader along the outside rail. Hit the front near the 100m, but was collared late.
Worked forward and crossed to lead along the grandstand side. Was under pressure after the 400m, but failed to find any extra at the business end.
Camped behind the speed, 3-4 off the outside fence. Kept on well to the post.
Bumped soon after the start, settling midfield on the outside rail. Made steady ground right to the wire.
Got cover behind the leaders along the grandstand side. Was briefly held up near the 200m, held its ground thereafter.
Crowded at the start settling worse than midfield near the centre of the track. Drifted in over the concluding stages finishing off soundly.
Raced in a forward position close to the centre of the course. Tired gradually in the final stages.
Rated close to midfield towards the outside rail. Maintained an even gallop to the finish.
Began awkwardly racing along the grandstand side behind midfield. Was dour in the run home.
Was prominent in the run near the centre of the track. Began to fade after the final 300m.
Travelled about midfield with cover. Commenced to give ground inside the last furlong.
Jumped on terms then settled midfield with cover, towards the centre of the track. Was a beaten horse after the 400m.
Was steadied soon after the start settling towards the rear. Failed to close off.
2-wide in leading section early. Led solo on fence at 900M and held a 1L advantage turning in. Lengthened the gap passing 300M. Tiring but hung on for a narrow victory.
Began well but was caught wide. Taken to race 4-wide at midfield until home straight. Fought on determinedly to make up substantial ground from the tiring winner. Just denied at post.
Slow to begin. Soon driven along the fence and raced towards rear. Checked passing 600M. Came 4-wide and was 8Ls adrift passing 400M. Made up many lengths to finish 3rd.
2-wide behind midfield until home turn. Peeled out gradually and was 5Ls down turning home. Progressed steadily to the line to make frame without threatening the front trio.
Raced within 3Ls of the pace in a 2-wide position through to home straight. One-paced to conclude.
Slow to begin. Urged along to stay towards rear. Took inside run and was 6Ls off rounding home turn. Covered good ground in the straight.
Niggled early and raced 3-wide ahead of midfield to home straight. Couldn't quicken when the race got serious passing 400M. Stayed ahead of beaten runners home.
3-wide in the leading section early. Taken to sit 2-wide behind the leader from 900M. Hard ridden top of home straight but gave very limited response. Weakened 100M.
Midfield on fence. Shifted out for clear run home straight but couldn't turn up a notch.
Trapped 4-wide behind the pace group early. Improved to 3-wide behind the leader home turn. No extra final 300M.
3-wide behind midfield until swung wide to challenge on straightening. Vigorously ridden but found nothing. Beaten well before home.
Dropped to rear after start. Some headway home turn but no further impression in the straight. (Substantial amount of blood in horse's trachea.)
Always at rear. Detached leaving the bend and finished tailed out.
In front rank before weakened rapidly passing 700M. Finished tailed out.
Moderate break, bustled up to take fourth on rail, found gap between two leaders mid straight, led, held on.
Well away, led early, then settled third one off, challenged 250m out, just held by winner.
Well away, not rushed early, midfield two off, urged into turn, brought mid track, ran on well.
Good break, but not pace to lead, settled third one off, out to challenge early straight, weakened late.
Well away, beaten for early speed, settled sixth rail, fifth into straight, ridden, no more progress.
Fair break, taken back to second last, kept to inside straight, kept on well without threatening.
Slight bobble start, rushed up on inside to lead after 300m, led until headed 300m out, weakened.
Fair break, no early speed, urged midfield rail, smack at turn, ridden, no progress.
Good break but held wide, back to third last, ridden straight, minor progress late.
Fluffed start, back to last urged, last into straight, passed beaten horses late.
Fair break, up wide to share fourth, gradually lost ground, eased late.
Moderate break, hurried early but only reached midfield one off, weakened.
Fast away out wide, led and crossed, hard ridden in straight, gamely kept challengers at bay.
Well away, ridden to hold place among leaders, up to second one off, harried winner all the way to the line.
Well away, up on rail to settle third, challenged between winner and runner-up, no extra last 50m.
Well away, not involved in early lead battle, settled sixth one off, ridden early straight, kept on one pace.
Fair break, rail midfield, kept on straight without ever threatening.
Fair break, up on rail to fifth, sixth into straight, driven, no progress.
Well away, taken back but only as far as midfield, three off, wide into straight, shaken up, late progress.
Not fast away, held up fourth last on rail, kept on, no threat.
Not fast away, held up second last, wide run, little progress.
Fair break, midfield one off, tried to challenge between horses, no kick.
Taken back from wide draw, two lengths last into turn, shaken up early straight, wide run, no impact.
Moderate start, bustled but third last one off, ridden entering straight, driven, no response.
Fair break, back to midfield but still stuck out wide, ridden, weakened.
Fair break, tried to compete for lead from wide, fourth two off, bid early straight, weakened, eased.
Settled in front, 1.5Ls off the leader 2 wide, not suited by the fast early sectionals, closed the race off strongly 250M and won.
Hard ridden early to keep up with the field, 7.5Ls off the leader on the rails, benefited by the fast pace, lacked room 400M, progressed steadily when clear and ran 2nd.
Behind midfield, 4LS off the leader 2 wide, helped by the fast pace, made ground 300M and took 3rd.
Eased early and trapped very wide, pressed forward 1000M to sit outside the lead, used up too much fuel during the fast early sections, ran on well until 150M flattened.
Hard ridden to occupy the box seat, not suited by the fast tempo, out of fuel 200M.
Hard ridden early to keep up with the field, more than 8Ls off the leader on the fence, benefited by the fast pace, progressed steadily 200M.
Pushed forward, 2.5Ls off the fast pace 2 wide, flattened 200 M.
Eased back, 5Ls off the leader along the fence, benefited by the fast pace, just held ground in straight.
Midfield, 3.5Ls off the leader, trapped 3 wide, favoured by the fast tempo, no progress in final stages.
Pushed forward, 2.5Ls off the fast pace 2 wide, lacked turn of foot in straight, flattened 200M.
Pushed to taka the rail and led by 0.5L at fast sectionals, emptied 300M.
In front of midfield, 2.5Ls off the fast pace, dropped off in straight.
Pushed early, suited by the fast pace, never better than midfield.
Never competitive at rear.
Well away, settled fourth one off, out to challenge mid straight, led 100m out, ran on well.
Fast away, wide first turn, led and crossed, fought on very well in straight, caught last 100m.
Fair break but three wide first turn, settled fifth last, wide challenge, finished well.
Fair break, very wide first turn, circled field into second one off, sustained challenge straight, fought on well.
Well away, up on rail into third, then nudged out by inside runner, settled fifth one off, challenged outside, not sustain run.
Fast away, led, taken back to third n rail, every chance when aimed for gap between leaders, no kick.
Taken back, held up second last, went for run between horses straight, ran on well but not dangerous, checked late.
Fair break, four wide first turn, held up third last, short of room mid straight, kept on well.
Slow into stride, not rushed early, settled rear one off, last into straight, brought wide, not pace to challenge.
Taken back to fourth last rail, ridden, no real improvement.
Missed break, rushed up on rail to fourth, slight check, settled fifth, pumped along, found nothing straight.
Towards the rear and given a patient ride, picked up strongly when clear 300M, surged to the lead near 100M and drew clear.
6Ls back in midfield and well covered, crept closer passing 500M, quickened well in the drive but had no answer to the winner's late surge.
Led reluctantly from 1200M to avoid racing wide, all out inside 250M, headed 100M from home.
Within striking distance throughout, loomed up as a possible danger 300M but couldnt sustain effort and turned flat in late stages.
Fractious in stalls and lost considerable amount of ground at the start, towards the rear throughout, came home well under hard pressure final 200M.
Travelled 3-wide without cover in midpack, had his chance but lacked further response going into 300M, one paced in 2nd half of the straight.
Dropped back and tucked into a 3-wide position towards the rear, shaken up passing 600M, stayed on down the outside without threatening.
Slightly slow out, soon taken to the rail and improved to midfield, kept to inside throughout and made some progress late on.
Led early then sat one back behind leader, run ended near 300M and weakened away. (Lame next day.)
Rushed along early to hold a rail position ahead of midfield, kept on same pace to line and could not land a serious blow.
Raced at the tail of the field after a slow start, had plenty to do turning in but stayed on only fairly, never a factor.
Prominently ridden from the outset and chased leader, found little under pressure in straight, dropped off rapidly final 150 M.
Placed 2-wide in midfield, travelled only fairly and had to be niggled along over the home turn, kept on same pace and was eased passing 200M. (Jockey expressed concern over the horse's action.)
Never better than midfield, gave ground rapidly inside 400M, soon behind.
Well away, third on rail going well, shaken up entering straight, challenged between horses, ran on strongly for comfortable win.
Fair break, lacked early pace, back to second last one off, improved turn, run between horses, finished well.
Well away out wide, sat on leader's shoulder, led 400m out until headed by winner.
Fast away but caught wide, settled fourth one off, kept on well straight but not pace to challenge.
Sluggish start, last early, up along rail to mid/rear, ran on well to finish on heels of placed horses.
Well away, led after 400m, headed mid straight, weakened.
Away well but not pace to join leaders, settled midfield rail, urged along straight, no real progress.
Bobbled start, last and wide early, on heels turn, but kept on quite well.
Fair break, not much early pace, back to third last one off, wide into straight, kept on.
Fair break, pushed along early, midfield run straight, up to fifth, weakened.
Sluggish start, pumped along early, up on outside for wide bid, flattened out late.
Fair break, back to second last but four wide, ridden along, found nothing, tailed off.
Away nicely, up just off speed closer to middle, improved at 350 M, joined in strongly and dashed away final furlong to record an easy win.
OK away, tracked speed 2Ls away on stand side, improved at 300 M, kept on soundly but found winner far too strong.
Good early speed, shared lead towards stand side, prominent throughout, couldn't lift at 250 M and just held ground.
Standard beginning, sat behind speed between middle and stand side, 2 to 3Ls back throughout, kept on at same speed to make frame.
Bounced out well, ended up midfield or worse along stand side, 5Ls back and midpoint, just held ground late.
No real early speed, next to last on stand side 6 to 7Ls back, gave a start but did best work late making ground to be nearest on line.
Little speed early, behind midfield between middle and stand side, improved to midpoint, 4Ls down at 300 M, kept on OK without threatening.
Lacked usual dash, behind midfield near to middle, 6Ls down at midpoint, didn't find much in run to line.
Bumped early, ended up in midfield towards centre of course, fair run throughout, bumped 400 M, lacked extra gear final 300 M and flattened final furlong.
Prominent early sharing lead towards stand side, in mix until 300 M, didn't find when pressure applied, folded tamely.
Didn't jump with usual pace, tracked speed group 3Ls back closer to middle of course, bumped at 400 M, little extra at business end.
No early speed, at rear on stand side, outpaced for majority, never likely.
Behind midfield on stand side, niggled by midpoint, gradually faded.
Positioned ahead of midfield but unable to tuck in from a wide barrier, strongly challenged inside 400M and showed a determined attitude to edge out the 2nd and 3rd just before the line.
At the hindquarters of the leader and enjoyed the run of the race, battled on gamely to the line and was only beaten by the narrowest possible margin.
Led and dictated the tempo, rallied on well when challenged passing 400M, narrowly beaten.
Dropped back to the rear after the start, saved ground on the inside but had trouble getting a clear run on straightening, ran on strongly when clear 200M and finished nearest at the line.
With leader early then dropped back to race in chasing group, had every chance, kept on to the line but lacked a further response.
Behind midfield, well covered but endured a rough passage nearing 1000M, finished off the race reasonably well.
Settled behind midfield after a slow start, had to be nudged along 500M out, ran on one-paced on straightening.
Placed in midfield off the rail, kept on same pace in the drive home.
Handily placed off the rail just behind leader, lacked further response when the race got serious, turned flat in late stages.
Positioned in midfield 3-wide, ran on fairly without threatening the principals.
Raced in midpack, not helped by the slow early pace and proved difficult to settle down the back straight, kept on until run ended 150M from home.
Dropped back to the rear of the field and had plenty to do turning in, made some progress down the outside but never looked like catching the horses in front.
Switched off to last and given a patient ride, hard driven inside 400M but made limited progress only.
Awkwardly away, moved forward to be prominent behind leading pair but raced 3-wide without cover, run ended near 350M and weakened away rapidly. (Irregular Heart Rhythm.)

Gradually moved up to dispute lead, took over 1100 M out, led until coming out of back straight, re-gained lead turning in and soon drew clear, won readily.
Began well, settled just better than midfield on rails, shaken up to challenge entering straight, ran on steadily to be closest at finish.
Began with others, settled in mid-division, picked up late to produce good impression inside final 200 M.
Bumped at start, gradually settled at or around midfield, saved ground turning in, ran home one-paced.

Soon taken across in rear after beginning from a wide barrier, made gradual headway far side, saved ground around home bend to reach mid-division turning for home, kept on without quickening under pressure.
Soon taken across in rear after beginning from the widest barrier, remained in last few, saved ground turning in, kept on steadily without threatening.
Broke well, led early stages, settled just of the pace to straight, kept on under pressure without finding any extra inside final 200 M.
Well there early, gradually settled in 4th about 3Ls off the speed, made early move to take up running around the bend, unable to sustain short-lived effort and soon overhauled upon straightening.
Close up, led briefly after first time past the post, ceded advantage to eventual winner 1100 M out, in similar position but became 3rd going up Rock, dropped out tamely after straightening.
Raced wide without cover towards the rear, widest runner turning in, made no impression in the run home.
Tightened at start, gradually shuffled back to last few before stables bend, remained well behind thereafter. (Lame.)
Settled behind midfield, towards rear most of far side and home bend, found nil in the run home.
Box seated in the run. Rolled out on the final bend, and kept up its workload to hold off a late challenge.
Settled behind midfield, 1 off with cover. Circled the field after the 450 M and ran on well only to come up marginally short.
Made his run from better than midfield, 1 off with cover. Rallied 4-wide and maintained an even gallop right to the finish.
Raced at the tail of the field with cover. Kept to the inside and closed off well to make the frame.
Worked forward to settle outside the leader. Had every chance, weakening over the latter stages.
Sent forward to lead along the paint. Under pressure from the 300 M, faded over the final stages.
Parked 3 back the rail. Found little when asked for an effort in the final stages.
Travelled at the rear, 2-wide with cover. Worked home fairly without threatening.
Camped midfield, 2 deep with cover. Peeled out turning into the home straight, one paced over the final stages.
Raced with the backmakers but was caught wide for most of the run without cover. Never a factor
Travelled midfield the fence. Cornered 3-wide, but failed to find any extra in the run to the line.
Settled worse than midfield the fence. Struggled in the home straight. (Reported to be lame the following day.)
Moderate start. 3-wide at midfield through to home turn. Swung out to improve and was 3Ls down passing 400 M. Finished off strongly and always had enough to repel rivals.
Soon taken to race 2-wide at rear from high draw. Commenced run outside from 500 M and was 5Ls away into final stretch. Kept on impressively but found the winner too strong.
Trapped wide and without cover behind pace group through to home straight. Ran on fairly well to snatch 3rd at line.
Well enough away. Elected to sit behind leaders through to home straight. In traffic until shifted out for daylight at 200 M. Closed off strongly and was nearest at finish. Promising debut.

Soon in front rank but caught 3-wide and overaced. Gradually eased 2-wide behind leaders from the Rock. Hung on well early home straight until no extra to threaten the top pair 200 M out. Just failed to make frame on line.

Away in line. Gradually taken to sit 2-wide towards rear from first turn. Peeled out to challenge and was 4Ls off on straightening. Progressed steadily but failed to find extra gear to stay in the battle close home.
Slow to begin. Stayed towards rear on fence. Shuffled to last passing 500 M and was 7Ls adrift leaving the bend. Made up good ground late.
Nice jump but trapped widest. Eased to 3-wide at rear first turn. Came wide and was 7Ls back rounding home turn. Covered good ground in the straight.
Handy position near the fence behind the speed through to home straight. Failed to quicken thereafter.
Last out. Resumed to 2-wide behind midfield first turn. Badly held up rounding home turn and top of home straight. Not really tested.
Travelled wide and without cover in the leading section until dropped out 250 M.
Led on fence until faded 250 M out.
Fair break, ridden up to take fifth one off, ridden entering turn, wide into straight, really hit stride 250 M out, led, drew away.
Out fast, fourth on rail, challenged for lead alongside winner, overpowered late.
Out well, taken back to seventh rail, moved up entering straight, not go pace of first two.
Fair break, ridden up to lead after first turn, headed early straight, fought on but no chance with first two.
Out fast, led early, headed leaving first turn, led narrowly entering straight, weakened.
Taken back to fourth last one off, improved exiting back, kept on but never threatened.
Taken back to second last one off, improved turn, kept on wide without being able to threaten.
Good break, fourth one off, ridden into turn, no progress, weakened late.
Unhurried start, back to rear rail, wide bid straight, passed only beaten horses.
Fair break, short of early pace, back to fifth last rail, driven turn, no progress.
Missed break, lost length, up on rail to sixth, ridden early straight, weakened.
Fair break, no early speed, second last rail, ridden exiting back, found nothing.
Flew the gate, length clear after 100 M, kicked early straight, never headed.
Broke well, sat on leader's shoulder early, left behind early straight, kept on well and closing close home.
Moderate break, up to midfield rail, overracing, ran on straight without being able to get to leader.
Broke well, third on rail, kept on along rail, outpaced by first three.
Reared start losing two lengths, up along rail to midfield, kept on well straight.
Well away out wide, but caught wide and back through field, ran on steadily on outside.
Away well, kept clear of traffic midfield three wide, ridden straight, no improvement.
Slightly awkward start, third last one off, ridden turn, kept on but no real improvement straight.
Fair break but no early speed, back to last urged, picked up a little under pressure but never a factor.
Fair break, slight stumble, up to third one off, wide into straight, weakened.
Fair break but caught four wide, never a factor.
Fair break but caught five wide, never near leaders, eased late.
Pushed forward, just off the good pace 2-wide, closed the race off strongly 300 M to score a 4th goal over the course and distance.
Midfield, 4Ls off the good pace 2 to 3-wide, progressed steadily 300 M for 2nd.
Very slow away, 8Ls behind the good pace 2-wide, made steadily ground final 200 M to grab 3rd.
Eased to sit behind midfield, 5-1/2Ls off the good pace 2-wide, progressed steadily 200 M.
More prominent without using much, 2-1/2Ls off the good pace 2-wide, just held ground in straight.
Hard ridden to keep up in midfield, 4Ls off the good pace on the fence, ran on fairly in final stages.
Eased back, 6-1/2Ls off the good pace along the fence, made minor ground 100 M.
Pushed to obtain the box seat, pace good, emptied 300 M.
Pushed forward, 1-1/2Ls off the good pace, trapped 3-wide throughout and lost too much ground, weakened 250 M.
Eased back, 8Ls behind the good pace, trapped 3-wide throughout and lost too much ground, lacked turn of foot in straight.
Pushed early but failed to cross in front, 3Ls off the good pace, trapped 3 to 4-wide throughout and lost too much ground, hung in and raced flat in straight.
Hard ridden to take the rail and led by 1L at good pace, soon dropped off 350 M.
Fair break, taken back, held up last, launched down middle straight, finished fast to win going away.
Well away, ridden up on outside to share lead first turn, then settled second one off, led briefly mid straight until winner swept past.
Smartly away, found good position one off in fourth, steadied far side, squeezed between horses for rail gap, just outpaced.
Quick start, but midfield three wide first turn, up to fourth entering straight, hard ridden and led momentarily 150 M out, weakened last 50 M.
Not fast away but found rail midfield going well, no run available mid straight, unbalanced, made some ground once extracted from pocketed.
Well away, settled midfield one off, held up and back through field, shaken up turn, ran on well but just outpaced.
Moderate start, not hurried and settled second last one off, wide into straight, kept on quite well.
Well away, led early then back to third on rail, went for rail run in straight, hard ridden, no extra.
Away well, led on rail first turn, uncontested until straight, swamped 300 M out, weakened.
Moderate start, settled fourth last on rail, urged leaving back, no progress.
Broke well, front rank early then back to fourth last one off, improved leaving back, run flattened right out, eased last 50 M.
Settled near last, commenced his run nearing 400 M, put in a sustained effort in the drive home and got up just in time.
Went forward to press the pace, wide till 1100 M then tracked leader one out one back to straight, challenged strongly from 300 M and briefly led, galloped on in late stages and was just caught.
Towards the rear along the fence, held up near the entrance of the straight, came through horses inside 200 M and finished with a late flourish.

Obtained a fence position in midfield after a slow start, moved up to challenge on the inside approaching home straight, kept on well to the post and was just edged out by the top 3 in a close finish.
Switched off to last about 6 to 7Ls behind leader, moved away from fence inside 350 M for a clear path, finished off strongly final 200 M and narrowly missed out on a placing.
In mid-division 3-wide and ran on well to the line under top weight, not beaten far.
Crossed to the lead passing 1200 M and set a decent pace upfront, all out leaving the home bend, weakened final 150 M and was swamped late.
Broke well and sat handily behind the pace, shaken up passing 400 M, gave all in his final career start but couldn't quite get to the leaders.
Held up in midfield, had his chance but lacked further response when the race got serious final 200 M.
Quickly into stride and sat in the slipstream of leader, found disappointingly little turning in and weakened away 200 M.
Placed 3-wide in the group chasing the pace and was left without cover from 1100 M, outpaced inside 300 M and had no extra to offer under pressure.
Positioned 3-wide towards the rear, soon behind coming off the bend, eased.

Began with others, settled wide in rear of midfield, one of the widest turning for home, ran home well to win readily.
Travelled in midfield on rails, saved ground to get closer up turning in, quickened under pressure to hit front over 100 M out only to be caught final strides.

Ridden along from the start to eventually take up running approaching home bend, crossed for rails run and soon joined around the bend, came under pressure when over 2Ls clear over 200 M out, unable to sustain effort close home.
Contested lead early, settled one-back in 3rd, remained similar turning into straight, kept on same pace without quickening.
Began with others, soon settled towards the rear, went widest turning for home, made good progress down centre of straight to be nearest at finish.
Raced in midfield, awkwardly placed close to heels when forced to shift out around the bend, held same when wider entering straight, worked home steadily without quickening.
Settled in midfield on rails, kept on same pace to the line.
Disputed lead early, settled in 4th about 3Ls off the speed, shuffled further back around the bend, ran home one-paced under pressure.
Soon dropped to the rear, took closer order around the bend saving ground turning in, fought on steadily down inner of straight to be nearest at finish.
Raced 3-wide without cover in midfield, remained similar turning in, soon weakened after straightening.
Bumped start, urged along to hold a fence position 7Ls behind the leader, responded only fairly when asked for efforts final 450 M, failed to make up any ground.

Began from a wide barrier, remained wide in midfield down far side, improved to a one-out-one-back spot coming out of back straight and dispute lead into home straight, soon weakened after straightening.
Always struggling in tail-end. (Mucus.)
Opened up a commanding break in the early stages and never looked like being headed, making every post a winner.
Rated worse than midfield, along the fence. Maintained a rail advantage in the home straight and closed off well.
Raced near the rear of the field, 2 deep with cover. Made good progressive ground in the run to the wire.
Tracked the leader a distant 2nd, battled on to make the frame.
Raced with the backmakers, 3 wide, with some cover. Made good late ground during the backend of the race.
Made its run from behind midfield, 1 off with cover. Worked home evenly along the inside.
Posted 3 wide without cover on the circle, in a handy position. One paced in the final stretch.
Slow to begin settling with the backmarkers, 2-3 wide with cover. Wound up nicely in the straight without threatening.
Parked behind a good speed on the rail. Had nothing left in the tank after the 100m.
Tracked the tear away leader 1 off the rail. Had every chance, fading over the last 250m.
Raced at the tail of the field along the paint. Was dour in the run to the line.
Was niggled for most of trip but failed to keep in touch whilst racing midfield 2 deep. Produced nothing when placed under pressure in the run home. (Heart irregularity.)
Raced prominently but coursed wide & without cover, hanging out for most of the trip. Struggled in the home straight.
Travelled with the tailenders 1 off with cover. Finished well back. (To trial.)
Midfield on fence through to home straight. 5Ls behind the lead at 400M. Fought on determinedly to charge down the runaway leader final 100M. Kept on to score with some comfort.

Began well and raced outside the speed early. Sat 4Ls behind the leader which made run home turn. Chased strongly in the straight to catch the leader final 100M but couldn't repel the winner close home.
Behind midfield near the fence until home straight. Shifted out and was 10Ls back passing 400M. Made up many lengths to snatch 3rd at line.
Well enough away but caught wide. Taken to race 3-wide behind midfield from 1200M. Swung out and was 9Ls off on straightening. Covered considerable ground to make frame at post.
Soon taken to rear from high draw. 10Ls adrift turning in. Made up good ground thereafter but couldn't sustain its effort closing stages.
Travelled wide and without cover at midfield. 6-7Ls away into final stretch. Rallied but peaked 100M.
Crowded for room and lost ground at start. Niggled early to race 2-wide at midfield. 8Ls down leaving the bend. Progressed steadily in the straight without threatening the principals.
Driven early and took lead at 1200M. Attempted to make all passing 600M and held a 4Ls advantage turning home. Hung on until overhauled final 100M.
Prominent spot through to home straight. Failed to quicken when asked.
Began in line but trapped widest. Gradually taken to race 2-wide towards rear. Over 10Ls to make up rounding home turn. Minor headway in the straight to beat tired runners.
One-out-one-back until no extra to stay forward top of home straight.
Behind midfield early. Dropped towards rear home turn. No real improvement in the straight.
Broke well, prominently placed 3Ls off the speed, quickened well when asked at the top of home straight, finished off soundly, hung out final 100 M, hit the front in last few strides.
Taken to a fence position from gate 6 and travelled 3-4Ls off the speed, responded well under pressure final 350 M, finished off soundly for 2nd.
Settled in midfield on 3-wide, crept closer when pace slackened in the middle stages, responded well when asked early in home straight, hung out under pressure, finished off soundly for 3rd.
Urged along to share the lead on rails, quickened well at the top of home straight, kept on under pressure, caught near 100 M out, remained one-paced.
Urged along to occupy a fence position 2Ls behind the leader, responded fairly when asked final 400 M, rather one-paced.
Pushed hard early to hold a one-off position in midfield, took time to pick up early in home straight, finished off strongly final 200 M, too late.
Restrained in a one-off spot 5Ls behind the speed, travelled keenly in the early stages, checked at 1400M and 1200M, shifted wider to improve at home turn, made up ground steadily final 300 M.
Niggled along early and soon shared the lead in a one-off position, held ground until flattened at 250 M.
Taken rearward from gate 9 and ended up travelling 5-6Ls off the pace, shifted wider for home, made up gradual ground when placed under pressure final 400 M.
Widely drawn, taken back and soon found the fence just behind the midfield, gave very limited response when asked for efforts in home straight, failed to make any progress.
Raced handy easily, gave limited response when asked at the top of home straight, failed to hold ground, soon faded.
Settled just off the pace early, travelled 3-wide with no cover, responded only fairly when asked early in home straight, failed to keep up final 250 M, soon faded.
Caught 4-wide with no cover in midfield throughout the trip, failed to keep up final 300 M, well beaten. (Lame right fore.)
Lacked early speed despite being urged along, at the rear throughout, never competitive.
Settled 1L behind the leader on rails, kicked strongly when asked at the top of home straight and soon hit the front, kept on, did well enough to withhold the challengers. (Lost left front plate.)
Slow away, given a waiting ride as usual and travelled about 9Ls off the speed, quickened well final 350 M when placed under pressure, finished off soundly for 2nd, just late.
Settled 7Ls off the pace, swung widest for home, ran on strongly down centre of home straight, finished off soundly for 3rd.
Easily ran up to lead 1L, caught at 350 M out but still kept on well under pressure, could not find extra final 50 M, just missed a place.
Awkward start, niggled along early and soon caught up 2Ls behind the leader, kept on under pressure early in home straight, could not find extra final 50 M, just lost a place.
Driven to hold a fence position in midfield, only one-paced when asked for efforts final 350 M, never really troubled the principals. (Lost left front plate.)
Settled 2Ls off the speed on rails, hung out at home turn, only one-paced when asked in straight.
Settled 4Ls off the pace, travelled satisfactorily on 3-wide, made up little ground in home straight when placed under pressure, rather one-paced.
Awkward start, taken to the rear and travelled 10Ls behind the speed, responded well when asked at the top of home straight, finished off strongly and cover substantial ground final 300 M, too late.
Urged along early, ended up in a 3-wide spot 3Ls behind the leader, only held ground until flattened passing the 200 M pole.
Settled 3-4Ls behind the leader, travelled 2-deep with cover, niggled along near 800 M, gave no response when asked at 400 M, failed to make up any ground.
Niggled along but lacked early speed, travelled satisfactorily on rails until outpaced from 600 M, weakened at 300 M, dropped out.
Taken rearward from gate 14, no cover, improved along 3-deep halfway, carried extremely wide at home turn, not tested when proved beaten.
Settled 7Ls off the pace, saddle shifted 12, eased out 7.
Eased to rear, 7Ls off the leaders, trapped 4-5 wide, harmed by the slow pace, demonstrated strong finishing efforts 400M, drifted away 200M to win.
Pushed early but failed to muster, took cover at back, 5Ls off the leaders 3 wide, dashed well 300M despite not suited by the slow pace and ran 2nd.
Pushed to occupy a more prominent spot, 3Ls off the slow tempo 2-3 wide, ran on well to the line for 3rd.
Pushed to cross in front, took rail, shared the lead at advantageous slow sectionals, flattened 300M.
In front of midfield, 3Ls off the leaders on the rails, not suited by the slow tempo, no turn of foot in last quarter.
Eased back, 5Ls off the leaders, trapped 4-5 wide, harmed by the slow pace, made early move 600M, just ran on fairly in straight.
Settled in a prominent spot, 1.5Ls off the leaders 2 wide, enjoyed the slow tempo, ran on until 250M weakened.
Slow away, pushed to obtain a midfield spot, 4.5Ls off the leaders 3-4 wide, not suited by the slow tempo, moved slightly forward 600M, no progress in straight.
Pushed early but not muster, 4.5Ls off the leaders 2 wide, harmed by the slow tempo, no turn of foot in final stages.
Settled 6-7Ls off the pace, travelled satisfactorily on the fence, made up some ground along the inner when asked for efforts 400 M out, blocked from 200 M, not fully tested.
Eased back, harmed by the slow pace, never a factor.
Shared the lead easily 2 wide at slow sectionals, weakened quickly 350M.
Midfield, 4.5Ls off the leaders along the fence, not suited by the slow pace, faded in straight.
Slow away, pushed to gain the box seat, suited by the slow tempo, however soon dropped off 400M.
Jumped fairly, settled cozily in a one-off position in midfield, quickened well when obtained clear run at 350 M, finished off strongly, hit the front just before the line.
Took the one-out-one-back spot easily, responded well when asked for efforts at 350 M, kept on strongly to contest the lead, just caught on line.
Awkwardly drawn, urged along to get across in front and soon settled 1L behind the leader on rails, took long to obtain clear run in the home straight, finished off strongly final 150 M, just late.
Broke fairly but soon occupied a prominent position 2-3Ls behind the speed, ran up to contest the lead at home turn, kept battling on in the straight, so unlucky to lose a place.
Crowded start, pushed forward to occupy a fence position in midfield, shifted outward for home, took time to pick up, kicked well final 200 M, too late, narrowly beaten by the top four.
Broke well but lacked early speed, ended up settling 2-wide 6Ls off the pace, crowded at 600 M, blocked early in straight, ran on strongly final 200 M, bumped at 50 M.
Crowded after start, settled 5Ls off the pace on rails, hung out 6, responded well when asked for efforts final 350 M, made up gradual ground along the inner.
Crowded start, taken rearward from gate 12, 5Ls away at the final turn, swung widest for home, made up ground steadily under pressure, never really troubled the principals.
Settled in midfield and caught 3-wide with cover, responded fairly well when asked for efforts final 350 M, made up gradual ground down the centre of home straight.
Niggled along to hold a 3-wide position just off the pace, no cover throughout the trip, only one-paced under pressure in the home straight, failed to find extra final 100 M, bumped at 50 M.
Slow away, pushed forward and soon took the lead near 1000 M, headed in near 300 M out, soon flattened.
Prominently placed 2Ls off the speed on rails, shifted wider for home, gave very limited response when asked for efforts final 400 M, soon faded.
Given a waiting ride as usual and settled one from the rear on rails, failed to make up any ground in the home straight.
Broke well but soon taken to the rear, at least 6Ls away from the leader throughout the trip, never competitive.
Never far off the pace, took a while to pick up on straightening but came with a late surge final 200M to get up a few strides from the line.
Placed 2-wide in midfield, quickened well to reach the lead, dueled with the 3rd horse from 250M, caught by fast finishing winner close home. (Bled 2nd time.)
Prominent behind leaders, moved to the front 300M out, was collared but refused to give in and kept battling towards the finish.
Towards the rear, stayed on well final 300M but couldn't find extra pace to challenge.
Raced keenly in middle stages but always in a good position behind leader, briefly threatened going into straight but run turned flat 200M out.
Settled midfield off the rail, switched to 2-wide nearing 600M, ran on fairly in straight without threatening.
Held up in last, kept on one-paced and unable to make up the ground.
Towards the rear, couldn't pick up when switched wide 500M out, eased final 150M.
Pressed the pace outside leader but had no extra inside 300 M.
Vied for lead on the inside, weakened rapidly passing 350M. (Blood in trachea / Unacceptable Performance.)
Settled 2Ls behind the leader, travelled keenly in the middle stages, took time to pick up early in straight, clicked into gear final 150 M, ran on strongly, just in time.
Caught 3-wide with no cover in midfield, crept closer rounding the bend, finished off strongly under maximum pressure final 300 M, just caught by the winner in the last stride.
Eased early but failed to find cover in midfield, ran up to share the lead halfway, kept on well under pressure final 400 M, caught by the top two at 50 M.
Settled cozily in the box-seat just behind the leader, only one-paced early in the home straight, kicked final 200 M, too late.
Easily ran up to lead 1L, responded satisfactorily when asked for efforts at the top of home straight, could not find extra final 50 M.
Broke well but soon eased to a one-off spot in midfield, responded well when asked for efforts final 350 M, finished off satisfactorily.
Jumped only fairly, urged along to catch up 2Ls off the speed, kept on fairly well under pressure early in straight, hung in, failed to find extra final 100 M.
Jumped fastest from gate 14, soon eased to the midfield to obtain cover on 3-deep, only one-paced in the home straight.
Lacked early speed and soon settled 5Ls off the pace, hung out and badly unbalanced at 800 M, took long to pick up early in home straight, clicked into gear and finished off well final 200 M.
Given a waiting ride as usual, settled 6Ls away at the rear, dashed well and covered substantial ground final 250 M.
Niggled along to hold a fence position in midfield, gave very limited response when asked at 400 M, flattened at 200 M.
Slow away, settled 5Ls off the pace on the rails, responded only fairly when asked at 400 M, failed to make up any ground.
Crowded start, settled 7Ls away at the rear, made up some late ground final 250 M, never really troubled the principals.
Bumped start, lacked early speed despite being urged along, ended up travelling 5Ls off the pace, outpaced at the top of home straight, soon dropped out.
Standard jump, posted 3 wide but had cover for best part, 2 to 3Ls down on circle, improved turning and put in a gallant bid at 250 M, did too well late in gaining a narrow result.
Assured a midfield role from an awkward alley, 4Ls back in 2 wide line, came off heels on bend, made a strong finish down centre only to come up narrowly short.
Out with rest, ended up behind midfield 3 wide 4 to 5Ls off pace, gradually improved in mid-section, tracked eventual winner on bend, made a decent finish but just couldn't lift final 100 M.
Positioned behind midfield in running line, 5Ls off top end on circle, came wide turning and made good late progress to make frame.
Positive from outset, camped on leaders back, no excuses 1L down to bend, lacked dash but kept on well without threatening.
Restrained from widest gate, travelled 6 to 7Ls back at rear, last on turning in, covered good ground in straight closing to be nearest on line.
Tardy away, recovered quickly to take a prominent spot behind pace pair, right there to bend, looked a brief place chance at 300 M but peaked soon after.
Out in line, ridden hard to take lead, set even tempo with pressure of horses outside, niggled straightening, condition gave out at 250 M and faded out.
Faded back, to rear, 6 to 7Ls away on rails, not asked but had job to do on turning in, made only minor progress in straight.
Even break, assumed a midfield role and angled to fence 4 to 5Ls off speed, soft trip throughout, just whacked away behind them lacking usual finish.
Drifted back to be in rear division 6Ls off top end, fair run but didn't respond at business end and didn't look to see out journey.
Moderate beginning, raced behind midfield about 5Ls from lead, saved ground on bend, found little under pressure and struggled in straight.
No speed, well back and wide early, rushed up to go forward but still 3 wide without cover, 1L down on bend, there to 250 M out, soon failed after working too hard.
Standard jump, pushed on to race outside lead, didn't back off with pressure from outside horse, niggled turning in, folded tamely.
Settled midfield in a strongly run race, angled into clear nearing 400M, swiftly moved to the front with 200M to go, kicked nicely clear and won in good style.
Began well, bagged the rail and sat 3Ls behind runaway leader, made a bold bid 300M but couldn't match the pace of the winner, weakened final 100M and just held on for 2nd.
Caught 3-wide in the group chasing the pace, kept on steadily inside final 200M to take 3rd close home.
Sat handily in 2nd 3Ls off the strong pace, held every chance but lacked extra pace to challenge the winner, battled on to the line and narrowly missed out on a minor placing.
Towards the rear 3-wide, had plenty to do turning in, made a short lived effort then turned flat final 150M. (Jockey reported his horse hung in and proved difficult to ride.)
Reserved off the pace, 9Ls to make up passing 400M, ran on strongly in straight making some late impression.
4-wide at the rear early, moved closer to midfield passing 900M, hung in under pressure in straight and couldn't find extra gear.
Began awkwardly, kept wide in midfield early but was able to tuck in before home turn, driven nearing 400M, kept on without threatening.
Dropped back to a position behind midfield, saved ground on the inside but couldn't find the extra pace to challenge.
In mid-division early but got shuffled back passing 1000M, moved away from the fence 450M but found less than expected in the drive home.
Fractious in stalls and very slowly away, ended up with last few about 10Ls off the strong pace, couldn't pick up off the bend and ran home one paced.
Towards the rear, driven 450M but no progress, never a factor.
Behind midfield and lacked further response on straightening, eased.
Driven to the lead but would not settle, set a blistering pace in front and built up a 3Ls lead, got tired and weakened rapidly passing 300M. (Unacceptable Performance.)
