Began well, made all, hung on well.
Broke well, settled in one-out-one-back position, failed to quicken under pressure but fought on steadily to the line.
Soon taken back from the widest barrier to last, remained well behind to straight, finished off race strongly to snatch a placing final strides.
Settled in forward of midfield, saved ground turning in, fought on down straight but unable to sustain effort close to home.
Settled one-back on rails, remained same on rails turning in, failed to quicken under pressure throughout straight.
Settled in 2L 4th, dropped further back in 4th far side, similar turning for home, fought on steadily without threatening.
Settled behind midfield, ran on well down centre of straight to be nearest at finish.
Soon in third last, saved ground turning in, never nearer.
Settled in midfield on rails, ran home one-paced under pressure.
Began with others from a wide barrier, soon settled at the back, wide turning for home, never nearer.
Began well, settled wide in midfield, faded soon after straightening.
Settled in midfield to straight, weakened.
Parked in a midfield position along the fence. Straightened up about 3 deep then went back to the fence near the furlong and swept to the lead close to home.
Travelled with backmakers along the rail. Swung wide into the home straight and navigated a passage through to close off soundly.
Had no excuses after settling in a handy position 1 off with cover. Laboured over the latter stages.
Camped midfield, 2-wide with cover. Made steady progress after coming wide.
Settled at the tail of the field along the paint. Made some good headway late. (Pulled up lame.)
Rolled forward and managed to race in 2nd position, 1 off. Was one paced over the final stages.
Settled 3 back the fence. Had every chance but came up flat in the run to the line.
Travelled worse than midfield, 1 off with cover. Came wide in the straight but only plugged to the line.
Lead early before taking up a trailing position after the 1200 M. Failed to find any extra at the business end of the race.
Worked forward to lead and crossed to the fence near the 1200 M. Faded over the concluding stages.
Settled in 2nd last position, 2-wide with cover. Never a factor.
Began poorly and lost ground settling behind midfield the fence. Struggled in the home straight.
Driven early to race with leaders but trapped 5-wide. Eventually cut to lead on fence at the Rock. Held a 1L advantage leaving the bend. Tiring late but clung on for a narrow victory.
Ahead of midfield on fence. Well positioned to launch challenge and was 3Ls down turning home. Rallied on to chase the winner. Just failed.
Sat 2-wide towards rear early. Moved closer home turn. Swung 5-wide and was 5Ls adrift on straightening. Finished off strongly and was nearest at finish.
Began fairly. Soon shaken up to race behind midfield on fence. Shuffled towards rear passing 500 M. Took inside run and was 5Ls back entering home straight. Covered good ground thereafter.
Soon in leading section on fence. Eased to sit behind pace at the Rock. Ideal spot to strike in the straight but was one-paced to conclude.

Jumped fairly well but insufficient speed to work across. Ended up 2-wide behind midfield first turn. Took closer order and was 4Ls off turning in. Made some headway outside without threatening the principals.
2-wide with leaders early. Elected to sit ahead of midfield passing 800 M. Angled out and was 2Ls away into final stretch. Held ground to line.
Travelled 2 to 3-wide in front rank until no extra gear final furlong.
Travelled wide and without cover behind midfield. Plugged on home.
Slow to begin. Trailed field through to home straight. Made up minor ground late.
Hard ridden early to race ahead of midfield. Gradually dropped behind midfield despite effort of rider rounding home turn. No progress thereafter.
Always at rear. Never likely.
Jumped cleanly, prominently placed 3 to 4Ls off the pace on rails, responded well when asked for efforts final 300 M, finished off strongly and hit the front in the last few strides.
Jumped fast and soon occupied the box-seat just behind the leader, quickened well when asked for efforts at the top of home straight, briefly led at 150 M, caught in the last few strides.
Urged along to find a fence position in midfield, ran on steadily when placed under pressure final 300 M, got a place in the final stride.
Pushed hard forward to hold a one-off spot 3 to 4Ls behind the speed, responded satisfactorily when asked at the top of home straight, ran on, just missed a place in the final stride.
Niggled along to get across in the front, settled 1L behind the pacesetter, ran on to contest the lead at home turn, hit the front at 300 M, caught at 150 M, could not find extra final 100 M.
Slow away, settled over 10Ls behind the leader at the rear, crept closer rounding the home turn, made gradual ground down centre of the straight, never really troubled the principals.
Sat in a one-off position in midfield, only gave limited response when asked for efforts final 300 M, rather one-paced.
Jumped only fairly, pushed forward and took the lead passing the 1200 M pole, caught at the top of home straight, soon flattened.
Urged along to take the one-out-one-back spot, travelled bit keenly when restrained in the early stages, held ground until flattened at 200 M, soon faded. (Lame in right fore.)
Given a waiting ride as usual and travelled about 8Ls off the speed, checked at 1400 M, urged from 500 M but took time to pick up, made very limited progress final 150 M.
Began very slowly, travelled rearward throughout the trip, failed to make up any ground in the home straight.
Taken back from gate 12 and travelled over 10Ls off the pace, struggled from 700 M, soon lost touch, finished tailed out.
Settled cosily in a fence position 3Ls behind the pace, clicked into gear when asked at 350 M, improved quickly along the inner and hit the front in the last few strides.
Settled 2Ls off the speed easily, travelled one-off with cover, quickened well when asked at the top of home straight, briefly led 150 M out, just caught in the last few strides.
Worked early to hold a 3-wide position just off the pace, took time to pick up early in the home straight, ran on well final 200 M under maximum pressure, narrowly beaten by the top two.
Started awkwardly, pushed early to hold a one-off spot in midfield, responded fairly well when asked in home straight, made up gradual ground final 300 M.
Niggled along to hold a one-off position just behind the speed, kept on fairly under pressure in home straight, lacked a decisive kick final 150 M, one-paced.
Easily ran up to share the lead, travelled 3-wide without cover, held ground until passed 200 M, no extra.
Slow away, taken to a fence position 5Ls behind the speed, made up ground gradually final 250 M when placed under pressure.
Pushed forward to share the lead, passed at 300 M, soon weakened.
Restrained to a one-off position just behind the mid-division, niggled along rounding the home turn, only made limited progress in the home straight.
Settled about 2Ls off the pace on rails, held up for room early in the home straight, failed to make any progress when asked for efforts final 150 M.
Widely drawn, taken back to the rear and travelled about 10Ls behind the pace, struggled halfway to catch up with the pace, failed to make up any ground in the home straight.
Lacked early speed despite being urged along, ended up in a rearward spot 8Ls off the speed, struggled halfway to catch up with the pace, weakened 4, finished tailed out.
Eased to sit in midfield, 5Ls off the leaders, favoured by the fast pace and the rail run, progressed steadily 300 M to win.
Pushed early, 3Ls off the fast pace along the fence, closed the race off strongly for 2nd.
Hard ridden to hold the rail and shared the lead at very fast sectionals, hung on strongly until 50 M overhauled, stayed on for 3rd.
Eased at start to take rail behind the field, 7Ls off the leaders, benefited by the fast pace and the rail trip, progressed steadily 200 M.
Pushed early, obtained a midfield spot, 4Ls off the leaders 2-wide, favoured by the fast pace, made ground 200 M without making much threat.
Eased to rear, 8Ls off the leaders along the fence, benefited by the fast tempo, made late ground 200 M.
Eased to sit behind midfield, 6Ls off the leaders 2-wide, favoured by the fast pace, made ground 200 M.
Settled in a prominent spot, 2Ls off the leaders, not suited by the fast pace, flattened in straight.
Hard ridden forward, trapped 2-wide just behind the leaders, not suited by the fast tempo, emptied 250 M.
Pushed early, 7Ls off the leaders 2 to 3-wide, suited by the fast pace, however only ran on fairly in final stages.
Very slow away, hard ridden to battle for the lead at very fast sectionals 2-wide, soon weakened 250 M.
Suited by the fast tempo, never a factor at rear.
Cosily placed on the rails in midfield, patiently ridden until the home straight, kicked strongly when asked for efforts final 350 M, hit the front 100 M out, scored with some in hand.

Occupied a one-off spot 2 to 3Ls off the pace easily, travelled nicely throughout the trip, responded well when asked at the top of home straight, finished off soundly for 2nd. (Lost right hind plate.)
Niggled along to take the one-out-one-back spot, proved difficult to settle early, responded satisfactorily when asked and briefly led at 250 M, soon caught, kept on for 3rd.
Broke well, soon occupied a fence position just behind the leader, took long to obtain clear run in the home straight, kept on satisfactorily for 4th.
Slow away, settled 4 to 5Ls off the speed, crept closer along 2-deep halfway, obtained clear run at the top of home straight, only made gradual ground under pressure, rather one-paced.
Broke well, worked early to lead and found the fence near 900 M, passed at 250 M, kept on fairly under maximum pressure, could not find extra final 100 M. (Blood in trachea.)
Taken rearward from gate 10 and travelled 6 to 7Ls off the speed, bumped when shifting ground at the top of home straight, made little progress final 200 M, only passed the beaten rivals.
Awkwardly drawn, lacked early speed and ended up being caught 3-wide in midfield, badly bumped at 350 M, weakened and dropped out.
Crowded soon after start and soon taken to the rear, failed to make up any ground in the home straight.
Given a waiting ride and travelled 6Ls off the pace, raced greenly early, caught 3-wide throughout the trip, on heels at 300 M, failed to make any progress in the home straight.
Settled one-off in midfield, niggled along rounding the home turn, only held ground under pressure, weakened passing the 200 M pole.
Worked early but failed to get across in the front, ended up being caught 3-wide in midfield, got tired in the home straight, finished tailed out.
Positioned in midfield, responded to pressure 400 M out, came with a sweeping run outside and got up just in time.
Not hurried in early stages and settled behind midfield 7Ls off the strong pace, ran on well down the inside but just found one too strong.
Tracked leaders in the first half then sped off to a clear lead making the home turn, held 3Ls advantage final 200 M, weakened in late stages and caught near line.
Dropped back and taken across to the rail, 10Ls off the pace in middle stages, made steady progress down the inside without reaching the top 3.
Settled 4 to 5Ls behind runaway leader, given every chance but found less than expected when the race got serious, turned flat after being taken in near 100 M.
Settled 2-wide in mid-division, kept on final 200 M but failed to make an impression.
With leaders early, dropped back to midfield halfway down the back straight, into clear 300 M but couldn't find an extra gear to seriously challenge.
Placed behind midfield, had 9Ls to make up turning in but could only make minor progress late on.
Never far off but could only keep on at the same pace, weakened close home.
Switched off to last and trailed over 10Ls to leader in a strongly run race, picked up fairly on straightening and never looked like getting to the horses in front.
Went forward from a wide barrier but had to make some use early, gave up the lead approaching home turn, driven inside 300 M but no progress, weakened gradually.
Taken back on jumping from a wide barrier and settled over 10Ls off the strong pace, took a while to pick up and made some headway late on.

Settled in last few of the small field, moved slightly closer up around home bend, quickened to hit the front over 250 M out, just held off runner-up's late revival nearing home.
Ridden to muster early speed, took up running while racing keenly around the bend, headed inside 300 M but found on gamely to nearly peg back winner.
Lacked early speed, urged along to muster pace to go within 2Ls of leader, well there turning in, fought on under pressure to narrowly miss first two.
Raced mainly 3-wide but never far off in midfield of small field, similar turning in when shifted ground under pressure, produced a strong late dash inside final 100 M.
Began with others, settled in midfield of small field within 3Ls of pace, held up for a run early in straight until the 300 M, fought on steadily without threatening.
Jumped best from the middle draw, raced 3-wide with leaders early before taken backward briefly, soon back to dispute lead rounding home bend, gradually faded under pressure in the run home.
Shared early pace, settled just off the speed making home bend, saved ground on inside turning for home, kept on at the one pace.
Soon taken back from the widest barrier, travelled behind in last few most of way, found nothing under pressure in the run home.
Raced wide without cover in midfield far side, lost position from around home bend dropping to last few entering home straight, made no further impression.
Raced keenly in midfield early before dropping to rear of field, never seen with a chance.

Placing: TNP
Comment: Reared and refused to jump, took no part.
Sent forward and led at even sections to make every post a winner.
Travelled ahead of midfield, 1 off with cover. Rounded the home turn 4 deep and made steady ground in the final stretch.
Stalked the leader along the paint. Stayed on gamely despite being hampered after the 200m.
Settled at the rear of the field along the rail. Switched to the outside early in the straight and found the line soundly.
Rated close to the speed 1 off without cover. Failed to quicken when asked for an effort in the home straight and faded over the final stages.
Began on terms settling 3 back the rail. Ran out the final stages one paced.
Raced behind midfield 1 off with cover. Plugged home.
Settled in 2nd last position, 1 off with cover. Failed to lengthen in the home straight.
Slow to begin then crowded soon after losing ground and despite being ridden along never really mustered, settling towards the rear. Not likely.
Settled midfield early then when trapped wide worked forward but was caught on a limb on the speed 3 deep no cover. Never a factor.
Shared lead on fence. Opened a 3Ls gap turning in. Powered clear passing 300M. Easy.
Trailed field despite the effort of rider. Some improvement approaching home straight. 8Ls down passing 400M. Did the best work late but the winner was long gone.
Raced outside the leader. Drew well clear of the rest into final stretch. Attempted to challenge the lead passing 400M but was soon knocked out. Lost 2nd place final strides.
Well back with last few through to home straight. Made up good ground closing stages to make frame.
6-7Ls down until some progress 400M out but never looked likely to threaten the principals.
Sat 3Ls behind the leading pair. Failed to quicken when the race got serious passing 400M.
Camped behind the pace group, enjoyed a good trail 3-4Ls back. Nothing to offer in the straight.
Travelled wide and without cover ahead of midfield through to home straight. Soon folded tamely.
Moderate break, not rushed early, confidently ridden in fourth last three wide far side, out wide to challenge straight, strong run to get up inside last 50m, won going away.
Well away, declined battle for lead, settled midfield two off, wide to challenge straight and ran on strongly, led 200m out, just caught.
Fair break, settled fourth one off rail, ridden early straight, ran on but outpaced by wide finishers.
Awkward start, back to second last and short of room back straight, rail run straight, ran on but never able to challenge.
Fair break but taken back to rear from outside gate, held up last one off, wide bid straight,, kept on well without threatening.
Ridden early from wide gate but caught wide as a result, third three off into straight, kept on but no further progress, weakened late.
Even break, settled midfield one off, slight check 900m, ridden early straight, not pace to challenge.
Fast away, second one off, then shared lead, narrow lead early straight, headed and swamped last 150m.
Fair break, lacked early speed, eighth on rail entering straight, short of room mid straight, outpaced.
Air break, ridden to lead after 100m, joined on outside and shared lead into straight, ridden, weakened.
Not well away, midfield and check far side, back to last entering straight, kept on but no impression.
Broke well, took rail in fifth, pulled round two horses entering straight, led 200m out, comfortably.
Broke well, unhurried, back to rear, moved up sharply three wide far side, led into straight, ran on well, winner too strong.
Fair break, up to third one off, fourth into straight, ran on, no extra.
Slightly sluggish start, midfield rail, kept on one off rail in straight, never able to challenge.
Well away, up three wide to share lead then go on, tried to stack up field but quickly overtaken, kept on along rail under driving.
Fair break, unhurried, mid-rear one off, refused to settle briefly far side, wide into straight, threaded through gap, ran on without threat.
Fair break but settled midfield three off, ridden entering straight, mid track bid, only modest progress.
Well away, settled sixth one off, slight stumble exiting back, wide bid straight, one pace.
Fair break, ridden early to take fourth one off, back to eighth as pace slowed, ridden early straight, one pace.
Slight bobble start, taken back to rear rail, urged out of back straight, ridden mid-track, little progress.
Well away, up four wide to share lead, then eased back to third last one off, wide bid straight, driven, no progress.
Broke well, not rushed early, midfield two off, slight check exiting back, wide into straight, ridden, found little.
Sluggish start, stumbled badly shortly after, held up second last on rail, went for inside run, found nothing.
Fast break, ridden to lead early, headed after 450m, raced third one off, ridden early straight, found nil, eased.
Eased back, 5.5Ls off the good pace, trapped 3-4 wide, progressed steadily 300M to win by a nose.
Very slow away, pushed to keep up with the field at rear, 7Ls off the good pace 2-3 wide, blocked 4-2, dashed well when clear, just missed by a very narrow margin.
Eased to sit in midfield, 5Ls off the good pace 3 wide, progressed steadily 400M to take 3rd.
Jumped very well, settled in prominent spot, 2.5Ls off the good pace on the fence, just held ground in final stages.
Settled in prominent spot, 2.5Ls off the good pace 2 wide, no dash in straight, flattened 150M.
Eased to sit in midfield, 4Ls behind the good pace 2 wide, lacked turn of foot and just held ground in straight.
Progressed steadily to cross in front and took rail, led by 1.5Ls at good pace, hung on until 200M emptied.
Trapped 4-5 wide in midfield throughout and lost too much ground, flattened in straight.
Eased back, 5.5Ls off the good pace along the fence, made ground 500M, run ended 150M.
Eased at start and took rail at rear, 8.5Ls off the good pace, no dash.
Hard ridden early but failed to cross in front, trapped 3-4 wide and lost ground, 3Ls off the good pace, weakened 200M.
Pushed forward, 1.5Ls off the good pace 2 wide, ran on until 250M dropped off.
Hard ridden early but not muster, never better than midfield.
Easily ran up to lead, quickened well when asked for efforts at 350 M, kept on soundly, never challenged.
Jumped well, settled cosily just behind the leader on the standside rails, hung in near 400 M, kept on well for 2nd.
Crowded start, prominently placed just behind the speed, kept on well when asked final 400 M, could not find extra final 100 M, and just did enough for a place.
Broke well, held up to a fence position on the standside just off the pace, on heels 4, made gradual ground final 250 M, just late for a place.
Awkwardly started, urged along to catch up 2-3Ls off the pace, hung in when placed under pressure halfway, made gradual ground final 200 M, rather one-paced.
Broke well from gate 1, soon eased to the midfield and got across towards the standside, lacked a kick when asked for efforts final 350 M, flattened at 150 M.
Crowded start, taken back towards the rear and moved towards the standside, gave very limited response when asked final 400 M, soon faded. (Blood in trachea.)
Lacked early speed despite being urged early, lost touch halfway, made some late ground final 200 M.
Soon guided to 2nd place about 3Ls behind the pace, picked up gradually on straightening and got past the long time leader close home.
Sped off to a clear lead after the start, kept on well in straight but got tired in late stages losing 1st place near finish.
Taken back on jumping and settled in last 10Ls off the strong pace, shaken up passing 600M, gradually responded to riding and finished fastest of all inside 200M. Never nearer.
Towards the rear way off the pace in early stages, took time to gather and came through with a good run final 200M.
Never far off behind the runaway leader but could only keep on at the same pace in straight.
Settled behind midfield, into clear 400M, made a short-lived effort turning one paced inside 150M.
Settled near rear under a patient ride, made some progress from off the pace but never seriously threatened.
Positioned in midfield but couldn't pick up when asked going into straight, left behind passing 200M and eased.
Jumped well, held a 2-wide position 2Ls off the pace, shifted out in search of clear run 400M out, finished off strongly, hit the lead 30 M to score.
Broke well, settled in a 2-wide position 1L off the pace, travelled nicely, ran on to contest the lead passing 200M, kept on under pressure, headed in by winner 30 M out.
Jumped well, urged along early and took the lead near 1100M, kept on well when placed under pressure at the top of home straight, passed at 200 M, kept on for a place.
Out in line but lacked early speed as usual, sat two from the rear 6Ls behind the speed, swung widest for home, dashed too late, ran 4th.
Slow to begin, urged along to hold a 3-wide spot in the mid-division, on heels at 800 M, shifted to centre of straight for home, kept on fairly.
Jumped fast and soon occupied a fence position 1L just the leader, urged along rounding the bend, only one-paced when placed under pressure in the home straight.
Out in line, settled 4Ls behind the speed, rather one-paced when asked for efforts final 400M, finished off fairly.
Slow away, urged along and ended up settling at the rear on rails, on heels at 700 M, swung wide for home, obtained clear run near 250M, finished off satisfactorily.
Bit slow to begin, travelled 5Ls behind the speed, shifted away from rails for home, held up for room at the top of the straight, made up little ground when clear final 250 M.
Jumped well, settled just off the pace but caught wide with no cover, got tired at the top of home straight, soon faded.
Out in line, prominently placed 2Ls behind leader on rails, gave no response when asked for efforts at the top of the straight, soon flattened.
Broke well, held up in a rearward position, made no progress in the home straight, finished tailed out.
Away well and angled into a nice position, had a good trial 3Ls back throughout, improved rounding bend, laid down a strong challenge inside 200 M to score a solid win.
No early toe, faded back to race at rear, best part of 8 to 9Ls back throughout, came widest straightening, made many lengths down middle to take 2nd late. Nice return.
Showed speed after average jump to lead, set reasonable fractions with attention from outside horses, 1/2L in front rounding bend, kept on but overhauled inside 100 M.
Not much early speed, ended up behind midfield, saved ground on rails on circle, 4Ls down turning, got going late between horses to make frame.
Average break and faded back as usual, best part of 7Ls or so from speed throughout, made a strong sprint at 400 M, in mix until 100 M when run ended.
Broke well, had speed to cross and race behind leader, no excuses throughout and made a bid at 300 M, no extra final 200 M.
Not much speed from gate, assumed a midfield role 5 to 6Ls off pace, niggled on bend, just kept on gradually without quickening to be nearest on line.
Out with test, trailed pace group 3Ls back but was 3 wide for best position, same margin down to bend, there to 200 M before fading.
Broke in line, pressed on but wide without cover first half, kept speed honest on circle, tackled leader on straightening, early effort told inside 300 M and dropped off.
Showed speed and contested for a position early, did share of work in first half, close enough on turning but struggled at business end.
Ordinary break and settled at rear 9 to 10Ls away, stuck to rails in straight but made no real impression.

Began well in front early, gradually taken back to 4th in forward of mid-division, responded well inside final 200 M to take charge about 70 M out.
Settled just worse than midfield, inconvenienced behind runners early in straight, finished off race nicely inside final 200 M, did best work late.
Began moderately from an awkward draw, ridden to muster speed to take up running going up Rock, held a length's advantage turning in, tiring when overhauled about 100 M out.

Began with others, travelled with leaders mainly two off the rails settling 1-out-1-back far side, held same turning in, fought hard to peg back tiring leader 200 M out, unable to sustain effort and overhauled by late finishers close home.
Settled 3-wide without cover in midfield, kept on same pace before producing late impression nearing home.
Began fairly, settled one from last on rails, found nil under pressure in the run home.
Soon dropped to the rear of field, never seen with a chance.
Shared early pace settling just behind leader, folded up quickly after straightening.
Hard ridden to take the rail and led by 1-1/2Ls at fast early sectionals, never challenged and clocked solid time.
Eased back, 6Ls off the leader, benefited by the fast pace and the rail-run, progressed steadily 200 M and ran 2nd.
Pushed to take a midfield spot, 4Ls off the leader 2-wide, favoured by the fast tempo, made ground in straight for 3rd.
Pushed to sit in front of midfield, 3Ls off the leader 2-wide, benefited by the fast pace, held ground in straight.
Hard ridden to occupy the box seat, harmed by the fast tempo flattened 100 M.
Awkward away, sat back, 6-1/2Ls off the leader 2 to 3-wide, helped by the fast pace, ran on ok in final stages.
Pushed to keep up with the field at rear, 7Ls off the leader on the fence, favoured by the fast tempo, but only ran on fairly.
Hard ridden forward, 1-1/2Ls off the leader 2-wide, not suited by the fast sectionals, weakened 200 M.
Hard ridden throughout along the fence, struggled in midfield, never picked up.
Never competitive at rear.
Driven from widest draw. Camped one-off behind the speed 1000 M out. Challenged leader turning into home straight. Fought on determinedly to come out on top final stages.
Soon led on fence. Battled gamely with the eventual winner in the straight. Knocked out near the post and barely clung on for 2nd.
Eased to sit 2-wide at rear shortly after start. Stayed near the fence and was 4Ls down rounding home turn. Did the best work late through runners and nearly snatched 2nd.
Slow to begin. Raced behind midfield on fence at the Rock. Peeled out and was 3Ls down turning in. Closed off well and was nearest at finish.
Began well. Eased to one-out-one-back from first turn. Looked dangerous top of home straight but couldn't sustain effort final furlong.
Box-seat through to home straight. Ideal spot to strike but failed to turn up a notch.
Proved difficult to settle and was checked early stages. Raced towards rear back straight. Hard ridden approaching home straight but no progress.
Steadied start and brought across to fifth last one off, began to improve leaving back, fifth four wide into straight, led 250 M out, ran on strongly.
Broke well. Travelled well two off in fifth, moved up leaving far side, shared lead with winner 300 M out, ran on well but outpaced.
Fast away, ridden early wide to lead after 200 M, settled in lead, kicked early straight, ran on, just outpaced by first two.
Fair start, urged along rail to midfield, clung to rail until mid straight, ran on but not pace to challenge.
Unruly start, slow away, settled rail in last, improved as field packed home turn, ran on well centre of course.
Fair break, unhurried, settled rail fourth last, improved wide approaching straight, kept on but never able to challenge.
Broke well, ridden up wide to take third three off, up to second one off, ridden to challenge early straight, no extra.
Well away, raced second one off, hard ridden straight, no real progress.
Moderate break, no early rush, settled second last two off, wide bid straight, no progress.
Broke well, led early, headed from outside, settled fourth on rail, scrubbed along straight, no impression, weakened.
Moderate break, midfield one off, then rail in fifth, lost ground as field packed, ridden early straight, no progress.
Fair broke, midfield but caught three wide, lost ground approaching turn, ridden to midfield, found nothing straight, eased late.
Broke well, but caught wide from high drawer racing without cover in fifth, still powered through in straight to lead 200 M out and win comfortably.
Fair break, took midfield rail, pulled out for run in straight, kept on very well without troubling winner.
Fast break, led one off early, then raced second, led early straight, kept on when headed.
Sluggish start, raced fourth last pulling slightly, wide bid straight, picked up late under driving to snatch fourth on line.
Broke well, found rail in fourth travelling well, asked to quicken early straight, kept on one pace.
Broke well out wide, ridden up to join leading group, bustled leaving back, ridden straight, kept on though never able to challenge.
Fair break, midfield one off, shaken up straight, kept on but never dangerous.
Slow start, third last rail, overracing slightly, ridden early straight, kept on but no significant progress.
Broke well, led after 200 M, headed entering straight, tried to fight back, weakened.
Moderate start, unhurried in rear, last into straight, kept on but no real progress.
Fair break, held up one off in second last, tried to make ground on outside straight, no progress.
Fair break, pushed early, three wide round home turn, ridden, found little.
Eased back, 4-1/2Ls off the leader 2 to 3-wide, harmed by the slow pace, demonstrated strong finishing efforts 200 M to score.

Pushed early but failed to muster, soon eased back for cover, 5-1/2Ls off the leader, made its run in 5-wide around the field, dashed strongly 300 M despite not suited by the slow pace and finished 2nd.
Eased back, 4-1/2Ls off the leader, trapped 3 to 4-wide throughout and lost too much ground, harmed by the slow pace, dashed well for 3rd.
Midfield, 3-1/2Ls off the leader, trapped 3-wide, moved forward 600 M to take advantage from the slow tempo, ran on ok in final stages.
Eased to obtain the box seat, blocked most straight and was pushed back, harmed by the slow pace, just ran on.
Pushed to take the rail and led by 1L at advantageous slow sectionals, soon emptied 250 M.
Eased to sit in midfield, 3-1/2Ls off the leader along the fence, harmed by the slow pace, held up badly and was carried back in straight, just ran on.
Awkward away, sat 2-1/2Ls off the leaders 2-wide, harmed by the slow pace, held up 4-2, no dash when clear.
Pushed forward to sit just off the lead in 2-wide, suited by the slow tempo, soon weakened 300 M.
Jumped fastest, easily ran up to lead, responded well when asked for efforts at the top of home straight, kept on well, just withheld the challenger.
Jumped only fairly, pushed to occupy the box-seat just behind the leader, quickened well to chase the winner in home straight, narrowly beaten.
Slow to begin, niggled along to catch up about 6Ls off the pace on rails, saved ground on inside turning for home, finished off strongly but blocked final 100 M, not fully tested.
Out in line, lacked early speed, sat three from the rear 5Ls off the speed, dashed well in the home straight, finished off soundly for 4th.
Bumped after the start, pushed early and soon settled 2Ls behind pace, caught 3-wide without cover, ran up to join the lead in the middle stages, could not find extra final 200 M.
Jumped well, urged along to hold a fence position 4Ls in midfield, lacked a kick when asked for efforts in home straight, flattened at 100 M.
Broke well, settled cosily 3Ls off pace on rails, only gave limited response when placed under pressure in the home straight.
Broken well, urged along to occupy the one out one back spot, weakened at the top of home straight, soon faded.
Out in line, settled in a one-off position 4Ls behind leader, shifted wider in search of clear run at the top of home straight, failed to make up any ground.
Bumped after start, taken back from the widest barrier, travelled rearward throughout the trip, found nothing under pressure, never a factor.
Began fairly, travelled wide without cover in the mid-division, no progress throughout, never closer.
Awkwardly started, always at rear, finished tailed out.
Positively ridden from the start and took them along at a decent pace, pushed clear from pursuers 250 M out and kept on strongly to the line.
Positioned 2-wide in midfield, had a clear path in home straight, finished well under a strong drive and took 2nd near the line.
Driven forward and pressed the pace, challenged from 350 M out but couldn't get to the winner, lost 2nd place close home.
Drawn on the inside and maintained a rail position just behind the pace, kept on final 300 M but couldn't find extra to challenge.
Taken back and travelled 2-wide in the rear, shifted out to improve 550 M, ran on well from last to finish 5th about 2Ls behind the winner. (Jockey questioned.)
Dropped back to a rearward position after the jump, shaken up 450 M and made minor headway final 200 M.
Placed in midfield along the fence, kept on same pace in straight and never threatened.
Ordinary jump but soon pushed forward to track leaders, not quickened final 300 M.
Began with the rest but lacked early pace, ended up in the rear 6Ls behind leader, made a short-lived effort after turning in, one paced final 200 M.
Restrained to a position behind midfield and travelled wide in the first half of the race, stayed on same pace in straight.
Placed towards the rear after a slow start, hung out making the home turn and was steadied near 450 M, soon left behind on straightening, eased.

Slightly jostled at start, settled in rear of midfield (about 2Ls back) and without cover near centre of track, quickened well inside final 250 M to hit front 50 M out.
Disputed lead early, settled just off the speed within 1L of leader, responded under reminders to hold every chance inside final 300 M, unable to sustain effort inside final 50 M.
Picked up steadily to cross and join leaders early, shared pace onto course proper, unable to sustain effort inside final 100 M.
Began restrained settling just off the pacesetters, did not find much room for a clear run most of way inside final 400 M, fought on well.
Began fairly, settled within 2Ls of speed near stands' side, came under pressure inside final 400 M but unable to sustain effort inside final 50 M.
Soon dropped behind midfield despite given early reminders but within 2Ls of speed near centre of the track, failed to make any impression inside final 200 M.
Began fairly, settled within 1L of speed near the centre of the track after beginning from the one draw, held similar through to 200 M when soon weakened under pressure.
Shared early pace gaining slender advantage shortly afterwards, joined coming onto course proper, soon dropped out noticeably.
Began moderately, gradually settled in rear on stands' rails found no response under pressure in the final stretch.
Began awkwardly, travelled in rear of bunched field behind runners, yielded ground from the 300 M mark.
Speared straight to the lead and bowled along against the rail. Made every post a winner drawing away in the straight for a comprehensive win.
Raced worse than midfield the fence. Ran on well to grab second place.
Enjoyed a nice run in the race stalking the leader along the paint. Kept on evenly to finish in the frame.
Raced at the tail of the field with cover. Railed up in the run home and worked to the finish well.
Travelled with the backmakers, 1 off with cover. Made some late ground towards the inside.
Settled midfield the fence. Ranged up near the 300 but ended its run well short of the post.
Camped behind midfield, 1 off with cover. Came widest in the straight but only plugged to the line.
Slow to begin, settling midfield 1 off with cover. Struggled over the last furlong.
Parked in second position 2 deep without cover. Was a beaten horse turning for home.
Settle behind the first 2, 1 off with cover. Gave ground quickly in the final stretch.
Never far off the pace. Picked up gradually when asked 400M out. Hit front 100M and won with some comfort.
Bumped at start but soon resumed to lead. Caught final 100M. Barely clung on for 2nd.
Fair start and raced towards rear. Commenced run passing 400M and made up good ground. Run finished short of the line and failed to snatch 2nd.
Slow to begin from low draw. Tacked on the back of the field near the centre of the track early. Shifted to stand's rail passing 600M. Ridden out 450M and responded well. Nearest at finish.
Always at midfield down the centre of the track. Plugged on home.
Behind the leading pair near the stand's rail. Shifted in for clear run passing 400M but was one-paced to conclude.
Shared lead on stand's rail until no extra to stay in the battle final 100M.
Behind midfield on the far side. Never improved from there.
Began awkwardly and bumped at start. Raced at rear despite rider's effort. Beat tired runners final furlong.
Knuckled over at start and raced towards rear. Progressed with the rest passing 400M until faded final 200M.
Travelled behind leaders early. Struggled from mid-point. Beaten well before home.
Out well, ridden from wide to secure third on rail, nudged along entering straight, ridden and passed by runner-up, fought on to lead 50m from the line, soon in charge.
Good break, settled just back of midfield rail, improved turn, challenged two off to lead narrowly 100m out, headed again, could not respond.
Broke well, shared lead, then led exiting back, re-challenged entering straight, fought on well until headed 100m out.
Fair break, ridden to settle midfield rail, bid between horses straight, kept on, not reach leading trio.
Moderate start, shuffled back, rear group rail, short of room far side, improved along rail turn, check mid straight, ran on well.
Well away, ridden to take fourth rail, challenged down middle of track, ran out of steam 300m out, kept on one pace.
Missed break, back to rear early, the fourth last three wide, shaken up straight for wide bid, stayed on well.
Well away, restrained, raced six from rear one off, improved on inside, check mid straight, kept on well.
Fair break, joined leading group one off, bustled turn, ridden, one pace.
Away well, ridden out wide to fifth one off, shaken up early straight, ridden wide, check early straight, kept on, no threat.
Slow start, held up third last one off, switched to rail, improved straight, run already coming to an end when checked 300m out.
Fair break, held up rear, pulling, ridden early straight, found little.
Sluggish start, back to rear, ridden before exiting back, no progress, looked unwilling.
Well away, ridden from gate but still caught wide, then led one off, headed rail, nudged before turn, ridden early straight, weakened quickly, eased.
Fair break, midfield two off, always travelling well, improved wide straight, centre field run, led 300m out, drew away easily.
Fair break, ridden early, sixth one off, moved to rail, challenged between horses, ran on well but no chance with winner.
Fair break, not rushed early, fourth last rail, shaken up straight, ran on.
Fast break, ridden but not pace to lead, settled one off in third, slight check and lost ground early straight, ran on well.
Fair start, midfield rail, urged, back to second last, bustled, kept on straight after being short of room.
Well away, ridden to take third rail, improved turn, second into straight, ridden, weakened gradually.
Easily ran up to lead 1L, kept on fairly early straight, caught near 200 M, soon weakened.
Slow start, last early, ridden, second last into straight, wide run, no impact.
Out in line, settled 2Ls off the pace, caught 3-wide with no cover, niggled along rounding the bend, could not find extra final 200 M.
Missed break, lost length, last early, lost further ground.
Hard ridden forward, 4Ls off the fast pace along the fence, closed the race off strongly 250M to score.
Eased to sit in midfield, 5.5Ls off the leader 2 wide, benefited by the fast tempo, progressed steadily 400M for 2nd.
Hard ridden to occupy the box seat, not suited by the fast early sectionals, ran on well to the line for a creditable 3rd.
Midfield, 7Ls off the leader along the fence, benefited by the fast pace, made steady ground 200M.
Eased to rear, more than 11Ls off the leader on the fence, suited by the fast tempo, progressed steadily in straight.
Eased at start, 10Ls off the leader along the rails, favoured by the fast pace, made some ground 200M.
Hard ridden to keep up in midfield, 5.5Ls off the leader along the fence, suited by the fast tempo, just held ground in straight.
Hard ridden to take the rail and led by 1L, clocked fast sectionals and used up too much fuel, hung on until 200 M emptied.
Eased back, 9Ls off the leader 2-3 wide, helped by the fast pace, no progress in straight.
Eased to rear, more than 10Ls off the leader, favoured by the fast tempo, ran on fairly.
Behind midfield, suited by the fast pace, never progressed.
Prominently placed just behind the speed, kicked strongly when asked for efforts 350 M out, hit the front near 150 M, drew clear easily.
Out in line, pushed hard forward to share the lead, kept on well under pressure in the closing stages, headed in by the winner at 150 M, did enough for 2nd.
Settled 3Ls off the pace, responded well when asked final 350 M, ran on for 3rd.
Broke well, urged along early to share the lead, passed 3, soon flattened.
Out in line, lacked early speed despite being urged along, bumped at 300 M, made limited progress when placed under pressure final 250 M. (Bled.)
Standard jump, settled 2Ls off the pace, only gave limited response when asked final 400 M, soon faded.
Started very awkwardly, urged along to catch up about 3Ls behind the speed, made no progress in the closing stages. (Sustained a cut to the inside of the right front heel.)
Bumped start, settled about 4Ls off the pace, niggled along halfway, bumped again at 300 M, failed to make any progress. (Blood in trachea.)
Always struggled at the rear, never competitive.
Rushed along in early stages and travelled near the rear 6Ls back, responded well passing 400 M and made the most of an uninterrupted run in straight, got up just in time.
Restrained in midfield, taken out nearing 400 M, came home with a surging run and was just denied.
Not far off the pace, picked up gradually passing 350 M and ran on well to take 3rd close home.
Had to overcome a wide barrier to lead, looked to have the race won 150 M out but weakened as the finish neared, headed close home and beaten to 4th by a narrow margin.
Settled on the inside just off the pace, battled on well and finished off willingly, not beaten far.
Positioned at the rear, switched to outside 450 M, looked one paced early straight but started to motor inside 200 M and finished off strongly.
Positively ridden from the outset and positioned one out one back, kept on till weakening inside 100 M.
Guided to a rail spot in midfield, pushed along midway but had no clear passage until the race was almost over.
Towards the rear, hung out under pressure on straightening and could make limited progress only.
In touch, driven 400 M out but no response, never a factor.
Behind midfield 5Ls off the pace and not able to quicken on this ground inside 350 M.
Close to the pace but travelled 4 to 5-wide throughout and was unsurprisingly a spent force from 350 M, eased late on.
Patiently ridden early and settled 6Ls off the pace, suited by the fast tempo, kicked strongly when asked 350 M out, hit the front near 50 M, won with some in hand.
Jumped fairly, urged along early and soon settled 5Ls off the speed, crowded at 1000 M, ran on strongly under maximum pressure final 350 M, narrowly beaten by the winner.
Lacked early speed despite being urged and soon drifted back to the rear, crowded at 700 M, held up for room early in straight, finished off soundly when clear final 150 M, too late.
Driven to lead 1.5L and found the fence approaching the 800 M pole, quickened well when asked at 400 M, kept on well under maximum pressure, caught near 100 M.
Urged along early and soon occupied a fence position just behind the leader, kept on fairly well when asked in the home straight, could not find extra final 50 M.
Settled 4Ls off the pace, caught 3-wide without cover throughout the trip, on heels at 350 M, soon recovered and made gradual ground.
Bumped start, urged along early and soon settled 4Ls off the pace, on heels at 1200 M, only gave limited response when asked at the top of home straight, rather one-paced.
Settled 4Ls off the pace on rails, only one-paced when placed under pressure in the home straight.
Bumped start, driven early to find a fence spot 3Ls off the pace, failed to quicken when asked for efforts in the home straight, soon flattened.
Prominently placed 2-3Ls behind the leader, got tired near 300 M, soon weakened.
Lacked early speed despite being urged, always rearward, lost touch at the top of home straight, finished tailed out.
Out in line, pressed on but posted 4 wide without cover, did it the hard way in mid-section despite in better going, 3Ls down on bend, chimed in at 250 M, dashed away to win with ease.
Crowded early, ended up near to last 3 wide 7Ls away at rear, conditions didn't suit, held up from turning to 200 M, closed well but no match for winner.
Prominent from outside gate, sat 3 wide without cover 2Ls off lead, crept closer on bend, no dash but kept on soundly when winner spaced them.
Even break, took a midfield trail 3 wide with cover, made some ground in straight to make frame.
Little early speed, raced 3 wide close to rear, 7Ls off speed, not aided by conditions, came widest and hung out in straight, closed evenly late.
Out in line, midfield or worse 5Ls off lead, 4 wide with cover on bend in better ground, whacked away OK in finish.
Standard jump, mustered to be midfield 3 to 4Ls down, OK to turn, just one speed in straight.
Amongst first few to begin, pushed up to race behind leader, in worst going throughout, struggled when asked in straight, faded late.
First to hit ground, assumed usual role in front, set even tempo, crept 2Ls clear on turning, peaked at 200 M and stopped quickly.
Took a midfield position, 4Ls or so off lead on rails, in worst going throughout, no response in straight.
Ordinary jump, soon at rear, struggled 8Ls or so away throughout, only passed tired runners in straight.
Showed speed, parked outside leader 1L down in mid-section, close enough to bend, faded out from 400 M.
Posted wide from an awkward draw, 4 wide without cover at rear, did too much throughout, never made impression.
Well enough away, took ideal spot 2Ls back with cover behind pace pair, then to bend, stopped soon after turning. (See explanation.)

Broke well to soon cross to lead setting a steady pace, soon drew clear inside 200 M before eased down near line.
Began fairly, held rails run in 2L 3rd becoming 4th far side, same turning in, fought on gamely to close on easy winner late.
Settled in last few, rattled home despite hanging in and a difficult ride in straight.
Began awkwardly from the widest draw, settled well behind, saved ground turning in, shifted out for a run inside 200 M, fought on steadily to be nearest at finish.
Began with others from a wide draw, ridden to soon gain one-out-one-back prominent spot, held same to home turn but failed to sustain effort in straight.
Began moderately, gradually picked up along rails to midfield, held similar position turning in, found nothing under pressure in the run home.
Began well but soon taken back, hampered at 1000 M bend shuffling back to midfield spot, travelled 3-wide down far side and widest turning for home, fought on steadily without quickening.

Steadied in midfield early, travelled wide without cover in midfield before taking closer order down far side, disputed 3rd from Rock and as close as joint 2nd 500 M out, yielded ground steadily from 400 M.
Niggled at early, prominent when steadied around 1000 M bend, midfield down far side, made no impression soon after straightening.
Began with others, gradually shuffled back to last, tailed-off into straight, never on terms.
Stalked the leader along the fence. Rolled off the rail turning for home and speared through to have the race in its keeping 100 M out.
Enjoyed a nice run in the race, 1 out 1 back. Cornered 4-wide and closed off nicely.
Worked through to race as joint leader before settling in the early stages to hold 2nd spot on the paint. Hit the front near the 300 M, but was mowed down over the concluding stages.
Began well then despite being steadied raced very keenly in the lead, 1 off. Battled on gamely but was gassed over the final stages.
Raced behind midfield, 1 off with cover. Peeled out on the home turn and made a good late bid to finish just out of the frame.
Failed to match the early speed of the race settling midfield, 1 off with cover. Only plodded to the line.
Positioned at the tail of the field towards the running rail with cover. Worked to the wire evenly.
Travelled with the back makers, 1 off with cover. Failed to make any impression in the run home.
Settled towards the rear along the fence. Struggled in the home stretch. (Pulled up lame in the right fore following day.)
Raced within 3Ls of the pace on fence through to home straight. Rallied down the rail and took charge final 150 M.
Drawn high, ended up 2-wide at rear first turn. Took inside run and was 7Ls away home turn. Left the fence to launch attack and responded well final stretch. Snatched 2nd last stride.
Never far off the pace in a 2-wide position through to home straight. Kept on but lacked the finishing touch of the front pair.
Shaken up to lead early. Eased to sit one-off behind pace from 900 M. Challenged leader on straightening and looked dangerous final 250 M. Couldn't sustain effort closing stages.
Began with others. Raced 2-wide at midfield through to home turn. Ridden out 500 M but was checked rounding home turn. Resumed well late.
Trailed field. Swung widest and was 8Ls back approaching home straight. Covered substantial ground and was nearest at finish.
Behind pace on fence until home straight. One-paced to conclude.
Behind midfield on fence through to home straight. Made up some ground closing stages.
Driven forward from high draw but was trapped wide. Eventually took lead at the Rock. Levelled soon after straightening and weakened thereafter.
Midfield on fence through to home turn. Shifted out for clear run entering home straight but failed to progress.
Back with last few always. Never likely.
Travelled wide and without cover at midfield early and middle stages. Bumped and became badly unbalanced rounding home turn. Never recovered.
Fair break, not involved in lead battle, fourth last one off, improved wide far side and turn, fourth into straight wide, ran on very strongly.
Good break, fifth one off, tried to quicken with winner, ran on well but outpaced mid-straight.
Awkward start, lost length, second last one off not perfectly settled on heels, improved wide approaching turn, ran on well out wide.
Fair break, held rail in fourth, found good split straight and ran on, not quite pace to challenge.
Dwelt, held up last, urged exiting back as lost further ground, found seam between horses straight and kept on well.
Broke well, joined leading group four wide, led leaving back, two lengths clear into straight, ridden, weakened.
Dwelt, lost two lengths, ridden early but still third last rail, slight check far side, kept on well but never dangerous.
Fast out, settled midfield one off, pulling slightly, tried to improve turn but no run available, kept on well on outside late.
Fair break, quickly found rail midfield, urged exiting back, rail run straight, flattened out late.
Well away, led early rail, challenged and passed far side, shaken up early straight but unable to fight back, weakened.
Fair break, ridden wide for bid at early lead, settled third one off, ridden early straight, weakened.
Well away, good early speed to take second one off without effort, led mid straight, drew clear.
Good break, ridden early out wide, settled fourth one off, kept on under pressure without being able to challenge.
Well away, raced third rail, challenged on inside early straight, outpaced by winner.
Moderate break, back to last held up, improved rail home turn, kept on without being able to challenge.
Fair break, midfield two off, improved turn, wide bid, kept on.
Well away, not involved in early lead battle, settled midfield two off, improved turn, wide bid, kept on.
Awkward start, dwelt, rushed up along rail to midfield, kept on rail until one pace late.
Well away, not pace to stay with leaders, back through field, kept on late.
Moderate break, third last, urged, no impact.
Hard ridden to early lead, led into straight two off, folded.
Fair break, not much early pace, slipped back to last, wide bid, no progress.
Pushed forward and secured a prominent spot, 2Ls off the good pace 2-wide, drifted away 200 M to win with ease.
Pushed to obtain a midfield spot, 3-1/2Ls off the good pace 2 to 3-wide, progressed steadily 300 M to grab 2nd.
Hard ridden forward, 1-1/2Ls off the good pace, trapped 3-wide throughout and lost too much ground, still ran on well to the line for 3rd.
Settled in box seat, pace good, carried back badly 500 M, ran on ok when clear 250 M.
Eased back, 6Ls behind the good pace 2 to 3-wide, made good ground 200 M.
Slow away, pushed early but not muster, 4-1/2Ls off the good pace 2-wide, ran on ok in final stages.
Pushed to sit outside the lead, pace good, ran on until 250 M weakened.
Midfield on the fence, 3-1/2Ls off the good pace, no turn of foot in straight.
Pushed to take the rail and led by 1/2L at good pace, soon weakened 500 M.
Trapped 3 to 4-wide throughout and lost too much ground, never competitive at rear.
Eased at start, benefited by the rail run, never better than midfield.
Jumped fast, pushed to occupy the box-seat just behind the leader, quickened up well when asked for efforts final 250 M, led at 150 M, kept on soundly win.
Broken well, settled 3Ls off the pace on rails, checked at 1000 M, finished off strongly when asked final 250 M, but couldn't catch up the winner.
Out in line, settled 2-wide spot 4 to 5Ls off the pace, kicked 250 M, on heels at 200 M, soon recovered and ran on well, took the 3rd in the final stride.
Started well, settled one-off 4Ls off the speed, ran on well towards the finish, just late for a place. (Epiglottic entrapment.)
Jumped fast from the wide draw, urged along to share the lead, kept on satisfactorily in the home straight, caught at 100 M, lost a place in the last few strides.
Began well, urged along to take a one-off spot 3Ls off the speed, made ground steadily in the straight, but never really threaten the principals.
Taken rearward from the widest alley, patiently ridden in the early and middle stages, swung widest for home, closed off only fairly.
Began fairly, lacked early speed and ended up settling 7Ls off the pace, only covered limited ground in the home straight.
Jumped fastest, niggled along to lead on rails, flattened early in the home straight, soon faded.
Awkwardly started, placed about 5Ls behind the speed, proved difficult to settle when restrained in the early stages, only one-paced when asked in the home straight.
Out in line, always rearward, travelled wide without cover throughout the trip, made no progress under pressure, never in contention.
Slow to begin, urged along to hold a fence position 4Ls off the pace, bumped at 1100 M, gave no response when asked, on heels near the line, finished last.
Settled midfield and saved ground on the inside, held up midway round the home turn as the pace slackened, picked up well from 250 M, finished the race with a flourish and got up right on the line.
Towards the rear, shifted out 3-wide approaching home turn and moved closer, ran on strongly and led 100 M out, just caught on the line by stable companion.
Tracked pace in 3rd, took over 300 M out but not matched winner's pace final 100 M.
Broke well but was restrained to a midfield position along the inside, pushed along 450 M, loomed up as a main threat near 200 M but was no match with first two.
Checked at the start and ended up towards the rear, held up near 400 M and had 5Ls to make up turning in, ran on well up the fence.
Dropped back to last almost 10Ls behind leader, shifted wide for a run nearing 400 M, stayed on well down the outside but couldn't reach the principals.
Overcame a wide draw to lead on the outside, kept on till weakening inside 150 M.
Placed 2-wide in midfield about 5Ls off the pace, ran on final 300 M but lacked pace to seriously challenge.
Restrained to a position behind midfield and got shuffled further back over the home turn, shifted out for a clear path in straight but could make limited progress only.
Crowded at the start, pushed along to 4th position not far off leaders, had his chance but ran on only one-paced.
Hampered at the start and ended up towards the rear 8Ls behind leaders, was 3-wide no cover from 1000 M and pushed forward nearing home turn, no extra 200 M. (Lame right hind leg.)
Led steadily from 1300 M, pressed along 400 M out, soon weakened. (Lame right front leg.)

Broke well, never far off, quickened well to take command over 200 M out, easily.
Close up early, travelled about 3Ls off the speed onto course proper, renewed effort inside 200 M to just pip 2nd.
Amongst leaders ploughing lone furrow down the centre of the track, came under pressure to hold position inside 300 M but had not much to give.
Travelled about 3Ls off the speed early, fought on steadily from 300 M to narrowly miss the placegetters.
Led or disputed lead, came under pressure inside 300 M but soon dropped out.
Ridden to be close up early, yielded ground steadily on course proper.
Began awkwardly, given a reminder early but soon dropped well behind travelling down the centre of the track, went past well-beaten horses closing stages.
Soon dropped to last few of bunched field, ran home one-paced. (Bled.)
Began awkwardly, settled about 2Ls off the pace and found cover down the centre of the track, dropped out tamely from 300 M.
Enjoyed the run of the race tracking the 2 leaders. Peeled out soon after turning for home and swept forward to take a commanding victory a furlong out.
Travelled on a limb, midfield 3 wide no cover. Ran on well despite covering ground.
Began awkwardly and lost ground. Made its run from near the rear whilst on the paint. Closed off soundly.
Raced midfield the fence. kept on steadily without threatening over the concluding stages.

Slow to jump then for some distance after the 1000m had to be checked away from heels, settling 2 deep midfield. Rounded the home turn about five deep but ended its run well short of the line after ranging up as a place chance.
Worked forward to vie for the lead near the 800m, after being slow to begin, travelling 1 off. Steadied to settle a neck behind the leader nearing the 650m. Faded over the final stages.
Settled 1 out 1 back. Produced little when asked for an effort in the home straight.
Raced at the tail of the field. Switched out early in the straight and battled away in the final stretch.
Made the running along the fence as joint leader in the early stages. Travelled in front after the 600m, but found no extra in the run to the line.
Traveled with the backmakers, 1 off with cover. Cornered 4 deep but failed to close off.
Led on fence all along. Never challenged.
3-wide close to pace through to home straight. Fought hard to snatch 2nd at finish but never hope with the winner.
Raced within 2Ls of the speed on fence early and middle stages. Soon outsprinted by the winner in the straight but held 2nd well until final stride.
2-wide behind midfield. 3Ls down on straightening. Checked passing 400M and failed to see daylight until 300M. Ran on fairly well once into clear.
3-wide behind midfield. 3-4Ls away into final stretch. Kept giving but was too one-paced.
Soon taken to sit 2-wide at rear from high draw. Swung wide and was 5Ls back turning into home. Made up some ground late.
Away in line but trapped wide. Gradually eased to race 3-wide at rear. Came widest and was 6Ls adrift rounding home turn. Covered decent ground closing stages.
Pressed early and raced 3-wide in a forward spot. Ridden soon after straightening but failed to improve. Weakened final 100M.
Prominent spot through to home straight. No response when asked 300M out. Faded final furlong.
Towards rear on fence. Never a factor.
Fair break but little early speed, settled fourth last on rail, pulled out and squeezed through gap straight, finished strongly to lead 50m out.
Sluggish start, settled mid-rear one off, ridden home turn, challenged outside winner, just run out of it.
Fair break, settled sixth on rail, quickened between runners to lead 150m out, no extra last 50m.
Fair break, midfield one off, mid-track bid, kept on but no kick.
Fair break, ridden to lead after 150m, two lengths clear and settled exiting back, ridden early straight, still two clear 250m out, weakened.
Missed beat start, back to second last one off, held up, wide bid, modest progress.
Well away, led early, headed and settled third on rail, hard ridden early straight,, little progress, weakened late.
Good break, not rushed, back to fifth last one off, shaken up early straight for wide bid, never able to challenge.
Well away, lacked early pace, mid-rear one off, driven, kept on but never threatened.
Well away, with leaders but three wide, second one off entering straight, ridden, weakened.
Fair break, settled rear one off, centre track challenge, ridden, no real progress.
Good break but caught four wide in sixth, never near rail, ridden early straight, weakened.
Moderate start, ridden up to fifth one off, bustled early straight, no progress, weakened.
Sluggish start, ridden early but continued to lose ground, eight lengths last entering straight, no progress, eased.
Good break, ridden up out wide to sit outside leader, then third one off, led mid straight, drew clear, kept on when challenged late.
Fair break from wide draw, taken back to fourth last one off, pulled out for mid-track challenge, ran on very well, just failed.
Broke well, then rail in fourth, kept on well straight but not pace to trouble leading pair.
Moderate start, held up rail in fourth last, ridden and some late progress mid track, never dangerous.
Fair break, tacked over to rear but still three wide, wide bid straight, ran on well.
Broke well, settled midfield rail, ridden and kept on straight, never able to challenge.
Broke well, reined back to mid-rear one off, wide bid straight, only modest progress.
Broke well, narrow early lead rail, then neck second still holding rail, led briefly early straight, ridden, weakened.
Fair break but caught wide, midfield three off, tried to improve mid-track, no progress.
Awkward start, took 300m to reach desired lead and then only by a neck on outside, ridden early straight, weakened.
Missed break then sluggish, back to last, last and ridden entering straight, only passed beaten horses.
Good break, taken back to second last rail, held up, inside bid, no real progress.
Fair break, took while to settle one off in fifth, ridden early straight, no progress, eased.
Fair break, took fourth but two off, lost ground turn, shaken up, found nil.
Midfield, 5Ls off the leader along the fence, harmed by the slow pace, held up 400M, dashed strongly when clear to win without being fully tested.
Pushed forward, 3.5Ls off the leader on the fence, favoured by the slow pace, closed the race off strongly and took 2nd.
Midfield, 5Ls off the leader 2 wide, harmed by the slow pace, dashed well 300M for 3rd.
Eased to sit in midfield, 5.5Ls off the leader, trapped 3 wide throughout, dashed well 200M despite not suited by the slow pace.
Settled 3.5Ls off the leader 2 wide, favoured by the slow tempo, just held ground in straight.
Hard ridden to take the rail and led by 2.5Ls at slow sectionals, hung on until 150M flattened.
Eased back, 7.5Ls off the leader 3 wide, harmed by the slow pace, little dash in straight.
Pushed to obtain the box seat, benefited by the slow sectionals, flattened 250M.
Eased back, 9.5Ls off the leader, raced 3-4 wide, harmed by the slow tempo, little dash 200M.
Very slow away, at rear, 8.5Ls off the leader 2 wide, harmed by the slow pace, ran on ok final stages.
Slow away, behind midfield along the fence, 7Ls off the leader, not suited by the slow tempo, no turn of foot.
Slow away, hard ridden to keep up behind midfield, 6.5Ls off the leader 2 wide, harmed by the slow pace, no progress.
Trapped 3-4 wide in midfield, 4.5Ls off the leader, not suited by the slow pace, dropped off 400M.
Prominently placed just behind the leader, kicked strongly when asked at 350 M, hit the front 150 M out, drew clear easily.
Driven hard to lead 1L on rails, quickened well when asked for efforts early in the home straight, caught by the winner at 100 M, kept on soundly for 2nd.
Jumped well, urged along to hold a one-off spot 3Ls behind the leader, bumped at 900 M, made gradual ground under pressure final 350 M, finished 3rd without threatening the top two.
Settled cosily 4Ls off the speed on rails, bumped at 900 M, made ground steadily final 300 M under pressure, just missed a place.
Settled 4Ls off the pace in the mid-division, made gradual ground final 350 M under pressure, rather one-paced.
Awkwardly started, settled 5Ls off the pace, on heels at 900 M, covered some ground final 300 M, rather one-paced.
Slow to begin, lacked early speed despite being driven hard, struggled 8Ls off the pace at the rear, only made limited progress final 250 M.
Pushed hard early and soon occupied a fence position 2Ls behind the leader, held ground until got tired 300 M out. (Abnormal breathing noise.)
Settled 7Ls off the speed, rearward throughout the trip, never competitive.
Slow to begin, pushed forward to catch up 3Ls off the pace, caught 3-wide without cover throughout the trip, crowded at 900 M, weakened at the top of home straight, finished tailed out.
Towards the rear and not used in early stages, picked up very strongly on straightening, drew away from the field and had the race won with 250M to go. Impressive.
Dropped back to last about 7Ls behind leader, ran on from off the pace to take 2nd close home, beaten 5Ls by the winner.
Tracked leaders, driven 450M, briefly led near 300M but was no match with the runaway winner, kept on to the line.
Placed 3-wide in midfield, had a rough run down the back straight due to the slow early pace, made progress from 400M but was severely checked near 300M, recovered to finish 4th.
Slow to muster but gradually improved to a midfield position along the fence, kept on one paced in straight and was never a danger.
Positioned 2-wide in the group chasing the pace, bumped near 300M, kept on one paced.
Towards the rear, headway from 400M but was severely checked passing 300M, had to shift out for a clear path and not able to be tested until 150M.
Led slowly to 1200M then raced one out one back to straight, faded out of contention passing 300M.
Led from 1200M and took them along steadily, headed nearing 300M and no extra.
Out in line, settled 3Ls off the pace on rails, blocked early in home straight, quickened well when clear at 250M, finished off strongly to score.
Began well, restrained to a 2-wide spot 5Ls off the speed from the widest draw, took time to muster in early straight, clicked into gear at 200M, just late.
Started fast, settled one-off 3Ls behind the leader, responded well when asked for efforts final 350 M, ran on soundly for 3rd.
Broken fast, urged along to lead on rails, kept going well for home, led 1L in final furlong, but failed to repel the first three final 50M, just lost a place.
Slow to begin, settled 7Ls off the speed patiently, made gradual progress down centre of straight, nearest at finish.
Began with others, patiently ridden at rear as usual, hung out in home straight, made up some ground final 200 M.
Jumped fast, niggled along to share the lead, kept on fairly well early in home straight, could not find extra final 150 M.
Started well, settled 2Ls behind the leader on the fence, bumped at 1100M, only one-paced when asked in the home straight.
Slow to begin, urged along to catch up 6Ls off the pace on rails, made up gradual ground final 300M without threatening the principals.
Began fast, prominently placed within striking distance from the leader, bumped at 1100M, finished off on fairly under pressure, on heels at 200 M, soon faded out.
Started fairly, travelled rearward, caught wide with no cover after 800M, failed to make up any ground in the home straight, checked at 200M.
Out in line, lacked early speed and taken rearward, swung widest for home, only made limited progress in the home straight.
Broken well, pushed to occupy the box-seat just behind the leader, on heels at 1000M, gave limited response when asked at the top of home straight, soon faded out.
Jumped fast, settle in the one out one back spot, weakened early in the home straight, finished tailed out.
Settled in midfield, had good trip throughout with decent pace, 5 to 6Ls down to bend, came with a strong run between runners at 250 M, won with some ease.
No early speed, ended up 6 to 7Ls back in running line, aided by pace, swung wide on turning, made a big finish down middle to score 2nd late.
Drifted back from an awkward draw, raced behind midfield 3 wide with cover, 6Ls down to bend, came wider in straight and finished strongly down outside for place.
Just out with rest, drifted back to race in midfield 5Ls back 3 wide with ease, kept improving on circle made a decent bid in straight but run ended inside 100 M.
Taken back from widest alley, best part of 8Ls away on rails, took inside runs, warmed up late between horses to be not far away in finish.
Well enough away, angled in to trail pace group, 2 to 3Ls away throughout, travelled nicely to turn, led briefly at 200 M but didn't go on with it late.
Jumped in line, pressed on but ended up 3 wide, without cover 3Ls or so back, came 1 wide on turn, just whacked away in straight.
Taken back from wide gate, 6Ls away on rails throughout, used little to bend, checked at 300 M, made only minor progress.
No pace as usual, shared rear 8Ls back, pace helped but was checked at 600 M, plenty to do last on turning.
Fair to begin, raced 4 to 5Ls back on rails in midfield, soft run to home bend, held up at 300 M, didn't find much when clear.
Shared early speed, wide before dropping into 1 out 1 back spot, had OK tempo to turn, didn't find much and folded at 300 M.
Began well, took a sit on leaders back, had the rails run throughout, niggled turning but found little and faded right out.
Shared usual speed to take up running, pestered in front by outside horse, 1L clear on turning, dashed only briefly and soon overhauled, disappointing.
Went forward to race outside leader, kept pace reasonable in mid-section, urged on turning in, faded tamely.

Niggled along on rails to travell in 1L 3rd, steadied on heels of leader coming out of back straight, in similar spot turning in, hit front over 50 M out despite hanging in under
Settled in midfield, soon came to challenge upon straightening, did not find much daylight early in straight before running home strongly inside final 200 M.
Settled in last few, shifted out for a clear run turning in, ran on well to be nearest at finish. (Questioned.)
Began fairly from the widest barrier, travelled wide without cover better than midfield, similar turning in, produced good late impression closing stages.
Began with others, gradually dropped back to last few down far side, shared last swinging for home, made up good late ground down centre of straight.
Travelled wide without cover better than midfield, one-paced without quickening in straight.
Held up behind midfield on rails, saved ground turning in, ran home one-paced under pressure without quickening.
Began with others, gradually settled in a forward spot within 2Ls of speed mainly in 5th, similar turning for home, one-paced under pressure in straight.
Began moderately, soon driven to take narrow lead, headed after straightening, found no extra inside final 200 M.
Slow to muster, made steady headway under pressure going up Rock to reach midfield, one-paced under pressure in the run home.
Soon dropped back from a wide barrier to settle well back, never a danger.
Enjoyed the run of the race tracking the leader along the paint. Drew clear approaching the final 100 M.
Sent forward but was posted 3-wide just behind the speed. Fought on gamely to grab second position.
Led along the fence at even fractions. Faded over the final stages.
Managed to settle 1 out 1 back by the 600 M. Kept on steadily in the home straight.

Travelled just behind the speed, before being hampered near the 600 M, losing some and ground settling 3 back, 1 off with cover. Straightened near the inside and maintained a good gallop right to the wire.
Hampered at the start and received tightening near the 800 M, settling behind midfield the fence. Worked home evenly out wide.
Jumped in at the start then drifted back to camp behind midfield, 1 off with cover. Kept on evenly in the final stretch.
Slow to begin the travelled towards the rear 2 deep with cover. Swung wide on the home turn but only plodded to the line.
Had every chance after settling outside the leader.
Received some tightening after the 800 M, settling back in the event. Never a factor.
Was crowded near the 800 M, settling with the backmakers along the fence. Failed to close off.
Settled at the rear early then copped a check near the 800 M, never recovered and finished well back.
2-wide behind pace. Challenged leader rounding home turn. Hit front final furlong. Easy.
3-wide in the front rank passing winning post first time. Eventually took lead 1000 M out. Held the winner from 400 M until outrun final furlong. Barely clung on for 2nd.
Quickly into stride. Took box-seat passing winning post first time. Hard ridden from 500 M to chase the leading pair. Just failed to snatch 2nd.
2-wide at rear. Vigorously ridden and was 7Ls down rounding home turn. Made up good ground home straight.
Given reminder early to race 2-wide ahead of midfield. Under pressure from 500 M but only plugged on home.
Began well, ended up towards rear on fence from 1300 M. Pressed home turn but remained one-paced.
At rear on fence until making up some ground close home.
Travelled wide and without cover at midfield. Moved up to race outside the leading pair down the Rock but faded soon after straightening.
2-wide behind midfield. No progress home straight.
Fair break, no rush early, settled third last one off, stoked up on turn, rapid progress to lead 150 M out, comfortably.
Good break, settled midfield one off, made ground exiting back, third into straight, led 200 M out until collared by winner.
Well away, ridden out wide to lead first turn, headed far side but retained rail, led early straight, unable to resist first two.
Steadied start, taken to last one off, tried to follow winner round outside when that horse took off, ran on, not enough pace.
Fair break, unhurried, took rail mid-rear, ridden turn to make ground rail, never quite able to challenge.
Fair break, joined leading group three wide, settled fourth one off, urged turn, ridden and kept on but no real progress.
Moderate start, ridden to lead on rail, headed and back to fourth, ridden early straight, kept on, not quicken.
Steadied start, held up rear, shaken up turn, kept on steadily until gap closed late and no more progress.
Fair break out wide but caught four wide and no route to rail, ridden turn, second into straight, ridden, weakened.
Fair break, ridden from gate but caught wide, always wide, driven, no progress.
Broke well, settled rail in fifth, every chance, ridden straight, found nil.
Away well, ridden but unable to lead, fourth one off, urged but gradually slipped back.
Fair break, well positioned fourth one off, improved rail, gap came early straight, ran on well to lead 200 M out.
Missed beat start but ridden up to lead early, set even pace two lengths clear, quickened sharply turn, kept on but not match winner.
Well away, claimed rail in second, quickened with first two, no extra close home.
Fair break, positioned midfield one off, up to fifth turn, ridden and kept on but no real kick.
Fair break, eased inside and held up third last rail, briefly baulked early straight, ran on but never able to challenge.
Fair break, looked for rail but nudged out early, held up fourth last, ridden turn, kept on wide but no real impact.
Steadied start, taken back to second last one off, ridden and improved turn, wide bid but never got to grips.
Broke well, up on pace settled third one off, asked to improve early straight, found little.
Well away, not rushed early settled near rear rail, ridden exiting back, never able to challenge.
Quick break, settled fifth rail, inside bid, ridden, no progress.

Midfield, 6-1/2Ls off the leader on the fence, benefited by the fast pace and the rail-trip, progressed steadily 300 M for 3rd.
Hard ridden forward, parked 1L off the leader 2-wide, harmed by the fast early sectionals, ran on well to the line.
Bumped start, hard ridden forward, checked first bend, 4Ls off the fast pace on the fence, just ran on ok in straight.
