Trapped 3-wide throughout in midfield, 4Ls off the fast pace, just held ground in straight.
Eased back, 10Ls off the leader 2 to 3-wide, suited by the fast tempo, progressed steadily 300 M.
Behind midfield, 6-1/2Ls off the leader 2 to 3-wide, favoured by the fast pace, made ground 300 M.
Very slow away, 8Ls off the leader on the fence, helped by the fast tempo, made minor ground 200 M.
Eased to rear and took rail, more than 10Ls off the leader, suited by the fast pace, made some ground in straight along the fence.
Urged early to occupy a one-off position 2Ls off the pace, responded well when asked for efforts final 400 M, hit the front at 250 M, kept on soundly to win.
Settled one-off 4Ls off the speed, made up gradual ground under pressure final 450 M, kept battling on under maximum pressure, just narrowly beaten by the winner.
Niggled along to hold a one-off spot in midfield, dashed well under pressure final 300 M, but bit too late, kept on for 3rd.
Settled one from the rear 5Ls behind the pace, responded well when asked at the top of home straight, ran on steadily along the inner part of the track, just late for a place.
Patiently ridden and soon settled 8Ls off the pace at the rear, unbalanced at 1400 M, finished off satisfactorily final 250 M, but never really troubled the principals.
Settled in the one-out-one-back spot easily, niggled along rounding the home turn, only one-paced under maximum pressure in the straight.
Driven to lead and found the rails near 1200 M, passed near 250 M, soon flattened.
Taken rearward from gate 7 but soon caught up 4Ls off the pace, unbalanced at 1400 M, niggled along rounding the bend, failed to make up any ground in the straight.
Awkward start, urged along to catch up 2Ls off the pace, on heels at 1400 M, lost cover and caught 3-wide from 1200 M, ran up to share the lead at 700 M, weakened at 200 M.
Settled cosily 1L behind the leader on rails, struggled from 500 M, only one-paced at the top of home straight, on heels at 200 M, soon weakened.
Held up in midfield and guided to a rail position passing 800 M, switched to outer on straightening, ran on strongly final 200 M and got up close home.
Swiftly away then restrained to a position ahead of midfield, moved closer rounding the home turn, ran on well under a strong drive to take 2nd last stride.
Ordinary jump only but quickly pushed to 3rd position, responded well turning in and took over from 250 M, led till dying strides.
Average start, positioned in midfield but was kept wide without cover in first half of the race, picked up gradually and did best work towards finish.
Quickly into stride and pressed leader to straight, ran on one-paced. (Jockey dropped whip at 200 M.)
Switched off and taken across to the fence shortly after the start, remained in the rear section to straight, finished fastest final 400 M.
Held up in mid-division, headway from 350 M but had to shift away from beaten runner mid straight, turned one paced final 100 M.
Broke smartly and chased leaders in a 3-wide position without cover, not quickened on straightening.
Taken back on jumping from draw 11, raced in 2nd last to home turn, shifted wide passing 500 M to improve but only one paced finish down the outside of track.
Taken across behind runners soon after the jump and raced as the backmarker 7Ls off the pace, driven 350 M out but made very limited progress.
Behind midfield throughout and made no impression in straight. Never threatened.
Took up running passing 1000 M but was difficult to settle once in front, headed 250 M and weakened rapidly from 150 M. (Unacceptable Performance.)
Started well, settled 2-wide 3Ls off the pace, kicked strongly in the home straight, led at 200 M, won easily.
Out in line, patiently ridden in the early stages, held a one-off position 5Ls behind the leader, quickened well final 200 M, but never really threatened the winner.
Bumped after start, urged along to catch up 4Ls off the speed on rails, responded well when asked for efforts in the home straight, ran on soundly for 3rd.
Bumped after start, settled 6Ls off the pace on the fence, kept going well along the inner side of the track, but lacked a decisive kick final 200 M.
Jumped fast, settled in the box-seat just behind the leaders, only one-paced under pressure in the home straight. (Lost left hind plate.)
Slow to begin, niggled along to catch up 7Ls off the speed on rails, checked at 1600 M, made up some ground in the home straight.
Began well, pushed to occupy the one out one back spot, weakened at the top of home straight, dropped out.
Widely drawn, taken towards the rear, shifted wide for home, only made limited progress in the concluding stages.
Jumped fastest, took the lead easily, got tired at early home straight, faded out.
Broke well from gate 10, soon taken to the rear to obtain cover, failed to make up any ground in the home straight.
Out in line, travelled wide without cover throughout the trip, swung widest for home, never nearer.
Checked after start, restrained to a 3-wide position at rear, gave no response when asked at the top of straight, tailed out.
Began in line, trailed first few with ideal run 4Ls away in mid section, set out after leader at 400 M, hit front inside 150 M and drew away to score easily.
Just out with rest, sat in ideal spot 1 out 1 back, 3Ls or so back throughout, couldn't dash but kept on well to snatch 2nd late.
Showed speed, raced on pace first without cover 2Ls or more back, fair run with race to suit, kept on evenly to snatch a place.
Fast out, took up running after some early work, rolled along freely 2 to 3 Ls clear, kicked on circle, weakened inside 150 M but was still able to make frame.
Dropped into midfield from a wide draw, raced 4 to 5 Ls back throughout, used little to bend, made some minor ground without really threatening.
No early speed, shared rear soon after start, 8Ls or so back in running line, set too much to do but made many lengths late from well back on turn. Good effort.
Just fair to begin, raced in midfield on rails, had a soft trip to bend, 4 to 5Ls back and niggled turning, only made minor ground in straight. (No explanation.)
Taken back, raced behind midfield 5 to 6Ls off top end, even run throughout, same margin back to bend, one speed in run home.
Ordinary jump and soon dropped to rear, near to tail 7Ls from them, ok trip, saved ground on bend, passed a few tired runners in straight.
Fast away, led early before taken a trail, tracked decent speed throughout, forced to chase from 500 M, pressured bend and gradually faded.
No early pace, at tail 8Ls off leaders, struggled to keep in touch first part, last turning, made no serious progress in straight.
Standard jump, 6Ls away on fence, no excuses, ordinary response and never factored.

Broke well, with leaders early, gradually settled in 5th over 3Ls off the speed near mid-division, switched sharply to avoid heels upon straightening, fought on down straight to just get up on line.

Began with others, quickly driven to take up running, failed to cross to rails and settled in one-out-one-back spot, hit front upon straightening, fought on under pressure to be just pipped at post. (Questioned for forward tactic.)
Settled at the back, wide into straight, made significant progress down centre of straight to be nearest at finish.
Settled in midfield, lost position and dropped towards rear rounding home bend, produced good late finish to do best work late.
Soon picked up along rails to travel in 2L 3rd, briefly baulked for a run upon straightening, ran on steadily to be nearest at finish.
Began with others, settled in forward of midfield, in closer order when bumped on straightening, kept on one pace in the run home.
Settled in midfield on rails, saved ground turning in, did not find much room until 200 M out, recovered some late ground closing stages.
Soon dropped towards rear despite ridden along, checked and lost position coming out of back straight, ran on past beaten horses in the run home.
Began fairly, raced wide without cover in rear of midfield down far side, ran home one-paced before fading inside final 100 M.
In last few to straight, kept on same pace without quickening under pressure.
Always in last few on rails, saved ground turning in, found nothing under pressure in the run home.
Not far off at far side, dropped back to about 3L 4th around the bend, kept on before fading inside final 200 M.
Raced wide without cover just worse than midfield, ran home one-paced.
Began only fairly from the widest barrier, travelled wide down far side before gaining a 1L break around the bend, headed shortly after straightening and folded up quickly.
Raced with the leading division 3 deep without cover. Fought on strongly under heavy pressure to prevail in the shadows of the post.
Enjoyed a nice run in the race, settling in 2nd position along the fence. forged to the lead near the furlong but was collared close to home.
Travelled at the tail of the field. Switched out early in the straight and closed off soundly.
Raced prominently, 2 back, 1 off with cover. Was overhauled in the run to the finish.
Remained racing 1 off in the lead for most of the trip. Faded inside the last 100m.
Travelled midfield but was caught on a limb 4 wide with some cover on the circle. Was gassed over the concluding stages.
Positioned midfield, 1 off with cover. Kept on one paced in the home straight.
Raced behind midfield the fence. Kept to the inside in the straight and worked home evenly.
Tracked the on pace runners along the fence. Had every chance.
Settled with the backmakers, 3-4 wide with cover. Struggled in the home straight.
Raced with the leaders but posted 4 deep without cover. Never a factor.

Placing: UR
Comment: Travelled behind the speed 3 wide with cover. Clipped heels turning for home and dislodged rider.
Ridden early and middle stages to maintain 2-wide behind midfield. Moved closer home turn. Swung wide and was 4Ls down on straightening. Finished off strongly and won with comfort.

Soon taken to rear from high draw. Long way back early and middle stages despite effort of rider. Improved wide gradually home turn. 7Ls adrift turning in. No hope with the winner but did the best of the rest.
Hard ridden early. Settled 2-wide behind the pace group stable bend. Angled out to challenge leaders approaching home straight. Kept on but lacked the finishing touch of the front pair.

Vigorously ridden early to hold a spot behind midfield on fence. Similar position home turn. Left the rail and was 5Ls back into final stretch. Responded fairly well under strong pressure to make frame.
Pressed early to occupy prominent spot from stable bend. Ideal position to strike home straight but was one-paced to conclude.
Drawn high, trapped wide stable bend. Eventually parked 3-wide ahead of midfield back straight. 3Ls away turning into home. Plugged on but not threatening.
Began well. Took lead on fence from stable bend. Held a 1L advantage rounding home turn. Hung on until final furlong. Weakened closing stages.
Urged along the fence at midfield through to home straight. Improved inside until got traffic at 150M. Not fully tested.
Towards rear on fence. Ridden home turn and made up minor ground late.
3-wide behind midfield. No real progress in the straight.
2-wide towards rear. Beat tired runners home.
Driven forward from wide barrier and settled outside the leader back straight. Dropped off soon after straightening.
2-wide at midfield through to home straight. No response when asked and faded final furlong.
Travelled wide and without cover behind pace. Weakened badly home straight. (Lame right fore.)
Not well away but soon up to take good position midfield rail, always going well, switched out to challenge mid-track, led 200m out, easily.
Well away, up to second rail, led and ridden early straight, kept on but unable to resist winner.
Broke well, joined leaders but two off, eased back to fifth one off, mid-track bid but outpaced.
Fair break, eased back to rear rail, improved early straight, ran on well late under driving.
Moderate start, not rushed, held up rear one off, out for wide bid straight, ran on but never near to challenge.
Well away, ridden up wide, settled third one off, early bid straight, kept on but not quicken.
Fair break but lacked early pace, settled midfield rail, ridden early straight but no further progress.
Well away, no early rush, settled mid-rear one off, out for mid-track bid in straight, driven, no impact.
Well away, led on rail early, then settled fifth rail, bustled exiting back, very little progress.
Fair break, not rushed, taken back to rear to find rail, angled out to one off, ridden turn, modest late progress.
Well away, up to early lead one off, crossed to rail, tried to kick early straight, headed and weakened.
Fair break, bustled early but lacked pace to lead, mid-track bid straight, no kick, weakened late.
Missed break losing length, rail third last, improved slightly far side, ridden turn, found little.
Fair break, no early speed, mid-rear one off, ridden turn, no progress.
Well away, settled mid-rear rail, out to challenge but denied run mid-straight, finished very strongly once clear.
Moderate break, ridden up to lead wide, crossed to rail, second into straight, kicked well to lead by two entering last 100m, unable to resist winner.
Good break, settled fifth one off, short of room early straight, switched inside, ran on well.
Fast out, ridden up for share of early lead, settled fourth on rail, hard driven mid-straight, kept on but not quite pace to challenge.
Fair break out wide but caught four deep without cover, made ground leaving back to lead into straight, ridden and weakened late.
Missed break, bustled up along rail but still second last, pulled out for wide bid, ran on but no extra late.
Well away the caught three wide, made ground approaching straight to take fourth, ridden, weakened late.
Broke well but caught wide, wide challenge straight, kept on but not get to leaders.
Moderate break, held up last on rail pulling slightly, looking for room straight, slightly hampered, not much progress.
Good break, bustled up to lead, reined back to fourth on rail not settling, ridden early straight, found little.
Lost length start, midfield one off, moved wide iinto straight, short of room and slight bump, some late progress when switched inside.
Fair break, up to third two off, ridden straight, gradually lost ground.
Well away but caught wide, and pulling, taken back towards rear but still wide, shaken up, found nil.
Eased to rear, progressed steadily towards rail, 8Ls off the leader, harmed by the slow pace, held up badly 4-2, stormed home strongly when clear and scored.
Awkward away, hard ridden for a midfield spot along the fence, 6Ls off the leader, not suited by the slow pace, demonstrated strong finishing efforts 400M and grabbed 2nd.
Pushed to occupy a prominent spot, 1.5Ls off the leader 2 wide, benefited by the slow sectionals, ran on well to the line for 3rd.
Eased back as usual, 6.5Ls off the leader, trapped 4-5 wide throughout and lost too much ground, harmed by the slow pace, dashed strongly 300M.
Behind midfield, 6Ls off the leader 2 wide, momentarily held up 400M, dashed well when clear despite not suited by the slow pace.
Hard ridden to take the rail in front, then eased back for box seat, enjoyed the slow tempo, hit front 350M, overhauled and flattened 150M.
Eased back, 7.5Ls off the leader 2-3 wide, harmed by the slow pace, held up 4-2, little dash when clear.
Pushed early, sat 3Ls off the slow pace, trapped 3 wide, moved forward 700M, flattened 200M.
Pushed early, but soon eased to sit behind the front runners, 4Ls off the leader 2-3 wide, harmed by the slow tempo, just held ground in straight.
Mid-back, trapped 4-5 wide throughout and lost too much ground, clipped heels and blundered 800M, harmed by the slow pace, ran on ok to the line despite all negative racing situations.
Pushed to sit in front of midfield, 4.5Ls off the leader 3-4 wide, harmed by the slow pace, no turn of foot in straight.
Pushed to take box seat early, checked 800M, not suited by the slow tempo, flattened 250M.
Pushed to take the rail and led by 1L at slow sectionals, soon out of fuel 300M.
Eased back, trapped 3-4 wide, harmed by the slow pace, never competitive.
Settled 3Ls off the pace on rails, checked and blocked early in the home straight, kicked when asked at 200 m, bumped at 150 M, checked again at 100 M, finished off strongly when clear, just in time.
Lacked early speed as usual despite being pushed along, ended up settling 5Ls off the leader, clicked into gears when asked for efforts final 250 M, bumped at 150 M and 50 M, narrowly beaten.
Easily ran up to share the lead on rails, quickened well when asked at the top of home straight, kept on soundly under maximum pressure, headed in by the top two in the last few strides.
Sat in a one-off spot in the mid-division, ran on well final 250 M and looked possible to score, lacked a decisive kick final 100 M, just missed a place. (Sustained a cut to left hind plate.)
Broke well, ran up quickly to share the lead on 2-deep, headed in at 300 M, kept on satisfactorily under maximum pressure.
Settled 4Ls off the pace, caught wide throughout the trip, made gradual ground down centre of home straight final 250 M, but never really threatened the principals, bumped at 50 M.
Lacked early speed as usual and travelled 6Ls off the pace at the rear, took time to pick up at the top of home straight, only made up limited ground final 150 M.
Widely drawn, worked early to get across just behind the pace on 2-deep, only held ground when placed under pressure in the home straight, couldn't find extra final 150 M. (Bled.)
Crowded start, settled 3Ls off the pace on 3-wide, only one-paced in the home straight, crowded at 150 M, never really troubled the principals.
Niggled along to occupy the box-seat, only held ground when placed under pressure in the home straight, flatten passing the 200 M pole, soon faded.
Worked hard early to join the lead, caught 3-wide with no cover, got tired near 200 M, checked at 150 M, soon faded.
Slow away, lacked early speed and soon drifted back towards the rear, crowded at 700 M and 400 M, checked at 150 M, made no progress in the home straight.
Caught 3-4 wide in midfield and raced without cover from 1100M, picked up well and moved to the front inside 200M, battled on to fend off the persistent runner up final 150M. Just held on.
Travelled strongly in midfield, shaken up 400M and made rapid headway, dueled with the eventual winner final 150M and was just touched off on the line.
Switched off to the rear and given a patient ride, switched out into clear 300M and finished off the race strongly. (Jockey dropped his left rein inside 100M.)
Mid-division early, shifted out to 3-wide near 1200M and closed in on leaders approaching home straight, briefly led 300M-200M, weakened in late stages.
In midfield along the fence, held up behind beaten runners until 250M, ran on well to take 5th.
With leaders early, eased off approaching 1000M to sit in 3rd, had his chance but got outsprinted passing 200M, one paced in late stages.
Unable to shift in and caught 4-wide in a position towards the rear, driven along 600M and finished off the race fairly in straight. (Jockey reminded to use sufficient vigour on his horses.)
Held up in last about 9Ls off the pace in early stages, saved ground along the fence, headway 400M out but never looked like reaching the leaders.
In touch, made a short-lived effort early straight, one-paced final 200M.
Restrained to a position behind midfield, 3-wide over the home turn and shuffled back to last approaching straight, made limited progress final 200M.
Positively ridden from the outset but unable to cross whilst in the lead, set a good pace first 800M, kept on early straight but weakened inside 300M.
Rushed along early to find his way to the front and set a solid tempo in the first half of the race, one-paced turning for home, weakened rapidly final 150M.
Dropped back to the rear about 8Ls off the pace, in early stages, moved closer over the home turn as the pace slackened, found nothing when asked 350M, soon behind.
Checked after start, restrained to 9Ls off the speed, finished strongly when asked for efforts in the home straight, hit the front in the last few strides.
Awkward start, urged along to catch up 2Ls behind the leader on 2-deep, kicked strongly to lead at 100M, looked possible to score, caught by the winner in last few strides.
Jumped fast, pushed to occupy the box-seat just behind the leader, quickened up well when asked in the home straight, but couldn't threaten the first two.
Out in line, settled 7-8Ls off the pace, responded well when asked in the home straight, made up gradual ground, hang in final 200M.
Broken well, settled one-off 4Ls off the pace, only one-paced under pressure in the home straight.
Jumped fastest, niggled along to take the lead, kept on fairly early in home straight, could not find extra final 150 M.
Began with others, settled 2-wide 6Ls off the speed, made gradual progress in the home straight, nearest at finish.
Awkwardly started, urged along to catch up 6Ls off the pace on rails, blocked at 300M, made up some ground when clear.
Started fairly, pushed to hold a fence position in the mid-division, only gave limited respond under pressure, flattened near 200M, dropped out.
Taken back from the widest barrier, swung widest for home, made up some late ground and passed a few tired runners.
Broken fairly, lacked early speed as usual, travelled rearward throughout the trip, never competitive. (Lame in left front leg.)
Jumped well, settled in the one out one back spot, hung out at 600M, weakened at the top of straight, faded out.
Slow to begin, travelled at the rear, found nothing in the home straight. (Lame in left front knee and left eye corneal ulcer.)
Began moderately, travelled wide without cover throughout the trip, gave no response when asked, finished well back. (Heart irregularity.)
Out in line, camped just off pace group, 3Ls back on rails, came with a strong run at 250 M when gap appeared, finished off too strongly for rivals to score nicely.
Fair to begin, raced in midfield on rails 4 to 5Ls back, had a soft run, followed eventual winner on bend, shifted into clear 200 M and closed well last bit.
Rest assured from a wide gate, well back 9 to 10Ls off top end, saved ground on rails but still last turning in, produced a big finish from tail to snatch 3rd late.
Slow into stride, soon near to rear 8Ls back, raced 2 wide in mid-section, came wide turning, made many lengths down middle to make frame.
Bounced out, led before taking a trail when pressured, behind leader to bend, took inside runs but just held position in run to line.
Positioned well in midfield off solid speed, did overrace in mid-section, 4Ls back to turn, kept on evenly in finish.
Angled in behind midfield, raced 6Ls back in a 2 wide position, made some improvement on circle, challenged at 300 M but that was shortlived.
Showed good speed early, pushed on to race outside leader, used plenty in speed duel there to 300 M before early burn took toll.
Away OK, posted 3 wide not far off solid pace, did too much without cover to bend, joined in and led briefly at 250 M, condition gave out late.
Began well, landed 1 out 1 back position, did some work with speed on and raced a bit keenly, a minor chance before checked at 300 M, tired thereafter.
Out in line, forced to race 3 wide from an awkward draw, 5Ls back on settling, had cover to bend, came down middle but no progress inside 200 M.
Crowded early, 6 to 7Ls back on rails, pace advantaged, still well back to bend, made no real progress.
Bounced out, used plenty to drive through and lead, worked throughout by outside horse, under pressure straightening, dropped out at 300 M.
Taken back from an awkward alley 3 wide at rear 7Ls or more from top end, never really looked comfortable going speed, whacked away.

Travelled outside leader early, taken back to one-back position in 3rd, came to challenge turning in and soon hit front, won readily.
Settled about 3Ls off the speed in 5th, remained same turning for home, ran on steadily in straight despite hanging in, never threatening.
Began well from the 6 gate, disputed lead 3-wide early then 2-wide down far side and around home bend, one-paced under pressure in the run home.
Trailed the small field about 4Ls off the speed, kept on past two beaten horses in home straight.
Restrained to about 2Ls off the pace, moved close up on rails rounding home bend, found nothing under pressure in one-back position on straightening.
Began well, held narrow advantage most of way to 350 M, folded up quickly. (Questioned for disappointing performance.)
Stalked the leader after the 800m on the rails. Shifted out early in the straight and drew clear after the 200m winning convincingly.
Couldn't match the early speed of the race and got shuffled back to settle behind midfield, 2 deep with cover. Knuckled down to its task after the furlong and finished off well.
Camped in 4th spot along the rail. Loomed up at the 200m but failed to sustain its effort and was hampered close to the line.
Travelled back in the event eventually settling last after being tightened for room near the 800m. Worked home soundly despite being baulked over the latter stages.
Enjoyed a nice run in the race, settling in 3rd position, 1 off. Kept on one paced over the concluding stages.
Missed the start then was ridden along, crossing to the lead on the fence after the 800m. weakened inside the final furlong.
Took up a midfield position 2 wide with cover. Only paddled in the run to the winning post.
Settled back in the field, 1 off with cover. Looked for inside runs in the final stretch but just whacked away over the final stages.
Travelled midfield but was posted most of the trip wide and without cover. Struggled in the run home.
Taken back soon after the start to settle with the backmakers, 3 deep with cover. Peeled out on straightening but was never likely.

Eased to race 2-wide towards rear from high draw. Swung widest and was 6Ls down turning in. Made up ground rapidly top of home straight. Battled determinedly inside final furlong and prevailed final strides.

Towards rear on fence. Took inside run and was 6Ls away home turn. Soon found clear run near the fence in the straight. Fought on gamely and looked extremely dangerous final 150 M. Just failed to last.

Taken to race 2-wide at rear. Came wide to track the eventual winner and was 7Ls off rounding home turn. Rallied strongly but was always a length behind the eventual winner. Snatched 3rd near the post.
Quickly into stride. Rolled along and led on fence from 1100 M. Travelled well to home straight and opened up a 2Ls gap at 400 M. Kept on until overhauled by the front trio closing stages.
Raced ahead of midfield on fence. Gradually shifted 4-wide and was 2 to 3Ls back approaching home straight. Kept chasing the principals final stretch but couldn't get closer.
Midfield on fence. Moved closer home turn. Shifted 3-wide and was 4Ls adrift turning into home. Failed to quicken thereafter.
Raced 2-wide ahead of midfield early. Shuffled to midfield from 1300 M. Peeled out entering home straight. Found nothing when asked. (Wounded left hind.).
Soon taken to rear on fence from wide barrier. Given reminder and was 6Ls behind pace home turn. Made up some ground in restricted room early home straight before held up at 250 M. Resumed fairly.
Behind midfield on fence. Switched out and tried to improve top of home straight but was soon held up. Never really afforded clear run.
Away in line but was caught wide. Gradually taken to race 2-wide behind midfield. Shifted 4-wide for clear run on straightening but soon got traffic until passing 200 M. No progress thereafter.
Ridden early and sat 2-wide behind leader. Faded top of home straight.
Travelled wide and without cover behind pace through to home straight. Soon flattened.
3-wide at midfield. Wide into home straight. Dropped out well before finish.
Pressed forward early and settled behind the leader on fence. Struggled passing 500 M and weakened badly.
Jumped fastest, urged along and soon settled 2Ls behind the leader on rails, took the lead at 350M, kept going well to score.
Began well, settled 2-wide 4Ls off the pace, finished strongly down centre of the home straight, ran on soundly for 2nd.
Started well and settled in midfield, on heels at 1200M, travelled wide without cover after 1000M, ran on well final 300 M, but never threaten the first two.
Checked after start, urged early and soon settle 7Ls off the speed on rails, shifted wide for home, kicked well when clear at 300M, nearest at finish.
Started awkwardly, niggled along to lead at a fast tempo, caught at 350 M, held ground until flattened at 150 M.
Awkward start, settled one-off 5Ls behind the leader, only made limited progress in the home straight, rather one-paced.
Broke well, urged along to occupy a fence position 3Ls off the pace, niggled along rounding the home turn, only one-paced in the home straight.
Taken back from gate 10, patiently ridden in the early stages, made gradual ground when asked for efforts final 350 M, rather one-paced.
Slow to begin, urged along and travelled 9Ls off the pace, closed off the race well under pressure despite being blocked at 150M.
Broke fast, restrained to a one-off spot 3Ls behind the leader, on held ground early in the home straight, couldn't find extra final 150 M.
Taken back from gate 11, swung to widest for home, made limited progress under pressure, just passed a few tired runners.
Bumped after start, settled one-off 8Ls off the speed, gave no response when asked for efforts in the home straight, dropped out.
Began with others, pushed to hold a fence position in midfield, found nothing in the home straight.
Taken rearward from the wide draw, on heels at 800 M, travelled wide, never competitive.
Broke fast, easily ran up to lead 1L, quickened well when asked passing the 400 M pole, couldn't find no extra final 50 M, just did enough to win.
Jumped well, settled 2Ls off the pace, clicked into gear at 300 M, finished off strongly under maximum pressure, just late.
Prominently placed within striking distance from the leader, on heels at 400 M, ran on soundly final 250 M for 3rd.
Travelled 4Ls off the pace early, proved difficult to settle when restrained, on heels at 500 M, made ground steadily final 300 M, just missed a place.
Crowded start, settled 3Ls off the pace, blocked from 400 M to 300 M, made gradual ground when clear at 200 M, bit too one-paced.
Easily ran up and soon settled just behind the leader, travelled satisfactorily until got tired passing 200 M.
Prominently placed 2Ls off the pace, crowded at 400 M, gave nothing when placed under pressure, soon faded.
Lacked early speed despite being niggled along, travelled 4-5Ls off the pace, failed to make up any ground in the closing stages.
Settled 3Ls off the pace, gave no response when asked for efforts final 350 M soon dropped out.
Showed good early speed but travelled bit keenly in the early stages, kept on until flattened at 250 M, soon weakened.
Lacked early speed and struggled in the rear throughout the trip, only passed a few tired runners in the closing stages.
Crowded start, urged early and travelled 4Ls off the pace, failed to quicken when placed under pressure halfway, never competitive.
Broke well, urged along to track the leader on the stand rails, got tired near 300 M, gave ground.
Never better than midfield, held ground until flattened at 250 M, finished tailed out.
Hard ridden to occupy the box seat, not suited by the fast tempo, closed the race off strongly to win by a short head.
Eased to sit in midfield, 4.5Ls off the leaders along the fence, benefited by the fast pace, progressed steadily 300M, just beaten by a very narrow margin in 2nd.
Eased to rear and took rail, 7Ls off the leaders, suited by the fast pace, held up 4-2, progressed steadily when clear and grabbed 3rd.
Pushed forward, 1.5Ls off the leaders 2 wide, not suited by the fast sectionals, just held ground in straight.
Midfield, 3.5Ls off the leaders on the rails, favoured by the fast tempo, made minor ground in straight.
Eased to rear, 6Ls off the leaders 2-3 wide, helped by the fast pace, made steady ground 300M.
Behind midfield, 5.5Ls off the leaders along the fence, benefited by the fast tempo, ran on ok in final stages.
Hard ridden to take the rail and shared the lead at fast sectionals, out of fuel 350M.
Midfield, 3Ls off the leaders 3 wide, suited by the fast pace, raced flat in last quarter.
Eased to rear, 7.5Ls off the leaders 2-3 wide, benefited by the fast tempo, however no progress.
Eased back, 3 wide, checked 1400M, favoured by the fast pace, but never competitive.
Hard ridden early but not muster, checked 1400M, 4.5Ls off the leaders 3-4 wide, suited by the fast tempo, however emptied 400M.
Eased to sit in front of midfield, 3Ls off the fast pace 2 wide, weakened in straight.
Pushed forward to share the lead in 2 wide, not suited by the fast tempo, dropped off rapidly 400M.
Broke well, settled last early one off, eased through field to lead 150m out, different class.
Unruly before start, fair break, second in mid-track halfway, led 250m out until swept aside by winner.
Broke well, steadied behind the pace, ran on well late, outpaced by winner.
Broke fast, led early, crossed to rail, headed, kept on but outpaced.
Slight bobble start, rear on outside early, tried to quicken centre, no impression.
Well away, settled behind leader near rail, short of room briefly, kept on but never a threat.
Broke well, outpaced early, ridden halfway, no extra under pressure.
Broke well, good early speed, led halfway two off rail, headed, weakened.
Broke well, settled behind pace, ridden halfway, no extra speed.
Fair break, tried to follow mid-track speed, ridden halfway, weakened.
In 3rd chasing leaders, always handy, rapid headway from 350M and took over near 200M, kept on well under pressure.
Taken back to rear 7Ls off the pace, shifted out approaching 450M to commence his run, finished fastest final 400M, nearest finish.
Held up in last 7Ls behind leaders, saved ground along inside but was in the most unpromising spot turning for home, picked up strongly from 300M, came through to take 3rd close home, nearest finish.
Travelled well on the rail 3-4Ls behind leaders, challenged strongly from 400M and looked a winner halfway down the straight, faded inside 100M, drifted out and lost 2nd place close home.
Taken back and moved across to find the rail soon after the start, made steady progress from 300M, not beaten far.
Close enough to leaders but was caught wide throughout the back straight, kept on one pace to line and found no extra to challenge.
Held up in midfield and raced a shade keen down the back straight, hung out badly under pressure in straight and never able to challenge, unbalanced near 100M.
Went forward soon after the start and pressed leader on the outside, took up inside 400M, kept on for another 200M then weakened.
Set the pace while being pressed from the outside by a rival, headed passing 300M and had little left in final stages.
Placed 3-wide behind midfield and left without cover from 800M, not quickened when placed under pressure 400M, eased 150M.
Behind midfield, lost touch approaching 400M, soon behind.
Fast away, settled rail in fourth, ridden to lead mid-straight, drew away easily.
Good break but caught three wide midfield, challenged down centre straight, ran on strongly without being able to threaten.
Fast away, led, two clear exiting back, challenged by winner early straight, struggled but overpowered, caught for second 100m out.
Fair break, ridden up to third one off, fourth into straight kept on down centre but no impact.
Fair break, sixth one off, kept on with usual determination but never able to challenge.
Steadied start and held up rear rail, wove between horses to run on well late.
Lost length start, up on rail to seventh, stuck to rail straight, some progress before flattening out.
Fair break, steadied back to rear two off, brought wide straight, ran on but never near to challenge.
Lost half length at break, three wide near rear, wide straight, kept on, no kick.
Fair break out wide, unhurried early, settled share of last one off, shaken up early straight, kept on without being able to threaten.
Sluggish start, ridden early, rear group, ridden straight, no impression.
Fair break, not pace to go with leaders, back to fifth last one off, ridden straight but never near leaders.
Well away but caught four wide, up to second one off, ridden turn, found little, weakened, eased.
Moderate break, up to midfield rail, ridden straight, found nil.
Showed speed, held lead despite being beached, dictated speed to suit, outside horses shaded on circle, headed at 300 M but fought back strongly to score a handy victory.
Even jump, caught wide and attempted to drop in, keen when speed steadied and forced 3 and 4 wide without cover, improved to hit lead at 300 M but leader fought back last 100 M.
No early speed and soon towards rear, 7Ls away on rails throughout, improved gradually on circle and took inside runs turning, did best work late to close into a place.
Not much speed, ended up in rear division, 6 to 7Ls off speed, came 2 wide on circle, kept improving 3 and 4 wide rounding bend, made steady ground to 200 M.
Faded back from a tricky alley, 3 wide 6Ls from top end, improved with a trail on circle, made some late progress to be nearest on line.
Began well and assumed a box seat role, had all favours in run, steadied turning in, only had 1 speed when clear and held same position to finish.
Used a bit to cross and challenge for front, shaded leader to bend, kept challenging but was outdashed at 300 M, folded late.
Only fair to begin, ended up 3 wide in midfield 4Ls or so away with cover, lost spot and bumped turn, only a fair response when clear last 300 M.
Began well enough, went forward but caught 3 wide, did have cover 3Ls from lead, niggled approaching bend, gradually faded out in straight.
Little early pace, 6Ls away on rails, checked at 700 M, saved ground on bend, came home at same speed.
Assumed a midfield position, 2 wide 3 to 4Ls away in pack with little room turning and lost spot, no extra from 300 M.
Began well, held a spot on leaders back, overraced on rails throughout, too keen to bend, there turning but didn't let down, faded.
Posted wide at rear from outside draw, 7 to 8Ls off speed, still 3 and 4 wide last turning, made no impression in straight.
Showed more speed than usual, 1 to 2Ls away 3 wide without cover, did too much to turn, dropped out tamely.

Began moderately, gradually moved up along rails in back straight to be just 2Ls off the pace, saved ground on inside turning in, ran on under pressure to gain upper hand passing 100 M.
Began with others, close up on rails before gaining narrow advantage coming off the Rock, maintained similar lead early in straight until swamped passing 100 M.
Niggled at in first few, taken back to 2L 4th halfway down far side, about 3L back in 5th around home bend, came under pressure soon after straightening, ran on steadily to reach 3rd late.
Travelled wide without cover from a wide barrier, rolled forward up the Rock to join leaders, 3-wide in 3rd rounding home bend, unable to sustain effort under pressure in the run home.

Began well, settled in 2L 4th before steadied and lost position early in back straight, renewed effort from 6th in forward of midfield approaching home bend, closer up turning in, kept on early in straight but found no extra near home.
Settled one from last after beginning from a wide barrier, commenced move around the bend, made steady headway in straight to be nearest at finish.
Began from the widest gate with others, soon taken back to trail the field, remained in last into straight, kept on past beaten horses closing stages.
Settled just worse than midfield, briefly short of room after straightening, kept on steadily without quickening. (Questioned for disappointing performance.)
Began moderately, remained in last few most of way, attempting to improve when steadied on rails about 500 M out, saved ground turning in but ran home one-paced.
Began moderately, raced wide at around midfield most of way to straight, folded up quickly after straightening.
Remained in rear of midfield despite niggled along, remained flat-footed when pace quickened around the bend, did nothing from the last spot into straight.
Ridden from a middle gate to gain slender early lead, dropped back to close 2nd around home bend, soon faded out of contention after straightening. (Questioned for disappointing performance.)
Crowded soon after the start, then ridden along to settle 4 back the fence. Peeled widest on the home turn and surged late to snatch victory close to the wire.
Camped 3 back, 1 off with cover. Loomed up in the straight and hit the lead approaching the 50, but was collared late.
Led with a number of runners early before handing up near the 600 M to take up a trailing position. Had every chance.
Coursed very wide in the early & middle stages before being able to cross to the fence and lead after the 600 M. Was gassed inside the final 100 M.
Managed to easily take up a handy position along the paint. Was 3 back by the 600 M, and despite enjoying a nice run in transit failed to find any extra at the business end of the race.
Settled with the backmakers, 2 deep with cover. Railed up in the straight battled away fairly in the run to the line.
Sent forward from the outside gate but had to use plenty of petrol, eventually crossing to race outside the leader near the 600 M. Was running on empty over the concluding stages.
Raced behind the speed 3-wide with some cover on the final circle. Kept on one paced in the home straight.
Steadied soon after the start settling well back in the race 2 to 3-wide with cover. Never likely.
Raced at the tail of the field some distance off the 2nd last runner. Struggled in the run home.
Raced with the leading division before settling 1 out 1 back after the 600 M. (Faded in the run to the finishing post.)
Was niggled along to maintain its position worse than midfield, 2 deep with cover. Rolled to the outside on the home turn but was a spent force soon after. (To trial.)
Pressed forward from wide draw after start. Eventually led on fence from 800 M. Levelled turning in. Fought on well in the straight to repel rivals.
Began well. Gradually taken to sit on fence at midfield first turn. Shaken up and was 3Ls down passing 400 M. Closed off well but the line came too soon.

3-wide ahead of midfield early. Ridden from the Rock and improved to race outside the leader home turn. Looked dangerous until no extra to challenge the winner passing 150 M. Held 2nd until final strides.

Away in line. Pushed early and slotted 2-wide behind midfield first turn. Badly unbalanced near 850 M. Gradually switched widest and was 4Ls down on home turn. Finished off strongly and was nearest at finish.
Eased to race 3-wide towards rear after start. Took inside run on home turn and was 6Ls off into final stretch. Made steady headway and was closest at post.
Pressed early to maintain 2-wide ahead of midfield. Shifted 3-wide and was 3Ls back on straightening. Made up some ground without threatening the principals thereafter.
Ridden early and raced towards rear on fence. Similar position turning in. Kept finding the line well.
Well enough away. Taken to sit behind pace on fence from first turn. Ideal spot to strike home straight but was one-paced to conclude.
Urged early and raced 2-wide behind midfield. Pressured home turn and made up minor ground in the straight.
Fair start. Ridden along but was trapped wide and without cover. Improved wide back straight and ended up behind leaders approaching home straight. Soon faded.
Always at rear. No impression.
One-off behind leaders until no extra approaching home straight.
Well away, settled fourth on rail travelling well, briefly pocketed early straight, gap came, through it, comfortably.
Fast away, led early, headed but retained rail keeping leader one off, led early straight, kept on well, winner too strong.
Broke well but lacked early pace, held up fourth last one off, improved wide but took time to pick up, finished well.
Well away, third one off, eager, joined leader entering straight, challenge turned back by eventual second, kept on but no threat thereafter.
Broke well, not rushed early, settled midfield rail, ridden for rail challenge, kept on but unable to get on terms.
Well away, sixth one off urged, ridden turn, driven straight, modest progress.
Well away, leading group but caught three wide, mid-track bit straight, one pace.
Sluggish start, bustled along rail in third last, ridden entering straight, rail run, little progress.
Not rushed from wide gate, settled second last one off, ridden early straight, weakened.
Fair break, up for lead out wide but unable to cross and caught one off, ridden early straight, weakened.
Fair break, bid for lead but caught four wide, tried to improve leaving back, ridden, weakened.
Taken back from wide draw, settled rear, urged far side, no progress.
Very coltish before start, fluffed break, backed to rear, held up fourth last going easily, improved rail, gap opened, comfortably.
Fair break, taken back from wide draw to settle third last one off, made good ground on inside following winner through, not quite pace to challenge.
Good break, reined back to midfield rail, improved turn, ran on but outpaced.
Fair break, held up second last, promising wide bid straight, flattened out late.
Good break but caught wide, back to last one off, wide bid straight, kept on well.
Well away, led rail early, then settled third on rail, ridden to challenge early straight, no kick.
Broke well, early leader, harried far side, two clear into straight, hard driven, weakened late.
Broke well but caught wide, up to second leaving back, ridden, weakened.
Out fast, second one off and eager far side, ridden, weakened.
Well away, up to third but three wide, ridden turn, weakened.
Fair break, fifth one off, urged but lost ground, last into straight, eased.
Awkward away, pushed to obtain a midfield spot, 4Ls off the leaders 2-wide, harmed by the slow pace, dashed strongly 250 M to produce another impressive victory.
Eased to sit behind the leaders 2 to 3-wide, moved forward to take advantages when the pace slacked in middle stages, led 500 M, hung on until 100 M overhauled, ran on for 2nd.
Eased to sit in front of midfield, 2-1/2Ls off the leaders 2-wide, not suited by the slow tempo, just held ground for 3rd.
Pushed forward, 1L off the leaders 2-wide, ran on until 150 M flattened.
Settled in prominent spot along the fence, 2Ls off the leaders, not suited by the slow tempo, no turn of foot in final stages.
Behind midfield, 5-1/2Ls off the leaders on the rails, not suited by the slow pace, ran on ok in straight.
Eased back, 6Ls off the leaders 2-wide, harmed by the slow tempo, little dash 200 M.
Pushed early, took rail in midfield, 3-1/2Ls off the leaders, not suited by the slow tempo, flattened 200 M.
At tail, 8-1/2Ls off the leaders on the fence, harmed by the slow pace, little dash 200 M.
At rear as usual, 7Ls off the leaders along the fence, not suited by the slow pace, lacked turn of foot, ran on fairly in final stages.
Very slow away, at rear, 7-1/2Ls off the leaders 2 to 3-wide, harmed by the slow pace, ran on ok in straight.
Pushed to hold the rail in the lead, clocked slow sectionals, faded rapidly 500 M.
Niggled along to hold a fence position in midfield, moved closer rounding the home turn, kicked strongly when asked final 350 M, hit the front at 150 M, drew clear very easily.
Prominently placed just behind the leader, finished off well under pressure final 300 M, took the 2nd in the final stride.
Broke well, settled cosily 3Ls off the speed on rails, bit one-paced early in the home straight, kept on soundly for a place.
Awkward start, soon ran up to catch up 5Ls behind the leader on rails, moved closer along the inner rounding the home turn, on heels at 150 M, made gradual ground, just late for a place.
Settled 4 to 5Ls off pace, proved difficult to settle in the middle stages, on heels at 600 M, blocked early in the home straight, ran on steadily when clear at 200 M, too late.
Jumped fast, pushed hard to lead and found the fence near 900 M, quickened well when asked at the top of the straight, looks possible for a place until flattened at 50 M.
Broke well, urged along to hold a one-off spot 3Ls off the speed, struggled rounding the home turn, covered some ground under pressure final 200 M.
Taken back from gate 12 and travelled 6 to 7Ls off the speed, made gradual ground along the inner final 350 M, but never really troubled the principals.
Urged along to hold a one-off spot in midfield, travelled keenly when restrained in the middle stages, on heels at 900 M, only one-paced when asked for efforts in the home straight.
Caught wide early and drifted back to the mid-division, travelled without cover throughout the trip, failed to quicken when asked early in straight, soon faded.
Pushed hard early to share the lead on 2-deep, outpaced at the top of home straight, soon weakened.
Taken rearward from gate 11, swung widest for home, failed to make up any ground.
Broke well, bagged the rail and vied for the lead, established a narrow lead going into final 200 M, fought on well in late stages to keep pursuers at bay.
Restrained after the start and placed midfield in a strongly run race, out into clear nearing 200 M, finished well and pushed the winner all the way to the line.
Towards the rear but never far off leaders, had not much room early straight, went through a gap inside 200 M to chase winner but was always held. (Lame next day.)
Dropped back to last from gate 11, ran on strongly in straight despite hanging in, nearest finish.
Began awkwardly and lost ground, recovered to race behind leaders, looked threatening from 300-150 M but eventually weakened.
Tracked leaders one back on fence, travelled well throughout but couldn't get out of the pocket until 200 M, kept on with leaders when clear but not much room again final 75 M.
Pushed along to a 2-wide position with leaders but found no extra turning in, eased when no chance final 100 M.
Dropped back to a rearward position, 5Ls behind leader at the 400 M mark, picked up only fairly when asked but jockey had to stop riding final 100 M when awkwardly placed behind a beaten runner.
With leaders early but caught very wide down the back straight, eased back for cover approaching the home turn, didn't find much under pressure and got past beaten runners only.
Hard driven after jumping from a wide barrier but engaged in a speed battle and unable to cross, 5-wide swinging for room and was a spent force going into straight.
Went forward as expected but unable to cross, caught 4-wide turning for home, faded gradually passing 350 M.
Ridden positively from the start and positioned 3-wide just behind leaders, not quickened under pressure, weakened rapidly 200 M.

Travelled in 2nd outside leader, hit front turning in, soon drew clear over 200 M out.
Chased leaders about 2Ls off the speed, came off the rails for a run turning in, only made moderate headway under pressure without threatening.
Slightly slow out, settled well back, made headway on rails around the bend, fought on steadily to be nearest at finish.
Began moderately, soon picked up to forward of midfield along rails, saved ground turning in, fought on under pressure to lose placing about 100 M out. (Blood in trachea.)
Began with others from a wide barrier, raced wide in forward of midfield far side, held similar position turning for home, made no progress in straight.
Settled in last few, made up late ground past beaten horses in straight.
Began moderately, settled in midfield, ran home one-paced.
Began with others, raced wide without cover in joint 3rd about 2Ls off the pace, gradually faded under pressure after straightening.
Began from a wide draw, soon taken back to race in rear, made no impression in straight. (Tactic questioned.)
Began with others from a wide barrier but failed to muster early, dropped back towards rear coming out of back straight, made no impression in home straight.
Soon took slender lead, narrowly headed into straight, folded up quickly after straightening. (Blood in trachea.)
EXPLODING (H046) Began with others, soon settled in rear of midfield, gave ground into straight.
Went back from the outside gate to settle at the rear of the field 1 0ff with cover. Ran on well.
Rated midfield, 2 wide with cover. Rallied strongly over the final furlong.
Box seated. Had every chance, overhauled late.
Led early along the paint before handing up near the 800m to travel in 2nd position. Swamped over the final stages.
Settled with the backmakers, 2 deep with cover. Peeled out early in the straight and closed off soundly.
Travelled behind midfield, 1 off with cover. Maintained a solid effort right to the wire.
Raced towards the rear of the field along the rails. Worked home evenly.
Enjoyed a nice run in the race on the back of the speed along the fence. Had every chance.
Settled behind midfield, the fence. Kept to the inside in final stretch and worked home fairly.
Vied for the lead before rolling forward to travel as outright leader after the 600m, 1 off. Soon faded in the run home.
Settled in last position. Never a factor.
Raced as part of the leading trio before steadying near the 900m to travel behind the speed, but was posted 3 wide without cover thereafter. Never likely.
Settled 2-wide towards rear. Gradually shifted out and was 5Ls down home turn. Finished off strongly inside 300M and took charge closing stages.
Quickly into stride. Led on fence 1000M. Sat behind pace home turn. Ran on well in the straight and hit front 250M. Caught final stages.
Slow to begin. Raced towards rear on fence. Took inside run and was 3Ls away rounding home turn. Made steady headway in the straight without troubling the front pair.
Behind speed on fence early. Raced outside leader turning into home. Kept on top of home straight but failed to sustain its effort passing 250M.
Soon slotted one-out-one-back from high draw. Taken to 3-wide without cover from 800M. Remained one-paced in the straight.
Eased to 3-wide at rear from wide barrier through to home straight. Hard ridden passing 350M and beat tired runners home.
Back with last few on fence until leaving the rail to keep making up ground home straight. Steadied near 50M.
Pressed early but caught 3-wide behind leader. Strode forward home turn and led on fence turning in. Hung on until no extra inside final 250M.
2-wide at midfield early. Moved closer into final stretch in a 3-wide position. No improvement thereafter.
Slowly away. Resumed to race at midfield on fence passing 1200M. On leaders back leaving home turn but failed to progress further when asked.
3-wide behind midfield throughout. Never a factor.
Travelled wide and without cover at midfield early and middle stages. Struggled home.
Trapped wide and without cover towards rear throughout. Never in the hunt.
Urged early, ended up 3-wide without cover at midfield. Dropped out soon after straightening.
Broke fast, led early rail, headed far side but did not relinquish rail, led again early straight, kept on strongly.
Well away, ridden up to second one off, settled fourth one off, four wide into straight, ran on well without getting to winner.
Moderate break, crossed to fourth last one off, mid track bid straight, ran on strongly.
Slowly away, back to mid-rear rail, found split on rail in straight, ran on well once gap came.
Fair break but caught very wide midfield first turn, never near rail thereafter, ridden up to share lead four wide, ran on well in circumstances.
Quickly away, up to fourth on rail, found rails gap early straight, ridden but not pace to take advantage.
Well away, up to fourth one off, ridden before turn and lost some ground, hard ridden into straight for wide bid, one pace.
Fair break, midfield one off, kept on in straight but no real progress.
Fair break out wide, tried to find rail but no route available, wide midfield, ridden and kept on but never a threat.
Moderate start, rear group two off, urged throughout, last into straight, kept on past beaten horses.
Well away out wide but kept very wide by pace inside, circled field to share lead, hard ridden, weakened late.
Well away but not quitepace to take desired position, midfield three off, urged, ridden, no extra.
Well away but caught wide midfield, up to share lead, ridden turn, led briefly, no more to give.
Fair break, urged but little early pace, back to second last rail, some progress far side, ridden along rail, late check, stopped quickly.
Broke well, not rushed early, sixth rail, out for mid-track challenge, ran on well.
Awkward start lost two lengths, fifth last rail, found gap straight and ran on strongly one off rail.
Broke well, ridden out wide to lead, crossed, led into straight, ridden and kept on, not resist first two.
Sluggish start but up to fifth one off, mid-track challenge, up to second briefly, no extra.
Moderate start, back to second last, urged two wide, wide bid straight, ran on quite well.
Fast away, led early, headed, settled third on rail, ridden early straight, no real kick.
Fair break but caught wide, back to midfield one off, ridden leaving back, wide bid, modest progress.
Missed beat start, back to fourth last rail. Improved wide turn, run flattened out late.
Fair break, midfield two off, tried to make ground mid-track straight, kept on but never a factor.
Well away, up to fourth one off, second leaving back, ridden, weakened.
Slow start. Taken back, settled last on rail, ridden early straight, kept on but no impact.
Fair break, midfield rail,ridden straight, found little.
Fair break, lacked early pace, dropped back to rear three wide, urged, lacked late pace too, eased.
Midfield, trapped 3 wide throughout, 5.5Ls off the leaders, harmed by the slow pace, dashed strongly 300M to score.
Very slow away, 7Ls off the leaders 3 wide, harmed by the slow pace, dashed strongly 250M to grab 2nd.
Settled in a prominent spot, 3.5Ls off the leaders 2 wide, made early move 600M, helped by the slow tempo, led briefly 200M, overhauled 100M, ran on for 3rd.
Hard ridden early to keep up in midfield, 5.5Ls off the leaders on the fence, not suited by the slow tempo, lacked room 200M, dashed well to the line.
Eased at start and took rail, 7Ls off the leaders, harmed by the slow pace, held up 4-2, dashed strongly when clear.
Eased back, 7Ls off the leaders, trapped 3-4 wide throughout and lost too much ground, harmed by the slow pace, demonstrated its usual strong finishing efforts 300M.
Eased back, 5.5Ls off the leaders 2 wide, not suited the slow tempo, little dash 300M but without much threats.
Eased to rear, 8.5Ls off the leader, harmed by the slow pace, raced 4 wide throughout and lost too much ground, dashed impressively 200M despite all negative racing situations.
Prominent, 2Ls off the leaders 2-3 wide, benefited by the slow tempo, ran on until 200M flattened.
Trapped 3 wide early, moved forward shared the lead at slow sectionals, weakened 200M.
Settled in box seat, held up 4-2, flattened when clear.
Midfield, 4.5Ls off the leaders along the fence, harmed by the slow tempo, blocked most straight, not tested.
Hard ridden to take the rail and shared the lead at slow sectionals, weakened 300M.
Pushed early but not muster, 4.5Ls off the leaders, trapped 4-5 wide throughout, harmed by the slow pace, flattened in straight after tough trip.
Jumped fast, prominently placed within striking distance from the leader, quickened well when asked for efforts final 300M, hit the front at 100 M, kept on soundly to win.
Broke well, urged along to hold a fence position in midfield, ran on strongly when placed under pressure final 300 M, just late.
Pushed hard to lead and found the fence before the first bend, quickened well at the top of home straight, caught at 100 M, no extra, just did enough for a place.
Eased early and soon found a one-off spot in midfield, showed good turn of foot under pressure final 350 M, just late for a place.
Jumped well, pushed forward and soon settled just behind the leader, one-paced in the home straight, lost a place in the final few strides.
Broke well, settled one-off 3-4Ls off the pace, kept on fairly in the home straight, rather one-paced. (Lame left fore.)
Taken rearward from gate 11, over 10Ls behind the leader at home turn, made up some late ground in the home straight, never really troubled the principals.
Urged to occupy a rail spot in midfield, niggled along halfway to hold his position, gave no response when asked for efforts in the straight, made no progress.
Eased back from the widest alley, ended up travelling 8-9Ls off the speed, only passed a few tired runners in the home straight.
Widely drawn, eased behind runners to obtain cover, swung widest for home, failed to make up any ground.
Out with others, laced early speed and soon drifted back towards the rear, lost touch halfway, never in contention.
Niggled along to catch up 2-3Ls behind the leader, outpaced at the top of home straight, weakened sharply and finished tailed out. (Abnormal breathing noise.)
Held up towards the rear 7Ls off the pace, ran on strongly final 300M and got up close home despite showing signs of greenness. Impressive debut.
Went forward setting the pace, caught wide down the back straight then crossed to the rail 900M, headed near 300M but fought back to regain the lead 100M out, caught by winner late.
Handily placed in 2nd, picked up well and hit the front 300M out, had every chance but turned one pace in 2nd half of straight, headed 100M.
Tracked leader along the rail, kept on and had his chance but couldn't find the extra pace to challenge seriously.
Positioned close enough in the group chasing the pace, ran on only fairly and couldnt get close to the leaders.
In mid-division, kept on same pace to line but never a serious threat.
Dropped back behind midfield, driven 500M out but found less than expected the finish. (Jockey reported his horse making abnormal breathing noise.)
Not far off in 5th, kept on at the same pace to 100M then weakened.
Caught 3-wide without cover in mid-division, driven approaching 400M but found disappointingly little in the finish.
Slow to begin, ended up 3-wide in the rear 8Ls behind leader, moved closer over the home turn and couldn't pick up when placed under pressure in straight.
Failed to muster speed, travelled in the rear along the fence, checked nearing 800M and shuffled further back, made little impression in straight and got past well beaten runners only.
Never better than midfield, struggled passing 600M and soon left behind on straightening.
Always near the rear, never any impression.
Driven to a midfield position after a slow start, weakened rapidly inside 300M.
Jumped well, settled 2Ls behind the leader on 2-deep, finished off strongly final 250M, won easily.
Began fast, pushed to occupy the box-seat just behind the leader, quickened well final 250M, bumped at 150 M, finished off soundly for 2nd.
Jumped fastest, settled in the one out one back spot, travelled keenly when restrained early, kept battling on in home straight, bumped at 150M, finished 3rd.
Crowded start, travelled 4Ls off the speed on the fence, shifted wide for home, took time to quicken, closed off strongly final 150M, just missed a place.
Started well, settled in the midfield, finished off satisfactorily down centre of home straight, but never really threaten the principals.
Crowded start, travelled 3Ls off the pace on rails, rather one-paced when placed under pressure in the home straight, made some late ground final 100 M.
Slow to begin, urged along early and soon caught up 6Ls behind the leader, made gradual ground when asked for efforts final 300M.
Jumped fast, niggled along to take the lead, kept on until flattened at 250M, soon weakened.
Started well, settled 7Ls off the pace, made gradually ground when asked for efforts final 350M, rather one-paced.
Taken back from gate 14, patiently ridden in the early stages, gave limited response when asked for efforts in home straight, just passed a few tired runners.
Broken well, travelled 6Ls behind the leader, found nothing for home, faded out.
Started fairly, settled 4Ls off the speed on rails, on heels at 900M and 700M, gave no response under pressure in home straight, dropped out.
Out in line, travelled wide without cover throughout the trip, never competitive.
Began moderately, lacked early speed, ran at rear throughout the trip, never a factor.
Out in line, trapped 3 wide without cover in midfield, 4Ls back working to bend, kept improving at 400 M and showed good fight last 200 M to finish over the top of rivals.
Positive from wide alley, box seated behind pace trio, travelled well in middle stages, stalked leaders on bend, made a well timed finish only to lose out in concluding stages.
Drifted back as usual, near last best part of 7Ls off speed, kept saving ground on circle, came through a narrow gap along rails to get up for a place.
Went forward to look for lead early, raced on speed outside leader, had a fair run to bend, boxed on gamely in straight losing place late.
Standard break, positioned closer than usual 4Ls away in mid-section, enjoyed a good trail to bend, slightly crowded at 200 M but worked the line evenly nevertheless.
Out in line, took an ideal position on leaders back throughout, popped off rails turning and looked a chance but run ended inside final furlong.
Showed good early speed, took up running and controlled race from top end, about a length clear turning, kept on but didn't see out journey final 200 M.
Tardy into stride, back with last few 7Ls or worse from lead, always well back, made some late ground from impossible spot on bend.
Worked a bit to slot in from a wide gate, got in 3 wide 5Ls off speed, covered ground to bend, followed eventual winner but didn't let down and struggled late.
Moderate beginning, raced behind midfield 5Ls or so back, had a fair run throughout, didn't have a finish in straight and just battled away late.
No speed and drifted back to last, best part of 8Ls or more from front end, still last on turning in, came to middle and did manage to close off OK late.
Standard jump, settled behind midfield 3 wide 6 to 7Ls off lead, had cover to bend, didn't have much to offer and condition gave out in straight.
Pressed on in hope of a close up spot, posted 3 wide without cover 1L down, did it tough to bend, faded after a hard run.
Even break, took up a midfield role 3 to 4Ls away on rails, used little in run, no turn of foot from 400 M and faded out.

Settled wide in rear of midfield, commenced run around the bend and remained wide into straight, ran on down centre of track to reach front late.
Settled on rails in midfield, found no room after straightening until about 150 M out, finished off race well once into the clear.
Settled in rear of midfield, commenced run around the bend, obtained a clear passage over 200 M out, finished off race well.
Soon took up running, held narrow advantage to straight, established over 1L break early on but soon flattered, swamped by fast-finishers nearing home.
Broke well from the one draw, settled just off the pace on rails in 3rd or 4th, remained in similar position to straight, fought on steadily without quickening.
Travelled in forward of midfield, gained 4th about 2Ls back off the Rock, similar position turning in, ran home one-paced.

Began awkwardly, soon taken across from a wide gate to race in last few, checked and dropped to last on rails approaching home bend, saved ground turning in, fought on under pressure without threatening.
Soon crossed to inside in rear, trailed behind before circling the field coming out of back straight, widest runner and well behind turning in, never nearer.
Settled well back, remained in rear and wide around the bend, never nearer.
Raced wide in forward of midfield, moved closer up in far side to settle in a one-out-one-back position, kept on same pace in straight before fading inside 200 M.
Travelled in 2L 4th before losing position when awkwardly placed behind horses about halfway out, soon hampered again and dropped towards the rear at Rock, never recovered.
Well there, lost position after the Rock and gave ground from there, dropped away quickly after entering straight. (Struck into and found lame day after racing.)
Stalked the leader along the rails. Peeled out rounding the home turn and was never headed after hitting the front near the furlong.
Travelled behind midfield, 1 off with cover. Closed off strongly.
Settled in a handy position, 2-wide with cover. Kept to the inside in the run home, maintaining a good gallop right to the wire.
Worked forward to lead along the paint. Skipped well clear after the 500 M but was collared late to still finish in the frame.
Settled at the tail of the field, 2 deep with cover. Was steadied when disappointed for running after the 600 M. made steady ground in the home straight.
Used plenty of gas during the early and middle stages to park outside the lead, 1 off without cover. Was gassed over the final stages.
Travelled on the speed but was posted 3-wide without cover on the circle. Not likely thereafter.
Settled about 3 back the fence. Made no impression in the home stretch.
Hung out in the early and middle stages whilst coursing wide. Travelled 3-wide with cover towards the rear. Never a factor.
Settled back at the rear 2 deep with cover. Struggled in the run home. (Bled.)
Away in line. Urged from 800 M to maintain 2-wide spot ad ahead of midfield. Swung out and was 3Ls down on straightening. Finished off strongly inside 250 M. Asserted authority final stages.
Ridden early. Settled ahead of midfield on fence passing the rock. Well positioned to strike in the straight. Responded well when asked but the winner was too strong.
Began awkwardly and was hampered. Resumed to race behind midfield on fence at the rock. Took inside run and was 4Ls off rounding the turn. Rallied to land 3rd.
Jumped well, ended up at midfield on fence passing 800 M. 3Ls adrift into final stretch. Closed off fairly well to make frame without threatening the front trio.
Soon in front rank. Sat behind pace on fence at the rock. Checked passing 600 M. Ran on in the straight and hit front briefly at 200 M. Couldn't sustain its effort closing stages.
Raced 2-wide behind midfield until home straight. Kept on steadily but not threatening.
Hampered at start. Raced 2-wide towards rear through to home straight. One-paced to conclude.
Driven early and led. Cut to the fence home turn. Held a 1L advantage turning in. Hung on until overhauled final 200 M.
Ridden early and raced 2-wide behind speed. Failed to progress further top of home straight. Weakened final furlong.
3-wide behind midfield early. Struggled home turn. No impression in the straight.
Taken towards rear from high draw. Pressured home turn but no response. Beaten well before home bend.
Slow to begin and was hampered. Detached thereafter and never recovered. (Substantial amount of mucopus in horse's trachea.)
Broke well, settled one off in sixth, travelling easily, made ground wide home turn, led 200 M out, ran on strongly.
Broke well but taken back to rear on rail, second last leaving back, rail run, wove through gaps, finished strongly.
Broke well, led early, dictated pace until challenged entering turn, fought on well but unable to resist first two.
Missed break by two lengths, settled rail third lastly, up o to midfield leaving back, overracing slightly, challenged straight, run flattened late.
Fair break, settled fourth rail trailing leader, every chance straight, ridden, no kick.
Fair break, not rushed early, held up third last one off, improved turn, ridden straight, kept on but no kick.
Broke well, ridden early but caught four wide, midfield wide until rapid improvement to share lead leaving back, ridden, weakened late.
Fair break, midfield to rear three off, lost ground turn although ridden, kept on wide but no threat.
Broke well, up to second one off, fourth into straight, mid track challenge, faded.
Broke well but caught five wide, back to last one off, settled fifth two off, tried to improve inside turn, ridden, no progress.
Broke fast, looked for lead but caught five wide, settled fifth two off, ridden before turn, weakened.
Moderate break, ridden early to join leaders three wide, began to weaken leaving back, no improvement straight.
Broke well but little early speed, settled fourth last one off, bustled turn, wide challenge, ran on strongly to lead 100 M out.
Broke well, ridden early to reach third on rail, bustled turn, led mid-straight, winner too strong.
Broke well, not rushed, back to second last one off, wide bid straight, ran on strongly.
Fast break, not rushed, settled third last rail, progress rail entering straight, ran on but lacked kick.
Broke well, leading group, moved to fourth two off, early bid leaving turn, kept on but run flattened.
Fast break, settled midfield rail, ridden turn, slightly short of room, kept on one pace.
Fair break, ridden early but caught wide, up to share lead leaving first turn, second leaving back, tried to improve early straight, one pace.
Fair break, ridden to lead, dictated pace, quickened turn, two clear into straight, weakened.
Missed break, lost two lengths. Last on rail, ridden turn and closed to mid pack, then ran out of racing room, baulked, eased.
Well away, fifth rail, the fourth one off, ridden early straight, found nil.
In front of midfield, 2-1/2Ls off the leader along the fence, dashed well 200 M to win despite not suited by the slow pace.
Settled 1L off the leader 2-wide, travelled nicely and took advantage from the slow sectionals, led 300 M, overhauled 50 M, just beaten by a head.
Pushed to hold the box seat, enjoyed the slow sectionals, just held ground in straight for 3rd.
Pushed to take the rail and led by 1L at slow sectionals, soon flattened 300 M.
At back but on the fence, 4-1/2Ls off the leader, harmed by the slow pace, little dash 200 M.
Hard ridden forward, 2-1/2Ls off the leader 2-wide, not suited by the slow tempo, flattened 200 M.
Eased back, 5Ls off the leader 2-wide, not suited by the slow tempo, ran on fairly in final stages.
Eased at start, 7Ls off the leader 2 to 3-wide, harmed by the slow pace, little dash in straight.
Hard ridden early but failed to cross, 3Ls off the leader, trapped 3 to 4-wide throughout, not suited by the slow pace, emptied 400 M.
Behind midfield, 4-1/2Ls off the leader 2-wide, not suited by the slow tempo, never a factor.
At rear, 6Ls off the leader on the rails, harmed by the slow pace, no progress.
Slow away, pushed forward, 2Ls off the leader, trapped 3-wide throughout, not suited by the slow pace, faded 400 M.
Jumped well, eased to a one-off position 5Ls behind the leader, finished off strongly final 200 M, kept going well to score.
Taken back from gate 12, patiently ridden in the early stages, shifted widest for home, took time to muster early in straight, clicked into gear at 150 M, just late.
Out in line, settled 2-wide in the midfield, closed off well down centre of home straight, but never really threatened the first two.
Crowded start, travelled rearward, save ground on the fence for home, made some late ground under pressure final 200 M, rather one-paced.
Broke fairly, settled 5Ls behind the leader on rails, made gradually ground when asked for efforts final 300 M. (Cut left front cannon.)
Started fast, urged along early and soon settled 2Ls behind the leader on 2-deep, gave limited response when asked for efforts final 300 M.
Jumped fast, pushed to take a forward position on rails from gate 11, took the led at 250 M, soon weakened.
Began fairly, travelled widest and hang out in the early stages, found nothing under pressure for home, never a factor.
Crowded start, settled 3Ls off the speed on 3-deep, failed to make up any ground in the home straight.
Crowded start, travelled wide in the early stages, took the led on 2-deep at 1100 M, flattened at 300 M, dropped out.
Started fast, settled 2Ls off the pace on rails, gave no response when asked for efforts in the home straight, faded out.
Broke well, travelled wide without cover throughout the race, never competitive.

Positively ridden after the start to obtain a 2-wide position ahead of midfield, travelled well and moved to the lead inside 200 M, ran on and found the necessary to fend off the runner-up in late stages.
Patiently ridden, towards the rear 8Ls off the pace, surged forward and mounted a strong challenge final 200 M, drifted in under pressure and was just held by the winner.
Behind mid-division about 6Ls behind leader, ran on strongly final 300 M, nearest finish.
Taken back from draw 12, settled in last for the 1st half of the race, 3-wide and moved closer turning for home, ran on well down outside of track, nearest finish.
Handily placed just off the speed, kept on and had his chance but was outpaced final 100 M.
Towards the rear 8Ls off the pace, saved ground on the inside, loomed a threat at 200 M then flattened out in late stages.
Bagged the rail soon after the start, travelled in 7th position throughout, driven passing 350 M but lacked a necessary response.
Broke well from the inside draw then restrained to a position behind leaders, ran on one paced final 300 M. (Mucus.)
Led as expected and set a decent pace to straight, couldn't sustain the momentum nearing 200 M.
Close up to the pace but was 3-wide without cover throughout, not quickened when asked, no impression.
Tracked leader, placed under pressure 400 M, ran out of it inside 200 M and weakened rapidly.
