Amongst leaders far side, held rails run in close 3rd inside leaders around the bend, gained clear advantage passing 200 M, just held off fast-finishing 2nd.
Soon taken back from the widest gate, trailed the field to straight, baulked briefly after straightening, ran home strongly down centre of track but the post came too soon.
Settled in midfield, ran on steadily in straight to be nearest at finish.
Began fairly, settled in 5th about 2Ls off the pace, in similar position turning in, fought hard under pressure without quickening.
Travelled behind midfield, similar into straight, ran on to be nearest at finish.
Disputed lead, gradually faded under pressure inside final 200 M.
Began well, settled just better than midfield on rails, commenced move rounding home bend to be close up on heels of leaders in 4th turning in, unable to sustain effort inside final 200 M.
Settled in midfield, wide into straight, one-paced when hampered over 100 M out.
Travelled just off the pace in 4th, came under pressure upon straightening, one-paced before fading inside final 100 M.
Settled well behind, ran on past well beaten horses in centre of straight.
Raced wide in rear of midfield, made no impression in straight.
Slow into stride, soon driven to rear of midfield, commenced move around home bend to be closer up turning in, kept on before fading inside final 200 M.
Raced wide without cover with leaders throughout far side and around the bend, in similar position into straight, dropped out noticeably inside 300 M. (Bled.)
Jumped awkwardly losing ground, soon recovered and travelled towards rear of field on rails, ran home one-paced.
Sent forward and traveled as joint leader along the fence. Shot clear early in the straight and drew away over the final furlong for an effortless win.
Rated midfield 3 wide with some cover on the circle. Closed off well.
stalked the leader on the rails. Managed to repel late challengers and hold on to 3rd placing.
Parked 3 back the fence. Stayed on to finish in the frame after having every chance.
Raced midfield, 2 deep with cover. Finished the race off evenly.
Settled handy to the leaders, 2 wide with cover. Maintained a fair gallop in the home straight.
Camped behind midfield along the paint. Worked to the winning post soundly.
Slow to begin settling towards the rear along the paint. Battled away making some ground in the final stages.
Missed the start and lost considerable ground, travelling near the tail of the field. Made good yards over the final 300 M.
Coursed 3 wide and without cover whilst sharing leading duties. Was gassed early in the straight.
Taken back from a wide barrier to race in a rearward position 2-3 wide with cover. Only plodded to the finish.
Couldn't go the early speed of the race, settling in last position. Became detached in the middle stages, failing to make any impression in the final stretch.
Was part of the leading trio early before settling a length back in 3rd position, 1 off. Struggled in the run to the line.
4Ls behind leader near the centre of the track early stages. Got closer passing 400M. Responded strongly when asked 300 out. Fought determinedly to the line to repel rivals.
Travelled well along stand's rail behind pace. Pressed from 250M and responded well. Looked dangerous but lacked the finishing touch of the winner final stages.
Led until challenged by the front pair final furlong. Battled gamely with them but failed to sustain closing stages.
Tracked leader early and middle stages. Remained one-paced when the tempo quicken after 350M. Ran on for a non-threatening 4th.
One-off the stand's rail behind leader. Plodded on when the race got serious passing 350M.
2-3Ls behind leader to midpoint. Couldn't pick up passing 400M. No extra final furlong.
Towards rear early. Shifted in passing 400M for clear run. Beat tired runners home.
Given reminder early but soon trailed field. Still at last passing 400M. Made up ground steadily passing 200M.
Always towards rear despite effort of rider. No impression.
Midfield until weakened passing 300M.
Began slowly, then was bumped and became unbalanced. Resumed to race at midfield 800M out. Found nothing when asked after 300M.
Towards rear early. Struggled midpoint. Out of contention well before the post.
Fast break, settled fourth on rail, eased out turn, found gap, led 150m out, drew clear.
Good break, but caught wide midfield, advanced quickly back, second into straight one off, led 200m out, winner too strong.
Broke well, up to third three wide, settled sixth one off, mid-track challenge straight, kept on steadily.
Broke well, led early, second rail, then third into straight, led narrowly 350m out, kept on one pace.
Fair break, midfield rail, found room on inside early straight, kept on but never threat.
Moderate break, taken back from wide draw to fourth last two off, wide bid, kept on under driving.
Sluggish start, ridden midfield one off, out for wide challenge, kept on but no kick.
Fast break, led early then second on rail, mid-track bid straight, no kick.
Taken back to rear from wide draw, held up second last, inside bid, kept on one pace.
Fair break, steadied third last on rail, out to challenge early straight, driven, no impression.
Sluggish start, ridden early, settled third last one off, ridden early straight, no significant response.
Slow start, back to rear on rail, ridden early straight, never threat.
Bobbled start, driven early to lead, three clear far side, still led leaving back, headed, weakened.
Fair break, ridden early, midfield one off, wide bid, found nil, eased.
Broke well, up to third on rail behind leader, had to wait for gap in straight, burst through to lead, ran on.
Broke fast, up on outside to lead, two clear leaving back, led into straight, ran on but unable to resist winner.
Broke well, up to fifth two off, kept on well straight but unable to challenge.
Fair break, ridden early to second one off, tried to challenge under pressure straight, run flattened.
Broke well, led rail early, then settled fourth on rail, angled out straight, clear run but not pace to trouble leading pair.
Missed break, lost two lengths, midfield rail taking time to settle, driven straight, kept on but no kick.
Moderate break, held up sixth last rail, pulling slightly, rail bid, kept on one pace.
Good break, not much early foot, midfield one off, urged, not much room straight, kept on one pace.
Fair break, midfield two off, improved wide turn, kept on one pace.
Steadied start, back to third last rail, looking for room early straight, found it but no kick.
Fair break, not much early pace, mid-rear three off, wide bid, kept on but no impact.
Slow start, lost four lengths, back to last on rail, ridden inside early straight, no significant progress.
Broke well out wide but caught four deep midfield, up to fourth still wide into straight, weakened.
Fair break, ridden early up to sixth one off, short of room straight, blocked, eased.
Eased to sit behind midfield, 5.5Ls off the leader 3 wide, harmed by the very slow pace, dashed strongly 250M to score.
Pushed to obtain a prominent spot as usual, 2.5Ls behind the slow pace 2 wide, lack room 400M, closed the race off strongly, beaten by a neck in 2nd.
Eased to sit in midfield, 4Ls off the leader 3 wide, harmed by the very slow tempo, dashed well 300M to grab 3rd.
Settled 1.5Ls off the leader 2 wide, enjoyed the very slow sectionals, led 250M, hung on until 50M flattened.
Eased to rear, 8Ls off the leader 1-2 wide, dashed impressively 200M despite not suited by the very slow pace.
Eased to sit in midfield, 4Ls off the leader 2 wide, harmed by the very slow pace, held up 400M, little dash when clear.
Eased to rear, 7Ls off the leader, trapped 3-5 wide and lost too much ground, dashed well 250M despite not suited by the very slow pace.
Awkward away, hard ridden to secure a midfield spot on the fence, 3.5Ls off the leader, not suited by the very slow pace, blocked 400M, just held ground when clear.
Behind midfield, 5.5Ls off the leader 2 wide, not suited by the very slow tempo, lack room 400M, dashed fairly when clear.
At back, 6Ls off the leader, trapped 4 wide throughout and lost too much ground, harmed by the very slow pace, showed little dash in straight.
Took rail easily, led by 1.5L and clocked very soft sectionals, hung on until 250M weakened.
Box seat, benefited by the very slow pace, however emptied 200M.
2.5Ls off the leader, trapped 3 wide throughout without cover, soon weakened 350M.
Eased at start and took rail, harmed by the slow pace, never a factor.
Broke well, mustered fast and soon led on the rails, travelled well throughout the trip, quickened well when asked for efforts at 300 M, kept on strongly to withhold challenger.
Driven to take the one-out-one-back spot, ran on to contest the lead early in straight, hung in under pressure, kept on soundly for 2nd.
Settled cosily 4Ls off pace on rails, clicked into gear when clear at 300 M, finished off satisfactorily for 3rd, but never really troubled the top two.
Out in line, niggled along early and ended up settling one-off 3Ls behind the speed, kept on fairly in the home straight, lost a place inside 50 M.
Bumped start, settled 7Ls off the pace on 2-wide, travelled keenly when restrained in the middle stages, held up for room early in straight, ran on well when clear at 200 M.
Lacked early speed despite being urged along, travelled 6Ls behind the leader with cover, made gradual ground under pressure final 300 M, never threatened the principals.
Lacked early speed as usual and soon drifted towards the rear, urged along in the early stages, took time to pick up early in the home straight, covered some late ground final 250 M.
Bumped at start, hung out in the middle stages, travelled wide with no cover, gave limited response when asked at 400 M, only passed a few tired runners.
Taken back from the widest alley and travelled 8Ls off the pace, swung widest for home, only made up little ground final 200 M. (Abnormal breathing noise.)
Jumped fairly, settled one-off in midfield, travelled satisfactorily in the early and middle stages, only gave limited response when asked at 400 M, flattened at 200 M, soon weakened.
Widely drawn, urged along early and soon occupied a 3-deep spot in midfield, held ground until flattened at 200 M, soon faded.
Slow away, urged along to catch up 4Ls off the pace near the rear, crowded at home turn, failed to make up any ground in the straight.
Pushed hard to hold the fence spot just behind the leader, flattened early in the home straight, soon dropped out.
Lacked early speed despite being niggled along, never better than midfield, weakened at 300 M, finished tailed out.
Took keen hold behind leading pair, responded well to pressure and surged to the front nearing 250M, all out final 200M and held on despite drifting out badly in closing stages.
Held up in midfield along the rail and travelled strongly, had trouble finding a clear path from 450M to 250M, ran on well when clear and only narrowly failed.
In touch, responded well under pressure in straight but was twice hampered by the winner which shifted out badly inside 200M, could have been closer.
Held up behind midfield, switched out to chase leaders 400 M out, kept on steadily to line but couldn't close the gap with leaders.
Dropped back to second last and a long way off the pace in first half of the race, took a while to pick up in straight, did best work late but never threatened the principals.
Behind mid-division and raced 3-wide without cover, 6Ls down approaching 400M, stayed on without reaching leaders.
Not far off in the group chasing leaders, couldn't step up a gear when the race got serious, faded final 100M.
Raced keenly in the lead, pressed by a rival and set a good pace upfront, run peaked at 200M, weakened noticeably close home.
Never better than midfield, found less than expected when placed under pressure 400M, one paced.
Switched off to the back, 10Ls off the good pace halfway, nudged along inside 600M but could only make very limited progress.
Sat outside leader in a strongly run race, raced keenly and moved to the lead from 600M, headed nearing 300M then gave ground rapidly. (Jockey advised not to set his mounts too great a task.)
Towards the rear, became detached nearing 600M, eased final 200M. (Lame left front leg.)
Broke fast and soon settled 1L off the pace on 2-deep, quickened well when asked at 300 M, hit the front at 200 M, kept on soundly under hard riding, just withheld the challenger.
Niggled along to hold a one-off spot in the mid-division, held up for clear run early in home straight, kicked strongly when clear at 250 M, narrowly beaten by winner.
Patiently ridden in the early stages, settled 4Ls off the pace on 2-deep, swung wide for home, responded well when asked at 350 M, finished off soundly for 3rd.
Started awkwardly, soon ran up to occupy the fence 2Ls off the speed, blocked early in home straight, made up gradual ground when clear at 250 M, rather one-paced.
Slow to begin, got across towards the fence and sat 6Ls off the pace, responded satisfactorily when asked final 350 M, did make up some ground, but never threatened the principals.
Broke well, driven to lead and found the fence near 900 M, kept on satisfactorily in the early straight, caught at the 200 M pole, couldn't find extra.
Easily ran up to take the box-seat, ran up to contest the lead at 400 M, passed at 200 M, soon flattened.
Jumped fast, urged along to hold a 3-wide position just off the pace, kept on fairly under maximum pressure in the home straight, failed to offer extra final 100 M.
Patiently ridden and ended up settling 6Ls off the pace, took time to pick up early in the home straight, only made limited progress final 200 M, rather one-paced, bumped at 100 M.
Started awkwardly, settled 6Ls off the pace, caught 3-wide throughout the trip, shifted widest for home, failed to make up any ground, bumped at 100 M.
Crowded start, settled one from the rear 7Ls behind the speed, only passed a few tired runners in the home straight.
Bumped start, travelled on-pace but caught wide without cover, allowed to stride forward at the home turn, got tired near 250 M, soon weakened.
Taken to the rear from gate 14, made no progress, never competitive.
Pushed hard to hold a fence position in the midfield, gave no response when asked for efforts at 400 M, soon got tired.
Taken down to rails to race behind midfield, 5Ls away in mid-section, improved on bend, tracked into clear at 300 M, let down with a strong sprint to score easily.
Out in line, pushed up along rails to race 4Ls back, trailed well and came 2 wide on circle, made a strong bid hitting front at 250 M, overhauled final 100 M.
No speed and allowed to drift back from a wide alley raced behind midfield 7 to 8Ls off pace, made a wide run turning, closed well down middle but well off first two.
Began well, drove up to hold leaders back, enjoyed run of race to turn, came wide and looked a hope but didn't find extra last 200 M, held on OK to make frame.
Taken in behind midfield from a awkward alley, 6 to 7Ls back in 2 wide line throughout, close to eventual winner from bend, kept on to 150 M before peaking.
No early pace, ended up next to last 9Ls away, stayed on rails and used little to turn, made some minor progress without threatening.
Began with rest, left 3 wide without cover from 100 M, worked mid-section and forced wide on bend, hard run took toll.
Crowded at start, ended up in rear, best part of 10Ls back, job to do on turning, came widest and made some solid progress late down centre of course.
Began in line, took a midfield position 2 wide 4Ls back, fair run throughout, didn't respond from turn and faded when unable to see out journey.
Shade tardy to begin rear division 7Ls away on rails, still well back to bend, made no real progress.
Even break, pressed on from wide alley to eventually cross outside leader, worked throughout, niggled before losing room turning, dropped out after hard run.
First to break, plenty of speed and rolled along throughout, kept pace genuine to bend, tackled soon after straightening, folded tamely. (Muco in trachea.)
Bounced out, prominent early before took a trail, tracked first few before coming 3 wide on bend, struggling turning in and steadily faded.
Fair to begin, raced 3 wide in midfield, had cover 5Ls back to bend, found little and dropped right out. (Blood in trachea.)

Settled one-back in 3rd on rails, came to challenge inside final 200 M, hit the front close to home and just held off fast-finishing 2nd final strides.
Niggled at early, travelled mostly in 4th about 2-1/2L off the lead, similar but became 5th around home bend, fought on gamely inside final 100 M to just fail to get up on line.
Settled one-out-one-back in 2nd, came under pressure to challenge turning in, fought hard to hold some chance inside final 100 M only to be swamped close to home.
Settled towards the rear, ran on well down centre of straight to be nearest at finish.
Soon took up running and attempted to make all, came under pressure when still 1L clear over 200 M out but soon found no extra.
Broke well but failed to muster under reminders, gradually dropping to forward of midfield on rails far side, saved ground turning in, kept on steadily under pressure without quickening.

Slightly slow to begin, picked up quickly to race wide without cover in midfield but refused to settle at about 800 M, took closer order rounding the bend, unable to sustain effort under pressure inside final 200 M.
Soon settled in midfield, ran home one-paced without quickening.

Checked and lost ground at start, travelled just worse than midfield most of way on rails, saved ground turning in and looked improving when chopped out on rails inside 300 M, made no further impression thereafter.
Broke well from the widest barrier, soon settled wide in midfield, remained similar turning into straight, ran home one-paced.
Soon taken back from a wide gate, remained similar throughout and made no show.
Checked and dropped to second last at start, checked twice again between 1100 and 1000 M dropping to tail-end, never recovered.
Travelled as joint leader early along the fence before handing up and taking a trailing position near the 700 M. Hit the front and held off late challenge.
Rated 1 off the fence on the back of the speed. Rallied 3 to 4-wide turning for home, kept on well.
Camped close to midfield, 2-wide with cover. Battled away gamely in the final stretch.
Not the best away the worked forward to eventually cross to lead on the fence near the 600 M. Maintained a sound gallop to the finish.
Was checked at the start settling worse than midfield the fence. Made some ground in the home straight without threatening.
Settled handy to the leaders on the rails before being shuffled back slightly near the 600 M. Failed to show any response when placed under pressure.
Raced behind midfield 2 deep with cover. Battled to the line one paced.
Settled back in the event along the fence after being checked at the start. Whacked away one paced over the final stages.
Went back from a wide gate to settle some distance off the field in last place. Gradually made ground and tacked on to the main body of the pack close to the 600 M. Only plodded to the line.
Raced greenly for most of the trip at the rear of the field. Never likely.
Coursed wide in the early stages before slotting in to race close to 1 off on the final circle on the back of the speed. Faded in the run to the line.
Travelled back in the field 2-wide with cover. Failed to close off.
Led 2-wide early. Got the fence 1100 M out. Held a 1L advantage turning in. Always had enough to hold off rivals.
Raced within 4Ls of the pace on fence through to home straight. Ran on strongly final furlong to snatch 2nd without threatening the winner.

2-wide at midfield early. Bumped and was taken 3-wide passing 1300 M. Made run 4-wide approaching 400 M and was 4Ls down into final stretch. Finished off satisfactorily without seriously challenging the front pair.
Soon in forward spot on fence. Elected to take box seat passing 1100 M. Under pressure from 600 M. Kept on in the straight but failed to progress further.
Eased to sit 2-wide towards rear from wide barrier. Gradually shifted 4-wide home turn and was 5Ls away leaving the bend. Made up decent ground thereafter.
Drawn high and trapped wide early. Eventually parked 2-wide behind leader 1300 M. Hard ridden passing 400 M to challenge leader but was one-paced to conclude.
Began well but caught 3-wide. Slotted 2-wide ahead of midfield passing winning post first time. Pressed approaching 400 M and was well-positioned to strike in the straight. Couldn't follow through.
2-wide behind midfield. Never nearer.
Taken to rear on fence after start. Urged from 500 M but still the last entering home straight. Beat tired runners late.

Ahead of midfield early. Switched 2-wide passing 1300 M. Forced 3-wide without cover 1200 M out. Struggled when the tempo quickened from 400 M. Beaten top of straight. (Substantial mucopus, lame left fore and stiff right hind.)
Taken to race towards rear from high draw but trapped 3-wide. Came widest with the main bunch home turn. No extra soon after straightening.
Towards rear on fence through to home straight. Never improved.
Well away, up to fifth one off, challenged down centre of track, ran on strongly to lead last 50 M.
Fast away, up to second one off, mid-track challenge, led briefly mid-straight, moved to rail, headed late.
Sluggish start, second last one off, wide bid straight, ran on well.
Fair break wide, back to fourth last one off, wide challenge, leant on briefly by third, kept on well.
Moderate break, midfield one off, mid-pack run, stayed on.
Fair break, raced fourth two wide, kept on straight but no kick.
Missed break, back to last on rail, last into straight, ridden first mid-track then wide, ran on well.
Well away rail, outpaced by wide runners, back to fourth rail, ridden, rail run, no extra.
Broke well rail, not rushed midfield rail, ridden early straight, no progress.
Broke well, ridden for early position midfield one off, ridden and no progress straight.
Sluggish start, urged forward but back to third last rail, urged again turn, kept to rail, kept on without threatening.
Fair break, ridden to lead rail, two clear leaving back and entering straight, weakened quickly.
Fast away, led rail, turned back early challenge, led into straight, kept on strongly.
Broke fast, fourth one off, wide challenge, ran on strongly.
Sluggish start, up quickly to midfield two off, wove way through along rail, finished well.
Broke well, challenged for lead one off, turned back by winner, second into straight, hard ridden, kept on.
Broke well, ridden early but caught wide, kept on well straight under driving, but unable to challenge.
Fair break, lacked early pace, midfield rail, ridden, kept on, unable to challenge.
Fair break, looked for lead but had to settle for third one off, ridden to challenge early straight, one pace.
Missed break, last by two lengths early, closed up, wide run, kept on.
Good break, lacked early speed, second last one off, wide turn, kept on, never dangerous.
Fair break, lacked early speed, fourth last one off, inside run straight, ridden, no progress.
Broke well, short of early speed, fourth last one off, ridden early straight, found nothing.
Well away, up to third on rail, ridden early straight, weakened quickly, eased.
Box seat, however not suited by the fast pace, ran on strongly 300 M to win by a neck.
Hard ridden forward, 1-1/2Ls off the leaders 2 to 3-wide, closed the race off strongly despite not suited by the fast pace, just beaten by a neck in 2nd. (Ride lost whip.)
Pushed early but not muster, trapped 4-wide at stable bend, taken back to rear, 6Ls off the leaders 2 to 3-wide, favoured by the fast pace, progressed steadily 300 M for 3rd.
Soon took rail and shared the lead at fast early sectionals, hung on strongly until 100 M overhauled, just missed place but still ran on well to the line.
Eased to rear and took rail, 6Ls off the leaders, benefited by the fast pace, held up 4-2, progressed steadily when clear.
Eased to sit in front midfield, 3Ls off the leaders 2-wide, suited by the fast tempo, made minor ground 200 M.
At back but on the rails, 4-1/2Ls off the leaders, favoured by the fast pace, made steady ground 200 M along the fence.
Pushed early but not muster, then eased back, 4-1/2Ls off the leaders, helped by the fast tempo, but trapped 3 to 4-wide throughout and lost too much ground, ran on ok in straight.
Eased back, 4-1/2Ls off the leaders 2-wide, benefited by the fast pace, lacked room 400 M, no progress when clear.
Midfield, 3Ls off the fast pace, raced 3 to 4-wide throughout and lost too much ground, emptied 300 M.
Trapped 3-wide early, hard ridden forward to share the lead 2-wide at fast sectionals, used up too much fuel, weakened quickly 400 M.
Midfield, on the fence, 3Ls off the leaders, suited by the fast tempo, however soon weakened 300 M.
Cosily placed in a one-off spot just behind the speed, responded well when asked for efforts final 350 M, hit the front at 100 M, finished off soundly to withhold the challenger.
Badly bumped after start, settled one from the rear on rails, niggled along in the middle stages, hung in under pressure in the home straight, ran on strongly final 250 M for 2nd.
Badly bumped after start, settled 6Ls off the speed on rails, checked at 500 M, finished off strongly down centre of home straight, got a place in the final stride.
Out in line, niggled long to share the lead on 2-deep, kept on satisfactorily when asked for efforts at the top of home straight, caught by the winner at 100 M, just missed a place.
Crowded after start, prominently placed in midfield on rails, responded well when asked for efforts final 250 M, improved gradually along the inner, just missed a place.
Lacked early speed as usual, travelled 5Ls behind the leader on the fence, took time to pick up early in the home straight, made gradual ground under maximum pressure final 200 M.
Awkwardly started, lacked early speed despite being urged along, travelled 8Ls away in the rear, niggled along in the middle stages, covered some late ground final 250 M, blocked at 50 M.
Jumped fastest, easily ran up to share the lead on rails, caught at 250 M, one-paced. (Sustained abrasions above the right hock.)
Crowded after start, urged along to hold a fence position just behind the speed, on heels at 350 M and 150 M, only one-paced when asked early in the home straight, soon flattened.
Jumped well, soon eased to a 3-wide spot 5Ls off the pace, crept closer at the home turn, kept on fairly when asked for efforts early in the home straight, no extra final 100 M.
Bumped after start, settled one-off in the mid-division, only gave limited response when asked for efforts at the top of home straight, soon faded.
Jumped only fairly, pushed hard to share the lead on 3-wide, got tired at the top of home straight, soon dropped out.
Travelled well in a position towards the rear, switched wide 500 M out to commence his run, came home very strongly and had the race won passing 100 M.
Caught 3-wide over the 1st turn then settled 2-wide in midfield 4Ls off the pace, finished well but not matched winner's pace final 150 M.
Had an uncontested lead and set steady pace upfront, drifted out under pressure in straight, headed 200 M, kept on to line.
Behind midfield along the fence, switched to outside for a clear path nearing home straight, stayed on well.
Prominent early then reigned back to sit behind leaders, moved up to challenge nearing 400 M, briefly led mid straight but run ended 100 M.
Settled in mid-division along the rail, shifted out 2-wide to challenge inside 450 M, kept on with leaders to 150 M then unable to obtain clear running, not properly tested.
Went forward, caught 3-wide over the 1st turn, settled one out one back from 1000 M, one paced turning in and weakened inside 200 M.
Placed 2-wide in mid-division, came under pressure 450 M and found no extra to challenge in straight.
Moved across to a rail position and settled in 10th 7Ls behind leader, cleared 250 M but couldn't quicken.
Held up in last well off the pace in first half of the race, not quickened under pressure in straight.
On the fence tracking leading pair, had to be nudged along approaching home straight, one paced and gave ground rapidly final 150 M.
Soon taken across from a wide barrier, settled in 2nd last 7-8Ls off the pace, made steady headway inside 350 M but was held up behind a beaten runner final 100 M.

Broke well, settled in 5th in better than midfield, soon came to challenge after straightening and hit front 200 M out, held off challenges under pressure.
Began fairly, raced keenly in forward of midfield on inside, soon came to challenge upon straightening, ran on steadily to be nearest at finish.
Began fairly, not far off in first few far side, held 3rd over 2Ls back in 3rd around the bend, failed to quicken under pressure throughout straight.
Settled behind midfield, went wide into straight, responded well inside final 200 M to be nearest at finish.
Soon picked up to a prominent spot in 4th about 3Ls off the speed, similar turning in, kept on steadily under pressure without quickening.
Settled wide in midfield, remained similar turning in, made moderate effort early in straight but failed to quicken to challenge in final stages.
Soon took up running and raced keenly coming out of back straight, held clear advantage around home bend, swamped under pressure inside final 200 M.
Began moderately, travelled wide without cover behind midfield, took closer order but hung out around the bend, went wide for home, kept on steadily until rider dropped whip 350 M out.
Began moderately, soon dropped to the rear, saved ground turning in, fought on steadily under pressure without quickening.
Jumped moderately, settled for midfield position on rails, kept on nicely in the run home.
Began well, chased leader to straight, faded steadily after straightening.
Soon dropped to last few, remained well behind, never in contention.
Always struggling in last few, never a factor.
Soon taken back to the rear and across for inside run, travelled in last few most of way, never seen with a chance. (Lame.)
Was taken back from a wide gate and immediately took up running along the fence worse than midfield. Finished off with a sound effort to grab victory in the shadows of the post.
Coursed wide and without cover in the early and middle stages, eventually gaining some cover on the circle near the 700m, whilst racing near the backmankers. Closed off strongly.
Box seated. Hit the front near the 100m but was swamped close to home. Had every chance.
Camped 3 back the rail with cover. Kept on working to the line nicely to finish in the frame.
Failed to show early speed despite being ridden vigorously, settling towards the rear of the field 3 wide with cover. Came widest in the straight and closed of solidly.
On the circle commenced to over race and was checked to avoid heels, whilst 3 wide in a midfield position. Ranged up at the 200m but was out of gas over the final stages.
Parked outside the leader. Failed to sustain its finishing effort inside the last 100m.
Traveled behind midfield, 2 deep with cover. Worked to the winning post evenly.
Ridden along early to cross and settle 1 out 1 back. Gave little when asked for an effort in the final stretch.
Settled with the backmakers had cover on the rail. Whacked away in the run to the line.
Jumped well and was sent forward to lead along the fence. Faded inside the last furlong.
Travelled 3 back 1 off the fence with cover. Only plodded to the finish line.
Copped a check near the 1000m and was never likely after settling 3 wide without cover handy to the speed.
Reared as the gates opened losing considerable ground. Settled a long last and was never in the hunt.

At midfield near the fence to home straight. Swung 3-wide and was 3Ls down leaving the bend. Ran on well top of home straight and kicked clear when asked passing 200M. Had enough to hold off rivals close home.

Proved difficult to settled early and raced behind midfield on fence. Took inside run and was 4Ls back rounding home turn. Got traffic until 300M. Kept making up ground from the winner once into clear but the post came too soon.

Travelled 2-wide behind midfield to home turn. Taken 4-wide and was 4Ls off into final stretch. Kept improving but couldn't match the finishing touch of the front pair. Held 3rd and left the rest of the field far behind.
2-wide towards rear to home turn. Forced 5-wide and was the last turning into home. 5Ls away passing 400M. Made up some ground late but was well beaten by the front trio.
On fence behind leader to home straight. Failed to progress thereafter.
2-wide behind leader to home straight. Hard ridden inside 400M but couldn't pick up. No extra final 150M.
At rear on fence until coming wide entering home straight. Found nothing when asked. (substantial amount of blood in horse's trachea.)
Led on fence until weakened 300M. Swamped inside final furlong.
Prominently placed in the box-seat just behind the leader, held up for clear run early in straight, dashed well when clear at 200 M and soon hit the front, kept on well to score.
Lacked early speed as usual, travelled 5Ls off the pace on 3-deep, suited by the genuine tempo, ran on strongly final 350 M for 2nd.
Bumped at start, settled one-off in the mid-division, responded well when asked for efforts final 350 M, finished off soundly for 3rd.
Prominently placed 2Ls off the speed, bumped at 500 M, ran on to contest the lead at the top of home straight, had all chances, failed to keep on final 100 M. (Blood in trachea.)
Easily ran up to lead and soon found the fence, travelled satisfactorily throughout the trip, kept on well early in the home straight, caught at 200 M, soon flattened.
Urged along to hold a 3-wide spot just behind the speed, travelled with no cover throughout the trip, rather one-paced when placed under pressure in the straight, no extra final 50 M.
Bumped at start, taken back from gate 10, ended up travelling 5Ls away on the fence, made up gradual ground when clear at 250 M, rather one-paced.
Eased back from gate 13, ended up in a one-off spot 5Ls off the speed, obtained clear run at the top of home straight, only one-paced when asked for efforts.
Taken back from gate 14, travelled in the rear early, took time to pick up early in the home straight, made some late ground and passed a few tired runners final 200 M.
Settled well in the mid-division on rails, one-paced when asked for efforts early in the home straight, crowded for room at 250 M, soon flattened.
Broke well, settled 3-wide in the mid-division, only gave limited response when asked for efforts in the home straight, flattened at 200 M.
Jumped well, urged along to take the one-out-one-back spot, held ground until got tired at 200 M.
Broke well, lacked early speed despite being pushed along, gradually drifted back towards the rear, failed to make any progress.
Started very awkwardly, soon eased out, took no part.
Fair break, not rushed, back to mid-rear rail, checked mid-straight, found gap, led 200m out, ran on strongly.
Moderate break, sixth one off, lost ground turn, ran on strongly straight but just outpaced by winner.
Well away, up along rail, settled fifth, rail run, kept on but not match strides with first two.
Fair break out wide, taken back to share last one off, improved wide turn, finish strongly wide.
Broke well, but caught wide, improved wide pulling briefly, settled fourth one off, ridden early straight, kept on.
Sluggish start, back to last on rail, mid-track run, stayed on well.
Fair break, not rushed, back to third last on rail, ridden and kept on quite well although short of room late.
Fair break, mid-rear one off held up, kept on under driving but not pace to challenge.
Fair break, led and crossed to rail, clear straight until weakened quickly last 200m.
Missed break, back to fourth last one off, mid-track run straight, unable to threaten.
Fair break, midfield two off, improved wide turn, ridden, little progress.
Fair break, ridden early to take second one off, second into straight, ridden, weakened.
Good break, rail third on settling, ridden mid-track, no kick, weakened.
Fair break, midfield three wide, wide into straight, ridden, found nil.
Very slow away, 5Ls off the leaders on the fence, dashed strongly 250M to win despite not suited by the slow pace.
Pushed to take the rail and led by 0.5Ls, then eased to clock very slow sectionals, hung on strongly until 100M overhauled, stayed on for 2nd.
Settled outside the lead, enjoyed by very slow tempo, ran on well to the line for 3rd.
Eased to sit in front of midfield, 2.5Ls off the slow pace 2-3 wide, showed little dash in straight.
Eased to sit midfield, 4Ls off the leaders 2 wide, harmed by the slow sectionals, little dash 200M.
Bumped start, pushed forward, 2.5Ls off the leaders, trapped 3-4 wide, not suited by the slow pace, just held ground in straight.
Pushed to obtain the box seat, benefited by the slow tempo, flattened 200M.
More prominent in midfield, 3.5Ls off the leaders along the fence, harmed by the slow pace, just held ground in straight.
Eased back, 6Ls off the leaders 2-3 wide, dashed well in straight despite not suited by the slow tempo, lacked room 200M and not fully tested.
Bumped start, eased to sit in midfield, 4Ls off the leaders 3 wide, not suited by the slow pace, ran on ok in last quarter.
Eased back, 7.5Ls off the leaders 3-4 wide, harmed by the slow tempo, ran on ok in final stages.
Bumped start, eased to rear and took rail, 6.5Ls off the leaders, not suited by the slow pace, dashed fairly.
Bumped badly at start, hard ridden, at rear, 7.5Ls off the leaders, trapped 4-5 wide, harmed by the slow sectionals, no dash.
At back, trapped 3-4 wide, harmed by the slow pace, never competitive.
Fair break but three wide no cover, driven and led mid straight soon clear, relaxed near finish.
Broke well, fifth one off, out for mid-track bid, ran on but no chance with winner.
Broke well, not rushed early, settled third on rail, had to wait for run straight, eventually followed winner through, outpaced.
Fair break, steadied, held up last, ran between rivals straight, finished well.
Out fast, up to second one off, led early straight, outpaced by winner, weakened late.
Good break, steadied midfield one off, rail run, kept on well but no real kick.
Fair start but checked early, held up last, short of room straight, kept on well when found space.
Broke fast, caught four wide midfield, wide bid straight, kept on without threatening.
Fair break, midfield two off, shaken up early straight, ridden, not quicken.
Good break, then taken back to second last one off, improved turn but failed to find a run straight, pulled wide, ran on late.
Fair break, caught wide three off rear group, wide into straight, weakened late.
Poor break, back to rear, bustled along rail to midfield, ridden, weakened.
Good break, ridden to lead rail, narrow lead into straight, ridden, weakened.
Placed behind midfield and had a smooth run along the fence, angled 3-wide nearing the home straight, picked up strongly from 300M, collared the leader final 50M out and edged away.
Placed 2-wide in the group chasing the pace, made smooth headway and hit the lead 250M out, kept on well under top weight and only caught late stages.
In midfield but never far off leaders, steadied near 350M then finished off the race strongly and almost reached 2nd at the line.
Settled near the rear, swung widest into the straight, closed in strongly and just missed a placing.
Tracked leader, briefly took over on straightening but run ended passing 200M, faded.
Restrained to last on jumping from 14, settled at the back of the field 9Ls off leader, ran on well final 300M.
Held up midfield, turned 4-wide from 600M in preparation for the home run but could keep on at the same pace only.
Slow to begin, ended up towards the rear 7-8Ls behind pace, had a mild response final 250M but not reached leaders.
Raced 3-wide behind midfield and unable to find cover in the 1st half of the race, stayed on but failed to threaten.
Held up behind midfield, shaken up 450M but never found the pace to challenge.
Taken back on jumping and raced near the rear 9Ls off the pace, had plenty to do turning in, kept on one paced and never reached contention.
Along the fence chasing leaders in 4th, not picked up when asked inside 400M, no impression.
Handily placed just off the speed but was pushed to a 3-wide position passing 900M, found nothing on straightening, eased final 150M.
Drawn wide and gradually moved across to lead at a steady pace, weakened inside 400M, eased.
Jumped fast, urged along to take the box-seat just behind the leaders, kicked strongly when asked for efforts at 400 M, hit the front at 200 M, kept on soundly to win.
Pushed forward to occupy a one-off spot 2Ls behind the leaders, hung in and raced greenly early in the home straight, clicked into gear near the 200 M pole, ran on well for 2nd.
Broke well, settled cozily 5Ls off the pace on rails, kicked well when clear final 350 M, finished off soundly for 3rd.
Prominently placed 3Ls behind the speed, travelled well in a one-off spot with cover, finished off satisfactorily final 250 M.
Jumped fast, driven to share the lead at a fast tempo, kept on satisfactorily when placed under pressure in the home straight, caught at 200 M, no extra final 100 M.
Jumped only fairly, settled three from the rear 6Ls off the pace, held up for clear run early in the home straight, finished off well final 200 M.
Lacked early speed, settled 3-wide 5Ls behind the pace, made gradual ground down centre of the home straight final 300 M, never really troubled the principals.
Jumped fairly, pushed forward to share the lead and found the fence just before the first turn, only gave limited response when asked final 250 M, got tired passing the 200 M pole.
Settled one-off 5Ls off the pace, lacked a kick when asked for efforts at the top of home straight, made no progress.
Out in line, urged along to hold a fence position 3Ls behind the leaders, outpaced at 400 M, soon weakened.
Urged along early and soon found a 3-wide position in midfield, travelled with no cover throughout the trip, gave no response when asked for efforts in the home straight, faded.
Taken back from gate 12, travelled rearward throughout the trip, never competitive.
Lacked early speed and soon settled 7Ls off the pace, niggled along at home turn, soon lost touch, finished tailed out.
Always in firing line, charged to the front near 200M and showed battling qualities to fend off challenges from both sides final 150M.
Prominent behind leader, fought on well under pressure and pushed the winner all the way to the finish.
In touch just behind leaders, had every chance in straight under a forceful ride but was always held by the winner.
Positioned 2-wide in midfield, turned 3-wide to be ready for challenge 550M, found less than expected in the finish and could not quite get to the first three despite a clear run.
Went forward from draw 11 and pressed the pace, crossed to the fence just before home turn, headed mid-straight and flattened out.
Crowded for room and steadied shortly after the start, ended up in last 8Ls behind leader, responded mildly to pressure 400M out, made some progress but never reached leaders.
In midfield, saved ground on the inside until switching to 2-wide nearing 700M, asked 450M but found disappointingly little in the drive home.
Dropped back to rear, had plenty to do turning in but could make limited progress final 400M.
On the inside never better than midfield, not quickened under pressure, one paced throughout.
Behind midfield throughout, briefly held up early straight, kept on same pace to line, never threatened.
With early leaders then dropped back to midfield nearing 1200M, swung 3-4 wide for home, pushed wider in straight and was never in contention, eased final stages.
Towards the rear, made a short-lived effort passing 400M, no extra mid-straight, eased when no chance inside 150M.
Slow to begin, ended up in a 3-wide position behind midfield, pushed wider over the home turn, soon beaten.
Pressed the lead, caught 3-wide without cover turning in, gave ground from 450M, soon out of contention.

Horse No: Comments on Running is not available for this race.
Horse Name: Comments on Running is not available for this race.

Gear: Comments on Running is not available for this race.

Ridden along to contest lead early, held half a length advantage leaving the Rock, held similar break turning in, hung on under pressure until eased final stride.
Chased leaders in 3rd, soon came to challenge after straightening, fought on doggedly to be nearest at finish but without threatening.
Began well, settled one-out-one-back in 2L 4th, similar turning in, fought on under pressure without quickening.
Travelled in midfield, commenced move entering home straight, met minor interference inside 300 M, fought on steadily to the line.
Raced wide in midfield, failed to quicken while hanging in straight.
Driven along to vie for lead early, settled half length back in second approaching the Rock, held similar turning for home, faded out of it inside final 200 M.
Soon drifted backward from a wide draw, remained well behind turning for home, ran past well beaten horses.
Began fairly, showed only moderate speed early despite niggled along in forward of midfield on rails, saved ground on inside turning for home, weakened under pressure inside final 200 M.
Gradually drifted backward from the widest barrier to reach last few after the Rock, ran past well beaten horses in the run home.
Began with others, settled in rear of midfield on rails, found nothing under pressure in straight.
Slowly away, never seen with a chance.
Always in last few, 9th into straight, made no impression.
Settled 1 out 1 back before rolling to the fence after the 600m. peeled out on straightening hit the front by the furlong and won nicely.
Settled behind midfield, 2 wide with cover. Gained a nice run early in the straight and fought on gamely right to the wire.
Began awkwardly and lost ground settled towards the rear of the field, 2 wide with cover. Ran on nicely.
Settled with the backmakers, 3 wide with cover. Closed off well down the centre of the course to figure in the frame.
Traveled midfield 1 off with cover. Commenced a forward move after the 600m, shifting out to race 3 wide without cover on the circle. Whacked away at the same speed in the run to the line.
Snagged back from a wide gate to settle in last position along the rails. Commenced to close off well but ran into traffic problems over the final 150m, not tested properly.
Worked forward to lead along the fence. Faded after the last 200m.
Copped some crowding early and was shuffled back to settle worse than midfield, along the paint. Only plodded to the line.
Settled 3 back 2 deep with cover. Never got going in the final stretch. (Pulled up lame in the RF the following day.)
Tracked the leader along the paint. Commenced to give ground after the 600m, struggled in the home straight.
Caught out on a limb, 3 wide without cover close to midfield. Never likely.
Spent plenty of petrol to work forward and cross to race outside the leader after the 1100. Hung in for most of the trip and finished well back. (To trial.)
Well enough away on fence, ended up at midfield to home turn. Shifted out for run but was blocked top of home straight. Forced its way out final 100 M, just made.

Good jump but was caught wide. Gradually taken to 3-wide behind midfield before stable bend. Improved to midfield from 700 M. 2Ls down on straightening. Hit front 200 M and had every chance to score. Caught final strides.

2-wide behind midfield to back straight. Dropped towards rear home turn. Swung widest and was 5Ls adrift into final stretch. Finished off well to snatch 3rd on line without seriously troubling the front pair.
Bumped at start and was taken to 2-wide towards rear. Progressed to 3-wide behind midfield passing the Rock. 3Ls away turning into home. Kept giving for a minor placing. Just failed.
3-wide at midfield early. Strode forward to track leaders back straight but left wide and without cover. Kept on home straight until no extra to repel the principals final 100 M.

Quickly into stride. Eased to sit 2-wide ahead of midfield stable bend. Dropped slightly to midfield back straight and was 3Ls off turning into home. Ran on steadily before checked near 100 M. Plugged on once resumed.

Away in line. Trapped wide and without cover at midfield stable bend. Strode forward passing 1200 M and parked outside the leader from 900 M. Led briefly top of home straight and weakened final furlong.
Driven to go forward but caught wide. Slotted outside the leader at 1300 M. Sat one-off behind leaders back straight. Close enough to strike home straight but failed to make any impact.
Soon taken to rear from widest barrier. Still the last turning in. Beat tired runners home.
Back with last few on fence through to home straight. Steadied at 300 M, then hung in and was unable to obtain clear running. Not fully tested.
Pushed early and led on fence 1500 M. Eased to box-seat from stable bend. Raced tight final 300 M but failed to improve when afforded clear run.
Urged early after start. Eventually led on fence from stable bend. Pressed to maintain lead passing 400 M. Steadied at 300 M when crowded for room. Never resumed.
Broke very fast, settled fourth one off, took off leaving back to join leader, led 300m out, ran on well.
Well away, up to leaders but caught three wide first turn, went second back straight, tried to go with winner when that horse quickened, kept on, just outpaced.
Broke well, up on rail to settle third, slightly outpaced turn, ran on late.
Slow away, held up third last one off, improved between runners exiting back, ran on, not quite pace to challenge.
Fast away, led early, tried to dictate slow pace until overtaken far side, ridden but not much response once headed.
Missed beat at start, bustled to take rail midfield, outpaced entering turn, ridden, kept on without threatening.
Slightly awkward start, taken back to rail fourth last held up, pulled out for mid track run, driven but no real impact.
Broke well, but then awkward, sixth two off, ridden early straight, no impression.
Fair break, held up mid-rear, tried to improve wide turn, never a threat.
Taken back from wide draw, last on rail, ridden leaving back, no progress.
Fair break but early bump, held up last one off, hard ridden entering turn, no progress.
Moderate start and bumped early, up to leading group, then midfield one off, ridden but lost ground, well adrift straight.
Driven from gate and headed off field to lead, still two lengths clear into straight, ran on, never challenged.
Broke well, not pace to lead, checked and reined back to fifth, ridden turn and throughout straight, ran on but not pace to challenge.
Fair break, not rushed early, midfield rail, pulled out for mid-track bid, ran on without troubling first two.
Broke well, second on rail, hard ridden straight but unable to make impression on winner.
Fai break, midfield but caught three wide, up to share second leaving back, no further progress, weakened late.
Not fast out of gate, little early speed, back to last on rail, urged, good progress late.
Fair break but no early speed, second last one off urged, ridden and ran on late.
Broke well, ridden up early to third one off, ridden along from long way out, gradually lost pitch.
Sluggish start, fourth last one off, ridden, no significant progress.
Fair break but lacked early pace, never a factor.
Sluggish start, back to midfield rail,checked early and lost ground, third last into straight, ridden, no response.
Hard ridden out of gate but beaten for early speed, gradually dropped back through field, eased when beaten.
Settled in front of midfield early, trapped 3 wide, moved forward to share the lead 2 wide at fast sectionals, led 300M, closed off strongly to win.
Eased back, 5.5Ls off the leaders along the fence, benefited by the fast pace, made steady ground 250M and took 2nd.
Settled in front of midfield, 2.5Ls off the leaders 2-3 wide, ran on well to the line for 3rd.
Midfield, 4.5Ls off the leaders 2-3 wide, favoured by the fast tempo, just held ground in straight.
Progressed steadily and crossed in front, shared lead at fast sectionals, flattened 200M.
Very slow away, at rear, 7Ls off the leaders 2-3 wide, benefited by the fast pace, made minor ground 200M.
Very slow away, hard ridden to keep up at back, 6Ls off the leaders 2-3 wide, helped by the fast pace, however ran on fairly.
Out paced at rear, never traveled well, ran on fairly although benefited by the fast tempo.
Midfield, 4Ls off the leaders on the fence, favoured by the fast pace, no progress.
Prominent, just behind the leaders 2 wide, not suited by the fast sectionals, emptied 300M.
Hard ridden to cross in front, then eased into box seat, not suited by the fast tempo, weakened 250M.
Trapped 3-4 wide in midfield throughout, lost too much ground at bends, never a factor.
Broke well, settled cosily 1.5Ls off pace, quickened well when asked at the top of home straight, kept on strongly, hit the front in the final stride.
Jumped only fairly, pushed hard to lead 1L on rails, responded well when asked for efforts at the top of home straight, kept on soundly, just caught on line.
Slow away and crowded for room shortly after start, settled well 5Ls off the pace, quickened well when clear at 200 M, finished off soundly for 3rd.
Widely drawn, driven to occupy a one-off spot 2Ls behind the leader, obtained clear run early in home straight, made gradual ground under maximum pressure, rather one-paced.
Taken back from gate 11, travelled 3-wide 6Ls off the speed, finished off satisfactorily under pressure final 250 M, but never really troubled the principals.
Settled 3Ls off the pace on rails, travelled satisfactorily throughout the trip, only one-paced when asked for efforts final 250 M.
Pushed hard early and soon settled in the one-out-one-back spot, kept on fairly under maximum pressure, rather one-paced.
Broke well, settled 4Ls off the pace in midfield, caught 3-wide throughout the trip, on heels at 300 M and 200 M, only gave limited response when asked.
Lacked early speed despite being urged along, ended up settling 6L away in the rear, failed to make up any ground in the home straight.
Settled rearward 6Ls off the pace, crowded at 600 M, made some late ground final 150 M under hands and heels riding.
Urged along to hold a one-off position in midfield, hung in in the home straight, on heels at 300 M, failed to make any progress.
Jumped fastest from gate12, lacked early speed despite being ridden hard, caught 3-wide, gradually drifted back to midfield, got tried at the top of home straight, faded.
Positioned 2-wide in mid-division and travelled strongly, made rapid headway on straightening to strike the lead 200M out, drew clear and kept on to the finish determinedly.
Restrained to a position behind midfield, saved ground on the inside, came through horses final 250M to go 2nd 50M out but not a threat to the winner.
Travelled 3-wide in midfield and covered more ground than rivals, driven along 500M out but took time to gather, closed well final 200M.
Raced in the 2 path throughout, in touch always, no match with winner but ran on under pressure and only lost 3rd close home.
In the front early but soon surrendered the lead, raced along the fence in a position ahead of midfield, came out 350M and finished off the race fairly, not reached leaders.
Chased leader, first to challenge in straight but hung in when placed under pressure, one-paced final 200M.
Held up near the rear and well off the pace in first half, moved closer as the pace slackened passing 800M, under pressure 500M out and made very limited progress in straight.

Struck its head on the barrier gate and lost ground at the start, raced towards the rear throughout and not picked up in straight. (Jockey reported the incident at the start had a large bearing on the horse's performance.)
Sped to the lead on jumping from 12 and set fast pace in the first half, led to 200M and weakened rapidly in late stages.
Close up tracking leader, not quickened turning into straight and weakened passing 200M.
Didnt muster despite ridden along early stages, ended up in the rear over 9Ls behind leader, travelled fairly throughout and couldn't quicken in the drive home.
Held up towards the rear, had plenty to do leaving the home turn and lacked any response.
Jumped fast, soon ran up to lead 1L on rails, quickened well when asked at 300 M, kept on soundly to score.
Broke well, prominently placed in the box-seat just behind the leader, responded well when asked for efforts final 250 M, finished off strongly for 2nd.
Bumped after start, urged along early to take the one-out-one-back spot, lacked a decisive kick to challenge the top two but did keep on well enough for a place.
Jumped only fairly, soon settled two from the rear on rails, swung widest for home, finished off strongly down centre of the home straight, too late.
Settled cosily in the mid-division on rails, looked possible for a place at the top of home straight, only one-paced when placed under maximum pressure.
Bumped after start, lacked early speed as usual, settled 7Ls off the pace, swung wide for home and obtained clear run at 250 M, made ground steadily without threatening the principals.
Started awkwardly, caught 3-wide with no cover in midfield, only one-paced when asked for efforts in the home straight.
Taken back from gate 12, settled 7-8Ls off the pace in rear, made some late ground when clear at 200 M.
Given a waiting ride in the early stages, settled one-off in midfield, responded only fairly when asked for efforts final 250 M, no extra final 100 M.
Out in line, urged along to hold a fence position 5Ls off the speed, only gave limited response when asked for efforts final 300 M.
Jumped fastest, settled 2-3Ls off the pace on 2-wide, held ground until got tired near 200 M.
Lacked early speed despite being niggled along, caught 3-wide just behind the mid-division, outpaced rounding the home turn, soon dropped out.
Broke well, restrained to travel mainly in 4th or 5th within 2Ls of pace, soon came under pressure to challenge after straightening, gained upper hand inside final 50 M.
Settled in midfield, commenced move entering straight, quickened well to hit front passing 200 M but unable to sustain effort and headed inside 50 M.
Settled towards the rear, one of the widest turning in, ran home strongly to narrowly miss 2nd.
Held up to race off the rails in rear of midfield, remained similar turning for home, fought on steadily to be nearest at finish.
Settled in last few, widest into straight, made up good ground down centre to be nearest at finish.
Settled well behind, saved ground on inside turning in, snuck up along rails early in straight, unable to sustain effort inside final 100 M.
Soon obtained a rails position at around midfield, remained similar into straight, kept on well for a nice run home.

Moderate start, raced wide in forward of midfield early, took closer order down far side to hit front going up the Rock, held 1L break around the bend but soon worn down turning in, quickly overhauled inside final 200 M.
Broke well, settled just off the pace in 2nd, folded up quickly upon straightening.
Began well, held up mainly in 3rd or 4th about 2Ls off the muddling pace, folded up quickly after straightening.
Jumped moderately but soon took up running coming onto stables bend, led until narrowly headed up the Rock, soon weakened from 3rd into straight.
Began with others, soon taken back to settle in midfield on rails, dropped away quickly after straightening. (Heart irregularity.)

Began fairly, settled wide in just better than midfield to straight, remained wide turning in, quickened well to take command inside final 200 M.
Began awkwardly, well behind early, took closer order despite minor interference coming out of back straight, sustained progress inside final 400 M to be nearest at finish.
Never far off in 4th, similar turning in, ran home one-paced under pressure without quickening.
Led far side, headed and settled for one-back position on rails into straight, disputed lead after straightening, unable to sustain effort inside final 200 M.
Tailed off most of way to straight, saved ground on rails turning in, made up good ground in the run home.
Well there, took up running around the bend, weakened under pressure inside final 200 M.
Began awkwardly losing ground, settled for rear of midfield position far side, failed to make any impression under pressure in the run home.
Began moderately, settled in forward of midfield on rails, saved ground on rails turning in, soon weakened out of contention after straightening.
Never better than midfield, drifted backward into straight, made no further impression.
Jumped slowly, gradually improved from towards rear to reach midfield around the bend, found nothing in the run home.
Broke well from the wide draw and given reminders early, well there to straight, dropped out noticeably after straightening.
Raced wide without cover in midfield far side, gradually dropped towards rear around the bend, made no further impression.
Camped 4 back the fence. Peeled out early in the home straight and let down strongly to record a convincing win.
Made its run from worse than midfield, 2 deep with cover. Took inside runs in the final stretch and closed off soundly.
Enjoyed the run of the race on the fence in fourth position. Loomed up and hit the front at the furlong but was overhauled soon after.
Posted 3-wide without cover on the circle, behind midfield. Straightened wide but fought on to finish in the frame.
Handed up the lead and took a sit along the paint after the 800 M. Had every chance but weakened in the run to the post.
Taken back from the outside alley to travel with the backmarkers, 3-wide with cover. Came wide in the straight but weakened on its run well short of the line.
Raced prominently, 1 off with cover. Whacked away at the same speed, had no excuses.
Slow to begin and raced in last position 1 off with cover. Plodded to the line.
Speared forward from a wide gate to lead along the fence after the 800 M. Faded inside the final 100 M.
Slow to begin settling 3 back the fence. Peeled out into the clear rounding the home turn but failed to find any extra at the business end of the race.
Knuckled over at the start settling with the tailenders, 1 off with cover. Never in the hunt.
Began very awkwardly losing ground and settling towards the rear along the paint. Made no impression in the run home.
Driven early in front rank but trapped wide. Rolled to sit outside leader on home turn. Ridden out 300 M and responded well. Always had enough to repel rivals in run home.

Began fairly and settled behind midfield on fence. Checked to rear passing 800 M and was steadied at 650 M. Finished off strongly once afforded unimpeded run in the straight. Covered substantial ground to snatch 2nd.
Slow to begin but soon made up lost ground. Tracked leaders home turn. Kept on in the straight but failed to threaten the winner. Peaked and lost 2nd near the line.
Settled 3-wide behind midfield to home straight. 5Ls down passing 400 M. Improved moderately to obtain a non-threatening 4th.
Travelled wide at rear to home straight. 6Ls adrift passing 400 M. Ran on steadily to the line.
Back with last few in a 4-wide spot. Swung widest turning into home. One-paced to conclude.
Urged early on fence in a forward spot. Hung out and shuffled to midfield passing 800 M. Peeled out and was 2Ls off turning in. Plugged on until no extra final furlong.
Hard ridden early but caught wide. Slotted 2-wide at midfield home turn. Forced 4-wide and was 3Ls back into final stretch. Failed to progress thereafter.
Raced 3 to 4-wide behind midfield to home turn. Found nothing when asked top of home straight. Beaten well before post.
Under pressure early. Eventually parked 2-wide behind leaders home turn. Faded soon after straightening.
Soon led on fence despite highest draw. Shared lead home turn. Dropped out final 300 M.
Away in line and raced behind midfield near the fence. Checked at 800 M. Dropped towards rear home turn. Never recovered.
Broke fast, led early, settled on rail, found seam to challenge in straight, driven and ran on strongly to lead last 75 M.
Fair break out wide, taken back to settle fifth last on rail, improved turn, wide challenge, finished fast, just failed.
Broke well, settle fifth one off, ridden turn, kept on under strong driving.
Sluggish start, rushed up first time past the post to lead far side, two clear into straight, weakened last 100 M.
Taken back to rail from wide draw, held up rear, improved wide turn, ran on wide under driving, never able to challenge.
Fair break, taken back to fourth last rail, hard ridden from turn and ran on, but never able to challenge.
Fair break, ridden early for lead but caught three wide, settled third one off, third into straight, ridden, weakened.
Out fast, ridden for lead but beaten for speed, settled midfield one off, short of room entering straight, kept on.
Broke well, led early, headed back straight, settled second, tried to challenge entering straight, ridden, weakened.
Well away but caught wide first turn, back to third last one off, tried to improve early straight, short of room, one pace.
Moderate start, short of early pace, second last and urged, only ran past beaten horses.
Slow start, ridden along rail to midfield, checked far side, weakened straight.
Broke well, hard ridden to seek lead but caught wide first turn, back to midfield two off, wide into straight, weakened.
Broke well, early speed but lacked pace to hold pitch, bumped turn, faded, eased when beaten.
Fair break wide, taken back to last on rail, time to settle, began to improve one off turn, wove through field, led last stride.
Broke well, pulled early before settling fourth on rail, ran on well to lead 100 M out, caught last stride.
Fair break but lost early place, back to fifth last on off, finished strongly out wide, just failed.
Broke well, led first turn until deep straight, just nailed by three finishers close home.
Good break, settled rail midfield, short of room early straight and beaten for momentum by closers, ran on late.
Not well away, lost length, rail mid-rear, found split straight but not pace to resist closers.
Fair break, ridden early but caught wide and bumped first turn, midfield rail, driven straight, kept on one pace.
Slow start, back to rail fourth last, driven and kept on along rail but never able to challenge.
Fair break, not much early speed, just behind pace one off, held place straight until weakened late.
Fair break, ridden early, not pace to go with leaders, slight bump first turn, ridden early straight, no progress.
Missed beat start, third last one off, urged, ridden, no impact.
Fair break, lacked speed early, last one off, ridden leaving back, wide straight, no progress.
Fair break wide, looking for lead, settled third one off, ridden entering straight, weakened.
Fast away and aimed for lead, caught wide instead, up to second two off back straight, ridden, weakened, eased.
Shared the lead easily at good pace along the fence, made all.
Eased to sit in front of midfield, 2-1/2Ls off the good pace 3-wide, closed the race off strongly, just beaten by a neck in 2nd.
At back, 5-1/2Ls off the good pace 3 to 4-wide, made steady ground 250 M.
Eased to sit in midfield, 4Ls off the good pace 3-wide, progressed steadily 300 M, run ended 50 M.
Slow away, hard ridden to share the lead 2-wide at good pace, out of fuel 200 M.
Eased to sit behind midfield on the rails, 4Ls off the good pace, blocked 4-2, just held ground when clear.
At back, 7Ls off the good pace, trapped 4 to 5-wide throughout and lost too much ground, still made some ground in straight.
Trapped 3-wide throughout in the lead, pace good, weakened 200 M.
Struggled at rear, 7-1/2Ls off the good pace on the fence, checked 400 M, held up 4-2, made some ground when clear.
Box seat, dropped off 400 M.
Eased at start, never better than midfield.
Slow away, 2-1/2Ls off the good pace along the fence, faded 350 M.
Easily ran up to lead and found the fence just before the bend, quickened well when asked for efforts at 300 M, kept on soundly to score, never really challenged.
Broke well, prominently placed 1-2Ls just behind the speed, travelled well on 2-deep with cover, finished off well under pressure in the home straight, kept on for 2nd.
Broke fast from the widest alley, urged along to take the one-out-one-back spot, unable to challenge the winner but did well enough for a place.
Out in line, settled one-off in the mid-division, obtained clear run at the top of home straight, made gradual ground under maximum pressure, just missed a place.
Settled cosily in the box-seat just behind the leader, kept on fairly well when placed under pressure in the home straight, rather one-paced.
Taken rearward from gate 10, caught 3-wide with no cover, bumped at 700 M, made ground steadily in the home straight, rather one-paced.
Given a waiting ride as usual, travelled 7Ls off the pace in rear, covered some late ground final 250 M, never really threatened the principals.
Jumped only fairly, pushed along to hold a fence position in midfield, crowded at 700 M and 400 M, failed to make up any ground in the home straight.
Slow away and crowded, lacked early speed and travelled 5Ls off the pace on 3-deep, bumped at 700 M, badly checked at 600 M, only made limited progress final 200 M.
Lacked early speed as usual, travelled one from the rear on rails, on heels at 700 M, made no progress in the home straight.
Driven hard to hold a one-off position just off the pace, hung in throughout the trip, failed to maintain his position at the top of home straight, soon faded.
Travelled 5Ls off the speed on 2-deep, need to be urged along to maintain his position, on heels at 700 M, outpaced at home turn, finished tailed out.
Up with the early pace then eased to sit in 3rd down the back straight, moved quickly to contention inside 300 M, took the lead near 150 M and was all out to fend off the runner up in late stages.

Positioned towards the rear 2-wide, unhurried early and was 10Ls off the pace in middle stages, driven inside 500 M, made significant headway final 350 M and was closing on the winner with every stride, just held.

Restrained to last to avoid being wide on the first turn, had plenty to do turning in, picked up well in straight, had to shift ground near 200 M to improve, closed off willingly but the first two had gone beyond reach.
Broke a bit slow, ended up at the rear over 12Ls behind runaway leader, swung widest into straight, ran on well from off the pace for a distant 4th.
Broke well, taken to the fence and raced in 5th position ahead of midfield, switched to 2-wide entering back straight, stayed on but didn't find extra pace to seriously challenge.
Positively ridden out the gate, chased runaway leader throughout, kept on to 100 M then weakened.

Dropped and was a long way off the pace in a strongly run race, made up ground early straight under some light urging, shifted ground 150 M to improve but never reached the 150 M leaders. (Jockey questioned.)

Knuckled over at the start, caught wide in early stages but managed to slot into a 2-wide position mid-pack nearing 1200 M, lacked a response when the race got serious and was never a threat to the leaders.
Positioned 2-wide behind midfield and 8Ls behind the pace in middle stages, driven along passing 600 M, ran on only fairly, one paced final 200 M.
Held up behind midfield in what was a strongly run race, saved ground on the inside but had to be taken wide in straight for a clear path, showed little in the drive home.
Never better than midfield, came under serious pressure 500 M out, run ended 200 M, eased when no chance over final stages. (Jockey questioned re the disappointing performance.)
Dropped back towards the rear and was over 10Ls behind in middle stages, urged along midway home turn but failed to respond.
Sped to the lead under some aggressive handling, raced fiercely in middle stages and wouldn't settle, opened up a 3Ls gap turning in, weakened rapidly from 200 M. (Jockey questioned re his ride.)

Handily placed in 4th, not picked up when asked leaving the home bend, weakened rapidly and dropped out of contention passing 200 M. (Jockey reported his horse had become stirred up prior to entering the barriers.)
