Settled in last few, commenced move around the bend, badly baulked for a run passing 400 M, soon renewed effort and finished off race strongly to wear down winner quickly but the post came too soon. (Promoted to 1st by Stewards.)
Settled in midfield on rails, switched out for a run inside 400 M taking the ground of the eventual winner, ran on under pressure to gain upper hand final strides. (Relegated to 2nd by Stewards.)
Tracked leader to straight, soon hit front after straightening but unable to sustain effort and headed final few strides.
Broke well, settled one-out-one-back in 2nd, kept on same pace under pressure without quickening in straight.
Travelled just better than midfield about 3Ls off the pace, came under strong pressure after straightening holding place chance until swamped late.
Settled well behind, made up good ground down centre of straight to be nearest at finish.
Began awkwardly losing ground, remained well behind, saved ground on rails home bend, ran past well beaten horses in straight.
Began well, soon taken back to race wide in rear of midfield, drifted out upon straightening, fought on steadily down lone furrow without recovering too much ground in the run home.
Settled in midfield, ran home one-paced.
Began from a wide draw with others and soon took up running, led until headed over 300 M out, dropped out noticeably.
Travelled in last few, racing keenly at times far side, in similar position turning in, found nothing in straight. (Tactic questioned.)
Travelled in better than midfield, similar turning in, made no impression in straight.
Began awkwardly from the widest draw, soon picked up to better than midfield far side, reaching 4th when 3Ls back and wide around the bend, dropped away quickly into straight.
Towards rear before dropping back to tail-end into straight.
Settled as equal leader along the rail. Shot clear early in the straight and held of late challenge.
Worked forward to vie for the lead, settling as joint front runner. Became unbalanced early in the straight and didn't sprint when called for an effort. Clawed back to finish just short of the post.
Raced prominently but was posted 3 wide without cover. Held on gamely in the final stages.
Slow to begin then hard ridden to improve, settling midfield on the fence after the 800m. Made steady headway in the home straight, raced in restricted room close to home.
Camped midfield, 1 off with cover. Made good ground after once properly into the clear near the furlong.
Was with the leading trio before easing in the early stages to track the leader along the paint. Came up short after enjoying a nice run in transit.
Covered ground for most of the journey, midfield 3 wide with cover. Plugged away to the winning post.
Slow to begin settling worse than midfield in the pace. Whacked away at the same speed over the latter stages.
Had every chance after settling 1 out 1 back. Was well beaten after the last 100m.
Jumped well then was steadied to obtain cover, I pair back. Obtained partial cover on the circle but course 3-4 wide for most of the trip. Battled away over the final stages.
Settled with the backmakers, 3 wide with cover. Failed to close off.
Crowded at the start settling back in the field, 2 deep with cover. Came wide in the final stretch but made no impression.
Raced worse than midfield, 2 deep with cover. Struggled in the run to the line.
Tailed the field for most of the trip. Never in contention.
Soon in front rank. Ridden 300M out. Powered clear final furlong. Easy.
One-off stand's rail behind leaders. Picked up passing 400M. Winner too strong but held 2nd comfortably.
Urged to race at midfield early. On leaders' back passing 600M. Battled for a minor placing and prevailed at post but never threatened the front pair.
Behind midfield early. Tracked leaders passing 500M. Hard ridden 350M out. Fought on for a minor placing. Just failed at line.

Slow to begin and was crowded for room. Travelled down the centre of the track behind midfield. Improved gradually from 600M and raced behind leaders at 400M. Pressed on but was one-paced to conclude.
On leader's back along stand's rail. Shifted in for clear running passing 350M but was steadied when disappointed for running. Made up minor ground once resumed.
Caught on the far side towards rear from low draw. Taken out for cover passing 600M. Made up ground briefly passing 400M but no extra final furlong.
Amongst leaders on stand's rail. Pressured from 500M to maintain lead. Dropped out gradually from 300M.
Began fairly well, ended up towards rear near stand's rail passing 600M. No real progress thereafter.
Towards rear throughout. Very little impression.
At rear until passing tired runners home. Never likely.
In the leading pack until faded 300M out. Emptied final furlong.
One-off stand's rail in a forward spot. Failed to quicken when the race got serious final 350M. Plodded on home.
Always at rear. Never in the hunt.
Jumped well, settled fifth one off, pulled out for mid-track challenge, led 200m out, drew right away.
Well away, third on rail, out to challenge mid-straight, kept on, no match for winner.
Fair break but caught wide, back to second last two off, ran on very well out wide but no chance with winner.
Not well away but quickly up to lead, still led 200m out, weakened.
Fair break, not much early speed, fifth last on rail, rail run straight, kept on.
Moderate break, bustled early but still back to second last, kept on from turn under urging but never able to challenge.
Fair break, up to midfield one off, wide bid, kept on but never able to challenge.
Broke well, settled fourth on rail, kept on mid track until weakened sharply late.
Fair break, taken back to rear, held up, ridden into straight, kept on but no real progress.
Broke well, led very briefly then outpaced, dropped to second last on rail, ridden straight, no progress.
Broke well out wide, up to fifth three off, wide bid straight, no progress.
Fair break, ridden up wide to third three off, still third into straight, ridden, weakened quickly.
Ridden out wide to lead early and cross to rail, headed far side and settled second as pace slowed, kicked early straight, soon clear, never threatened.
Moderate start, back to midfield rail, no racing room to improve before straight, ran on through horses but not reach winner.
Good break, settled fourth on rail, kept on in straight but outpaced.
Sluggish start, rear early, up to mid-rear one off, running on when checked mid-straight, picked up again and kept on well.
Broke well, up comfortably to lead, led narrowly into straight, hard ridden, weakened.
Taken back from wide draw to fourth last two off, improved wide turn, ran on wide but unable to challenge, weakened late.
Taken back and held up second last one off, kept on in straight but never able to challenge.
Fair break, sixth on rail, wide bid, no kick.
Slowly away, ridden early, second last on rail, kept on along rail under driving but never a threat.
Fair break, midfield two off, improved wide turn, ridden, no extra.
Fair break, up to third one off, fourth into straight, ridden, weakened.
Slowly away, taken back from wide draw to last one off, tried to improve wide, no progress.
Broke well, up with early lead but caught wide, settled midfield two off, improved wide on turn, ridden, weakened quickly.
Eased to sit in midfield, 4Ls off the leaders 2-3 wide, demonstrated its usual strong finishing efforts 300M to win without much threats.
Eased at start to take rail at rear, 7Ls off the leaders, harmed by the slow pace, held up 4-2, dashed strongly when clear and got 2nd.
Eased back and took rail, 5.5Ls off the leaders along the fence, harmed by the slow pace, dashed well in straight and grabbed 3rd.
Pushed forward to take rail and shared the lead at slow sectionals, ran on until 250M flattened.
Eased to sit in midfield, 2.5Ls off the leaders 3-4 wide, not suited by the slow pace, held ground until 200M flattened.
At rear, 9Ls off the leaders 2 wide, moved closer as the pace slackened 800M, little dash in straight despite not suited by the slow tempo.
Pushed to obtain a more prominent spot then usual, 2.5Ls off the leaders 2-3 wide, not suited by the slow tempo, no progress in last quarter.
At back, 5.5Ls off the leaders, trapped 3-5 wide and lost too much ground, not suited by the slow tempo, dashed fairly in straight, run ended 150M.
Eased back, not suited by the slow pace, never competitive.
Eased to sit 2Ls off the slow pace early, trapped wide, then pressed forward 1200M to share the lead 2 wide, emptied 300M.
Bumped start, hard ridden forward, 1.5Ls off the leaders 3 wide, faded 300M.
Raced 3-5 wide throughout, never better than midfield and tailed out.
Pushed forward, took rail and shared the lead at slow sectionals, however dropped off quickly 400M.
Jumped well, niggled along to track the leader on 2-deep, ran on easily to contest lead early in the home straight, dashed well when asked at 200 M, finished off soundly to score, impressive.
Prominently placed in the box-seat just behind the leader, responded well when asked for efforts at 400 M, finished off soundly for 2nd, impressive debut.
Broke well, easily ran up to lead and soon found the fence, caught by the winner passing the 200 M pole, kept on well for a place.
Jumped only fairly, urged along to hold a fence position 5-6Ls off the speed, ran on steadily final 300 M, but never really troubled the top three.
Driven to hold a one-off spot in the mid-division, made up gradual ground final 250 M without threatening the principals.
Settled in a fence position in midfield, responded only fairly when asked at the top of home straight, flattened at 150 M.
Awkward start and crowded, pushed early and travelled 7-8Ls off the pace in rear, only made very limited progress final 200 M.
Awkward start, urged along to catch up 6Ls behind the speed, only covered little ground final 200 M.
Lacked early speed as usual and settled one-off in midfield, failed to make up any ground in the home straight.
Jumped fast, prominently placed 2-3Ls off the speed, held ground until flattened near the 200 M pole.
Showed no early speed despite being pushed along, caught 3-wide without cover, made no progress in the home straight.
Jockey lost the use of left stirrup iron at jumping and soon re-gathered it, travelled rearward throughout the trip, never competitive.
Dropped in for cover behind leaders, made his move nearing 400M, quickened well and took the lead inside 200M, came under strong challenge in closing stages and was fully extended to prevail.
Reserved off the early pace and not hurried in early and middle stages, held up near 400M, ran on strongly final 200M and was closing on the winner with every stride, just missed.
Lost ground at the start, near the rear early but took closer order passing 600M, responded when put to pressure and looked a possible winner 200M out, fought on well to line and was just denied.
Right up with early pace, kept on well when asked and battled on doggedly through the final 200M, beaten only a neck.
Slow to begin, held up in last 5Ls behind the pace, made rapid headway 400M out, steadied 200M and was not properly tested when badly held up for running until the concluding stages.
Within easy striking distance, loomed a threat 300M but run ended 150M from home, gradually weakened.
Always in the firing line, briefly led inside 300M but couldn't sustain effort final 200M.
Behind midfield about 3Ls off the pace, shaken up midway, ran on only fairly and was unable to reach the horses in front.
Tracked leader along the Stands' rail but couldn't step up a gear when the race got serious inside 400M.
Tracked leader, not quickened when asked nearing 400M, kept on same pace then weakened over the final 200M.
Set the pace along the Stands' rail, couldn't find any extra when placed under pressure inside 400M, headed 300M and weakened.
Chased the pace under some urging, under pressure halfway, weakened passing 300M. (Lame next day.)
Not far off the lead, found nothing when asked 400M out, soon out of contention.
Towards the rear and never travelled at any stage, left behind halfway, eased.
Jumped well, prominently placed 2-3Ls off the pace on rails, kicked when obtained clear run at 350 M, finished off strongly, hit the front at 50 M, scored with some in hand.
Broke well, soon ran up to lead and found the fence at 1100 M, kept on soundly when placed under pressure in the home straight, caught by the winner at 50 M.
Started awkwardly, urged along to take the box-seat just behind the leader, ran on strongly final 250 M to contest the lead, passed by the winner at 100 M, kept on soundly for 3rd.
Settled cosily on the rails in midfield, made ground steadily along the inner of the home straight, lacked a decisive kick to challenge the top three.
Started awkwardly, urged along to hold a one-off spot 3Ls off the speed, travelled keenly with no cover, made gradual ground final 300 M, rather one-paced.
Settled one-off just behind the mid-division, crowded and blocked early in the home straight, ran on steadily when obtained clear run at 250 M, finished off satisfactorily.
Prominently placed in a one-off spot just off the pace, only one-paced when asked for efforts in the home straight.
Niggled along to hold a one-off spot in midfield, kept on fairly in the home straight, rather one-paced.
Taken back from gate 9 and travelled about 7Ls off the pace, made gradual ground final 300 M, never really troubled the principals.
Crowded after start, taken rearward from gate 11, 6Ls behind the leader at 400 M, failed to make up any ground.
Slow to begin and soon crowded, travelled 3-wide in the mid-division, only gave limited response when asked for efforts in the home straight, failed to make up any ground.
Out in line, urged along to take the one-out-one-back spot, held ground until got tired near 300 M.
Taken back from gate 12, travelled rearward throughout the trip, proved difficult to settle when restrained in the early stages, failed to make up any ground in the home straight.
Crowded start, travelled two from the rear on the fence, made no progress in the home straight, weakened at 200 M and gave ground. (Heart irregularity.)
Standard getaway, raced 4 to 5Ls away on rails, moved 2 wide on bend, travelled strongly turning and cruised to leader at 200 M, went on to score with ease.
Began well, took up a position role outside leader, fair run to turning in, took over and led until 200 M, stayed on bravely but dominated by winner late.
Checked early and settled in rear division, best part of 7 to 8Ls back on rails, 6Ls down at 400 M, made strong progress final furlong to take 3rd.
No early speed, ended up behind midfield 6Ls back had even trip on rails, steadied approaching bend, didn't have much clear running until 200 M, did best late when clear to make frame.
Plenty of speed, wide early before crossing to lead, did share of work with attention from outside horse in mid section, passed.
Began fairly, caught 3 wide without cover 4 to 5Ls back in mid section, worked throughout and pushed 4 wide at 600 M, kept improving turning, hard run took toll and faded from 300 M.
Settled behind midfield 6Ls back in running line, gradually improved on circle, brief place hope at 300 M but failed to see out journey and lost touch last 200 M.
Away well, behind leaders but proved difficult to settle, moved 2 wide on circle, still ungenerous to bend, niggled turning and bumped, didn't find thereafter.
Out well, took a trail on leaders back after working to cross, even run to bend, there turning but didn't put up at 250 M, one paced late.
Taken back from widest alley, raced at rear, best part of 9Ls down throughout, saved ground but still well back turning, moderate finish beating tired runners.
Taken back from a wider alley, raced 2 to 3 wide at rear 9Ls back, near to turn, only passed tired runners in stretch.
Even getaway, planted 3 wide 6Ls off speed just off midfield, had cover to bend, struggling turning in and faded out tamely.
No speed and allowed to fade back from a tricky alley, 3 wide 8Ls back, had cover to bend, found little at business end.
Awkward away, ended up in midfield, 4Ls back, carried 3 wide on bend, ridden along turning but soon under pressure and faded out.

Soon ridden to take up running setting a steady pace, made all to win decisively under pressure. (Questioned for improved performance.)
Chased behind leader in a prominent spot on rails throughout, failed to quicken to threaten in straight.
Squeezed at start, travelled mainly in rear of midfield to straight, fought on steadily to reach distant 3rd inside 200 M but never threatening.
Settled in last few, made moderate late headway past well beaten horses in the run home.
Broke well, remained prominent in 3rd or 4th about 3Ls most of way to straight, came under pressure around final bend, gradually weakened after straightening.
Raced wide in midfield after beginning from the widest barrier, remained similar throughout, kept on same pace under pressure.
Travelled just better than midfield in 5th on rails, faded gradually after straightening.
Travelled in rear of field most of way to straight, persevered down final stretch to go past well beaten horses.

Began fairly, made steady progress around home bend the first time to join leader briefly approaching stables bend, held one-out-one-back position on far side but dropped away quickly after straightening. (Tactic questioned.)
Settled mainly in midfield to straight, weakened under pressure after straightening.
Always well behind and never seen with a chance.
Towards rear, tired noticeably after straightening.
Parked in midfield the fence. Kept to the inside in the home straight and ran on nicely to overhaul the opposition.
Enjoyed an uncontested lead at even sections for most of the trip. Kicked well clear early in the home straight but was reeled in over the latter stages.
Camped 1 out 1 back. Came up somewhat flat over the concluding stages.
Box seated. Had every chance but failed to show any dash in the run home.
Raced towards the rear, 2-wide with cover. Worked home fairly.
Camped in second position, 2-wide. Was given every chance but faded over the final 100 M.
Didn't enjoy the best of trips towards the rear of the field whilst dodging a riderless horse. Worked to the line evenly.
Raced worse than midfield, 2-wide with cover. Came wide on the home turn, whacked away at the same speed over the final furlong.
Settled at the rear of the field along the paint. Only plodded to the finishing line.
Raced midfield, 2 deep with cover. Struggled in the final stretch.
From a wide gate was taken across behind runners to settle near last. Coursed wide in the early and middle stages, shifted in to travel 2-wide near the 600 M. Never likely.

Placing: UR
Comment: Knuckled over at the start and dislodged rider.
2-wide towards rear to home turn. Gradually shifted out and was 6Ls down passing 400 M. Finished off strongly wide. Just made it.
Travelled 3-wide and without cover ahead of midfield to home straight. Bumped and became unbalanced passing 200 M. Resumed well and rallied on. Narrowly beaten at post.
Soon in leading section. Parked 2-wide behind leader from 1200 M. Challenged lead passing 400 M and hit front at 200 M. Looked likely to score but caught by the front pair final stride.
Well away. Raced handily one-off behind leaders from stable bend. Had every chance in the straight but lacked the finishing touch of the front trio close to home.

Taken 2-wide towards rear from high draw. Checked and shifted 3-wide passing 1100 M. Improved to midfield approaching the Rock. Swung 4-wide and was 4Ls off at bend. Kept making headway in the straight.
Led 2-wide early. Took fence 1200 M out. Overtaken by the principals final 300 M but kept on to the line.
Away in line. Slotted 2-wide at midfield passing winning post first time. Kicked with the principals top of home straight. Blocked from 200 M to 50 M. Not fully tested.
Prominent spot to home turn. Took some time to shift out for clear run top of home straight. Awkwardly placed final 100 M. Not beaten far.
Good jump and soon settled on fence at midfield. Same position turning in. One-paced to conclude.

Taken to rear on fence from wide barrier. Took inside run and was 7Ls away rounding home turn. Kept progressing home straight until steadied when disappointed for running final 50 M. Not ridden out fully.
Behind midfield on fence. Peeled out for clear run final stretch. Ran on steadily to finish.
2-wide behind midfield early. Failed to quicken when asked home turn. Beaten early home straight.
Fair break, lacked early speed, back to second last rail, urged, swung wide to challenge turn, finished fast, led last 50 M.
Broke well, held rail position in third, rail run straight, narrow lead 50 M out, caught soon after.
Broke well, ridden hard out wide to reach second one off, led 200 M out, ran on but caught last 50 M.
Broke well, settled sixth on rail, bustled turn, ran on looking very strong until ran out of racing room 150 M out, unlucky.
Fair break, lacked early pace, held up third last one off, bustled far side, improved turn, wide bid, kept on.
Fair break, ridden early, fifth one off, ridden turn, wide bid, kept on.
Well away, led and crossed, led until 300 M out, driven, weakened.
Fair break out wide, ridden but unable to lead and caught three wide, joined leaders under driving straight, weakened late.
Sluggish start, ridden early but last one off, urged throughout, no progress.
Broke fast, led, headed and settled third, took gap to lead again early straight, ran on strongly.
Fast break out wide, ridden up to lead, crossed, caught by winner early straight, kept on.
Fair break but lacked early pace, settled fifth last rail, ridden between horses to try and challenge, kept on well.
Fair break, settled fifth on rail, inside bid straight, kept on but no kick.
Fair break, ridden but just lacked pace to lead, urged throughout, kept on but never quite on terms.
Fair break but not pace to lead and caught wide, up to second into straight, ridden, no further progress.
Fair break, ridden early but lacked pace, back to third last, ridden and kept on straight but never pace to challenge.
Sluggish and squeezed back early, second last one off, ridden and ran on but unable to challenge, ran out of racing room late.
Fair break, ridden out wide but not pace to lead, settled fifth one off, wide bid, weakened late.
Taken back from wide draw, held up last, rail bid, no significant progress.
Broke well but head in air and reined back, midfield one off, ridden turn, aimed wide but no progress under driving.
Fair break, lacked early pace and wide, back to fourth last one off, ridden turn, found nothing, eased when well beaten.
Pushed early to keep up with the field at rear, 9Ls off the leader 2 to 3-wide, harmed by the slow pace, dashed strongly 300 M to win by a neck.
Box seat, enjoyed the slow sectionals, led 300 M, hung on until 100 M overhauled, ran on for 2nd.
Eased to sit in midfield, 5Ls off the leader, trapped 3-wide throughout, made early move 700 M as the pace slackened, ran on strongly until 100 M, flattened, hung on for 3rd.
Behind midfield, 7Ls off the leader along the fence, harmed by the slow pace, blocked 4-2, dashed well when clear, just missed a place.
At back, 8Ls off the leader 2-wide, harmed by the slow pace, held up 400 M, dashed well when clear.
Pushed forward to cross, led by 3-1/2Ls at slow sectionals, ran on until 250 M flattened.
Eased back and took rail, 8Ls off the leader, little dash 200 M despite not suited by the slow pace.
In front of midfield along the fence, not suited by the slow tempo, no progress.
Behind midfield, 7-1/2Ls off the leader 2-wide, harmed by the slow pace, lack room 300 M, little dash when clear, eased out of race 100 M.
Pushed early but didn't muster, trapped 3-wide throughout at rear, not suited by the slow pace, no dash.
Midfield, 6Ls off the leader 2 to 3-wide, harmed by the slow pace, weakened 300 M.
Pushed to take up a prominent spot 2 to 3-wide, benefited by the slow tempo, dropped off badly 400 M.
Prominently placed in a one-off spot 3Ls off the speed, clicked into gear when placed under pressure at 300 M, hit the front at 100 M, kept on strongly to score.
Jumped fast, urged along to lead and found the fence before the first turn, suited by the soft tempo, quickened well when asked at 300 M, kept on soundly for 2nd.
Broke well, tracked the leader in the one-out-one-back spot, responded well when asked for efforts at the top of home straight, kept on soundly for 3rd.

Settled cozily in one-off spot in midfield, unbalanced at 1400 M, urged along turning for home, finished off fairly well in the home straight, never really threatened the top three. (Lost left front plate.)
Settled 3Ls off the pace on rails, blundered at 1400 M, bump the rail at 600 M, made gradual ground final 300 M under pressure, rather one-paced.
Broke well, prominently placed in the box-seat just behind the leader, on heels at 1400 M, had every chance in the home straight, only one-paced when asked.
Lacked early speed despite being pushed along, travelled 5Ls off the speed on in midfield, niggled along at home turn, failed to quicken.
Slow away, settled 8Ls off the pace in rear, not suited by the soft tempo, failed to make up any ground in the home straight.
Taken back from gate 8 and travelled one from the rear, on heels at 600 M, 5Ls behind the leader at home turn, failed to make any progress.
Taken across behind runners and travelled 7Ls off the pace, pulled halfway when being restrained, on heels at 600 M, failed to make any progress, tailed out. (Lame right fore.)
Began with more purpose, held a prominent role on leaders back, travelled well to bend, got inside run and dashed through, drew away late to score easily.
Restrained to tail. Best part of 8Ls away at rear, improved on rails on circle, had plenty to do still well back turning in, got gaps and made good progress to snatch 2nd.
Away well, angled into an ideal spot l out 1 back, had good trip to bend, kept digging straight but didn't have extra inside 150 M. (Jockey reminded to ride out.)
Taken back from a wide alley, next to last 7Ls away, improved wide rounding bend, finished nicely from difficult spot to snatch 4th.
Away OK, 2-wide 5Ls back for-first part, improved 3-wide with trail at 700 M, care widest into straight, kept going to just miss frame.
Not much speed, settled behind midfield on the rails, 5Ls or so away in mid section, kept to inside and closed gradually to be nearest on line.
Drifted back from a wider gate, further back than usual 6Ls away in running line, still job to do rounding bend, made some late progress without threatening.
Assumed a midfield spot, 3 to 4Ls back and running line throughout, no excuses to turn, came wider but proved 1 paced over concluding stages.
Positive from outset, took up running and set even tempo, 1L clear at 400 M, headed soon after turning in, faded out late.
Began well used a bit to cross outside leader, had a fair run throughout, niggled along bend, didn't see out journey and gradually faded.
Even getaway, ended up 3 to 4Ls back on rails plenty of favours in run, kept on at same speed but tightened at 100 M and dropped off despite not really threatening.
Began in line, posted 3 deep without cover, 2 to 3Ls back work throughout, began to lose touch turning and was eased down in straight.

Moderate start, gradually picked up under pressure to travel 2-wide in 4th just over 2Ls off the speed, came to challenge after straightening and hit front under pressure inside 200 M.
Settled one-back on rails, about 2Ls off the speed around the bend, shifted out for a clear run after straightening, ran on to be nearest at finish.
Settled at the back, snuck up down inside of straight to be nearest at finish.
Settled just better than midfield, fought on hard under pressure without threatening.
In last few when checked and shuffled further back early stages, remained well behind into straight, produced nice impression down centre of track late though never threatening.
Settled in midfield on rails, came under pressure to challenge after straightening but could only produce moderate headway.
Began from a wide barrier with others, soon positioned outside leader and remained similar into straight, failed to sustain effort inside final 200 M.
Restrained in midfield and wide without cover after beginning from the widest barrier, similar turning into straight, ran home one-paced.
Mainly in midfield, ran home one-paced under pressure.
Towards the rear, did not have the clearest of runs early in straight until the 200 M mark, failed to make any impression afterwards.
Began with others, soon settled in rear of midfield, yielded ground from rounding home bend.
Broke well to lead, held running to 200 M when dropped away quickly under pressure.
Slightly slow out, gradually picked up to just worse than midfield, made no further impression in the run home.
Midfield early stages, soon dropped to last few.
Raced keenly after handing up the lead passing the 900m. Thereafter shifted out into the 1 off line and raced in 2nd position. Was never headed after the 250m.
Camped midfield on the rails. Kept to the inside in the home straight, gained a split after the 100m, and lengthened nicely to secure second.
Raced keenly in the early stages, travelling 3 back the fence, had cover. Peeled out near the 300m and battled on gamely to the wire.
Coursed 3 wide with cover in a midfield position. Struck some interference near the 800m, but rallied nicely to finish in the frame.
Slow to begin, settling in last position. Rattled home strongly out wide in the final stretch.
Rated behind midfield, 1 off with cover. Copped a bit of crowding midrace, but recovered well to close off soundly.
Camped 1 out 1 back. Weakened over the concluding stages after having every chance.
Was posted 3 wide without cover behind the speed. Never likely.
Sent forward and crossed to lead on the fence near the 800m. Faded over the final 200m.
Missed the start settling with the backmakers along the paint. Made some ground along the inside but was flat over the last 100m.
Positioned worse than midfield, 3 wide with cover. Finished off somewhat one paced.
Travelled midfield 2 wide with cover. Raced greenly for the better part of the trip and came up empty after the furlong.
Was taken back from the outside barrier and settled with the tail enders, 2-3 wide with cover. Failed to close off. (See incident report.)
Travelled in front of midfield early, but propped badly near the 800m, and was never in contention thereafter. Eased out of the race soon after. (To trial.) (See incident report.)

Pressed early. Settled ahead of midfield near the fence passing 1300M. Raced behind leaders home turn. Held up top of home straight. Kicked strongly once into clear 200M and fought all the way to the line. Just made.
Dropped to rear from widest draw. Niggled from 1200M to stay in touch. Got closer home turn and was 6Ls down turning in. Swung widest passing 400M and rallied on. Narrowly beaten at post.
Ridden early from high draw to obtain forward spot. Shared lead one-off the fence from 1100M. Hit front 300M but couldn't repel the front pair closing stages. All out to hold 3rd.

Towards rear on fence. Took inside run and was 4Ls down rounding home turn. Kept on top of home straight and looked dangerous briefly passing 200M but failed to sustain effort. Battled for 3rd close home. Just denied.
2-wide behind midfield. Checked and shifted 3-wide at 1000M. 5Ls adrift turning into home. Covered decent ground in the straight but no hope to make frame.
Drawn high and was taken towards rear on fence to home straight. Held up top of home straight. Closed off well once into clear final furlong.
Urged early along the fence to assert a forward position. Shared lead from 1100M. Still there top of home straight but couldn't turn up a notch. Steadied final 100M.
Away in line but caught wide. Eased gradually towards rear from 1300M. Improved outside passing 600M and was 4Ls off on straightening. Made up some ground but no further headway final furlong.

Began fairly. Failed to take up forward spot despite effort of rider. Sat 2-wide at midfield from 1400M. Dropped towards rear when blocked rounding home turn. Steadied at 300M and remained one-paced once resumed.
Hard ridden early in the leading section but trapped wide. Gradually eased to slot 2-wide ahead of midfield 1200M out. Well positioned to strike in the straight but no extra gear.
Driven to go forward early but trapped 3-wide without cover behind leaders to home straight. Couldn't pick up passing 400M and faded final furlong.
On fence at midfield to home straight. Found nothing when asked.
2-wide behind leaders to home straight. Swamped final 300M. Struggled home.
3-wide at midfield to home straight. Weakened rapidly top of home straight. Finished tailed out.
Broke well, joined leaders but caught three wide no cover, up to second one off, kept on very well straight to wear down leader then hold on.
Fair break, settled midfield one off, short of room early straight, finished strongly when clear, just failed.
Well away, ridden to lead and crossed, kept on well until close home, just worn down.
Fair break, taken back to second last one off, improved quickly between horses straight, not quite able to reach leaders.
Fair break, taken back to mid-rear, check far side, not settling, wide bid straight, ran on strongly late.
Fair break but caught three wide, midfield three off, mid-track bid, no extra late.
Sluggish start, lost length, up on rail to midfield not settling, rail bid, kept on, not pace to challenge.
Fair break but caught three wide no cover, mid-track bid straight, reached narrow third, weakened late.
Taken back from wide draw, settled rear, ridden early straight, some progress but unable to challenge.
Fair break, up to fourth one off, third early straight, ridden, weakened.
Fair break, ridden wide to share lead one off, settled third on rail, ridden, weakened.
Sluggish start, up to midfield one off, checked far side, ridden mid-track, no progress.
Good break, ridden early to take fifth on rail, unable hold place early straight, weakened under pressure.
Slow away, held up second last, ridden before turn, found nothing, faded quickly.
Broke well, soon ran up to lead 1L on rail, quickened well when asked for efforts 250 M out, kept on soundly, just withheld furious challengers.
Eased back from gate 8, travelled 5Ls off the speed, kicked when obtained clear run 300 M out, finished off strongly for 2nd, just late.
Prominently placed in the box-seat just behind the leader, blocked early in the home straight, ran on strongly when clear 200 M out, narrowly beaten by the top two.
Jumped fast, soon taken to a 3-wide spot in midfield, niggled along halfway, crowded at 600 M, responded well when asked for efforts 350 M out, finished off soundly, just missed a place.
Niggled along to hold a one-off spot 1L off the pace, kept on satisfactorily when asked early in the home straight, could not find extra final 100 M.
Crowded at start, lacked early speed as usual and travelled 6Ls off the speed, only gave limited response when placed under pressure in the home straight, rather one-paced.
Slow to begin, urged along in the early stages, caught 3-wide in the mid-division, only one-paced when placed under pressure in the home straight, never really troubled the principals.
Taken to the rear from gate 12, made some late ground when clear 250 M, only passed a few tired rivals.
Broke well, urged along to hold a one-off spot in midfield, only one-paced when asked at the top of home straight, failed to keep on final 200 M, soon faded.
Taken back from gate 11, travelled rearward throughout the trip, never competitive.
Out in line but soon taken rearward, failed to make up any ground in the home straight.
Fair jump, urged along to share the lead on 2-deep, failed to keep on when placed under pressure early in the home straight, gave ground.
Eased to sit just off the leaders on middle part of track, stormed home 200M to win by a short head.
Shared lead on middle part of track, hung in steadily from 500M, dominated 300M, hung on strongly until last few strides, just beaten by a short head.
Prominent, 1.5Ls off the good pace on slower inside part of track, closed the race off strongly 300M, just beaten by a narrow margin in 3rd.
Shared lead easily on slower inside part of track, ran on well to the line but missed a place.
Eased to sit in front of midfield, 2Ls off the good pace on slower inside part of track, just held ground, on heels 50M.
Very slow away, 2Ls off the good pace on middle part of track, just held ground in final stages.
Awkward away, 4Ls off the good pace on slower inside part of track, made some ground 300M.
Behind midfield, 4Ls off the good pace on middle part of track, made minor ground 200M.
Eased to sit just off the leaders on middle part of track, emptied 200M.
Eased back, 4Ls off the good pace on slower inside part track, ran on ok in final stages.
Bumped start, at rear, 6Ls off the good pace on outside part track, no dash.
Midfield on middle part of track, 3Ls off good pace, soon weakened 400M.
Bumped start and checked, at rear, never a factor.
Shared lead at good pace on outside fence, dropped off rapidly 400M.
Sweated up beforehand, taken back to settle three wide second last, challenged mid-track straight, led 200m out, drew clear.
Broke well, ridden to early lead, headed far side, led again early straight, kept on well.
Well away, settled fourth on rail, ridden but no progress early straight, stayed on well late.
Well away, taken back to settle one off fourth last, improved three wide turn, up to close third 150m out, weakened slightly late.
Fair break, settled fifth one off, lost couple of places far side, went for rail run straight but short of room and checked late.
Fair break, up to second one off first bend, led back straight, crossed, narrow lead into straight, headed, weakened gradually.
Fair break, aimed for lead but caught three wide, settled third one off, fifth into straight, ridden, no progress.
Fairbreak, taken back to fifth last rail, third last into straight, ridden, kept on one pace.
Slow away, lost length, held up last one off, ridden and kept on straight, but never near leaders.
Very slowly away, left three lengths, taken to rail sharing last, last into straight, driven, no impression.
Fair break but caught wide, raced midfield three wide no cover, up to third leaving back, ridden, weakening quickly when checked 300m out.
Raced in a 2-wide position behind midfield, taken to 3-wide passing 800M and gradually moved into contention, made rapid headway in straight to hit the lead 150M out and continued gamely late stages.
Towards the rear and unhurried along the inside, angled out passing 400M to improve, closed off the race well but couldn't quite get to the winner.
Began awkwardly, raced keenly without cover in a 3-wide position just off the pace, briefly led mid straight but couldn't stay with the first two through the final 150M.
Raced near last about 6Ls off the pace, finished off willingly inside 300M to take 4th close home.
Along the fence and raced within striking distance throughout, loomed 300M but couldn't sustain run over the final 150M.
Went forward to press leader, kept on to 150M, flattened out final stages. (Jockey reported his saddle shifted in early part of the straight.)
Towards the rear 2-wide about 6Ls off the pace, swung to the outside of home straight to commence his run, kept on one-paced.
Patiently held up on the outside of the last pair, had to switch widest in the straight for a run, passed some tiring rival while making no impression on the leaders.
Raced very keenly in midfield and failed to mount a serious challenge turning into the straight.
Checked at the start, restrained to last and taken across to the fence, nudged along 600M out but could only make very limited progress in the straight.
Positioned 3-wide in midfield but came up empty leaving the home turn, never a factor.
Taken to the rail soon after the start, never better than midfield, badly outpaced passing 250M and was well beaten.
Ordinary jump, soon sped to the lead and took them along at a decent pace, headed near 250M and weakened rapidly in late stages.
2-wide in the group chasing the pace, not quickened in straight, out of contention 200M and eased.
Out in line, pushed along to hold a one-off spot in midfield, swung widest for home, kicked strongly when asked 300 M out, hit the front at 50 M, kept on, just prevailed.
Out with others, lacked early speed despite being urged along, travelled 3-4Ls off the pace, on heels at 700 M, finished off strongly when asked 300 M out, just late.
Jumped well but soon taken to midfield to obtain cover, caught 3-wide throughout the trip, ran on strongly when asked for efforts 350 M out, narrowly beaten by the top two.
Settled 2Ls off the speed on rail, on heels at 700 M and 100 M, hung out in home straight, ran on well when asked final 300 M, but lacked a decisive kick to challenge the top three.
Jumped fastest, caught 3-wide just off the pace, kept on well and looked possible for a place, but could not offer extra final 100 M.
Easily ran up to share the lead on rail, kept on satisfactorily until passed at 200 M, soon flattened.
Prominently placed just behind the pace, only one-paced when asked for efforts early in the home straight, soon faded.
Started awkwardly, travelled 4Ls off the pace, on heels at 700 M, hung out, failed to make up any ground in the home straight. (Continuous dorsal displacement of the soft palate.)
Broke well, urged along to take the box-seat, kept on until got tired near the 200 M pole.
Jumped fairly, caught wide with no cover throughout the trip, hung out and drifted back gradually at the home turn, made no progress in the straight.
Jumped fairly and soon taken towards the rear, only made very limited progress in the home straight, never in contention.
Out in line, soon ran up to share the lead on 2-deep, failed to keep on at the top of home straight, soon weakened sharply, finished tailed out.
Faded back to settle 5 to 6Ls away on rails, came 2 wide on circle, shifted into clear not long after 400 M, stormed down middle to run away for an easy win.
Awkward jump, regathered to assume 1 out 1 back role, 2Ls back to bend, loomed strongly at 300 M and led briefly, found winner too classy but finished well clear of 3rd.
Even getaway, took good spot 2 to 3Ls behind pace group, tracked nicely to bend, no match for first two but stayed on nicely all the same.
Positioned from gates to assume a role outside the leader, travelled well to bend, chased lead and took over at 300 M, couldn't find extra however hung on to make frame.
Broke well, in prominent spot first behind leader on rails throughout, right there to bend, lacked required dash and just stayed on at 1 speed final furlong.
Went back from tricky gate, behind midfield 8Ls down in running line, job to do turning, closed best of rest to be nearest on line.
Planted 3 wide from an outside gate, 3Ls or so away without cover throughout, tough run impacted and struggled from bend.
Pressed on to take up usual spot in front, kept even speed throughout, led them to bend, collared inside 300 M and folded tamely.
Began in line, faded back to behind midfield from a wide gate, caught 3 and 4 wide on circle, niggled approaching turning, didn't respond after hard run.
Standard jump, ended up 3 wide 7 to 8Ls back, had cover in mid-section, steadied briefly at 400 M but unable to make an impact in straight.
Drifted back from awkward draw, 3 wide at rear 9Ls from leaders, overraced in mid-section, didn't produce usual finish in straight. (Muco.)
Drifted back to last in running line 9Ls or so away, set big task still last leaving bend, produced a lack lustre response final 400 M.
Lost ground at start, rear division on rails 8 to 9Ls back, had most in front on bend, disappointing effort in straight.
Positioned well 3 to 4Ls back on rails, used nothing in run, stopped soon after straightening and beaten a long way.

Began with others, settled in forward of midfield on rails, lost position when hampered far side, recovered to midfield into straight, fought on gamely to just get up on line.
Prominently early, shuffled back to midfield rounding stables bend, commenced move entering straight, fought on under pressure to hit front narrowly 200 M out only to be pipped at post.
Began with others, settled one-back in 3rd on rails, saved ground turning in, failed to quicken to draw level throughout straight.
Squeezed at start and soon dropped to tail-end, trailed the field into straight, finished off race well down centre of track, did best work late.
Settled just worse than midfield, shifted wide into straight, ran on steadily to be nearest at finish.
Raced wide without cover in midfield behind midfield, took closer order up the Rock, wide in a prominent spot entering straight, ran home one-paced under pressure.
Travelled one-out-one-back in 2nd, commenced move to join leader around home bend hitting front into straight, tired noticeably inside final 200 M.
Hampered at start, travelled in last few throughout, saved ground on rails turning in, kept on same pace in the run home.
Always well behind, made no impression in the run home.
Travelled in mid-division to halfway before dropping behind midfield, made no impression in straight.
Soon took up running and led until folded up quickly after straightening. (Sustained tendon injury.)
Slightly slow out, ridden along to muster early speed, gave ground from rounding home bend.
Went forward and crossed to race along the fence passing the 700 M, got a breather soon after and had enough in reserve to post its maiden victory.
Went back from the outside alley settling in last position along the paint. Commenced to peel out after the 600 M, came widest in the run home and finished off strongly.
Not the best away, settling midfield the fence. Got all the favors along the inside, lengthened soundly.
Camped midfield, 2-wide with cover. Peeled out early in the straight and closed off well to finish in the frame.
Led early before handing up to track the leader after the 700 M. Had no excuses despite drifting out over about the last 100 M.
Parked 1 out 1 back by the 700 M. Had every chance but came up well short at the business end.
Travelled at the rear of the field, 1 off with cover. Worked to the line evenly.
Managed to slot in and travel in 2nd position, 1 off after the 700 M. Went to the post one paced.
Settled worse than midfield from a wide gate, 3 deep with cover. Failed to show any dash in the final stretch.
Ridden along but coursed wide and without cover for most of the journey, 3-4 deep, rolling forward to race on the speed after the 600 M. Never a factor.
Pushed to race prominently but copped some tightening near the 1000 M and was never really in the hunt thereafter, travelling 3-wide, had cover on the final circle.
Slow to begin settling with the backmakers, 2-wide with cover. Struggled in the home straight.
Last out. At rear on rail to home straight. Kept making up ground passing 300 M but not the clearest passage. Took split final 50 M, through it, just made it on line.
Began well. Gradually moved to rail and settled ahead of midfield. Every chance in the straight. Shifted out and bumped another runner near the post. Narrowly beaten.
Hard ridden early. Slotted 2-wide ahead of midfield approaching home turn. Rallied on with the front pair home straight. Snatched 3rd on line.
Quickly into stride from widest barrier. Found the fence on home turn. Hung on well home straight and looked set for victory. Caught by the front trio final strides.
Well enough away. Elected to sit 2-wide behind midfield early. Hard ridden passing 400 M. Finished off well down the centre of the track.
Good jump and tracked leader on fence. Pressed turning into home straight. One-paced to conclude.
Crowded at start. Parked 2-wide at midfield approaching the Rock. Urged along to home straight. Made up decent ground thereafter.
Bumped and was crowded at start. Soon resumed to race 2-wide behind leader. Kept on in the straight until no extra to stay in battle final 150 M.
Began awkwardly. Driven early but trapped wide and without cover near the pace. Dropped to midfield at bend. No further headway.
Slowly away. Pressured along the fence and raced behind midfield. Found nothing final stretch.
Began awkwardly. Towards rear to home straight. No impression.
3-wide behind midfield to home turn. Dropped out top of home straight. Never a factor.
Bumped start, soon settled on rail in the mid-division, responded well when asked or efforts 400 M out, finished off soundly and hit the front at 200 M, just prevailed.
Widely drawn, taken back towards the rear, on heels at 1300 M, swung widest for home, finished off strongly down centre of the home straight, just late.
Eased behind horses and travelled 5Ls off the speed, niggled along and swung wide at home turn, ran on soundly final 300 M under maximum pressure, narrowly beaten by the top two.
Broke well from gate 10, travelled 3-wide with cover just off the pace, bumped at 1400 M, finished off well under maximum pressure final 300 M, just missed a place.
Settled cozily in the box-seat just behind the leaders, obtained clear run and looked possible to win early in the home straight, lacked a decisive kick final 100 M, one-paced.
Taken rearward from gate 8, saved ground along the inner at home turn, finished off satisfactorily final 250 M.
Started awkwardly, driven to lead and found the fence at 1400 M, kept on fairly early in the home straight, caught at 150 M, flattened.
Out in line, settled 3-wide 5Ls off the pace, niggled along rounding the final bend, only one-paced in the home straight.
Jumped fast, urged along to take the one-out-one-back spot, got tired early in the home straight, soon faded.
Niggled along to hold a one-off spot in midfield, bumped at 1400 M, drifted back gradually from 700 M, failed to make up any ground in the home straight.
Jumped only fairly, niggled along to hold a 2-wide spot just behind the pace, failed to keep on at home turn, gave ground.
Jumped only fairly, caught wide with no cover 1L off the pace, struggled at home turn, weakened sharply at 300 M, finished tailed out.
Settled cozily on rail 6Ls off the pace, checked at 1100 M, shifted wide turning for home, finished off soundly down centre of the home straight final 300 M, just in time.
Prominently placed within striking distance from the leader, responded well when asked at 400 M, ran on soundly, just caught by the winner in the final stride.
Bumped at start, pushed forward to hold a one-off spot just off the speed, suited by the soft tempo, kept on well under pressure in the home straight, narrowly beaten by the top two.
Taken back from gate 11, 6Ls off the lead at home turn, ran on strongly along the inner part of the home straight, blocked at 100 M.
Broke well, urged along to lead and found the fence at 1100 M, suited by the slow tempo, kept on satisfactorily early in the home straight, caught at 100 M, one-paced.
Settled cozily on rail in the mid-division, took time to pick up early in the home straight, finished off fairly well final 200 M.
Settled three from the rear on rail, not suited by the soft tempo, swung widest for home, only one-paced when asked for efforts.
Taken back from the widest alley, travelled rearward in the early and middle stages, made some late progress in the home straight, only passed a few tired runners.
Urged along to take the box-seat, only one-paced when asked in the home straight, crowded final 50 M.
Broke well, settled one-off in the mid-division, moved closer at home turn, held ground until flattened 100 M out.
Urged along early and travelled 3Ls off the pace on rail, held ground until flattened at 200 M, soon dropped out.
Travelled 6Ls off the pace on 2-deep, outpaced at home turn, finished tailed out.
Eased to rear, 6Ls off the leader 2-wide, benefited by the fast tempo, stormed home strongly 200 M to win.
Bumped start, at back, 5-1/2Ls off the leaders 2 to 3-wide, favoured by the fast pace, progressed steadily in straight for 2nd.
Eased to sit in front of midfield, 3Ls off the leader on the rails, benefited by the fast pace, made steady ground 300 M to take 3rd. (Mucopus.)
Box seat, not suited by the fast tempo, ran on strongly to the line, hung in abruptly 150 M whilst reaching its max.
Jumped very well, eased to sit in midfield, 4-1/2Ls off the leader 2 to 3-wide, favoured by the fast pace, progressed steadily 300 M, once threatened, however run ended 50 M.
At back, 5-1/2Ls off the leader on the fence, benefited by the fast pace and the rail run, made ground 300 M, run ended 50 M.
Eased to sit behind midfield, 4Ls off the leader, trapped 3 to 4-wide throughout, suited by the fast pace but lost too much ground on bend, still ran on well to the line.
Took rail and led by 1-1/2Ls at fast sectionals, hung on until 200 M weakened.
At rear, 7Ls off the leader 2 to 3-wide, favoured by the fast tempo, checked 400 M, no progress.
Eased to sit in front of midfield, 2-1/2Ls off the fast pace, trapped 3-wide throughout and lost too much ground, emptied 250 M.
Pushed forward, 3Ls behind the fast pace 2 to 3-wide, faded 400 M.
Just off the leader 2-wide, not suited by the fast pace, dropped off badly 600 M.
Checked after start, taken back and travelled 5Ls off the speed, kicked strongly when asked for efforts 250 M out, hit the front in the last few strides, won with some in hand.
Jumped only fairly but soon ran up to share the lead, responded well when asked at the top of home straight, kept on soundly, caught by the winner in the final few strides.
Broke well, urged along to hold a 3-wide spot 2-3Ls off the speed, finished off well under maximum pressure final 300 M, took a place in the final stride.
Jumped well and urged along early, ended up settling one-off in midfield, swung wide for home, ran on well under pressure final 250 M, just late for a place.
Jumped fast, niggled along to share the lead on rail, settled in the box-seat rounding the bend, kept on satisfactorily in the straight, looked possible for a place, just missed out.
Broke well, prominently placed just behind the pace group on rail, kept on fairly in the home straight, rather one-paced.
Taken back from gate 12 and travelled 5Ls off the pace on rail, improved gradually along the inner part of the home straight, on heels at 50 M, not fully tested.
Out with others, pushed forward to share the lead on 3-wide, kept on fairly early in the home straight, passed at 150 M, could not find extra.
Checked after start, eased towards the rear, failed to make any ground in the home straight.
Jumped fast but caught wide early, gradually drifted back to midfield, hung out at home turn, gave no response when asked for efforts in the home straight.
Urged along to hold a fence position in midfield, struggled rounding the bend, got tired at the top of home straight, soon dropped out.
Out with others, lacked early speed despite being urged along, 8Ls off the lead turning for home, made no progress.
Got away well and was always in touch with leader, responded well in straight and wrapped up late to share the spoils on the line.

Away in good order and quickly established a lead under some light urging, dictated the race with a steady pace, kept on well in straight, under strong challenge final 100 M but rallied on to salvage a dead-heat.
Overcame the wide draw and managed to settle in a good position with cover not far away from leaders, looked a possible winner 200 M out, fought on gamely and only gave in near finish.
Assumed a forward position after a good start, tracked leader one out one back, loomed a threat 300 M out, pushed the winner all the way to the line and drew clear from the remainder.
Taken back and moved across to find the rail after the start, took closer order nearing the home turn, stayed on without reaching the top 4 which drew well clear.
Driven to a forward position just behind leader, had his chance but was outpaced inside 150 M.
Placed 2-wide in mid-division, driven 450 M out, kept on at the same pace and not reached leaders.

Taken to a midfield position and had a ground-saving trip along the fence, made a mild bid down the inside of track inside 350 M, had to shift ground passing 200 M but had little left to offer in the finish.
Not hurried in early stages, sat towards the rear 7Ls off the pace, ran on at the same pace inside 350 M, tightened for room 50 M out, eased.
Shifted out at the start and was then restrained to a rearward position, placed 2-wide and 6Ls off the pace down the back straight, kept on one paced to the line.
Ended up in last after a sluggish start and over 10Ls behind down the back straight, attempted a run down the inside final 250 M, steadied near 100 M and was then held up to the line.

Switched off to near last after the start and was well off the pace in 1st half of the race, made no progress in the straight. (Jockey reported his saddle shifted and couldn't ride out the horse properly in the finish.)

Began fairly, gradually took up running out wide down far side, crossed for rails coming out of back straight causing interferences, held a 1L break turning home, kicked nearly 2Ls clear over 200 M out, held on well to the line.
Close up early, soon settled wide in midfield without cover, circled field around the bend joining 3rd into straight, fought on steadily to reach 2nd 300 M out without threatening the winner.
Settled well behind, commenced move after straightening, fought on well under pressure to be nearest at finish.
Close up early, shuffled back to midfield approaching home bend, commenced run turning for home, veered inward behind runners early in straight, did best work late. (Tactic questioned.)
In touch early, gradually shuffled back to forward of midfield around the bend, met minor interference early in straight, fought on under pressure for remote 5th.
Settled behind midfield, ran home one-paced without quickening.
Well there and wide far side, gained 2nd into straight, gradually weakened under pressure after straightening.
Broke well from a wide barrier, soon taken well back, trailed the field into straight, ran past well beaten runners.
Began fairly, settled within 3Ls of pace around the bend, found nothing under pressure after straightening.
Well there on rails early after beginning from the one draw, checked of its own accord and lost position at about 750 M, midfield on rails around the bend, faded in straight.
Showed good early speed to share early pace, remained well there to 350 M before tiring noticeably.
Began with others but gradually taken back to race wide throughout and behind midfield, made no impression in straight. (Questioned for disappointing performance.)
Never seen with a chance. (Blood in trachea.)
Always in last few.
Enjoyed the run of the race on the back of the leader, box seating. Peeled out early in the straight and pinched victory on the line.
Cruised along to race in second position upsides the leader. Hit the front near the furlong but was nabbed late.

Did plenty of work early to go forward and cross to the fence in the lead after the 800m. was pressured for most of the trip by a runner to its outside, but had enough in reserve to finish in third position.
Copped some interference approaching the 800m and was shuffled back to travel towards the rear along the paint. Made nice ground in the home straight.
Had every chance settling 1 out 1 back. Was one paced in the final stretch.
Settled 3 back the fence. worked home soundly but was unable to obtain clear running over the concluding stages.
Restrained early to take up a midfield position, 2 wide with cover. Failed to show any dash in the home straight.
Travelled near the rear of the field along the rail with cover. Ran on fairly.
Blundered near the 900m and clipping heels settling with the backmakers 2-3 wide with cover. Never likely.
Couldn't match the early speed of the race, travelling midfield. Coursed 3 wide without cover and in the straight gave ground.

Broke evenly then was allowed to travel back in the event, had cover but was wide. Became unbalanced on a couple of occasions midrace and in the straight failed to show any dash. (Vet reported the horse was sore behind. To trial.)
Began very awkwardly losing ground. Raced keenly at the tail of the field and was checked to avoid heels near the 900m. Coursed wide thereafter and weakened in the straight.
Away in line. Gradually taken 3-wide towards rear. Commenced run wide and was 4Ls down rounding home turn. Kept on strongly in the straight to score with some comfort.
Fair start. Resumed to race 3-wide at midfield at 1400M. Made run 4-wide 600M out. Rallied on with the winner in the straight until 100M. Held 2nd fine.

Driven early to take forward spot. Eased to sit behind leader from 1200M. Ideal spot to strike in the straight. Ran on well until no extra to repel the front pair closing stages. Drew clear from the remainder.
Sat 3-wide behind midfield. Dropped 2-wide towards rear home turn. Shifted out for clear run home straight and made up decent ground to snatch a non-threatening 4th.
Taken to 3-wide at rear from widest barrier. Same position leaving the bend. Made some headway to nearly make frame but was left far back by the front trio.
Soon led on fence. Overtaken by the principals final 200M. Plugged on.
Ahead of midfield on fence to home straight. One-paced to conclude.
Taken 2-wide at rear from high draw. Had difficulty to find clear run in the straight until 300M. Minor improvement close home.
2-wide ahead of midfield. No impact in the straight.
Towards rear on fence to home straight. Never really progressed.
2-wide at midfield. Steadied twice passing 400M. No further impression.
Never far off the pace but failed to quicken when the race got serious passing 400M.
Pushed up to hold a fence position in midfield, shifted wider at home turn, quickened well when asked for efforts 400 M out, ran on and hit the front at 150 M, kept on soundly to score.
Jumped fast, soon ran up to lead 1L on rail, travelled well throughout the trip, responded well when asked for efforts 400 M, caught by the winner at 150 M, kept on well for 2nd.
Out with others, urged along and soon settled just off the pace, caught 3-wide with no cover throughout the trip, lacked a kick the challenge the top two but did keep on well for a place.
Taken back from gate 13 and travelled rearward, saved much ground along the inner at home turn, dashed well when clear 200 M out, closed off soundly, just late for a place.
Taken back from gate 14 and then urged to improve along the inner, ended up settling 6-7Ls off the speed, finished off satisfactorily when asked 350 M, but too late for a place.
Broke well, prominently placed 2Ls off the pace on rail, niggled along rounding the home turn, checked at 400 M, took long to pick up, ran on steadily final 150 M, rather one-paced.
Jumped only fairly, pushed up to occupy a fence position in midfield, made gradual ground when asked in the home straight, rather one-paced.
Broke well, pushed up to occupy the one-out-one-back spot, held ground until got tired near the 200 M pole.
Lacked early speed as usual and travelled at the rear, moved closer at the home turn, took very long to pick up, only made limited progress final 200 M, never threatened the principals.
Settled one-off in the mid-division, blundered badly near 1400 M, gave no response when asked for efforts at the top of the home straight, soon faded.
Started awkwardly and crowded, urged along early and travelled 7Ls off the pace, crowded again at 700 M, on heels at 600 M, niggled along at home turn, made no progress.
Jumped well, settled cozily in midfield, drifted back gradually at home turn, failed to make any ground in the home straight.
Taken back from gate 12, travelled 5Ls off the speed, made no progress in the home straight.
Prominently placed 2-3Ls off the speed, outpaced at the home turn, soon weakened, finished tailed out.
Urged along to share the lead on rail, quickened well when asked for efforts early in the straight, passed 150 M out, kept on soundly, fought back in the final stride.
Trapped 3-wide in the mid-division, bumped at 800 M, kicked strongly when asked 350 M out, took the lead at 200 M, hung in, kept on, caught in the final stride.
Jumped well, settled 2-3Ls off the speed on 3-deep, ran on soundly to contest the lead final 350 M, kept battling on, narrowly beaten by the top two.
Broke well from gate 12, soon taken towards the rear to obtain cover, responded well when asked for efforts in the home straight, covered substantial ground, still too late.
Lacked early speed despite being urged along, travelled 5Ls off the pace, on heels at 400 M, bumped at 200 M, closed off strongly when clear at 150 M, too late.
Lacked early speed as usual, travelled 3-wide near the rear, shifted wide for home, finished off well down centre of the home straight final 350 M without threatening the principals.
Settled one-off in the mid-division, travelled keenly when restrained in the early stages, crowded at 350 M, only gave limited response when placed under pressure.
Settled two from the rear on rail, took long to obtain clear run in the home straight, kicked strongly when clear 200 M out, too late.
Started awkwardly, urged along and soon settled in midfield on rails, blocked early in the home straight, only one-paced when clear at 200 M.
Jumped well, niggled along to hold a 3-wide spot just off the speed, flattened near 300 M, soon dropped out.
Prominently placed just behind the leader, held ground until flattened at 300 M, soon weakened.
Jumped well from gate 13, soon taken back towards the rear, swung widest for home, failed to make up any ground.
Settled 2-3L off the speed, crowded at 350 M, soon weakened.
Slow away, driven to catch up with the leader, travelled with no cover, failed to keep on 300 M out, bumped at 200 M, soon weakened.
Pushed to occupy a prominent spot on the fence, took advantage from the slow sectionals and the rail run, ran on strongly to win by a short head.
Pushed to keep up in front of midfield, 4Ls off the leader along the fence, not suited by the slow tempo, closed the race off well 300M, just beaten by a short head in 2nd.
Eased to sit in midfield along the fence, 6Ls off the leader, harmed by the slow pace, dashed strongly 300M to finish a very close 3rd.
Eased to sit in front of midfield, 4.5Ls off the leader 2 wide, not suited by the slow pace, raced flat until 200M commenced to dash well to the line.
Eased to sit in midfield, 6Ls off the leader 2 wide, not suited by the slow tempo, dashed well 200M.
Eased to rear, 9Ls off the leader, trapped 3-4 wide, demonstrated strong finishing efforts 250M despite not suited by the slow pace.
Eased back, 7.5Ls off the leader 2 wide, not suited by the slow tempo, little dash 200M.
Bumped start, at rear, 9.5Ls off the leader on the fence, harmed by the slow pace, little dash in straight.
Pushed forward, enjoyed the slow sections in box seat, ran on until 250M weakened.
Hard ridden early but not muster, trapped 3 wide in midfield, 4.5Ls off the leader, harmed by the slow pace, no progress.
Eased back, 7.5Ls off the leader on the rails, not suited by the slow tempo, no turn of foot.
Eased to sit in midfield early, however trapped very wide, then was allowed to stride into the lead, led 1.5Ls at slow sectionals, out of fuel 350M.
Eased at start, not suited by the slow pace, never competitive.
Eased to sit in midfield, trapped 3-4 wide, raced keenly, not suited by the slow tempo, dropped off badly 500M.
Easily ran up to lead, quickened up when asked for efforts 300 M out, kept on soundly to score, never challenged.
Settled 5Ls off the speed on rail, kicked when clear at 250 M, finished off soundly for 2nd.
Prominently placed within striking distance from the leader, obtained clear run at the top of home straight, kept on well enough for 3rd, but never really threatened the top two.
Settled in the one-out-one-back spot, kept on satisfactorily when asked for efforts at the top of home straight, lacked a kick to challenge the winner, missed out a place in the final stride.
Taken back form the widest alley, travelled 6Ls off the pace at the rear, on heels at 1400 M, blocked early in the home straight, finished off well when clear at 200 M.
Settled cozily in the box-seat, held ground until flattened 200 M out.
Broke well, soon eased towards the midfield to obtain cover, raced keenly when restrained, only one-paced when asked for efforts in the home straight, on heels at 200 M.
Given a waiting ride as usual, travelled 4Ls off the speed on rail, swung widest for home, only one-paced when placed under maximum pressure, on heels at 200 M.
Taken towards the rear after a fair jump, never better than midfield, only passed a few tired runners in the home straight.
Settled three from the rear, shifted wide for home, failed to make up any ground.
Settled one-off in the mid-division, only gave limited response when asked in the home straight, on heels 200 M out, soon weakened.
Slow away, urged along to catch up 2Ls off the pace, travelled with no cover, got tired early in the home straight, dropped out.

Never far off the pace, advanced steadily down the inside passing 400M, switched to top gear150M out, finished off the race willingly and hit the line together with One World which is 5lbs better off in weight..
Positioned 2-wide towards the rear, had about 6Ls to make up passing 400M, shifted to outside of track and finished off the race strongly and got up just in time for a dead heat with Rocket Man.

Held up in midfield 2-wide, made steady headway in straight, looked a possible winner 150M out, shifted out under pressure late on but did well to finish half a length behind two horses with International Group One form.
Sped to the lead and set a fast pace early stages, shook loose opening a clear advantage in upper straight, kept on well only to be headed 50M from home. Sound effort.

Restrained to a position behind midfield, turned 3-wide rounding the home turn, made steady progress to 100M then flattened out late. (Jockey reported his horse commenced to lay in over the concluding stage.
Dropped back from draw 12 and moved across to a 3-wide position near the rear, ran on evenly final 300M but never looked like getting involved.
Unhurried early and settled in at the rear 7Ls off the pace, badly unbalanced 700M out, swung widest into straight, gradually progressed without threatening.
Failed to muster speed despite being vigorously ridden in early stages, ended up near last 6-7Ls off the pace, made limited progress final 300M.
Raced in mid-division along the rail, lacked a strong closing bid, not reached leaders and never threatened.
Tracked the pace in 2nd, placed under pressure 400M out but couldn't get near to the leader, run ended 200M from home, weakened rapidly.
Stalked the pace 3-wide, had to be niggled along nearing home straight, weakened under pressure 300M out and was eased late.
Assumed a 3-wide position in midfield and raced without cover over the home turn, came up empty leaving the bend, soon out of contention.
Given a waiting ride and travelled 6Ls off the pace, kicked strongly when asked for efforts 350 M out, hit the front near 50 M, kept on soundly to score.
Lacked early speed and soon settled in mid-division on rails, swung widest for home, responded well when asked 400 M out, finished off strongly, just late.
Broke well, pushed up to share the lead on 2-deep, quickened well when asked for 250 M out, kept on satisfactorily, caught by the top two final 100 M.
Prominently placed 2-3Ls off the speed, improved along the inner part of the home straight, ran on steadily final 250 M under maximum pressure, never really troubled the top three.
Broke well from gate 11 but soon eased back to obtain cover, quickened well when clear at 400 M, failed to offer extra to challenge the principals final 100 M.
Niggled along to lead on rail, kept on satisfactorily early in the home straight, passed near the 200 M pole, one-paced.
Broke well, prominently placed in the box-seat, kept on satisfactorily when asked for efforts at the top of the home straight, but lacked a decisive kick to challenge the principals.
Caught wide with no cover in midfield, proved difficult to settle, on heels at 1000 M, only one-paced when placed under pressure in the home straight, no extra final 150 M.
Pushed up to occupy a one-off spot just off the pace, held ground until flattened 200 M out.
Settled 3Ls off the speed on rails, only give limited response when asked, got tired 250 M out.
Lacked early speed despite being urged along, never better than midfield.
Taken back from gate 13 and travelled 5Ls off the speed, only made little late progress final 150 M.
Taken back from gate 14, travelled rearward throughout the trip, never competitive.
Broke well, soon settled one-off in the mid-division, flattened and checked at 400 M, never recovered, finished tailed out.
Out with first few, pressed on when posted 3 wide but forced to race without cover, did work to bend, joined in at 300 M and stuck to task solidly pulling out everything to score.
Showed speed, sat outside leader, aided by steady tempo in mid-section, took over briefly at 250 M, in battle for most of straight and narrowly deprived late. Well clear of 3rd.
Standard jump, ridden hard to drive up and take lead, dropped speed in front, had terms to suit until bend, headed inside 300 M and couldn't find extra to stay with first two.
Drifted back soon after start, 3 to 4Ls back in running line, not helped by tempo, improved between horses turning, picked up well final 200 M to make frame. (See Racing Incidents regarding riding.)
Out in line, took a midfield spot 3 to 4Ls away, overraced and moved 3 wide in midfield, into clear from bend but found it hard to dash given way race was run. Just battled.
Restrained to rails, behind midfield but only 4Ls back when pace slackened, kept to rails turning, just held ground in straight.
Slow into stride, settled 5Ls away on rails, harmed by steady tempo throughout, still well back turning, made only minor headway final 300 M.
Restrained from a wide gate, ended up with last few 5Ls back in running line, came 3 wide on circle, lacked a response but never really suited by tempo throughout.
Out only fairly, pressed forward from an outside gate, 4 wide without cover in mid-section, up challenging leaders on bend, folded at 200 M when hard run took toll.
Showed speed, took a trail soon after, had OK run despite checked at 900 M, there to bend, didn't let down in straight and gradually lost touch.
Out on line, drifted back and then pushed wider when pace slackened, 4 wide with cover and overraced to bend, dropped right out in straight. (Roarer.)
Caught very wide in midfield early, hampered at 800 M, drifted back toward the rear at the bend, failed to make up any ground in the home straight.
