Settled in midfield, commenced move entering straight, barged his way out for a run 300 M out, quickened well to take command over 50 M out.

Began fairly from the widest barrier, driven along to take up running up Rock and eventually crossing to rails over 500 M out, still maintained 1L advantage into straight, just held 2nd for a quickly eroding margin.
Slowly away, remained in rear to straight, finished off race well down centre of track.
Broke well, with leaders early before settling just off the pace, back closer up on 3rd turning for home, could only keep on at the same pace under pressure without quickening in the final stretch.

Began fairly settling 3-wide in forward of midfield, took closer order up Rock to be wide in 2nd around the bend, joined by a line of horses upon straightening and swamped under pressure inside final 200 M.
Jumped moderately, soon picked up to forward of midfield out wide down far side, unbalanced for a stride after swinging for home, plugged on without quickening under hard driving.
Began well from a bad draw, gradually shifted across for rails run in a prominent spot, shuffled backward rounding home bend when crossed, swamped under pressure inside final 200 M.
Gradually settled just worse than midfield after beginning from a poor draw, received a minor bump when widest on straightening, produced some late impression closing stages.
Settled mainly in midfield, slightly baulked on rails around the bend, ran home one-paced when not much room behind runners most of way in straight.

Began well, gradually settled just off the pace on rails, hampered and lost position coming out of back straight, renewed effort from midfield after straightening but was badly baulked in the run to the line.

Began moderately, ridden along to pick up ground until hampered about 800 M out, remained just worse than midfield on rails thereafter, ran home one-paced when not much room behind runners most of way in straight.
Soon dropped to the rear, tailed off into straight, no further impression.

Missed the start settled with backmakers 2-wide with cover. Circled the field near the 800 M and travelled outside the leader. Went stride for stride over the final furlong but fought strongly to gain the upper hand late.
Tracked the leader along the rail then was shuffled to race 3 back after the 800 M. Struck interference whilst closing off near the 100 M, successfully protested and was placed runner up.

Raced handy 3-wide with cover. Strolled forward to lead after losing cover after the 1000 M. Dictated terms along the fence but commenced to drift out approaching the 100 M and was relegated on protest.
Pushed forward to lead along the fence after the mile. Handed up leading duties near the 800 M and box seated. Was one paced in the home straight, and was nabbed for third on the line.
Made its run from the rear, 2-wide with cover. Made gradual progress without threatening the principals.
Travelled at the rear of the field along the paint. Worked to the wire fairly.
Settled back in the field along the paint. Struggled in the home straight.

Travelled in a handy position, 1 off with cover. Attempted to quicken passing the 800 M, however was left racing 3-wide without cover on the final circle and in the straight failed to make any impression.
Travelled 3-wide without cover early before rolling forward to settle outside the leader after the 1100 M. Never fired a shot when the filed quickened passing the 800 M.
Settled 1 out 1 back. Copped a check near the 1000 M, and when the pace quickened near the 900 M, drifted back and was never likely.
Began awkwardly. Urged along the fence ahead of midfield. Swung wide and was 4Ls down rounding home turn. Finished off well and took charge closing stages.
Driven forward from high draw but caught 4-wide stable bend. Slotted 2 to 3-wide behind pace from 1200 M. Challenged lead passing 400 M and hit front 200 M. Crushed by the winner final stages.

Slow to begin. Shaken up early in leading section but trapped 3-wide stable bend. Led solo 2-wide back straight. Held a 1L advantage home turn. Couldn't resist the front pair passing 200 M but hung on for 3rd narrowly.
Good jump but caught wide. Cut 2-wide ahead of midfield first turn. Swung widest and was 4Ls off turning into home. Progressed steadily and just made frame.
Out nicely on fence. Elected to take seat from 1200 M. Ridden out 400 M and rallied on with the winner top of home straight. Remained one-paced passing 200 M.
Soon parked 2-wide at midfield. Same position home turn. Kept on steadily in the straight.
Away with them. Shifted to the rail and raced behind midfield stable bend. Stayed near the fence into final stretch. Covered decent ground late.
Slowly away and lost a considerable amount of ground. Resumed 2-wide behind midfield stable bend. Pressured 400 M. Made up minor ground close home.
Eased to rear on fence. Still last leaving home turn. Beat tired runners home.
Slow to begin and lost a considerable amount of ground. Pressed to race behind midfield on fence first turn. Clear run in the straight but found nothing when asked.
Towards rear always. Never a factor.
Never far off the pace before faded top of home straight. Struggled home.
Broke well, urged along to hold the box-seat, proved difficult to settle when restrained halfway, checked at 1000 M, dashed well when asked 250 M out, just in time.
Started awkwardly, pushed up to lead and found the fence near 1000 M, responded well when asked for efforts at the top of home straight, kept on, just caught on line.
Bumped at start, worked early to hold a one-off spot 2Ls off the speed, on heels at 1000 M, closed off well under maximum pressure final 250 M, narrowly beaten.
Bumped at start, lacked early speed and ended up settling 4Ls off the pace, quickened well when clear 250 M out, ran on soundly, just late.
Bumped at start, caught 3-wide with no cover in midfield, urged along from 800 M, kept on satisfactorily under pressure in the straight, but lacked a kick to challenge the principals.
Jumped fast, urged along to take the one-out-one-back spot, held ground early in the home straight, failed to keep on final 200 M.
Crowded at start, lacked early speed despite being urged along, travelled 6Ls off the pace, only made limited progress final 250 M.
Bumped at start, sat one-off in midfield, proved difficult to settle halfway, held up for clear run at 350 M, only one-paced when asked for efforts.
Showed no early speed despite being urged along, travelled one from the rear 6Ls off the speed, failed to make up any ground in the home straight.
Failed to muster speed despite being aggressively ridden, drifted back gradually rounding the home turn, made no progress in the home straight.
Caught wide throughout the trip, never better than midfield.
Taken back from the widest alley, travelled rearward throughout the trip, never in contention.
Broke well, settled cozily in the mid-division on rail, swung widest for home, clicked into gear when clear 250 M out, finished off soundly, hit the front at 100 M, drew clear.
Prominently placed 2Ls off the speed on rail, ran on steadily when clear 250 M out, failed to hold off the winner but did well enough for 2nd.
Caught wide with no cover in midfield early, strode forward to lead halfway and kept on well in the home straight, caught by the top two inside 100 M.
Out in line, settled just behind the leader, had all chances in the home straight, kept on fairly well but lacked a decisive kick to challenge the top three.
Jumped only fairly, caught 3-wide in the mid-division, made up gradual ground down centre of the home straight without threatening the principals.
Slow to begin, lacked early speed as usual and travelled at the rear, swung widest for home, only covered little late ground and passed a few tired runners.
Broke well, prominently placed in a one-off spot just behind the speed, held up for clear run early in the home straight, only one-paced when clear 200 M out, made no progress.
Jumped fairly, travelled 4-5Ls off the speed, raced keenly when restrained in the early stages, failed to make up any ground when asked for efforts in the home straight.
Slow to begin, settled one from the rear on rail, never better than midfield.
Broke well, caught 3-wide in midfield, race keenly when restrained in the middle stages, strode forward rounding the bend, bumped at 300 M, soon flattened.
Settled 2Ls off the pace on 3-deep, failed to keep on after entering the home straight, gave ground.
Caught very wide in the midfield after jumping from gate 12, raced keenly and hung out when restrained, weakened sharply at the top of home straight, finished tailed out.
Settled nicely in midfield along the fence, 3-1/2Ls off the good pace, progressed steadily 250 M to win by a head.
Pushed forward, 1L off the good pace 2-wide, ran on strongly to the line, just beaten by a head in 2nd.
Pushed to cross in front and took rail, led by 1L at good sectionals, hung on until 100 M overhauled, ran on for 3rd.
Eased back and soon took rail, 5Ls off the good pace, lacked room 300 M, made steady ground when clear.
Eased to sit behind the leaders, 2-1/2Ls off the good pace 2 to 3-wide, ran on well to the line.
Hard ridden to keep up with the good pace in box seat, just held ground in straight.
Eased to rear, 6-1/2Ls off the good pace 2 to 3-wide, progressed steadily 300 M.
Eased to sit in midfield, 4Ls off the good pace 2-wide, made some ground 300 M.
Pushed early to take a midfield spot, 5-1/2Ls off the good pace 2-wide, held up 4-2, made minor ground when clear.
Eased back, 5Ls behind the good pace 2 to 3-wide, ran on ok in straight.
Eased at start to take rail at rear, 6-1/2Ls off the good pace, no progress.
Midfield, 3Ls off the good pace, raced 3 to 4-wide throughout and lost too much ground, dropped off 400 M.
Jumped fast, easily ran up to lead 2Ls, quickened well when asked 300 M out and kept on soundly to win.
Prominently placed 2Ls behind the leader, kept on soundly for 2nd under maximum pressure, but never really threatened the winner.
Pushed up to occupy a fence position 3Ls off the pace, responded well when asked for efforts at the top of home straight, finished off well for 3rd.
Bumped at start, settled one-off 4Ls off the speed, had all chances in the home straight, only one-paced under maximum pressure.
Crowded at start, taken back from gate 9 and travelled 9Ls off the pace at the rear, improved along the rail in the home straight, finished off well for 5th.
Niggled along to hold a one-off spot in midfield, responded fairly when asked for efforts 400 M out, made gradual round, rather one-paced.
Crowded at start, settled 7Ls off the pace, urged along halfway, made gradual ground final 250 M, never really troubled the principals.
Bumped at start, lacked early speed as usual and travelled 7Ls off the speed, covered some ground early in the home straight, could not find extra final 100 M.
Urged along to hold a fence position in midfield, held ground until flattened at 200 M.
Bumped at start, raced on-pace but caught wide with no cover throughout the trip, outpaced at home turn, weakened at the top of the straight, faded.
Crowded at start, lacked early speed and lost touch halfway, 20Ls away at home turn, never competitive.
Crowded at start, caught wide with no cover in midfield, over-raced when restrained, weakened at the top of home straight, finished tailed out. (Abnormal breathing noise.)
Switched off to near last, travelled well and picked up strongly passing 300 M, surged to the front 100 M out, held on gamely.
Slow to begin but not hurried, raced at the back 6Ls off leaders, no clear path in straight and had to weave his way through, ran on strongly final 100 M, just failed.
Well covered in midfield and was never far off the pace, responded well inside 300 M, dueled with the eventual winner to 50 M and only lost 2nd place close home.
Niggled along in early stages to maintain his position behind midfield, turned 3-wide passing 1100 M, swung widest to straight and stayed on well final 300 M.
Tracked leaders in the 2-path, shaken up nearing 400 M, had his chance but was out-sprinted final 200 M, flattened out late stages.
Chased the pace but was 3-wide without cover to 600 M, took over passing 400 M, headed 150 M and faded.
Slow to begin, taken across behind runners and remained at the back to home straight, held up to 300 M but could only make limited progress when clear, no impression.
Unable to slot in from draw 12 and travelled 4-wide without cover in the first half, driven nearing home straight but didn't pick up, ran home one paced.
Raced in mid-pack along the fence, switched out inside 350 M to find clear passage but not quickened under pressure, eased when no chance over closing stages.
Away in good order, bagged the rail and moved to a forward position just behind leaders, shuffled back to midfield entering the home turn, driven out 350 M but didn't respond, eased 100 M.
Began awkwardly, strode forward to press the pace and dueled for the lead down the back straight, took over 600 M out, weakened under pressure 350 M, eased.

Pushed to the lead and went a good gallop, vied for lead down the back straight, outpaced nearing the home turn and soon beaten turning in, heavily eased. (Unacceptable performance / Blood in trachea.)

Settled one-back in 2L 3rd on rails, soon came to challenge after straightening, hit front over 300 M out and drew clear gradually.
Disputed lead most of way until taking over briefly turning into straight, headed by the eventual winner 300 M out but fought on gamely to maintain 2nd spot.
Ridden to take up running, established as much as 1L advantage 1200 M out, headed by eventual 2nd turning into straight, gradually faded under pressure. (Bled.)
Settled in 4th mainly 2Ls off the speed, kept on at the same pace without quickening.

Wide in midfield early, tightened and shuffled back towards rear about 1200 M out, remained wide in last few around the bend and into straight, made up good ground down centre of track to be nearest at finish.
Settled in 5th about 3Ls off the pace, raced without cover most of way to straight, similarly positioned turning in, kept on same pace without quickening.
Soon settled at the back after beginning from the widest barrier, remained similar to straight, finished off race well down the centre of the straight.
Settled in midfield, saved ground turning into straight, made short-lived effort early in straight but unable to sustain effort inside final 200 M.
Soon taken well back, last into straight, produced some late impression at the finish.
Tightened and lost position early, gradually recovered to midfield, kept on steadily without quickening.
Soon settled behind midfield after beginning from a poor draw, remained similar to straight, no further impression.
Soon settled in last few, took closer order turning in, made no impression in the run home.
Tightened at start, soon dropped to last few, similarly positioned turning into straight, ran home one-paced.
Settled in midfield on rails, gradually shuffled backward around the bend dropping to last few into straight, no extra.
Cruised to cross and lead in the early stages towards the outside rail. Drew a margin midrace and took control thereafter to land a deserved victory.
Couldn't match the early speed settling midfield near the middle of the course. Closed off well under strong riding.
Began awkwardly but recovered to camp close to the speed 3-4 off the grandstand side. Maintained a good gallop right to the finish.
Ridden prominently with a good trail behind the speed. Made reasonable ground over the last 100m.
Had every chance after tracking the leader near the stand side. Stayed at the same speed over the closing stages.
Travelled close to midfield with cover. Rolled in near the 400m and commenced to challenge but never really quickened.
Raced behind midfield 2-3 off the outside rail. Ranged up and made reasonable ground from the final 100m, was steadied and shifted in whilst continuing to run on near the 50m.
Race midfield along the grandstand stand side. Kept on evenly over the last 100m.
Blundered at the start racing back in the event with cover. Only plodded to the line.
Missed the start settling a long last. Ridden along to keep in touch with the field and made some ground on tiring runners in the latter stages.
Slow to begin settling well back in the field. Struggled in the run home.
Raced close to midfield towards the middle of the course. Gave ground quickly inside the final furlong.
Raced handy to the speed but weakened sharply over the final stages. (Reported to be lame in the left fore the following day.)
Travelled near the centre of the track behind the speed. Was well beaten near the 200m, and tired noticeably in the run to the wire and was eased down.
Prominent position to home straight. Took charge inside final furlong. Easy.
Led on fence to home straight. Swept by the winner passing 200M. Hung on gamely to figure in quinella.
Outside leader to home straight. Ridden out 300M but couldn't quite catch the front pair. Barely clung on for 3rd.
Raced behind midfield on fence early despite effort of rider. Closed off strongly near the fence home straight. Shifted in for clear run near the post and lost a minor placing narrowly.
Began awkwardly. Urged along and parked 3-wide in leading section home turn. Ran on steadily in the straight without seriously threatening the principals.
Slow to begin. Soon taken 2-wide towards rear. Checked when over-raced making home turn. Swung out on straightening but got traffic at 300M. Covered good ground when clear and was nearest at finish.
3-wide behind midfield early. Improved wide to race behind leaders rounding home turn. One-paced to conclude.
2-wide behind leaders to home straight. Couldn't turn up a notch thereafter.
Never better than midfield. Very little impression in the straight.
At rear to home straight. Never a factor.
3-wide towards rear early. Came widest turning in. Failed to pick up final stretch.
Trapped wide and without cover behind midfield early. Strode forward to race 4-wide with leaders from 700M. Weakened rapidly top of home straight. Finished tailed-out. (Bled).
Taken back, held up third last rail, threaded between horses straight, ran on strongly to lead 50m out.
Fluffed start, three lengths last after 100m, up to second last turn, wide un, finished well, winner just too strong.
Fair break wide, settled midfield three wide, finished well down centre, led 125m out, no extra close home.
Moderate start, ridden up to secure midfield rail, pulled out to challenge, ran on but just outpaced.
Moderate break, lacked early pace, fifth last three off, wide bid, ran on one pace.
Fast away, led, crossed and steadied pace, ridden early straight, headed, weakened 200m out.
Moderate start, mid-rear three off, mid-track bid, no kick.
Fair break, sixth one off, wide bid, not pace to challenge.
Fair break, sixth one off, ridden up to join leaders, settled fourth one off, ridden, no kick.
Fair break, ridden but lacked early pace, midfield one off, driven, weakened late.
Fair break, ridden early to hold rail, settled third, ridden to challenge but no kick, weakened late.
Well away, ridden early but not pace to lead, fourth one off, hard ridden mid-track, no kick, weakened late.
Fair break but caught very wide, taken back to rear one off, last on rail into straigh, ridden, weakened, eased.
Good break, ridden up wide, second into straight, ridden, weakened quickly, eased.
Broke well, ridden to narrow lead, stretched away early straight, never challenged.
Fair break, up along rail to settle fourth, tried to quicken with winner, not pace to challenge.
Fair break, no early pace, mid-rear one off, wide bid, ran on well without being able to threaten.
Slight bobble start, midfield one off, then fifth rail, inside bid, kept on, not pace to challenge.
Fair break, settled fifth one off, ridden straight, reached third place, weakened late.
Fair break, settled second last, mid-track bid straight, kept on well late but never able to challenge.
Sluggish start, last and bustled one off, improved wide straight, ran on late but never able to challenge.
Bobbled start, up to midfield rail, ridden entering turn, driven early straight, kept on one pace.
Fair break, settled midfield one off, mid-track bid, reached fourth, flattened out late.
Moderate break, ridden up wide to midfield, ridden early straight, no progress.
Well away, shared lead one off, ridden early straight, weakened.
Well away but lacked early pace, back to rear not settling, ridden turn, found little.
Well away out wide, fifth four off, gradually lost ground.

Placing: DNF
Comment: Jumped well, restrained to a 3-wide spot in midfield, broke down near the 900 M.
Shared the lead at good pace 2 wide, dominated from 400M.
Settled in front as usual, 1.5Ls off the good pace 2 wide, closed the race off well for 2nd.
Eased to rear, 6.5Ls off the good pace 2 wide, made steady ground 300M to grab 3rd.
Pushed forward to take rail in front, shared the lead at good pace, ran on well until 100M flattened.
At back, 5Ls off the good pace on the fence, progressed steadily 400M.
Eased back, 4.5Ls off the good pace 3 wide, made some ground 300M.
Midfield, 3.5Ls off the good pace, trapped 4 wide throughout and lost too much ground, still ran on well to the line.
Settled in box seat, pace good, raced flat in straight, emptied 250M.
Pushed to hold the rail in midfield, 3.5Ls off the good pace, just held ground in straight.
Eased to rear, 6.5Ls off the good pace, trapped 3-4 wide, ran on fairly.
Midfield, trapped 3 wide, 3Ls behind the good pace, flattened 200M.
Eased to sit in front of midfield, 2.5Ls off the good pace on the fence, weakened 300M.
Raced 4 wide throughout, never better than midfield.
Settled cozily just behind the leader, ran on to contest the lead at the top of home straight, kicked strongly under maximum pressure, hit the front 100 M, kept on well to score.
Out in line, urged along to lead 1L, quickened well when asked for efforts 300 M out, headed in by the winner at 100 M, kept on soundly for 2nd.
Jumped only fairly, settled 3Ls off the speed on rails, kicked strongly when clear 300 M out, ran on soundly for 3rd.
Prominently placed in the box-seat, had all chances in the home straight, kept on fairly well under maximum pressure, lacked a decisive kick to challenge the top three.
Given a waiting ride and settled 5Ls off the speed on rail, improved along the inner part of the home straight, ran on steadily final 350 M without threatening the principals.
Slow to begin, settled 5Ls off the speed, improved along 4-deep rounding the home turn, made up gradual ground down centre of the straight, only one-paced final 100 M.
Patiently ridden and settled just behind the mid-division, held up for clear run early in the home straight, finished off well when clear at 250 M.
Settled 2Ls off the speed on 2-wide, only gave limited response when asked for efforts in the home straight, very one-paced.
Pushed up to hold a one-off spot in the mid-division, only made limited progress when clear at 300 M.
Broke fast, restrained in a 3-wide spot just behind the leader, travelled without cover and proved difficult to settle, held ground until flattened at 300 M, soon weakened.
Lacked early speed despite being urged along, travelled 4-deep in the mid-division, crept closer rounding the bend, failed to quicken when asked at 400 M, soon faded.
Lacked early speed as usual, ended up settling 7Ls off the speed, swung widest for home, failed to make up any ground in the home straight.
Taken back from gate 14, travelled rearward throughout the trip, never in contention.
Travelled 3-wide in the mid-division, proved difficult to settle in the early and middle stages, checked at 700 M, weakened 300 M, finished tailed out.
Unhurried in the opening half and placed towards the rear in the 2-path, turned 3-wide over the home turn, ran on strongly and took over 100M out, continued on well while being kept busy to the line.

Within striking distance and was in a good striking position leaving the home bend, had an uninterrupted run and took lead briefly inside 200M but couldn't match terms with the winner over final 100M.
Guided to a fence position towards the rear, angled out 500M, came home willingly from near last to take 3rd.
Given a patient ride and settled at the back 6-7Ls off the pace, saved ground on the inside, niggled along 500M out, made steady progress without reaching the top three.
Positioned one out one back, continued to chase leader in straight but steadily faded from contention passing 100M.
Emerged as the leader nearing 1600M, set even pace at the front and was unchallenged to home straight, offered good resistance until 200M, gradually weakened.
Guided to the rail in early stages and settled not far off the pace, angled out passing 400M for a run but not much room nearing 250M, shifted back to inside and ran on only fairly.
Positioned 3-wide behind midfield down the back straight, moved closer passing 700M, lacked the needed closing response.
Never better than midfield and one off the fence throughout, not quickened turning into straight, raced in restricted room 200M out, one paced in closing stages.
From gate 1 went forward to sit just behind leader, nudged along nearing 500M, didn't find the pace to challenge and weakened gradually over the final 150M.

Travelled 3-wide in midfield and raced without cover from 700M, took closer order home turn, didn't find much when called upon and weakened rapidly nearing 200M. (Jockey reported his horse failed to see out 1800M.)
Taken back from wide barrier, in the last pair one off the fence, swung widest for home and didn't pick up.
Prominently placed just behind the leader, quickened well when asked for efforts 350 M out, hit the front at 150 M, kept on soundly, just withheld the furious challengers.
Out in line, settled 3-wide in the mid-division, responded well when asked for effort s 400 M out, ran on soundly down the centre of the home straight, narrowly beaten by the winner.
Broke well, urged along to hold a 3-wide spot just off the pace, finished off well under maximum pressure final 350 M, kept on soundly for 3rd.
Slow to begin, gradually made up ground along the rail, 4Ls off the pace turning for home, finished off soundly under pressure final 350 M, just missed a place.
Jumped well, settled one-off 2Ls behind the pace, quickened well when clear 250 M out, made up gradual ground, just missed a place.
Broke well, prominently placed in a fence position in midfield, blocked in the home straight, not fully tested.
Broke well, pushed up to share the lead on 2-deep, responded satisfactorily when asked for efforts early in the home straight, could not find extra final 150 M, passed.
Out in line, soon taken towards the rear in search of cover, failed to obtain clear run in the home straight, kept on satisfactorily, not fully tested.
Taken back from the widest alley, travelled 6Ls off the speed at the rear, made up gradual ground down centre of the home straight, but never threatened the principals.
Jumped only fairly, soon ran up to share the lead on rails, only gave limited response when asked 300M out, passed at 200 M, soon flattened.
Taken back from gate 11 and travelled rearward throughout the trip, never competitive.
Broke well but soon restrained to a 3-wide position near the rear, proved difficult to settled in the middle stages, failed to quicken when asked 400 M out, soon dropped out.
Jumped well, easily ran up to track the leader, caught 3-wide with no cover, got tired early in the home straight, finished tailed out.
Average jump, mustered to settle just off pace 3Ls back in running line, enjoyed ideal trip to bend, set out after leader and prevailed after a decent battle, with other placegetters well back.
Showed good speed to across to lead from widest alley, even sections in front with some attention from outside horse, led still at 300 M, decent duel with eventual winner but lost out late.
Drifted back from a wide gate, 3 wide with cover, best part of 5 to 6Ls away, came 4 wide on circle, closed off solidly down middle to snatch 3rd late.
Even jump, settled behind pace 3 to 4Ls back on rails, had an easy time throughout, saved ground on bend, battled away effectively to make frame.
Began with rest, assumed a midfield position 5Ls back in 2 wide line, even trip to bend, didn't quicken but managed to hold ground to line.
Reasonable break, had cover early but posted 3 wide facing breeze from 1000 M, gradually improved on bend, spent force at 200 M when hard run took toll.
Out in line, worked a bit to cross outside leader, fair run in mid-section, levelled up turning but didn't have dash final 300 M, faded late.
Awkwardly away, settled further back than usual 5 to 6Ls back in running line, same margin down to turn, made some minor progress late.
Bounced out, settled in nice spot behind pace pair, had ideal run to bend, didn't find much when asked and weakened disappointingly.
Drifted back from a difficult draw, 7 to 8Ls back in 2 wide line, back with last few turning, made some good headway late. Nice debut.
No early speed, in 2nd half of field 6Ls back, saved ground on bend, took inside runs but didn't get much clear running and was not ridden out as normally would be.
Awkward jump, assumed usual spot at rear on rails, best part of 7Ls away, still had job to do rounding bend, no real impact in straight.
No early pace, 3 wide at tail 7Ls back, had cover to turn, made no serious progress in straight.
Showed natural speed to race behind leader, fair run throughout, soon under pressure turning and didn't see out additional journey.

Settled towards the rear, took off from Rock to circle the field around home bend, widest runner in 6th turning in, ran on well down centre of straight to win decisively.
Began with others, settled wide in midfield, commenced run from Rock to dispute lead into straight, overhauled by winner 200 M out but fought on for 2nd.
Began slowly, travelled well behind to straight, did best work late to just snatch a placing in the shadows of the post.
Began awkwardly, given reminders to muster early, held midfield spot while under urge throughout far side, in similar position turning in, fought on to only narrowly miss a placing.
Always thereabouts, under pressure to take up running when challenged by FRAMES DEPOT far side, held 1L advantage around the bend and into straight, soon overhauled.

Began well, close up early when forced to steady approaching winning post the first time, settled on rails in forward of midfield to straight, checked passing 300 M, recovered well to be nearest at finish.
Settled behind midfield, fought on steadily without quickening down centre of straight.
Began restrained, crossed for rails run at the back from the widest barrier, remained same into straight, kept on steadily past well beaten horses in the run home.
Well there early, gradually settled in 5th just better than midfield, held similar position turning into straight, ran home one-paced. (Blood in trachea.)

Gradually crossed inside to lead from a wide draw, led until challenged and conceded advantage far side, dropped away quickly from 2nd into straight despite saving ground turning in. (Questioned for disappointing performance.)
In front briefly then gradually settled just off the pace, remained in prominent position turning into straight, dropped out tamely.
Wide in midfield early, made steady progress around 1000 M bend to join the leaders, up with the pace until dropping out from around home bend. (Jockey warned re his riding in the middle stages.)
Wasn't the best away but soon mustered speed to hold the fence in 2nd position. Ranged up to hit the front near the furlong and held off serious challenge.
Rated midfield, 3-wide with cover. Loomed up in the straight but was just unable to claw back the margin.
Parked 1 out 1 back. Went to the line soundly along the inside.
Travelled midfield, 2-wide with cover. Raced a little keenly after the 700 M, closed off well to figure in the frame.
Travelled back in the race 2 to 3-wide with cover. Made some late ground in the run home without threatening.
Worked forward to lead, was never properly clear to cross to the rail and therefore raced 1 off the fence. Faded in the run home.
Hit the ground running and raced on the speed, but coursed 3-wide and without cover. Struggled over the latter stages.
Settled with the backmakers along the fence. Worked evenly to the post.
Camped about 2-3 back the fence. Drifted back after the 500 M and was never really in the hunt.
Couldn't go the early speed of the race and settled from a wide barrier in a rearward position. Copped a check on the home turn and was out of business thereafter.
Was posted 4-wide without cover for the major part of the trip, travelling behind the speed. Never a factor.
Slow to begin trailing the field in last position. Never likely.
2-wide handy to home straight. Kept giving and just got up on line.
Led along on fence. Caught final stride.
Prominent spot to home straight. Couldn't match the finishing touch of the front pair but hung on for 3rd with some comfort.
Caught 3-wide early in a forward spot. Parked one-off behind leader near the Rock. One-paced to conclude.
2-wide at midfield to home straight. Plugged on.
At midfield on fence. Improved slightly home turn. Couldn't turn up a notch thereafter.
Taken to rear from highest draw. Found the fence from 700 M. Still the last turning in. Made up some ground in run home.
Began awkwardly. Progressed to race behind midfield near the fence first turn. Hard ridden 500 M out but failed to make headway.
2-wide towards rear. Swung out for clear run home straight but made very little impact.
3-wide behind midfield. Pressured 500 M out. Beaten top of home straight.
Towards rear always. Never a factor.
3-wide at midfield early. Left without cover passing 900 M. Found nothing in the straight.
Good break, not rushed early, settled fifth on rail, out to challenge early straight, led near finish.
Good break, settled third on rail, led 200 M out, just caught.
Well away, settled three wide mid-rear, circled field to lead back straight, ran on well along rail, caught 150 M out.
Broke well, taken back to fourth last one off, not much room first turn, improved four wide home turn, ran on well until flattened out last 50 M.
Missed beat start, taken to rail third last, overracing slightly far side, out for mid-track bid, ran on without being able to threaten.
Slowly away, settled midfield one off, short of room straight, ran on quite well when gap came.
Taken back from wide draw, settled last, pulled off heels approaching turn, ridden and ran on quite well.
Fair break, not rushed, settled second last one off, shaken up turn, wide bid, modest progress.
Lost half length start, ridden early to midfield rail, lost ground although ridden far side, improved turn, rail bid, no kick.
Fair break, settled midfield one off, ridden and kept on straight, never a threat.
Fast away, led and crossed, headed far side, settled second, challenged turn, ridden, weakened.
Broke well, up to second one off, fourth and ridden turn, gradually lost ground.
Fair break, good early speed, led after 150 M, kicked clear early straight, never in danger.
Good break, led early, settled third on rail, tried to challenge throughout straight, never able to get on terms.
Fair break, up to sixth but caught wide, ran on well down outside but never able to challenge.
Fair break, not rushed, settled third last one off, improved wide, kept on well late.
Fair break, caught wide, up to third two off, kept on quite well but never a threat.
Sluggish start, lost length, up to fifth one off, ridden and kept on straight.
Taken to rail from wide draw, settled rear, improved turn, ran on well along rail.
Fair break, taken back to second last one off, improved turn kept on wide.
Good break, aimed for lead but headed inside by winner, raced second, ridden turn, weakened.
Fair break, settled rail but losing ground although bustled, ridden before turn, no progress.
Fair break, not rushed, held up fifth last one off, ridden, found very little.
Fair break, but caught four wide, back through field but no route to rail, last into straight, ridden, no progress.
Hard ridden to share the lead at good pace 2-wide, closed the race off strongly to win by a very narrow margin.
Took rail and shared the lead easily at good pace, hung on strongly until last few strides, just beaten by a short head in 2nd.
Eased to sit in front of midfield, 2Ls off the good pace 2-wide, ran on well to the line for 3rd.
Eased back, 6LS behind the good pace, trapped 3-wide throughout, dashed well 200 M.
Eased to take box seat, pace good, lacked room 400 M, just held ground when clear.
Eased back, 4Ls off the good pace, trapped 3-wide throughout, made some ground 200 M.
Pushed early, sat midfield, 3-1/2Ls off the good pace 2-wide, just held ground in straight.
Checked start, pushed to keep up in midfield, 2-1/2Ls off the good pace 2 to 3-wide, no progress.
Pushed early but not muster, 5Ls off the good pace 2-wide, ran on fairly in final stages.
Hard ridden to share the lead at good pace, trapped 3-wide throughout, emptied 250 M.
Hard ridden to hold the rail in midfield, 3-1/2Ls off the good pace, no progress.
Eased at start to take rail at rear, 5Ls off the good pace, ran on fairly in straight.
Patiently ridden and soon settled in midfield, shifted wide for home, kicked strongly when asked for efforts 250 M out, ran on soundly and hit the front in final few strides.
Pushed hard forward to lead and found the fence near 700 M, kept on soundly when placed under pressure final 300 M, just caught by the winner in final few strides.
Niggled along to hold a one-off spot just behind the pace, ran on soundly under maximum pressure final 250 M, caught by the winner in last few strides, kept on well for 3rd.
Jumped fast, prominently placed on the rail within striking distance, had all chances in the home straight, kept on satisfactorily but lacked a decisive kick to challenge the top three.
Broke well, prominently placed 2Ls off the speed on rail, only one-paced when asked for efforts in the home straight.
Jumped only fairly, pushed hard to hold a one-off spot in midfield, swung widest for home, ran on steadily under maximum pressure, rather one-paced.
Lacked early speed despite being urged along, travelled one from the rear 4-5Ls off the speed, made up gradual ground in the home straight, never really troubled the principals.
Broke well, settled just behind the leader, caught 3-wide throughout the trip, held ground until flattened 150 M out. (Mucus.)
Checked at start, urged along to catch up 4Ls off the pace, responded fairly when asked 300 M out, made up gradually ground, badly checked at 100 M. (Blood in trachea.)
Taken rearward from gate 12, caught 4-wide with no cover throughout trip, outpaced at the top of home straight, dropped out.
Bumped at start, blundered at 950 M, drifted back gradually towards the rear, 11Ls away at home turn, covered little ground in the straight. (Mild lameness in left fore leg.)
Jumped fairly, settled two from the rear on rail, made no progress when urged along 700 M out, outpaced at the top of home straight, finished tailed out.
Positively ridden from the outset and travelled strongly behind leader, swiftly took over 250 M, drew clear under confident handling, never challenged.
Patiently ridden in a position behind midfield, angled out 3-wide inside 500 M and began his challenge, kept on resolutely to the line but couldn't get to the winner.
Guided to a fence position in midfield, held up on the inside to 250 M, ran on well but winner had first run and built up an unassailable lead.
Dropped back to a rearward position along the fence, urged along halfway round the home turn, out into clear 250 M and closed off the race willingly.
Taken back from the wide barrier and settled near last 8Ls off the steady pace, taken wide early straight and finished off the race fairly.
In the group chasing the pace and within striking distance always, maintained momentum to 200 M then lacked further response.
Raced well back in last, 9Ls to make up going into straight and could make no significant headway final 300 M.
Raced in the middle of the pack in the 2-path, didn't pick up when put under pressure and failed to threaten.
Sent to the lead after a slow start, set steady pace in the first half, headed 250 M and gave way.
Tracked leader one out one back, under pressure 400 M, dropped out mid-straight.
Broke well from inside draw, sat in 5th place along the fence, driven along nearing 400 M, didn't find much and weakened rapidly 150 M. (Lame next day.)
Reserved in the rear and well off the pace, 9Ls down passing 400 M and came up empty for the home run.

Well there, gained narrow advantage coming out of back straight, soon driven clear after straightening, won easily.
Soon dropped towards the rear, made up a lot of ground down inner of straight to snatch 2nd over 100 M out.
Settled within 3Ls of pace in 5th before losing position approaching home bend, held 6th spot into straight and took time to switch out for a clear run, fought on nicely to be nearest at finish.
Raced in rear of midfield to straight, fought on steadily down centre of track to be nearest at finish.
Jumped moderately but soon urged to go forward, chased leaders in 3rd on rails into straight, ran home one-paced.
Soon dropped to second last, remained same into straight, made up ground down centre of straight past well-beaten runners.
Raced wide without cover in better than midfield, made short-lived effort down centre of track after straightening reaching 2nd over 200 M out, unable to sustain effort thereafter.
Travelled in rear of midfield to straight, fighting on under pressure when hampered and lost momentum over 200 M out, no further impression afterwards.
Mainly on rails in midfield, lost position approaching home bend, made no impression in straight.
Disputed lead to straight, soon weakened under pressure.
Soon dropped to tail-end and never sighted.
Began with others, niggled along just off the pace, chased leaders into straight, compounded badly.
Very slow away, 3Ls off the leaders, dashed strongly 200 M and drifted away to win despite not suited by the slow pace.
Bumped start, hard ridden to share the lead at slow sectionals, hung on until 150 M overhauled, ran on for 2nd.
Eased to sit 2Ls off the slow pace, ran on well to the line for 3rd.
Hard ridden early but not muster, 3Ls off the leaders, not suited by the slow tempo, just held ground for 4th.
Jumped well but eased back, 5Ls off the leaders, harmed by the slow pace, ran on well to the line.
Shared lead easily at slow sectionals, weakened 250 M.
Eased to sit 2Ls off the slow tempo, ran on until 250 M flattened.
Very slow away, pushed along all the way at back, not suited by the slow pace, no turn of foot.
Eased to sit 2Ls off the leaders, out of fuel 300 M.
Bumped start, pushed to regain a forward spot, 2Ls off the slow pace, emptied 300 M.
Eased to sit in midfield, 3Ls off the leaders, not suited by the slow tempo, weakened 300 M.
Never a factor at rear.
Eased back, never better than midfield.
Very awkward away, never competitive and tailed out.
Urged early on fence. Led passing winning post first time. Held a 2Ls advantage turning in. Never seriously challenged home straight.

Away in line. Gradually eased to 3-wide behind midfield passing winning post first time. Slotted 2-wide back straight. Ridden home turn and was 9Ls down turning in. Finished off strongly wide but the winner was gone.

Trapped wide at midfield passing winning post first time. Improved wide gradually and parked one-off behind pace 1000 M out. Pressured rounding home turn but couldn't get close to the winner. Held 2nd until closing stages.
Well enough away but insufficient speed to lead. Found the fence towards rear passing winning post first time. Swung out and was 9Ls away on straightening. Closed off fairly well thereafter.
Began well. Cut to the fence ahead of midfield from 1400 M. Urged along the fence to maintain position back straight. Pressed home turn. Covered minor ground late.
Driven forward from wide draw. Slotted 2-wide behind pace passing winning post first time. Challenged leaders 3-wide turning into home. One-paced to conclude.
Eased to 2-wide at rear after start. Same position into final stretch. Made up good ground through runners thereafter.

Driven to 3-wide ahead of midfield passing winning post first time after fair start. Shifted 2-wide passing 800 M. Made some headway home straight before being awkwardly placed concluding stages. Not fully tested.
Crowded for room at start. Pushed to muster and held the fence behind midfield passing winning post first time. Minor progress in the straight.
Trapped wide early. Eventually slotted 2-wide towards rear from 1200 M. No significant improvement in the straight.
Lifted front feet off the ground at start and lost ground. Resumed 2-wide behind midfield passing winning post first time. Failed to pick up in the straight.
Midfield on fence to home straight. Found nothing when asked.
Taken to rear after start. Never recovered.
2-wide at midfield. Struggled from home turn. Well beaten final furlong.
Slow away, back to second last on rail, slight check far side, found gaps along rail, finished fast to lead last 25 M.
Fair break, fourth last one off, improved turn, had to wait for run, found gap, finished well, just outpaced late.
Well away, led early but three wide, unable to cross, still led until deep straight, just caught late.
Slight stumble start but fast away, third holding rail, joined lead early straight, weakened 150 M out.
Fair break, ridden early, midfield one off, ran on well until run flattened out late.
Fair break, not pace to lead, settled midfield rail, driven straight, kept on but no kick.
Slow away, two lengths last early, improved wide turn, kept on until run flattened late.
Fair break, up on outside but caught wide, taken back to rear but still wide and not settling, wide bid straight, no kick.
Fair break, vied for lead, third one off, weakened straight.
Fair break, ridden early, caught wide, ridden before turn, wide bid, weakened.
Well away, six wide no route to rail, always wide, ridden, found nil.
Fair break, ridden early, not reach lead, caught five wide, began to weaken before straight, eased.
Broke well, led, two clear far side, ridden and strongly pressed straight, fought on, drifted towards rail late, held on.
Broke well, settled rail third, challenged leader early straight seemingly going better, long duel, just held.
Fair break, settled one off midfield, rail bid straight, finishing strongly when gap closed, checked and lost second.
Well away, settled fifth one off, mid-track bid, never quite pace to challenge.
Broke well, midfield one off, ridden and kept on mid-track, no kick.
Fair break, caught wide mid-rear, up to midfield turn, wide bid, kept on quite well.
Slow into stride, squeezed back, midfield rail, rail bid, kept on under driving, never threatened.
Fair break, taken back mid-rear one off, wide bid under pressure, modest progress.
Broke well, ridden wide up to second, then third one off, ridden early straight, weakened.
Missed break, last early, three lengths last leaving back, urged, kept on past beaten horses late.
Fair break, ridden up early, settled midfield one off, awkward out of turn, ridden, found nil.
Taken back from outside draw, third last one off, ridden early straight, no response.
Sluggish start, ridden, settled fourth last rail, ridden, no progress.
Well away but caught wide, up to second three off, began to weaken leaving turn, eased.
Hard ridden to cross in front, 2Ls off the good pace on the rails, dominated from 350 M.
Pushed forward, 4Ls off the good pace along the fence, ran on well to the line for 2nd.
Eased back, 8Ls off the good pace along the fence ,dashed well 300 M for 3rd.
Bumped start, pushed along at rear as usual, 9Ls off the good pace, lack room 400 M, made good ground when clear.
Hard ridden to keep up in midfield, 7Ls off the good pace 2-wide, progressed steadily in straight.
Hard ridden forward, 3-1/2Ls off the good pace 2-wide, flattened 250 M.
Midfield, 5-1/2Ls behind the good pace 2-wide, no turn of foot.
Eased back, 7-1/2Ls off the good pace 3-wide, no progress.
Raced 4-wide throughout at rear, never competitive.
Took rail easily and led by 2Ls at good pace, dropped off quickly 350 M.
Hard ridden early but not muster, hung on badly at bends and tailed out.

Placing: PU
Comment: At rear, eased out of race in straight.
Out in line, niggled along to lead and found the fence at 1200 M, responded well when asked 350 M, passed at 250 M, kept battling on, fought back at 100 M, just prevailed.
Broke well, prominently placed in the box-seat, responded well when asked for efforts 250 M out, finished off soundly, just late.
Jumped well, settled cozily in the one-out-one-back spot, ran on to contest the lead early in the home straight, could not offer extra final 100 M, but still did enough for a place.
Out in line, urged along to hold a 3-wide spot in midfield, responded well when asked for efforts early in the home straight, finished off satisfactorily final 250 M.
Driven to hold a fence position in midfield, only one-paced when placed under pressure final 400 M. (Blood in trachea.)
Out in line, urged along to take a one-off spot in midfield, only gave limited response when asked for efforts in the home straight, failed to make up any ground.
Slow to begin, travelled 4Ls off the pace near the rear, shifted widest for home, bumped early in the home straight, no kick when asked for efforts, no progress.
Lacked early speed as usual and travelled rearward throughout the trip, badly crowded at the top of home straight, failed to make up any ground.
Widely drawn, pushed up 2Ls off the speed, caught 3-wide with no cover, held ground until got tired near 200 M.
Lacked early speed despite being urged along, travelled 4Ls off the speed at the rear, crept closer rounding the home turn, bumped 400 M out, made no progress in the straight.
Guided to a midfield position along the rail and was unhurried for 900 M, quickened impressively when asked, took lead 100 M, lengthened away and won by a decisive margin.
Away in good order and stalked leader off the inside rail, kept on willingly to the line but was unable to fend off the fast finishing winner nearing100 M.
Forwardly placed in 4th chasing leaders, closed well and battled determinedly through the final 200 M to gain 3rd while no match for the winner.
Obtained a midfield position along the inside under light urging early, ran on final 300 M but lacked extra pace to mount a serious challenge.
Fair start only and was vigorously ridden to find the lead, led nearing 800 M and took them along at a good pace, kept on well to 150 M then tired steadily to the line.
Raced in mid-division along the 3-path and left without cover from 900 M, urged along nearing 400 M, kept on at the same pace and failed to threaten.
Began awkwardly, restrained in midfield and was a shade keen down the back straight, driven 400 M out but lacked a rally.
Lacked speed and had to be driven along shortly after the start, detached in last about 10Ls off the pace over the home turn, went past beaten runners only in the straight.
Began well, restrained to a midfield position one off the fence, unbalanced near 1000 M and lost ground, not quickened under pressure, eased when no chance final 100 M.
Went forward from a wide barrier and raced within striking distance, hung out badly when placed under pressure in the straight, eased 200 M out.
Towards the rear 3-wide, didn't pick up and eased mid-straight when well beaten.
Restrained after the start then taken across to a fence position near the rear, under serious pressure inside 500 M, eased 300 M and finished tailed out. (Unacceptable performance.)
Out in line, urged along to hold a fence position in midfield, shifted wider for home, quickened when clear 250 M out, ran on strongly, hit front at 100 M, kept on well to score.
Pushed along early and soon settled one-off 3Ls behind the speed, ran on to contest the lead rounding the home turn, kept on soundly, only caught by the winner at 100 M.
Lacked early speed as usual and travelled one from the rear 9Ls off the pace, blocked early in the home straight, kicked strongly when clear near 200 M, ran on for 3rd, too late.
Urged along to take the one-out-one-back spot, kept on satisfactorily when asked, caught 250 M out, rather one-paced, just missed a place.
Slow to begin, pushed along to catch up 7Ls off the pace on rail, blocked at the top of home straight, quickened when clear at 250 M, ran on steadily, rather one-paced.
Started awkwardly, pushed up to lead 1L, hung out throughout the trip, caught by the winner 250 M out, kept on fairly, got tired final 50 M.
Started awkwardly, lacked early speed and travelled 7Ls off the pace, responded satisfactorily when asked 300 M out, ran on steadily, could not find extra final 50 M.
Out in line, settled one-off in the mid-division, niggled along rounding the home turn, only one-paced when asked for efforts in the straight.
Prominently placed 3Ls off the pace on rail, proved difficult to settle in the middle stages, quickened well when asked for effort 300 M out, blocked final 200 M, not tested.
Settled one-off 2-3Ls behind the leader, held ground until flattened near the 300 M, soon faded.
Taken back from the widest alley, settled at the rear until the home straight, covered some late ground final 250 M, only passed a few tired runners.
Out in line, caught wide with no cover in midfield, held ground until got tired near the 200 M pole, soon dropped out.
Jumped only fairly, urged along to hold a one-off spot in midfield, moved closer rounding the home turn, failed to keep on final 300 M, dropped out.
Driven to take the box-seat, weakened sharply at the top of the home straight, finished tailed out. (Bled.)
Jumped OK, took ideal role in 1 out 1 back spot, overraced 2 to 3Ls back in middle stages, improved 3 wide rounding bend, lengthened nicely final 300 M to win well in end.
Began well took up a prime position on leaders back, had run of race to bend, loomed up between horses near 200 M but outdashed last 100 M by winner.
No speed, settled behind midfield 6 to 7Ls away in running line, even trip but had task in front coming 3 to 4 wide turning, closed race off strongly for 3rd.
Taken back from an awkward alley, 5Ls back in midfield, 2 wide, tracked 3 wide approaching bend, made good ground in straight to make frame.
Showed speed, took up running at a decent tempo, held a 1L advantage to bend, kicked but overhauled approaching 300 M, faded last bit however not beaten that fair.
No early pace, positioned behind midfield 5 to 6Ls off top end, pace even set a task when still well down to bend, did close off well late.
Outpaced early, ended up with last few on rails, 6 to 7Ls back settling, took inside runs on circle, made decent progress along rails late to be nearest on line.
Taken back and down to rails from a wide alley, had a soft trip midfield on rails 4 to 5Ls away, made some minor ground to 300 M but no progress thereafter.
Decent getaway, camped not far from speed 3Ls back on rails, quiet time throughout, struggled to dash and just battled away.
Began OK, went forward but posted 3 wide outside leaders, up challenging but hanging on bend, did too much work and folded at 300 M.
Restrained from widest gate, ended up 8Ls from them, still well back to bend, took inside runs and didn't have the clearest passage but made some even progress late.
Angled into midfield role, 4 to 5Ls back in 2 wide line, travelled 3 wide approaching bend, lacked usual finish and faded final furlong.
Showed enough speed to settle outside leaders, close enough but niggled before bend, gave in weakly in straight.
Failed back after a standard getaway, 3 wide 7 to 8Ls back at rear, never travelled and beaten a very long way.

Broke well to hold prominent position, took up running passing 1200 M holding 1L advantage most of way, kept on well under pressure inside final 200 M to win readily.

Soon settled in last few, rolled forward around stables bend to be wide in midfield far side, moved further closer up around the Rock, fought on steadily down straight to reach 2nd without threatening winner.
Quickly into lead after beginning from the widest draw, ceded advantage to eventual winner about 1100 M out, held similar spot on rails behind leader to straight, kept on same pace to finish.
Settled towards rear, saved plenty of ground turning home on rails, fought on steadily without quickening.

Began awkwardly, jockey said saddle shifted early but was corrected passing the winning post the first time, travelled in midfield on rails before losing position going up Rock, saved ground turning in, kept on same pace under pressure.
Towards rear, made short-lived effort around field at home bend, widest runner turning in, ran home steadily down centre of straight without threatening.
Gradually dropped to last spot despite niggled along, trailed the field to straight, kept on steadily past well beaten horses inside final 200 M.
Settled in midfield, came under pressure turning in, made no impression in straight.
Settled well back, taken wide into straight, made no impression thereafter.
Began with others, settled just off the speed before shuffled backward to midfield going up the Rock, remained similar turning for home, gradually faded under pressure.
Pulled to first few after beginning from a wide draw, held the one-out-one-back spot to straight, weakened under hard driving in the run home.
Broke with others, soon taken back to race in midfield, faded under pressure in straight.
Camped 3 back, 2-wide with cover. Dashed well early in the straight and took control of the race in the final stages.
Settled with the backmakers, 1 off with cover. Closed off strongly.
Parked worse than midfield 2-wide with cover. Came widest in the straight and finished off smartly.
Went forward and led from the early stages, crossing to the fence near the 800 M. Commenced to tire over the concluding stages but was able to hold on to finish in the frame.
Travelled in 2nd position, 1 off with cover. Maintained its ground over about the last 100 M.
From a wide gate was taken back and made its run from the rear of the field, 2 deep with cover after settling. Ran on soundly.
Blew the start by lifting its front legs off the ground, losing considerable ground settling behind midfield the fence. Railed up in the straight and made good ground in the home straight.
Began awkwardly by getting its fore legs off the ground and consequently travelled at the rear of the field 1 off with cover. Ran on fairly.
Sent forward and took a sit in the early stages. Tracked the leader along the paint, faded inside the furlong.
Settled 3 back the fence. Never looked likely and in the final stretch only plodded home.
Coursed wide and without cover for most of the trip whilst racing on the speed. Never likely.
Settled close to midfield 3-wide with cover. Struggled in the home straight.
2-wide towards rear early and middle stages. Swung out rounding home turn. Responded well under pressure. Asserted authority concluding stages.
Rolled to one-off fence behind pace after start. Pressed to get closer to leader home turn. Every chance final furlong. Couldn't contain the strong finishing winner near the post.
Held fence behind midfield. Left the rail gradually to progress home turn. Kept making up ground before held up at 200 M. Resumed well to snatch a minor placing final stages.
Began well. Took seat on fence behind the leaders from first turn. Shaken up home turn. One-paced to conclude.
2-wide at midfield to home turn. Bumped and taken wider passing 500 M. Ran on in the straight until no extra gear to threaten the front trio close to home.
Driven early to take forward spot on fence first turn. Eased to sit behind leader from 850 M. Hard ridden from 450 M and made steady headway in the straight without troubling the principals.
On fence at midfield to home turn. Shifted out for clear run passing 500 M. Kept on steadily before crowded for room at 250 M. In traffic again at 100 M. Not fully tested.
Away in line. Parked 3-wide towards rear first turn. Slotted 2-wide from 1200 M. Covered decent ground home straight.
Well enough away and raced outside leader first turn. Led solo on fence at Rock. Quickened and held a 2Ls advantage home turn. Caught final furlong and weakened.
Travelled wide and without cover at midfield. Struggled home turn. No impression in the straight.
Slow to begin and was bumped. At rear throughout. Never a factor.
Began awkwardly. Back with last few to home straight. Never in the hunt.
Pushed up to lead 1L on rail, enjoyed an uncontested lead, quickened well when asked for efforts 300 M out, kept on soundly, scored with some hand.
Taken back from gate 12 and travelled 6Ls off the speed, finished off strongly along the inner part of home straight final 300 M, got 2nd in the final stride.
Urged along to take the box-seat, suited by the soft tempo, responded well when placed under pressure in the home straight, kept on well for 3rd.
Settled one-off in the mid-division, niggled along at home turn, crowded at 250 M, made up gradual ground under maximum pressure final 200 M, just missed a place.
Taken towards the rear from gate 11, given a waiting ride until the home straight, dashed strongly when clear at 200 M, ran on soundly under maximum pressure, too late.
Taken back from gate 9 and travelled 8Ls off the pace, swung widest for home, made up gradual ground final 250 M down the centre of the straight.
Broke well, settled in a 3-wide spot in midfield, crept closer rounding the home bend, only one-paced when asked for efforts in the straight.
Prominently placed 2 to 3Ls off the speed, badly held up in the home straight, not fully tested.
Crowded at start, settled 3 to 4Ls off the pace on rail, only gave limited response when asked for efforts at the top of home straight, no extra final 200 M.
Pushed up to hold the one-out-one-back spot, niggled along at home turn, failed to keep on near the 200 M pole, hung out 150 M out, faded.
On-pace but caught 3-wide with no cover throughout the trip, gave no response when asked at the top of home straight, soon got tired, bumped 150 M out.
Settled 6Ls off the pace on rail, drifted back towards the rear at the home straight, never recovered.
Fair break, settled midfield one off, wide challenge straight, ran on strongly to lead 100 M out.
Fair break, taken back from wide draw, settled rear one off, followed winner through but never able to challenge.
Broke well, shared early lead then went on alone, clear into straight until caught 100 M out.
Fair break, settled rail third last, ran on well without being able to threaten.
Well away, not much early pace, settled midfield rail, urged leaving back, ran on along rail under driving.
Well away, up to fifth three wide, still wide into straight, kept on.
Well away, led early one off, then disputed lead, second into straight, hard ridden, one pace.
Moderate start, ridden up behind leaders one off, ridden early straight, one pace.
Fair break, mid-rear two off, firmly ridden turn, no real progress.
Fair break, on leaders' tails but pulling slightly far side, ridden straight, no response.
Not fast away, second last two off, last into straight, ridden along rail, no progress.
Fair break, ridden up early to join leaders three wide, not turn well and lost ground into straight, weakened, eased.
Pushed to occupy the box seat, pace good, led 100 M, ran on strongly to win.
Eased back, 9Ls off the good pace 2 to 3-wide, dashed strongly 300 M for 2nd.
Hard ridden to take the rail and led by 1-1/2Ls at good sectionals, hung on strongly until 100 M overhauled, ran on for 3rd.
Settled in front, 2Ls off the good pace 2-wide, closed the race off well.
In front of midfield, 4-1/2Ls off the good pace 2-wide, made steady ground 250 M.
Midfield, 6Ls off the good pace, trapped 3-wide throughout and lost too much ground, ran on well to the line.
Prominent along the fence, 3Ls off the good pace, just held ground in straight.
Pushed early, 7-1/2Ls behind the good pace 2-wide, made ground in straight, lacked room 200 M.
Eased to sit behind midfield, 7-1/2Ls off the good pace along the fence, made minor ground 100 M.
Bumped start, 9Ls off the good pace 2-wide, little dash 200 M. (Lame.)
Eased to sit in midfield, 5-1/2Ls off the good pace on the fence, no progress.
Eased back to take rail at rear, 11Ls off the good pace, ran on fairly.
Given a waiting ride and settled one from the rear, swung widest for home, dashed strongly when asked for efforts final 300 M, hit the front 50 M out, brilliant win.
Broke fast and soon ran up to lead, quickened well when asked for efforts at the top of home straight, caught by the winner 50 M out, kept on soundly for 2nd.
Pushed up to hold the one-out-one-back spot, responded well when asked 300 M out, hung out and bumps near 150 M and 100 M out, kept on well for 3rd.
Bumped at start, settled one-off just off the speed, ran on well when placed under pressure final 300 M, bumps near 150 M and 100 M, hung out 50 M out, just missed a place.
Lacked early speed as usual and travelled 7Ls off the pace at the rear, niggled along from 600 M, made up gradual ground along the inner part of the home straight.
Broke well from gate 10, pushed forward but caught 3-wide with no cover throughout the trip, kept on satisfactorily in the home straight, could not find extra final 50 M.
Started awkwardly, urged along to hold a fence position in midfield, took time to pick up early in the home straight, made up gradual ground final 200 M, rather one-paced.
Lacked early speed despite being urged along, ended up settling near the rear on the rail, responded fairly when asked in the home straight, made some late progress final 200 M.
Prominently placed in the box-set, niggled along rounding the home turn, flattened 250 M out, soon faded.
Settled one-off in the mid-division, only one-paced when asked for efforts in the home straight, failed to make any progress.
Bumped at start, settled 3Ls off the pace on 3-deep, on heels at 1400 M, failed to make up any ground in the home straight.
Out in line, never better than midfield, struggled rounding the home turn, soon dropped out.
Behind midfield early, switched to 3-wide approaching the back straight and moved closer to leaders in a slowly run race, picked up gradually under a forceful ride and got to the front inside 100 M.
Held up in midfield along the fence, had a ground saving trip throughout, steadily gathered momentum up the inside but just found one too good.
Tracked leader from early on, in a good striking position leaving the home bend and had every chance down the inside, finished evenly and not beaten far.
Soon led along the inside and controlled the pace under restraint, nudged along nearing 400 M, rallied on when pressed by rivals in straight, hung on to the lead till 100 M and faded late stages.
Closest to the pace outside leader, benefited from the slow pace and had a soft run to straight, held on well to 100 M and weakened late stages.
Slow to begin but not hurried, placed towards the rear 5Ls off the pace, took time to pick up in straight and found his best stride too late.
Away in good order and sat handily just off the pace, didn't have a sudden acceleration but kept battling on behind leaders till final 50 M when running out of room.
Raced in mid-division for the first 800 M, not helped by the slow pace and shuffled back to a position towards the rear, ran on one-paced final 300 M and not getting any closer to the leaders.
Guided to the inside early while being settled in the rear well off the pace, unsuited by the slow tempo and had to wait for an opening until 350 M, made some progress from near last.
Urged early to secure a 2-wide midfield position, well covered to the straight, was about to pick up but unable to obtain clear running final 200 M, not properly tested.
Raced 3-wide without cover in the second flight, made a brief bid turning into straight, faded gradually over the final 200 M.
Switched off to last after the start, 6Ls behind leader passing 400 M but couldn't pick up under pressure.
