Never far off, quickened well to hit front narrowly over 200 M out, hung on well to the line.

Broke well from the rail draw to lead throughout far side, ceded advantage coming onto home bend, held every chance early in home straight, fought on nicely but failed to peg back winner throughout closing stages.
Began well from a wide draw, soon taken back to race in midfield and remained very wide throughout without cover, fought on gamely down straight to be nearest at finish.
Raced wide in rear of midfield, failed to quicken to threaten in straight.
Close up briefly, soon settled in rear of midfield, saved ground straightening, fought on under pressure to reach distant 5th at the finish.
Held prominent position to straight, kept on same pace in the run home for a creditable effort.
Soon taken backward to settle wide behind midfield, remained similar into straight, fought on steadily under pressure without quickening.
Ridden along in midfield far side, gained closer order on rails rounding home bend, just behind leaders turning for home, soon weakened under pressure after straightening.
Slow to muster speed early, gradually picked up to rear of midfield, saved ground on rails turning for home, did not find much daylight on rails in the run home and was not fully tested.
Trailed the field to straight, ran past well beaten horses in straight.
Raced freely towards the rear, in similar position entering straight, ran home one-paced.
Very slowly away, soon recovered to join rear of field, saved ground turning in, made no impression in straight.
With leaders to straight, yielded ground quickly from approaching home turn.
With leaders out wide after beginning from the widest barrier, disputed lead into straight, folded up quickly after straightening. (Bled.)
Raced behind midfield 1 off with cover. Commence to travel well and shifted into the 3-wide line passing the 600 M. Closed off strongly for a well deserved win.
Strolled to the lead on the paint after the 900 M. Fought on well to hold second placing.
Box seated after the 900 M. Ranged up at the furlong, had no excuses.
Made its run from 2nd last position along the rail. Finished off soundly to make the frame.
Parked midfield the fence. kept on at the same speed for most of the home straight.
Ambled forward to eventually roll across to race outside the leader after the 800 M. Faded over the latter stages.
Raced towards the tail of the field 2-wide with cover. Closed off well.
Camped behind midfield the fence. Ran on adequately although struck some traffic problems nearing the furlong.
Copped a check near the 1500 M thereafter travelled 3 back, 1 of with cover. Commenced to tire inside the 100 M.
Raced behind midfield, 3-wide with cover. Worked to the line evenly.
Began awkwardly then failed to muster speed settling in last position. Only plodded to the line.
Travelled with the backmakers 3-wide with cover. Struggled in the home straight.
Coursed 3-wide and without cover just behind the speed. Never likely.
Raced prominently, 4-wide and without cover for most of the trip. Not likely.
First to hit ground. Led on fence 1000 M out. Held a 1L advantage turning into home. Always had enough to repel rivals.
Near the fence at midfield. Took inside run home turn. Held up until 300 M. Finished off strongly once into clear but the winner was gone.

Away in line but caught wide. Taken to 3-wide towards rear at 1200 M. Improved wide home turn and was 4Ls down turning in. Ran on well without seriously troubling the front pair. Fought gamely to the line to hold 3rd.
2-wide behind midfield. Checked at 700 M. Got traffic top of home straight. Kept making up good ground when clear and nearly snatched a minor placing. Promising debut.
Switched off from widest gate after start. Improved widest passing 700 M. 6Ls away into final stretch. Rallied on until no extra to threaten the principals close home.
Prominent spot to home straight. Every chance but was one-paced to conclude.
2-wide ahead of midfield to home straight. Afforded unimpeded run from 300 M but couldn't turn up a notch.
Never far off the pace on fence. Failed to pick up when asked passing 300 M. Weakened final furlong. (Substantial blood in trachea.)
2-wide towards rear. Swung wide on straightening. Held ground thereafter.
Slow to begin and raced 2-wide behind midfield on fence. Never nearer.
Taken to rear from high draw. Shaken up approaching home straight but failed to quicken. Just beat tired runners home. (Lame left fore.)
One-off behind leader until faded passing 300 M.
3-wide at midfield. Left without cover passing 800 M. Improved 4-wide behind leaders leaving the bend. Gave ground rapidly passing 300 M. (Substantial blood in trachea.)
Moderate start but soon up to third on rail, moved out and led early straight, soon clear, kept on strongly.
Fair break, settled rail midfield, made ground inside, out to challenge 250m out, never able to trouble winner.
Fair break, settled mid-rear one off, improved on outside turn, driven and ran on but never able to challenge.
Fair break, unhurried on rail fourth last, improved along rail straight, kept on.
Not hurried from wide gate, settled rear, improved wide turn, kept on steadily.
Fair break, settled midfield one off, improved along rail turn, kept on, not pace to challenge.
Broke well, led, headed early straight, gradually weakened.
Well away, up wide to fourth one off, lost ground slightly turn, kept on straight, not pace to challenge.
Fair break, settled near rear one off, ridden early straight, one pace.
Fair break, up to second one off, lost ground entering straight, ridden, weakened.
Fair break, fourth two off, slight stumble first turn, midfield three off, improved to fourth far side, ridden, weakened.
Taken back from wide draw, settled towards rear, tried to improve three wide turn, no progress.
Fair break up on outside, but fifth last, ridden entering turn but no progress, weakened, eased.
Fair break, up to fourth one off, challenged alongside second, fierce battle, just prevailed.
Well away, settled third on rail, ridden to narrow lead mid-straight, fought hard but just caught last strides.
Well away, settled fifth on rail, strong inside run to almost share lead 100m out, weakened slightly late.
Well away out wide, up to midfield one off, ran on well out wide, not quite pace to challenge.
Broke well, settled mid-rear one off, ran on well out wide.
Fair break, settled seventh rail eight lengths off lead, improved rail early straight, ran on, not quite pace to get involved.
Missed break, lost couple of lengths, urged along second last far side, ran on very well between runners.
Fair break, not go early pace, fourth last on rail, ran on well in straight.
Fair break, hard ridden early to lead, led until caught 200m out, weakened late.
Moderate break, fourth last one off, ridden early straight, kept on but not pace to challenge.
Well away, looked for route to rail, settled near rear three wide, wide bid, no real progress.
Fair break, settled two off mid-rear, mid-track bid, no progress.
Blew start, head in air and clear last early, tried to improve along rail, found very little.
Fair break, hard ridden but not quite pace to lead, settled second, challenged early straight, ridden, weakened.
Took rail and led by 1L easily at slow sectionals, drifted away 300M.
Eased to sit in midfield, 3.5Ls off the leaders, trapped 4 wide, hampered 600M, harmed by the slow pace, dashed strongly 250M for 2nd despite all negative racing situations.
Eased to sit just behind the leading bunch, 2.5Ls off the slow pace 2 wide, closed the race off strongly 300M for 3rd.
Eased to sit behind midfield, 4.5Ls off the leaders 2 wide, held up 4-2, dashed strongly when clear.
Hard ridden to sit just off the leader 2 wide, enjoyed the slow sectionals, ran on until 250M flattened.
Eased back, 6Ls off the leaders, trapped 3-4 wide, harmed by the slow pace, showed good finishing efforts 200M.
Eased back, 7Ls off the leaders 2 wide, dashed well 200M along the fence despite not suited by the slow pace.
Very slow away, pushed to take midfield spot, 4Ls off the leaders 2 wide, harmed by the slow pace, ran on ok, checked 250M.
Eased back, 6Ls off the leaders along the fence, harmed by the slow pace, blocked most straight, ran on ok.
Eased back, 5Ls off the leaders 3-5 wide, harmed by the slow pace, no dash.
Pushed to occupy the box seat, suited by the slow tempo, however soon weakened 300M.
Pushed to sit in front of midfield, 3Ls off the leaders 3 wide, not suited by the slow tempo, raced flat in straight.
Raced keenly in prominent spot, 3 wide no cover, emptied 400M.
Eased back, harmed by the slow pace, trapped 5 wide throughout, moved forward 800M, faded 400M.
Broke well, tracked the leader in the one-out-one-back spot, responded well when asked 350 M out, soon hit the front, kept on soundly under maximum pressure, fought bravely to score.
Taken to the rear from gate 12 and travelled 7Ls off the speed, shifted widest for home, responded well when asked for efforts 350 M out, ran on strongly for 2nd.
Settled 3-wide in the mid-division, lost cover at 1000 M, ran up gradually at the top of the home straight and looked possible to score, no extra final 50 M, just did enough for a place.
Urged along to hold a one-off spot in midfield, on heels at 800 M, finished off well when placed under pressure final 300 M, just missed a place.
Prominently placed 2-3Ls off the pace on 2-deep, bumped at 1000 M, kept on soundly in the home straight, just missed a place.
Settled one-off in midfield, on heels at 800 M and drifted back rounding the bend, bumped at 600 M, made up gradual ground final 300 M, rather one-paced. (Blood in trachea.)
Urged to lead 1L and found the fence easily, caught by the winner 350 M out, soon got tired.
Out in line, settled 5Ls off the speed on rail, only made limited progress along the inner part of the home straight, never really troubled the principals.
Jumped only fairly, pushed up to take the box-seat, bumped at 1000 M, failed to quicken when asked for efforts at the top of the home straight, outpaced 200 M out.
Jumped fast, soon taken towards the rear, bumped at 600 M, failed to make up any ground in the home straight.
Settled 4Ls off the pace on rails, crowded at 1000 M, blocked early in the home straight, failed to quicken when clear 150 M out.
Crowded at start, travelled 6Ls off the speed near the rear, only made limited progress at the top of home straight, couldn't find extra final 100 M. (Lost left front plate.)
Taken back from gate 13 and travelled rearward throughout the trip, swung widest and obtained clear run 450 M out, only one-paced when asked, failed to make up any ground.

Dropped back to near last after the start, confidently ridden, 6Ls to make up passing 400 M, accelerated impressively from a near impossible position, drew level with runner-up 50 M out and edged away.
Positioned 2-wide and held up behind midfield, ran on gamely final 300 M only beaten by UK's champion 3yo filly Snow Fairy near finish.
Led uncontested and took them along at a sedate tempo, pressed nearing top of straight, held on to lead until 100 M, battled on well late stages for place honour.
Towards the rear and not hurried, travelled well throughout, driven along inside 500 M, finished well down the outside final 250 M, just beaten for 3rd.
Positioned 2-wide in mid-division, out into clear 350 M, ran on well to 150 M but turned one pace thereafter.
Placed off the rail ahead of midfield, held up along the inside till 250 M but found less than expected when clear.
Positively ridden early to overcome a wide draw, sat one out one back and chased leader to 150 M, outpaced late stages.
Prominent behind leaders in the 2-path, loomed a threat 250 M out but tired inside 100 M.
Reserved in last over 10Ls behind leader in a slowly run race, finished the last 400 M 2nd fastest but was left with too much to do.
Forwardly placed just behind leader, went off the rail nearing 500 M to challenge, found no extra pace in straight and weakened steadily 200 M.
Not suited by the slow pace and raced keenly behind midfield in the first half, brushed the rail at 400 M and lost momentum, one-paced final 200 M.
Held up towards the rear, made very limited progress inside 400 M, never a factor.
Held up behind midfield 7 to 8Ls off a sedate pace, didn't pickup turning for home, weakened steadily final 200 M. (Lame right front leg.)
Jumped fast, soon ran up to occupy the box-seat, blocked and bumped early in the home straight, quickened well when clear 200 M out, hit front at 150 M, kept on soundly to win.
Settled one-off in the mid-division, hampered at 1000 M, responded well when asked for efforts 400 M out, ran on soundly for 2nd.
Crowded after start, settled one-off just off the pace, bumped at 1000 M, blocked early in the home straight, bumped again at 200 M, ran on well for 3rd when clear at 150 M.
Settled 2-3Ls off the pace on rail, blocked at the top of the home straight, quickened well when clear 150 M out, just late for a place.
Raced on-pace but caught 3-wide with no cover, on heels at 1000 M, kept on satisfactorily under maximum pressure, bumped and crowded in the concluding stages, just missed a place.
Crowded after start, settled one-off just behind the mid-division, swung widest for home, only made up gradual ground down centre of the straight, rather one-paced.
Bumped at start, urged along to occupy a one-off spot just off the speed, ran on to contest the lead 350 M out, bumped at 300 M, caught by the winner near 150 M, soon flattened.
Raced handy early but caught 3-wide with no cover, ran up to share the lead halfway, held ground until got tired near the 200 M, soon faded.
Taken to the rear from gate 13, took time to pick up early in the home straight, made some late progress final 200 M.
Taken rearward from the widest alley and travelled 7Ls off the speed, responded only fairly when asked for efforts in the home straight, failed to make up any ground.
Widely drawn, taken to a 3-wide spot near the rear, shifted widest for home, gave no response when asked for efforts, made no progress in the home straight.
Lacked early speed as usual, pushed hard to hold a 4-wide spot in midfield, travelled with no cover throughout the trip, crept closer rounding the bend, got tired 300 M out, gave ground.
Bumped at start. pushed up to share the lead on rail, held ground until got tired near the 200 M pole, weakened sharply.
Slow to begin, travelled 5Ls off the pace on rail, disunited in action 350 M out, eased out. (Lame left fore.)
Positive break, assumed race spot 3Ls off pace 2 wide with cover, travelled well to bend, loomed up and took over at 300 M, scored nicely.
Crowded at start, faded back to tail, 8Ls back on rails throughout, saved ground turning and slightly crowded at 400 M, finally clear at 150 M and did best work late.
Slotted into running line 5Ls away in mid-section, same margin down to bend, came to middle of course and closed soundly for 3rd.
Began fairly, pushed up to race in midfield 4Ls back on rails, had an easy time to bend, kept coming in straight and went down in 3 way go for place.
Prominent from outset, raced outside leader on a decent tempo, led briefly at 250 M, lost place final 150 M.
Crowded early and taken back from an awkward draw, 3 wide 6 to 7Ls back in mid-section, cut back to inside in straight and made some late ground without threatening.
Restrained from outside alley, 3 wide 7Ls or so away, had cover to turn, still well back and came widest in straight, made some nice ground late.
Away smoothly, took closer order than usual, raced 2Ls back to bend, niggled turning and looked a place hope but didn't find much and faded final furlong.
Pressed on to take up running from a wide gate, rolled along OK in front, pressured from turn at there to 200 M, no response thereafter.
Drifted back from an awkward draw, raced 3 and 4 wide at rear 7Ls back, did too much work on bend, spent force final 300 M.
Moderate jump, midfield 3 wide with cover 5 to 6Ls back, made some ground on bend, 1 paced in straight.
No early speed, settled in rear division 6 to 7Ls back in running line, had pace to suit, found little in run home, just battling late.
No early speed, settled 6Ls or so away on rails, quiet time to turn, didn't respond in straight. (Rider lost whip at 300 M.)
Out in line, pressed on but raced 2 to 3 wide in mid-section, 4 to 5Ls back on bend, found little in run home.

In first few, rolled forward to take up running before 1000 M bend, held 1L lead until joined turning for home, just held off runners-ups' late challenge throughout closing stages.

Soon led, crossed to rails and steadied pace on stables bend, ceded advantage to eventual winner before 1000 M bend and tracked him to straight, responded to strong pressure on rails after straightening only to fail by a narrow margin.
Began fairly, ridden along to muster early pace and never far off, took closer order coming off the Rock, disputed lead into straight, fought on under pressure to miss narrowly.
Began awkwardly losing ground, never better than midfield to straight, fought on steadily to be nearest at finish.
Trailed the field to straight, taken widest turning in, made up ground under pressure down centre of track to be nearest at finish.
Travelled on rails in midfield, came off the rails for a run entering straight, ran home one-paced. (Mucus.)
Midfield most of way to halfway, became 3L 4th when pace slackened after the Rock, gave ground gradually in straight.

Broke well from a wide draw, close up when badly checked and lost about 2Ls approaching 1000 M bend, travelled in 3L 4th down far side and then 5th after the Rock, in similar position turning for home, found nothing under pressure.
Ridden for speed immediately after jump, gradually shuffled backward to be wide in midfield far side, remained similar turning for home, found nothing under pressure.
Well back, very wide turning for home, not much room after straightening, made no impression thereafter.
Began moderately and bumped a runner losing ground, travelled mainly in midfield to straight, found nothing under pressure in the run home.
Soon taken back to race in rear, saved ground on inside turning in, made no impression.
Parked 3 back the fence. Hit the front passing the 100 M and held on to post a sound win.
Slow to begin settling in last position. Swung widest in the straight and rattled home strongly.
Ridden along early and dictated terms in front. Set a leisurely pace but couldn't repel challengers over the final stages.
Made this run from back in the field after settling 2 deep with cover. Commenced a forward move passing the 500 M, coursing wide from that point on. Closed off well to make the frame.
Began awkwardly settling handy, 2 deep with cover. Peeled out passing the 700 M, however was left 3-wide without cover thereafter. Kept on evenly in the run to the line.
Raced behind midfield 2-wide with cover. Had to be checked off heels after the 500 M, but recovered to rally fairly in the final stretch.
Had cover, 3 deep in a midfield position. Only plodded to the finishing line.
Stalked the leader along the fence. Had every chance but faded in the latter stages.
Camped outside the leader in the early and middle stages. Was unable to hold its position and was crossed after the 700 M gave ground steadily soon after.
Unsettled before the start then travelled with the backmakers 3-wide with cover. Was left 4-wide without cover after the 600 M. Struggled in the home straight.
Worked hard in the early and middle stages to obtain a forward position but coursed wide and without cover until shifting in to race 1 off in 2nd spot near the 700 M. Never likely.
Settled with the backmakers along the fence. Vet reported post race that the horse was displaying an irregular heart rhythm.
Driven early from wide barrier to take up a forward position. Cut to the fence and led 800 M out. 2Ls clear turning into home. Ran on and was never challenged.
Jumped well but trapped 3-wide. Elected to sit 2-wide at midfield first turn. Urged along back straight to maintain position. Did the best of the rest in the straight but no hope with the winner.
Behind leader on fence to home straight. Ridden out but couldn't get close to the leader. Hung on for 2nd until closing stages.
Quickly into stride. Elected to sit ahead of midfield on fence after first turn. Pressed home turn and was 4Ls down into final stretch. Progressed steadily to the line to make frame.
Began well and was eased to find cover. Ended up 2-wide behind midfield 900 M out. Swung out and was 6Ls off on straightening. Made good headway thereafter.
3-wide towards rear early. Shifted 2-wide near the Rock. Pressured 500 M and was 7Ls away turning in. Covered decent good thereafter.
Slow to begin. Failed to muster despite effort of rider and raced towards rear on fence to home turn. Over 10Ls back rounding home turn. Finished off fairly well.
Away in line from high draw. Soon taken towards rear but still caught wide to home straight. Some improvement late. home straight.
Slowly away. Shaken up wide early and parked 2-wide behind pace 900 M out. Failed to pick up in the straight. Weakened final 100 M.
Taken to race 2-wide at rear from widest barrier. Same only position leaving home turn. Beat tired runners home.
Began awkwardly and lost ground. Soon resumed to midfield on fence. Hard ridden home turn but found nothing. Faded inside 150 M.
Behind midfield on fence early. Struggled home turn. Beaten well before the post.
Taken back from wide draw, last on rail, urged turn, rail run, led 50 M out, won going away.
Fair break, up three wide to midfield urged, wide bid, ran on strongly.
Fair break, up to third, found rail, squeezed between horses straight to lead 200 M out, kept on when caught.
Fair break, reined back to midfield one off, improved wide turn, ran on but no extra close home.
Good break, settled fourth on rail, out to challenge straight but found very little room, ran on quite well when clear.
Fair break, dropped out and held up third last rail, rail bid straight, kept on but not pace to challenge.
Fair break, reined back to settle rear one off, improved turn, wide bid, ran on, not pace to challenge.
Fair break, not rushed early, settled fourth last one off, wide turn, then switched inside, kept on.
Broke well, not rushed early, settled sixth on rail, looked for run in crowded mid-pack, slight check, pulled out, no extra.
Well away, settled behind leaders in fourth one off, hard ridden to challenge straight, weakened late.
Good break, up very fast to lead and cross, headed 200 M out, weakened.
Fair break, up very wide to share lead two off, second into straight, weakened quickly.
Taken back from wide gate, third last rail, last leaving back, improved wide, ran on strongly to lead 150 M out.
Moderate start, ridden early to take position fourth last one off, urged to improve mid-track, kept on well, outpaced.
Good break, third on rail, slipped back turn, ridden, challenged between horses, just outpaced.
Moderate start, midfield three off, improved wide turn, led mid-straight, unable to resist wide closers.
Broke well, led rail then settled second, lost place slightly approaching turn, out to challenge, one pace.
Broke well shared early then went on, three clear then slowed pace, led until mid-straight, weakened.
Broke well, settled sixth rail, lost place far side, second last into straight, rail bid, modest progress.
Fair break, not much early, settled mid-rear rail, lost place as field quickened, some late headway under driving.
Broke well, taken back to rear from wide, improved wide into turn, no further progress under pressure.
Fair break, fourth one off, then up to second, ridden entering turn, no further progress, weakened.
Slight bobble start, settled rear one off, improved wide far side and turn, ridden, weakened.
Good break, lacked early pace, midfield one off, bustled far side, no response, weakened.
Pushed to keep up in midfield, 2-1/2Ls off the good pace along the rails, made steady ground 200 M to win, not fully tested.
Pushed to hold the rail and shared the lead at good pace, hung on until 150 M overhauled, ran on for 2nd.
Very slow away, at back, but on the fence, 4-1/2Ls off the good pace, progressed steadily 300 M for 3rd.
Eased to rear, 6Ls off the good pace on the fence, held up and checked 300 M, made ground when clear. made gradual ground final 200 M.
At rear, 5-1/2Ls off the good pace 2-wide, made ground 200 M.
Eased to sit in midfield, 2-1/2Ls off the good pace 2-wide, no progress.
Slow away, hard ridden forward, just off the good pace 3-wide, flattened 200 M.
Hard ridden to obtain a spot in midfield 4-wide, 2-1/2Ls off the good pace, lost too much ground at bends, ran on ok.
In front of midfield, 2-1/2Ls off the good pace 3-wide, flattened 200 M.
Eased to sit behind midfield, 3-1/2Ls off the good pace, trapped 4-wide throughout and lost too much ground, flattened in straight.
Pushed forward, 1L off the good pace, trapped 4-wide throughout and lost too much ground, emptied in straight.
Shared lead 2-wide, pace good, dropped off 300 M.
Broke well, pushed up to lead and found the rail just before the first turn, quickened well when asked for efforts 350 M out, kept on soundly to score.
Awkward start, urged along early and settled in a fence position in midfield, on heels at home turn, kicked strongly when asked 300 M out, blocked at 100 M, finished off well for 2nd.
Given a waiting ride and settled one from the rear on rail, responded well when asked for efforts 300 M out, ran on soundly for 3rd.
Prominently placed in the one-out-one-back spot, kept on satisfactorily when asked for efforts at top of the home straight, bumped at 200 M, couldn't find extra final 50 M.
Jumped fast, settled one-off in midfield, kept on fairly well when placed under pressure in the home straight, but lacked a decisive kick to challenge the principals.
Jumped well, settled cozily in the box-seat, kept on fairly when placed under pressure early in the home straight, bumped at 200 M, checked at 50 M, flattened.
Lacked early speed and travelled 4Ls off pace, proved difficult to settle in the early stages, checked at 1200 M, niggled along at home turn, made gradual ground final 300 M.
Taken back from gate 8 and travelled 6Ls off the pace at rear, bumped when improving along 5-deep rounding the home turn, finished off fairly, only passed a few tired runners.
Awkwardly drawn, caught 4-wide with no cover throughout the trip, bumped at home turn, failed to make up any ground in the straight.
Settled in a 3-wide spot near the rear, on heels at 1000 M, niggled along rounding the home turn, badly checked at 200 M, never recovered. (Blood in trachea.)
Broke well, settled 3-wide 2Ls off the speed, travelled with no cover, outpaced at home turn, weakened sharply at the top of the home straight, dropped out.
Settled in a 3-wide spot in midfield, struggled rounding the home turn, soon weakened and gave ground, bumped at 200 M, tailed out.
Urged lightly to maintain a position in midfield, well covered throughout the race, taken outside 350 M, picked up strongly, surged to the front 100 M out and won in fine style.
Crossed to a 3-wide position from draw 12 and not far off leaders, responded well under pressure, ran on soundly but was firmly put aside by the winner inside 100 M.
Away in good order, quickly moved to the lead but was pressed by a rival throughout, battled on well in front, overhauled near 100 M but managed to hang on for 3rd.
Began awkwardly and lost ground at the start, raced in a rearward position 6Ls off leaders, advanced passing 700 M, finished well down the outside final 300 M and just missed out 3rd place.

Driven early but unable to cross, sat back in a 2-wide position within striking distance, pushed along 500 M out and held every chance turning in, kept on effort and could have challenged for 3rd if wasn't steadied inside 100 M.
First to jump, guided to the rail and raced ahead of midfield, loomed a threat 200 M but flattened out in late stages.
Urged to race with leaders, restrained to sit in 3rd passing 700 M, didn't find extra pace to challenge leaving the home bend, one-paced throughout.
Held a fence position on jumping from draw 1, raced with mid-pack throughout, guided to outside passing 350 M, ran home one paced.

Switched off after the start and raced in detached last about 9Ls behind leader, made some progress in straight without threatening, held up over final 50 M and was not properly tested over the concluding stages.
Checked at the start and near 1100 M, ended up racing in 2nd last about 7Ls off the pace, found very little under pressure inside 400 M, never a threat.
Began well but lost considerable amount of ground when checked near 1100 M, shuffled back to near last turning in and came up empty in the drive.
Caught wide early, crossed to 2-wide passing halfway and dueled for lead, run ended nearing 200 M then weakened rapidly.

Settled within striking distance after beginning from the coveted outside rails draw, moved up to join leader coming onto course proper, hit front under pressure over 200 M out, won readily.
Never far off, came to challenge holding some chance from 400 to 150 M out, outsprinted by winner close to home.
Always thereabouts down the centre of the track, ran home one-paced under pressure inside final 200 M.
Settle well back, responded well to hard driving coming onto course proper, ran on to be nearest at finish.
In similar better than midfield position throughout, kept on same pace to the line over an apparently insufficient trip.
Broke well to lead, held front-runner position until joined passing 400 M when rider dropped his whip, shifted in while giving ground in the run to the line.
Travelled about 3Ls off the speed in midfield, ran home one-paced.
Closer up early, came under pressure coming onto course proper, found nothing.
Soon dropped to last few, never posed any danger.
Trailed the main field most of the way, never seen with a chance. (Bled.)
Close up briefly, dropped backward under pressure from halfway out. (Questioned for disappointing performance.)
Began with others, never travelled better than midfield, dropped out tamely.
Began moderately, travelled about two to three lengths off the speed, faded out from 400 M.
Reared jumping out and badly blundered and almost dislodged rider losing considerable ground, ignore run.
Blundered on jumping then settled behind midfield the fence. Got all the favors along the inside and after peeling off the fence near the 200, kept up a good gallop to claim the price.
Camped 3 back the rail. Had every chance after hitting the front near the 200m.
Led early the handed up approaching the 700m and travelled in the sweet seat behind the leader. Couldn't find any extra over the concluding stages.
Didn't enjoy the best of runs in transit and got shuffled back in the early stages, settling near the rear. 2-3 wide with cover. Ran on soundly to make the frame.
Raced greenly through the middle stages and lost its position on a couple of occasions to travel worse than midfield 2 deep with cover. Ran on reasonably along the inside.
Sent forward and crossed to lead along the fence after the 800m. Faded passing the 200m.
Settled towards the tail of the field 2 wide with cover. Failed to close off.
Did plenty of work to cross from a wide gate to eventually park outside the leader near the 700m. faded inside the final furlong.
Began awkwardly then copped a savage check when racing greenly and shifting out across heels near the 800m whilst travelling near the rear of the field along the paint. Never a factor.
Didn't jump cleanly and was wide early but managed to settle midfield 2-3 deep with cover on the circle. Copped a bump rounding the home turn and was never in the hunt afterwards.
Raced behind midfield 3 deep with cover. Struggled in the run home. (Vet reported that the horse had pulled up with mucopus in the trachea.)
Taken back from a wide gate to settle at the tail of the field 2 deep with cover. Rolled out 1 further position after the 700m, but gave in tamely thereafter.

Well enough away. Taken to sit 3-wide behind midfield from 1400M. Cut to 2-wide near 1000M. Swung out and was 4Ls off on straightening. Finished off strongly and asserted authority inside final furlong.

Detached early despite effort of rider. Reached the back of the field passing 1000M. Hard ridden wide from 700M and was 7Ls adrift turning in. No hope with the winner but kept dashing to the line well.

Began in line but trapped wide. Gradually taken to 2-wide towards rear. Shifted 3-wide to make run from 600M and was 6Ls down turning into home. Covered good ground to snatch 3rd at post but was well beaten by the front pair.
Sat outside leader early. Pressed from 750M to maintain position. Hit front 400M. Caught final furlong but fought gamely to make frame.
Away with them but caught wide. Slotted 2-wide at midfield 1200M. Switched 4-wide and was 3Ls back into final stretch. One-paced to conclude.
Raced 2-wide behind midfield early. Checked severely near 1000M. Took inside run and was 5Ls away rounding home turn. Made up decent ground through runners home.
Slow to begin. Shaken up along the fence to take box seat from 1500M. Every chance in the straight but just plugged on.
Out in line but trapped wide. Gradually taken 2-wide behind midfield at 1200M. Shifted out entering home straight and ran on steadily before checked at 150M. Kept on once resumed.
Began fairly well. Gradually eased 2-wide ahead of midfield from 1400M. Well positioned to strike in the straight but couldn't turn up a notch. No extra closing stages.
Driven early and took fence ahead of midfield from 1300M. Found nothing when asked in the straight.
Towards rear to home straight. Beat tired runners home.
Led on fence until swamped 250M. (Mucopus and "roarer").
Midfield on fence to home straight. Never picked up. (Mucopus).
Slowly away but soon resumed one-out-one-back. Beaten soon after straightening.
Broke well, led early, crossed to rail, kept on strongly.
Broke well, always just outside leader one off, narrow lead halfway, kept on, just held.
Fair break, wide early, joined main group, kept on well down centre.
Broke well, trailed second overracing slightly, hard ridden and no extra late.
Well away, not rushed, followed winner, outpaced and hard ridden mid-race, kept on late.
Moderate start, urged to midfield four off, hard ridden 300m out, no real progress.
Good break, midfield position after moving towards rail, ridden halfway, no real progress.
Moderate break, mid-rear ridden, kept on from halfway but no impact.
Moderate break, rousted early, crossed to rail, kept on but always outpaced.
Not well away, last early, short of room, then ran on quite well mid-track.
Broke well, moved across to join main group, ridden halfway, no progress.
Fair break, short of early speed, urged before halfway, drifted wide, no progress.
Fair break, up to second rank mid-track, ridden halfway, weakened, eased late.
Reared start but without losing much ground, ridden well before halfway, weakened quickly, eased.
Fast break, led and crossed comfortably, kicked early straight, always holding opposition.
Broke well, ridden up wide to take second one off, tried to challenge straight, always held.
Fair break, settled mid-rear one off, improved wide turn and straight, kept on well until run flattened late.
Fair break, not rushed, settled third last one off, ran on under strong driving.
Moderate break, taken back to second last two off, ridden early straight, kept on wide.
Moderate break, lacked early pace, raced more generously entering turn, wide bid, kept on but never threatened.
Fair break, ridden early, midfield three off, wide bid, reached third briefly, weakened.
Fair break, hard ridden early, midfield one off, tried for gap between horses straight, slight check, no progress thereafter.
Broke well, up to fifth one off, ridden turn, found little.
Broke well, settled third on rail, fourth into straight, ridden, no further progress.
Broke well, up to third one off, third into straight on rail, ridden, weakened.
Moderate break, short of early pace, settled fourth last rail, ridden entering straight, found little.
Broke well, up to join leaders four wide, fourth into straight, ridden, weakened.
Clumsy start, last early, ridden up along rail to midfield, shaken up entering straight, found nil, eased late.
Eased to sit slightly in advance of midfield, 4.5Ls off the good pace 2 wide, closed the race off strongly 300M to score its first victory.
Pushed to sit in front of midfield, 3Ls off the good pace 2 wide, ran on well to the line for 2nd.
Pushed early, 3Ls off the good pace along the fence, blocked 4-2, progressed steadily when clear and grabbed 3rd.
Eased back, 6.5Ls off the good pace, trapped 3 wide throughout, progressed steadily 300M despite hanging out badly.
Hard ridden to take rail in front and led by 1.5Ls at good sectionals, hung on strongly until 100M overhauled, ran on OK.
Midfield, 5Ls off the good pace along the rails, held up badly in straight, made ground when clear.
Behind midfield, 6.5Ls off the good pace on the fence, blocked most straight, made good ground when clear.
Slow to muster at rear, 9.5Ls off the good pace 2-3 wide, made steady ground 200M.
Eased at start, 8.5Ls off the good pace on the fence, progressed steadily 200M.
Eased back as usual, 7.5Ls off the good pace 2 wide, lacked room 400M, made minor ground when clear.
Pushed to obtain a midfield spot, 5Ls off the good pace, trapped 3 wide no cover throughout, no turn of foot.
Eased at start, 6Ls off the good pace 2 wide, no progress.
Hard ridden forward, 1.5Ls off the good pace 2 wide, soon emptied 300M.
Hard ridden forward, box seat, pace good, lack room 4-2, weakened when clear.
Slow to begin, soon caught up and settled 3Ls behind the leaders, kicked strongly when asked for efforts 300 M out, hit the front 200 M out, drew clear easily.
Broke well, prominently placed 3Ls off the speed, responded well when asked for efforts 400 M out, finished off soundly for 2nd.
Pushed up and soon settled 1L off the speed, urged along halfway, quickened well when asked near the 400 M pole, kept on soundly for 3rd, crowded at 50 M.
Broke well, settled 2-3Ls off the speed, responded satisfactorily when asked for efforts 400 M out, kept on for 4th.
Broke well, prominently placed just behind the speed, blocked from the 400 M to 200 M, finished off fairly well when clear 150 M out, rather one-paced.
Settled cozily 1.5Ls off the pace, kept on satisfactorily when asked for efforts 350 M out, caught by the winner at 200 M, couldn't find extra final 100 M, crowded at 50 M.
Jumped fast, easily ran up to lead 1L on the grandstand side, held ground, headed 200 M out, soon flattened.
Started awkwardly, restrained just behind the leader, passed 400 M out, got tired near the 200 M pole, soon faded.
Broke well, taken to a midfield spot with cover, niggled along 400 M out, failed to make up any ground.
Urged along early and travelled 3Ls off the pace, struggled halfway, soon faded. (Moderate left sided laryngeal paralysis and mucus.)
Settled 3Ls off the speed, gave no response when asked for efforts 400 M out, failed to make any progress. (Bled.)
Jumped well, prominently placed just behind the leader, got tired near the 400 M pole, soon dropped out.
Settled 2Ls behind the leader, outpaced near the 400 M pole, soon dropped out.
Pushed up early and travelled 3Ls off the pace, outpaced halfway, soon weakened sharply, finished tailed out.
In midfield, came off the rail nearing 700M, badly held up for clear running 450M-400M, finished off willingly with a clear run final 300M, led 50M out and held off challenges from outside late on.
Positioned 3-wide towards the rear, shaken up inside 500M, finished off the race well and was nearest to winner at the line.
Reserved in a 3-wide position near the rear, swung widest into straight, closed with a belated rally beaten only a neck. Promising first up.
Placed in mid-division, made a 3-wide move round the turn, made smooth progress to hit the front near 200M, flattened inside 100M and relinquished the lead close home.
Behind midfield, held up early straight, made good headway to loom a threat 250M out, outpaced final 100M.
Sped to the front from a wide barrier, led uncontested to 600M, headed mid-straight but still in contention for a minor placing until finding no extra inside 100M.
Towards the rear 7Ls off leader, moved closer when pace slackened round the turn, rallied mildly along the inside rail, kept on to the line but failed to seriously threaten.
Guided to the rail soon after the start and raced behind midfield 5-6Ls from leader, moved closer 500M out, ran on without threatening.
Chased leader in a race ran at good tempo, kept on same pace to 150M then dropped away rapidly. (Jockey said his horse had failed to run out 1800M.)
Refused to stride out in early stages and lost a considerable amount of ground, ended up 9Ls off the pace, moved closer nearing the top of straight but lacked a closing response when driven.
In chasing group along the inside, always in touch, came off the rail halfway round the turn, run ended 300M and dropped out of contention.
Caught racing behind runners in early stages, switched outside and moved forward to track leader, had nothing left when put to test passing 350M, weakened rapidly.
Niggled along to stay in touch with the field after a slow start, in last place for most of the trip, came up empty in the straight, eased 200M out and beaten over 20Ls.
Fractious in the barriers, took early lead then restrained to a spot ahead of midfield, moved to a striking position 500M out but soon dropped away, heavily eased. (Unacceptable performance.)
Prominently placed in the box-seat, bumped at 500 M when looking for clear run, quickened well when asked 350 M out, hit the front 150 M out, kept on soundly to score.
Taken back from gate 12 and travelled 7Ls away at the rear, blocked early in the home straight, kicked strongly when clear at 250 M, ran on soundly for 2nd.
Broke well, soon taken rearward, proved difficult to settle when restrained, checked at 1200 M, blocked at the top of home straight, kicked when clear at 250 M, ran on well for 3rd.
Taken back from gate 11 and travelled 5Ls off the speed, improved along the inner part of the home straight final 250 M, ran on soundly, just missed a place.
Settled one-off in the mid-division, crowded at 450 M, kept on fairly well when placed under pressure, but lacked a decisive kick to challenge the principals.
Out in line, urged along to hold a 3-wide spot 2Ls off the pace, checked and carried wide at 500 M, only one-paced when placed under pressure in the home straight.
Jumped only fairly, pushed up to share the lead and found the fence near the 800 M, kept on well when asked at the top of the home straight, passed 150 M out, soon flattened.
Restrained to a 3-wide spot 4Ls off the pace, responded only fairly when asked for efforts in the home straight, rather one-paced.
Pushed up early to hold a fence position 4Ls off the pace, checked 250 M out, recovered gradually and made some late progress final 150 M.
Lacked early speed, travelled 5Ls off the pace, urged along at the home turn, responded satisfactorily when asked 400 M out, made gradual ground, couldn't find extra final 100 M.
Jumped only fairly, settled cozily 2-3Ls off the speed on rail, held ground until flattened at 200 M.
Broke well, prominently placed 2Ls off the pace, checked at 1200 M, bumped and carried wide at 500 M, held ground until flattened 250 M out.
Widely drawn, lacked early speed despite being urged along, drifted back gradually towards the rear, failed to make up any ground in the home straight.
Jumped fast, urged along to share the lead on 2-deep, caught at 400 M, soon weakened, finished tailed out.
Began in line, pressed on from wider gate to slot in behind leader, tracked even speed to turn, eased out and soon took over at 300 M, ran away for convincing win.
Limited early speed, 5Ls or so back on rails, not used in mid-section, drove through passing 300 M and closed soundly for 2nd although no match for winner.
Out with rest, planted 3 wide in midfield 4 to 5Ls back, not much cover to bend, kept coming down centre on track and did well to place given workload.
No early dash, behind midfield 6Ls or so back, saved ground on rails throughout, held up to 200 M, dashed well when clear and unlucky not to place.
Awkwardly away, assumed a midfield role, 4Ls back in running line, eased wider turning, looked a place chance on turning but didn't go on final furlong.
Took a little closer order than usual just held midfield 6Ls back to bend, didn't sprint as usual and just battled away behind them in straight.
Well enough away, raced 3 to 4Ls back along rails, enjoyed an easy trip to turn, made a brief effort turning but lacked extra gear, faded late.
Began well, settled not far away from speed, raced first without cover 2 wide 4Ls back, closed on turning to be 1L down, didn't see out trip final 300 M.
Jumped with more purpose, slotted in 1 out 1 back spot from tricky alley, 3Ls down to bend, made brief effort at 250 M but didn't let down and was disappointing in finish.
Drifted right back from a wide gate, 8Ls away on rails sharing rear, well back to bend, no close and beat tired runners home.
Awkwardly away, ended up 3 wide behind midfield, 7Ls off top end, had a trail on circle, came wide but didn't make an impression in straight.
No early pace, settled last from outside gate, 8Ls back throughout, offered nothing in run home.
Fast away and led easily, ran along 2Ls clear, collared at 300 M and faded soon after.

Soon taken across from a wide gate to trail the field, waited with, loomed up down grandstand side of straight to snatch victory on line.
Soon took up running and attempted to make all holding 1L advantage most of way, died on its run inside final 100 M and swamped late.

Raced wide searching for a prominent spot early, settled in 4th just over 3Ls off the speed turning into far side, took closer order but wider swinging for home, sustained steady headway under pressure down centre of track.
Began with others, settled on rails in rear of midfield, in similar position turning in, fought on steadily to be nearest at finish.
Began well, chased leader on rails to straight, came under pressure turning in, kept on same pace without quickening.
Began with others, soon settled on rails in midfield in 5th, came under pressure after straightening, kept on steadily without quickening.
Settled in midfield after beginning from a wide gate, remained similar for remainder of race, only produced moderate impression late in straight.
Soon crossed from the widest gate to settle in rear of field, made some late progress past beaten runners in the run to the line.
Began with others, settled in 4th and then 3rd within 3Ls of pace, saved ground when one-back on rails turning for home, kept on before fading inside final 100 M.
Slow out, settled towards the rear, produced some late impression closing stages.
Slightly slow out, settled in rear of midfield, slightly worse rounding home bend and into straight, ran home one-paced.
Began awkwardly, soon dropped to last few, wide turning into straight, fought nil under pressure.
Went straight to the lead along the fence. Found plenty early in the straight and managed to repel a late challenge to claim the prize.
Came from second last position, straightened 3 deep, was steadied briefly near the furlong before accelerating quickly. Eye catching finish but just failed to snatch victory.
Box seated. Finished off soundly.
Made its run from third last position. Railed up in final stretch and closed off well to finish in the frame.
Couldn't match the early speed of the race and settled in last position. Came down the outside and motored to the line over the last 200 M.
Did itself no favors by overracing when travelling handy to the leaders, 3 deep with cover. Battled on gamely to the wire.
Camped 1 out 1 back. Had every chance but was somewhat flat at the business end of the race.
Raced midfield the fence. kept on one paced in the run to the line.
Travelled 3-wide with cover behind midfield. Brought to the outside in the straight but only plodded to the line.
Speared forward but was unable to cross and was posted 3-wide without cover on the circle, whilst in the leading division. Faded over the final furlong.
Began awkwardly the settled behind midfield, 2-wide with cover. Failed to make any impression in the run home.
Not the best to begin then was ridden along to race prominently but was caught wide and without cover for most of the trip. Never likely.
Behind leader on fence to home straight. Powered clear inside 250 M. Proved too strong for the rest.
Near the pace on fence after start. Checked to midfield first turn. Pressed home turn. Got clear run final 300 M. Did the best of the rest but was outclassed by the winner.
Taken 2-wide at rear from high draw. Swung wide and was 6Ls down on straightening. Covered substantial ground for a minor placing.
Began well. Eased to sit behind midfield on fence first turn. Peeled out and was 5Ls away turning in. Made up minor ground in run home.
Dropped to rear on fence. Took inside run home turn. 5Ls off into final stretch. Plugged on but not threatening.
2-wide ahead of midfield to home straight. One-paced to conclude.
Trapped wide and without cover ahead of midfield, slotted 2-wide midfield passing 600 M. No extra in the straight. straight.
Led one-off early. Found the fence approaching home turn and held a 1L advantage turning into home. Soon caught by the winner and weakened final 200 M.
Travelled wide behind midfield throughout. Never nearer.
Never far off the pace. Found nothing when asked final 300 M. Faded final furlong. (Mucopus.)
At midfield early. Struggled home turn. No impression in the straight.
Never better than midfield early. Couldn't follow home turn. Beaten well before the post. (Mucopus.)
Broke well, not rushed, settled sixth one off, brought wide to challenge, ran on strongly, held on.
Slight bobble start, ridden early, midfield rail, wide bid straight, ran on strongly, just failed.
Fair break, reined back to fourth last rail, slight check far side, rail bid, finished well.
Missed beat start, not rushed, fifth rail, ran on between horses, not quite pace to challenge.
Fair break, one off in fourth, ridden entering straight, kept on.
Fast away, up wide but unable to lead, second one off, led briefly mid-straight, weakened.
Taken back to last rail, tried to improve wide straight, not pace to challenge.
Fair break, taken back to second last one off, urged far side, improved turn, kept on but no extra.
Fair break, taken back to third last one off, aimed for run between horses straight, gradually making ground when ran out of room late.
Broke well, back to midfield two off, vigorously ridden entering turn and in straight, kept on but never able to challenge.
Broke well, led and crossed, led going well into straight, ridden, weakened quickly.
Broke well, settled third on rail, ridden, found nil.
Fair break, taken back, then improved wide turn, finished very strongly wide.
Fair break, midfield one off, ran on between horses, finished well.
Fair break, up to midfield one off, wide challenge, ran on well.
Well away, ridden early to lead, two lengths clear ridden but still clear mid straight, weakened.
Fast break, ridden to join lead, settled fourth on rail, hard ridden straight, no further progress.
Broke well, short of early pace, third last rail, improved straight until hampered and short of room, kept on.
Well away, midfield rail, rail bid straight, no progress.
Fair break, taken back to rear, improved between runners straight, run flattened late.
Well away, up wide to join leaders, caught three wide in fifth, ridden, weakened straight.
Fair break, ridden early to lead, settled second, urged early straight, weakened.
Very poor break, then stumbled, tailed off last, no chance thereafter.
Fair break, third two off, ridden early straight, weakened quickly.
Pushed to obtain a midfield spot along the fence, 1-1/2Ls off the leader in main bunch, closed the race off strongly 300 M to score a comfortable win.
Eased to rear, 7Ls off the leader in main bunch 2-wide, favoured by the fast pace, progressed steadily 250 M and took 2nd.
Eased to sit behind midfield, 3-1/2Ls off the leader in main bunch along the fence, benefited by the fast tempo, made ground in straight for 3rd.
Eased back, 4Ls off the leader in main bunch 2 to 3-wide, favoured by the fast pace, made steady ground 200 M.
Pushed to sit 2-1/2Ls off the leader in main bunch 2-wide, helped by the fast pace, just ran on ok in straight.
Settled 1L off the leader in main bunch 2 to 3-wide, not suited by the fast tempo, made good ground 300 M, run ended 100 M.
Eased back, 5-1/2Ls off the leader in main bunch 2-wide, benefited by the fast pace, lacked room 4-2, ran on ok when clear.
Hard ridden to cross in front, 5Ls behind the extremely fast sectionals, led by 1L in main bunch, weakened 200 M.
Very slow away, 5-1/2Ls off the leader in main bunch along the fence, favoured by the fast tempo, however no progress late. (Tendon injury next day.)
Eased back, 5-1/2Ls off the leader in main bunch, suited by the fast pace but trapped 3-wide throughout, no progress.
Hard ridden to hold the rail in the lead with extremely fast sectionals, 5Ls ahead of main bunch, faded 300 M. (See racing incidents.)
Hard ridden forward, shared the lead at extremely fast sectionals, 5Ls ahead of the main bunch, dropped off 300 M. (See racing incidents.)
Given a waiting ride and travelled 6Ls off the pace, responded well when asked for efforts at the top of the home straight, ran on strongly, hit the front 50 M out, won easily.
Broke well, settled one-off just behind the leaders, ran on to contest the lead early in the home straight, briefly led near the 150 M, caught by the winner at 50 M.
Jumped well, urged along to lead 1L on rail, responded well when placed under pressure at the top of the home straight, headed at 150 M, kept on well for 3rd.
Cozily placed 2 to 3Ls off the speed on rail, had every chance in the home straight, only one-paced when asked for efforts, kept on for 4th.
Niggled along to hold a one-off spot in the mid-division, on heels at 1400 M, made up gradual ground under pressure final 400 M, rather one-paced.
Caught 3-wide in the mid-division throughout the trip, on heels at 1400 M, lost cover halfway, only one-paced when asked for efforts in the home straight.
Pushed up early and soon found a one-off spot just off the speed, on heels at the home turn, responded only fairly when asked for efforts in the straight, flattened at 150 M.
Taken rearward from gate 9 and travelled 7Ls off the speed, on heels at 400 M, swung wide for home, only covered little ground in the straight.
Taken back and travelled 7Ls away at the rear, swung widest for home, only made limited progress in the straight.
Started awkwardly and crowded, sat 4Ls off the pace on rail, proved difficult to settle in the early stages, gave no response when asked in the home straight, never competitive.
Taken rearward from gate 8 and travelled 6Ls off the pace, on heels at 1400 M, failed to make up ground in the home straight.
Raced handy but caught 3-wide with no cover early, on heels at 1400 M, pushed up to track the leader halfway, struggled round the home turn, soon weakened, finished tailed out.
In midfield off the inside and well covered, made the most of an uninterrupted run down the centre of straight, dueled with the runner-up for 250 M and gained upper hand in late stages.
Behind midfield in 8th position, out to center of track and made smooth progress from 350 M, held narrow lead final 100 M, fought on determinedly to hold off the winner and was just denied.
Restrained to a rearward position 5Ls off the pace and forced wide throughout, began to move closer halfway round the turn, finished willingly but could not catch the first two.
Switched off to the rear and not used to 350 M, checked near 250 M when making his run, altered course and finished off the race well.
Blundered at the start but soon recovered to race behind leaders, loomed a threat 300 M but couldn't sustain effort, one paced final 150 M.
Held up behind midfield along the fence, hampered near 200 M but was no real threat afterwards when presented with clear running.
Close up tracking leader off the inside, made a short lived effort 300 M, outpaced final 150 M.
Dropped back to the rear about 5Ls from leader, inclined to hang out throughout the race and could not be ridden out properly in the straight. (Unacceptable racing manners.)
Began awkwardly, settled 3-wide in the group chasing the pace, driven 350 M out but found very little in the finish.
In the 2-path pressing the leader, not quickened under pressure in early straight, weakened steadily over the final 150 M.
Unable to cross and caught wide at the front for most of the trip, came up empty leaving the bend, soon behind and eased.
Led steadily, lost the lead soon after turning in, gave way rapidly and eased.

Bumped at start but gradually improved from a wide barrier to join leaders, eventually took up running coming out of back straight, soon drew clear after straightening, won easily.

Soon taken across for rails run at the back from the widest gate, well behind until effort approaching home turn, switched out for a run after straightening in midfield, fought on to reach remote 2nd 150 M out.
Settled in last few, baulked for a run briefly after straightening, switched to the widest and ran on steadily down centre of straight to reach distant 3rd late.
Rear early, improved to wide in midfield coming out of back straight and similar turning in, kept on steadily under pressure without quickening.
Chased leader mainly in one-out-one-back position, came closer approaching home turn, weakened under pressure inside final 200 M.
Trailed the field, commenced move on top of home bend, fought on steadily without threatening. (Bled.)
Travelled in better than midfield in 4th or 5th, reached 3rd briefly after straightening, found no extra closing stages.
Prominent early, travelled just worse than midfield to straight, ran home one-paced.
Raced 4-wide without cover in midfield, moved closer around the bend, soon faded under pressure.
Broke well, close up hitting front 200 M after start, led until taken over by eventual winner halfway out, settled in 2L 3rd rounding home bend, dropped out tamely soon after straightening.
Settled in midfield on rails, shuffled backward behind a weakening horse around the bend, never recovered in straight. (Mucus.)
Raced freely in midfield, took closer order entering straight, met minor interference after straightening, kept on under pressure before weakening inside final 200 M.
Jumped awkwardly, ridden along but failed to muster out wide far side, remained in last few dropping to tail-end into straight, no further impression.
Not far off early stages, dropped to midfield around the bend, soon weakened after straightening.
Speared across from an outside barrier to race in the lead along the paint by the 900m. Made every post a winner thereafter to record a strong win.
Missed the start then raced on the bridle just behind midfield. Stayed to the inside in the straight and ran on soundly.
Camped 1 out 1 back. Maintained an even gallop right to the wire.
Struck some interference early settling in the box seat. Travelled comfortably in the run but tired over the latter stages.
Settled in last position. Rounded the home turn widest and closed off nicely.
Settled at the tail of the field along the paint. Railed up in the straight and worked home fairly.
Luckless in the run coursing 3-4 wide without cover, behind midfield. Straightened wide and was never likely.
Was prominent early before receiving interference on the first turn and setting 3 back thereafter. Faded over the final 300m.
Raced behind midfield 2 wide with cover. Stayed on at the same speed over the concluding stages. An endoscopic examination after the race showed a substantial amount of blood in the horse's trachea.
Copped a check near the 800m, settling 1 off with cover close to midfield. Looked for runs through the field in the straight but was only one paced in the run home.
Raced near the tail of the field 3-4 wide with cover. Only plodded to the finishing line.

Travelled behind midfield 3 wide with some cover on the circle. Gave ground in the final stretch. An endoscopic examination after the race showed a substantial amount of mucopus in the horse's trachea.
Settled with the backmakers, 2 deep with cover. Struggled in the home straight.
Not the best away but mustered sufficient speed to improve early and parked outside the leader. Was eased down over the final furlong. To trial. (See incident report.)
Travelled wide and without cover at midfield to home straight. Responded well under vigorous riding passing 250 M. Battled determinedly to prevail final stride.
Pressed forward from widest barrier. Eased to one-out-one- back from 1000 M. Every chance when hit front 200 M and fought gamely with the winner to the line. Just failed at post.
2-wide at midfield early and middle stages. Swung 4-wide home turn. Finished off strongly in the straight but couldn't quite catch the front pair.
Pressed early from high draw and sat outside the leader from 900 M. Kept on well top of home straight but couldn't withstand the finishing effort of the front trio close home. (Blood in trachea.)
Ahead of midfield on fence to home straight. Quickened with the principals thereafter until no extra gear final 50 M.
Behind midfield on fence to home straight. Closed off fairly well.
At rear early despite effort of rider. Swung widest turning in and covered substantial ground late.
Towards rear on fence to home straight. Made up good ground thereafter.
Box-seat to home straight. Failed to pick up final 300 M.
Led on fence before overhauled final 250 M. Swamped thereafter.
2-wide at midfield to home straight. Found nothing when asked.
Ran wide behind midfield and dropped out home straight. Never a factor.
Broke well, settled fifth one off, mid track challenge to lead 150 M out, stayed on.
Fair break, held rail in sixth, out to challenge straight, strongly ridden to lead 200 M out, just outstayed.
Well away, tacked across to mid-rear one off, pulled out for mid-track challenge, kept on.
Fair break, taken back to rear, settled second last on rail, ran on between horses under driving straight, not quite pace to challenge.
Fair break, settled third last one off, went for mid pack run and briefly short of room early straight, ran on well when clear.
Fast away, led early then settled fourth on rail, second into straight, challenged leader mid-straight but immediately headed, outstayed.
Fair break, settled midfield one off, tried to challenge between runners straight but not able to take the gap, kept on one pace.
Slightly awkward start, ridden to midfield rail, inside bid straight, kept on but not pace to challenge.
Broke well, aimed for lead but caught eight wide first turn, still led exiting that turn, went six lengths clear, still clear entering straight, ridden and caught 250 M out.
Well away, aimed for lead but caught seven wide first turn, settled midfield two off, tried to improve wide straight, not pace to threaten.
Fair break, taken back to rear, last into straight, wide bid, found little.
Moderate break, taken back to mid-rear three off, wide bid, no progress.
Fair break, ridden for early lead, caught four wide, settled third one off, short of room and unbalanced home turn, weakened.
Fair break, aimed for lead and reached it but headed almost immediately, settled second rail, ridden turn, weakened quickly.
Well away, retain rail settling third, challenged two off to lead 100 M out, kept on strongly.
Fair break, settled midfield one off, rousted early straight and out to challenge, ran on well, just outpaced late.
Not fast away, midfield rail, out to challenge straight, finished well.
Out fast, raced second one off, slightly eager, led mid-straight until caught 150 M out, weakened.
Fair break, taken back to second last one off, improved wide into straight, ran on without pace to threaten.
Fair break, not rushed early, held up mid-rear one off, wide bid, hard ridden, ran on well late.
Fast out, led and crossed, ridden and challenged 200 M out, headed, weakened.
Not well away, settled third last on rail, bustled entering straight, kept on one pace.
Fair break out wide, reined back to rear, last into straight, improved along rail and ran on quite well but never able to challenge.
Well away, up to fourth one off, ridden to challenge early straight, no response, weakened quickly.
Missed break, lost length, up along rail to midfield, rail run, no acceleration.
Fair break, up wide to midfield three off, ridden early straight, no response.
Fair break, back to third last one off, wide bid straight, found nil, eased late.
Fair break, up to fifth three wide, began to lose ground on turn, ridden, beaten, eased.
Hard ridden to cross in front, took rail and shared the lead at advantageous slow sectionals, dominated from 400M.
Pushed early but not muster, 3Ls off the leaders 2-3 wide, not suited by the slow tempo, dashed well 300M to grab 2nd.
Eased at start, 5Ls off the leaders on the fence, not suited by the slow tempo, lack room 400M, dashed strongly to the line for 3rd.
Eased back, 4.5Ls off the leaders, trapped 3-4 wide, harmed by the slow pace, dashed strongly 300M despite all negative racing situations.
Crossed in front easily and shared the lead at slow sectionals, ran on until 150M flattened.
Eased back, 6Ls off the leaders 2-3 wide, dashed well 200M despite not suited by the slow pace.
Eased to take box seat, enjoyed the slow sectionals, flattened 250M.
Pushed to take a midfield spot along the fence, 3Ls off the leaders, not suited by the slow tempo, held up 4-2, no turn of foot when clear.
Eased to rear and took rail, 7Ls off the leaders, harmed by the slow pace, dashed fairly.
Eased to rear, 7Ls off the leaders 3-4 wide, harmed by the slow pace, ran on ok in straight.
Hard ridden to take prominent spot, 1.5Ls off the leaders 2 wide, benefited by the slow pace, but soon emptied 300M.
Midfield, 2.5Ls off the leaders 3 wide, moved forward 800M, suited by the slow tempo, however weakened 350M.
Slow away, behind midfield, 4.5Ls off the leaders 2-3 wide, not suited by the slow pace, no progress.
Settled in a fence position in midfield, quickened well when clear 350 M out, ran on soundly, took the lead just before the line.
Settled 5Ls off the speed, swung widest for home, ran on strongly down the centre of the home straight, briefly led 100 M out, caught by the winner in the last few strides.
Prominently placed on rail just behind the leaders, held up for clear run early in the home straight, ran on well when clear 200 M out, kept on for 3rd.
Urged along to occupy a one-off spot just off the speed, responded well when asked for efforts 400 M out, ran to contest the lead, headed 100 M out, just missed a place.
Given a waiting ride and settled 7Ls off the pace at the rear, blocked early in the home straight, quickened well when clear 250 M, ran on soundly, too late.
Given a waiting ride as usual and travelled 6Ls behind the pace, made up gradual ground down the centre of the home straight, but lacked a decisive kick to challenge the principals.
Settled one-off in the mid-division, ran on to contest the lead early in the home straight, passed 100 M out, soon got tired.
Tracked the leader in the one-out-one-back spot, niggled along rounding the home turn, got tired 300 M out, crowded at 200 M, soon faded.
Crowded at start, urged along to lead 1L on rail, held ground until passed 250 M out, checked at 150 M, faded.
Raced on-pace but caught 3-wide with no over, got tired at the top of the home straight, dropped out. (Mucus.)
Patiently tracked leaders and always travelling well, surged to the lead with an impressive acceleration, lengthened away to win with some authority.
From outside barrier worked his way to share the lead just in time for the turn, had no chance with the winner but rallied on willingly to hold 2nd.
Began awkwardly, soon recovered to share the lead on the inside, headed 250M out and weakened steadily over final 100M.
Restrained in a rearward position 6Ls behind leaders, urged along passing 400M, stayed on well.
Placed in midfield after an awkward start, took inside route but was bumped and badly unbalanced 750M, placed under pressure near 500M, finished well.
Nudged along early stages to keep up with rivals, checked near 750M and shuffled back to the rear, progressed steadily to 100M then flattened.
Hard pushed early to stay in touch with the field, hampered near 750M and was 8Ls down leaving the bend, finished off the race soundly but was left with too much to do.
Raced keenly in 6th place about 3Ls behind leaders, made a short lived effort early straight and soon flattened out.
Not far off from leaders but had to be pushed along to maintain that position, outpaced by leaders turning for home and weakened passing 250M.
Held up in midfield, badly unbalanced and almost dislodged rider near 750M when bumped with a rival, never in contention after this incident. (Jockey reported his saddle shifted.)
Forwardly placed behind leading pair, came under pressure nearing 400M and had nothing left when asked for an effort, eased inside 300M.
Positioned 3-wide at the back, hampered near 750M and pushed wider, not picked up and eased final 300M.
Broke well, settled just off the pace on the standside, ran on to lead 400 M out, responded well when asked for efforts, kept on soundly to score.
Settled 2Ls off the speed, responded well when placed under pressure 400 M out, ran on soundly for 2nd.
Settled 2Ls behind the speed, quickened well when asked for efforts 400 M out, ran on soundly for 3rd.
Prominently placed just off the pace, quickened well when asked 400 M out, ran on to contest lead, couldn't find extra final 50 M, just missed a place.
Settled 3Ls off the speed on the stand rail, made up gradual ground final 250 M, too late.
Settled 3Ls off the pace, niggled along halfway, held up for clear run 400 M out, kicked strongly when clear 200 M out, too late.
Started awkwardly, prominently placed just off the pace on the standside, ran on to contest the lead 400 M out, headed near the 200 M pole, one-paced.
Settled 3Ls off the speed, niggled along halfway, made some late ground final 200 M, rather one-paced.
Slow to begin, urged along to catch up 4Ls off the speed, only one-paced when asked for efforts final 400 M.
Easily ran up to share the lead, got across towards to standside halfway, passed 350 M out, soon got tired.
Settled 2Ls off the pace, crowded at 600 M, blocked 400 M out, made up gradual ground when clear at 300 M, but couldn't find extra final 100 M.
Easily ran up to share the lead, got across towards to standside halfway, headed passing the 400 M pole, failed to keep on.
Prominently placed just off the pace, proved difficult to settle when restrained, checked at 800 M, on heels at 600 M, failed to quicken when asked, flattened 200 M out.
Settled 2Ls off the pace, proved difficult to settle in the early stages, on heels at 600 M, got tired near the 200 M pole, soon dropped out.
No early speed, ended up in midfield 4Ls back on rails, suited by easy run, tracked up nicely on bend, kept chasing to catch pace trio, held off fast finisher narrowly.
Drifted back to race in rear division, best part of 9Ls back at rear, unsuited by tempo, produced a remarkable finish from tail making many lengths to nearly snatch victory.
Took up nice spot 1 out 1 back, had all favours to bend, improved 3 wide at 400 M, kept finding despite hanging in, went down in 3 way go.
Out well and slotted in behind pace pair 2Ls away on rails, used little in mid-section, came 2 wide on bend and joined in at 400 M, led inside 200 M, missed place late.
Shared speed, worked to lead from widest gate, set a moderate speed to bend, kicked turning but overhauled inside 200 M, just held ground thereafter.
No speed from inside alley, ended up 7 to 8Ls back on rails, saved ground on rails throughout but pace against to turn, made some nice ground late.
Faded back as usual, 7Ls or so away, 2 wide behind midfield to bend, made some progress in straight without really threatening.
Posted wide in midfield from an awkward draw, pressed on but still 3 wide no cover on circle, niggled turning and couldn't find extra after hard run. Faded out in straight.
Standard jump, positioned behind midfield 5Ls back, used nothing in run, crept a little closer turning, made no progress and battled in straight.
Positive from a wide gate, took a trail on leader, slow pace suited, came 2 wide bend, soon under pressure and dropped out easily.
Settled in mid-division or so back in running line, no excuses to bend, gave in tamely in straight.
Faded back to be 7 to 8Ls away, 3 wide with cover, struggling approaching bend, dropped out in straight.
Drifted back, best part of 9 away, 3 wide at tail, checked at 1100 M, never got into it and beaten a long way out.
